NK118(se)002:1: // su b+ha shi t+aa sh+tsa r+ya ka lpa ma ny+dza
NK118(se)002:2: r+ai n+aa ma stri sa m+ba ra bi ni sh+tsa
NK118(se)002:3: ya bri t+ti bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK118(se)002:4: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa legs
NK118(se)002:5: bshad ngo mtshar dpag bsam gyi snye ma zhes bya
NK118(se)002:6: ba bzhugs so // sdom pa gsum rnam par nges
NK118(se)002:7: pa'i bstan bcos kyi 'grel pa legs bshad ngo mtshar
NK118(se)002:8: dpag bsam gyi snye ma zhes bya ba /
NK118(se)002:9: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi
NK118(se)002:10: bdag nyid dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i zhabs kyi
NK118(se)002:11: rdul dri ma med pa la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs
NK118(se)002:12: su mchi'o // gang sku'i gsang ba brtan g.yo kun
NK118(se)002:13: khyab gdul bya'i mos ngor cir yang 'char ba sprul
NK118(se)002:14: su mchi'o // pa'i sku // gsung gsang brjod bral
NK118(se)002:15: n+aa da'i rang bzhin mtha' dag 'gro ba'i sgra skad
NK118(se)002:17: thugs kyi gsang ba bde chen 'od gsal 'gyur ba mi mnga' dmigs pa kun bral chos kyi sku //
NK118(se)002:18: gsang gsum dbyer med ye shes rdo rje gter chen bla ma'i zhabs kyi pad+mora phyag bagyi'o //
NK118(se)002:19: sku gsum bdag nyid dag pa gnyis ldan don gnyis mthar phyin rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK118(se)002:20: don dam brjod bral rnam byang bden pa gsung rab rnam par ston pa'i chos //
NK118(se)002:21: rig grol gnyis ldan rgyal sras dge 'dun nyan rang 'phags pa gnyis dang bcas //
NK118(se)002:22: ma lus 'gro ba'i skyabs dang mgon gyur skyabs gnas dkon mchog gsum la 'dud //
NK118(se)002:23: rgyal kun mkhyen brtse nus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK118(se)002:24: bgrang yas dkyil 'khor 'khor lor rtag 'char yang //
NK118(se)002:25: zhing 'dir slob dpon tshul bzung theg mchog gi //
NK118(se)002:26: ston pa mtshungs med pad+ma ka ra rgyal //
NK118(se)002:27: tshul gnas byang chub sems kyi sa gzhi la //
NK118(se)002:28: smin grol bdud rtsi'i chu klung cher 'bab cing //
NK118(se)002:29: lung rigs rba rlabs g.yo bas lus can gyi //
NK118(se)002:30: gdung sel bshes gnyen tshogs kun phyag gi gnas //
NK118(se)002:31: khyad par lnga rig mkhyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rgyas //
NK118(se)002:32: 'chad rtsol rtsom pa'i 'od stong 'phro ba can //
NK118(se)002:33: thub bstan yangs pa'i mkhas la rtag 'char ba //
NK118(se)002:34: pan chen pad+ma dbang gi rgyal pos skyongs //
NK118(se)002:35: mdo rgyud bstan pa'i nyams len sdom pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:36: rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa legs bshad kyi //
NK118(se)002:37: rtsa brtan ngo mtshar phan bde'i 'bras smin pa'i //
NK118(se)002:38: lha yi dpag bsam snye ma deng 'dir 'khrungs //
NK118(se)002:39: gang 'di mang thos lung rig lde mig gis //
NK118(se)002:40: mdo sngags grub matha'i sgo brgya rab phye nas //
NK118(se)002:41: thar mchog rin chen khang par 'jug 'dod la //
NK118(se)002:42: shing rta'i lam srol dabye'o dga' bas nyon //
NK118(se)002:43: zhes mchod par brjod cing rtsom par dam bca' ba sngon du btang nas /
NK118(se)002:44: 'dir ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:45: bcom ldan 'das thabs mkhas la thugs rje tshad med
NK118(se)002:46: pa dang ldan pa 'dis bskal pa dpag tu med
NK118(se)002:47: pa'i sngon rol du mngon par sangs rgyas nas de
NK118(se)002:48: bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par rol pa tshad med pa'i
NK118(se)002:50: 'gro ba rnams ji ltar 'tshams pas 'dul ba'i don
NK118(se)002:51: bsam gyis mi khyab pa rgyun chad med cing lhun
NK118(se)002:52: gyis grub par mdzad pa las /
NK118(se)002:53: zhing khams 'di'i gdul bya las brtsams te /
NK118(se)002:54: slar yang 'tshang rgya ba'i tshul bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:55: chos phung brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang bsdu na /
NK118(se)002:58: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi go 'phang la sems can rnams 'god pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:59: nyan thos kyi don du gsungs pa theg dman gyi sde snod gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:60: byang sems kyi don du gsungs pa theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa'i sde snod gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:61: rgyu'i theg pa'i sde snod gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:62: thun min rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod dang bzhir 'du ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:64: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni /
NK118(se)002:65: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK118(se)002:66: zhe sdang 'dul mdo sde'i gti mug mngon pa'i thams
NK118(se)002:67: cad 'dul ba'i sde snod bzhi pa zhes 'byung zhing
NK118(se)002:68: / de bzhi'i nyams su blang bya thams cad kyang /
NK118(se)002:69: sdom pa gsum gyi nyams len gyi khongs su 'du ste /
NK118(se)002:70: 'di ltar nyan thos kyi 'dul ba dang thun mong pa'i bstan pa'i nyams len so thar du dang /
NK118(se)002:71: theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa dang thun mong ba'i bstan pa'i nyams len byang sdom du dang /
NK118(se)002:72: rdo rje theg pa thun mong ma yin pa'i bstan
NK118(se)002:73: pa'i nyams len rig 'dzin sngags kyi sdom pa'i nang
NK118(se)002:75: de bas na sdom pa gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:76: de'i bslab bya la rdzogs par slob pa'i khongs su
NK118(se)002:77: mdo sngags kyi bstan pa mtha' dag gi nyams su
NK118(se)002:78: blang bya ma lus pa yongs su tshang bar gzigs
NK118(se)002:79: nas / bdag nyid chen po sa skya pan+di ta
NK118(se)002:80: sogs mkhas mchog mang pos kyang sdom pa gsum gyi
NK118(se)002:81: rnam gzhag lung dang mthun cing rigs pas grub pa'i
NK118(se)002:82: bstan bcos kyis bstan pa gsal bar mdzad la /
NK118(se)002:83: khyad par 'dir rje btsun 'jam dpal dbyangs chos kyi
NK118(se)002:84: rgyal po'i tshul bzung ba mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u
NK118(se)002:85: btsan zhes kha ba can gyi ljongs 'dir thub bstan
NK118(se)002:86: gsar du 'dren pa'i shing rta pa chen po de
NK118(se)002:88: bstan pa la zhugs pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i rten dge slong rdo rjee 'dzin pa /
NK118(se)002:89: spyir mdo sngags rig gnas dang bcas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:90: khyad par snga 'gyur bka' gter rgya mtsho'i pha rol tu gshegs pa'i mkhas pa chen po //
NK118(se)002:91: las 'phro bzang pos rang gter gyi bka' babs shing /
NK118(se)002:92: mdor na thos bsam sgom gsum mthar phyin pas rang rgyud grol nas /
NK118(se)002:93: gzhan don 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i phrin las la dbang
NK118(se)002:94: 'byor ba mnga' ris glo bo'i pan+di ta chen po
NK118(se)002:95: pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje grags pa rgyal mtshan dpal
NK118(se)002:96: bzang po zhes rig pa dang grol ba'i spobs pa
NK118(se)002:97: mchog tu dge ba gang gi zhal snga nas sdom
NK118(se)002:98: pa gsum gyi bstan bcos legs bshad rmad du byung
NK118(se)002:100: de rang gi gcung rig 'dzin rje nas /
NK118(se)002:103: gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub kyi bar rim par brgyud nas /
NK118(se)002:104: de la bdag cag gi rtsa ba'i bla ma shes
NK118(se)002:105: bya thams cad mkhyen cing rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK118(se)002:106: gyis dngos grub brnyes pas yang dag pa'i lam gyi
NK118(se)002:107: sa mkhan mtshan brjod par dka' ba gter chen chos
NK118(se)002:108: kyi rgyal pos gsan pa ni lung gi brgyud pa
NK118(se)002:109: yin la / sdom pa gsum so so'i brgyud pa'i rim pa ni /
NK118(se)002:110: rang rang gi skabs de dang der 'chad par 'gyur ba las shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:111: des na 'dir gang bshad par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK118(se)002:112: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i bstan bcos 'adi'o //
NK118(se)002:113: de ji ltar 'chad pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:115: mtshan de ldan gyi bstan bcos dngos /
NK118(se)002:116: bstan bcos ji ltar brtsams pa'i mdzad byang ngo //
NK118(se)002:118: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK118(se)002:119: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa zhes bya ba'i
NK118(se)002:120: bstan bcos / zhes glegs bam gyi zhal byang du smos te /
NK118(se)002:121: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK118(se)002:122: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa ste /
NK118(se)002:123: de gtan la 'bebs pa'i lam tshang la ma nor
NK118(se)002:124: ba ni gsang chen bla na med pa a ti
NK118(se)002:125: yo ga'i theg pa yin cing /
NK118(se)002:126: der ma zad 'di'i lam stegs su gyur pa'i a
NK118(se)002:127: nu sogs mdo sngags kyi theg pa ji snyed pa
NK118(se)002:128: thams cad kyang / dngos brgyud gang rung gi sgo nas de nyid rtogs byed du 'gro ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:129: rgyal ba'i bstan pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha rkyen yin pa'i gnad kyis /
NK118(se)002:130: de thams cad kyi nyams su blang bya'i rtsa ba'am
NK118(se)002:131: snying po sdom pa gsum gyi nyams len kyang der
NK118(se)002:132: 'gyur zhing / sdom pa gsum ni rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK118(se)002:133: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:136: de gsum gyi don sgro skur dang bral bar gtan la phab pas na rnam par nges pa'o //
NK118(se)002:138: 'dir rtsom pa po rnam g.yeng med pa'i yid can
NK118(se)002:139: gyis thar pa thob pa'i thabs su bka'i don bshad
NK118(se)002:140: pa'i ngag yin pas na de skad ces bya'o //
NK118(se)002:142: bshad pa la 'jug pa'i yan lag /
NK118(se)002:143: bshad pa rang gi ngo bo /
NK118(se)002:144: bshad pa rdzogs pa'i bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:149: thor mar sdom pa gsum gyi bka' drin rtsol ba'i bla ma la phyag mdzad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:154: gu ru'i sgra lci ba la 'jug pas yon tan gyi khur gyis lci ba'i phyir bla ma'o //
NK118(se)002:155: gang dag bla ma zhes gsang sngags pa la grags kyi /
NK118(se)002:156: so byang las de 'dra'i tha snyad bshad pa med do snyam na /
NK118(se)002:158: dge tshul gyi ka ri k+aa lnga bcu pa las /
NK118(se)002:159: bla ma gnas pa'i sgo glegs la //
NK118(se)002:160: lag pas dal gyis brdung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:163: bla ma sdom la gnas shing mkhas //
NK118(se)002:164: nus dang ldan las blang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:166: gnyis pa sku tshe 'dir chos thams cad thugs su
NK118(se)002:167: chud pa ni sngon rabs du mar slob dpon chen
NK118(se)002:168: po pad+mas rjes su bzung nas thugs rgyud byin gyis
NK118(se)002:169: brlabs pa'i mthu las byung bar mkhyen cing /
NK118(se)002:170: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu lung ston pa po'ang yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:171: de la phyag mdzad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:172: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis chu gter bsrubs pa las //
NK118(se)002:173: mkhyen brtse'i 'od dkar nges gsang gru char 'bebs //
NK118(se)002:174: gangs can mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan mchog /
NK118(se)002:175: mtsho skyes rdo rje 'gro ba'i bla mar 'dud //
NK118(se)002:177: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:178: dpal dang ldan pa de las shes bya thams cad
NK118(se)002:179: la chags thogs med pa'i mkhyen rab dang /
NK118(se)002:180: dmigs pa med pa'i brtse ba thugs rje chen po rtsol med du 'byung zhing /
NK118(se)002:181: des gdul bya rnams nges don gsang ba bla na
NK118(se)002:182: med pa'i lam dang 'bras bur bkri nus pa'i phrin
NK118(se)002:184: de dag gi dpe sngon rgya mtsho bsrubs pa las zla ba 'thon pa'i rig byed kyi gtam dang /
NK118(se)002:185: zla 'od bsil ba'i rang bzhin gyis tsha gdung sel
NK118(se)002:186: ba'i byed las dang ldan pas gru char gyi ngo
NK118(se)002:187: bor sbyar te gzugs can gyi rgyan du mdzad cing
NK118(se)002:188: / slob dpon nyid kyi khyad par gyi gdul zhing
NK118(se)002:189: yin pa'i dbang du mdzad nas gangs can zhes dmigs
NK118(se)002:190: / kyis bkar na'ang / don la de bzhin gshegs
NK118(se)002:191: pa thams cad kyi gsung rdo rje rnam pa slob
NK118(se)002:193: 'dzam gling na che ba'i rig sngags 'chang chen po /
NK118(se)002:194: rgyal ba'i bstan pa la ston pa gnyis pa lta bu yin pas na /
NK118(se)002:195: sa'i steng gi mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan mchog tu bsten par 'os shing /
NK118(se)002:196: gdul bya rnams rang skal bzhin phan bde la 'god par mdzad pas 'gro ba'i bla ma ste /
NK118(se)002:197: de lta bu'i yon tan dang ldan pa'i slob dpon
NK118(se)002:198: mtsho skyes rdo rje'i zhabs la rtsom pa po mngon
NK118(se)002:199: par dang bas 'dud do zhes sgo gsum mchog tu
NK118(se)002:200: gus pas phyag mdzad pa ni kun rdzob kyi phyag
NK118(se)002:201: dang / yul dang yul can gnyis med du rtogs
NK118(se)002:202: pa ni don dam lta ba mjal ba'i phyag go
NK118(se)002:203: dang / // dgos pa ni tshogs rdzogs pas bar gcod zhi nas brtsams pa mthar phyin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:204: 'di la thos bsam byed pa rnams kyang yul dang
NK118(se)002:205: bstan bcos mchog tu rig nas gus pas 'jug pa'i
NK118(se)002:208: bsod nams ldan pa'i mi yi bsam pa rnams kyang 'grub //
NK118(se)002:211: bstan bcos byed pos ston pa la //
NK118(se)002:212: mchod par brjod pa 'bras med min //
NK118(se)002:213: ston pa dang ni bstan bcos la //
NK118(se)002:214: dad 'dun bskyed par bya phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:217: 'gro blo'i dri ma 'khrud mkhas drang srong gis //
NK118(se)002:218: blo gros beed+aura bum bzang rab thogs nas //
NK118(se)002:219: legs bshad sdom gsum bdud rtsi'i chu sbyin gyi //
NK118(se)002:220: don gnyer skye bo'i tshogs rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK118(se)002:222: 'gro blo'i mi shes rmongs pa'i dri ma rnams 'khrud
NK118(se)002:223: pa la mkhas pa'i rtsom pa po rang nyid gang
NK118(se)002:224: 'jig rten na yon tan dang ldan par grags pa
NK118(se)002:226: gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i tshig don phyin
NK118(se)002:227: ci ma log par rtogs pa'i blo gros ni des
NK118(se)002:228: lag tu thogs pa'i beed+aur+ya'i bum pa lta bu dang
NK118(se)002:229: / gang rtsom rgyu'i legs bshad sdom pa gsum gyi
NK118(se)002:230: bstan bcos 'di ni 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi nad
NK118(se)002:231: 'joms pa la snod der blugs pa'i sman mchog bdud
NK118(se)002:232: rtsi'i chu rgyun dang 'dra ba'i dpe sbyar te /
NK118(se)002:233: de dang de'i gzugs su bkod cing /
NK118(se)002:234: de bas na thar pa don gnyer gyi blo dang
NK118(se)002:235: ldan pa'i skal bzang skye bo'i tshogs rnams la kho
NK118(se)002:237: dga' zhing spro ba dang bcas pas 'dir 'dus la longs spyod ces bskul ba'o //
NK118(se)002:238: 'dis bstan bcos 'di'i dgos sogs chos bzhi legs par bstan te /
NK118(se)002:239: sdom pa gsum ni brjod bya /
NK118(se)002:240: de rjod byed kyi legs bshad 'di las legs par
NK118(se)002:241: rtogs te thar pa'i lam la zhugs pa ni dgos
NK118(se)002:242: pa / zhugs pa mthar phyin pas byang chub 'grub pa ni nying dgos /
NK118(se)002:243: de dag kyang gcig la brten nas gcig 'byung bas 'brel ba can du grub pa ni 'brel ba'o //
NK118(se)002:244: gnyis pa bshad pa rang gi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:245: spyi'i bshad gzhi rim par phye ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan /
NK118(se)002:246: sdom gsum so so'i rang bzhin dang bslab bya bstan pa'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad /
NK118(se)002:247: de gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud la 'gal med
NK118(se)002:248: du nyams su len tshul gyi mtha' dpyad pas don
NK118(se)002:249: bsdu pa'o // dang po la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:250: shes thob kyi dmigs par bya ba'i yul sbyang gzhi
NK118(se)002:251: khams dang bral 'bras mthar thug gi 'bras bu ngos
NK118(se)002:252: bzung / sgrub byed lam gyi dbye ba spyir bshad /
NK118(se)002:253: theg pa thams cad kyi lam gyi gnad sdom pa
NK118(se)002:254: gsum gyi nyams len du bsdus pa'i 'brel gyis khog
NK118(se)002:256: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes spyi yi gzugs //
NK118(se)002:257: yongs su dag sku rdo rje 'chang chen po //
NK118(se)002:258: 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas nyag gcig de //
NK118(se)002:260: rkang pa dang po gnyis 'jam dpal zhal lung gi tshig 'dir drangs par snang bas /
NK118(se)002:261: bi t+aa pa da'i 'grel par rdzogs pa chen po
NK118(se)002:262: zhes pa rim pa gnyis pa'i rim pa gnyis pa
NK118(se)002:263: la bshad mod / 'dir rkang pa dang pos gzhi 'bras thun mong dang /
NK118(se)002:264: phyi ma gnyis kyis 'bras bu ston pa'i gzhung du bkral na 'chad bde bar snang ngo //
NK118(se)002:267: spyir bstan bcos rnams su rigs zhes grags pa la
NK118(se)002:268: grub matha'i bye brag gis 'dod pa mi 'dra ba
NK118(se)002:270: 'dir ltar bye brag tu smra ba ni /
NK118(se)002:271: srid pa dang srid pa'i yo byad la ma chags
NK118(se)002:272: pa'i sems byung chog shes pa la 'phags pa'i rigs
NK118(se)002:274: sems kyi sa bon zag med kyi ye shes 'byung rung gi nus pa la 'dod /
NK118(se)002:276: thog ma med pa nas sems rgyud la gnas pa'i
NK118(se)002:277: zag med kyi chos skyed par byed pa'i nus pa
NK118(se)002:278: chos nyid kyi thob pa la 'dod /
NK118(se)002:279: de thams cad 'dus byas te dngos por smra ba'i lugs so //
NK118(se)002:281: dri bcas chos nyid de bzhin nyid la rigs su 'dod par phal cher mthun kyang /
NK118(se)002:282: ngos 'dzin lugs mi 'dra ba mang du snang mod /
NK118(se)002:283: 'dir theg chen thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK118(se)002:284: sems nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa /
NK118(se)002:285: stong gsal 'gag med kun khyab kyi ngo bor 'pho
NK118(se)002:286: 'gyur med par gnas pa ni khams bde bar gshegs
NK118(se)002:289: dag pa dwangs pa 'od gsal ba //
NK118(se)002:291: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK118(se)002:292: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK118(se)002:294: snying po de yang rgyud bla mar //
NK118(se)002:295: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:296: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:297: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK118(se)002:298: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK118(se)002:299: zhes rgyu mtshan gsum gyi sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po can du bstan /
NK118(se)002:300: ngo bo rgyu 'bras las ldan 'jug pa dang //
NK118(se)002:301: gnas skabs de bzhin kun tu 'gro ba dang //
NK118(se)002:302: rtag tu mi 'gyur yon tan dbyer med pa'i //
NK118(se)002:303: don dam dbyings kyi dgongs don yin zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:304: zhes rnam gzhag bcus snying po'i don gtan la phab /
NK118(se)002:305: nyon mongs sbubs nang gnas pa de //
NK118(se)002:306: dpe dag gis ni shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:307: zhes dri mas bsgribs tshul dpe dgu'i sgo nas rgyas par bstan cing /
NK118(se)002:308: de nyid gsang sngags rdo rje theg par gzhi rgyud
NK118(se)002:309: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes grags
NK118(se)002:310: te / mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen dang rnam pa
NK118(se)002:311: kun ldan gyi stong nyid dbyer mi phyed pa'i sems
NK118(se)002:312: nyid ye nas sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i dkyil
NK118(se)002:313: 'khor chen por lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs
NK118(se)002:314: pas na rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK118(se)002:315: de nyid srid zhi kun khyab kyi ye shes yin
NK118(se)002:316: pas na ye shes thams cad kyi spyi gzugs so
NK118(se)002:318: rang byung ye shes byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:319: byang chub snying po 'dus ma byas //
NK118(se)002:320: kun rdzogs yon tan 'bar bas brgyan //
NK118(se)002:321: lhun grub dkyil 'khor bla med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:324: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK118(se)002:325: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK118(se)002:328: ye nas mngon rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK118(se)002:329: lus can kun la gnas pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:330: lhun grub rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK118(se)002:331: lus can kun gyi lus la gnas /
NK118(se)002:334: rnam rtog kun gzhi ma yin pa //
NK118(se)002:335: rang bzhin med pa don gyi gzhi //
NK118(se)002:336: de ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:337: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK118(se)002:340: gzhi gnas rig pa ngo bor rang bzhin dang //
NK118(se)002:341: thugs rje gsum ste rgyal ba'i snying po la //
NK118(se)002:342: sku gsum rang chas bzhugs par bshad pa yin //
NK118(se)002:344: snying po de la rten dang brten pa'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK118(se)002:346: rang bzhin dang ni rgyas pa dag /
NK118(se)002:347: de ni rten dang brten pa dang //
NK118(se)002:348: yod med nyid dang yon tan ni //
NK118(se)002:349: sgrol ba'i don du shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:350: zhes pas dbyings stong pa nyid kyi cha ni chos sku ngo bo nyid sku'i bral rgyu ste /
NK118(se)002:351: rin po che'i gter dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur
NK118(se)002:352: pa ltar sku dang ye shes 'char ba'i go 'byed
NK118(se)002:353: pas na rang bzhin gnas rigs dang /
NK118(se)002:354: de las shar ba'i ye shes snang ba'i cha ni gzugs sku gnyis kyi bral rgyu ste /
NK118(se)002:355: 'bras bu can gyi ljon shing gong 'phel ltar rkyen
NK118(se)002:356: sgrib pa bral stobs kyis rang la yod pa'i yon
NK118(se)002:357: tan mngon du 'gyur nges pas rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs
NK118(se)002:358: so // de ltar yang rgyud blar /
NK118(se)002:359: gter dang 'bras bu'i shing bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:360: rigs de rnam gnyis shes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:361: thog med rang bzhin gnas pa dang //
NK118(se)002:362: yang dag blangs pa mchog nyid do //
NK118(se)002:363: rigs 'di gnyis las sangs rgyas kyi //
NK118(se)002:364: sku gsum thob par 'dod pa yin //
NK118(se)002:365: dang pos sku ni dang po ste //
NK118(se)002:366: gnyis pa yis ni phyi ma gnyis //
NK118(se)002:368: gnas skabs kyi sgo nas dbye na /
NK118(se)002:369: chos nyid ris med kun khyab yin pas rang ngos nas dbye ba byar med kyang /
NK118(se)002:370: de rgyud ldan gyi gang zag ma dag pa dang /
NK118(se)002:372: shin tu rnam dag gi gnas skabs gsum la ltos nas ming gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:373: ma dag ma dag dag pa dang //
NK118(se)002:374: shin tu rnam dag go rim bzhin //
NK118(se)002:375: sems can byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK118(se)002:376: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod do //
NK118(se)002:378: de bzhin du dbyings kyi ngo bo la bzang ngan med kyang /
NK118(se)002:379: sad tshul la ltos nas theg pa gsum gyi rigs dang /
NK118(se)002:380: rnam par dag pa'i cha shas rtogs pa'i rim pa
NK118(se)002:381: la ltos nas 'phags bzhi'i gang zag rnams kyi rab
NK118(se)002:383: snod bzang ngan du snang yang nang gi nam mkha' la bzang ngan med pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:385: gzugs kyi rnam pa dman pa dang //
NK118(se)002:386: bar ma mchog la nam mkha' bzhin //
NK118(se)002:388: de ltar sbyang gzhi khams mdo tsam bshad nas /
NK118(se)002:389: phyogs gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'chad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:391: ji ltar bum nang mar me ni //
NK118(se)002:392: phyo rol kun tu mi snang ltar //
NK118(se)002:393: de bzhin chos kyi dbyings 'di yang //
NK118(se)002:395: bum pa de nyid bcag gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:396: thams cad kun tu snang ba ltar //
NK118(se)002:397: gang tshe ting 'dzin rdo rje yis //
NK118(se)002:398: sgrib pa kun tu bcom gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:399: de tshe nam mkha'i mthar thug gsal //
NK118(se)002:400: zhes pa ltar sbyang gzhi chos nyid kyi mdangs 'od
NK118(se)002:401: sbyang bya'i dri ma 'khor ba'i chos dang 'dzom pa
NK118(se)002:402: las sbyong byed lam gyi rnam par shar nas des
NK118(se)002:403: sbyang bya'i dri ma sbyong ba'i gnyen por 'gro ba
NK118(se)002:404: yin pas / 'dir mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:405: sdom pa gsum gyi lam gyi snying po rig pa
NK118(se)002:406: 'dzin pa sngags kyi lam smin grol gnyis kyis khams
NK118(se)002:407: kyi dri ma sbyangs pas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin
NK118(se)002:408: mngon du gyur pa mthar thug pa na 'bras bu'i
NK118(se)002:409: mchog yongs su rdzogs pa ni /
NK118(se)002:410: chen po gsum gyi mtshan nyid can te /
NK118(se)002:411: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa yongs su dag pa'i sku ni spong ba chen po /
NK118(se)002:412: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa sal ler gzigs pa'i ye shes ni rtogs pa chen po /
NK118(se)002:413: de'i mthus 'gro ba mtha' dag gi don rtag khyab
NK118(se)002:414: lhun grub tu mdzad pa ni sems chen po ste
NK118(se)002:416: sems can kun mchog nyid sems dang //
NK118(se)002:417: spong dang rtogs dang gsum po la //
NK118(se)002:418: chen po gsum gyi rang 'byung gi //
NK118(se)002:419: ched du bya ba 'di shes bya //
NK118(se)002:421: de ltar gyur pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi
NK118(se)002:422: gzugs sku gsum dang ye shes lnga dbyer mi phyed
NK118(se)002:423: pa'i bdag nyid rdo rje 'chang chen po'o //
NK118(se)002:425: chos thams cad mtshan ma med par thugs su chud
NK118(se)002:426: pas spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes
NK118(se)002:427: rang bzhin rnam dag mngon du gyur pa'i cha ni
NK118(se)002:428: chos kyi sku / de glo bur rnam dag mthar
NK118(se)002:429: thug pas khyad par du byas pa na shin tu
NK118(se)002:430: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyis chos thams cad
NK118(se)002:431: dag pa'i snang ba rab 'byams su gzigs pa'i cha
NK118(se)002:432: ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK118(se)002:433: de la mnga' ba'i yon tan gdul bya gzhan snang
NK118(se)002:434: du sku dang mdzad pa'i rnam rol ston nus pa'i
NK118(se)002:435: thugs rje dang nus mthu'i ye shes kyi cha ni
NK118(se)002:437: rang rgyud kyis sdus pa'i sku gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:438: ye shes de gnyis gdul bya'i sems dag pa dang smon lam gyi rkyen nye bar 'dzom pa las /
NK118(se)002:439: gzhan snang gi longs sprul gnyis chu zla'i gzugs brnyan ltar 'char ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:441: ji ltar beed+aura sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK118(se)002:442: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK118(se)002:443: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK118(se)002:444: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK118(se)002:447: shin tu rnam par dag pa spros bral gyi ye shes ni chos dbyings ye shes /
NK118(se)002:448: des chos thams cad gsal la mi rtog par gzigs pa'i cha ni me long ye shes /
NK118(se)002:449: de ltar gzigs pa'i chos thams cad mnyam par rtogs pa ni mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK118(se)002:450: ngo bo stong pa nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK118(se)002:451: chos can thams cad ma 'dres par mkhyen pa ni
NK118(se)002:453: sems can thams cad la mnyam par 'jug pa'i dmigs
NK118(se)002:454: med kyi thugs rje chen po ni 'gro don mdzad
NK118(se)002:455: pa la thogs pa med pa'i phyir bya grub ye
NK118(se)002:456: shes so // de bas na bla na med pa'i
NK118(se)002:457: byang chub don du gnyer ba rnams bsam pa yongs
NK118(se)002:458: su rdzos pas 'bras bu'i mthar thug tu nges pa
NK118(se)002:459: ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyag gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:460: de ni 'chad 'gyur ltar gsang sngags bla med kho na'i lam gyis bsgrub dgos pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:462: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam ngos bzung /
NK118(se)002:463: rnam grol gyi lam thams cad theg dgur 'du tshul bshad /
NK118(se)002:464: rigs can gsum so sor sngags kyi lam zhugs yod par sgrub /
NK118(se)002:465: blo khyad kyis sngags lam du 'jug sgo mi 'dra
NK118(se)002:466: ba mang yang 'dir bshad bya min par bstan pa'o
NK118(se)002:468: sngags lam nyid ma brten par mthar thug gi 'bras bu de mi thob par bstan /
NK118(se)002:469: theg pa gzhan thams cad de'i lam stegs su 'gro tshul bshad /
NK118(se)002:470: des sngags lam bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam yin par grub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:472: zab rgyas chos kyi sgo 'phar bgrang yas kyang //
NK118(se)002:473: gsang chen smin grol lam mchog ma bsten par //
NK118(se)002:474: thob pa min zhes rdzogs sangs rgyas des gsungs //
NK118(se)002:476: zab pa ji lta ba dang /
NK118(se)002:477: rgyas pa ji snyed pa'i don ston pa'i chos sgo bgrang ba las 'das pa dag snang yang /
NK118(se)002:478: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de
NK118(se)002:479: gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i smin grol gyi lam
NK118(se)002:480: mchog ma bsten par thob pa min te /
NK118(se)002:481: ci'i phyir na 'khor bar 'ching byed kyi kun rtog phra ba spangs pa tsam du ma zad /
NK118(se)002:482: klu byang gi las mtha' rnam 'byed las /
NK118(se)002:483: mgo dang rkang lag sogs byin kyang //
NK118(se)002:484: snang ba rnam par ma dag phyir //
NK118(se)002:486: zhes gsungs pa ltar snang gsum mam 'pho ba'i sgrib pa yang ma lus par spang dgos na /
NK118(se)002:487: de spong byed kyi lam pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg par ma bshad pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:489: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK118(se)002:490: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK118(se)002:491: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK118(se)002:492: bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:495: ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa ma zad par //
NK118(se)002:496: bsam yas theg pa'i grangs mthar thug pa med //
NK118(se)002:497: bgrod gcig lam la bkri ba'i ngal stegs te //
NK118(se)002:498: rang rang rjes mthun 'bras bu bla dang bcas //
NK118(se)002:501: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK118(se)002:502: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK118(se)002:503: ces gnas skabs theg pa du ma'i rnam gzhag mdzad kyang /
NK118(se)002:504: re zhig de dang des 'dul ba'i gdul bya drang ba'i thabs su bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:505: de dag mthar sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bgrod pa
NK118(se)002:506: gcig pa'i lam rdo rje theg pa mchog la bkri
NK118(se)002:507: ba'i ngal stegs tsam du gsungs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:508: lam stegs kyi theg pa de rnams kyis rang rang
NK118(se)002:509: dang rjes mthun gyi 'bras bu re thob tu zin
NK118(se)002:510: kyang / des go mi chod par da dung bla ste gong du bgrod bya dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:511: de ltar yang snying po las /
NK118(se)002:512: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK118(se)002:513: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK118(se)002:516: drang srong rnams kyis theg pa gsum bstan pa //
NK118(se)002:517: rnam 'dren rnams kyis thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK118(se)002:518: theg pa gcig ste gnyis su yod ma yin //
NK118(se)002:519: bsti ba'i don du theg pa gsum bstan no //
NK118(se)002:520: zhes pa dang tshul 'dra zhing bsti ba'i don ni /
NK118(se)002:522: srid pa'i lam gyis dub pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:523: ngal bso'i don te de nyid min //
NK118(se)002:524: zhes pa ltar re zhig ngal bso ba'i don no //
NK118(se)002:526: thob kyang theg pa so so'i nges 'byung las //
NK118(se)002:527: theg gcig lam la ma zhugs 'bras thob ci //
NK118(se)002:529: nyan rang byang sems kri yog gi theg pa so
NK118(se)002:530: sos rang rang gi mi mthun phyogs 'khor ba dang
NK118(se)002:531: mtha' gnyis sogs las nges par 'byung ba'i myang 'das
NK118(se)002:533: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i theg pa gcig pur da dung 'jug dgos te /
NK118(se)002:534: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sngags kyi theg mchog las 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:535: de bas na der ma zhugs par mthar thug gi
NK118(se)002:536: 'bras bu thob pa ci zhig yod de med do
NK118(se)002:537: // de ltar yang 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa las /
NK118(se)002:538: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK118(se)002:539: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK118(se)002:541: don dam bsnyen pa las kyang /
NK118(se)002:542: nyan thos theg pa nyid ni theg pa ma yin te //
NK118(se)002:543: rang rgyal 'di ltar rgyal ba'i sa ni min par gsungs //
NK118(se)002:544: dpal ldan rdo rje theg pa rgyal ba'i theg pa nyid //
NK118(se)002:545: de yang gnyis las theg pa bar dang tha mar byed //
NK118(se)002:546: de phyir bla na med pa'i theg pa bor nas ni //
NK118(se)002:547: 'dod pa'i bla med byang chub thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:550: 'dir ni rdzogs pa chen po'i ring lugs ltar //
NK118(se)002:551: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK118(se)002:552: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa gsum zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)002:553: kri ya u pa yo ga phyi rgyud gsum //
NK118(se)002:554: bla med pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang //
NK118(se)002:555: ma rgyud a nu yo gar grags pa dang //
NK118(se)002:556: gnyis med rgyud sde a ti yo ga la //
NK118(se)002:557: nang rgyud gsum zhes theg pa rim dgur bsdu //
NK118(se)002:559: spyir ya na'i sgra las theg pa zhes bya ba bzhon pa la 'jug pas /
NK118(se)002:560: 'dir lam gong nas gong du bgrod par byed pas /
NK118(se)002:561: de dang 'dra ba'i phyir theg pa'o //
NK118(se)002:562: de la theg pa rim pa dgu zhes grags kyang /
NK118(se)002:563: chos tha dad pa'i rim pa dgu yod pa ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:564: nyan rang gi theg pas dngos su lam dang 'bras bu thar pa'i cha shas tsam las /
NK118(se)002:565: rnam grol gyi lam 'bras rdzogs par ma bstan cing /
NK118(se)002:566: rang 'bras mthar phyin nas kyang theg chen la 'jug
NK118(se)002:567: dgos pas rang skya ma thub pa'i phyir theg chen
NK118(se)002:568: du 'du la / theg chen pha rol tu phyin
NK118(se)002:569: pa dang sngags phyi rgyud gsum du mthar thug gi
NK118(se)002:571: der bgrod byed kyi lam rdzogs par ma bstan cing /
NK118(se)002:572: sngags bla med kyi theg pas ni yongs rdzogs bstan pas 'phags par ma zad /
NK118(se)002:573: yo ga man chad kyi rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg
NK118(se)002:574: pa'i lam dang 'bras bu'i rnam pa thams cad sngags
NK118(se)002:576: bla med kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i khyad chos rnams de dag la med cing /
NK118(se)002:577: de dang de'i dod thub kyang bzhag tu med pa'i
NK118(se)002:578: don gyis nang pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi nang du
NK118(se)002:582: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK118(se)002:583: gsum du nges par snang ba ste //
NK118(se)002:585: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK118(se)002:586: zhes pa ltar gsum gyi re re la'ang gsum gsum du phye bas dagu'o //
NK118(se)002:587: dang po kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:589: chos bdag bzung 'dzin don dam du gtan la phab nas /
NK118(se)002:590: rang nyid zhi bde'i bsam pas /
NK118(se)002:591: so thar rigs brgyad gang rung gi tshul khrims blangs te nyes spyod spong zhing /
NK118(se)002:592: ting nge 'dzin gyis sems las rung du bsgrubs te /
NK118(se)002:593: bden bzhi rnam pa bcu drug sgom pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK118(se)002:594: 'bras bu rgyun du zhugs pa nas dgra bcom pa nyid kyi bar sgrub par byed do //
NK118(se)002:596: shes pa skad cig don dam du blta zhing /
NK118(se)002:597: bden bzhi rnam pa bcu drug nyan thos dang 'dra
NK118(se)002:598: ba'i steng du rten 'brel zab mo'i lam bsnan te
NK118(se)002:599: bsgoms pas / 'bras bu rang rgyal dgra bcom thob nas /
NK118(se)002:600: lus kyi rnam rig gis chos ston par mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:602: chos thams cad bdag med par gtan la phab nas /
NK118(se)002:604: phar phyin bcu dang bsdu dngos bzhi la spyod cing /
NK118(se)002:605: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis slob
NK118(se)002:606: lam du byang chub kyi phyogs chos so bdun bsgoms
NK118(se)002:607: pas / 'bras bu mi slob pa'i lam kun tu 'od kyi sa brnyes par 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:608: de gsum gyis 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i lam mtshon par byed pas mtshan nyid dang /
NK118(se)002:609: mthar thug sngags kyi myang 'das zung 'jug gi ye shes la ltos te /
NK118(se)002:610: de'i rgyu'i ched tsam du sbyor ba'i lam yin pas rgyu dang /
NK118(se)002:611: nang gses kyi dbye bas theg pa gsum zhes bya'o //
NK118(se)002:612: gnyis pa dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:613: kri ya ste bya rgyud du /
NK118(se)002:614: chu dang cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:615: bdag gi de kho na nyid don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par rtogs nas /
NK118(se)002:616: lha'i de kho na nyid lha drug gi sgo nas
NK118(se)002:617: bdag dam tshig par bskyed pa'i mdun du ye shes
NK118(se)002:618: pa spyan drangs te rje khol gyi tshul du bltas
NK118(se)002:619: la / sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol ba bzlas brjod kyi de nyid dang /
NK118(se)002:620: me gnas sgra gnas sgra matha'i de nyid gsum gyi bsam gtan sgom zhing /
NK118(se)002:621: khrus dang gtsang sbra la gtso bor spyad pas /
NK118(se)002:622: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:623: u pa ya ste spyod rgyud du /
NK118(se)002:624: chu dang cod pan gyi steng phyag mtshan dang ming dbang yang bskur nas /
NK118(se)002:626: spyod pa kri ya ltar spyod cing //
NK118(se)002:627: sgom pa rang nyid dam tshig par bskyed pa'i mdun
NK118(se)002:628: du lha ye shes pa spun nam grogs po'i tshul
NK118(se)002:629: du bltas nas / bzlas pa dang ting nge 'dzin brtan par byas pas /
NK118(se)002:630: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:631: yo ga ste rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du /
NK118(se)002:632: rdo rje slob ma'i dbang gi steng slob dpon gyi dbang mtha' brten dang bcas pa'ang bskur nas /
NK118(se)002:633: don dam par mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid kyi
NK118(se)002:634: byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar blta
NK118(se)002:635: zhing / mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo
NK118(se)002:636: nas bdag lhar bsgoms pa la ye shes pa dgug
NK118(se)002:637: cing bstim ste phyag rgya bzhis rgyas btab nas mchod
NK118(se)002:638: bstod bzlas pa sogs byas mthar /
NK118(se)002:639: phyag rgya bkrol nas gshegs su gsol ba thabs kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK118(se)002:640: sems kyi de kho na nyid sgom pa shes rab kyi rnal 'byor te /
NK118(se)002:641: nang gi ting nge 'dzin la gtso bor 'don zhing /
NK118(se)002:642: gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i spyod pa'ang grogs su bsten pas /
NK118(se)002:643: 'bras bu stug po bkod pa'i sar grol bar 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:644: de gsum gyis gang dang gang la blang dor dang
NK118(se)002:645: spang gnyen phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang tshul
NK118(se)002:646: 'dra bas phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa gsum
NK118(se)002:647: zhes bya'o // gsum pa dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:648: rnal 'byor bla med pha'i rgyud ces gtags pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK118(se)002:649: dbang bzhis bsdus pa phan nus zab mo'i dbang gis smin par byas nas /
NK118(se)002:650: gzhi chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por rtogs pas /
NK118(se)002:651: lam bsgom tshul ma h+aa la nang gses kyis pha
NK118(se)002:652: ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum du phye ba las
NK118(se)002:653: / gsang 'dus dang gshin rje gshed sogs pha rgyud rnams su thabs bskyed rim gyi spros pa dang /
NK118(se)002:654: rdzogs rim gsang dbang gi nyams len rlung gtso bor
NK118(se)002:655: byed pas gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK118(se)002:656: shes / yang dag dang 'khor lo sdom pa sogs ma rgyud rnams su bskyed rim cha tsam las /
NK118(se)002:657: rdzogs rim sher dbang gi nyams len khams byang chub
NK118(se)002:658: kyi sems thig le gtso bor byed pas bde stong
NK118(se)002:659: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK118(se)002:660: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs gnyis med kyi rgyud rnams su bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug dang /
NK118(se)002:661: khyad par rdzogs rim dbang bzhi pa'i nyams len bde
NK118(se)002:662: gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chen po
NK118(se)002:663: / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid //
NK118(se)002:664: mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i 'od gsal rang byung gi ye shes gtso bor nyams su len cing /
NK118(se)002:665: spyod pa gsum gyi nye rgyus 'bras bu tshe 'di
NK118(se)002:666: nyid la bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par
NK118(se)002:667: 'dod do // ma rgyud lung a nu yo ga ni /
NK118(se)002:668: phyi nang sgrub gsang bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug bskur nas /
NK118(se)002:669: gzhi chos thams cad kyi gshis lugs dkyil 'khor rnam
NK118(se)002:670: gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gnas pa nyid rtog
NK118(se)002:671: dpyod kyi rjes su 'jug pa lta ba gtan la
NK118(se)002:672: phab ste / don gyi rjes su 'jug pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK118(se)002:673: yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa lha'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa grol lam dang /
NK118(se)002:674: steng 'og gi sgo la brten nas bde stong gi
NK118(se)002:675: ye shes bskyed pa thabs kyi lam rnams bsgoms pas
NK118(se)002:676: / 'gyur ba ma nges pa la sogs te sa bcus bsdus pa'i slob lam bzhi mthar phyin nas /
NK118(se)002:677: 'bras bu mi slob pa'i lam tshe 'dir bde ba chen po'i sku mngon du byed par 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:678: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud man ngag a ti yo ga ni /
NK118(se)002:679: dbang bzhi pa rtsal du bton pa rig pa'i rtsal dbang sogs khyad par gyi dbang bskur nas /
NK118(se)002:680: gzhi snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos so
NK118(se)002:681: cog ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gtan
NK118(se)002:682: la phab ste / sems klong man ngag gi sde
NK118(se)002:683: gsum so so'i dgongs pa ltar ka dag gi don
NK118(se)002:684: sor bzhag gis nyams su len pa dang /
NK118(se)002:685: khyad par lhun grub lus kyi dkyil 'khor de bzhin ga shegs pa'i gsang mdzod sgo phye nas /
NK118(se)002:686: rig pa mngon sum gyi don dang por mthong ba /
NK118(se)002:687: bar du 'phel zhing tshad la phebs pa /
NK118(se)002:688: tha mar zad pas gdengs bzhi'i tshad du skyel ba thod rgal gyi lam sgom zhing /
NK118(se)002:689: gnas skabs thams cad du cir snang chos nyid rol
NK118(se)002:690: par bltas te dgag sgrub blang dor med par spyad
NK118(se)002:691: pas / 'bras bu lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i
NK118(se)002:692: sa la da lta nyid nas gnas pa mthar phyin
NK118(se)002:693: pas / te / gdong ma'i sar grol bar byed pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:694: de gsum gyis sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi
NK118(se)002:695: dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas dngos grub gzhan nas
NK118(se)002:696: mi 'tshol bar rang byung gi ye shes su mthong
NK118(se)002:697: bas nang rgyud gsum zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:698: des na rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs la rnam grol
NK118(se)002:699: gyi lam thams cad theg pa dgu po der 'du
NK118(se)002:700: la / de thams cad rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK118(se)002:701: po'i theg pa 'dir 'dus shing rdzogs pa yin no
NK118(se)002:703: nyan rang byang sems rigs can so so la //
NK118(se)002:704: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i lam zhugs yod do zhes //
NK118(se)002:705: 'bum lnga'i rgyud kyi lung las gsal bar grub //
NK118(se)002:708: rdo yi rigs kyi bye brag zhig /
NK118(se)002:709: bzhu bas lcags dang zangs dngul 'byung //
NK118(se)002:710: gser 'gyur rtsi yi dngos po yis //
NK118(se)002:711: kun kyang gser du sgyur bar byed //
NK118(se)002:712: de bzhin sems kyi bye brag gis //
NK118(se)002:713: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa yang //
NK118(se)002:716: zhes rgyud 'bum pa'i lung de kho na nyid kyi
NK118(se)002:717: ye shes grub pa zhes bya ba las byung ba
NK118(se)002:720: dngul rdo gsum ni skye bo phal pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:721: de gsum bzhu ba las byung ba'i lcags ni nyan thos /
NK118(se)002:723: dngul ni byang sems kyi bslab par bya ba yin cing /
NK118(se)002:724: lcags zangs dngul gsum po 'gyur rtsis gser du 'gyur
NK118(se)002:725: ba ni rigs can gsum so so'i sdom pa yang
NK118(se)002:726: dkyil 'khor du bcug ste dbang byin pa na gsum
NK118(se)002:727: ga rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom ldan du 'gyur ba'i
NK118(se)002:728: phyir / rigs can gsum ga la sngags kyi lam zhugs yod par grub bo //
NK118(se)002:730: bsam pa'i dbye bas sngags la 'jug pa'i tshul //
NK118(se)002:731: chos sgo mang yang de dag spro bya min //
NK118(se)002:733: spyir gzhi lam 'bras gsum ga nas sngags lam du 'jug pa yod par bshad de /
NK118(se)002:734: gzhi rigs gcig dang lam rigs bzhi //
NK118(se)002:735: gsang chen bla med mi ldog brten //
NK118(se)002:737: de yang gzhi nas 'jug pa yod de /
NK118(se)002:738: rang bzhin gyi dbang rnon kha cig grub mthas blo
NK118(se)002:739: ye ma bsgyur bar thog ma nas sngags lam du
NK118(se)002:744: la la thun mong lam rnams nas //
NK118(se)002:749: phyi rgyud sde gsum la bslab bzhin pa nas sngags lam du sked 'jus byed pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:751: nyan rang gi dgra bcom lhag med du zhugs pa
NK118(se)002:752: rnams yid lus kyis theg chen du 'jug par bshad
NK118(se)002:753: pa ltar / 'dir yang mtshungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:754: byang sems dang kri yog sde gsum gyis rang rang
NK118(se)002:755: gi 'bras bu thob nas kyang da dung sngags bla
NK118(se)002:756: med kyi lam du 'jug pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:758: thun mong sa mthar byas pa'i tshe //
NK118(se)002:759: yang dag sku gsung thugs bco lnga //
NK118(se)002:760: byin rlabs 'tshams par mos snang bas //
NK118(se)002:764: de bas sangs rgyas sems dpa' mchog /
NK118(se)002:765: sngags kyi spyod mchog spyod pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:766: zhes sangs rgyas dang byang sems mchog gnyis ka sngags la 'jug par bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:768: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams //
NK118(se)002:769: brod pa bskyed phyir kun tu 'od //
NK118(se)002:770: rdo rje 'dzin stug bkod par bstan //
NK118(se)002:771: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK118(se)002:772: ces phar phyin dang sngags gong 'og gi 'bras bu la mchog dman yod par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:774: byang sems dang phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi rang lam
NK118(se)002:775: kho nas sa bcu pa'i byang sems sangs rgyas kyi
NK118(se)002:776: rgyal tshab chen po'i go 'phang gi bar las lhag
NK118(se)002:778: skabs der sngags bla med kyi lam du zhugs nas sangs rgyas thob par bzhed /
NK118(se)002:780: phyi ma 'di 'chad bde bar snang mod /
NK118(se)002:781: de lta na'ang rang gi yi ge snga ma rnams su 'dod pa snga ma ltar bkod cing /
NK118(se)002:782: lung las brgal bar yang mi nub pas da dung dgongs pa len tshul dpyad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:784: nyan rang byang sems rnams kyi 'bras bu'ang rang lam
NK118(se)002:785: la bsten nas tshegs kyis sgrub pa la mi ltos
NK118(se)002:786: par / de thams cad rang rang gi bsam pas
NK118(se)002:787: kun nas bslangs te sngags kyi theg pa la spyad
NK118(se)002:788: pas tshegs chung ngus myur du 'grub pa yod de
NK118(se)002:789: par / / dper na nad gso ba la sman
NK118(se)002:790: spyad dang spyod lam gyi 'phrod bsten la mi ltos
NK118(se)002:791: par rig sngags rnon pos yud tsam gyis gso nus
NK118(se)002:792: par / / pa bzhin no // de bas na
NK118(se)002:793: sngags la 'jug pa'i sgo des mtshon te mang du
NK118(se)002:794: snang yang 'dir de dag spro bya min par bstan
NK118(se)002:795: par / / pa bzhin no // pa'o // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:796: dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum la ltos pa'i sdom gsum la bkri tshul spyir bstan /
NK118(se)002:797: bye brag bstan bcos 'dir bstan bya dbang po 'bring gi lugs yin par bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:799: 'dir ni dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum las //
NK118(se)002:800: zhes theg pa thams cad kyi lam gyi gnad sdom pa gsum du 'dus shing /
NK118(se)002:802: dbang po'i khyad par gyis gsum du yod do zhes mdor bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:803: de'i don rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:804: dang po gang zag dbang rab kyis sdom gsum gcig car du thob tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:805: rab mchog sbyangs pa mthar son skal ldan te //
NK118(se)002:806: dbang bskur thob pas sdom gsum gcig car skyes //
NK118(se)002:807: rtogs grol dus mnyam in+d+ra b+h+au ti bzhin //
NK118(se)002:809: ji ltar o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au tis
NK118(se)002:810: ston pa thub pa'i dbang po la 'dod yon ma
NK118(se)002:811: spangs par sangs rgyas thob pa'i thabs zhus pas /
NK118(se)002:812: ston pas der dkyil 'khor snang bar mdzad nas dbang
NK118(se)002:813: bskur ba'i dus de nyid du rgyal pos zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:814: gi sku brnyes te rtogs grol dus mnyam pa bzhin
NK118(se)002:815: / sngon sbyangs mthar son gyi las 'phro sad pa'i
NK118(se)002:816: skal ldan dbang po yang rab mchog tu gyur pa
NK118(se)002:817: / rnams ni / tshe 'dir lam thun mong pas rgyud sbyong ba la ma ltos par /
NK118(se)002:818: dang po nyid nas phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub
NK118(se)002:819: la yid brtan pa'i sgo nas dkyil 'khor chen por
NK118(se)002:821: sngags sdom kho na las phye ba'i sdom pa gsum gcig car skyes pa ste /
NK118(se)002:822: sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i sdom pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:823: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:824: gzhan la phan pa sgrub pa dang /
NK118(se)002:825: de thams cad kyang chos mnyam pa chen po'i thabs mkhas kyis zin pa'i sdom pa thob pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:827: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK118(se)002:828: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK118(se)002:829: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK118(se)002:830: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK118(se)002:832: gnyis pa dbang 'bring gis sdom gsum so sor len pa ni /
NK118(se)002:833: 'bring ni sdom gsum so so'i cho ga la //
NK118(se)002:834: brten nas rim thob n+aa gardzu na ltar //
NK118(se)002:836: gang zag dbang 'bring rnams ni 'phags mchog klu sgrub
NK118(se)002:837: kyi rnam thar ltar sdom gsum so so'i cho ga
NK118(se)002:838: la brten nas rim par len pa ste /
NK118(se)002:839: nyan thos dang thun mong ba'i 'dul ba'i cho gas so thar rigs 'dun gang rung /
NK118(se)002:840: theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa srol gnyis gang rung gi cho gas byang sdom /
NK118(se)002:841: gsang sngags phyi nang gang rung gi cho gas sngags sdom blangs te /
NK118(se)002:842: sdom pa gsum ldan du nyams su len pa'o //
NK118(se)002:843: gsum pa skal dman rim 'jug gi bkri tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:844: tha ma skal dman shin tu gdul dka' de //
NK118(se)002:845: gso sbyong bslab pa'i gnas bcu grub mtha' bzhi //
NK118(se)002:846: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud kun rim shes nas //
NK118(se)002:847: bla med 'jug pa brtag pa gnyis par gsungs //
NK118(se)002:849: kye rdo rje brtag pa phyi ma 'dul ba'i le'u las /
NK118(se)002:850: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK118(se)002:851: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK118(se)002:852: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK118(se)002:853: mdo sde pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:854: de nas rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK118(se)002:855: de yi rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK118(se)002:856: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK118(se)002:857: de rjes kye yi rdo rje bstan //
NK118(se)002:858: slob mas gus pas blangs nas ni //
NK118(se)002:860: ces gsungs pa ltar skal dman dbang po tha ma
NK118(se)002:861: shin tu gdul dka' ba rnams ni rim gyis bkri
NK118(se)002:862: ba'i thabs la mkhas par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:863: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs dang myang 'das kyi phan yon bsam du bcug pas blo sbyangs nas /
NK118(se)002:864: thog mar spyod pa la rim gyis slob ste /
NK118(se)002:865: dang por gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa'i dus khrims dang /
NK118(se)002:866: de rjes dge bsnyen dang dge tshul gyi bslab pa'i
NK118(se)002:867: gnas bcu nas dge slong gi sdom pa'i bar sbyin
NK118(se)002:868: par bya'o // de rjes grub mtha' bzhi'i lta ba ston te /
NK118(se)002:869: bye brag tu smra ba dang mdo sde pa'i gzung
NK118(se)002:870: ba rdul phran bskor ba bar bcas bar med dang
NK118(se)002:871: / 'dzin pa skad cig ma don dam du 'dod pa la sogs pa'i grub mtha' rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:873: chos thams cad sems tsam du gtan la 'bebs pa sogs rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhung dang /
NK118(se)002:874: chos thams cad spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral bar ston pa dbu ma'i grub mtha' ste /
NK118(se)002:875: de ltar grub mtha' bzhi shes pa'i 'og tu /
NK118(se)002:876: thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa la rim par slob ste /
NK118(se)002:877: rang rang gi dbang bskur ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:878: gtsang sbra'i spyod lam dang bzlas brjod sogs lus ngag
NK118(se)002:879: gi bya ba gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud
NK118(se)002:880: dang / lus ngag gi bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:881: sems kyi ting 'dzin cha mnyam du ston pa spyod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK118(se)002:882: sems kyi ting 'dzin gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kun rim par shes pa'i 'og tu /
NK118(se)002:883: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i rnal 'byor bde ba
NK118(se)002:884: chen pos khyad par du byas pa'i thabs ston pa
NK118(se)002:885: rnal 'byor bla na med pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi
NK118(se)002:886: rgyud sde la rim gyis gzhug par bya ba yin
NK118(se)002:887: no // de dang mthun par phur pa zhe sdang khros pa'i rgyud las kyang /
NK118(se)002:888: so so thar pa dang por sbyin //
NK118(se)002:889: de la nyan thos chos rnams bstan //
NK118(se)002:890: de nas byang chub sdom chen sbyin //
NK118(se)002:891: de la dbu ma'i chos rnams bshad //
NK118(se)002:892: mthar ni 'bras bu theg chen gyi //
NK118(se)002:896: 'dir ni dbang po 'bring gi tshul 'chad de //
NK118(se)002:899: tshigs gsum sngags kyi rten mchog dman du 'gro tshul dmigs gsal dang bcas pa bshad /
NK118(se)002:900: bstan bcos 'dir gtan la dbab bya'i sdom pa gsum ngos bzung /
NK118(se)002:901: so byang gnyis sngags sdom gyi yan lag tu bsdu tshul bshad /
NK118(se)002:902: sdom gsum so so'i lus rnam bzhag mdor bstan pas khog dbub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:904: dge slong dge tshul dge bsnyen sdom ldan de //
NK118(se)002:905: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab 'bring tha yin zhes //
NK118(se)002:906: phur pa'i rgyud dang dus 'khor las gsungs shing //
NK118(se)002:907: 'on kyang ye shes ldan pa gtso bor bzung //
NK118(se)002:909: spyir btang gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sdom pa la 'jug pa'i rten dge slong rab /
NK118(se)002:911: dge bsnyen tha ma yin par phur pa'i rgyud dang dus 'khor rtsa rgyud las gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:913: gsum las dge slong mchog yin 'bring //
NK118(se)002:914: dge tshul zhes bya de dag las //
NK118(se)002:915: khyim na gnas pa tha ma'o //
NK118(se)002:917: rta mgrin dgongs pa lung ston gyi rgyud las kyang /
NK118(se)002:918: dmigs pa phra ba'i rig pa ni //
NK118(se)002:919: gtso bo'i bsnyen pa 'bum du bya //
NK118(se)002:920: 'khor rnams la ni khri yin te //
NK118(se)002:921: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pas bya //
NK118(se)002:923: sngags su ma zad byang sdom gyi rten kyang khyim pa las rab tu byung ba 'phags te /
NK118(se)002:925: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs dag ni //
NK118(se)002:926: yon tan tshad med rnams dang ldan //
NK118(se)002:927: de ltar sdom brtson khyim pa yin //
NK118(se)002:928: byang sems rnams las mchog tu bshad //
NK118(se)002:930: rten khyim pa yin kyang ye shes dang ldan pa
NK118(se)002:931: ste sa thob pa yin na de nyid khyad par
NK118(se)002:932: du 'phags pas gtso bo brten pa dmigs bsal te
NK118(se)002:934: sa thob ma gtogs khyim pa ni //
NK118(se)002:935: rgyal pos bla mar mi bya ste //
NK118(se)002:936: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:937: de 'dra ba'i gang zag ni khyim pa'i rtags can
NK118(se)002:938: yin kyang sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo
NK118(se)002:939: dang 'dul ba lung las khyim pa 'phags pa'i chos
NK118(se)002:940: dang ldan pa don dam pa'i dge slong du bsdus
NK118(se)002:941: pa dang gnad gcig pa ste /
NK118(se)002:943: rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod cing //
NK118(se)002:944: dul zhing yang dag sdom la tshangs par spyod //
NK118(se)002:945: 'byung po kun la chad pa spangs pa de //
NK118(se)002:946: dge slong dge sbyong de yin /
NK118(se)002:947: zhes khyim bdag grags pa dge slong du gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:949: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i rtsa ba kun 'dus las //
NK118(se)002:950: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:951: so thar sems bskyed dbang bskur nyid yin te //
NK118(se)002:952: so sor 'dzin na nyan thos byang sems dang //
NK118(se)002:953: rig pa 'dzin pa zhes su mkhas la grags //
NK118(se)002:955: spyir sdom gsum gyi tha snyad grags pa'i rnam grangs la /
NK118(se)002:958: dge slong ste bslab tshigs gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:959: byang sdom gyi nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK118(se)002:961: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:962: sngags sdom gyi skabs su phra rgyas las /
NK118(se)002:963: de ltar sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK118(se)002:964: bdag gi rdo rje mchog gsum po //
NK118(se)002:965: log par mi gtong sdom pa'i dngos //
NK118(se)002:966: sa gzhi lta bur gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:967: zhes sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum la sdom
NK118(se)002:968: pa gsum du bzhag pa sogs mang du snang mod
NK118(se)002:969: kyang / 'dir skabs don ngos bzung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:971: de ltar sdom pa gsum po yang //
NK118(se)002:972: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che //
NK118(se)002:973: zhes pa ltar sde snod gsum gyi nang nas 'dus pa'i sde snod kyi bstan don so thar /
NK118(se)002:974: mdo sde'i sde snod kyi bstan don byang sdom /
NK118(se)002:975: sde snod bzhi pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod kyi bstan don sngags sdom rnams yin cing /
NK118(se)002:977: kun slong gi khyad par rang don zhi bde 'dod pas /
NK118(se)002:978: cho ga'i khyad par nyan thos dang thun mong ba'i 'dul ba'i cho ga la brten nas /
NK118(se)002:979: dus kyi khyad par nyin zhag gam ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK118(se)002:980: spang bya'i khyad par lus ngag gi mi dge ba
NK118(se)002:981: ci rigs spong ba'i rigs brgyad gang rung la bslab
NK118(se)002:982: pa'o // de bzhin du byang sdom ni /
NK118(se)002:983: kun slong gi khyad par gzhan don du rdzogs byang la dmigs pas /
NK118(se)002:984: cho ga'i khyad par srol gnyis gang rung gi sems bskyed kyi cho ga la brten nas /
NK118(se)002:985: dus kyi khyad par byang chub kyi bar du /
NK118(se)002:986: spang bya'i khyad par byang chub sems dpa'i 'chal tshul
NK118(se)002:987: gyi rgyun spong ba'i smon 'jug gnyis sam gang rung
NK118(se)002:988: la bslab pa'o // sngags sdom ni /
NK118(se)002:989: kun slong thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i gzhan don rlabs po che sgrub par 'dod pas /
NK118(se)002:990: cho ga'i khyad par rgyud sde bzhi gang rung gi dbang la brten nas /
NK118(se)002:991: dus kyi khyad par bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi bar du /
NK118(se)002:992: spang bya'i khyad par sngags phyi nang so so la
NK118(se)002:993: ltos pa'i rang skal gyi 'chal tshul sdom pa'i tshul
NK118(se)002:994: khrims gang zhig / btags pa ba brjod pa khas blangs dang /
NK118(se)002:995: mtshan nyid pa dbang gi dngos gzhi las thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:996: des na rang sde snod gang las bstan don ltar so sor 'dzin na /
NK118(se)002:999: dbang thob pas rig pa 'dzin pa zhes mkhas la grags mod /
NK118(se)002:1000: 'on kyang kun slong gi khyad par gyis mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK118(se)002:1002: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i //
NK118(se)002:1003: cho ga nyan thos lugs bzhin gyis //
NK118(se)002:1004: so so thar pa rigs brgyad po //
NK118(se)002:1005: byang sems so so thar par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:1006: zhes byang sems kyi so thar ngos 'dzin dngos su gsungs pas /
NK118(se)002:1007: de'i shugs kyis sngags kyi so thar kyang don gyis 'phangs pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:1008: dper na sngags sdom rgyud ldan gyis dge tshul slong
NK118(se)002:1009: gi sdom pa gsar du blangs na de dang de
NK118(se)002:1010: gsang sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i so thar
NK118(se)002:1011: gyi sdom par 'gyur dgos pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:1014: de ltar thun mong sdom pa 'og ma gnyis //
NK118(se)002:1015: 'dir ni bla med dbang gi yan lag tu //
NK118(se)002:1016: rgyud sde rgya mtshor bshad ltar 'dir 'chad do //
NK118(se)002:1018: bshad ma thag pa ltar rgyu'i theg pa dman mchog
NK118(se)002:1019: gnyis dang thun mong par gyur pa sdom pa 'og
NK118(se)002:1020: ma so byang gnyis 'dir bla med dbang gi yan
NK118(se)002:1022: so byang gi sdom ldan des sngags sdom blangs pa'i tshe /
NK118(se)002:1023: so thar ni sngags kyi nyes spyod sdom pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1024: byang sdom rnam snang gi dam tshig tu 'gyur ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:1026: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig ces bshad pa'i spyi'i dam tshig tu /
NK118(se)002:1027: so byang dang sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig thams cad tshang ba'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:1028: der ma zad so byang sngon du ma song ba'i
NK118(se)002:1029: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud la'ang dbang bskur kho nas
NK118(se)002:1030: thob pa'i skyabs gsum tsam mam bslab gzhi lnga 'dzin
NK118(se)002:1031: pa'i nyes spyod sdom pa so thar dang /
NK118(se)002:1032: dbang gi sngon 'gror rgyud sde nas gsungs pa'i sems
NK118(se)002:1033: bskyed kyi cho gas smon 'jug gi sems bskyed blangs
NK118(se)002:1035: des na skabs 'dir bstan gyi sdom pa gsum gyi rnam bzhag 'di ni /
NK118(se)002:1036: rgyu'i sde snod gsum du ma grags pas 'bras bu'i sde snod rgyud sde rnams kyi khyad chos te /
NK118(se)002:1038: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK118(se)002:1039: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK118(se)002:1040: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK118(se)002:1041: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK118(se)002:1044: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK118(se)002:1048: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:1049: rig 'dzin nyid kyi dge slong ngo //
NK118(se)002:1052: srog gcod rku dang 'khrig pa dang //
NK118(se)002:1053: rdzun dang chang ni rnam spangs te //
NK118(se)002:1054: khyim pa'i sdom pa legs gnas nas //
NK118(se)002:1055: gsang sngags rgyal po rab tu sgrub //
NK118(se)002:1056: gal te de dag rab byung gyur //
NK118(se)002:1057: sdom pa gsum dang yang dag ldan //
NK118(se)002:1058: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:1062: sdom gsum so sor khog dbub gleng gzhi dang //
NK118(se)002:1063: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob pa'i tshul //
NK118(se)002:1064: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs //
NK118(se)002:1065: tha mar nyams na gso tshul bzhi res sdom //
NK118(se)002:1066: zhes lus rnam gzhag gi tshigs su bcad pa 'di
NK118(se)002:1067: sdom pa gsum so sor gtan la dbab pa'i le'u
NK118(se)002:1068: gnyis pa dang / gsum pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1069: bzhi pa rnams kyis rgyas par 'chad par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1071: de ltar bshad zin nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:1072: sdom gsum spyi'i bshad gzhi'i rim par phye ba ste dang po'o //
NK118(se)002:1074: bstan bcos 'di la le'u lnga las /
NK118(se)002:1075: gzhi 'bras kyi mtshams sbyor lam thams cad kyi gnad
NK118(se)002:1076: sdom pa gsum du bsdus pa'i 'brel spyir bstan pa'i
NK118(se)002:1077: sgo nas bshad bya'i gzhi rim par phye ba ste
NK118(se)002:1080: rang bzhin lhun rdzogs 'od gsal byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:1081: sgrib bral sku bzhi'i 'bras bur mtshams sbyor ba'i //
NK118(se)002:1082: rnam dag legs pa'i lam mchog sdom gsum gyi //
NK118(se)002:1083: bshad bzhi'i rim pa legs par bkral ba'i mthus //
NK118(se)002:1084: lus ngag nyes spyod 'dul ba'i thabs kyis thul //
NK118(se)002:1085: sems glang gzhan phan lcags kyus dbang du byas //
NK118(se)002:1086: ma dag snang zhen smin grol chos kyis sbyangs //
NK118(se)002:1087: 'gro kun rnam grol dpal la spyod par shog /
NK118(se)002:1089: gang zhig mtshan dpe'i gzugs sku zhi ba'i dbyings //
NK118(se)002:1090: snyoms par zhugs kyang sdom brtson 'dus pa'i dbus //
NK118(se)002:1091: gnang bkag 'doms pa'i chos 'dul skur bzhengs pa //
NK118(se)002:1092: ston dang bstan pa gnyis gyur phyag gi gnas //
NK118(se)002:1093: lung rig sbrang rtsis myos pa'i b+h+ra ma ra //
NK118(se)002:1094: chos 'dul 'dab brgya bzhad pa'i skyed tshal du //
NK118(se)002:1095: legs bshad rnam par 'grel ba'i snyan 'gyur sgra //
NK118(se)002:1096: dpyod ldan rna ba'i bcud du de ring len //
NK118(se)002:1097: gnyis pa sdom pa gsum so so'i rang bzhin dang bslab bya rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:1100: sngags kyi sdom pa bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1101: de gsum ga la sngar lus rnam gzhag gi skabs su /
NK118(se)002:1103: ma thob pa thob par byed pa /
NK118(se)002:1104: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba /
NK118(se)002:1105: nyams na phyir bcos tshul dang bzhi'i sdoms kyis bsdus na'ang /
NK118(se)002:1106: 'dir blo gsar rnams kyi blo la 'char bde ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1107: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum du bsdus te 'chad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:1108: de la dang po so thar gyi sdom pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:1109: ston pas 'dul ba'i dam chos gsungs tshul /
NK118(se)002:1110: de bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung tshul /
NK118(se)002:1111: de ltar bzung ba'i 'dul ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1113: gleng gzhi ston pas w+aa ra n+aa s+ai ru //
NK118(se)002:1114: lhag pa'i tshul khrims gtsor ston bden pa bzhi //
NK118(se)002:1117: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa 'dis /
NK118(se)002:1118: sngon byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed pa nas brtsams te /
NK118(se)002:1119: bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs gnyis rdzogs par mdzad nas /
NK118(se)002:1120: mi rnams tshe lo nyis khri pa'i dus sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:1121: 'od srungs 'jig rten du byon pa'i tshe bram ze'i
NK118(se)002:1123: de'i phyi ma la dga' ldan du dam pa tog dkar por skye ba bzung zhing /
NK118(se)002:1124: de nas tshe lo brgya pa'i dus su dga' ldan
NK118(se)002:1125: nas 'pho ba sogs zhing 'dir mdzad pa bcu gnyis
NK118(se)002:1127: gang gi tshe dgung lo nyer dgu'i bar khab tu bzhugs pa'i mthar rab tu byung zhing /
NK118(se)002:1128: dka' ba lo drug spyad nas /
NK118(se)002:1129: dgung lo so lnga la babs pa na rdo rje
NK118(se)002:1130: gdan du sa ga zla ba'i tshes bco lnga'i srod
NK118(se)002:1132: thun dang po'i skabs de nyid du mnyam par bzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:1133: rab matha'i bsam gtan la brten nas rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes dang lha'i rna ba bsgrubs /
NK118(se)002:1134: gung thun la gzhan sems shes pa /
NK118(se)002:1137: thun tha ma skya rengs 'char ka la zag zad kyi mngon shes bsgrubs pas /
NK118(se)002:1138: bla na med pa'i ye shes brnyes nas mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas te /
NK118(se)002:1139: de'i tshe 'jig rten na dgra bcom pa gcig go //
NK118(se)002:1140: de nas zhag bdun phrag bdun 'das pa chu stod zla ba'i tshes bzhi nas brtsams te /
NK118(se)002:1141: 'dul ba'i dam chos gsungs pa'i gleg gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:1142: yul w+aa ra n+aa s+ai'i drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi nags su /
NK118(se)002:1143: ston pa thub pa'i dbang pos /
NK118(se)002:1144: 'khor lnga sde bzang po lha brgyad khri dang bcas pa la /
NK118(se)002:1145: chos lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa brjod bya'i gtso bor ston pa las brtsams te /
NK118(se)002:1146: 'dul ba'i 'dul ba bcas pa dang rang bzhin gyi rnam gzhag che long tsam dang /
NK118(se)002:1147: 'dul ba'i mdo sde ting nge 'dzin dang tshangs par
NK118(se)002:1148: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba'i rim pa dang
NK118(se)002:1149: / 'dul ba'i mngon pa de rnams kyi rab dbye
NK118(se)002:1150: rgya cher bshad pa sogs spangs gnyen gyi rim pas
NK118(se)002:1151: nyams su len pa'i thabs bden bzhi'i chos kyi rnam
NK118(se)002:1152: / grangs gsungs pas / lnga sdes dgra bcom pa thob /
NK118(se)002:1153: lha brgyad khris bden pa mthong /
NK118(se)002:1154: de'i tshe'i 'jig rten na dgra bcom pa drug go //
NK118(se)002:1155: de nas nye ba'i lnga ste la sogs pa nas rab bzang gi bar btul te /
NK118(se)002:1156: dgung lo brgyad cu pa la gyad yul r+ts+wa chen
NK118(se)002:1157: du phung po lhag ma med pa'i dbyings su mya
NK118(se)002:1158: ngan las 'da' ba ston par mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:1159: de yang lung bzhis bsdus pa'i 'dul ba'i sde snod ni /
NK118(se)002:1160: ston pa sangs rgyas nas mya ngan las ma 'das
NK118(se)002:1161: kyi bar du byung ba dang bcas pa'i rnam par
NK118(se)002:1162: bzhag pa thams cad ston pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1163: chos 'khor dang po kho na'i mtshan gzhir nges pa ma yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:1164: 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid spang bya las ldog pa'i lam ston pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1165: gtso che ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:1166: 'dir 'khor lo dang po'i mtshan gzhir mdzad pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:1169: bye brag bshad mdzod la sogs 'phags pas brtsams //
NK118(se)002:1170: yon tan 'od dang sh+aakya 'od kyis spel //
NK118(se)002:1171: snga 'gyur sdom rgyun zhi ba 'tsho dang ni //
NK118(se)002:1172: phyis nas sh+aakya sh+r+ai las kyang dar //
NK118(se)002:1176: sh+aa ra'i bu dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa brgyad khri /
NK118(se)002:1177: moong+gala gyi bu dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa bdun khri /
NK118(se)002:1178: bcom ldan 'das dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa khri brgyad stong mya ngan las 'das pas /
NK118(se)002:1180: dge slong dbang yod pa dag kyang mya ngan las 'das te /
NK118(se)002:1181: dam pa'i chos ni dud pa tsam du gyur /
NK118(se)002:1182: dge slong rnams sde snod gsum gyi sgra yang mi sgrag go //
NK118(se)002:1184: gnas rgyal po'i khab kyi nya gro d+ha'i phug tu /
NK118(se)002:1185: ma skyes dgras gnas mal dang yo byad thams cad sbyar te /
NK118(se)002:1186: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus nas dbyar gnas pa'i dus su /
NK118(se)002:1187: 'phags pa kun dga' bos mdo sde /
NK118(se)002:1189: 'od srungs chen pos mngon pa'i sde snod mtha' dag bsdus pas /
NK118(se)002:1192: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa yun ring bar gnas so //
NK118(se)002:1193: zhes lha rnams kyis 'og min gyi bar du go bar byas shing ched du brjod do //
NK118(se)002:1195: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgya dang bcu lon pa na /
NK118(se)002:1196: yangs pa can gyi dge slong rnams kyis rung ba ma yin pa'i gzhi bcu byas pa de /
NK118(se)002:1197: grags pa la sogs pa dgra bcom pa bdun brgyas sun phyungs shing /
NK118(se)002:1198: sde snod gsum ga tshang ba tshar gcig legs par bton /
NK118(se)002:1199: mthun pa dang bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong yang mdzad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1201: rgyal po mya ngan bral gyi bu rgyal po dpa' bo'i sde'i dus nas brtsams te /
NK118(se)002:1202: bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i dge slong lha chen po dang /
NK118(se)002:1205: yid brtan rnams rim par byung bas /
NK118(se)002:1206: gzhi lnga gzhan lan gdab dang mi shes pa //
NK118(se)002:1207: yid gnyis dang ni yongs su brtag /
NK118(se)002:1208: bdag nyid gso bar byed pa ste //
NK118(se)002:1209: 'di ni ston pa'i bstan pa yin //
NK118(se)002:1211: bsgrags te chos log bstan pas /
NK118(se)002:1212: rgyal po dpa' bo'i sde'i tshe smad /
NK118(se)002:1214: pad+ma chen po'i tshe ril po /
NK118(se)002:1215: ka nish+ka'i tshe stod yan te rgyal po bzhi'i ring dge 'dun rnams rtsod par gyur cing /
NK118(se)002:1216: ston pas 'dul ba yi ger 'dri bar ma gnang
NK118(se)002:1217: bas yun ring song ba na so so thar pa'i
NK118(se)002:1218: mdo'i 'don tshul ma mthun pa'i dbang gis sde pa
NK118(se)002:1220: ji ltar na gnas brtan klus rtsod pa spel ba'i rgyus rtsa ba'i sde pa bzhir gyes /
NK118(se)002:1221: de rjes yid brtan gyis rtsod pa rgya cher spel
NK118(se)002:1222: bas sde pa bzhi yang bco brgyad du rim gyis
NK118(se)002:1223: gyes rjes / phan tshun rtsod pa cung zad zhi nas so sor gnas pa'i dus su /
NK118(se)002:1224: rgyal po ka nish+kasa sbyin bdag byas nas bka' bsdu gsum pa mdzad /
NK118(se)002:1225: de yang kha che'i yul rna rgyan gyi gtsug lag khang du /
NK118(se)002:1226: 'phags pa rtsibs logs sogs dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang /
NK118(se)002:1227: ba su mi tra sogs btsun pa chen po bzhi brgya dang /
NK118(se)002:1228: byang chub sems dpa' lnga brgya rnams kyis bsdus zhes kha che ba rnams 'dod /
NK118(se)002:1229: dza lan+d+ha ra'i dgon pa ku ba na'i gtsug lag khang du dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang /
NK118(se)002:1230: btsun pa chen po lnga stong zhig gis bsdus so //
NK118(se)002:1231: zhes 'phags yul gyi pan+di ta phal cher bzhed gsung /
NK118(se)002:1232: ding sang bod du grags pa ltar na /
NK118(se)002:1233: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi brgyar nye ba na dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang /
NK118(se)002:1234: byang chub sems dpa' lnga brgya dang /
NK118(se)002:1235: so skye'i btsun pa chen po lnga bargya'am khri drug stong 'dus nas bsdus zer /
NK118(se)002:1236: gang ltar kyang gser phreng can gyi rtogs brjod ces
NK118(se)002:1237: pa rgyal po kri ki'i rmi lam lung bstan pa'i
NK118(se)002:1238: mdo drangs nas gyes pa bco brgyad po thams cad
NK118(se)002:1239: sangs rgyas kyi bkar bsgrubs shing /
NK118(se)002:1241: mdo sde dang mngon pa sngar yi ger ma 'khod
NK118(se)002:1242: pa rnams kyang dus der yi ger bris pa yin
NK118(se)002:1243: no // dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos byung tshul la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:1244: nyan thos kyi thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1247: bstan bcos bye brag bshad mdzod yin la /
NK118(se)002:1248: 'di ni nyer sbas kyi dus dgra bcom pa rnams kyis spyi mthun du brtsams zer ba dang /
NK118(se)002:1249: kha cig dgra bcom pa grags pa dang thams cad 'dod sogs kyis brtsams par grags shing /
NK118(se)002:1250: bod rnams gtam de gnyis bsres te /
NK118(se)002:1251: byang phyogs ri bo 'bigs byed gar mkhan gyi gtsug lag khang du nyer sbas dang /
NK118(se)002:1253: rgur po sogs dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas mdzad ces 'byung ngo //
NK118(se)002:1255: 'od byed kyi sa brnyes pa bram ze'i btsun pa
NK118(se)002:1256: slob dpon yon tan 'od kyis mdo rtsa ba dang
NK118(se)002:1257: karma sha tam la sogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1258: slob dpon sh+aakya 'od kyis sum brgya pa rtsa 'grel sogs mdzad cing spel bas /
NK118(se)002:1259: ding sang gi bar du slob dpon 'di gnyis kyi gsung la gtso bor bsten par byed do //
NK118(se)002:1260: so so thar pa'i sdom rgyun ji ltar byung tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:1261: gangs can gyi khrod 'dir sde pa gzhi thams cad
NK118(se)002:1262: yod par smra ba'i lugs gcig pu las gzhan ma
NK118(se)002:1263: byung / de lta na'ang sdom rgyun rim pa gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:1264: snga 'gyur gyi sdom rgyun smad 'dul ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1265: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK118(se)002:1276: bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK118(se)002:1277: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab /
NK118(se)002:1279: sne po grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK118(se)002:1287: gro ston kun dga' rgya mtshan /
NK118(se)002:1290: gnas rnying pa kun dga' bde legs /
NK118(se)002:1291: thams cad mkhyen pa dge 'dun rgya mtsho /
NK118(se)002:1292: bde ba can pa dge legs dpal bzang /
NK118(se)002:1293: rgyal khang rtse pa dpal 'byor rgya mtsho /
NK118(se)002:1294: gling smad khri chen dkon mchog chos 'phel /
NK118(se)002:1296: de la bdag gis tshigs gsum dus gcig la bar
NK118(se)002:1297: ma chad pa'i cho gas bsnyen par rdzogs pa thob
NK118(se)002:1298: bo // phyi 'gyur gyi sdom rgyun la gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:1300: shar phyogs kyi pan+di ta d+harma p+aa la'i mkhan bu p+aa la rnam gsum sogs nas brgyud pa ste /
NK118(se)002:1301: ding sang rgyun yod pa ma thos la /
NK118(se)002:1311: des 'jam dbyangs sa skya pan+di ta /
NK118(se)002:1313: rdo rje dpal rnams bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad pas /
NK118(se)002:1314: de gsum las rgyun 'phel nas dar bar gyur to //
NK118(se)002:1315: zhar byung 'dul ba'i bshad rgyun ni /
NK118(se)002:1318: 'od srung chen po nas legs mthong gi bar sangs rgyas dang 'dra ba'i nyan thos bdun /
NK118(se)002:1319: phyir mi 'ong blos mi phebs pa /
NK118(se)002:1323: slob dpon chos kyi bshes gnyen /
NK118(se)002:1326: de gnyis las slob dpon sh+aakya 'od /
NK118(se)002:1327: pan+di ta seng ge gdong can /
NK118(se)002:1348: dmar ston rgya mtsho rin chen nam /
NK118(se)002:1349: yang na rma tsho'i slob ma skyid shod pa tshul khrims 'phags nas /
NK118(se)002:1350: dmar ston dpal ldan rin chen gyi bar bla ma
NK118(se)002:1351: brgyad brgyud de dmar ston rgya mtsho rin chen no
NK118(se)002:1352: // de nas kun mkhyen sangs rgyas 'phel /
NK118(se)002:1354: grub chen nor bu phun tshogs /
NK118(se)002:1355: shangs ston byams pa chos bshes /
NK118(se)002:1357: gung ston bkra shis grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK118(se)002:1359: 'bum rab 'byams pa thar pa rgyal mtshan /
NK118(se)002:1362: de gnyis kyi slob ma bkra shis rgyal mtshan dang /
NK118(se)002:1363: byams pa rgyal mtshan gnyis la /
NK118(se)002:1364: lung rigs smra ba'i dbang phyug sangs rgyas chos dar gyis gsan /
NK118(se)002:1365: de la bdag gis legs par thos so //
NK118(se)002:1367: lung mang ba grub pa rdo rje la 'dul lung sde bzhi phran 'ga' dang bcas pa /
NK118(se)002:1368: rab 'byams pa sangs rgyas chos dar la mdo rtsa ba dang lung rig gter mdzod /
NK118(se)002:1369: sdom brtson kun dga' dar rgyas la me tog phreng rgyud dang /
NK118(se)002:1371: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i bdag nyid rig 'dzin chen po
NK118(se)002:1372: pad+ma phrin las la kun mkhyen bu'i las chog sogs
NK118(se)002:1373: kyi bklags lung kyang legs par zhus shing /
NK118(se)002:1374: 'dul ba'i brda' chad dang lag len rags tsam gzhon
NK118(se)002:1375: nu'i dus nas gcen sdom brtson mkhas pa chen po
NK118(se)002:1377: gung thang pan chen gnyis la bsten te cung zad sbyangs so //
NK118(se)002:1378: gsum pa de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa la bdun te /
NK118(se)002:1379: thob bya sdom pa'i ngo bo /
NK118(se)002:1381: ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i thabs /
NK118(se)002:1382: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba'i tshul /
NK118(se)002:1387: ngo bo nges 'byung bsam pas kun bslangs nas //
NK118(se)002:1388: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas ldog pa lus ngag las //
NK118(se)002:1389: skye phyir gzugs can yin ces 'dod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:1390: spong sems rgyun chags sa bon la 'dod pa //
NK118(se)002:1391: rang gi sde pa gong 'og so so'i lugs //
NK118(se)002:1393: so thar gyi sdom pa'i ngo bo la /
NK118(se)002:1395: nges 'byung gi bsam pas zin pa'i nyes spyod sdom
NK118(se)002:1396: pa'i tshul khrims gang zhig /'dod pa'i sas bsdus pa'o
NK118(se)002:1397: // zur dang pos phyi rol pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK118(se)002:1398: zur gnyis pas bar ma'i tshul khrims dang /
NK118(se)002:1399: zur gsum pas bsam gtan dang zag med kyi sdom pa gsal lo //
NK118(se)002:1400: 'dir bye brag tu smra ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:1401: sdom pa de gsum 'gal bar 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1402: 'dod pa'i sas bsdus pa so thar dang /
NK118(se)002:1403: gzugs kyi sas bsdus pa bsam gtan dang /
NK118(se)002:1404: khams gsum gang rung gi sas ma bsdus pa zag med do //
NK118(se)002:1405: theg chen ltar na de gsum mi 'gal te /
NK118(se)002:1406: theg chen 'phags rgyud kyi bsam gtan dngos gzhi'i ngo bor gyur pa'i sdom pa de /
NK118(se)002:1408: bsam gtan gyi dngos gzhis bsdus pa /
NK118(se)002:1409: 'phags lam gyi ngo bo yin pa'i cha nas de dang de yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1412: theg pa gsum gyi dbye bas gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:1413: de gsum gang yang rung ba'i kun slong gi bsam pas zin pa'i sgo nas /
NK118(se)002:1414: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas las ldog pa lus ngag gi
NK118(se)002:1415: nyes pa bdun spong ba'i las lam dngos gzhi dang
NK118(se)002:1416: / des drangs pa'i mjug gang rung gi ngo bor skye ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1417: sdom pa'i ngo bo gzugs can te /
NK118(se)002:1418: de yang bye brag tu smra ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:1419: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs su gnas par 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1421: rnam rig min rnam gsum zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:1422: sdom dang sdom pa min dang gzhan //
NK118(se)002:1423: sdom pa so sor thar zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:1424: de bzhin zag med bsam gtan skyes //
NK118(se)002:1427: nyan thos sdom pa rnam rig min //
NK118(se)002:1430: yang dag par blangs pa'i tshul khrims ni rnam par
NK118(se)002:1431: rig byed la rag las pa'i phyir las kyi lam
NK118(se)002:1432: gzugs can bdun ni gdon mi za bar rnam par
NK118(se)002:1433: rig byed dang rig byed ma yin pa gnyis ka
NK118(se)002:1434: yod do // zhes pas gnod do snyam na /
NK118(se)002:1436: de dus rig byed yod par ston gyi /
NK118(se)002:1437: de nyid las lam gyi dngos gzhir 'chad pa ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:1438: sbyor ba dang mjug nyid du nges pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:1440: rgyud yongs su 'gyur pa'i khyad par la 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1442: las sngon du 'gro ba'i sems phyir zhing 'byung ba gang yin pa de ni rgyud yin no //
NK118(se)002:1443: de gzhan dang gzhan du skye ba ni yongs su 'gyur ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:1446: 'chal tshul spong ba'i sems pa rgyun chags sa bon dang bcas pa la 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1447: sems pa rkyang pa la byas na rgyun med cing /
NK118(se)002:1448: bag chags tsam la byas na gtong rgyu byung ba'i gnas skabs su'ang rjes su 'brang ba'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:1450: gal te sems pa kho na lus kyi las su 'gyur na /
NK118(se)002:1451: sems g.yeng ba dang sems med pa dag la sems
NK118(se)002:1452: pa de med na sdom pa dang sdom pa min
NK118(se)002:1453: pa gnyis ji ltar yod ce na /
NK118(se)002:1454: sdom pa'i khyad par gyi bag chags ma bcom pa'i
NK118(se)002:1455: phyir sdom pa dang sdom pa ma yin pa gnyis
NK118(se)002:1458: spong sems mtshungs ldan dang bcas pa la 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1460: spong ba'i sems ni thob pa la //
NK118(se)002:1461: tshul khrims pha rol phyin par bshad //
NK118(se)002:1463: de ltar na rang sde'i grub mtha' gong 'og la
NK118(se)002:1464: so so'i blo khyad kyis 'dod lugs mtho dma' byung
NK118(se)002:1465: ba yin no // gnyis pa dbye ba ni /
NK118(se)002:1466: dbye ba bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis //
NK118(se)002:1467: khyim pa'i phyogs yin dge tshul pha ma dang //
NK118(se)002:1468: dge slob ma dang dge slong pha ma lnga //
NK118(se)002:1469: rab byung la yin so thar rigs brgyad po //
NK118(se)002:1470: rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'dod mdzod kyi lugs //
NK118(se)002:1472: so thar la dbye na rigs brgyad de /
NK118(se)002:1473: khyim pa'i phyogs kyi gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:1474: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs kyi lnga rnams su yod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1475: brgyad po de dag kyang rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'du ste /
NK118(se)002:1477: dge tshul pha ma dge slob ma dang gsum /
NK118(se)002:1478: dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis rnams mtshan phan tshun du
NK118(se)002:1479: gyur pa las ming 'pho ba tsam yin pas rdzas
NK118(se)002:1481: bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa dang rdzas rigs bzhir nges pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1483: so so thar zhes bya rnams brgyad //
NK118(se)002:1484: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK118(se)002:1485: mtshan las ming ni 'pho ba'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:1486: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK118(se)002:1491: dge slong bzhi'i sdom pa'i mtshan nyid rim bzhin /
NK118(se)002:1492: rang gi sdom par 'grub byed kyi rgyu phun sum
NK118(se)002:1493: tshogs pa la brten nas thob pa'i nges 'byung gi
NK118(se)002:1495: ces pa bzhi ga'i 'gor sbyar te /
NK118(se)002:1496: bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs su gyur
NK118(se)002:1497: pa'i spang bya brgyad nyin zhag phrugs gcig tu spong
NK118(se)002:1498: bar khas blangs pa'i sdom pa dang po'i mtshan nyid
NK118(se)002:1499: / 'di la dus khrims sam gso sbyong zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1500: khyim pa rnams kyi nya stong tshes brgyad kyi dus su blangs nas bsrung ba'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:1501: 'di dge bsnyen gyis blangs na de'i bslab bya gso
NK118(se)002:1502: zhing spang bya sbyong ba'i gso sbyong du 'gro bas
NK118(se)002:1503: so // dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs
NK118(se)002:1504: su gyur pa'i spang bya ji srid 'tsho'i bar du
NK118(se)002:1505: spong bar khas blangs pa gnyis pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:1506: 'di la 'dul bar yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen las gzhan pa'i 'bogs chog ma bshad kyang /
NK118(se)002:1507: mngon pa las skyabs gsum 'dzin pa dang sna gcig spyod pa sogs dbye ba mang ngo //
NK118(se)002:1508: dge tshul gyi sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs su gyur
NK118(se)002:1509: pa'i spang bya bcu ji srid mtsho'i bar du spong
NK118(se)002:1510: bar khas blangs pa gsum pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:1511: dge slob ma'i bslab bya rnams ni ji srid 'tsho
