NK118(se)002:1512: dang nyin zhag gi mtha' gang du'ang mi rung bas
NK118(se)002:1513: so thar gyi sdom pa mtshan nyid par mi rung
NK118(se)002:1514: ngo // spong bdun 'khor dang bcas pa mtha' dag
NK118(se)002:1515: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du spong bar khas blangs pa'i
NK118(se)002:1516: rigs gnas bzhi pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:1517: spong bdun ni lus ngag gi nyes pa bdun po'i
NK118(se)002:1518: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba'i cha spong
NK118(se)002:1520: 'khor bcas zhes pa lus ngag gi bcas rkyang gi dbang du byas so //
NK118(se)002:1523: dge slong gi sdom pa gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud la ji ltar ldan zhe na /
NK118(se)002:1524: sdom pa gzugs can du 'dod pa'i lugs ltar na
NK118(se)002:1525: tshigs gsum rim par nod pa'i gang zag gi rgyud
NK118(se)002:1526: la rdzas tha dad du ldan par 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:1528: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK118(se)002:1530: sdom pa shes par 'dod pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK118(se)002:1531: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:1532: gtso sems gcig gi 'khor du sems pa rigs mthun
NK118(se)002:1533: rdzas gzhan gnyis mi 'byung bas ngo bo gcig pa
NK118(se)002:1534: gang zhig / thob byed kyi rgyu dang spang bya
NK118(se)002:1535: dang blang bya so sor nges pas gsum po la
NK118(se)002:1536: gzhi mthun mi srid pa'i phyir ldog pa tha dad
NK118(se)002:1537: gang zhig / pa'o // gsum pa ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i thabs la /
NK118(se)002:1540: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul la //
NK118(se)002:1542: zhes pas tshegs chung ngus rdzogs pa sngon gyi cho ga dang /
NK118(se)002:1543: tshegs dang bcas pas rdzogs pa da ltar gyi cho ga ste len tshul gnyis su nges so //
NK118(se)002:1544: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:1545: dang po sngon gyi cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:1546: rang byung ye shes khong chud 'phrin gyi rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:1547: ston par khas blangs tshur shog gsol bzhi dang //
NK118(se)002:1548: dris pa'i lan ldon lci chos khas blangs sogs //
NK118(se)002:1549: gdul bya blo dag mkhan po 'phags pas yin //
NK118(se)002:1551: da ltar gyi cho ga la ma ltos par bsgrub
NK118(se)002:1552: bya bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa'i cho ga de
NK118(se)002:1555: bye brag tu smra ba 'dul ba pa rnams na re /
NK118(se)002:1556: rnam pa bcus bsnyen par rdzogs so //
NK118(se)002:1558: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang rang sangs rgyas gnyis zad
NK118(se)002:1559: mi skye shes pa'i byang chub brnyes pa'i tshe rang
NK118(se)002:1560: byung gis dang / lnga sde bzang po mthong lam skyes tshe ye shes khong chud kyis te /
NK118(se)002:1561: de gsum ni rang rgyud la ngang gis don dam pa'i dge slong skyes pas bsnyen par rdzogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1562: sh+aa ri'i bu sogs tshur shog gis dang /
NK118(se)002:1563: 'od srungs chen po ston par khas blangs pas dang /
NK118(se)002:1564: bzang sde'i tshogs drug cu la skyabs gsum khas blangs pas dang /
NK118(se)002:1565: skye dgu'i bdag mo sogs la lci chos brgyad spong bar khas blangs pas dang /
NK118(se)002:1566: legs byin dris pa'i lan la dgyes pas bsnyen par
NK118(se)002:1567: rdzogs pa dang lnga ni ston pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK118(se)002:1568: rdzogs pa'o // mchod byin ma pha ma'i dbang du
NK118(se)002:1569: song ba la dge slong ma ut+pa las pho nya
NK118(se)002:1570: byas te dge 'dun gyis 'phrin chog la brten nas
NK118(se)002:1571: rdzogs pa'o // dang / dge 'dun gyi grangs ma
NK118(se)002:1572: mtha' yul dbus su bcu dang mtha' khob tu lnga
NK118(se)002:1573: tshogs kyis gsol bzhi'i las kyis rab byung bsnyen rdzogs
NK118(se)002:1575: 'di dag la sngon gyi bsnyen par rdzogs tshul zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1576: sngon gyi gang zag las nyon rnam smin gyi sgrib pa gsum shas chung zhing /
NK118(se)002:1577: shes rab dang rgyud dang dbang po smin pa'i gdul
NK118(se)002:1578: bya blo dag pa sha stag gi rgyud la byung
NK118(se)002:1579: ba'i bsnyen rdzogs yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:1580: gang gis rdzogs par mdzad mkhan gyi mkhan po'ang 'phags pa kho na'i khyad chos yin pas so //
NK118(se)002:1581: de ltar na sngon chog rnams mkhan slob la ltos mi dgos par bshad pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK118(se)002:1582: de dag rgyud sgrib gsum shas che zhing smin shas
NK118(se)002:1583: chung ba da ltar gyi gdul bya bzhin du tshegs
NK118(se)002:1584: chen po'i sgo nas mkhan slob kyis khrid cing skyong
NK118(se)002:1585: ba la ltos mi dgos pas de skad bshad kyi
NK118(se)002:1587: tshur shog sogs kyi tshe ston pa sangs rgyas mkhan po yin par grub la /
NK118(se)002:1588: gsol bzhi'i las kyi sngon chog byas tshe las byed
NK118(se)002:1589: pa po de'i don grub pa na slob dpon du
NK118(se)002:1591: de yang dang po bdun la gsol bzhi'i cho ga
NK118(se)002:1592: mtshan nyid pa med pas sngon chog btags pa ba
NK118(se)002:1593: dang / 'phrin ni da ltar gyi cho ga yin mod /
NK118(se)002:1594: gsol bzhi'i las kyi sngon chog la brten pa'i 'phrin
NK118(se)002:1595: chog kyang 'byung rung bas mtha' gcig tu ma nges
NK118(se)002:1596: pa'i phyir / 'dir sngon chog mtshan nyid pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1597: bcu tshogs sam lnga tshogs kyi dge 'dun la gsol btab sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:1598: gsol bzhi'i las kyis gcig car rab tu byung ba
NK118(se)002:1599: dang bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa'i cho ga nyid
NK118(se)002:1600: yin no // de la rang byung ni ston pa sangs ma rgyas pa'i sngon rol tu byung zhing /
NK118(se)002:1601: tshur shog ni sangs rgyas nas mya ngan las 'da' kha'i bar du'ang mdzad /
NK118(se)002:1602: 'di la nyes dmigs 'ga' zhig byung ba la brten nas gsol bzhi'i sngon chog gnang la /
NK118(se)002:1603: gzhan rnams sangs rgyas nas ring po ma lon par
NK118(se)002:1604: dar chog ma byung gi bar du byung bas sngon
NK118(se)002:1606: gnyis pa da ltar gyi cho ga la /
NK118(se)002:1610: sngon chog gi rjes su bcas pa mdzad pa'i gsol
NK118(se)002:1611: bzhi'i cho ga 'khor dang bcas pa de da ltar
NK118(se)002:1615: lnga tshogs sam dmigs bsal la bzhi tshogs dang /
NK118(se)002:1616: dge 'dun sde gnyis las rdzogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1617: 'phrin gyis tshigs snga phyi rim can du sgrub par byed pa rnams so //
NK118(se)002:1618: dge slong grangs mang nyung rnyed dka' sla'i khyad par
NK118(se)002:1619: gyis bcu tshogs dang lnga tshogs su 'jog pa'i yul
NK118(se)002:1622: li khar na tshang tshing nags //
NK118(se)002:1623: li khar shing 'phel shar phyogs nyid //
NK118(se)002:1624: u shi ri zhes brjod pa yi //
NK118(se)002:1625: ri bo mun pa can ni byang //
NK118(se)002:1626: ka ba nye ba'i ka ba yi //
NK118(se)002:1627: grong khyer nub na gnas pa yin //
NK118(se)002:1628: grong khyer 'dam bu can gyi drung //
NK118(se)002:1629: chu klung 'dam bu can ni lho //
NK118(se)002:1630: 'di dag gi ni bar rnams la //
NK118(se)002:1631: yul dbus su ni shes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:1632: phyi rol mtha' 'khob ces byar ni //
NK118(se)002:1633: mtha' yas mkhyen pas gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:1634: zhes sa tshigs kyis phye ba ste /
NK118(se)002:1636: lung rtogs kyi bstan pa gnas pa'i sa phyogs ni dbus so //
NK118(se)002:1637: da chog gi sgo nas sdom pa len pa'i cho ga la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:1642: dma' bar 'dug smras bzlas pa yi //
NK118(se)002:1643: mi brgyan nam ni langs bar du //
NK118(se)002:1644: bsnyen gnas yan lag tshang bar ni //
NK118(se)002:1645: nang par gzhan las nod par bya //
NK118(se)002:1647: de la bye brag tu smra ba ni /
NK118(se)002:1648: len pa po gling gsum gyi skyes pa'am bud med gang rung gis /
NK118(se)002:1649: blang yul dge slong kho na las len par bzhed /
NK118(se)002:1651: dud 'gro'i rten la'ang skye bar 'dod cing /
NK118(se)002:1652: blang yul kyang dge bsnyen gso sbyong la gnas pa yan chad las len par 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:1653: gnyis ka de ring nyi ma ma shar gong du blangs nas /
NK118(se)002:1654: zhag phyi ma'i nyi ma ma shar bar du bsrung bar bzhed pa mthun mod /
NK118(se)002:1656: zla ba byung ngo cog gi nya stong tshes brgyad
NK118(se)002:1657: la bsrung bar khas blangs pa'i gang zag des kyang
NK118(se)002:1658: phyis gang bsrung ba'i dus de dang der len dgos
NK118(se)002:1659: na'ang / sngar stabs gcig tu blangs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1660: bye smra ltar na zas zos rjes blangs kyang skye ba dang /
NK118(se)002:1661: mdo sde pa ltar na rten gyi drung du rang
NK118(se)002:1662: nyid kyis blangs kyang skye ba'i don du 'dod do
NK118(se)002:1664: skyes pa'i bslab tshigs gsum len pa'i cho ga dang /
NK118(se)002:1665: de bud med kyi bslab tshigs lnga la ji ltar sbyor tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:1671: dri dang dge bsnyen bslab pa dang //
NK118(se)002:1672: zhu dang mkhan po dang po dang //
NK118(se)002:1673: rab byung dge tshul grib tshod dang //
NK118(se)002:1674: bslab pa brjod pa tha ma yin //
NK118(se)002:1676: thog mar sngon dang zhes 'byung bas sngon chog bstan kyang /
NK118(se)002:1677: sngar bshad tshar bas 'dir dri dang zhes sbyar ro //
NK118(se)002:1682: rab byung gi mkhan po nyid du phyogs pa'i dge
NK118(se)002:1683: slong des rab tu dbyung bar rung mi rung brtag
NK118(se)002:1684: pa'i phyir bar chad dris nas /
NK118(se)002:1686: bsgrub bya de bstan pa la rim gyis gzhug pa'i phyir dge bsnyen nyid du bsgrub par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1688: skyabs su 'gro ba khas blangs pa'i tshig rtsom pa
NK118(se)002:1689: dang dge bsnyen nyid du khas blang ba'i tshig bya'o
NK118(se)002:1690: // de'i 'og tu bslab pa brjod pa khas blang ba'i tshul gyis bya'o //
NK118(se)002:1693: yul dge bsnyen las kyang len du rung bar sdom pa brgyad par bshad kyang /
NK118(se)002:1694: 'dir rab byung gi mkhan po'i sta gon nyid du gnas par ma zad /
NK118(se)002:1695: gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i lugs kyis dge slong nyid las len dgos par bshad /
NK118(se)002:1696: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa la'ang sna gcig spyod pa sogs nye tshe ba dang /
NK118(se)002:1697: yongs rdzogs gnyis las 'dir phyi ma ste /
NK118(se)002:1698: rigs brgyad kyis zlas phye ba'i dge bsnyen du 'gyur ba la /
NK118(se)002:1699: bslab gzhi lnga 'dzin pa'i yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen nyid bgrang dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:1703: bar ma rab byung gi cho ga ste /
NK118(se)002:1704: mkhan por phyogs pa'i dge slong rang nyid kyis bsgrub
NK118(se)002:1705: bya de dge bsnyen du bsgrubs zin pa'i 'og tu
NK118(se)002:1706: / mi brkus so zhes pa'i skur pa spang zhing
NK118(se)002:1707: ngo tsha khrel yod kyi bsam pa bskyed pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:1708: / / dge 'dun la rab tu byung bar zhu ba byed pa'i dge slong la gtad cing /
NK118(se)002:1709: des kyang yongs su dag gam zhes dris la /
NK118(se)002:1710: dag na mkhan po ma gtogs pa'i dge 'dun thams cad 'dus pa'am /
NK118(se)002:1711: gnas khang so sor 'khod pa la'ang rung /
NK118(se)002:1712: bsgrub bya de khrid nas zhu ba yin la /
NK118(se)002:1713: dge 'dun gyis gnang na sngar sta gon du gnas
NK118(se)002:1714: pa'i dge slong de la mkhan por gsol ba 'debs
NK118(se)002:1715: te / mkhan po de rab byung gi med na mi 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:1716: gsol ba ma btab na mkhan por mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:1717: de'i 'og tu chos 'di ba'i bsam pa bskyed pa'i phyir barje ba gsum bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1718: mkhan po bskos pa'i dge slong zhig gis spyir skra dang kha spu /
NK118(se)002:1719: bye brag gtsug phud 'breg tu 'jug na bregs te /
NK118(se)002:1721: mkhan pos yo byad lnga byin nas //
NK118(se)002:1722: rang ngam bskos pas bskon zhing mtshan brtag /
NK118(se)002:1724: rab byung gi bsam pa gsal btab nas /
NK118(se)002:1725: mkhan po rang nyid kyis bsgrub bya de bar ma rab byung du sgrub ste /
NK118(se)002:1726: skyabs su 'gro ba rtsom pas rab tu byung ba nye bar bsgrub par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:1729: mkhan pos dge tshul nyid du sgrub par byed pa'i dge slong la gtad /
NK118(se)002:1731: 'gal rkyen bar chad kyi chos bzhi dang bral zhing /
NK118(se)002:1732: mthun rkyen lnga tshang ba'i sgo nas /
NK118(se)002:1733: skyabs 'gro rtsom byed du byas te dge tshul nyid du nye bar bsgrub par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1734: dge tshul nyid du nye bar sgrub par byed pa'i dge slong la gtad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:1735: ci yongs su dag gam zhes dris nas /
NK118(se)002:1736: dag na nye bar bsgrub par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:1739: dge slong gzhan zhig gis grib tshod gzhal te dge tshul thob pa'i dus go brjod cing /
NK118(se)002:1740: slob dpon gyis dge tshul gyi bslab gzhi bcu brjod pa khas blang du gzhug go //
NK118(se)002:1741: gnyis pa tshigs phyi ma dge slong du sgrub pa'i cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:1742: dang por bya dang mkhan po dang //
NK118(se)002:1743: chos gos gnyis dang lhung bzed gnyis //
NK118(se)002:1744: spro bya gsol ba gsang ston dang //
NK118(se)002:1745: zhu dang gsol dang gsol ba dang //
NK118(se)002:1746: dri dang las dang grib tshod dang //
NK118(se)002:1747: nyin mtshan dus tshod gnas rnams dang //
NK118(se)002:1748: ltung dang dge sbyong mchog 'dod dang //
NK118(se)002:1749: tshul khrims mnyam dang tshul 'brel dang //
NK118(se)002:1750: dul dang dgos dang ma brjod dang //
NK118(se)002:1751: gus pa dang ni bsgrub bya la //
NK118(se)002:1752: mu stegs gnas pa sbyin pa yi //
NK118(se)002:1753: sde tshan yang dag bsdus pa yin //
NK118(se)002:1757: dang po bsgrub bya de lo nyi shu lon /
NK118(se)002:1758: chos gos gsum dang ltung bzed tshang /
NK118(se)002:1760: yo byad rnams tshags su bcug nas /
NK118(se)002:1761: dkon mchog gsum dang slob dpon mngon du 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyir dang por bya ba ni /
NK118(se)002:1763: skyabs 'gro'i yul du gyur pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1764: don dam pa'i dkon mchog gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:1766: gang zhig gsum la skyabs 'gro ste //
NK118(se)002:1767: sangs rgyas dge 'dun byed pa'i chos //
NK118(se)002:1768: mi slob pa dang gnyis ka dang //
NK118(se)002:1770: zhes pa la yid ches kyi dad pa dang ldan pas /
NK118(se)002:1772: brdar btags pa'i dkon mchog gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:1773: sangs rgyas ston pa'i sku gzugs /
NK118(se)002:1774: chos las kyi cho ga nan tan byed pa po'i rgyud la bzhugs pa /
NK118(se)002:1775: dge 'dun spyir btang bcu tshogs sam lnga tshogs /
NK118(se)002:1776: dmigs gsal la bzhi tshogs kyang gsungs /
NK118(se)002:1777: de'i go don mkhan po dang gsang ston med mi rung gi yan lag ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:1778: mkhan po'i bya ba rnams der gsol ba ma btab
NK118(se)002:1779: pa'i dge slong zhig gis bsgrubs kyang 'grub pa dang
NK118(se)002:1780: / bar chad ma dris kyang chog pa'i bsgrub bya srid pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:1782: mkhan por ma gsol ba la yang ngo //
NK118(se)002:1783: bar chad ma dris par yang ngo //
NK118(se)002:1785: des na mkhan por 'os pa des /
NK118(se)002:1787: slob dpon kha skong gi chos dang ldan pa'i dge slong gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:1788: dge 'dun gyi dbus su las kyi cho ga brda sprod pa la mkhas pa'i las slob dang /
NK118(se)002:1789: 'gro ba bzhi bral lkog tu bar chad dris nas
NK118(se)002:1790: nang du 'ong ba zhu ba la mkhas pa'i gsang
NK118(se)002:1791: ston du 'os pa gnyis la tshig gis gsol ba
NK118(se)002:1792: btab / de rnams kyis kyang rang rgyud la brtags te /
NK118(se)002:1793: ltung ba yod na bshags bsdams byin brlabs byas nas las gral du 'dus pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1794: gnyis pa mkhan po mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1795: spyir brtan mkhas kyi yon tan dang ldan zhing /
NK118(se)002:1796: khyad par bsgrub bya'i ngos nas mthong thos dogs gsum
NK118(se)002:1797: gyi skyon med pa'i dge slong la mkhan por gsol
NK118(se)002:1798: ba btab cing khas blangs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1799: gsum pa yo byad mngon gyur ni /
NK118(se)002:1800: mkhan pos chos gos gsum byin gyis brlabs nas gnang ba'am /
NK118(se)002:1801: drubs zin med na rgyur rung ba byin gyis brlabs nas gnang ba ste /
NK118(se)002:1803: lhung bzed dge 'dun la bstan pa dang mkhan pos
NK118(se)002:1804: byin gyis brlabs nas gnang ba ste ltung bzed gnyis
NK118(se)002:1805: so // bzhi pa yongs su dag pa mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1806: las slob tu phyogs pa'i dge slong des thog mar
NK118(se)002:1807: 'khrul bcas dang ma 'dus pa'i nyes pa khegs pa'i
NK118(se)002:1808: phyir / ltung mthun byin brlabs dang /
NK118(se)002:1809: gnas la blo mthun sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:1810: gsang ston gang yin dris nas /
NK118(se)002:1812: de spro na gsol ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las kyis gsang ston du bsko /
NK118(se)002:1813: bskos pa des kyang bar chad yod med bden par
NK118(se)002:1814: smra ba'i phyir dge 'dun gyi lkog tu bar chad
NK118(se)002:1815: dri zhing / bsgrub bya bar chad kyis dag tshul
NK118(se)002:1816: dge 'dun la brjod nas nang du 'ong bar zhu
NK118(se)002:1817: dri zhing / ba'o // lnga pa gsol ba mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1818: stod 'dul ba rnams brjod pa gsum gyi thog mar
NK118(se)002:1819: byung ba'i gsol ba la 'chad pa ni mi rigs
NK118(se)002:1820: te / las mngon du gyur pa'i tshad gsol bzhi'i las la 'chad dgos pas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:1821: des na smad 'dul ba ltar gsol ba 'debs pa'i tshig lan gsum brjod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1822: 'dir gang la gsol ba 'debs pa'i yul ni /
NK118(se)002:1823: mtshan nyid gsum dang ldan pa'i dge 'dun te grangs tshang ba /
NK118(se)002:1825: ma rdzogs nyams dang mtshams med min //
NK118(se)002:1826: sdig sa tha dad 'khrul bcas min //
NK118(se)002:1827: mtshams mtshan dkon mchog gzhan min pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1828: zhes kha skongs kyi chos dang ldan pa /
NK118(se)002:1829: ma 'dus pa dang 'dus pa phyir log gi mi mthun pa gnyis dang bral ba'o //
NK118(se)002:1831: bsnyen par rdzogs 'dod mngon du gyur pa zhes bsgrub bya ste /
NK118(se)002:1832: bsam pa thag pa nas nod par 'dod pa /
NK118(se)002:1833: nges 'byung gi bsam pa brtan pa /
NK118(se)002:1834: don go zhing nges pa lnga dang bral ba /
NK118(se)002:1835: rgyud tshogs su ma tshang ba zhig dgos so //
NK118(se)002:1836: drug pa yongs su dag par dge 'dun thugs yid
NK118(se)002:1837: ches par bya ba'i phyir nang du bar chad dri
NK118(se)002:1838: ba ni / las slob tu phyogs pas gsol ba
NK118(se)002:1839: 'ba' zhig pa'i las sngon du 'gro bas dge 'dun
NK118(se)002:1840: gyi dbus su bar chad dri ba'o //
NK118(se)002:1841: de yang yul rten gnyis ka'i ngos nas bar chad
NK118(se)002:1842: dang mi ldan par shes pa tsam gyis chog gi
NK118(se)002:1843: / don la bar chad dang mi ldan par dgos pa'i khyab pa med de /
NK118(se)002:1844: lo nyi shu ma lon pa la lon par 'du shes pa bzhin //
NK118(se)002:1846: las mngon du gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:1847: las slob tu phyogs pa'i dge slong des bsgrub bya la /
NK118(se)002:1848: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK118(se)002:1849: mkhan po slob dpon bsnyen rdzogs 'dod //
NK118(se)002:1850: yo byad yongs su dag pa dang //
NK118(se)002:1851: gsol dang las ni mngon sum mo //
NK118(se)002:1852: zhes bsdus pa'i don ltar gdams ngag gi bshad pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs kyis brda' sprad nas /
NK118(se)002:1853: chad lhag nor 'khrugs med pa'i cho ga rnam par
NK118(se)002:1854: dag pas gsol bzhi'i las byas shing chags pa'i sgo
NK118(se)002:1855: nas dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1856: de yang gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i lug la /
NK118(se)002:1858: rgyu'i rkyen rang rgyud kyi 'byung ba bzhi /
NK118(se)002:1859: bdag rkyen gzhan gyi rnam rig /
NK118(se)002:1862: skal mnyam gyi rgyu gsum gyis dge slong gi sdom
NK118(se)002:1863: pa rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs kyi ngo bor
NK118(se)002:1864: skye bar 'dod / mdo sde pa yan chad /
NK118(se)002:1865: nges 'byung gi bsam pas nyer len gyi rgyu dang /
NK118(se)002:1866: mngon gyur bcus lhan cig byed rkyen byas te sdom pa sems pa'i ngo bor skye bar 'dod do //
NK118(se)002:1867: gsum pa rjes la gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:1868: dang po bsnyen bkur gyi gnas dang gnas ma yin pa shes pa'i phyir dus go ni /
NK118(se)002:1869: dus 'gyur rkyen pas phra rim nas gzhal dgos te /
NK118(se)002:1870: thur ma sor bzhi pas grib tshod gzhal /
NK118(se)002:1871: nyin mtshan gyi cha nyi shu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK118(se)002:1872: dus tshod rnams nges par byas la brjod do //
NK118(se)002:1874: 'jig rten gyi grags pa ltar na bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:1878: ston bzhi re re la rab 'bring tha gsum du phye ba'o //
NK118(se)002:1879: phyag dar khrod kyi gos ngos bzung ba'i ched du dgun /
NK118(se)002:1882: re re la zla ba bzhi bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:1883: 'di la'ang dbyar la gsum du phye na dus tshigs lngar 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:1884: dbyar tsam gyi dus zla ba gcig /
NK118(se)002:1885: dbyar thung ngu nyin zhag gcig /
NK118(se)002:1886: dbyar ring po nyin zhag gcig gis ma tshang pa'i zla ba gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:1888: dbyar phyi ma khas len gyi dus rtogs byed de /
NK118(se)002:1889: dbyar thung ngu'i nyin zhag gcig po de la khas
NK118(se)002:1890: ma blangs na gzhan la blang du med pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:1891: ro // yang gso sbyong zhag mi thub kyi dus ngo shes pa'i ched du /
NK118(se)002:1892: dgun dpyid dbyar gsum po re re la gnyis gnyis su phye nas drug tu bshad de /
NK118(se)002:1893: dus tshigs re la zla ba gnyis gnyis yod pa'i phyed dang gnyis 'das /
NK118(se)002:1894: phyed lus pa na zhag mi thub 'dor bas gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa go nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:1895: 'o na dus tshigs kyi 'go gang nas 'dzin zhe na /
NK118(se)002:1897: sangs rgyas pa rnams kyi dus kyi dang po ni dgun dag yin la /
NK118(se)002:1898: zla ba thams cad kyi mar gyi ngo snga ste /
NK118(se)002:1899: zhes pas mar ngo sngon 'gro'i dgun nas 'go 'dzin cing /
NK118(se)002:1901: ston zla tha chung rdzogs pa'i phyi de ma thag pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:1902: ston zla tha chung gang la ngos 'dzin na /
NK118(se)002:1904: bdag gis rgyu skar smin drug brjod //
NK118(se)002:1905: zla ba nya tshe zla rangs 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:1906: ston zla tha chung zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)002:1907: 'dir ni rab tu brjod pa yin //
NK118(se)002:1908: zhes pas hor zla bcu pa smin drug gi phyed phyi ma nas dus 'go 'dzin no //
NK118(se)002:1909: de yang skabs 'dir dus tshigs la lngar phye ba nyid bzung la /
NK118(se)002:1910: brjod pa'i tshe bsgrub bya'i blo yul du 'char bde ba'i phyir lo dang /
NK118(se)002:1915: nyin mo yin na grib tshod 'di tsam gyi dus
NK118(se)002:1916: su zhes rags rim nas brjod de go bar bya'o
NK118(se)002:1917: // gnyis pa thob pa mi nyams shing 'phel bar
NK118(se)002:1918: bya ba'i phyir gdams ngag bcu gcig brjod pa la
NK118(se)002:1920: bslab byed yul can la gdams pa gnyis /
NK118(se)002:1922: bslab bya'i gtso bo dngos su brjod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1923: ma brjod pa yongs su shes pa'i thabs la gdams pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1924: dang po la rnam dag rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:1925: rten sa 'tsho ba rnam dag gnas bzhi la brten par /
NK118(se)002:1926: bsrung bya tshul khrims rnam dag rtsa ba'i ltung ba cha bcas spong bar /
NK118(se)002:1927: nyams len spyod pa rnam dag la /
NK118(se)002:1928: dge sbyong gi chos la brten par /
NK118(se)002:1929: mchog tu 'dod pa'i don grub par /
NK118(se)002:1930: gnas brtan rnams dang tshul khrims mnyam par /
NK118(se)002:1931: 'jig rten gyi pha bu'i tshul dang 'brel bar mkhan slob la gus par /
NK118(se)002:1932: grogs la sems dul bas gus pa dang lngar gdams pa dang /
NK118(se)002:1933: rtogs don lta ba rnam dag rang gi dgos pa
NK118(se)002:1934: rjes su sgrub pa lung rtogs kyi yon tan dang
NK118(se)002:1936: gnyis pa 'dir ma brjod pa slad nas shes par gdams pa rnams so //
NK118(se)002:1938: bslab pa la gus par sbyar ba dang /
NK118(se)002:1939: gus pa bskyed de slob pa'i thabs bag yod la sbyar ba'o //
NK118(se)002:1941: mu stegs gnas pa sbyin pa zhes pa ni /
NK118(se)002:1942: sh+aakya dang mu stegs ral pa can las gzhan pa'i
NK118(se)002:1943: mu stegs can la sems mgu ba brtag pa'i ched
NK118(se)002:1944: du zla ba bzhir gnas pa sbyin pa'i gsol bzhi'i
NK118(se)002:1945: las te / sbyor chog gi spros pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1947: dge bsnyen ma dang dge tshul mar sgrub pa'i cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:1948: sgrub byed dge slong gi tshab tu dge slong ma dang /
NK118(se)002:1949: bsgrub bya skyes pa'i tshab tu bud med zhes sbyar ba ma gtogs pha chog dang 'dra zhing /
NK118(se)002:1950: de rjes khyim so ma bzung na lo bco brgyad ma dang /
NK118(se)002:1951: bzung na lo bcu lon pa'i bsgrub bya mo la /
NK118(se)002:1952: yul dbus matha'i khyad par las /
NK118(se)002:1953: dge slong ma'i dge 'dun bcu gnyis dang drug tshogs
NK118(se)002:1954: kyis gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis dge slob
NK118(se)002:1956: de nas dge slong mar sgrub pa la sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK118(se)002:1958: bsgrub bya mo khyim so bzung ma bzung gi khyad
NK118(se)002:1959: par las lo nyi shu dang bcu gnyis lon pa
NK118(se)002:1960: la / dge slong ma'i dge 'dun bcu gnyis sam
NK118(se)002:1961: drug gi tshogs kyi dbus su mkhan mor phyogs pa
NK118(se)002:1962: des rdul gzan dang shing nga dpung chad gnyis bsnan
NK118(se)002:1963: te chos gos lnga sogs rtags sbyin /
NK118(se)002:1964: slob dpon ma gnyis bskos te /
NK118(se)002:1965: gsang ston mas bar chad dris pa'i rjes su bsgrub
NK118(se)002:1966: byas tshangs spyod la nyer gnas kyi sdom pa nod
NK118(se)002:1967: pa'i ched du gsol ba btab cing /
NK118(se)002:1968: de sgrub byed kyi las slob mas bar chad mngon
NK118(se)002:1969: du dris nas gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis
NK118(se)002:1970: tshangs spyod la nyer gnas kyi sdom pa sbyin /
NK118(se)002:1972: dbus matha'i khyad par gyis dge slong pha'i dge 'dun bcu'am lnga'i tshogs bsnan nas /
NK118(se)002:1973: gnyis ka'i dge 'dun la gsol ba btab la /
NK118(se)002:1974: las slob tu phyogs pa'i dge slong des gsol bzhi'i las kyis dge slong ma'i sdom pa sbyin no //
NK118(se)002:1976: gdams ngag gi skabs su gnas shing drung mi brjod /
NK118(se)002:1977: ltung ba'i skabs su thun mong ma yin pa'i pham bzhi bsnan nas pham pa brgyad dang /
NK118(se)002:1978: lci ba'i chos brgyad brjod par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:1979: 'o na dge tshul ma dang dge slong ma'i bar
NK118(se)002:1980: du thun mong min pa'i bslab tshigs gnyis med par
NK118(se)002:1981: pha'i dge 'dun tsam la brten nas dge slong ma'i
NK118(se)002:1982: sdom pa skye ba yod dam zhe na /
NK118(se)002:1983: skye la nyes byas kyi dbang du byas na skye ba yod de /
NK118(se)002:1984: tshigs snga ma med pa la nyes byas tsam du zad pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:1985: dge slong dang dge slong ma nyid dag gi las
NK118(se)002:1986: gzhan byed pas ni mi chags pa ma yin no
NK118(se)002:1989: gnyis pa gzhung gi don ni /
NK118(se)002:1990: da lta'i cho ga nges pa lnga bral zhing //
NK118(se)002:1991: ma ning la sogs skye ba'i bar chad dang //
NK118(se)002:1992: rgyal pos ma gnang la sogs gnas pa dang //
NK118(se)002:1993: bya rog skrod mi nus sogs khyad par dang //
NK118(se)002:1994: skra ser can sogs mdzes pa'i bar chad med //
NK118(se)002:1995: nges 'byung blo can skal bzang skyes bu de //
NK118(se)002:1996: legs gsungs 'dul ba rgya mtsho mtha' dag dang //
NK118(se)002:1997: brgya rtsa gcig pa'i las phran la byang ba'i //
NK118(se)002:1998: mkhan por bcas pas rim bzhin bsnyen par rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:1999: snga ma ma byas rdzogs pa'ang mdo sder snang //
NK118(se)002:2000: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi tha mar 'dod //
NK118(se)002:2002: da ltar gyi cho gas rab tu byung ba'i tshigs snga phyi len pa la /
NK118(se)002:2003: 'gal rkyen spang zhing mthun rkyen tshang dgos par bstan pa /
NK118(se)002:2004: tshigs gsum rim par nod mi nod kyi khyad par /
NK118(se)002:2005: sdom pa'i thob mtshams ngos bzung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2007: sdom pa len pa'i tshe rang rang gi bslab bya
NK118(se)002:2008: la ltos nas nges pa lnga bral dge slong la
NK118(se)002:2009: dngos dang / dge tshul la'ang cha 'dra zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2010: mthun rkyen tshang ba'i yul 'dir bsrung gi gzhan du bsrung mi nus snyam pa lta bu yul /
NK118(se)002:2011: lo'am zla ba gcig tsam du spong gi de phan chad bsrung mi nus snyam pa lta bu dus /
NK118(se)002:2012: 'thab rtsod kyi skabs ma gtogs gzhan du bsrung snyam pa lta bu tshe /
NK118(se)002:2013: dgra ma gtogs pa gzhan gyi srog mi gcod snyam pa lta bu sems can /
NK118(se)002:2014: bslab bya rags pa 'ga' zhig las phra ba rnams
NK118(se)002:2015: bsrung mi nus snyam pa lta bu yan lag nges
NK118(se)002:2016: pa ste / yan lag rgyu la dbye ba yod //
NK118(se)002:2017: ces dge tshul la yan lag nges par ma bshad pas nges pa lnga bral cha 'dra zhes bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2018: der ma zad 'gal rkyen bar chad kyi chos dang bral ba zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2019: ma ning dang mtshams med byas pa sogs ni skye ba'i bar chad de /
NK118(se)002:2020: de dag la sdom pa phog kyang mi skye ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2021: rgyal po dang pha mas ma gnang ba sogs gnas pa'i bar chad de /
NK118(se)002:2022: de dag la sdom pa skyes su zin kyang rang
NK118(se)002:2023: dbang du ma gyur pas 'bab dgos pa sogs kyis
NK118(se)002:2024: yun ring mi gnas pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2025: bya rog skrod mi nus pa'am nad dang sdug bsngal
NK118(se)002:2026: gyis gzir ba sogs khyad par du 'gyur ba'i bar
NK118(se)002:2027: chad de / sdom pa gnas kyang bslab pa la
NK118(se)002:2028: sbyor mi bzod pas yon tan khyad par du 'phags
NK118(se)002:2030: skra ser can dang lag rdum sogs lus la skyon
NK118(se)002:2031: chags pa dang gdol pa sogs rigs la skyon chags
NK118(se)002:2032: pa rnams rten mdzes pa'i bar chad de /
NK118(se)002:2033: de dag la sdom pa skye bas bsgrub bya la
NK118(se)002:2034: phan par 'gyur na'ang khyim pa rnams bstan pa la
NK118(se)002:2035: ma dad pa'i rgyu byed pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2036: des na de bzhi dang bral bas rgyud dag pa zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2037: dang po la mi skye ba dang /
NK118(se)002:2038: gnyis pa la mi gnas pas bsgrub byar phan mi thogs shing /
NK118(se)002:2039: phyi ma gnyis la skye ba dang gnas pa'i sgo nas bsgrub byar phan pas 'bogs rigs na'ang /
NK118(se)002:2040: sgrub par byed pa po la bcas 'gal gyi nyes pa cung zad 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2041: de ltar dgag phyogs nas nges pa lnga dang bral zhing ba ra chad bzhi med la /
NK118(se)002:2042: sgrub phyogs nas sngar bshad pa'i mthun rkyen thams cad tshogs shing /
NK118(se)002:2043: khyad par myang 'das gsum gang rung thob 'dod kyi
NK118(se)002:2044: nges 'byung gi bsam pas zin pa zhig dgos te
NK118(se)002:2045: / gzhan du na 'jigs skyob dang legs smon tsam du zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2046: des na 'gal rkyen spangs shing mthun rkyen tshang ba'i
NK118(se)002:2047: bsgrub bya skal ba can de nyid dge slong du
NK118(se)002:2049: sgrub byed mkhas btsun gyi yon tan dang ldan pa zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2050: de la btsun pa'i yon tan las gral du 'dus
NK118(se)002:2051: pa'i dge 'dun thams cad rang rgyud la nyes pa
NK118(se)002:2052: phra mos kyang ma gos pa'i tshul khrims rnam par
NK118(se)002:2053: dag pa dang ldan pa zhig dgos la /
NK118(se)002:2054: de'i yan lag las la 'du ba'i sngon du /
NK118(se)002:2055: thun mong ma yin pa'i ltung ba rnams bshags par bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:2056: thun mong pa rnams la byin brlabs dang /
NK118(se)002:2057: bshags yul du 'os pa yod kyang /
NK118(se)002:2058: bshags bya la ltos pa'i grangs ma longs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2059: chad las sngon du 'gro dgos pa'i rigs rnams las
NK118(se)002:2060: la 'du ba'i gong du bshags chog mi tshar ba
NK118(se)002:2061: sogs kyis ma grub pa rnams byin gyis rlob pa
NK118(se)002:2062: sogs gang la gang 'os kyis phyir bcos pa'i sgo
NK118(se)002:2064: mkhas pa'i yon tan spyir sde snod gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:2065: khyad par 'dul ba la mkhas pa /
NK118(se)002:2066: de'i nang nas kyang las byed pa la 'dul ba 'dzin pa zhes gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:2067: de'i tshad 'dul ba'i don shes pas chog pa ma yin gyi /
NK118(se)002:2068: las brgya rtsa gcig las phran so so dang bcas
NK118(se)002:2069: pa'i sngags kyi cho ga de nyid bzung nas tshig
NK118(se)002:2070: phyed kyang ma 'khrul bar kha ton du bya nus
NK118(se)002:2071: pa zhig dgos pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:2072: de ltar sngags tshig dang lag len la byang ba'i
NK118(se)002:2073: mkhan slob dge 'dun dang bcas pa mtshan nyid tshang
NK118(se)002:2074: bar tshogs pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2075: nyes med phun sum tshogs kyi dbang du byas na /
NK118(se)002:2076: tshigs gsum rim bzhin blang ba'i sgo nas bsnyen par rdzogs pa bya dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2079: dge slong nyid dag gis snga ma bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa la phyi ma mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2081: gal te tshigs snga ma gnyis sngon du ma byas
NK118(se)002:2082: na'ang bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa mi skye ba ma
NK118(se)002:2084: khyim pa rab tu ma byung ba zhig bsnyen par rdzogs par bgyid na /
NK118(se)002:2085: bsnyen par rdzogs zhes bagyi'am ma rdzogs zhes bgyi /
NK118(se)002:2086: nye ba 'khor bsnyen par rdzogs zhes bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2088: 'on kyang 'bogs byed mkhan slob dge 'dun dang bcas pa la bcas 'gal gyi nyes pa 'byung bas /
NK118(se)002:2089: skye la nyes byas kyi dbang du byas pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2090: tshigs snga ma med pa la nyes byas tsam du zad do //
NK118(se)002:2092: gzhan du mdo sde las tshigs phyi ma blangs pas
NK118(se)002:2093: snga ma zhar thob kyis ched du blang mi dgos
NK118(se)002:2094: pa'ang gnang ste / drin lan gsab pa'i mdo las /
NK118(se)002:2096: gal te khyim pa khrims lnga ma nos par thal
NK118(se)002:2097: byung du khrims bcu nos na khrims thob par 'gyur
NK118(se)002:2099: dus gcig tu dge bsnyen gyi khrims dang /
NK118(se)002:2100: dge sbyong gi khrims rnam pa gnyis thob bo //
NK118(se)002:2101: gal te khrims lnga yang ma nos /
NK118(se)002:2102: khrims bcu yang ma nos par thal byung du khrims rdzogs par nos na'ang /
NK118(se)002:2103: dus gcig tu khrims gsum char thob par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:2106: tshigs snga ma gnyis la sngags tshigs lan gsum bzlas pa'i tha mar /
NK118(se)002:2110: bdag brjod rdzogs pa dge bsnyen du'am /
NK118(se)002:2111: dge tshul du zhes rdzogs ma thag /
NK118(se)002:2112: de dang de'i sdom pa skye zhing /
NK118(se)002:2113: tshogs phyi ma dge slong ni /
NK118(se)002:2114: dge 'dun gyis gsol bzhi'i las nyams su myong ba la rag las pas na /
NK118(se)002:2115: las brjod pa gsum pa la /
NK118(se)002:2116: mchi ste yan chad ngo bo brjod pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2117: sdom pa'i rgyu rkyen tshang bas bsnyen par rdzogs rigs pa'i ngo bo brjod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2118: gsol na zhes pa yan chad bya ba brjod pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2119: bsnyen par rdzogs par bya ba brjod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2120: de'i slad du man chad byed pa brjod pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2121: byed pa po dge 'dun byed pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2122: des na bya ba brjod pa rdzogs ma thag der sdom pa skye ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:2123: brjod pa tha ma gang yin pa'i cha gsum pa la grub pa nyid do //
NK118(se)002:2125: de dang de'i tshe byed pa po de yang slob dpon du 'gyur ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:2126: don grub na gyur pa nyid do //
NK118(se)002:2127: zhes dge bsnyen sogs don grub pa nyid kyis slob dpon du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2128: bzhi pa thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba'i tshul la /
NK118(se)002:2131: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba la //
NK118(se)002:2133: ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i cho gas sdom
NK118(se)002:2134: pa dang por thob pa tsam gyis mi chog gi
NK118(se)002:2135: / de bar du thob zin mi nyams par bsrung ba la bslab dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2136: ma bsrungs na nyes dmigs dang /
NK118(se)002:2137: bsrungs na phan yon chen po dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2138: dge slong la rab tu gces pa'i mdo las /
NK118(se)002:2139: la la'i tshul khrims bde ba ste //
NK118(se)002:2140: la la'i tshul khrims sdug bsngal yin //
NK118(se)002:2141: tshul khrims ldan pa bde ba ste //
NK118(se)002:2142: tshul khrims 'chal ba sdug bsngal yin //
NK118(se)002:2144: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:2145: dngos bstan blang dor gyi bslab bya rgyas par bshad /
NK118(se)002:2146: shugs bstan de'i rung mthun bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2148: khyim pa'i phyogs su gtogs pa'i dang /
NK118(se)002:2149: rab tu byung ba'i phyogs su gtogs pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2155: thun min dkon mchog gsum so so la skyabs su song ba'i bslab bya dang /
NK118(se)002:2156: gsum ka'i thun mong gi bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2158: bslab bya skyabs 'gro thun mong min gsum ni //
NK118(se)002:2159: skyabs gzhan mi 'tshol sems can 'tshe ba spong //
NK118(se)002:2160: mu stegs mi 'grogs so sor gus bskyed do //
NK118(se)002:2164: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su
NK118(se)002:2165: song nas so so'i bslab bya ni rim pa ji
NK118(se)002:2166: lta bar / skyabs gzhan 'jig rten pa'i lha la re ltos bkal nas skyabs 'gro mi bya /
NK118(se)002:2168: grogs mu stegs can dang mi 'grogs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2169: de dag dang 'gal na dkon mchog gsum po de dang de'i skyabs 'gro gtong ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2171: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs 'gro ba //
NK118(se)002:2172: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen te //
NK118(se)002:2173: nam du'ang lha ni gzhan dag la //
NK118(se)002:2174: skyabs su 'gro ba ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:2175: dam pa'i chos la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK118(se)002:2176: 'tshe zhing gnod pa'i sems dang bral //
NK118(se)002:2178: mu stegs can dang 'grogs mi bya //
NK118(se)002:2181: sangs rgyas kyi sku'i rten sats+tsha'i chag dum tsam dang /
NK118(se)002:2182: chos kyi rten yig 'bru gcig tsam dang /
NK118(se)002:2183: dge 'dun gyi gzugs lhan pa ser po btab pa
NK118(se)002:2184: yan chad la dkon mchog de dang de'i 'du shes
NK118(se)002:2185: bzhag nas gus par bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2187: srog dang bya dgar dkon mchog gsum mi spang //
NK118(se)002:2188: dgos gal che yang thabs gzhan mi 'tshol zhing //
NK118(se)002:2189: dus mchod mi bcag rang gzhan skyabs 'gror 'god //
NK118(se)002:2190: gar 'gro'i phyogs kyi sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK118(se)002:2191: lnga rnams thun mong bslab byar jo bo bzhed //
NK118(se)002:2193: srog dang rgyal srid la sogs pa'i ched du'ang dkon mchog mi spang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:2194: dgos gal ji ltar che yang dkon mchog la blo
NK118(se)002:2195: gtod pa las 'jig rten pa'i thabs gzhan mi 'tshol
NK118(se)002:2196: ba dang / rtag tu yon tan dran pas dus kyi mchod pa mi bcag pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2197: phan yon shes pas rang skyabs su 'gro zhing gzhan dag kyang 'gror gzhugs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2198: gar 'gro'i phyogs kyi sangs rgyas dang de'i sku gzugs la phyag 'tshal ba dang lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:2200: dus khrims bsnyen gnas dngos kyi bslab bya dang /
NK118(se)002:2201: de gtan khrims su byas na go mi'i dge bsnyen du 'gro tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:2203: rtsa bzhi spong ba tshul khrims yan lag bzhi //
NK118(se)002:2204: chang spong bag yod yan lag mal che mtho //
NK118(se)002:2205: gar phreng la sogs phyi dro'i kha zas gsum //
NK118(se)002:2206: brtul bzhugs yan lag bsnyen gnas sdom pa yin //
NK118(se)002:2207: yan lag 'di brgyad gtan du ma yin pas //
NK118(se)002:2208: yon tan rten min de phyir so thar ni //
NK118(se)002:2209: mtshan nyid ldan pa rigs bdun kho na yin //
NK118(se)002:2212: tshul khrims yan lag bag yod pa'i //
NK118(se)002:2213: yan lag brtul zhugs yan lag ste //
NK118(se)002:2214: bzhi gcig de bzhin gsum rim bzhin //
NK118(se)002:2215: zhes pa ltar mi tshangs spyod sogs rtsa ba'i ltung ba bzhi spong ba tshul khrims kyi /
NK118(se)002:2216: chang spong ba bag yod kyi /
NK118(se)002:2219: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas te gsum spong ba brtul zhugs kyi yan lag ste /
NK118(se)002:2220: yan lag 'di brgyad po nyin zhag gi mtha' tshun
NK118(se)002:2221: chad du khas blangs pa'i dus khrims yin gyi gtan
NK118(se)002:2222: khrims ma yin pas sdom pa gong ma rnams kyi
NK118(se)002:2223: yon tan gyi rten du mi rigs pa'i phyir ma
NK118(se)002:2224: yin la / des na gong ma'i yon tan gyi
NK118(se)002:2225: rten du gyur pa'i mtshan nyid can ni rigs bdun
NK118(se)002:2228: so so thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK118(se)002:2229: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK118(se)002:2230: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK118(se)002:2231: skal pa yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK118(se)002:2234: 'di brgyad ji srid 'tsho yi bar bsrungs na //
NK118(se)002:2235: go mi'i dge bsnyen yin kyang yod smra'i min //
NK118(se)002:2236: gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed //
NK118(se)002:2238: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad ji srid 'tsho'i bar du khas len pa go mi'i dge bsnyen te /
NK118(se)002:2239: 'di gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba las ma bshad na'ang /
NK118(se)002:2240: 'phags pa gnas brtan pa'i sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed de /
NK118(se)002:2241: go mi'i dge bsnyen zhes bya ba 'di ni 'phags
NK118(se)002:2242: pa gnas brtan pa'i man ngag brgyad pa las thos
NK118(se)002:2243: kyi bde bar gshegs pas gsungs pa ni ma mthong
NK118(se)002:2245: 'on kyang theg chen gyi sde snod las gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:2246: rgyal bu snying rje cher sems kyis bsnyen gnas yan
NK118(se)002:2247: lag brgyad ji srid 'tsho'i bar du blangs par dkon
NK118(se)002:2248: brtsegs las bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2249: gsum pa dge bsnyen gyi bslab bya la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:2250: dge bsnyen gyi spang bya lnga ngos bzung /
NK118(se)002:2251: de bsrung tshul gyi grangs las dge bsnyen gyi dbye ba bshad /
NK118(se)002:2252: phyogs mthun gyi bslab bya bstan pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2254: gsod rku rdzun smra 'dod pas log par g.yem //
NK118(se)002:2255: myos 'gyur spong rnams dge bsnyen sdom pa ste //
NK118(se)002:2256: zhes pas dge bsnyen gyi spang bya la rtsa ba dang /
NK118(se)002:2260: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2261: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2263: 'di dag la yul gyi yan lag tu mi yin pa dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2264: de ma tshang na rtsa bar gtogs pa'i nyes pa tsam du zad kyi /
NK118(se)002:2265: rtsa ba dngos ma yin pas sdom pa nyams par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK118(se)002:2266: 'dir bslab gzhir mi tshangs spyod mi 'jog par 'dod log 'jog pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2267: khyim pas bsrung sla ba la sogs kyi phyir te /
NK118(se)002:2269: log g.yem shin tu dmad phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:2270: sla phyir mi byed thob phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2274: de ma spangs na bslab pa gzhan rnams bsrung mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2276: bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba //
NK118(se)002:2277: myos 'gyur las gzhan srung phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2280: de las phye ba nyan thos sde pa'i lugs dang /
NK118(se)002:2281: de las gzhan pa sde pa gzhan gyi lugs so //
NK118(se)002:2283: gang 'dod khas len grangs ltar sna gcig spyod //
NK118(se)002:2284: sna 'ga' phal cher spyod dang yongs rdzogs spyod //
NK118(se)002:2285: gcig gnyis gsum dang lnga spong zhes pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2286: skyabs 'gro blangs nas de'i bslab bya tsam bsrung ba
NK118(se)002:2287: skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen zhes sngar bshad pa
NK118(se)002:2288: de la / nyi 'og pa dang mdo sde pa dag /
NK118(se)002:2289: de dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa ma yin yang dge bsnyen mtshan nyid pa yin zer /
NK118(se)002:2291: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa med na /
NK118(se)002:2292: de dge bsnyen mtshan nyid pa ma yin par 'dod /
NK118(se)002:2293: bshad ma thag pa'i dge bsnyen gyi spang bya lnga las /
NK118(se)002:2294: srog gcod tsam spong ba sna gcig spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2295: de'i steng ma byin len tsam spong ba sna 'ga' spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2296: de gnyis kyi steng rdzun dang gsum spong ba phal cher spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2297: de gsum gyi steng du 'dod log dang chang ste lnga char spong ba yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen no //
NK118(se)002:2298: de bzhin la bye brag tu smra ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:2299: sdom pa len pa'i tshe dge bsnyen tsam du khas
NK118(se)002:2300: blangs nas phyis bsrung dus sna gcig sogs gang 'dod
NK118(se)002:2301: bsrung ba la de dag spyod ces 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:2303: sna gcig spyod sogs ji lta bu //
NK118(se)002:2304: de bsrung ba la bsrung zhes grags //
NK118(se)002:2307: len pa'i tshe bdag sna gcig spyod pa'i dge bsnyen
NK118(se)002:2308: du bzung du gsol zhes pa lta bu gang 'dod
NK118(se)002:2309: khas blangs nas de bsrung ba ste /
NK118(se)002:2310: de las gzhan du yongs rdzogs blangs nas phyis de ma bsrungs na tshul 'chal du 'gyur pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2314: mi tshangs spyod spong tshangs spyod dge bsnyen no //
NK118(se)002:2315: 'di dang go mi gnyis ni khyim pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2316: rab byung gnyis ka min zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK118(se)002:2318: yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi spang bya'i steng mi tshangs
NK118(se)002:2319: spyod spong ba ni tshangs spyod kyi dge bsnyen te
NK118(se)002:2320: / rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod la //
NK118(se)002:2321: zhes sogs kyis bstan par mdo sde pa 'dod cing /
NK118(se)002:2322: 'di dang go mi'i dge bsnyen gnyis cho 'phrul bstan pa'i mdo las kyang gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:2324: rab byung yon tan du ma ldan pa zhes //
NK118(se)002:2325: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis basngagasa mod kyi //
NK118(se)002:2326: sems can kun la snying rjer gyur pas na //
NK118(se)002:2327: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis rgyal srid sgrub //
NK118(se)002:2328: ji srid 'tsho'i bar tshangs par spyod byed cing //
NK118(se)002:2329: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa'ang blang bar bgyi //
NK118(se)002:2331: 'di gnyis khyim pa dang rab byung gnyis ka ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:2332: khyim thab spang bas 'dod pa 'khrig bcas kyi khyim pa ma yin pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:2333: rab byung gi rtags ma blangs pas de yang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2334: gsum pa dge bsnyen gyi phyogs mthun gyi bslab bya la /
NK118(se)002:2336: sngags pa khyim pas kyang 'dul ba'i bslab bya la gces spras bya dgos par gdams pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2338: mi dge lhag drug phyogs mthun spang bya dang //
NK118(se)002:2340: spyir mi dge ba bcu las mi gsod pa sogs lus kyi las gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:2341: ngag gi rdzun smra ba rnams ni rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2342: de bzhi byung na sdom pa gtong bas slar blang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:2343: mi ma yin gsod pa sogs bzhi dang chang 'thung
NK118(se)002:2344: ba'i nyes pa ste lnga byung na sdom ldan gyi
NK118(se)002:2345: drung du bshags / de las gzhan pa phra ma
NK118(se)002:2346: sogs ngag gi las gsum dang yid kyi gsum ste
NK118(se)002:2347: mi dge ba lhag ma drug ni phyogs mthun gyi
NK118(se)002:2348: drung du bshags / spang bya ste / de dag
NK118(se)002:2349: kyang 'gyod sdom gyi sems kyis phyir 'chos par bya
NK118(se)002:2350: drung du bshags / spang bya ste / ba yin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2351: dge bsnyen sdom ldan rig pa 'dzin pas kyang //
NK118(se)002:2352: rab byung rtags dang cho ga ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)002:2353: lhag rnams nyams su len par dpung bzang bshad //
NK118(se)002:2355: dge bsnyen gyi sdom ldan sngags la zhugs pa yin na /
NK118(se)002:2356: de lta bu'i dge bsnyen rig pa 'dzin pa des kyang /
NK118(se)002:2357: ngur smrig bgo ba dang lhung bzed 'chang ba sogs rab byung gi rtags kyi bskor dang /
NK118(se)002:2358: las kyi cho ga dang bcas rkyang 'ga' zhig ma
NK118(se)002:2359: gtogs lhag rnams 'dul ba nas ji ltar 'byung ba
NK118(se)002:2360: bzhin du nyams su len dgos par gsungs na sngags
NK118(se)002:2361: pa rab byung gis lta smos kyang ci dgos te
NK118(se)002:2363: rgyal ba ngas gsungs so so thar pa yi //
NK118(se)002:2364: tshul khrims rnam dag 'dul ba ma lus las //
NK118(se)002:2365: sngags pa khyim pas rtags dang cho ga spang //
NK118(se)002:2366: lhag ma rnams ni nyams su blang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:2368: gnyis pa rab tu byung ba'i phyogs su gtogs pa'i bslab bya la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:2374: phyogs mthun bsdam bya'i nyes byas /
NK118(se)002:2375: rab byung gi dus su blangs pa las 'das pa'i phyogs mthun no //
NK118(se)002:2377: srog gcod rku dang mi tshangs spyod dang rdzun //
NK118(se)002:2378: chang 'thung gar sogs phreng sogs mal che mtho //
NK118(se)002:2379: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul spong ba ste //
NK118(se)002:2380: zhum pa spang phyir rags pa bcur dril gsungs //
NK118(se)002:2383: dngos su bshad pa rags pa bcu /
NK118(se)002:2384: de las zhib mor rtsis na sum cu rtsa gsum du 'gyur ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2386: bri dzi'i bu bzhin du bslab gzhi mang po thos pas zhum ste /
NK118(se)002:2387: sdom pa len pa las ldog pa spang ba'i ched
NK118(se)002:2388: du rags pa bcur dril nas gsungs pa'ang gnyis su
NK118(se)002:2391: dang po bzhi la rtsa ba zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:2392: bsrungs na tshul khrims su 'gyur zhing ma bsrungs na khrims 'chal du 'gyur bas so //
NK118(se)002:2393: phyi ma drug la yan lag ces bya ste /
NK118(se)002:2394: rtsa ba bzhi po de bsrung ba'i thabs su gyur pas de skad ces bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2395: de yang chang gis dran pa nyams par byed pas de spang ba bag yod kyi yan lag dang /
NK118(se)002:2396: gzhan lnga brtul zhugs kyi yan lag ste /
NK118(se)002:2397: gar sogs kyis dregs pa bskyed cing gser dngul len
NK118(se)002:2398: pa gsog 'jog gi rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyir ro
NK118(se)002:2399: // de la dge tshul gyi ltung ba thams cad
NK118(se)002:2400: nyes byas kho nar 'dus pas pham 'dra'i nyes byas
NK118(se)002:2401: // ni / mi'am mir chags pa'i srog bcad pa /
NK118(se)002:2402: rin thang tshang ba'i dngos po rku ba /
NK118(se)002:2404: mi chos bla ma'i rdzun smra ba ste /
NK118(se)002:2405: 'di bzhi la dge slong gi skabs su 'chad 'gyur
NK118(se)002:2406: ltar gzhi bsam sbyor ba mthar thug gi yan lag
NK118(se)002:2407: tshang na pham 'dra'i nyes byas su 'gyur zhing /
NK118(se)002:2408: 'chab med la gsor rung dang 'chab bcas byung na gsor mi rung ba'ang dge slong dang 'dra ste /
NK118(se)002:2410: mi gsod la sogs bzhi rnams kyis //
NK118(se)002:2411: dge tshul las ni nyams byung na //
NK118(se)002:2412: dge slong bzhin du dge tshul la'ang //
NK118(se)002:2413: phyi nas sdom skye'i skal ba med //
NK118(se)002:2415: bshags bya'i nyes byas la drug ste /
NK118(se)002:2417: rgod bag gis rang dgar glu gar rtse zhing rol mo 'khrol ba ste gar sogs gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:2418: 'phyor sgeg gis rgyan phreng 'dogs pa kha dog 'chang ba spos byug pa ste phreng sogs gsum /
NK118(se)002:2419: rgyu rin thang can dang khru gang las lhag pa'i mal che mtho /
NK118(se)002:2420: phyi dro dus rung gi zas la spyod pa /
NK118(se)002:2421: gser dngul len pa spong ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2423: rtsa bzhi gsod gsum bzhi med nas //
NK118(se)002:2424: sun 'byin bar lnga shes bzhin bshes //
NK118(se)002:2425: 'phya dang zas cung lhag mas skur //
NK118(se)002:2427: gar gsum phreng gsum mal che mtho //
NK118(se)002:2428: dus min rin chen bar ma gsum //
NK118(se)002:2429: de ltar sum cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:2432: srog gcod kyi pham 'dra'i char gtogs dud 'gro gsod pa /
NK118(se)002:2433: srog chags dang bcas pa'i rtsa dang chur 'debs pa /
NK118(se)002:2434: srog chags dang bcas pa'i chur spyod pa ste gsod pa gsum /
NK118(se)002:2437: bag tsam gyis pham pa'i skur 'debs /
NK118(se)002:2441: shes bzhin rdzun du smra ba /
NK118(se)002:2444: zas cung zad kyi phyir chos ston zhes skur 'debs /
NK118(se)002:2446: bslab pa la khyad gsod kyis spong ba /
NK118(se)002:2447: lhag po len phyir 'bras chan 'gebs pa ste bcu gnyis /
NK118(se)002:2448: de ltar rtsa bzhi dang de'i char gtogs bco lnga ste bcu dgu /
NK118(se)002:2452: mal che mtho rnams so sor grangs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2454: gser dngul len pa rnams bsnan pas sum cu dang /
NK118(se)002:2455: 'og nas 'byung ba'i nyams pa gsum dang bcas pas blangs 'das sum cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:2458: rdzun las 'bras chan 'gebs pa dor ba'i lhag bcu gcig ste bcu bzhi po sngar ltar las /
NK118(se)002:2459: de'i steng du ma byin len gyi char gtogs khang pa /
NK118(se)002:2461: rin po che'i khab ral byed pa gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:2462: mi tshangs spyod kyi char gtogs dge 'dun gyis spangs
NK118(se)002:2463: pa'i mtshan mi mthun pa dang lhan cig nyal ba
NK118(se)002:2464: spong ba / rtsa ba bzhi ga'i char gtogs gso sbyong /
NK118(se)002:2467: gnas slob la bsten nas gnas pa rnams ste /
NK118(se)002:2468: rtsa ltung bzhi'i char gtogs nyer gnyis su bzhed do //
NK118(se)002:2469: gnyis pa phyogs mthun bsdam bya'i nyes byas ni /
NK118(se)002:2470: chos gos lhung bzed 'chang ba 'bral ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2471: sa rko rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK118(se)002:2472: spangs nas za dang shing 'dzeg shing gcod dang //
NK118(se)002:2473: byin len r+ts+wa sngon khrod du mi gtsang 'dor //
NK118(se)002:2474: gsog 'jog za dang sa bon 'joms pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:2475: gnang bas nyes med bcu gsum ma gtogs pa /
NK118(se)002:2476: dge slong ji bzhin spang blang mtha' dag gcig /'chang
NK118(se)002:2477: ba'i zlar bsdu gos rgyu zla bar 'jog /'bral ba'i
NK118(se)002:2478: zlar bsdu dgon pa'i 'bras spang byed //
NK118(se)002:2479: gsog 'jog zlar bsdu gsog 'jog byed pa'ang gnang //
NK118(se)002:2481: nyes med bcu gsum po 'di ni bstan bcos bye brag bshad pa las /
NK118(se)002:2483: de bzhin sa ni rko ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2484: rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK118(se)002:2485: spangs nas za bar byed pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2486: ljon shing 'dzeg dang shing gcod dang //
NK118(se)002:2487: byin len ma byas za ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2488: rtsa sngon mi gtsang 'dor ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2489: de bzhin gsog 'jog za ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2490: sa bon 'joms dang bslab pa'i gzhi //
NK118(se)002:2491: bcu po rnams ni ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)002:2492: so so thar par bstan pa dag /
NK118(se)002:2493: blangs pa'i phyogs mthun shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:2494: zhes gsungs pa'i 'chang ba la gnyis su phye bas nyes med bcu gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:2495: de'i steng du bod kyi 'dul 'dzin rnams kyis rung mthun sbyar ba la /
NK118(se)002:2497: ma smras 'dun sgyur ma rdzogs nyal //
NK118(se)002:2498: zhes pa ltar drug bsnan nas nyes med bcu dgur 'dod cing /
NK118(se)002:2501: gsog 'jog gi spang ba rnams nyes med du zhu
NK118(se)002:2502: ba kha che ba las dngos su bshad ces mkhas
NK118(se)002:2503: mchog bu ston rin po ches gsungs pa ltar mdzad
NK118(se)002:2505: dor nas las kyi gnas nas mi smra bar 'gro
NK118(se)002:2506: la / ba dang / dge tshul nang du nub
NK118(se)002:2507: lhag nyal bsrung mi dgos kyang khyim pa dang bsrung
NK118(se)002:2509: de ltar nyes med phyed dang bco brgyad do zhes bzhed /
NK118(se)002:2510: gang ltar yang bslab pa'i gzhi /
NK118(se)002:2511: bcu po rnams ni ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)002:2512: zhes sngar drangs pa ltar gyi dngos su blangs 'das
NK118(se)002:2513: rnams pham 'dra dang bshags bya'i nyes byas ci rigs
NK118(se)002:2514: su 'gyur ba'i phyir de rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:2515: gnang ba'i nyes med rnams ma gtogs pa'i gzhi dang
NK118(se)002:2516: rnam 'byed nas bshad pa'i spang blang phal cher dge
NK118(se)002:2517: slong ltar las / de thams cad dge tshul gyi
NK118(se)002:2518: skabs 'dir phyogs mthun gyi nyes byas su 'gyur zhing
NK118(se)002:2519: slong ltar las / / de dag bshags yul la
NK118(se)002:2520: mi ltos par yid kyis bsdams pa tsam gyis 'dag
NK118(se)002:2521: slong ltar las / / pa yin te / mdo rtsar /
NK118(se)002:2522: de'i phyogs dang mthun pa la ni yid kyi'o //
NK118(se)002:2524: gsum pa rab byung gi dus su blangs pa las 'das pa'i phyogs mthun ni /
NK118(se)002:2525: khyim rtags spong nyams rab byung rtags len nyams //
NK118(se)002:2526: brnyas pas mkhan por nyams te nyams pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:2527: spang ba dge tshul sdom pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2530: rab byung gi rtags len pa /
NK118(se)002:2531: mkhan por gsol ba btab pa rnams las nyams pa'i phyogs mthun gyi nyes pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2532: gal te 'di gsum rab byung gi blangs 'das dngos dang khyad par yod dam med /
NK118(se)002:2533: med na dge tshul gyi blangs 'das su ji ltar 'gyur /
NK118(se)002:2534: yod na khyad par gang yin zhe na /
NK118(se)002:2535: de'i khyad par yod tshul 'di yin te /
NK118(se)002:2536: rab byung gi sdom pas ma bsdams pa'i rab byung
NK118(se)002:2537: bar ma tsam zhig blangs pa des ni bar ma'i
NK118(se)002:2538: dus thob pa'i blangs 'das dngos gsum po de bsrungs
NK118(se)002:2540: gal te de ma bsrungs na rab byung gtong byed kyi rgyur yang gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:2541: bsam pa thag pa nas khyim pa'i rtags nyin gcig tsam blangs pas kyang de gtong ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2543: bar ma shugs blangs bya ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2544: don tshe rtsa ba chad pa las //
NK118(se)002:2546: dge tshul gyis ni bar ma'i dus dngos su blangs pa gsum du ma zad /
NK118(se)002:2547: de'i phyogs mthun sum brgya par rgyas par bshad pa rnams kyang bsrung dgos pa'i khyad par yod cing /
NK118(se)002:2548: phyogs mthun rnams kyis ni bar ma gtong ba'ang ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:2549: 'dir bshags bya dang bsdam bya'i nyes byas ci rigs su bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2550: gnyis pa dge slob ma'i bslab bya ni /
NK118(se)002:2551: dge slob ma ni dge tshul thob pa'i steng //
NK118(se)002:2552: zhes pas dge tshul gyi bslab gzhi bcu thob pa'i
NK118(se)002:2553: steng du dge slob ma'i sdom pa blangs nas lo
NK118(se)002:2554: gnyis su de'i bslab bya la slob pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2557: rjes mthun gyi chos drug go //
NK118(se)002:2559: gcig 'gro chur rgyal skyes reg lhan cig 'dug /
NK118(se)002:2560: smyan bya nyes 'chab rtsa ba'i chos drug go //
NK118(se)002:2563: gcig pur lam du mi 'gro zhing //
NK118(se)002:2564: chu bo'i pha rol rkyal mi bya //
NK118(se)002:2565: skyes pa la ni mi reg cing //
NK118(se)002:2566: de dang lhan cig 'dug mi bya //
NK118(se)002:2567: kha na ma tho mi 'chab cing //
NK118(se)002:2568: gnyen du 'gyur bar mi bya ste //
NK118(se)002:2569: rtsa ba'i chos drug 'di dag ni //
NK118(se)002:2570: dge slob ma la gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:2573: gser bzung 'doms spu 'dreg dang sa rko spang //
NK118(se)002:2574: byin len med dang gsog 'jog byas mi za //
NK118(se)002:2575: r+ts+wa sngon mi gcod 'di rnams rjes mthun drug /
NK118(se)002:2578: sa le sbram ni len pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2579: gsang ba'i gnas kyi spu 'dreg dang //
NK118(se)002:2580: sa rnams rko bar byed pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2581: r+ts+wa sngon la sogs gcod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2582: byin len ma byas za ba dang //
NK118(se)002:2583: gsog 'jog byas pa za ba las //
NK118(se)002:2584: ldog pa zhes bya de bzhin gzhan //
NK118(se)002:2585: rjes mthun chos ni drug tu 'dod //
NK118(se)002:2587: de dag dge slob ma'i blangs pa las 'das pa'i nyes byas yin la /
NK118(se)002:2589: nyes med bdun ma gtogs pa dge slong ma'i bslab
NK118(se)002:2590: gzhi gzhan dag ni 'dir blangs pa'i phyogs mthun yin
NK118(se)002:2591: pas / de dag las 'das na yid kyi bsdam bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2592: de la nyes med bdun ni /
NK118(se)002:2594: spangs pa za dang sa bon 'jig /
NK118(se)002:2595: r+ts+wa sngon yod pa'i phyogs dag tu //
NK118(se)002:2598: gsum pa dge slong gi bslab bya la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:2599: gang zag gzhan la brten nas bsrung ba //
NK118(se)002:2600: rang gi bsam sbyor phun sum tshogs pas bsrung ba //
NK118(se)002:2601: ji ltar bsrung ba'i bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2603: dge tshul dang bsnyen rdzogs byas ma thag pa des /
NK118(se)002:2604: rang nyid bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo bcu bar ma
NK118(se)002:2605: chad du lon pa dang lnga phrugs dang ldan pa
NK118(se)002:2606: ste brtan mkhas kyi yon tan gnyis dang ldan pa
NK118(se)002:2607: ma byung gi bar du gnas kyi bla ma khyad
NK118(se)002:2608: par can la bsten nas blang dor ma nor bar
NK118(se)002:2609: byed pa ste / de la gnas dang gnas pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:2611: tshul khrims ldan zhing 'dul ba'i cho ga bshad /
NK118(se)002:2612: nad par snying brtse 'khor ni dag pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2613: chos dang zang zing phan 'dogs kyis brtson pa //
NK118(se)002:2614: dus su 'doms pa de dag bla mar basngagasa //
NK118(se)002:2615: zhes pas brtan mkhas phan 'dogs kyi yon tan dang ldan pa gnas kyi mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:2617: slob dpon la gus tshul khrims yang dag dang //
NK118(se)002:2618: bsam gtan dang ni 'don la rtag brtson dang //
NK118(se)002:2619: grims shing dul la bzod dang ldan pa ni //
NK118(se)002:2620: sdom brtson gnas pa'i chos ldan shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:2621: zhes gnas pa slob ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK118(se)002:2622: gnas ji ltar bca' tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:2623: mkhan po yod na der gyur pa nyid kyis gnas
NK118(se)002:2624: kyi bla mar yang gyur zin yin pas gnas gsar
NK118(se)002:2626: mkhan po de nyid gnas nyid yin no //
NK118(se)002:2628: mkhan po med na bla mar 'os pa'i dge slong zhig la gnas 'cha' ba'i cho ga byas te /
NK118(se)002:2629: lhan cig gnas nas zhag gnyis pa'i skya rengs shar
NK118(se)002:2630: ba'i tshe de nyid gnas kyi slob dpon du 'gyur
NK118(se)002:2631: zhing / bla ma gcig gi 'khor du gnas pa dge slong gi tshogs mang po dag rung mod /
NK118(se)002:2632: dge tshul ni gcig las bzhag tu mi rung bar bshad la /
NK118(se)002:2633: de yang nub gsum las lhag par lhan cig gnas su mi rung bas /
NK118(se)002:2634: lhan cig gnas pa zhes ni mi bya ste /
NK118(se)002:2636: gnas kyi slob dpon la brten tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:2637: gnas pas gnas la ma zhugs par bya ba mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2638: zhes pas nye 'khor gyi mchod rten la phyag bya ba dang gshang gci 'dor ba /
NK118(se)002:2639: zhag gcig gnas gzhan du phyin pa la sogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:2640: bya ba dang dus kyi dmigs bsal gsungs pa rnams
NK118(se)002:2641: ma gtogs bya ba thams cad rang nyams su mi
NK118(se)002:2642: gtong bar de la zhu zhing /
NK118(se)002:2643: des kyang legs par 'doms pa'i sgo nas tshul bzhin du bsten pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:2644: gnas bcas pa 'jig pa'i rgyu ni /
NK118(se)002:2645: gnyis ka la ltos med kyi 'du shes skyes pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2650: blang dor la spro ba'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK118(se)002:2651: 'jug ldog gi gnas la gzob pa lhur len pa'i bag yod dang /
NK118(se)002:2652: rang rgyud la nyes pa byung ma byung rtog pa'i shes bzhin rnams la rtag tu bsten dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2653: nyes pa 'byung ba'i rgyu'i gtso bo ni /
NK118(se)002:2657: nyon mongs pa mang ba rnams yin pas /
NK118(se)002:2658: de dag rnam par sun 'byin pa'i gnyen po brten par bya dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2660: rang gis ji ltar khas blangs pa'i blang dor gyi
NK118(se)002:2661: gnas rnams shes pa'i ched du 'dul ba'i sde snod
NK118(se)002:2662: la thos bsam legs par bya dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2664: de nas rab tu byung ba yis //
NK118(se)002:2665: dang por bslab la rab gus bya //
NK118(se)002:2666: so so thar pa 'dul bcas pa //
NK118(se)002:2667: mang thos don gtan dbab la bsgrims //
NK118(se)002:2674: yan lag gi don gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:2678: phan yon can gyi bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2680: ston pas gang la brten nas bslab pa 'cha' bar
NK118(se)002:2681: mdzad pa byung ba dang bcas pa'i gleng gzhi rnams
NK118(se)002:2684: nyon mongs pa ji lta bus /
NK118(se)002:2685: nyes pa gang byas pa rnams kyis shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2686: 'o na bcas pa mdzad pa dus nam gyi tshe yin zhe na /
NK118(se)002:2687: kha cig da ltar gyi cho ga dang dus mtshungs par byung ba dang bcas pa mdzad zer kyang /
NK118(se)002:2689: ston pa sangs rgyas nas lo drug pa la 'char ka dar chog gis rdzogs par bshad cing /
NK118(se)002:2690: bcas pa mdzad pa ni lo bcu gnyis 'das nas yin par gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2693: ston ka'i chu bzhin dri med par //
NK118(se)002:2694: ston pa'i bstan pa bcu gnyis lor //
NK118(se)002:2695: ltung ba med par legs gnas te /
NK118(se)002:2696: nyon mongs spong bar byed pa yin //
NK118(se)002:2699: bslab pa bcas pa la phan yon bcu gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:2701: dge 'dun bsdu dang legs par bsdu //
NK118(se)002:2702: bder gnas gnod mi 'khur tshar gcod //
NK118(se)002:2703: ngo tsha shes rnams bder gnas dang //
NK118(se)002:2704: ma dad dad dang dad rnams 'phel //
NK118(se)002:2705: 'di yi zag bsdam phyi ma'i ldog /
NK118(se)002:2706: bstan pa yun ring gnas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2707: zhes pa'i don ni rnam par bshad pa'i sgo bsdu ba las /
NK118(se)002:2708: dang po ni mdor bstan no //
NK118(se)002:2709: gnyis pa ni 'ded pa bsod nyams kyi mtha' spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2710: gsum pa ni ngal zhing dub pa'i mtha' spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2711: bzhi pa ni tshul 'chal rnams nan tur bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2712: lnga pa ni tshul ldan rnams sdig pa'i 'gyod pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2713: drug pa ni ma zhugs pa rnams gzhug pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2714: bdun pa ni zhugs pa rnams smin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2715: brgyad pa ni kun dkris rnam par gnon pa dang mthun pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2716: dgu pa ni legs smon gyi tshangs spyod rnams bsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2717: bcu pa ni bstan pa rgyun mi chad par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2725: sde lnga'i dngos gzhi ji lta ba bzhin bskyed pa'i rgyu rten gyi gang zag ni /
NK118(se)002:2726: sdom pa gso rung yan chad dang ldan pa /
NK118(se)002:2727: ston pa'i bcas pa dang 'brel ba /
NK118(se)002:2728: shes pa rang bzhin du gnas pa dang gsum tshang ba zhig dgos so //
NK118(se)002:2729: kun slong thun mong pa'i rgyu ni /
NK118(se)002:2731: de yi rgyu yang rnam bzhi ste //
NK118(se)002:2732: mi shes pa dang bag med dang //
NK118(se)002:2733: nyon mongs mang dang ma gus pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2735: byed rgyu thun mong ma yin pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2736: gzhi gang la ltung ba 'byung ba gtso bo'i rgyu ste /
NK118(se)002:2737: mi'am mir chags pa la der 'du shes pa ni
NK118(se)002:2738: srog gcod kyi pham pa'i byed rgyu yin pa bzhin
NK118(se)002:2740: ston pas rab byung gi rten la bcas pa'i bslab
NK118(se)002:2741: pa las 'das pa'i lus ngag gi las ni ltung
NK118(se)002:2743: spong bdun gyi rang bzhin tshul khrims kyi mi mthun phyogs su gyur pa'i ltung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2745: 'chal pa'i tshul khrims mi dge'i gzugs //
NK118(se)002:2746: de spong tshul khrims rnam gnyis so //
NK118(se)002:2747: sangs rgyas kyis ni bcad pa yang //
NK118(se)002:2750: so thar gyi sdom ldan du khas 'che ba'i gang
NK118(se)002:2751: zag gis lus ngag gi bcas pa las 'das pa'i
NK118(se)002:2753: 'o na dge slong mas zla bo'i pham pa 'chab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2754: gso sbyong gi dus su ci 'di la khyed yongs
NK118(se)002:2755: su dag gam zhes dris pa na ltung ba shes
NK118(se)002:2756: bzhin du 'chab pa dag ltung ba ma yin par
NK118(se)002:2757: thal / lus ngag gi bcas pa las 'das pa ma yin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK118(se)002:2758: de dag la lus ngag gi rig byed rags pa
NK118(se)002:2759: med kyang kha 'gyur ba dang ba spu g.yo ba
NK118(se)002:2760: sogs kyi rig byed phra mo dang ldan pa'i gzugs
NK118(se)002:2761: yod pa'i phyir skyon med do //
NK118(se)002:2763: yid kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK118(se)002:2764: zhes pa'ang blang dor mi brjod pa'i dran shees la
NK118(se)002:2765: yid kyii sdom pa'i ming gis btags pa tsam du
NK118(se)002:2766: zad de / yid kho na la ltung ba rnam par bzhag pa med pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2768: sems la byung ba 'ba' zhig gi ltung ba med do //
NK118(se)002:2774: sde tshan gyi sgo nas dbye ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2776: rang bzhin dang bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba gnyis ste /
NK118(se)002:2777: spyir bcas pa med pa'i rgyud la 'byung ba'i mi
NK118(se)002:2778: dge ba la rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho
NK118(se)002:2779: ba zhes grags kyang 'dir 'chad pa'i skabs ma yin
NK118(se)002:2780: la / 'dir ltung bar gyur pa'i rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba'i mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:2781: bcas ldan dge slong gi rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:2782: ltung ba khyod kyi dus kyi kun slong de nyon mongs pa can gyis nges par byed dgos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2784: ltung ba khyod kyi dus kyi kun slong gi rigs
NK118(se)002:2785: la nyon mongs pa can yang srid lung ma bstan
NK118(se)002:2786: yang srid pa de bcas rkyang gi mtshan nyid do
NK118(se)002:2787: // des na ma byin len gyi pham pa lta bu rang bzhin dang 'brel ba'i bcas ltung dang /
NK118(se)002:2788: skye ba gcod pa'i ltung byed lta bu bcas rkyang gi ltung ba yin la /
NK118(se)002:2789: de gnyis 'gal ba ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:2790: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi ma byin len gyi pham pa de /
NK118(se)002:2791: rnam smin sdug bsngal bskyed pa'i cha nas rang bzhin dang /
NK118(se)002:2792: ston pa'i bcas 'gal gyi cha nas bcas ltung du bzhag pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:2793: de la bye brag tu smra bas ni /
NK118(se)002:2794: ltung ba'i ngo bo gzugs can du 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:2795: so thar gyi sdom pa'i 'gal zla'i nyes pa yin na lus ngag gi las yin pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:2796: de la rig byed yin min gyi dbye bas gnyis su 'byed do //
NK118(se)002:2798: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba'i sbyor mjug
NK118(se)002:2799: gi ltung ba la rig byed yin min gnyis ka
NK118(se)002:2800: yod cing / dngos gzhi'i ltung ba la rig byed ma yin pas khyab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2801: bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba'i dbang du byas
NK118(se)002:2802: pa'i dngos gzhi la'ang rig byed kyi gzugs 'dod pa'i
NK118(se)002:2803: skabs yod de / dgra bcom pa'i rgyud kyi bcas ltung bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:2804: de yang lung gtam gyi gzhi las /
NK118(se)002:2805: dge slong dgra bcom pas byed na nyes pa de
NK118(se)002:2806: thams cad kyang lung du ma bstan pa'i sems kyis
NK118(se)002:2807: byed / ces gsungs pa ltar de 'dra de lung ma bstan yin pas /
NK118(se)002:2808: rig byed min pa'i gzugs su mi 'thad de /
NK118(se)002:2810: rnam rig min lung bstan min med //
NK118(se)002:2812: gnyis pa yan lag gi sgo nas dbye na /
NK118(se)002:2813: dngos po gtso bor gyur pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2814: 'du shes gtso bor gyur pa gnyis /
NK118(se)002:2816: mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa lta bu /
NK118(se)002:2818: rdzun smra'i ltung ba ltu bu'o //
NK118(se)002:2819: gsum pa rgyu 'bras kyi sgo nas phye na gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:2824: bya ba de rtsom pa'i phyir sems bskyed pa dang stan las ldang ba la sogs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2825: nyes byas kho na yin la /
NK118(se)002:2826: de yang yid la 'gyu ba tsam la bsdam bya dang /
NK118(se)002:2827: lus ngag tu 'thon nas bshags bya'i nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:2829: bya ba de la dngos su sbyor bar byed pa'i lus ngag gi las te /
NK118(se)002:2831: pham lhag gi sbyor ba ni sbom po dang /
NK118(se)002:2832: gzhan rnams kyi sbyor ba ni nyes byas kho na yin no //
NK118(se)002:2834: bya ba de mthar thug pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2836: spyir yon tan gyi sgra'i sbom po zhes pham lhag
NK118(se)002:2837: lta bu lci ba dang ltung byed man chad lta
NK118(se)002:2838: bu'i nyes pa mang ba la zer ba'i lugs kyis
NK118(se)002:2839: sde lnga ga la de'i ming gis btags nas bstan
NK118(se)002:2840: pas na sbom po btags pa ba yin la /
NK118(se)002:2841: 'dir ming du chags pa'i sbom po zhes pa sbom po mtshan nyid pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2843: pham lhag gang rung gi dngos gzhi bskyed nges pa'i
NK118(se)002:2844: sngon 'gro'i sbom po lta bu sbyor ba'i sbom po
NK118(se)002:2845: dang / dngos gzhi'i dus su pham lhag gang rung
NK118(se)002:2846: bskyed par mi byed kyang rang gi ngo bo pham
NK118(se)002:2847: lhag gang rung gi sbyor ba dang cha 'dra ba
NK118(se)002:2848: sbyor ba'i rnam pa'i sbom po ste /
NK118(se)002:2849: dper na mi'i 'gro ba pa la 'chi nges kyi
NK118(se)002:2850: mtshon bsnun nas gsod sems log pa'i sbyor ba lta
NK118(se)002:2851: bu'o // pham lhag gang rung gi mthar thug gi
NK118(se)002:2852: rigs su gnas kyang rgyu tshogs 'ga' zhig ma tshang
NK118(se)002:2853: bas rang gi ngo bo pham lhag gi dngos gzhi'i
NK118(se)002:2854: char gtogs pa'i nyes pa rnams ni dngos gzhi'i rnam
NK118(se)002:2856: dper na lha'i rten can gyi dgra bcom pa bsad pa dang /
NK118(se)002:2857: gsod sems med kyang zhe sdang gis mi'i 'gro ba
NK118(se)002:2858: pa'i lag pa gcod pa'i dngos gzhi'i ltung ba lta
NK118(se)002:2859: bu'o // bzhi pa sde tshan gyi sgo nas phye na /
NK118(se)002:2867: dngos po de spangs nas bshags dgos pa spang ltung dang /
NK118(se)002:2868: de 'dra'i chad las la mi ltos pa 'ba' zhig pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2869: de yang sbom po ni pham lhag gang rung dang /
NK118(se)002:2870: sbyor ba'i nyes byas rnams kyang rang rang gi sde tshan de dang der gtogs la /
NK118(se)002:2871: gzhi bcu bdun nas bshad pa'i nyes byas rnams kyang
NK118(se)002:2872: nyes byas kyi sde tshan las gzhan ma yin pas
NK118(se)002:2873: sde lnga'i rigs su ma 'dus pa'i ltung ba med
NK118(se)002:2874: cing des na nyes byas yin na so thar gyi
NK118(se)002:2875: mdo'i sdom tshig gis bsdus pa'i nyes byas yin pas
NK118(se)002:2876: ma khyab bo // sde tshan lnga po'i khyad par yang kun slong gi sgo nas 'byed dgos te /
NK118(se)002:2877: dper na bud med la reg pa lta bu mi
NK118(se)002:2878: tshangs spyod kyi kun slong gis bslangs na de'i sbyor
NK118(se)002:2879: ba dang / des ma bslangs na dge 'dun lhag mar 'gro ba bzhin te /
NK118(se)002:2880: de'i cha nas der gtogs so //
NK118(se)002:2882: gnyis pa yan lag gi don la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:2883: dge slong pha'i bslab bya dang /
NK118(se)002:2884: dge slong ma'i bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2886: dge slong khrims la nyis brgya lnga bcu gsum //
NK118(se)002:2893: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:2894: nyis brgya dang lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:2898: sdom pa'i rtsa ba pham pa bzhi zhes pa //
NK118(se)002:2899: zhes pas bcas ldan dge slong gis 'di bzhi gang
NK118(se)002:2900: rung la spyad nas skad cig ma gcig bcabs kyang
NK118(se)002:2901: sdom pa lhag ma med par gcod par byed pas
NK118(se)002:2902: na rtsa ba'i ltung ba ste /
NK118(se)002:2903: mi mthun phyogs kyis gnyen po mthu med par bcom pa'i phyir pham pa bzhi zhes bya'o //
NK118(se)002:2905: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rigs rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:2906: rang gi dag byed bslab pa byin nas spyod pa'i gnas pham pa tsam gyi mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:2908: rten de la rgyud gsor rung du byas pa 'chab med dang /
NK118(se)002:2909: sor chud pa mi srid pa pha'i 'chab bcas kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK118(se)002:2910: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:2911: dang po mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2912: gzhi yi yan lag cha kun bzung 'os pa //
NK118(se)002:2913: skye gnas lam du pho dbang las rung ni //
NK118(se)002:2914: bsam pa ngo tsha 'jigs med chags sems kyis //
NK118(se)002:2915: sbyor ba drud pa mthar thug sims pa thob //
NK118(se)002:2916: des ni tshangs par spyod las rnams par nyams //
NK118(se)002:2918: gleng gzhi ston pa mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:2919: nas lo bcu gsum pa la yul spong byed du
NK118(se)002:2920: gang zag dge slong bzang byin gyis nyon mongs pa
NK118(se)002:2921: 'dod chags kyis nyes pa sngar gyi khyim thab la
NK118(se)002:2922: mi tshangs spyod spyad pa la brten nas bcas pa
NK118(se)002:2923: mdzad do // de yang gzhi bsam sbyor ba mthar thug gi yan lag bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:2925: brten bya yul 'khrig pa'i ro'i bde ba bskyed nus
NK118(se)002:2926: kyi yan lag de nyid tshang ba ni yan lag
NK118(se)002:2927: gi cha kun bzung bar 'os pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2928: lus phyed du longs pa yan chad kyi skye gnas
NK118(se)002:2929: su gtogs pa'i kha'am gshang lam mam chu lam gsum
NK118(se)002:2930: po gang yang rung ba ma nyams pa don byed
NK118(se)002:2931: nus pa'o // rten byed rang gi pho dbang nad med las su rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:2932: bsam pa ngo tsha dang 'jigs skrag med cing chags
NK118(se)002:2933: par gyur pas kun slong reg bde nyams su myong
NK118(se)002:2934: 'dod kyis / sbyor ba brten byar stsal zhing drud pas /
NK118(se)002:2935: mthar thug lam gsum gyi mtshams las 'das nas sim pa thob pa ste /
NK118(se)002:2936: bde ba lus kyis myong zhing yid kyis bdag gir byas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:2937: de lta bu'i yan lag tshang na mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa'i dngos gzhir 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:2939: kha shun so dang lpags pa las //
NK118(se)002:2940: nor bu 'das na phas pham ste //
NK118(se)002:2941: phyi rol char ni ci rigs par //
NK118(se)002:2944: gnyis pa ma byin len gyi pham pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2945: brku ba'i gzhi ni mi gzhan nor yin pa //
NK118(se)002:2946: bsam pa rang nyid 'tsho phyir brku sems kyis //
NK118(se)002:2947: yul dus rin thang tshang ba sbyor bas brkus //
NK118(se)002:2948: mthar thug brkus sam brkur bcug rtsad nas thob //
NK118(se)002:2950: gleng gzhi rgyal po'i khab tu dge slong nor can
NK118(se)002:2951: gyis rang gi khang pa brtsig pa'i phyir ma skyes
NK118(se)002:2952: dgra'i shing brkus pa la brten nas bcas so //
NK118(se)002:2955: yul rang dang nor mi gcig pa'i mi'i 'gro ba pas bdag tu bzung ba'i rdzas /
NK118(se)002:2956: dngos po kha zas dang dur khrod kyi rdzas sogs dman pa ma yin pa /
NK118(se)002:2957: yul gang du dus der sbyor ba gcig gi nang
NK118(se)002:2958: du brku bya rku byed gnyis ka la ltos pa'i
NK118(se)002:2961: k+aa ri k+aa lnga bcu pa las /
NK118(se)002:2962: kar+sha pa na'i bzhi cha brkus //
NK118(se)002:2963: de brkus tshul khrims zhig par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:2964: zhes pas kar+sha pa na'i bzhi cha rin thang gi tshad yin la /
NK118(se)002:2965: de yang rgya gar du mgron bu bsregs pa'i thal
NK118(se)002:2966: ba la rtsis po cher byed pas mgron bu'i rin
NK118(se)002:2968: ka ka ni re la mgron bu nyi shu /
NK118(se)002:2969: ka ka ni bzhi la ma sha ka gcig ste mgron bu brgyad cu /
NK118(se)002:2970: ma sha ka nyi shu la kar+sha pa na gcig ste mgron bu stong drug brgya yin /
NK118(se)002:2971: de'i bzhi cha mgron bu bzhi brgya'i tshad ma sha ka lnga rin thang gi tshad de /
NK118(se)002:2972: spyir ma sha ka ji tsam la kar+sha pa nar byed pa'i tshad mtha' gcig tu ma nges kyang /
NK118(se)002:2973: 'dir mdo rtsa ba las 'bring tshad ma sha ka lnga la mdzad pa ltar ro //
NK118(se)002:2974: de gser gyi thang du rtsis na /
NK118(se)002:2975: ka ka ni zhes guny+tsa ste ma ru mgo nag /
NK118(se)002:2976: de bzhi la ma sha ka ste gser se pa do /
NK118(se)002:2977: de lnga la kar+sha pa na'i bzhi cha ste gser se ba bcu yin pas /
NK118(se)002:2978: 'dir nas khal lnga tsam rin thang gi tshad du rigs te /
NK118(se)002:2979: mu ge med pa'i dus su gser se ba nyi
NK118(se)002:2980: shu la dbus zho gang du byas pa'i zho re
NK118(se)002:2981: la nas khal bcu ma byed pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:2982: bsam pa mi'i rdzas la de yin par 'du shes
NK118(se)002:2983: pa'am yid gnyis za bas kun slong rang 'tsho ba'i
NK118(se)002:2985: sbyor ba rin thang tshang ba'i dngos po lus ngag
NK118(se)002:2986: gi rig byed du grub pas rku bar rtsom pa
NK118(se)002:2987: / mthar thug rang gis brkus sam gzhan brkur bcug
NK118(se)002:2988: pa'am rtsad pa gang yang rung bas brku bya'i rdzas
NK118(se)002:2989: bdag po dang phral nas bdag gir byas pa'i tshul
NK118(se)002:2991: gsum pa srog gcod kyi pham pa ni /
NK118(se)002:2992: srog gcod gzhi ni mi gzhan ma 'khrul bar //
NK118(se)002:2993: bsam pa gsod sems gsad bya der shes pa //
NK118(se)002:2994: sbyor ba gsod par brtsams nas ma bzlog pa //
NK118(se)002:2995: mthar thug srog gi dbang po 'gags pa dang //
NK118(se)002:2996: gsod bcug yi rang basngagasa sogs rkyen byas kyang //
NK118(se)002:2998: gleng gzhi yul spong byed du dge slong mang po
NK118(se)002:2999: mi sdug pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas lus mi
NK118(se)002:3000: gtsang bas yid byung nas dge sbyong sbed gsod du
NK118(se)002:3001: bcug pa la brten nas bcas so //
NK118(se)002:3003: gzhi ni mi'am mir chags pa rang las rgyud gzhan pa /
NK118(se)002:3004: bsad do bsam pa de nyid ma 'khrul pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3005: bsam pa bsad bya der 'du shes pas kun slong gsod sems rgyun ma chad pa /
NK118(se)002:3006: sbyor ba dug mtshon sogs kyis gsod par brtsams pa las ma bzlog pas /
NK118(se)002:3007: mthar thug de'i tshe'am gzhan gyi tshe gsod pa po
NK118(se)002:3008: rang nyid ma shi ba'i snga rol tu bsad bya'i
NK118(se)002:3011: gang zhig rang bzhin gnas la bslab bcas pas //
NK118(se)002:3012: mi gzhan yin la mir ni 'du shes dang //
NK118(se)002:3013: bsad pa'i bsam pas 'khrul med gsod byed cing //
NK118(se)002:3014: mi shi rmi lam ma gtogs de brlag 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:3016: de yang rang gis bsad pa tsam du ma zad /
NK118(se)002:3017: gzhan gsod du bcug pa dang gsod pa la yi
NK118(se)002:3018: rang ba'i basngagasa pa brjod pa la sogs pas rkyen
NK118(se)002:3020: dge slong mang pos gros byas nas gcig gis bsad kyang thams cad la pham pa 'byung ste /
NK118(se)002:3022: dmag la sogs pa don gcig phyir //
NK118(se)002:3023: thams cad byed pa po bzhin ldan //
NK118(se)002:3025: bzhi pa rdzun smra'i pham pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3026: rdzun gyi gzhi ni smra shes don go'i mir //
NK118(se)002:3027: bsam pa 'du shes bsgyur nas brjod blo skyes //
NK118(se)002:3028: sbyor ba mngon shes la sogs yon tan tshogs //
NK118(se)002:3029: med kyang yod ces bla ma'i rdzun smras pa //
NK118(se)002:3030: mthar thug gzhan gyis rdzun de go na nyams //
NK118(se)002:3032: gleng gzhi yul yangs pa can du nya pa las
NK118(se)002:3033: rab tu byung ba'i dge slong lnga brgyas mi chos
NK118(se)002:3034: bla ma'i rdzun smras pa la brten nas bcas so
NK118(se)002:3036: gzhi ni gang la smra ba'i yul rang las rgyud gzhan pa'i mi tha snyad lnga ldan te /
NK118(se)002:3039: shes pa rang bzhin du gnas pa /
NK118(se)002:3040: ma ning dang mtshan gnyis pa ma yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3041: gang smra ba'i dngos po ni 'dod khams las gong
NK118(se)002:3042: du 'phags pa bsam gtan dang po nas sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:3043: kyi bar gyi 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK118(se)002:3044: pa'i yon tan gang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:3046: 'dir ni sgrib pa rnam pa lnga //
NK118(se)002:3047: mi rnams kyi ni chos su thos //
NK118(se)002:3048: de zad bla ma'i chos su 'dod //
NK118(se)002:3050: bsam pa 'du shes bsgyur nas rdzun brjod 'dod kyi blo skyes pa /
NK118(se)002:3051: sbyor ba mngon shes sogs gzhan las khyad par du
