NK118(se)002:3052: gyur pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs med kyang yod ces
NK118(se)002:3053: ngag mtshan nyid drug ldan gyis mi chos bla ma'i
NK118(se)002:3054: rdzun mngon pa'i nga rgyal med par smra ba'am /
NK118(se)002:3055: gzhan gyis smras pa dang du len par rtsom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3056: ngag mtshan nyid drug ldan ni /
NK118(se)002:3063: mthar thug gzhan gyis de ltar go na pham pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3064: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3065: 'di bzhi gang spyad dge slong de pham phyir //
NK118(se)002:3066: phas pham bzhi zhes thams cad mkhyen des gsungs //
NK118(se)002:3068: de ltar bshad ma thag pa'i chos bzhi po 'di
NK118(se)002:3069: gang la spyad kyang rang rang gi rgyu tshogs su
NK118(se)002:3070: bshad pa ltar gyi yan lag mtha' dag ma tshang
NK118(se)002:3072: tshang na pham pa dngos gzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:3073: mi mthun phyogs kyis gnyen po bcom pas dge slong de pham par byas pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:3074: phas pham bzhi zhes ston pa thams cad mkhyen des gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:3075: de ltar yang so so thar pa las /
NK118(se)002:3076: dge slong dag gis de dag las ltung ba gang yang rung ba zhig byas na /
NK118(se)002:3077: thog ma ji lta bar phyis kyang de bzhin pham par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:3078: dge slong rnams dang lhan cig gnas pa dang longs spyod du mi dbang gis gnas par mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:3080: gnyis pa dge 'dun lhag ma'i sde la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:3082: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsum zhes grags pa //
NK118(se)002:3084: gso ba dge 'dun la rag las shing sdom pa
NK118(se)002:3085: rnam dag gi lhag lus pas na dge 'dun lhag
NK118(se)002:3088: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:3089: lhag ma'i ming gis phyir bcos na dag tu rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3091: nang sems can la chags pa lnga dang phyi rol
NK118(se)002:3092: yo byad la chags pa gnyis te 'dod pa las
NK118(se)002:3093: gyur ba bdun / gnod pa las gyur pa gnyis /
NK118(se)002:3094: bsgo ba las gyur pa bzhi ste bcu gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:3096: bgrod min gnas su khu ba 'byin pa dang //
NK118(se)002:3097: chags pas bud med lus kyi cha shas 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:3098: 'khrig tshig rjen smra bud med chags phyir bkur //
NK118(se)002:3099: pho mo phan tshun smyan byas 'dus te 'phrad //
NK118(se)002:3100: rang don tshad lhag khang pa khang chen brtsigs //
NK118(se)002:3101: brjod gzhi med dang snyad ka bag tsam la //
NK118(se)002:3102: brten nas dge slong skur btab dge 'dun dbyen //
NK118(se)002:3103: dbyen de'i rjes phyogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba //
NK118(se)002:3104: khyim sun 'byin tshe skrod byed la snyon pa //
NK118(se)002:3105: ltung byang bskul tshe bka' blo mi bde ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3106: zhes pa ltar bcu gsum las /
NK118(se)002:3107: dang po 'byin pa'i lhag ma ni /
NK118(se)002:3108: 'di ni bsnyen bkur gyi bar bzhi'i gleng gzhi gnyan yod du 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3109: bgrod bya'i yul lam gsum min pa'i rang ngam gzhan
NK118(se)002:3110: gyi yan lag gi gnas su dbyung 'dod kyi bsam
NK118(se)002:3111: pas rang gi nor bu reg cing rtsol ba las
NK118(se)002:3112: / khu ba gnas nas 'phos shing bde ba myong ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3113: gnyis pa 'dzin pa'i lhag ma ni /
NK118(se)002:3114: yul lus brten rung gi bud med la chags sems kyis reg par 'dod pas /
NK118(se)002:3115: de'i lus dngos sam skra sogs cha shas la bar
NK118(se)002:3116: du chod pa med par reg pa las byung ba'i
NK118(se)002:3119: yul brda 'phrod pa'i bud med brten rung la chags
NK118(se)002:3120: sems kyis yul dus der 'khrig pa'i dngos ming du
NK118(se)002:3121: grags pa'i tshig rjen par smras pa yul des go
NK118(se)002:3122: ba'o // bzhi pa bsnyen bkur basngagasa pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3123: yul bud med la chags sems kyis 'khrig pa don
NK118(se)002:3124: du gnyer phyir bdag lta bu'i dge slong la 'khrig
NK118(se)002:3125: pas bsnyen bkur na bsnyen bkur rnams kyi nang nas
NK118(se)002:3126: mchog go zhes rang gis smras sam yul gyis smras
NK118(se)002:3127: pa dang du blangs kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:3128: go yul de la brda 'phrod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3129: lnga pa smyan byed pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3130: mnyan yod du drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3131: sprad bya rang las gzhan pa'i pho mo sprad du
NK118(se)002:3132: rung ba phan tshun sbyor 'dod kyis rang ngam bskos
NK118(se)002:3133: pas 'phrin gsum gyi sgo nas smyan byas pas de
NK118(se)002:3135: drug pa khang pa'i lhag ma ni /
NK118(se)002:3136: 'di dang khang chen gnyis ston pa koo sham+b+hira bzhugs pa'i tshe drug sde la bcas /
NK118(se)002:3137: de yang gzhi srog chags mang zhing rtsod pa can
NK118(se)002:3138: dang 'jig rkyen yod pas mi rung ba'i sar gzhan
NK118(se)002:3139: la 'bad pas btsal ba'i yo byad kyis dge 'dun
NK118(se)002:3140: las gnang ba ma thob par rang don du khang
NK118(se)002:3141: pa rtsig 'dod kyis srid du mi'i khru bco brgyad
NK118(se)002:3142: dang zheng du khru phyed dang bcu gcig gi tshad
NK118(se)002:3143: las lhag pa'i khang pa rang ngam gzhan la bskos
NK118(se)002:3144: kyang rung ste / rtsig pas kun nas bskor zhing thog phub zin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3146: gang zag bzhir longs pa yan chad kyi don du brtsigs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:3147: 'di la btsal ba dang tshad lhag yan lag tu mi dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:3148: gzhan thams cad sngar dang 'dra ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3149: brgyad pa gzhi med kyi skur 'debs ni /
NK118(se)002:3150: 'di dang bag tsam gyi skur 'debs gnyis rgyal po'i
NK118(se)002:3151: khab tu mdza' bo dang sa las skyes la bcas
NK118(se)002:3152: / yul dge slong gzhan la brjod pa'i gzhi mthong
NK118(se)002:3153: thos dogs gsum med par pham bzhi gang rung gi
NK118(se)002:3154: sgo nas skur 'debs kyi tshig gsal por smras pa
NK118(se)002:3156: dgu pa bag tsam gyi skur 'debs ni /
NK118(se)002:3157: yul dge slong gzhan la gleng ba'i snyad ka bag
NK118(se)002:3158: tsam yod pa la brten nas tshig zur gyi shugs
NK118(se)002:3159: kyis pham pa'i sgo nas skur pa btab cing go
NK118(se)002:3160: ba'o // bcu pa dge 'dun dbyen ni /
NK118(se)002:3161: rgyal po'i khab tu lhas sbyin la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3162: mtshams nang gcig tu bcas ldan dge slong gis rang
NK118(se)002:3163: mi the ba'i dbye bya dge 'dun du longs pa
NK118(se)002:3164: gnyis chos min gyi lta bas phan tshun 'byed pa
NK118(se)002:3165: la zlog byed lngas bzlog kyang de'i tha ma brjod
NK118(se)002:3166: pa gsum pa'i mtha' la ma btang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3171: de las ltung ba bskyed tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:3172: dang po bzhi'i mthar sbom po re re dang /
NK118(se)002:3173: brjod pa gsum pa'i mthar mi gtong na lhag ma'i dngos gzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:3176: de'i mtshams med la khyad par yod dam med ce na /
NK118(se)002:3178: mtshams med la dge 'dun bye ba zhig nges par dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:3179: 'byed pa po'ang dge slong du nges la /
NK118(se)002:3180: lhag ma ni dge 'dun bye bar ma nus kyang /
NK118(se)002:3181: de'i sbyor bar zhugs pa la zlog byed lnga'i mthar ma btang ba nyid kyis chog cing /
NK118(se)002:3182: 'byed pa po'ang dge slong nyid du ma nges te /
NK118(se)002:3183: dge slong ma la'ang dbyen gyi lhag ma 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:3184: bcu gcig pa dbyen de'i rjes su phyogs pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3185: rgyal po'i khab tu lhas sbyin gyi grogs byed pa'i
NK118(se)002:3186: dge slong ko ka li ka sogs bzhi la bcas
NK118(se)002:3187: te / dge slong gang dge 'dun gyi dbyen la
NK118(se)002:3188: zhugs pa'i dge slong de'i grogs byed 'dod kyis rjes
NK118(se)002:3189: su zhugs shing zlog byed lnga'i mtha' la ma btang
NK118(se)002:3190: te / ba'o // bcu gnyis pa khyim sun 'byin pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3191: gnyan yod du nabs so dang 'gro mgyogs la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3192: bud med dang lhan cig rtsed 'jo dang bza' btung
NK118(se)002:3193: la spyod pa sogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba'i ngan
NK118(se)002:3194: spyod kyis khyim pa'i sems sun phyungs te ma dad
NK118(se)002:3195: par byed pa po'i dge slong gang dge 'dun gyis
NK118(se)002:3196: bskrad pa na / skrod byed dge 'dun la 'gro
NK118(se)002:3197: min bzhi'i snyon tshig gis skur 'debs la zhugs shing
NK118(se)002:3198: zlog byed lnga'i mthar ma btang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3199: bcu gsum pa bka' blo mi bde ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3200: koo sham+b+hira 'dun pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3201: ltung ba byung bar gleng dran byas la chags pa'i
NK118(se)002:3202: dge slong la lhag pa'i tshul khrims kyi dbang du
NK118(se)002:3203: byas te dge 'dun gyis phyir bcos bya bar bskul
NK118(se)002:3204: ba na / khyed cag dge yang rung sdig kyang
NK118(se)002:3205: rung kho bo la ci yang ma smra zhig ces
NK118(se)002:3206: bka' blo mi bde ba'i gzhir zhugs pa nyid zlog
NK118(se)002:3207: byed lnga pa'i mtha' la ma btang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3210: zhes ma nges pa gnyis gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:3211: khrims grogs med pa'i dben pa sgrib byed kyi skyabs
NK118(se)002:3212: yod pa'i gnas su dge slong dang bud med lhan
NK118(se)002:3214: gnas de mi tshang spyod byar rung mi rung gi khyad par las /
NK118(se)002:3215: dge slong de la pham lhag ltung byed gsum gang rung ngam /
NK118(se)002:3216: lhag ma da nga ltung byed gnyis gang byung ma
NK118(se)002:3217: nges pa'am dngos po la mtha' gang du 'gyur ma
NK118(se)002:3218: nges pa'o // ma nges pa gnyis gzhung 'dir tshig zin la mi 'byung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3219: gnas der 'dug tsam ltung byed dang /
NK118(se)002:3220: de'i 'bras bur gyur pa pham lhag gang rung gi nang du 'dus pas logs su ma gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:3221: gsum pa spang ba ltung byed kyi sde la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:3223: spang ba ltung byed sum cu'i sde bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:3225: gang la ltung ba byung ba'i dngos po de spangs pa'i sgo nas phyir bcos dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:3226: ma bcos na rnam smin ngan song du ltung bar byed pas na spang ltung zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:3228: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:3229: spang ba ltung byed kyi ming gis phyir bcos na dag tu rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3233: lhung bzed sogs kyi sde gsum re re la bcu bcu ste /
NK118(se)002:3238: rang gi gos lhag zhag bcu 'das par 'chang //
NK118(se)002:3239: chos gos dang bral zhag gcig lon pa dang //
NK118(se)002:3240: gos rgyu zla gcig 'jog dang dge slong mar //
NK118(se)002:3241: chos gos 'khrur 'jug de la gos rgyu len //
NK118(se)002:3242: nye min khyim par gos rgyu slong ba dang //
NK118(se)002:3243: ster na stod g.yogs smad g.yogs lhag por len //
NK118(se)002:3244: rang la ster bsam chos gos gnas dpags pa //
NK118(se)002:3245: rin dang khru tshad kyis slong rtags dran slong //
NK118(se)002:3246: gos rin rin chen bskur ba len rnams so //
NK118(se)002:3248: dang po 'chang ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3249: 'chang 'bral 'jog gsum gnyan yod du dge slong mang po la bcas /
NK118(se)002:3250: de yang sra brkyang ma bting ba'i gang zag gis /
NK118(se)002:3251: rang dbang zhing bdag tu bzung ba'i gos lhag po /
NK118(se)002:3252: tshad 'khor gsum khebs pa'i matha'i tshad du longs pa'am /
NK118(se)002:3253: gal te byin gyis brlab rung gi chos gos rnam gsum yod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3254: med kyang chos gos kyi kha bskang ba'i re ba med na khru gang gi tshad du longs pa /
NK118(se)002:3255: rang ming ngam rnam brtags gang rung gis byin gyis
NK118(se)002:3256: ma brlabs pa'am brlabs kyang shan dang rjes su 'brel
NK118(se)002:3257: bas / rang stobs sam shan stobs gang rung gis
NK118(se)002:3258: zhag bcu 'das nas bcu gcig pa'i skya rengs dang
NK118(se)002:3259: bas / po shar ba'o // 'di la gos lhag po lta ci smos /
NK118(se)002:3260: rang dbang zhing gnas skabs dbang byar yod pa'i gos rnyed nas zhag bcu'i nang du /
NK118(se)002:3261: gos byin brlabs can sngar med na 'tsho ba'i yo
NK118(se)002:3262: byad bcu gsum po gang rung du rang ming gis
NK118(se)002:3264: gal te byin brlabs can snga ma yod na /
NK118(se)002:3265: phyis rnyed pa de zhe thag pa nas gzhan la bsngo ba dang /
NK118(se)002:3266: lhag po'am mkho ba'i yo byad du rnam brtags kyis
NK118(se)002:3267: byin gyis brlab pa gang rung bya dgos pa yin
NK118(se)002:3268: no // 'o na spang ba bskyed pa la byin
NK118(se)002:3269: gyis ma brlabs pa'i gos des rang stobs nyid kyis
NK118(se)002:3270: zhag bcu 'das dgos sam snyam na /
NK118(se)002:3272: byin gyis ma brlabs pa'i gos snga mas zhag gcig nas dgu'i bar gang rung lon la /
NK118(se)002:3273: de'i rjes su gos gnyis pa zhig rnyed na /
NK118(se)002:3274: de nyid kyi nyin par snga ma'i zhag shan phyi ma la 'byung bas /
NK118(se)002:3275: snga mas zhag gang lon de phyi mas kyang lon par 'jog dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:3276: 'di la gzhan yod na byin gyis ma brlabs pa de'i shan tshun chad nas so //
NK118(se)002:3278: byin gyis brlabs pa tsam gyis nyes pa de khegs sam zhe na /
NK118(se)002:3279: snga phyi gnyis ka brlabs pa'am /
NK118(se)002:3280: shan ma 'dres gong du snga ma de brlabs na khegs mod /
NK118(se)002:3281: snga ma byin gyis ma brlabs na phyi ma brlabs
NK118(se)002:3282: kyang snga ma'i shan stobs kyis de'i nyes pa mi
NK118(se)002:3283: khegs te / 'brel kyang rjes su zhugs pa dang bcas pa la'o //
NK118(se)002:3285: snga ma brlab pas rting ma la shan mi 'byung na'ang /
NK118(se)002:3286: des rting ma byin gyis brlabs pa'i go mi chod de /
NK118(se)002:3287: rting mas zhag bcu lon pa'i tshe rang stobs kyis ltung ba bskyed pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:3288: spyir shan gyi rnam grangs la bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:3296: de gnyis spyir btang la brdeg bya rdeg byed du mi rung mod /
NK118(se)002:3297: dmigs bsal la mu bzhi yod de /
NK118(se)002:3298: sngar rnyed pa'i zla 'jog gi gos te /
NK118(se)002:3299: phyis chos gos yongs rdzogs rnyed pa'i stobs kyis zhag bcu pa'i gos su rigs log cing /
NK118(se)002:3300: gos phyi ma de snga ma'i phyi dro de ka rnyed pa yin na shan mi 'byung la /
NK118(se)002:3301: zhag phyi ma rnams la rnyed na shan kyang 'byung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:3302: yang gos snga rting gnyis ka zla bar bzhag tu rung ba'i gos yin na rig ma log mod /
NK118(se)002:3303: rting ma rnyed pa'i gos de zhag phyi ma'am /
NK118(se)002:3304: zhag de ka'i nang du rnyed pa'i khyad par las shan 'byung mi 'byung ste /
NK118(se)002:3306: des na gos dang lhung bzed kyi shan ni /
NK118(se)002:3307: rdeg byed byin gyis ma brlabs pa nyid kyis /
NK118(se)002:3308: brdeg bya rang dang dus mnyam pa'am rting la rnyed
NK118(se)002:3309: pa'i gos dang lhung bzed byin gyis brlabs ma brlabs
NK118(se)002:3310: gang yin kyang 'dra ste shan 'jug pa yin no
NK118(se)002:3311: // sman gyi shan ni rdeg byed byin gyis brlabs pa nyid kyis /
NK118(se)002:3312: brdeg bya byin gyis brlabs pa dang ma brlabs pa gzhan la shan rdeg pa yin cing /
NK118(se)002:3313: de yang snga dro thun tshod du rung ba'i sman gnyis dang /
NK118(se)002:3314: zhag dang po la zhag bdun pa'i sman bu ram lta bu gnyis rnyed pa las /
NK118(se)002:3316: gcig ma brlabs par bzhag pa na /
NK118(se)002:3317: thun tshod kyi mtha' dang zhag bdun pa 'das nas
NK118(se)002:3318: brgyad pa'i skya rengs shar ba'i tshe byin gyis brlabs
NK118(se)002:3320: ma brlabs pas shan stobs kyi gsog 'jog gi spang ba bskyed la /
NK118(se)002:3321: yang dus mi mnyam pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK118(se)002:3322: thun tshod kyi sman snga dro rnyed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3323: tshes gcig lta bur bu ram gyi sman rnyed pa byin gyis brlabs nas bzhag /
NK118(se)002:3324: phyi dro thun tshod kyi sman gnyis pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3325: zhag gnyis nas bdun gyi bar bu ram gyi sman
NK118(se)002:3326: gnyis pa rnyed pa byin gyis brlabs sam ma brlabs
NK118(se)002:3327: kyang 'dra ste / rang rang gi dus 'das pa'i
NK118(se)002:3328: tshe snga mas rang stobs dang phyi mas shan stobs
NK118(se)002:3330: khyad par zhag bdun pa'i sman shan ni bu ram
NK118(se)002:3331: gyis bu ram la rdeg pa lta bu sman snga
NK118(se)002:3332: phyi rigs mthun pa dgos te /
NK118(se)002:3333: zhag bdun pa ni rigs mthun pa la'o //
NK118(se)002:3335: gzhan rnams la ni bcas pa rigs 'dra bas chog
NK118(se)002:3336: gi rdzas snga phyi rigs mthun pa mi dgos shing
NK118(se)002:3337: / 'tsho bcangs kyi sman ni ji srid 'tsho'i bar du gnang bas shan mi 'byung ngo //
NK118(se)002:3339: spang ltung sum cu las gang rung byung ba phyir
NK118(se)002:3340: bcos ma byas pa'i bar la gos sogs 'tsho ba'i
NK118(se)002:3341: yo byad gang rnyed kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:3342: ltung ba snga ma de phyir bcos byed pa'i tshe
NK118(se)002:3343: de'i rgyur gyur pa'i rdzas de nyid du ma zad
NK118(se)002:3344: / yo byad rting ma de rnams kyang snga ma'i shan gyis spong dgos pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:3345: ltung ba de yod na yo byad tsam bdag gir byas pa la spang ba nyid do //
NK118(se)002:3348: sra brkyang bting chags kyi gang zag la mi 'byung ste /
NK118(se)002:3349: de la de gsum bag yangs kyi tshul du gnang ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:3350: gnyis pa 'bral ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3351: rnam sbyar la 'bral ba'i gnang ba ma thob cing
NK118(se)002:3352: sra brkyang ma bting ba'i gang zag gis 'jigs bcas
NK118(se)002:3353: kyi dgon pa las gzhan du byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK118(se)002:3354: chos gos gsum po thams cad dam gang rung bzhag
NK118(se)002:3355: pa'i gnas nye 'khor dang bcas pa las zhag gcig
NK118(se)002:3356: bral nas zhag phyi ma'i skya rengs shar ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3357: gsum pa zla 'jog gi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3358: sra brkyang ma bting zhing chos gos gsum gang rung
NK118(se)002:3359: med pa'i gang zag gis kha bskang ba'i re ba
NK118(se)002:3360: dang bcas pa'i chos gos kyi rgyu khru gang gi
NK118(se)002:3361: tshad du longs shing 'khor gsum mi khebs pa /
NK118(se)002:3363: brlabs kyang shan dang rjes su 'brel bas /
NK118(se)002:3364: rang stobs sam shan stobs gang rung gis zhag sum
NK118(se)002:3365: cu 'das nas so gcig pa'i skya rengs shar ba'o
NK118(se)002:3366: // bzhi pa 'khrur 'jug pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3367: gnyan yod du 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3368: bdun rgyud tshun chad kyi nye du ma yin pa'i
NK118(se)002:3369: dge slong ma la rang gi chos gos gsum dang
NK118(se)002:3370: gding ba rnyed pa las gang rung 'khrur bcug pa
NK118(se)002:3371: na / gos kyi phyogs gcig tsam 'khru ba'i las byas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3372: lnga pa gos len pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3373: 'di nas bskur ba'i bar drug ka gnyan yod du nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3374: chos gos rnam gsum yod pa'i dge slong gis nye
NK118(se)002:3375: du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma la 'khor gsum
NK118(se)002:3376: khebs pa'i matha'i tshad du longs pa yan chad kyi
NK118(se)002:3377: gos bslangs pas lag tu thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3378: drug pa slong ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3379: chos gos rnam gsum yod pa'i dge slong gis nye
NK118(se)002:3380: du ma yin pa'i khyim pa la 'khor gsum khebs
NK118(se)002:3381: pa'i tshad du longs pa'i gos bslangs te thob pa'o
NK118(se)002:3382: // bdun pa slong bar rigs pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3383: chos gos rnam gsum med pa'i dge slong gis khyim
NK118(se)002:3384: pa nye du ma yin pa la bslangs pas gos
NK118(se)002:3385: mang po ster na'ang stod g.yogs dang smad g.yogs tsam
NK118(se)002:3386: blang rigs kyis / de las lhag pa len na ltung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3387: brgyad pa dpags pa slong ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3388: khyim pa nye du ma yin pas sbyin gnas dge
NK118(se)002:3389: slong rang nyid la ster bar bsam pa'i gos 'di
NK118(se)002:3391: dngos su 'bul long med par snga tshoms su rin
NK118(se)002:3392: dang khru tshad kyis dran pa brjod nas bslangs pas
NK118(se)002:3393: thob pa'o // dgu pa so so nas dpags pa slong ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3394: nye du ma yin pa'i khyim bdag pho mo so
NK118(se)002:3395: so nas gos re re'am mang po dge slong rang
NK118(se)002:3396: la 'bul bar dpags pa de thos nas 'bul mi
NK118(se)002:3397: 'bul brtag pa'i bsam pas dran pa brjod de bslangs
NK118(se)002:3398: pas thob pa'o // 'di gnyis rang la bsngosa tshod
NK118(se)002:3399: las lhag pa'i dngos po thob pa zhig dgos gsung
NK118(se)002:3400: pas thob pa'o // na'ang / mdo'i dngos bstan la
NK118(se)002:3401: 'bul long med par snga tshoms su blangs pa'i nyes
NK118(se)002:3403: bcu pa bskur ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3404: sbyin bdag pho nya ba zhal ta pa ste khyim pa gsum las /
NK118(se)002:3405: sbyin bdag gis gos rin rung ba ma yin pa
NK118(se)002:3406: gser dngul lta bu zhig bskur ba pho nyas dge
NK118(se)002:3408: de len du mi rung zhes spangs pa na /
NK118(se)002:3409: pho nya des dge slong rang gi zhal ta pa la gtad nas gos sgrub tu bcug pa las /
NK118(se)002:3410: gos dus su ma byung na dge slong gis zhal ta pa la dngos su bskul ba gsum bya /
NK118(se)002:3411: de la ma byung na lan gsum mthong sar cang
NK118(se)002:3412: mi smra bas sdang nas bslangs pa la nyes pa
NK118(se)002:3413: med cing / de las lhag par byas pas gos thob na spang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:3415: srin bal nang tshang byas pa'i stan byed dang //
NK118(se)002:3416: dkon sar bal nag 'ba' zhig stan du 'ding //
NK118(se)002:3417: bal nag cha gnyis stan byed lo drug ni //
NK118(se)002:3418: ma song stan gsar byed dang tshad ldan gyi //
NK118(se)002:3419: 'ding ba yod kyang slar bzo bal nag ni //
NK118(se)002:3420: rnyed nas lam gyi dpag tshad gsum mthar byed //
NK118(se)002:3421: dge slong mar ni bal 'khru rmel bcug dang //
NK118(se)002:3422: gser dngul len dang tshong 'bun mngon mtshan can //
NK118(se)002:3425: stan gyi spang ba lnga po gnyan yod du dge slong mang po la bcas /
NK118(se)002:3427: dang po rin thang che ba'i dngos po srin bal sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:3428: gnyis pa gang du bal nag dkon sar bal nag 'ba' zhig dang /
NK118(se)002:3429: gsum pa bal nag po stan gyi cha gnyis las lhag pa ste /
NK118(se)002:3430: de ltar rgyu de gsum las rang ngam gzhan la
NK118(se)002:3431: bskos pas stan nang tshang can gsar du byed na
NK118(se)002:3432: / de dag bkram pa tsam gyis de dang de'i spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3433: bzhi pa lo drug gi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3434: stan snga ma yod bzhin du gnang ba ma thob
NK118(se)002:3435: par lo drug gi nang du stan nang tshang can
NK118(se)002:3436: gnyis pa byas shing zin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3437: lnga pa mtho gang gi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3438: tshad ldan gyi 'ding ba rnyed pa yod na gsar
NK118(se)002:3439: du bzo ba'i tshe rnying pa nas chung tha yang
NK118(se)002:3440: bde bar gshegs pa'i mtho gang ste mi'i khru phyed
NK118(se)002:3441: do gsar pa la ma bslan par longs spyad pa'o
NK118(se)002:3442: // drug pa lam du bal thogs pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3443: 'di nas nyo tshong gi bar lnga drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3444: rang dbang ba'i dngos po bal la sogs pa'i khur
NK118(se)002:3445: chen po chags sems kyis khyer nas nyi ma gcig
NK118(se)002:3446: gi nang du rgyang grags las 'das pa ste /
NK118(se)002:3447: de yang dge tshul lta bu 'khur khyer grogs gzhan med na dpag tshad gsum tshun chad gnang bas /
NK118(se)002:3448: de nas brtsams te rgyang grags gcig gi mthar phyin pa'am /
NK118(se)002:3449: khyer grogs yod na dang po nas brtsams te rgyang grags 'das pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3450: bdun pa 'khrur 'jug pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3451: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma la dge
NK118(se)002:3452: slong gis bal 'khru ba dang rmel ba dang 'tshed
NK118(se)002:3453: du bcug pa las des de dang de byas pa'o
NK118(se)002:3454: // brgyad pa rin chen la reg pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3455: dge slong gis gser dngul sogs rung ba ma yin
NK118(se)002:3456: pa la rung ba ma byas pa'i rin po che
NK118(se)002:3457: chud za ba sogs kyi nyes pa med bzhin du
NK118(se)002:3458: chags sems kyis reg gam reg du bcug ste bdag
NK118(se)002:3459: gir byas pa'o // rung ba bya tshul la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:3460: sbyin bdag bdag po nyid du mos su gzhug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3461: zhal ta byed pa bdag po nyid du khas len du gzhug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3463: dgu pa mngon mtshan can gyi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3464: dge slong gis nye du ma yin pa'i khyim par
NK118(se)002:3465: 'dod zhen gyis khe spogs 'dod pas tshong zog rin
NK118(se)002:3466: po che sogs mngon mtshan can 'bun bskyed du btang
NK118(se)002:3467: bas / de las bskyed gos khru gang du longs pa thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3468: bcu pa nyo tshong byed pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3469: dge slong gis khe spogs 'dod pa'i ched du khyim
NK118(se)002:3470: pa nye du ma yin pa la rin po che
NK118(se)002:3471: las gzhan pa'i dngos po 'bru dang gos sogs mod
NK118(se)002:3472: na nyo zhing dkon na tshong bar byed pas bskyed
NK118(se)002:3473: thob pa'o // bcu tshan gsum pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3475: zhag bcu 'das 'chang lhung bzed zung 'chang ba //
NK118(se)002:3476: glang rngan med par 'thag 'jug thags rgya bskyed //
NK118(se)002:3477: dge slong gos byin slar phrogs gtad byung gos //
NK118(se)002:3478: sbyin dus bshad las snga bar bdag gir byas //
NK118(se)002:3479: dgon par 'jigs bcas gos bral zhag bdun 'das //
NK118(se)002:3480: ras chen dgag dbye zin kyang zla phyed 'das //
NK118(se)002:3481: dge 'dun bsngosa pa'i rnyed pa bdag tu bzung //
NK118(se)002:3482: na sman zhag bdun 'das nas gsog 'jog go //
NK118(se)002:3484: dang po ltung bzed 'chang ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3486: rang gi lhung bzed tshad ldan byin gyis ma brlabs
NK118(se)002:3487: pa'am brlabs pa'am brlabs kyang shan stobs kyis zhag bcu'i
NK118(se)002:3488: bar bcangs nas bcu gcig pa'i skya rengs shar ba'o
NK118(se)002:3489: // gnyis pa lhung bzed lhag po tshol ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3490: 'di nas byin phrogs kyi bar bzhi nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3491: rgyu dbyibs kha dog gis rung zhing mthe bo'i lto
NK118(se)002:3492: gang gi lhag mar phul dgu shong ba yan chad
NK118(se)002:3493: kyi lhung bzed spyad bzod rang la yod bzhin du
NK118(se)002:3494: khyim pa nye du ma yin pa la bslangs pas
NK118(se)002:3496: 'di yang byin gyis ma brlabs par zhag bcu 'das na ltung ba snga mar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:3497: gsum pa 'thag tu 'jug pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3498: nye du ma yin pa'i thags mkhan la gla rngan
NK118(se)002:3499: med par rang ngam bskos pas gos 'thag tu bcug
NK118(se)002:3501: bzhi pa 'thag pa bkyed pa'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3502: nye du ma yin pa'i khyim pas rang la 'bul rgyu'i gos 'thag pa na /
NK118(se)002:3503: bdag pos ma gnang bar bsngosa tshod las lhag pa bkyed du bcug ste thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3504: lnga pa byin phrogs kyi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3505: dge slong gis rang dang lta mtshan mthun pa'i dge
NK118(se)002:3506: slong gzhan la gos sam lhung bzed sogs yo byad
NK118(se)002:3507: sngar byin pa phrogs te pha rol po las bral
NK118(se)002:3508: ba'o // drug pa gtad pa las byung ba'i spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3509: 'di dang dgon pa'i 'bral spang gnyis gnyan yod du drug sde la bcas /
NK118(se)002:3510: de yang dbyar gnas pa'i dge 'dun la phul ba'i
NK118(se)002:3511: rnyed pa dbyar nang du bdag gir byas pa dang
NK118(se)002:3513: dgag dbye'i phyi de nyin ma bgos pa ste /
NK118(se)002:3514: de ltar sngas phyis kyi ltung ba gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:3516: gtad pa las byung ba'i gos lnga po /
NK118(se)002:3521: 'gro bar chas pa las sbyin pa /
NK118(se)002:3523: dgag dbye'i gong rol tu sbyin bdag gis gtad pa'i
NK118(se)002:3524: rnyed pa rkyen ldan de dag la rkyen dbang gis
NK118(se)002:3525: dbyar matha'i zhag bcu'i nang du so sor sbyin pa
NK118(se)002:3527: dbyar nang du chos smra ba'i rnyed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3528: nad pa'i rim gro la sogs pa'i ched du sbyin pa'i rnyed pa ni 'dir mi gtogs so //
NK118(se)002:3529: bdun pa dgon pa'i 'bral spang ni /
NK118(se)002:3530: dge slong dgon pa bas byin rlabs can gyi chos
NK118(se)002:3531: gos rnam gsum dang zhag drug tshun chad bral kyang
NK118(se)002:3532: nyes pa med par gnang la /
NK118(se)002:3533: gal te 'jigs pa dang bral kyang zhag drug na
NK118(se)002:3534: ma sleb par bdun pa'i skya rengs shar ba'i tshe
NK118(se)002:3535: spang ba'o // brgyad pa ras chen gyi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3536: gnyan yod du dge slong rab tu mang po la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3537: dbyar gyi gos ras chen rang nyid dbyar snga phyi
NK118(se)002:3538: gang khas len pa de'i zla gcig gi snga rol
NK118(se)002:3539: du btsal zhing rnyed na tshol sngas pa'i spang ba
NK118(se)002:3540: dang / dgag dbye zin pa'i 'og tu zla phyed
NK118(se)002:3541: las 'das par bcangs na bzhag 'phyis kyi spang ba'o
NK118(se)002:3542: dang / // dgu pa sngos sgyur gyi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3543: gnyan yod du nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3544: khyim pas dge 'dun nam dge slong gzhan la bsngosa
NK118(se)002:3545: pa'i gos dang lhung bzed lta bu'i rnyed pa rang
NK118(se)002:3546: nyid la bsgyur te bdag gir bzung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3547: bcu pa gsog 'jog gi spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:3548: rgyal po'i khab tu 'phags pa pi lin+ta'i lhan cig gnas pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3549: zhag bdun pa'i sman smos pa ni mdo'i dngos bstan ltar dpe tsam du zad pas /
NK118(se)002:3550: 'dir sman bzhi gang rung rang dus las 'das par bcangs pa la gsog 'jog gi spang ba ste /
NK118(se)002:3552: byin gyis ma brlabs na sman bzhi po gang yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:3553: snga dro byin len byas pa gung tshigs las 'das pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3554: de bzhin du phyi dro dang /
NK118(se)002:3557: mtshan mo'i thun tha ma bzhi po re re bzhin /
NK118(se)002:3558: snga ma snga mar byin len byas pa /
NK118(se)002:3559: phyi ma phyi ma'i dus las 'das na'o //
NK118(se)002:3561: dus rung la ni byin rlabs ma bshad kyang byin
NK118(se)002:3562: len snga dro byas pa phyi dro ma zhig par
NK118(se)002:3563: bcangs pa dang / thun tshod du rung ba snga
NK118(se)002:3564: dro brlabs pa zhag de'i mtshan mo'i mtha' 'das pa
NK118(se)002:3565: bcangs pa dang / dang / zhag bdun pa'i sman
NK118(se)002:3566: brlabs pa brgyad pa'i skya rengs shar ba'i tshe na
NK118(se)002:3567: bcangs pa dang / dang / dang / 'tsho bcangs
NK118(se)002:3568: kyi sman ni nad sos kyi bar du brlabs pa
NK118(se)002:3569: nad las grol nas kyang bcangs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:3570: 'di ji srid 'tsho'i bar du brlabs pa la ni gsog 'jog tu mi 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:3571: de ltar spang ltung sum cu las phyir bcos kyi
NK118(se)002:3572: tshe byin phrogs dang lhung bzed tshol ba gnyis kyi
NK118(se)002:3573: rdzas rtsa ba nas spang dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:3574: gzhan rnams zhag gcig gi ring spang ba sngon du btang bas chog go //
NK118(se)002:3575: bzhi pa ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa'i sde la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:3577: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa ni //
NK118(se)002:3579: spyad na ngan song du ltung bar byed cing /
NK118(se)002:3580: de dag bshags pa la spang bral sngon du gtong
NK118(se)002:3581: mi dgos pas na 'ba' zhig pa zhes bya ste
NK118(se)002:3583: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:3584: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa'i ming gis phyir bcos na dag tu rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3587: shes bzhin dang ni sa bon dang //
NK118(se)002:3588: ma bskos pa dang yang dang yang //
NK118(se)002:3589: chu dang khyim dang bsam bzhin dang //
NK118(se)002:3590: 'gron mang rkun ma chos ston no //
NK118(se)002:3591: zhes spyi sdoms kyis 'go drangs pa'i sde tshan dgu
NK118(se)002:3592: po re re la'ang bcu bcu ste dgu bcu tham
NK118(se)002:3593: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la /
NK118(se)002:3595: dang po shes bzhin gyi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3596: shes bzhin rdzun smra dge slong skyon brjod pa //
NK118(se)002:3597: phra mas 'byed dang skyo sngogs zlums kyang dbye //
NK118(se)002:3598: bud med chos ston bsnyen par ma rdzogs dang //
NK118(se)002:3599: lhan cig chos 'don gnas ngan len ltung brjod //
NK118(se)002:3600: mi chos bla ma bden smra bsher ngor 'phya //
NK118(se)002:3603: dang po rdzun smra'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3604: gnyan yod du sh+aakya lag rgyud la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3605: dngos po pham lhag sbom po nyes byas su gyur pa'i rdzun bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:3606: ltung byed rang gi nang tshan gyi rdzun drug bshad pa /
NK118(se)002:3607: de rnams las gzhan pa'i dge slong gis shes bzhin
NK118(se)002:3608: du rdzun smras pa nyan pa pos brda' 'phrod cing
NK118(se)002:3609: don go ba'o // de la rdzun bzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:3611: gzhi med dang bag tsam gyi lhag ma /
NK118(se)002:3612: shes bzhin du chos ma yin pa la chos su dang /
NK118(se)002:3613: chos yin pa la ma yin par smra ba sbom por gyur pa'i rdzun dang /
NK118(se)002:3614: gso sbyong gi dus su ci 'di la khyed yongs
NK118(se)002:3615: su dag gam zhes dris pa la cang mi smra
NK118(se)002:3616: bas 'da' bar byed pa'i nyes byas rnams so //
NK118(se)002:3617: ltung byed kyi nang tshan gzhan pa drug ni /
NK118(se)002:3624: gnyis pa skyon brjod kyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3625: 'di nas lnga brgyad dgu gsum po ma gtogs drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3626: dge slong gis yul dge slong gzhan la yul dus
NK118(se)002:3627: der skyon du grags pa'i tshig phan sems ma yin
NK118(se)002:3628: par brjod pa phal rol pos go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3629: gsum pa phra ma byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3630: dge slong gis yul dge slong mthun pa dag phra ma'i tshig gis 'byed par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3631: bzhi pa skyo sngogs byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3632: dge slong gnyis rtsod pa dge 'dun gyis chos phyogs su zhi bar byas zin cing /
NK118(se)002:3633: rang dang go bya zhi byed kyi las de byed
NK118(se)002:3634: pa la gtogs pas zlums pa slar dbye 'dod kyis
NK118(se)002:3635: rtsod pa de legs par ma zhi bas yang zhi
NK118(se)002:3636: bar byed dgos so zhes sngar byas kyi las skyo
NK118(se)002:3637: sngogs kyis bshis par rtsom pa'i tshig smras shing don
NK118(se)002:3638: go ba'o / lnga pa bud med la chos ston pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3640: khrims grogs med par yul nyan 'dod kyi bud med
NK118(se)002:3641: la des mi shes pa'i chos 'dus byas mi rtag
NK118(se)002:3642: ces pa lta bu'i tshig lnga'am drug las lhag par
NK118(se)002:3643: bstan pa'o // drug pa 'don pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3644: dge slong gis rgod bag gi bsam pas bsnyen par
NK118(se)002:3645: ma rdzogs pa dang lhan cig tu chos kyi tshig
NK118(se)002:3646: gdangs sna tshogs kyis 'don par byas na'o //
NK118(se)002:3647: bdun pa gnas ngan len brjod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3648: pham lhag gang rung byung ba'i dge slong la gnas
NK118(se)002:3649: ngan len gleng bar ma bskos bzhin du brjod yul
NK118(se)002:3650: dge slong min pa'i gang zag bslab bya la mi
NK118(se)002:3651: mkhas pa'i drung du pham lhag gi ltung ba brjod
NK118(se)002:3652: cing go ba'o // brgyad pa mi chos bla ma bden par smra ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3653: nya pa'i rigs kyi dge slong lnga brgya la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3654: mi chos bla ma'i yon tan thob pa'i dge slong
NK118(se)002:3655: gis yul bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa la dgos pa
NK118(se)002:3656: khyad par can med bzhin du de thob bo zhes
NK118(se)002:3657: smras pa yul gyis go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3658: dgu pa bshes ngor byed ces skur pa 'debs pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3659: mdza' bo dang sa las skyes la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3660: dge 'dun gyi bya ba byed pa'i dge slong la
NK118(se)002:3661: zas las gzhan pa'i rung ba tshad ldan gyi yo
NK118(se)002:3662: byad cung zad byin pa la mi bzod pas /
NK118(se)002:3663: dge 'dun gyi rdzas gang zag la bshes ngor byas
NK118(se)002:3664: nas sbyin no zhes 'phyas pa pha rol pos go
NK118(se)002:3665: ba'o // bcu pa khyad du gsod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3666: gso sbyong gi dus lta bu so thar gyi mdo
NK118(se)002:3667: 'don pa'i tshe bslab pa'i gzhi phra zhing phra ba
NK118(se)002:3668: 'di dag 'don pas ci bya zhes khyad du gsod
NK118(se)002:3669: pa'i tshig smras pa gzhan gyis go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3670: bcu tshan gnyis pa sa bon gyi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3672: bdag gi ngor 'phya bsgo ba rnar gzon ni //
NK118(se)002:3673: ltung byung gleng la ma thos lan gzhan 'debs //
NK118(se)002:3674: khri dang 'ding ba ma bsdus gting song dang //
NK118(se)002:3675: dge slong skrod dang tho mtshams phyis gnon byas //
NK118(se)002:3676: mal khris bug dbyung srog chags ldan pa'i chu //
NK118(se)002:3677: r+ts+war 'debs gtsug lag pha gu rim gnyis brtsig /
NK118(se)002:3680: dang po sa bon dang skye ba 'jig pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3681: 'di dang bcu pa dag drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3682: dge slong gis nas sogs sa bon dang /
NK118(se)002:3683: myu gu sogs skye ba gang rung /
NK118(se)002:3684: rang gi chos su grub pa /
NK118(se)002:3687: rang r+ts+was bcings pa sogs kyi rkyen dang ldan pa ma yin par /
NK118(se)002:3688: rang gis nyams par byed dam gzhan byed du 'jug kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:3689: nyams pa'i tshe shing re re dang /
NK118(se)002:3690: r+ts+wa nyag ma re re dang /
NK118(se)002:3691: sa bon re re la de dang de 'joms pa'i ltung byed re rer 'gyur zhing /
NK118(se)002:3692: star ka la sogs pa'i 'bras bu smin pa sdong
NK118(se)002:3693: bu las bral bar byas pa sogs la nyes byas
NK118(se)002:3694: so // 'dir rung ba byas pa ni /
NK118(se)002:3695: shing thog sogs la mes reg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3696: mtshon dang sen mo dang ne tso sogs kyis rma gtod pa sogs kyis rung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:3697: dus rung ma gtogs pa'i sman gzhan gsum phyi dro
NK118(se)002:3698: longs spyod pa'i tshe chu grang mo gtor bas rung
NK118(se)002:3699: bar byas pa'o // gnyis pa 'phya ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3700: mdza' bo dang sa las skyes dag la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3701: dge 'dun gyi zhal ta chos dang mthun par byas
NK118(se)002:3702: sam byed bzhin pa'i dge slong rang la gnas mal
NK118(se)002:3703: sogs ngan pa stob pa po ma yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:3704: bdag gi ngor 'dis ngan pa stob bo zhes sogs dngos su'am /
NK118(se)002:3705: kha cig 'di ltar byed do zhes zur gyis 'phya na'ang rung ste 'phyas pa go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3707: zhes pas 'phya ba po de nyid dge 'dun gyis
NK118(se)002:3708: gsol ba'i las kyis ngan pa'i grangs su bcug pa
NK118(se)002:3710: gsum pa bsgo ba rnar gzon pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3711: 'di dang dgu pa koo sham+bira 'dun pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3712: dge slong ltung ba byung ba phyir bcos la 'god
NK118(se)002:3713: pa'i phyir ltung ba gleng ba lta bu chos mthun
NK118(se)002:3714: gyi bsgo ba dang dri ba dris pa na /
NK118(se)002:3715: de ma thos pa ltar ram khyad gsod lta bus /
NK118(se)002:3716: de'i lan mi smra bar lan gzhan log par 'debs pa'i tshig smras pa yul gyis go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3717: bzhi pa khri dang zhes pa gnas mal gyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3718: gnyan yod du dge slong rab tu mang po la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3719: khri dang khri'u sogs dge 'dun gyi gnas mal la
NK118(se)002:3720: spyad nas rang gis ma bsdus shing gzhan la'ang ma
NK118(se)002:3721: bcol bar bla gab med sar bor bas chud zos
NK118(se)002:3722: pa'am / ma zos kyang gnas mal gyi nye 'khor nas 'dom zhe dgu 'das te phyin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3723: lnga pa 'ding ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3724: lho lam nas 'ongs pa'i dge slong gnyis la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3725: dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang srog chags skye ba'i
NK118(se)002:3726: nyes dmigs yod sar r+ts+wa la sogs pa'i 'ding ba
NK118(se)002:3727: bting ba rang ngam gzhan bskos kyis ma bsdus par
NK118(se)002:3728: bor bas srog chags skyes pa sogs chud zos sam
NK118(se)002:3729: / ma zos kyang nye 'khor las 'das te song ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3730: drug pa skrod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3731: 'di dang phyi ma gnyis ka 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3732: dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang nas dge slong gzhan
NK118(se)002:3733: zhe sdang gis skrod dam skrod du bcug pas de
NK118(se)002:3735: bdun pa phyis gnon byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3736: dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang du sngar zhugs pa'i
NK118(se)002:3737: dge slong gzhan la tho 'tshams pa'i bsam pas lus
NK118(se)002:3738: ngag gang rung gis gnod pa brtsams te zil gyis
NK118(se)002:3739: mnan pa'o // brgyad pa rtsa ba 'byung ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3740: gnyan yod du nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3741: dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang gi steng thog snyi
NK118(se)002:3742: ba la gnas mal gyi khri rkang rnon po btsugs
NK118(se)002:3743: te 'dug pas bug pa thal byung du brdol ba'o
NK118(se)002:3744: // dgu pa 'debs pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3745: srog chags dang bcas pa'i chu dang r+ts+wa shing sogs
NK118(se)002:3746: la der shes bzhin du 'debs pa dang spyod pa
NK118(se)002:3747: gang rung byed dam byed du bcug pas srog chags
NK118(se)002:3748: ji snyed shi ba de snyed kyi ltung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3749: bcu pa rim pa lhag par rtsig pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3750: gzhi mi brtan pa dang chu khung ma gtod pa
NK118(se)002:3751: sogs 'jig rkyen yod par shes bzhin du spyod lam
NK118(se)002:3752: bzhi shong yan chad kyi gtsug lag khang rang ngam
NK118(se)002:3753: bskos pas nyin gcig la pha gu'i rim pa 'jim
NK118(se)002:3754: pa dang bcas pa gnyis sam gsum las lhag pa
NK118(se)002:3755: brtsigs pa'o // bcu tshan gsum pa ma bskos pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3757: ma bskos chos ston bskos kyang nyi nub dang //
NK118(se)002:3758: kha zas phyi ston gos brtsems chos gos sbyin //
NK118(se)002:3759: don mthun lam 'grogs gru de gyen mthur 'gro //
NK118(se)002:3760: dben par gcig 'dug pa dang 'greng ba dang //
NK118(se)002:3761: sbyor bcug zas za rnams ni spang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:3762: 'di man zhes pa bcu tshan gcig pu 'di dge
NK118(se)002:3763: slong ma nyid la brten par shes pa'i ched du'o
NK118(se)002:3765: dang po ma bskos par ston pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3766: 'di dang drug pa bdun pa bcu pa rnams drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3767: dge slong ma'i ston par ma bskos sam /
NK118(se)002:3768: bskos kyang mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i dge slong
NK118(se)002:3769: gis dge slong ma la chos bstan cing des go
NK118(se)002:3770: ba'o // gnyis pa nyi ma nub kyi bar du ston pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3771: 'di dang gsum pa dag dga' byed la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3772: dge slong ma'i ston par bskos kyang 'jigs pa dang
NK118(se)002:3773: bcas pa'i gnas su dge slong ma la nyi ma
NK118(se)002:3774: nub nas kyang chos bstan cing des go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3775: gsum pa zas ngor ston pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3776: dge slong ma'i ston par 'os shing bskos pas rnyed pa'i phyir chos mi ston kyang /
NK118(se)002:3777: phrag dog gis zas cung zad tsam gyi phyir chos
NK118(se)002:3778: ston par byed do zhes skur ba btab pa yul
NK118(se)002:3779: gyis go ba'o // bzhi pa gos byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3780: 'di dang brgyad pa dang dgu pa rnams 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3781: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma'i gos brtsems te bzo grub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3782: lnga pa gos sbyin pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3783: ded dpon las rab tu byung ba'i dge slong la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3784: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma la bshes
NK118(se)002:3785: ngo tsam gyi phyir rang gi chos gos rung ba
NK118(se)002:3786: tshad ldan byin pa des lag tu thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3787: drug pa lhan cig lam du 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3788: dge slong gang 'jigs pa med pa'i sa'i lam du
NK118(se)002:3789: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma dang lhan
NK118(se)002:3790: cig don mthun pas 'gron thabs su 'grogs te 'gro
NK118(se)002:3791: na rgyang grags re re 'das pa la ltung ba
NK118(se)002:3792: re re dang / rgyang grags phyed re la nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:3793: bdun pa lhan cig grur 'jug pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3794: sngar bzhin dge slong ma dang lhan cig grur zhugs
NK118(se)002:3795: nas thad ka min par rgyun las bzlog ste gyen
NK118(se)002:3796: dang rgyun phyogs su mthur du phyin nas rgyang grags
NK118(se)002:3797: las 'das pa'o // brgyad pa lhan cig 'dug pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3798: yul nye du ma yin pa'i bud med dang dben
NK118(se)002:3799: pa skyabs yod du khrims grogs med par 'dom gang
NK118(se)002:3800: tsam gyis bar chod kyang gnyis ka sa la 'dug
NK118(se)002:3801: na'o // dgu pa lhan cig 'greng ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3802: dben par bud med dam khyad par dge slong ma
NK118(se)002:3803: dang bar 'dom gang tsam du gnyis ka 'grengs te
NK118(se)002:3805: bcu pa zas sbyor du 'jug pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3806: dge slong gis dge slong ma nye du ma yin
NK118(se)002:3807: pa sbyin bdag khyim pa la dge slong rang yon
NK118(se)002:3808: tan dang mi ldan yang ldan no zhes rdzun gyi
NK118(se)002:3809: sgo nas dus rung gi zas sbyor du bcug ste
NK118(se)002:3810: zos pa'o // bcu tshan bzhi pa yang dang yang gi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3811: yang yang zas za mu stegs 'dug pa'i sar //
NK118(se)002:3812: zhag gcig lhag bsdad za dang lhung bzed do //
NK118(se)002:3813: za dang zos rjes bza' bca' za ba dang //
NK118(se)002:3814: spangs zas ltung 'byung ched du rdzun gyis stob //
NK118(se)002:3815: gnang min mtshams nang logs su 'dus nas za //
NK118(se)002:3816: dus min phyed yol za dang gsog 'jog za //
NK118(se)002:3817: sbyin len ma byas sman bzhi khar mid pa //
NK118(se)002:3818: bsod pa zhim pa'i zas slong /
NK118(se)002:3820: dang po yang yang za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3821: 'di nas bzhi ba'i bar dang dgu pa dang bcu pa rnams drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3822: bsod snyoms lan gcig gis gso mi nus pa'i nad kyis btab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:3823: dge 'dun dang mchod rten gyi las dang /
NK118(se)002:3825: dpag tshad phyed du phyin pa ma yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:3826: sra brkyang ma bting pa'i dge slong gis /
NK118(se)002:3827: khyim pa nye du ma yin pa la khru gang
NK118(se)002:3828: yan chad kyi gos kyi rnyed pa med pa'i dus
NK118(se)002:3829: rung gi kha zas dus nyi ma gcig la khyim
NK118(se)002:3830: gzhan du zos zin nas yang zas kyi bsod snyoms
NK118(se)002:3831: gnyis dang gsum sogs bslangs te yang yang zos pa'o
NK118(se)002:3832: // gnyis pa 'dug gnas su za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3833: nye du ma yin pa'i khyim pa'i gnas mu stegs
NK118(se)002:3834: pa'i 'dug gnas su zhag gcig las lhag par bsdad
NK118(se)002:3835: nas sbyin bdag gis ma stabs par nyi ma gnyis
NK118(se)002:3837: gsum pa lhung bzed do gsum las lhag pa len pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3838: nye du ma yin pa'i khyim nas ci bder stob
NK118(se)002:3839: pa ma yin par dus rung gi zas lhung bzed
NK118(se)002:3842: chung tshad gsum ste bre phyed dang lnga bslang du rung la /
NK118(se)002:3843: de las lhag pa bslangs te gnas gzhan du khyer nas zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3844: bzhi pa spangs pa za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3845: mu ge'i dus dang nad pa ma yin pa'i dge
NK118(se)002:3846: slong gis dus rung gi zas bza' bca' gang rung
NK118(se)002:3847: zos rjes / da de ring mi za'o snyam du blos bcad cing ngag tu brjod nas /
NK118(se)002:3848: slar yang lhag por ma byas par de nyid zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3849: gal te spangs pa za na /
NK118(se)002:3850: yul dge slong gnas ma btang ba'i mdun du tsog pus bzung nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK118(se)002:3851: yul des blangs nas kham gnyis sam gsum gyi phud za zhing /
NK118(se)002:3852: zas spangs pa yin na za mi dgos /
NK118(se)002:3853: gang ltar kyang des za ba po la gtad nas zar rung ngo //
NK118(se)002:3854: zas brtsams pas ldang bar mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:3855: zhes pa'i don zas za ba'i 'phro ma rdzogs pa
NK118(se)002:3856: la langs nas lhag ma phyis za na brtsams ldang
NK118(se)002:3857: ngo // lnga pa spangs pa stob pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3858: gnyan yod du dge slong rgan zhugs shig la bcas
NK118(se)002:3859: te yul dge slong gzhan gyis spangs pa'i zas lhag
NK118(se)002:3860: por ma byas bzhin du de la ngan sems kyis
NK118(se)002:3861: ltung ba 'byung ba'i ched du lhag po byas so
NK118(se)002:3862: zhes rdzun gyis stob pa'i tshig smras pa des go
NK118(se)002:3863: nas zos na stob pa po la ltung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3864: drug pa 'dus shing za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3865: rgyal po'i khab tu lhas sbyin 'khor bcas la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3866: yang yang za ba'i skabs ltar na ba sogs gnang
NK118(se)002:3867: ba'i dus ma yin par mtshams nang du bsam pa
NK118(se)002:3868: mi mthun pas kun nas bslangs te dge 'dun spyi
NK118(se)002:3869: las logs su dge slong gsum yan chad dang lhan
NK118(se)002:3870: cig 'dus nas dus rung gi zas zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3871: bdun pa dus ma yin par za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3872: gnyan yod du gzhon nu bcu bdun sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3873: dus rung gi zas za ba'i dus ma yin pa gang zhe na /
NK118(se)002:3874: dge slong rang gang du gnas pa'i gling gi nyi
NK118(se)002:3875: ma phyed yol nas skya rengs dang po ma shar
NK118(se)002:3876: gyi bar te / dus der na ba sogs kyi
NK118(se)002:3877: rkyen med par zos na mgul du ji tsam mid
NK118(se)002:3878: pa de snyed kyi ltung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK118(se)002:3879: nad pas kyang za ba'i tshe nad pa la 'di
NK118(se)002:3880: ltar gnang ba yin snyam du dus dran bya dgos
NK118(se)002:3881: so // brgyad pa gsog 'jog byas pa za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3882: dge slong nag po pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3883: na ba sogs kyi rkyen med par sman bzhi po
NK118(se)002:3884: gang rung byin len byas pa rang dus las 'das
NK118(se)002:3885: pas gsog 'jog tu song zhing ma zhig pa mu
NK118(se)002:3886: ge'i dus min par zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3893: chud za ba sogs kyi rkyen med par zas gang
NK118(se)002:3894: la byin len ma byas pa'i gong du dge slong
NK118(se)002:3897: dge slong rang dbang ba'i mtshams dngos sam de'i nye
NK118(se)002:3898: 'khor gyi nang du zas rjen pa zhig btsos pa
NK118(se)002:3900: mtshams nang der de 'dra'i dngos pos zhag lon pa /
NK118(se)002:3902: de 'dra'i dngos po mtshams kyi phyi nang gang rung du dge slong gis btsos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3903: de bzhin nad la phan pa'am mu ge'i dus min par zos na nyes byas su 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:3904: dgu pa byin len ma byed par za ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3905: gnas sgra mi snyan nam de dang 'dra ba ma yin pa /
NK118(se)002:3906: bdag nyid zan chad pa dang nad la phan pa
NK118(se)002:3907: sogs kyi rkyen med par chu dang so shing ma
NK118(se)002:3908: gtogs sman bzhi gang rung byin len ma byas pa
NK118(se)002:3909: la der 'du shes pas kham gcig yan chad mid
NK118(se)002:3911: nod pa po stob pa po'i glo dang rgyab na
NK118(se)002:3912: gnas pa ma yin pa la mtshams gzhan gyis bar
NK118(se)002:3914: nod pa pos kyang lag gnyis gan rkyal du bkan pas blang ngo //
NK118(se)002:3917: phrogs dang 'dril dang reg pa dang //
NK118(se)002:3918: bsngosa dang dge slong min gyur dang //
NK118(se)002:3920: dor ba yis ni byin len 'jig /
NK118(se)002:3922: bcu pa zas bsod pa slong ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3923: rang nyid na ba la sogs pa'i rkyen med cing
NK118(se)002:3924: dngos po 'o ma sogs yul dus der bsod par
NK118(se)002:3925: grags pa zhim pa'i zas bzang po khyim pa nye
NK118(se)002:3926: du ma yin pas ci bder ma stabs kyang chog
NK118(se)002:3927: mi shes par bslangs te zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3928: bcu tshan lnga pa chu dang gi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3930: chur spyod nyal po byed pa'i shul du nyal //
NK118(se)002:3931: dben pa'i skyabs su 'greng dang gcer bu rgyu //
NK118(se)002:3932: dmag blta dmag sar zhag gnyis lhag par bsdad //
NK118(se)002:3933: dmag gi ru bkod byed dang dge slong brdeg /
NK118(se)002:3934: brdeg brtsams gnas ngan len gyi ltung ba 'chab //
NK118(se)002:3936: dang po srog chags dang bcas pa'i chur spyod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3937: koo sham+b+hira 'dun pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3938: rang don du srog chags dang bcas pa'i chu la
NK118(se)002:3939: khrus dang btung ba dang gos 'khrud pa dang 'gog
NK118(se)002:3941: r+ts+wa shing gcod cing mer 'jug pa sogs sems can
NK118(se)002:3942: 'chi bar mthong yang ltos med du longs spyod na
NK118(se)002:3943: shi ba de snyed kyi ltung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3944: des na mar me'i 'od khang bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:3945: chu tshags bcang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:3946: chu tshags kyi dbye ba la /
NK118(se)002:3950: ril ba zhabs tshags can dang /
NK118(se)002:3952: gnyis pa nyal po byed pa'i khyim du 'du pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3953: 'di dang gsum pa brgyad pa dgu pa bcu pa rnams 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3954: khyim pa pho mo rang khyim du nyal po byed pa la zhugs pa'am der phyogs pa la /
NK118(se)002:3955: de dang nye ba'i sar nyal lam 'dug ste /
NK118(se)002:3956: de dag gis dge slong der yod pa'i tshor ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3957: gsum pa nyal po byed pa'i khyim du 'greng ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3958: nye ba'i sar zhes pa'i gnas su dge slong gi bar na skyabs yod par zhes dang /
NK118(se)002:3959: nyal lam 'dug ste zhes pa'i gnas su 'grengs te
NK118(se)002:3960: gnas pa zhes barje ba ma gtogs sngar ltar ro
NK118(se)002:3961: // bzhi pa gcer bu pa la zas byin pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3962: kun dga' bo la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3963: mu stegs gcer bu pa pho mo gang rung la
NK118(se)002:3964: nad pa dang nye du dang dge ba la sbyor
NK118(se)002:3965: ba'i don ma yin par rang dang de gnyis kas
NK118(se)002:3966: zar rung ba'i dus rung gi zas rang gi lag
NK118(se)002:3967: gis byin cing des thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3968: lnga pa dmag la blta ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3969: 'di dang drug pa dang bdun pa rnams drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:3970: rgyal pos bos pa sogs rkyen dgos dang mi ldan
NK118(se)002:3971: pa'i dge slong gis rang gi gnas kyi nye 'khor
NK118(se)002:3972: las 'das te dmag gi dpung la bltas pas mthong
NK118(se)002:3974: drug pa dmag gi nang du gnas pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3975: sngar bzhin rkyen dgos med par dmag gi nang du zhag gcig gam gnyis las lhag par bsdad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3976: bdun pa dpung gi yan lag nyams su myong ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3977: rkyen dgos kyis dmag nang du sdod dgos pa'i tshe
NK118(se)002:3978: yang rang dgar go mtshon la reg pa dang dpag
NK118(se)002:3979: dpung gi ru bsham bkod sogs byas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:3980: brgyad pa brdeg pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3981: khro bos dge slong gzhan la brdeg gam brdeg tu
NK118(se)002:3982: bcug pas phog pa na brdeg thengs de snyed kyi
NK118(se)002:3984: dgu pa brdeg pa gzas pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3985: khro bas dge slong gzhan la brdeg par brtsams pa ste brdeg tshul byas pa des go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:3986: bcu pa gnas ngan len 'chab pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:3987: mthol yul mtshan nyid dang ldan pa yod pa'i dbus
NK118(se)002:3988: su dge slong gzhan la gnas ngan len gyi ltung
NK118(se)002:3989: ba pham lhag gang rung byung ba ngo shes sam
NK118(se)002:3990: yid gnyis za ba dgos pa khyad par can med
NK118(se)002:3991: par bcabs te mtshan mo 'das na ltung byed de
NK118(se)002:3992: / pham lhag las gzhan pa'i ltung ba 'chab na nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:3993: bcu mtshan drug pa khyim dang gi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:3994: dge slong zas gcod me la reg tu bcug /
NK118(se)002:3995: dge 'dun las la 'dun phul phyir ldog smra //
NK118(se)002:3996: bsnyen ma rdzogs dang nub gnyis lhag par nyal //
NK118(se)002:3997: sdig lta'i chos lugs mi gtong phebs par smra //
NK118(se)002:3998: dge tshul sdig lta mi gtong lhan cig nyal //
NK118(se)002:3999: rung ba'i tshon min kha dog can gos gyon //
NK118(se)002:4000: rin chen dmag chas rol mo'i chas la reg /
NK118(se)002:4001: tsha dus rang gar khrus byed /
NK118(se)002:4003: dang po zan gcod du 'jug pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4004: 'di dang bzhi pa drug pa bdun pa rnams nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4005: khyim pa dge slong gzhan la dus rung gi zas
NK118(se)002:4006: 'dren pa na dge slong la ngan sems kyis de
NK118(se)002:4007: 'gog pa'i tshig smras nas gcod du bcug ste khyim
NK118(se)002:4009: gnyis pa me la reg pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4010: 'di dang brgyad pa dgu pa bcu pa rnams drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4011: rgod bag gi bsam pas me la reg gam reg tu bcug nas reg pa'i tshe na'o //
NK118(se)002:4012: de yang chos ldan gyi bya ba'i ched du me la reg dgos na /
NK118(se)002:4013: dus 'di'i tshe ston pas gnang ba yin snyam du
NK118(se)002:4014: dus dran byas nas reg na ltung bar mi 'gyur
NK118(se)002:4015: ro // gsum pa 'dun pa phyir bsgyur gyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4017: dge 'dun gyis dge slong gi ched du las byas
NK118(se)002:4018: shing chags pa la dang por 'dun pa phul nas
NK118(se)002:4019: / slar bdag gi 'dun pa phyir byin cig ces ldog pa'i tshig smras te don go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4020: las ma zin gong du phyirasgyura na ni las de mi chags par zad kyi /
NK118(se)002:4021: de ltung ba 'di 'byung ba ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:4022: bzhi pa nub lhag nyal gyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4023: dge slong gis bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa'i gang zag
NK118(se)002:4024: dang lhan cig gnas gcig tu nub gnyis nyal du
NK118(se)002:4025: rung la / de las lhag par na ba sogs
NK118(se)002:4026: kyi rkyen dgos med par nub gsum 'das nas bzhi
NK118(se)002:4028: gal te gnas khang gcig tu nyal kyang bar du
NK118(se)002:4029: khru phyed dang dgus chod na ltung ba med de
NK118(se)002:4031: 'di la bya gag 'phur nas 'bab pa'i lam ni bar du chod pa nyid yin no //
NK118(se)002:4032: zhes pas gnas gcig par mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:4033: lnga pa sdig lta mi gtong ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4034: dge slong 'chi ltas la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4035: chang 'thung ba dang phyi dro za ba sogs la
NK118(se)002:4036: nyes pa mi 'byung ngo zhes sdig lta'i chos lugs
NK118(se)002:4037: smra ba nyid zlog byed lnga pa'i mtha' la ma
NK118(se)002:4038: btang ba'o // drug pa spangs pa'i rjes phyogs kyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4039: dge 'dun gyis gnas nas phyungs pa'i dge slong dang
NK118(se)002:4040: lhan cig gtam phebs par smra ba sogs spyod lam
NK118(se)002:4041: mthun par byas nas mtshan de'i matha'i skad cig ma
NK118(se)002:4042: 'das pa'o // bdun pa bsnyil ba sdud pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4043: sdig lta mi gtong ba'i dge tshul dge 'dun gyis
NK118(se)002:4044: bsnyil ba dang lhan cig nyal ba sogs spyod lam
NK118(se)002:4045: la mthun par byas nas mtshan mtha' 'das pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4046: brgyad pa kha ma bsgyur ba'i gos gyon pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4047: chu tshags ma gtogs rung ba'i tshon gsum gyis kha
NK118(se)002:4048: ma bsgyur ba'i gos khru gang yan chad kha dog
NK118(se)002:4049: dkar po can gzhan gyis g.yogs med par gyon du
NK118(se)002:4050: ltung byed dang / nag po dang khra bo dang
NK118(se)002:4051: tshon chen brgyad kyis kha bsgyur ba la nyes byas
NK118(se)002:4052: ltung byed dang / so // dgu pa rin po che la reg pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4053: chud 'dza' ba dang sbyin bdag bsod nams 'dod pas
NK118(se)002:4054: stabs pa dang chos 'chad pa sogs don khyad par
NK118(se)002:4055: can sgrub pa'i skabs ma yin par rang mi dbang
NK118(se)002:4056: ba'i nor bu dang mu tig sogs rin po che'am
NK118(se)002:4057: / der ming gis smos pa mda' mdung sogs dmag chas dang /
NK118(se)002:4058: rnga bo che sogs rol mo'i chas la rgod bag gi bsam pas rang ngam bskos pas reg pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4059: bcu pa khrus byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4060: tsha ba'i dus dbyar zla gsum dang nad la phan
NK118(se)002:4061: pa sogs gnang ba'i dus ma yin par sngar khrus
NK118(se)002:4062: byas nas zla ba phyed ma 'das pa'i snga rol
NK118(se)002:4063: tu chu la rang dgar khrus byas te lus phyed
NK118(se)002:4064: chur nub pa'o // bcu tshan bdun pa bsam bzhin gyi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:4066: dge slong byas la 'gyod bskyed gag tshil sgog /
NK118(se)002:4067: chu rtse bud med gnas gcig nyal ba dang //
NK118(se)002:4068: dge slong dngangs byed de yin yo byad sbed //
NK118(se)002:4069: sngar byin gding med slar blangs spyod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4070: gzhi med skur btab bud med lhan cig tu //
NK118(se)002:4073: dang po dud 'gro gsod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4074: 'di dang gnyis pa dang drug pa rnams 'char ka la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4075: gsod 'dod kyi bsam pas dud 'gro'i rigs su gtogs
NK118(se)002:4076: pa gsod dam gsod du bcug ste rang ma shi
NK118(se)002:4077: ba'i gong du shi na ji snyed shi ba de
NK118(se)002:4079: gnyis pa 'gyod pa bskyed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4080: dge slong gzhan yid mi bde bar bya ba'i phyir
NK118(se)002:4081: khyood la sdom pa ma skyes zhes sam nyams so
NK118(se)002:4082: zhes sogs 'gyod pa bskyed pa'i tshig smras pa des
NK118(se)002:4083: go ba'o // gsum pa gag tshil byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4084: 'di dang bzhi pa bcu bdun sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4085: dge slong gzhan gyi lus la skyi g.ya' bar bya
NK118(se)002:4086: ba'i bsam pas mchan khung sogs la reg ste gag
NK118(se)002:4087: tshil sgog pa'o // bzhi pa chu la rtse ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4088: rgod bag gi bsam pas lus phyed nub pa'i chu la rtses sam rtser bcug pa las gyur pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4089: lnga pa bud med dang lhan cig nyal ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4091: dge slong gis khrims grogs med par bud med dang
NK118(se)002:4092: lhan cig gnas gcig tu gnyis ka nyal ba'i spyod
NK118(se)002:4093: lam gyis mtshan mo'i mtha' 'das pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4094: drug pa dngangs par byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4095: dge slong gis dge slong gzhan dngangs par byed 'dod
NK118(se)002:4096: pas yid du mi 'ong ba'i 'jigs pa sna tshogs
NK118(se)002:4097: ston nam ston du bcug pas de skrag pa skyes
NK118(se)002:4098: pa'o // bdun pa sbed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4100: dge slong gis rab byung sde lnga gang yang rung
NK118(se)002:4101: ba de'i chos gos dang lhung bzed sogs 'tsho ba'i
NK118(se)002:4102: yo byad rku 'dod dang phan sems ma yin par
NK118(se)002:4103: sbed dam sbed du bcug ste sbas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4104: brgyad pa gdengs med par spyod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4106: dge slong gzhan gyi gos sngar rang gis byin pa
NK118(se)002:4107: rku sems dang yid gcugs min par des gnang ba'i
NK118(se)002:4108: gdengs med bzhin du slar blangs nas ci dgar longs
NK118(se)002:4109: spyad pa'o // dgu pa skur 'debs kyi ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4110: mdza' bo dang sa las skyes la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4111: mthong thos dogs gsum gyi gzhi med pa'i dge slong
NK118(se)002:4112: gzhan la lhag ma bcu gsum gang rung gis skur
NK118(se)002:4113: pa btab cing des go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4114: bcu pa bud med dang lhan cig lam du 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4115: gnyan yod du 'gro ba'i dge slong zhig la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4116: dge slong gis nye du ma yin pa'i bud med
NK118(se)002:4117: dang lhan cig skyes pa'i khrims grogs med par lam
NK118(se)002:4118: du 'gro na rgyang grags re re 'das pa ltung
NK118(se)002:4120: de'i phyed la nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:4121: bcu tshan brgyad pa mgron mang rkun ma zhes pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:4123: nyi shu ma lon pa la brnyes rdzogs phog /
NK118(se)002:4124: sa brko mgron pos zla bzhi lhag par zas //
NK118(se)002:4125: mi shes brjod dang 'thab pa'i nyan rna byed //
NK118(se)002:4126: nyes med mi smra 'gro dang mi gus 'gal //
NK118(se)002:4127: chang 'thung dus min phyi dro grong du rgyu //
NK118(se)002:4129: dang po rkun ma dang lhan cig lam du 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4130: 'gron lam du 'gro ba'i dge slong la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4131: dge slong gis chom rkun nam sho gam ma byin
NK118(se)002:4132: pa'i tshong pa dang lhan cig lam du 'gro na'ang
NK118(se)002:4134: rgyang grags re re la ltung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4135: gnyis pa nyi shu ma lon pa rdzogs par byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4136: moong+gala gyi bu la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4137: bsgrub bya skyes pa mngal shol rtsis kyang lo nyi
NK118(se)002:4138: shu ma lon pa la der 'du shes sam the
NK118(se)002:4139: tshom za bas bsnyen rdzogs phog na /
NK118(se)002:4140: las brjod pa gsum pa'i bya ba brjod pa rdzogs
NK118(se)002:4141: nas byed pa brjod pa'i 'go brtsam pa'i tshe mkhan
NK118(se)002:4143: slob dpon dang dge 'dun la nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:4144: gsum pa sa brko ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4145: 'di dang bzhi pa dang lnga pa rnams drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4146: dge slong gis 'jig rten la grags pa'i sa sra
NK118(se)002:4147: zhing 'thas par gnas pa dgos pa khyad par can
NK118(se)002:4148: med par barko'am brkor bcug ste sor bzhi yan chad
NK118(se)002:4149: brkos pa'o // bzhi pa mgron du gnyer ba las ring du 'dug pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4150: sbyin bdag gis dus ji tsam mgron du bos pa las lhag pa 'dug pa'am /
NK118(se)002:4151: tshigs bzhag pa med na zla ba bzhi las lhag par sdod nas zas zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4152: lnga pa bslab pa nye bar 'jog pa spong ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4153: dge slong gzhan gyis rang nyid bslab pa la slob par bskul ba na /
NK118(se)002:4154: bskul ba po la khyod kyis mi shes pas gzhan
NK118(se)002:4155: shes pa la ma dris kyi bar du mi slob
NK118(se)002:4156: bo zhes pa lta bu'i khyad gsod kyis spong ba'i
NK118(se)002:4158: drug pa nyan rna byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4160: dge slong rang dang rtsod zlar gyur pa'i dge slong
NK118(se)002:4161: gzhan gnyis man chad gros byed pa la rtsod pa
NK118(se)002:4162: zhi 'dod ma yin par 'thab mo de sbar ba'i
NK118(se)002:4163: ched du nyan rna byas pas rang gis don go
NK118(se)002:4164: ba'o // bdun pa mi smra bar 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4166: rang kha skong du 'os pa'i dge slong gis gso
NK118(se)002:4167: sbyong sogs dge 'dun gyi chos ldan gyi las gral
NK118(se)002:4168: du dang por 'dus nas gsol ba tsam yang ma
NK118(se)002:4169: byas pa'i gong du dge 'dun mthun pa sgrub byed
NK118(se)002:4170: kyi 'dun pa ma phul ba'am ltag 'og gi dge
NK118(se)002:4171: slong la 'gro ba mi smra bar thos pa'i nyer
NK118(se)002:4173: gsol ba thos nas phyin na nyes byas dang /
NK118(se)002:4174: rang kha skong du mi 'os pa sogs la ltung ba med do //
NK118(se)002:4175: brgyad pa ma gus pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4176: glang chen lhas kyi bdag po'i bu nag pa la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4177: dge slong gis sangs rgyas dngos su bzhugs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4179: dge 'dun gyi tha snyad pa dge bskos te gsum
NK118(se)002:4180: po gang yang rung bas chos ldan gyi bka' bsgo
NK118(se)002:4181: ba'i don la kho bos sgrub mi nus so zhes
NK118(se)002:4182: shad sbyang med par ma gus pas de las bzlog
NK118(se)002:4184: dgu pa chang 'thung ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4186: phabs btab pa 'bru'i chang dang rgun chang sogs bcos pa'i chang dang /
NK118(se)002:4187: de dag gi sbag ma dang tshigs ma sogs myos
NK118(se)002:4188: pa'i nus pa can rnams 'thung ngam za bar 'dod
NK118(se)002:4189: pas mgul du mid pa na ltung byed de /
NK118(se)002:4190: bskol bas chang gi ro nus nyams par byas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4191: nad pa la phan pa'i phyir khar bsrel ba tsam
NK118(se)002:4192: dang lus la bkud pa tsam la nyes pa med
NK118(se)002:4193: do // bcu pa dus min par grong du 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4194: dus ma yin pa'i phyi dro ste /
NK118(se)002:4195: rang gling gi nyi ma phyed yol nas skya rengs
NK118(se)002:4196: ma shar gyi bar du rkyen dgos med cing der
NK118(se)002:4197: 'khod kyi grogs la ma smras par khyim pa'i grong
NK118(se)002:4198: du rgyu bar byed pas sgo gtan dang nye 'khor
NK118(se)002:4199: las 'das pa'o // bcu tshan dgu pa chos ston gyi sde tshan ni /
NK118(se)002:4200: zas bcas phyi dro rgyu dang khyim gsum 'das //
NK118(se)002:4201: rgyal po btsun mor rtse ba'i khab tu nyal //
NK118(se)002:4202: mdo sogs 'don la da gdod shes zer dang //
NK118(se)002:4203: rin chen khab ral khri rkang tshad lhag bzos //
NK118(se)002:4204: ngan sems shing bal khri steng brdal te bgos //
NK118(se)002:4205: gding g.yan ras chen chos gos tshad lhag go //
NK118(se)002:4207: dang po grong gzhan du rgyu ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4208: 'di dang drug pa dang bcu pa rnams nyer dga' la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4209: dge slong gis snga dro rang tshig gis sbyin bdag khyim pa'i gnas su zas la spyan drangs nas /
NK118(se)002:4210: dus la brim zhes ma bsgos par rang nyid khyim
NK118(se)002:4211: gcig nas gcig tu rgyu bas khyim gsum 'das te
NK118(se)002:4212: dge 'dun gyi gdugs tshod la gnod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4213: phyi dro khyim bzhi phan chad 'das pas dge 'dun gyi chos kyi longs spyod la gnod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4214: gnyis pa rgyal po'i pho brang du nub mo 'gro ba'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4216: chos ldan gyi don du bos pa sogs dgos pa
NK118(se)002:4217: khyad par can med bzhin du rgyal po btsun mo
NK118(se)002:4218: dang lhan cig rtse ba'i khab ste btsun mo dang
NK118(se)002:4219: bcas pa'i pho brang du nyi ma dmar thag chod
NK118(se)002:4220: nas skya rengs tha ma ma shar gyi bar 'gro
NK118(se)002:4221: na gnas de'i sgo gtan nam /
NK118(se)002:4223: nub mor ma zad nyin mo phyin nas mtshan la der nyal kyang 'dra'o //
NK118(se)002:4224: gsum pa bslab gzhi khyad du gsod pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4225: 'di dang lnga pa dag drug sde la bcas te /
NK118(se)002:4226: so thar gyi mdo lan gnyis yan chad thos shing
NK118(se)002:4227: mdo de la don de yod pa sngar nas shes
NK118(se)002:4228: kyang shes rin mi chog par ston pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:4229: gso sbyong gi dus su don 'di yod pa da
NK118(se)002:4230: gdod shes so zhes 'dul bar gtogs pa'i bslab pa
NK118(se)002:4231: khyad gsod kyi tshig smras pa pha rol pos go
NK118(se)002:4233: mdo sde sogs la nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:4234: bzhi pa khab ral 'chos pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4235: 'di dang bdun pa dang brgyad pa dang dgu pa
NK118(se)002:4236: rnams dge slong rab tu mang po la bcas te
NK118(se)002:4237: / dkon zhing rin thang che ba'i rdzas ba so
NK118(se)002:4238: sogs la khab ral byed dam byed du bcug ste
NK118(se)002:4239: / zin pa'o // lnga pa khri rkang 'chos pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4240: dge slong gis dge 'dun gyi khri'am khri'u'i rkang pa
NK118(se)002:4241: bu gar gzhug pa man chad khru gang tshad yin
NK118(se)002:4242: pas de las lhag pa bazo'am bzor bcug ste zin
NK118(se)002:4243: pa'o // drug pa shing bal gyis gos par byas pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4244: dge 'dun gyi khri dang khri'u'i steng du dge slong
NK118(se)002:4245: gis ngan sems kyis shing bal brdal te gos par
NK118(se)002:4246: byas pa'o // bdun pa gding ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4248: dgu pa dbyar gyi gos ras chen rnams tshad lhag byed pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4249: dge slong gis rang don du de gsum rang rang
NK118(se)002:4250: gi tshad las lhag pa byed dam byed du bcug
NK118(se)002:4251: ste zin pa na de dang de'i ltung byed do
NK118(se)002:4253: gding ba srid du khru gsum dang zheng du khru do dang sor drug /
NK118(se)002:4254: g.yan dgab kyi srid du khru drug dang zheng du khru gsum /
NK118(se)002:4255: ras chen gyi srid du khru dgu dang /
NK118(se)002:4256: zheng du khru gsum dang sor bco brgyad do //
NK118(se)002:4257: de yang khru dang sor gyis 'jal ba thams cad
NK118(se)002:4258: la rang rang gi 'jal byed kyi phyed kyis lhag
NK118(se)002:4259: na ltung ba'o // 'di dag gi ltung ba bshags pa'i tshe /
NK118(se)002:4260: khab ral bcog cing khri'i shing bal bsdus nas dang /
NK118(se)002:4261: khri rkang gding g.yan ras chen bzhi'i lhag po bcad nas bshags dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:4264: bcad dam zhes ma dris na nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:4265: bcu pa bde bar gshegs pa'i chos gos kyi tshad las gyur pa'i ltung byed ni /
NK118(se)002:4266: ston pa'i lus tshad tsam med par de'i chos gos kyi tshad dam /
NK118(se)002:4267: de bas lhag pa byed dam byed du bcug ste zin pa las gyur pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4268: de la ston pa'i chos gos kyi tshad ni /
NK118(se)002:4269: srid du ston pa rang gi khru lnga yin pas mi phal ba'i khru bco lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:4270: zheng du ston pa'i khru gsum la phal pa'i khru dgu yod de /
NK118(se)002:4271: ston pa'i khru re la mi 'bring po'i khru gsum re yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:4272: lnga pa sor bshags la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:4274: so sor bshags bya'i sde ni bzhi yin te //
NK118(se)002:4276: smre sngags kyi rnam pas so sor bshags dgos pas na sor bshags kyi sde zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4278: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:4279: sor bshags kyi ming gis phyir bcos byas na dag tu rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4282: khyim pa'i gzhi las gyur pa gnyis gnyis te bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4284: dge slong ma las grong du zas bslangs zos //
NK118(se)002:4285: khyim du dge slong ma bsgos ma bzlos zos //
NK118(se)002:4286: bslab sdom sbyin las rung min bslangs te zos //
NK118(se)002:4287: nags ma myul bar dgon par bslangs zos bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4289: dang po nyer dga' dang phyi ma gsum drug sde la bcas /
NK118(se)002:4290: de la dang po dge slong ma la zas len pa'i sor bshags ni /
NK118(se)002:4291: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong mas rang nyid
NK118(se)002:4292: bza' ba'i ched du bsgrubs pa'i dus rung gi zas
NK118(se)002:4294: lam po che gang rung du dge slong gis bslangs te zos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4295: gnyis pa dge slong mas ngos mgron byed pa ma bzlog par zos pa'i sor bshags ni /
NK118(se)002:4296: dge slong gsum yan chad khyim pas mgron du bos
NK118(se)002:4297: pa na dge slong mas bsko bsham ste gral rim
NK118(se)002:4298: par 'brim du mi 'jug par ngos mgron gyis 'di
NK118(se)002:4299: la phul cig ces bsgo ba de dge slong gcig
NK118(se)002:4300: gis ma bzlog par dge slong ji snyed pas zos
NK118(se)002:4301: pa de thams cad la sor bshags kyi kha na
NK118(se)002:4303: gsum pa bslab pa bral te khyim du 'jug pa'i sor bshags ni /
NK118(se)002:4304: dge 'dun blo mthun pas gsol ba'i las kyis khyim
NK118(se)002:4305: pa ci rigs las dgag bya dang dgos pa'i dbang
NK118(se)002:4306: gis zas mi slong ba'i bslab sdom sbyin pa na
NK118(se)002:4307: / khrims der gtogs pa'i dge slong gis /
NK118(se)002:4308: de las len rung ba lo ma sogs mod pa
NK118(se)002:4309: ma yin pa'i dus rung gi zas bslangs te zos
NK118(se)002:4310: pa'o // bzhi pa nags ma brtags pa las gyur pa'i sor bshags ni /
NK118(se)002:4311: grong nas rgyang grags spags pa'i 'jigs bcas kyi dgon
NK118(se)002:4312: par dge 'dun gyis nags myul bar bskos pa'i dge
NK118(se)002:4313: slong gis / dge 'dun dang sbyin bdag gi gnod
NK118(se)002:4314: pa bsrung ba'i bya ba 'dis ci bya snyam pas
NK118(se)002:4315: nags ma myul bar khyim pa las dus rung gi
NK118(se)002:4317: drug pa nyes byas la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:4319: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis zhes grags pa //
NK118(se)002:4320: zhes pa nyes pa phra mo'i rang bzhin yin pas na nyes byas te /
NK118(se)002:4322: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i rgyud kyi bcas 'gal gyi ltung ba gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:4323: nyes byas kyi ming gis phyir bcos byas na dag tu rung ba /
NK118(se)002:4325: mdo'i sdoms kyis bsdus pa la brgya dang bcu gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:4326: 'di rnams phal che ba drug sde la bcas so //
NK118(se)002:4327: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la dgu las /
NK118(se)002:4328: dang po gos bgo ba'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4329: sham thabs zlum min brtsengs 'jol glang sna 'dra //
NK118(se)002:4330: lteb dang phur ma gdengs ka lta bu bdun //
NK118(se)002:4331: zlum min ring thung stod gsum gos kyi bcu //
NK118(se)002:4333: sham thabs kyi gyon lugs la /
NK118(se)002:4334: ya mtha' dang ma mtha' mtho dman mi mnyam pas zlum por ma bgos pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4335: ha cang brtsengs pas pus mor ma sleb pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4336: ha cang 'jol bas long bu la reg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4337: glang po'i sna ltar mas zur gyi grwa mdun du 'phyang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4338: ska rags kyi gong du t+aa la'i lo ma ltar lteb pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4339: ska rags kyi bar nas 'bru'i phur ma ltar 'bur ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4340: ska rags kyi steng du sbrul gyi gdengs ka ltar
NK118(se)002:4341: mtho dman du 'dug pa ma yin pa ste bdun
NK118(se)002:4342: dang / stod g.yogs kyi gyon lugs la /
NK118(se)002:4343: snam sbyar dang bla gos zlum por ma bgos pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4345: ha cang thung ba ma yin pa gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:4346: de ltar bcu la bslab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4347: gnyis pa spyod yul du 'gro ba'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4348: ma bsdams bgo ba ca co mig g.yengs dang //
NK118(se)002:4349: ring blta mgo bstums gos bardzesa phrag la gzar //
NK118(se)002:4350: lag pa gnya' gong bsnol dang ltag par bsnol //
NK118(se)002:4351: mchong rkyang rkang pa'i brang dang rting btsugs 'gro //
NK118(se)002:4352: lag pa dkur brten lus bsgyur lag pa g.yug /
NK118(se)002:4353: mgo bsgyur phrag pa sprad dang lag sbrel rnams //
NK118(se)002:4354: mi byed khyim 'gro'i spyod yul nyi shu'o //
NK118(se)002:4356: khyim du 'gro ba'i tshe dran shes kyis lus ngag ma bsdams par 'jug pa /
NK118(se)002:4357: bla gos dang thang gos legs par bgo ba ma yin pa /
NK118(se)002:4358: ca co'i sgra dang bcas pa /
NK118(se)002:4359: mig g.yas g.yon du g.yengs pas blta ba /
NK118(se)002:4360: mig gnya' shing gang las ring bar blta ba /
NK118(se)002:4362: sham thabs 'doms snang bar bardzesa pa /
NK118(se)002:4363: bla gos phrag pa'i phyogs gnyis kar gzar ba /
NK118(se)002:4364: lag gnyis mdun nas gnya' gong du bsnol ba /
NK118(se)002:4365: lag gnyis rgyab nas ltag par bsnol ba /
NK118(se)002:4367: ha cang gom pa che bas sgyid pa rkyang bskum byed cing 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4368: rting pa bteg nas rkang pa'i brang gis 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4369: rting pa gtsugs te tsog pus 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4370: lag dkur brten nas gru sbyangs te 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4371: lus skyog por bsgyur zhing 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4372: mgo lcog cing bsgyur nas 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4373: gzhan dang phrag pa sprad de 'gro ba /
NK118(se)002:4374: gzhan dang lag sbrel nas 'gro ba rnams te /
NK118(se)002:4375: de ltar skyon nyi shu po de rnams mi byed
NK118(se)002:4376: pa ste spangs nas spyod yul gyi khyim du zhi
NK118(se)002:4377: dul gyi spyod pas 'gro ba la bslab par bya'o
NK118(se)002:4378: // gsum pa stan la 'dug pa'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4379: stan la ma bsgos ma brtags 'phongs rdeb dang //
NK118(se)002:4380: rkang brkyang bsnol dang barla bsnol long bu brtsegs //
NK118(se)002:4381: khri 'og rkang dgug rkang pa gdangs te 'dug /'doms mthong rnams spang 'dug tshul dgu yin no //
NK118(se)002:4383: khyim gzhan du khyim bdag gis ma bsgos par stan la 'dug pa /
NK118(se)002:4384: de bzhin du stan la srog chags yod med ma brtags pa /
NK118(se)002:4385: lus kyi lci phab la 'phongs rdeb pa /
NK118(se)002:4386: rkang pa brkyang ste bsnol ba /
NK118(se)002:4388: long bu'i steng du long bu brtsegs te /
NK118(se)002:4389: hor 'dug gi rnam pas khri'i 'og tu rkang pa bkug pa /
NK118(se)002:4390: rkang pa phan tshun gdangs pa /
NK118(se)002:4391: 'doms snang bar byas nas sdod pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4392: de ltar 'dug tshul gyi skyon dgu spangs nas khyim
NK118(se)002:4393: du mnyam gzhag gi 'dug stangs skyil krung gis 'dug
NK118(se)002:4394: go // bzhi pa zas blang ba'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4395: legs par mi len mu kha mnyam par len //
NK118(se)002:4396: mthar chags mi len lhung bzed zur mig blta //
NK118(se)002:4397: bzed sngas sngar byung sbas nas bzed pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4398: snod gzhan steng bzed spang ba zas blang brgyad //
NK118(se)002:4400: grong dang gtsug lag khang sogs thams cad du 'dul
NK118(se)002:4401: ba dang mi 'gal bar zas legs par mi len
NK118(se)002:4402: pa / snod kyi mu dang khad chad du len pa /
NK118(se)002:4403: 'bras mchan dang tshod ma ste zan dang byan mnyam par len pa /
NK118(se)002:4404: gral rim ltar mthar chags su mi len pa /
NK118(se)002:4405: lhung bzed la yid gtad de mi len par zur mig gis blta ba /
NK118(se)002:4406: zas 'dren pa ma sleb par snod bzed sngas pa /
NK118(se)002:4407: lhag po 'dod pas zas sngar byung sbas nas yang bzed pa /
NK118(se)002:4408: snod gzhan zas kyi steng du bzung nas bzed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4409: de ltar zas blang pa'i skyon brgyad spang ba la bslab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4410: lnga pa zas za ba'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4411: 'gal za kham che chung dang ran par min //
NK118(se)002:4412: kha gdangs za bzhin smra dang tsug tsug dang //
NK118(se)002:4413: cag cag hu hu phu phu lce phyung za //
NK118(se)002:4414: 'bru nas gud phye zas la skyon 'phya dang //
NK118(se)002:4415: kham gcig mkhur spo rkan tog kham 'phro bcad //
NK118(se)002:4416: lag pa 'dag 'byog lag sprug skyom skyom byed //
NK118(se)002:4417: mchod rten 'drar byed nyer gcig za tshe spang //
NK118(se)002:4419: thams cad du 'dul ba dang 'gal bas legs par mi za ba /
NK118(se)002:4422: rang ngam 'jig rten dang mthun pa'i kham ran pa ma yin pa /
NK118(se)002:4423: kham kha'i sgor ma sleb par kha gdang ba /
NK118(se)002:4424: za bzhin du gtam smra ba /
NK118(se)002:4425: za ba'i tshe skyur ba la tsug tsug /
NK118(se)002:4428: tsha ba la phu phu'i sgra dang bcas za ba /
NK118(se)002:4429: lce phyir phyungs te za ba /
NK118(se)002:4430: nas yos sogs 'bru re nas gud du phye nas za ba /
NK118(se)002:4431: sbyin bdag gi zas la skyon kha'o skyur ro sogs 'phya smod byed pa /
NK118(se)002:4432: kham gcig mkhur ba g.yas g.yon du spo zhing za ba /
NK118(se)002:4434: dud 'gro ltar kham 'phro bcad de za ba /
NK118(se)002:4435: lag pa la zas chags pa 'dag pa /
