NK118(se)002:4436: lhung bzed dang phor bu sogs lces 'dag pa /
NK118(se)002:4437: lag pa la zas chags pa sprug pa /
NK118(se)002:4438: zas dang bcas pa'i lhung bzed sogs skyom skyom byed pa /
NK118(se)002:4439: zas la mchod rten gyi gzugs 'dra ba bcos te gzhom zhing za bar byed pa rnams te /
NK118(se)002:4440: de ltar skyon nyer gcig po de rnams za ba'i tshe spang ba la bslab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4441: drug pa lhung bzed la spyod pa'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4442: lhung bzed la 'phya phyir blta lag pa ni //
NK118(se)002:4443: zas 'bags chu snod mi reg chu mi gtor //
NK118(se)002:4444: ma dris 'bags chu 'bo dang zas lhag bzhag /
NK118(se)002:4445: sa rjes gad kha ri gzar bang rim bzhir //
NK118(se)002:4446: mi bzhag gad g.yang rkan gzar du mi 'khru //
NK118(se)002:4447: langs dang chu drag mi gcu bcu bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4449: gzhan gyi lhung bzed la 'phya ba'i phyi blta bar mi bya /
NK118(se)002:4450: lag pa zas kyis 'bags pas chu snod la mi reg /
NK118(se)002:4451: zas dang bcas pa'i 'bags chu drung na gnas pa'i dge slong la mi gtor /
NK118(se)002:4452: khyim bdag la ma dris par zas dang 'bags pa'i khrud chu de'i khyim du 'bo bar mi bya /
NK118(se)002:4453: zas lhag lhung bzed du bzhag nas mi 'dor /
NK118(se)002:4454: lhung bzed 'og gzhi med pa'i sa rjen dang /
NK118(se)002:4456: ri do chad kyi g.yang gzar po dang /
NK118(se)002:4457: bang rim gzhol po'i rkan te bzhir mi bzhag go //
NK118(se)002:4458: de bzhin du lhung bzed gad kha dang /
NK118(se)002:4461: langs te lam gyi gzhi mdo rnams su mi bkru /
NK118(se)002:4462: 'bab chu drag po'i rgyun las ldog ste lhung bzed kyis chu mi gcu pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4463: de ltar lhung bzed la spyod pa'i bslab bya bcu bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4464: bdun pa chos 'chad pa'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4465: chos ston sde ni langs nyal rang dmar 'dug /
NK118(se)002:4466: mdun nas 'gro la phyi bshad lam po'i 'gram //
NK118(se)002:4467: mgo g.yogs bardzesa gzar lag pa gnya' ltag bsnol //
NK118(se)002:4468: do ker bcings dang zhwa gyon cod pan btags //
NK118(se)002:4469: phreng ba dang ni mgo dkris glang rta zhon //
NK118(se)002:4470: khyogs dang bzhon pa mchil lhwam gyon pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4471: 'khar ba gdugs mtshon ral gri dgra cha mda' //
NK118(se)002:4472: go cha gyon la mi bshad nyer drug go //
NK118(se)002:4474: nyan pa po min bzhin du 'dug pa la 'chad pa po langs te chos mi 'chad /
NK118(se)002:4475: de bzhin du nyal ba la 'dug pas mi 'chad /
NK118(se)002:4476: stan mthon por 'dug pa la 'chad pa po rang dma' bar 'dug pas mi 'chad /
NK118(se)002:4477: mdun nas 'gro ba la phyi bzhin 'ong bas mi 'chad /
NK118(se)002:4478: lam gyi dbus nas 'gro ba la lam po'i 'gram nas 'gro zhing mi 'chad do //
NK118(se)002:4479: mi na bar mgo g.yogs pa /
NK118(se)002:4482: lag pa gnya' gong du bsnol ba /
NK118(se)002:4483: lag pa ltag par bsnol ba /
NK118(se)002:4484: skra spyi bor bsdus te do ker bcings pa /
NK118(se)002:4486: mgo la cod pan btags pa /
NK118(se)002:4487: mgo la phreng ba bcings pa /
NK118(se)002:4489: glang po che dang rta la zhon pa /
NK118(se)002:4491: bzhon pa gzhan shing rta sogs la zhon pa /
NK118(se)002:4495: mdung sogs mtshon cha thogs pa /
NK118(se)002:4497: dgra cha ste mda' gzhu thogs pa /
NK118(se)002:4499: de ltar nyer drug la dge slong gis chos mi bshad de /
NK118(se)002:4500: nyan pa po na ba'i rkyen dbang du gyur pa la ni nyes pa med do //
NK118(se)002:4501: brgyad pa sgrub pa'i sde ni /
NK118(se)002:4502: sgrub tshul gsum ni 'grengs te bshang gci 'dor //
NK118(se)002:4503: chu dang r+ts+wa la bshang gci snabs mi 'dor //
NK118(se)002:4505: mi na bar 'grengs te bshang gci mi 'dor /
NK118(se)002:4506: gzhan du 'dor sa ma rnyed pa'i rkyen med par chu'i nang dang /
NK118(se)002:4507: r+ts+wa sngon yod pa'i sa phyogs su bshang gci dang
NK118(se)002:4508: mchil snams skyugs pa sogs mi 'dor ba ste gtsang
NK118(se)002:4509: sbra sgrub pa'i tshul gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:4510: dgu pa rgyu ba'i bslab bya gcig ni /
NK118(se)002:4511: shing la mi gang mthor 'dzeg rgyu gcig go //
NK118(se)002:4513: stag la sogs pa'i gnod pa med par shing la
NK118(se)002:4514: mi gang tsam las mtho ba 'dzeg par mi bya'o
NK118(se)002:4515: // gnyis pa dge slong ma'i bslab bya bshad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:4516: dge slong ma la pham brgyad lhag nyi shu //
NK118(se)002:4517: spang ltung so gsum ltung byed brgya brgyad cu //
NK118(se)002:4518: sor bshags bcu gcig nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK118(se)002:4519: sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi mdo tsam mo //
NK118(se)002:4520: zhes pas dge slong ma'i bslab bya la khrims sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:4521: dang po pham pa la brgyad las /
NK118(se)002:4522: mi tshangs spyod rku gsod dang rdzun //
NK118(se)002:4523: zhes pa bzhi ni thun mong pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4525: thun mong min pa bzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:4526: reg pa lus bkan 'chab dang bzlog pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4528: de ltar na dge slong ma la mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa mi 'byung bar thal /
NK118(se)002:4529: de'i snga rol du reg pham byung zin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK118(se)002:4531: skyes pa'i lus yongs rdzogs dang ma 'phrad par dbang
NK118(se)002:4532: po nyid 'phrad pa tsam gyi mi tshangs spyod 'byung
NK118(se)002:4534: gnyis pa lhag ma nyi shu la /
NK118(se)002:4535: bdun ni thun mong pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4537: gzhi med nas bka' blo mi bde ba'i bar ro //
NK118(se)002:4538: thun min ni bcu gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:4539: ci yang len dang len 'jug dang //
NK118(se)002:4540: mtshan bral nyin bral lam du 'jug /
NK118(se)002:4541: chu brgal rab 'byin shi nor len //
NK118(se)002:4542: bzod byed spong dang 'thab krol byed //
NK118(se)002:4545: gsum pa spang ltung so gsum la /
NK118(se)002:4546: thun mong pa ni bcu dgu ste /
NK118(se)002:4548: bcu tshan gnyis pa nas gser dngul la reg pa sogs gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:4553: ras chen bzhi ma gtogs drug po rnams so //
NK118(se)002:4554: thun min ni bcu bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:4555: lhung bzed zhag gcig 'das 'chang byin ma brlabs //
NK118(se)002:4556: sra brkyang 'byin dang mi 'byin rin chen slong //
NK118(se)002:4557: gos dang gos rgyu dang ni mal cha'i rgyu //
NK118(se)002:4558: dbyar khang rgyu rnams zas su bsgyur ba dang //
NK118(se)002:4559: mang la bsngosa dang dge 'dun bsngosa byin brlabs //
NK118(se)002:4560: bcings pa 'grol 'jug gos lci yang ba brtan //
NK118(se)002:4562: bzhi pa ltung byed brgya dang brgyad cu la /
NK118(se)002:4564: dge slong gi 'ba' zhig pa dgu bcu las /
NK118(se)002:4565: ma bskos pa la sogs pa'i bcu tshan dang /
NK118(se)002:4570: phyir ma bslangs par spyod pa /
NK118(se)002:4572: dbyar gyi ras chen las gyur pa ste bco brgyad ni dge slong ma la med cing /
NK118(se)002:4573: de lhag bdun cu rtsa gnyis ni thun mong pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4574: thun min la brgya rtsa brgyad de /
NK118(se)002:4577: khyim so bzung dang ma bzung bye brag las //
NK118(se)002:4578: bcu gnyis nyi shu ma lon rdzogs par byed //
NK118(se)002:4579: tshigs las 'das pa gnyis dang ma bslabs rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:4580: bslabs zin mi rdzogs chos tshong 'drid pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4581: 'khor mang gsog dang ma gnang sdud pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4582: 'khrul mo sbrum ma mya ngan gyis gzir dang //
NK118(se)002:4583: 'thab krol can te skyon can sdud pa bzhi //
NK118(se)002:4584: mi 'dogs mi 'dren mi slob nad pa'i g.yog /
NK118(se)002:4585: mi byed pa ste yal bar 'dor ba bzhi //
NK118(se)002:4586: 'dod rten 'dod rten ltar bcos ltar gnod dang //
NK118(se)002:4587: brten par bya ba 'chos pa'i ltung byed do //
NK118(se)002:4588: khyim pa dang ni dge slong yul dag la //
NK118(se)002:4589: brten nas bla gab yod med 'greng ba bzhi //
NK118(se)002:4590: de bzhin phan tshun shub cing smra ba bzhi //
NK118(se)002:4591: khyim pa las ni rig pa len dang klog /
NK118(se)002:4592: rma bcings 'grol du 'jug dang bu 'tsho dang //
NK118(se)002:4593: mtshan mo khyim gzhan nyal dang ma btags nyal //
NK118(se)002:4594: gcig nyal stan gcig spyod cing gnas pa btang //
NK118(se)002:4595: rang lus dge slong ma dang dge slob ma //
NK118(se)002:4596: dge tshul mo dang khyim mo mu stegs mo //
NK118(se)002:4597: dril phyis lnga ste bkru bshal byed du 'jug /
NK118(se)002:4598: dri zhim 'bru mar tshigs skud chur longs spyod //
NK118(se)002:4599: spu shel rtsi dang so mngas smyig shad gsum //
NK118(se)002:4600: so so'am gsum gas skra shad skra tshab dang //
NK118(se)002:4601: khyim pa'i rgyan thogs bro glu rol mo byed //
NK118(se)002:4602: gdugs thogs mchil lhwam gyon dang khri'ura 'dug /
NK118(se)002:4603: phyis gnon log thabs byed dang skud pa 'khal //
NK118(se)002:4604: dge 'dun ma'i gos bdag gir byed pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4605: zas 'tshong khyim gyi bya ba rjen pa 'tshod //
NK118(se)002:4606: lto 'dun sgog za rme gab mi brten dang //
NK118(se)002:4607: chu gos mi 'chang bkru bshal gos 'khrur 'jug /
NK118(se)002:4608: rung ba'i gos la ma gus ster dang barje //
NK118(se)002:4609: gzhan basngagasa khyim gnas rnyed chos ser sna lnga //
NK118(se)002:4610: dbyar khang khyim gzhan nas skrod tho 'tsham pa //
NK118(se)002:4611: log par ston dang rnam 'gyur brnyas thabs byed //
NK118(se)002:4612: spyo dang chu 'thor 'khrug long yal bar 'dor //
NK118(se)002:4613: blo mthun mi byed gdams ngag myong mi byed //
NK118(se)002:4614: dge slong med par gso sbyong dbyar gnas byed //
NK118(se)002:4615: gnyis ka'i tshogs la dgag dbye mi byed dang //
NK118(se)002:4616: dbul po sra brkyang sbyor 'jug dbyung 'gyed phyir //
NK118(se)002:4617: tshogs pa mi sbyin dbyar khang yal bar 'dor //
NK118(se)002:4618: ljongs rgyur 'gro dang mi 'gro dogs bcas 'gro //
NK118(se)002:4619: bkag pa'i phyogs 'gro gzhan gnas 'thab krol byed //
NK118(se)002:4620: skabs ma phye 'dri phyi sar gcig pur 'gro //
NK118(se)002:4621: r+ts+wa sngon steng dang ma bltas bshang gci 'dor //
NK118(se)002:4623: lnga pa sor bshags la bcu gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:4624: thun mong pa ni bslab pa bral te khyim du 'jug pa nyid yin la /
NK118(se)002:4626: 'o zho mar zhun 'bru mar sbrang rtsi dang //
NK118(se)002:4627: bur khu nya sha sha dang sha skam rnams //
NK118(se)002:4628: khyim nas mi na bzhin bslangs zas sam 'thungs //
NK118(se)002:4630: drug pa nyes byas la brgya dang bcu gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:4632: sham thabs sked par snang bar mi bgo ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4633: chags par gyur cing khyim gzhan du mi 'gro ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4634: thun mong pa ni brgya dang bcu ste /
NK118(se)002:4635: ma'i skabs 'dir phyis gnon byed pa zhes ma bsgos par stan la 'dug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:4636: r+ts+wa sngon gyi steng du bshang gci 'dor ba gnyis ltung byed du bshad zin pas /
NK118(se)002:4637: de gnyis ma rtogs pa'i lhag rnams dge slong dang 'dra ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:4638: de dag ni spang bar bya ba dgag pa'i bslab bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4639: mi mthun phyogs ngo shes pa'i sgo nas bsrung ba'i thabs so //
NK118(se)002:4640: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i bslab bya ni /
NK118(se)002:4641: lung gzhi las gsungs pa rnams yin cing /
NK118(se)002:4642: de la wa stu'i sgra las gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4643: bslab pa gsum gyi rten byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:4647: rab byung gso sbyong gzhi dang ni //
NK118(se)002:4648: dgag dbye dbyar dang ko lpags gzhi //
NK118(se)002:4649: sman dang gos dang sra brkyang dang //
NK118(se)002:4650: koo sham+b+hi dang las kyi gzhi //
NK118(se)002:4651: dmar ser can dang gang zag dang //
NK118(se)002:4652: spo dang gso sbyong bzhag pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4653: gnas mal dang ni rtsod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:4654: dge 'dun dbyen rnams bsdus pa yin //
NK118(se)002:4656: de yang koo sham+b+hi ni las bye ba'i gzhi /
NK118(se)002:4657: dmar ser can ni phyir bcos kyi gzhi /
NK118(se)002:4658: gang zag ni dus dang dus ma yin pa bsdus pa 'byung ba'i gzhi /
NK118(se)002:4659: spo ba ni sa gzhan gnas pa spyod pa'i gzhi /
NK118(se)002:4660: gso sbyong bzhag pa ni yongs su sbyang ba'i gzhi /
NK118(se)002:4662: gzhi bcu bdun po de rnams bsdu na gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:4663: sdom pa ma thob pa thob par byed pa /
NK118(se)002:4664: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba /
NK118(se)002:4665: nyams na phyir bcos pa dang gsum du 'du ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:4667: rab byung gi gzhi yin te /
NK118(se)002:4670: phyir bcos kyi gzhi bdun te /
NK118(se)002:4671: rtsa ba'i sa bcad drug par 'chad par 'gyur la /
NK118(se)002:4672: 'dir gnyis pa bshad par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4673: bslab pa yongs sbyong gi gzhi gsum /
NK118(se)002:4674: bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen gyi gzhi lnga /
NK118(se)002:4675: thob byed bsrung thabs phyir bcos thams cad la khyab pa las kyi gazhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4677: sgrub pa'i bslab bya yongs su sbyong ba'i tshul /
NK118(se)002:4678: gso sbyong dbyar gnas dgag dbye /
NK118(se)002:4681: rgyal po'i khab kyi 'od ma'i tshal du dge bsnyen mang pos zhus pa la brten nas gnang ngo //
NK118(se)002:4683: gzhi gsum gyi nang tshan bslab gsum rnam par dag byed kyi thabs gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:4684: zhi mthun gang rung gis bsdus pa'i rigs gnas dbye na gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:4685: sngar bsags kyi sgrib pa sbyong zhing lhag pa'i sems
NK118(se)002:4686: dang shes rab dag par bya ba'i phyir zhi gnas
NK118(se)002:4688: phyis 'byung gi rgyun tshe 'di'i zag pa sdom zhing
NK118(se)002:4689: lhag pa'i tshul khrims dag par bya ba'i phyir mthun
NK118(se)002:4693: tshul gnas thos dang bsam ldan pas //
NK118(se)002:4694: sgom pa la ni rab tu sbyor //
NK118(se)002:4695: zhes pa ltar gzhi tshul khrims rnam par dag pa la gnas pa'i gang zag /
NK118(se)002:4697: ma chags 'phags rigs zhes pas 'dod chung chog shes dang ldan pa des /
NK118(se)002:4698: lam gyi rgyu sde snod kyi lung thos shing /
NK118(se)002:4700: bsam don sgom par byed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4701: de la spong ba'i gnas dang /
NK118(se)002:4702: der 'gal spong mthun sgrub kyi rkyen sgrub cing /
NK118(se)002:4703: spong ba'i zhal ta pa bskos la /
NK118(se)002:4704: des bsam gtan las ldang ba'i dus sbron pa sogs bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4705: ji ltar bsgom bya'i lam gyi ngo bo la /
NK118(se)002:4709: de la 'jug pa mi sdug dang //
NK118(se)002:4710: dbugs rdub 'byung ba dran pa yis //
NK118(se)002:4711: 'dod chags rnam rtog lhag rnams so //
NK118(se)002:4712: zhes pas 'dod chags shas che ba'i gnyen por mi sdug pa'i sgom tshul gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:4713: rnam rtog shas che ba'i gnyen por rlung 'byung 'jug dran pa'i sgom tshul drug ste /
NK118(se)002:4714: dmigs pa gnyis po de dmigs pa la sems 'jog
NK118(se)002:4715: pa sogs sems gnas pa'i thabs dgus zhi gnas 'grub
NK118(se)002:4716: par byed pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:4718: zhi gnas grub par gyur pa yis //
NK118(se)002:4719: dran pa nyer gzhag bsgom par bya //
NK118(se)002:4720: zhes pas lus tshor sems chos bzhi la gtsang bde rtag bdag tu lta ba'i gnyen por /
NK118(se)002:4721: rang mtshan mi gtsang ba sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:4722: spyi mtshan mi rtag pa sogs bzhir sgom pa'i rnal 'byor la spyod cing /
NK118(se)002:4723: de ltar tshogs lam la sogs pa'i lam lnga byang phyogs so bdun gyi rim pas bgrod de /
NK118(se)002:4724: rgyun zhugs la sogs pa'i 'bras bu bzhi thob par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4725: gnyis pa mthun pa'i gso sbyong ni /
NK118(se)002:4727: mthun pa'i gso sbyong ni rnam pa lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:4730: bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong dang /
NK118(se)002:4731: gnod pa byung ba'i gso sbyong dang /
NK118(se)002:4732: bsdum pa'i gso sbyong dang lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:4735: tshes zhag chu tsho dang dgu rjes 'brang dang bcas
NK118(se)002:4736: pa des nyin zhag chu tshod drug cu'i dod ma
NK118(se)002:4737: thub pas / nyin zhag lnga bcu nga dgu na tshes zhag drug cur longs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:4738: des na hor zla bcu pa'i mar ngo'i tshes gcig
NK118(se)002:4739: nas dgun ra mgo zlar byas te dus 'go bzung
NK118(se)002:4740: bas / de nas zla ba phyed dang gnyis 'das
NK118(se)002:4741: pa hor zla bcu gcig pa'i mar ngo la rgyal
NK118(se)002:4742: zla'i bcu bzhi pa 'byung ba nas /
NK118(se)002:4743: hor zla dgu pa'i mar ngo la smin drug zla
NK118(se)002:4744: ba'i gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa 'byung ba'i bar bgrangs
NK118(se)002:4745: pas / lo re la gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa drug ste /
NK118(se)002:4747: rgyal dang dbo dang sa ga dang //
NK118(se)002:4748: chu stod khrums smad smin drug bcas //
NK118(se)002:4749: 'di rnams kyi ni nag po'i phyogs //
NK118(se)002:4750: zla phyed gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4753: yar ngo'i nya bcu gnyis dang /
NK118(se)002:4754: hor zla bcu pa nas brgyad pa'i bar gyi mar ngo drug ste bco brgyad do //
NK118(se)002:4755: de ltar nyin tshes kyi bar nas zhag mi thub 'thon pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:4756: tshes zhag gis khyim zhag chu tshod drug cu dang
NK118(se)002:4757: chu srang nga gnyis lhag bcas kyi dod ma thub
NK118(se)002:4758: pas khyim zhag phyed bcas so gnyis na tshes zhag
NK118(se)002:4759: gcig theb tu don te tshes zhag phyed dang so
NK118(se)002:4761: de bsags pas lo gcig gi bar khyad la zhag
NK118(se)002:4762: bcu gcig lhag tsam 'ong bas lo gnyis dang zla
NK118(se)002:4763: ba phyed dang dgun zla ba gcig bshol du 'thon
NK118(se)002:4764: pa yin zhing / de 'don tshul 'dul bar dngos su ma gsungs la /
NK118(se)002:4765: 'on kyang rgyal po'i 'khor du rtsis mkhan mkhas pa dag phal cher 'byung bar dgongs te /
NK118(se)002:4766: zla ba shol dor ba ni rgyal po'i rjes su 'brang bas so //
NK118(se)002:4767: rgyu skar ni skar mkhan gyi rjes su 'brang bar shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4770: zla shol gyi mar ngo'i gso sbyong ni rang thub
NK118(se)002:4771: mi thub gang yin de dang 'dra bar byed ces
NK118(se)002:4773: mi thub pa'i rjes su mi thub pa byed na
NK118(se)002:4774: nyin zhag sum cu na tshes zhag so gcig tu
NK118(se)002:4775: longs par thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:4777: mi rung ba'i gzhi bcu lta bu sel ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4778: rab gnas sogs bkra shis pa'i dus su'o //
NK118(se)002:4780: nad yams sogs gnod pa byung zin ldog pa'am slar mi 'byung ba'i phyir byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4782: dge 'dun bye ba bsdum pa'i phyir gso sbyong byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4783: de ltar bkra shis pa sogs dus ma nges pa'i gso sbyong gsum yang /
NK118(se)002:4784: gsol ba'i las kyi tshe rang rang gi dus brjod
NK118(se)002:4785: dgos pa'i khyad par tsam ma gtogs gzhan cho ga
NK118(se)002:4786: thams cad dus nges pa'i gso sbyong dang 'dra'o //
NK118(se)002:4787: 'dir skabs su bab pa bslab pa sbyong byed ni dus nges pa'i gso sbyong ste /
NK118(se)002:4790: gso sbyong ji ltar bya ba'i tshul dang gsum las /
NK118(se)002:4792: mtshams chen bcad na de nyid du dang /
NK118(se)002:4793: che chung gnyis ka bcad na chung ba nas 'thon nas che bar dang /
NK118(se)002:4794: chung ba bcad na gso sbyong sogs las thams cad der bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:4795: rtsig pas bskor na de nyid mtshams yin la /
NK118(se)002:4796: ma bskor na wa kha nas chu 'dzag pa gang du 'bab pa tshun chad yin par bshad do //
NK118(se)002:4798: rab byung sde lnga kas so //
NK118(se)002:4799: gsum pa la sbyor dngos gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:4801: las gral du ma 'dus gong gi bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4804: gso sbyong snga ma zin nas de ring gi bar
NK118(se)002:4805: rang rgyud la ltung ba byung ma byung brtags te
NK118(se)002:4806: / byung na bshags bsdams byin brlabs gang la gang 'os bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4808: thog mar gan+di'i sgras dge 'dun bsdu ste /
NK118(se)002:4813: rgya star t+aa la kim shu ka /
NK118(se)002:4814: shing sha pa dang ta m+aa la //
NK118(se)002:4815: a mra sta ra bu skyu ru ra //
NK118(se)002:4816: tin ti s+aa ra a sho ka /'di dag thams cad med na yang //
NK118(se)002:4819: tshad ni mchu ru sor tshad kyi //
NK118(se)002:4820: brgyad cu rtsa bzhi nyid bya zhing //
NK118(se)002:4821: zheng du sor ni drug pa ste //
NK118(se)002:4822: dpangs su yang ni gnyis bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4823: sor mo'i tshigs kyi tshad dag gis //
NK118(se)002:4824: zur bzhi tshad ni gnyis pa yin //
NK118(se)002:4825: legs mnyam nyid ni shin tu gsal //
NK118(se)002:4826: rtse gnyis sbal pa'i mgo bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:4827: de nas brdung bar byed pa yang //
NK118(se)002:4828: shing de nyid las bcad de bya //
NK118(se)002:4829: sor bcu gnyis kyi tshad dag la //
NK118(se)002:4830: zlum zhing rtse gnyis ne'u le'i mgo //
NK118(se)002:4831: chang bzung tshad kyang de bzhin te //
NK118(se)002:4834: rab byung sde lnga'am gso sbyong la gnas pa'i dge bsnyen gyis kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:4835: rgya dper &a&a&ashadadza zhes shad tsar grags pa shad gsum sngon du 'gro ba gzhir bzhag nas /
NK118(se)002:4836: spyir dge 'dun bsdu ba'i don du rgyud gsum dang tog gsum /
NK118(se)002:4837: las bya ba'i don du rgyud gcig dang tog gsum /
NK118(se)002:4838: phung po dbyung ba'i don du tog med pa'i byi bo /
NK118(se)002:4839: gnod pa bzlog pa'i don du ji tsam chog pa ste /
NK118(se)002:4840: de yang rgyud re la brdeg thengs so drug gi
NK118(se)002:4841: gcig nas bco brgyad bar je che dang bcu dgu
NK118(se)002:4842: nas so drug bar je chung du brdung ngo //
NK118(se)002:4843: de las 'dir las kyi gan+d+aisa bsdus te /
NK118(se)002:4845: nyin re bzhin gyi bya ba rgyud chags gsum dang gtor ma btang ba /
NK118(se)002:4846: dus bzang po la chos 'chad nyan byed pa'i dod
NK118(se)002:4847: mdo 'don pa rnams gso sbyong gi med mi rung
NK118(se)002:4848: ba'i sbyor ba ma yin kyang phyag bzhes ltar sngon
NK118(se)002:4849: la btang nas / dge tshul gyi bshags pa sngar ma grub na 'dir bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:4850: yongs dag blangs nas logs su bkar la /
NK118(se)002:4851: 'dir med du mi rung ba'i sbyor ba la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:4852: dang po rgyud dag par byed pa ni /
NK118(se)002:4853: dge 'dun gyi nang du ltung ba dran na drung na mo la byin gyis brlab cing /
NK118(se)002:4854: las byed pas ni sems kyis brlab ste /
NK118(se)002:4855: ltung ba thun min rnams de yan chad kyis dag par bgyis nas /
NK118(se)002:4856: thun mong pa rnams gsol ba 'ba' zhig pas byin gyis brlab par bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4857: gnyis pa gnas kyi blo mthun ni /
NK118(se)002:4858: gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis gnas la blo bstun pa'am /
NK118(se)002:4859: mtshams che chung gang rung gcod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:4860: gsum pa dge 'dun mthun pa sgrub pa dang 'du
NK118(se)002:4861: bar mi nus pas gso sbyong nyams su myong ba
NK118(se)002:4862: sgrub pa ni / gnas brtan gyis so thar gyi mdo'i bstod ra dang /
NK118(se)002:4864: bag yod par gdams pa rnams bton la /
NK118(se)002:4865: dge bskos kyis brtags nas nad pa lta bu ma
NK118(se)002:4866: lhag pa yod na 'dun pa blangs nas nang du
NK118(se)002:4867: brjod pa'o // gnyis pa dngos gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:4868: gnas brtan gyis so thar gyi mdo nyan par gdams nas /
NK118(se)002:4869: gsol ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las kyis dge 'dun thugs bstun pa /
NK118(se)002:4870: tshe dang ldan pa dag bdag cag gso sbyong bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4871: zhes sogs kyis rnam par bzhag pa 'dzin du bcug ste /
NK118(se)002:4872: de nas mdo 'don pa dngos ni /
NK118(se)002:4877: ril gyis 'don pa dang lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:4878: re re'i rjes la yongs su dag pa lan gsum dri'o //
NK118(se)002:4879: de lta mod kyi gleng gzhi tsam las mi 'don na /
NK118(se)002:4880: de'i mjug sdud brjod nas yongs dag 'di ba nyid dngos gazhi'o //
NK118(se)002:4882: gleng gzhi 'don pa dang gsol ba ni tshig tu
NK118(se)002:4883: brjod pa nyid kyis bsgrub par bya ba nyid yin
NK118(se)002:4884: no // lhag ma ni thos pa bsgrags pas kyang ngo //
NK118(se)002:4886: gal te gnas der dge slong gsum man chad las med na dus kyi bar du sgug pa'am /
NK118(se)002:4887: yang na gso sbyong yod pa'i gnas su 'gro /
NK118(se)002:4888: de ltar ma grub na dmigs bsal gyi cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:4889: phan tshun gcig gi mdun du gcig 'dug nas byin gyis brlab cing /
NK118(se)002:4890: rang gcig pu las med na yid kyis bsam zhing brjod /
NK118(se)002:4891: de tsam yang ma grub na thub pa'i sngon gyi
NK118(se)002:4892: gso sbyong tshigs su bcad pa phyed dang bzhi tsam
NK118(se)002:4893: 'don par bya'o // gzhan yang gnas der dge slong
NK118(se)002:4894: bzhi kho na yod pa des ni gsol ba byas
NK118(se)002:4895: te gso sbyong bya zhing nad pa'i yongs dag mi
NK118(se)002:4896: 'don par bya'o // len pa dang / gzhi 'gro
NK118(se)002:4897: na tshes grangs ma mthun zhing glo bur ba mang
NK118(se)002:4898: na de dag gi 'dod pa dang bstun nas gso
NK118(se)002:4900: gzhi 'gron gang rung gi dge 'dun gso sbyong byed
NK118(se)002:4901: 'phrol phyis de dag dang grangs mnyam pa'am lhag pa'i
NK118(se)002:4902: dge slong byung na slar yang snga ma rnams kyis
NK118(se)002:4903: gso sbyong bzlas te bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4904: gso dgag dgos pa gcig pas dgag dbye byas nas
NK118(se)002:4905: slar gso sbyong bya mi dgos pa sogs kyi dmigs
NK118(se)002:4906: bsal rnams kyang shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4908: ston pa rgyal byed tshal na bzhugs pa'i tshe dge
NK118(se)002:4909: slong dag dbyar ljongs rgyu ba la mu stegs rnams
NK118(se)002:4911: gang gi tshe ri bor gyi gtsug lag khang zhig
NK118(se)002:4912: tu dbyar gnas pa las 'jigs pa byung nas dgag
NK118(se)002:4913: dbye ma byas par gnyan yod du 'ongs pas dbyar
NK118(se)002:4914: phyi ma rjes su bcas so //
NK118(se)002:4916: gzhi gsum gyi nang tshan gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:4917: gso sbyong dang dgag dbye gang rung rnam par bcad pa'i tshul rnam par dag byed kyi rigs gnas /
NK118(se)002:4922: dbyar snga ma yin na gro zhun zla ba dbyar zla tha chung gi mar ngo'i tshes gcig dang /
NK118(se)002:4923: phyi ma yin na khrums zla ston ra'i mar ngo'i
NK118(se)002:4924: tshes gcig nas dbyar zla gsum du khas len pa
NK118(se)002:4926: gro zhun zla ba'i tshes gcig nas //
NK118(se)002:4927: snga ma'i dbyar de gtso bo yin //
NK118(se)002:4928: de nyid khrums kyi zla ba yas //
NK118(se)002:4929: tshes gcig nas ni phyi mar grags //
NK118(se)002:4932: dbyar gnas par khas blang bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4937: de ldan gyi dbyar gnas ji ltar bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4940: 'phya dang srog chags gnod spong dang //
NK118(se)002:4941: lus srog gnod spong ral grum 'chos //
NK118(se)002:4942: don bya nyung dang thos sogs 'phel //
NK118(se)002:4946: khas len pa'i cho ga dang /
NK118(se)002:4947: khas blangs pa'i dam tshig bsrung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:4954: 'thab krol can sogs med cing sde snod 'dzin pa
NK118(se)002:4955: sogs yod pas bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen tshang ba
NK118(se)002:4956: / steng g.yogs sgo glegs dang bcas pa'i gtsug lag
NK118(se)002:4957: khang ral grum bcos pa dang byi dor bya ba
NK118(se)002:4958: sogs zhag bcu'am zla phyed tsam gyi snga rol nas
NK118(se)002:4959: / sta gon bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:4960: dbyar snga ma yin na dbyar 'bring hor zla drug pa'i nya dang /
NK118(se)002:4961: phyi ma yin na dbyar tha hor zla bdun pa'i nya la gso sbyong byas nas /
NK118(se)002:4962: gnas dang gnas mal dag stob rgyu yod na /
NK118(se)002:4963: de stob pa po dge slong gcig gam du ma bsko zhing /
NK118(se)002:4964: med na tshul shing brim pa po nyid bsko bar bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4965: las byed pa pos bsko byar spro ba dri /
NK118(se)002:4966: spro na gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis bskos la /
NK118(se)002:4967: des khrims su bya ba brtan par brjod nas /
NK118(se)002:4968: tshul shing blang ba'i phyir las byed pas gsol ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las kyis thugs bstun la /
NK118(se)002:4969: bskos pas tshul shing brim zhing blangs pa'i grangs go bar bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4970: gnas dang gnas mal stob cing /
NK118(se)002:4971: gnas mal la log par mi spyad pa dang sang
NK118(se)002:4972: nang par gnas par khas blang ba dag go bar
NK118(se)002:4975: tshes bcu drug gi nang par gnas steng g.yogs dang
NK118(se)002:4976: bcas par dge slong gi mdun du sngags lan gsum
NK118(se)002:4978: dmigs bsal yul med na 'dir gnas par bya'o snyam
NK118(se)002:4979: du dam bcas pas kyang gnas pa'i go chod de
NK118(se)002:4980: / gnas par khas ma blangs pas gnas mi gtong na gnas pa nyid yin no //
NK118(se)002:4982: gnyis pa dam tshig bsrung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:4983: byin gyis ma brlabs par mtshams kyi phyi rol tu skya rengs 'char bar mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:4984: zhes pas rkyen dbang gis 'das kyang nyes pa med
NK118(se)002:4985: pa'i dmigs bsal gsungs pa rnams ma gtogs byin gyis
NK118(se)002:4986: ma brlabs par / gang du gnas par khas blangs
NK118(se)002:4987: pa'i gnas de'i nye 'khor gyi mtshams las 'das nas
NK118(se)002:4988: phyi rol tu skya rengs shar na dbyar ral ba'i
NK118(se)002:4990: gal te 'gro dgos na byin gyis brlab par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:4991: gnang ba ma thob pas zhag gcig nas bdun gyi bar brlabs nas 'gro ba dang /
NK118(se)002:4992: dge 'dun la zhag bzhi bcu'i gnang ba thob na /
NK118(se)002:4993: des zhag bzhi bcu man chad ci rigs par byin gyis brlabs nas 'gro bar bshad cing /
NK118(se)002:4994: bdun pa'i byin brlabs lan du ma bzlas su rung
NK118(se)002:4995: kyang thams cad bsdoms pa la zhag bzhi bcu las
NK118(se)002:4997: matha'i zhag drug la byin rlabs mi chags so //
NK118(se)002:4998: zhes gsungs pa'i don la bya 'dul chen po ni /
NK118(se)002:4999: de'i tshe zhag bdun nyid mi chags pa yin gyi /
NK118(se)002:5000: zhag gcig gnyis sogs kyi byin brlab byar rung bar ba zhed do //
NK118(se)002:5002: ston pa gnyan yod na bzhugs pa'i tshe ljongs shig
NK118(se)002:5003: tu dge slong rnams mi smra ba'i khrims byas te
NK118(se)002:5004: dbyar gnas pa la brten nas mthong thos dogs gsum
NK118(se)002:5005: gyis dbyar gnas pa'i dge 'dun la dgag dbye byed
NK118(se)002:5006: par gnang ngo // mtshan nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:5007: gzhi gsum gyi nang tshan chos rnam par dag byed gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5008: dbyar tshul la brten nas byung ba'i de ma thag gi rigs gnas /
NK118(se)002:5018: zhag bdun la sogs pa'i snga rol nas spyod yul du go bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:5020: gtsug lag khang brgyan pa sogs tshes bcu gsum yan chad la tshar bar byas nas /
NK118(se)002:5021: bcu bzhi'i mtshan thog thag chos rnam pa gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5023: dbyar snga ma khas blangs na ston 'bring dbyug zla dang /
NK118(se)002:5024: phyi ma la ston zla tha chung smin drug zla
NK118(se)002:5025: ba gang rung gi tshes bco lnga'i snga dro dge
NK118(se)002:5026: 'dun thams cad 'dus nas phan tshun phyag byas la
NK118(se)002:5027: dbyar nang du thugs dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol
NK118(se)002:5028: zhing / rgyud chags gsum pa nas dge tshul gyi
NK118(se)002:5029: bshags pa'i bar gso sbyong ltar byas la dge tshul
NK118(se)002:5031: 'du bar ma nus pa'i 'dun pa dang dgag dbye
NK118(se)002:5032: len dgos na blangs te dge 'dun la brjod ltung
NK118(se)002:5033: ba thun mong ma yin pa rnams gso sbyong gi
NK118(se)002:5034: skabs ltar las gral la ma 'dus gong du phyir
NK118(se)002:5035: bcos bya zhing / 'dir las byed pas ltung mthun byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK118(se)002:5036: bsko bya la spro ba dri /
NK118(se)002:5037: spro na gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis dgag dbye byed pa po bskos nas /
NK118(se)002:5038: dgag dbye bya ba'i phyir gsol ba'i las kyis thugs bstun pa rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5040: bskos pa des r+ts+wa dar+b+ha brim zhing /
NK118(se)002:5041: de yul rten gnyis kas bzung nas sngags lan gsum mam gcig gis ltung ba'i dgag dbye byas te /
NK118(se)002:5042: bskos pas dgag dbye legs par byas pa dge 'dun la go bar bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5043: rdzas kyi dgag dbye bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5047: dge tshul ma rnams kyi dgag dbye byed par gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:5050: ltung ba gleng ba'i tshe gzhi dang gang zag gang
NK118(se)002:5051: rung re re'am gnyis ka bzhag pa'i dgag dbye byar
NK118(se)002:5053: gnyis pa dus min gyi dgag dbye ni /
NK118(se)002:5054: rkyen dbang gis zla ba gcig gam /
NK118(se)002:5055: phyed dang gnyis 'das pa'i nya shi gang rung la dgag dbye byar rung zhing /
NK118(se)002:5056: gal te gso sbyong gnyis sogs ma song ba dang
NK118(se)002:5057: nya stong ma yin pa'i dus su'ang dmag 'khrug la
NK118(se)002:5058: sogs pa'i rkyen gyis dge 'dun thams cad 'gyes dgos
NK118(se)002:5059: na phan tshun gcig gis gcig la tshogs kyi dgag
NK118(se)002:5060: dbye bya ste / dge slong gang rung rkyen dbang gis 'gro dgos na'ang 'di byar rung ngo //
NK118(se)002:5061: de dag ni dus kyi dmigs bsal lo //
NK118(se)002:5062: yang gang zag gi dmigs bsal ni /
NK118(se)002:5063: dge slong bzhi las med na dgag dbye byed pa po mi bsko bar /
NK118(se)002:5064: gsol ba'i las dang dgag dbye dngos bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:5065: dge slong gsum mam gnyis las med na dgag dbye byin gyis brlab /
NK118(se)002:5066: rang gcig pu las med na dngos gzhi tsam lan gsum brjod do //
NK118(se)002:5067: gzhan yang dbyar byin gyis brlabs te song bas mtshams
NK118(se)002:5068: gzhan du dgag dbye byed pa dang thug na de
NK118(se)002:5069: dag dang lhan cig dgag dbye byas kyang chags par
NK118(se)002:5070: bshad cing / dbyar dral ba'am de nyin glo bur
NK118(se)002:5071: du lhags pa'i rab byung gzhan gyis kyang dgag dbye
NK118(se)002:5072: bshad cing / bya dgos so // gnyis pa bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen gyi gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:5074: ko lpags gnas mal sman sogs gzhan du shes //
NK118(se)002:5081: bag yangs dang 'brel ba sra brkyang /
NK118(se)002:5082: 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang 'brel ba gos /
NK118(se)002:5083: dmigs bsal dang 'brel ba ko lpags kyi gazhi'o //
NK118(se)002:5085: ston pa gnyan yod na bzhugs pa'i tshe gnas bcas
NK118(se)002:5086: su dbyar gnas pa 'thon nas phyag 'tshal du 'ongs
NK118(se)002:5087: pa'i dge slong rnams tshegs chen pos ngal bar gyur
NK118(se)002:5088: pa la brten nas gnang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5089: de la ka thin zhes pa gtan pa'am sra brkyang ste /
NK118(se)002:5090: dngos ming chos gos dras drub byed pa'i tshe 'ding ba'i gzhi pang leb kyi ming yin la /
NK118(se)002:5091: de 'dir dge 'dun spyi dbang ba'i chos gos sum
NK118(se)002:5092: phrugs la 'dra ba rgyu mtshan du byas nas btags
NK118(se)002:5094: gtan pas chos gos la khyab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5096: de'i steng du chos gos kyi dngos po gcig tu 'gyur ba ltar /
NK118(se)002:5097: 'dis kyang 'ding ba po thams cad la khyab cing /
NK118(se)002:5098: gnang ba bag yangs dang 'brel bas bag rkyong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5099: 'ding ba po rnams blo gcig tu mthun par byed pas so //
NK118(se)002:5101: sra brkyang bting chags kyi dge slong gis phan yon rnam pa bcu thob pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:5106: gos slong ba'i nyes pa rnams khegs shing /
NK118(se)002:5107: 'ding ba la gtogs pa'i dge slong yul gang na
NK118(se)002:5108: 'dug kyang rnyed pa thun mong du dbang ba dang
NK118(se)002:5109: / rung ba ma byas pa'i gos 'chang du rung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5110: snam sbyar med par ljongs rgyur rung ba rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5113: dbyar khas blangs pa'i gnas de'i 'ding khar mtshams gcig tu byas par yang rung ngo /
NK118(se)002:5114: gang gi tshe 'ding ba'i dus ni /
NK118(se)002:5115: smin drug nas ni khra yi bar //
NK118(se)002:5116: sra brkyang 'ding ba rjes su gnang //
NK118(se)002:5117: zhes pas dgag dbye 'thon pa'i phyi de nas spyir btang la yun zla ba lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:5118: gang gis 'ding ba'i gang zag ni /
NK118(se)002:5119: dbyar snga ma khas blangs shing ma ral ba'i dge slong rnam dag gis so //
NK118(se)002:5121: dbyar rnyed kyi rgyu las byung zhing dge 'dun dbang
NK118(se)002:5122: ba'i chos gos sum phrugs gcig yan chad du tshang
NK118(se)002:5123: ba'o // ji ltar 'ding ba'i cho ga la sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5125: dge slong rnams rang rang gi chos gos kyi byin brlabs phyungs te /
NK118(se)002:5126: 'ding rgyu'i chos gos dbyar nang gi nyi ma gang
NK118(se)002:5127: la grub pa de nas zhag ma lon par dge
NK118(se)002:5128: slong thams cad mtshams nang du tshogs pas de der
NK118(se)002:5129: gding ngo zhes mos par byas la /
NK118(se)002:5130: gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis blo bstun te /
NK118(se)002:5132: gsol ba byas nas de la gtad /
NK118(se)002:5133: des kyang sems gsum bskyed nas dge 'dun la sang gding bar 'gyur gyi zhes brjod /
NK118(se)002:5134: gal te chos gos de sngar ma zin na bskos
NK118(se)002:5135: pas bkru ba kha bsgyur ba drub pa sogs sngon
NK118(se)002:5136: du btang nas / gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5137: ston zla 'bring po'i tshes bcu drug gi nang par dge 'dun bsdus la /
NK118(se)002:5138: bskos pas sra brkyang 'ding ba'i sngags lan gsum brjod /
NK118(se)002:5139: de nas sra brkyang thogs te rgan rim bzhin dge
NK118(se)002:5140: slong re re'i mdun du 'dug nas bting ngo zhes
NK118(se)002:5141: go bar bya / gsum pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5142: de ltar brjod pa la dge 'dun gyis legs par
NK118(se)002:5143: gding ngo zhes sogs rjes su yi rang bya ba'o
NK118(se)002:5144: // de ltar bting nas dus dus su gseng ba sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:5145: bskos pa des zhag gis chod par mi 'bral zhing gzhan du mi khyer /
NK118(se)002:5146: bsrung ba po med par mi 'jog pa sogs kyis bskyang zhing /
NK118(se)002:5149: sra brkyang gis mtshams gzhan du phyin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5150: bskos pa'i dge slong mtshams gzhan du skya rengs shar ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5151: mtshams der gtogs thams cad mtshams khongs su mi gtogs par chad pa la sogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5154: de la'ang dbo zla'i nya la dbyung ba dus can dang /
NK118(se)002:5155: rkyen dbang gis de'i snga rol dus min du dbyung ba gnyis so //
NK118(se)002:5156: gnyis pa gos kyi gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:5157: ston pas dbyar rnyed kyi ras rnams dras nas kha
NK118(se)002:5158: dog ngan par byas te bcang bar gnang ba las
NK118(se)002:5159: / gzugs can snying pos 'tsho ba po mthong ba
NK118(se)002:5160: nyan thos su 'khrul nas mtshan ma gdab par zhus
NK118(se)002:5161: pas dras shing drub pa'i gos rjes su gnang ngo
NK118(se)002:5163: rgyu'i khyad par gos sgrub lugs /
NK118(se)002:5165: dbye ba so so'i rnam bzhag /
NK118(se)002:5166: ji ltar bcang ba'i tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:5168: log 'tshos ma bsgrubs shing rgyu ha cang ngan pa
NK118(se)002:5169: dang bzang ba ma yin pa'i rgyur rung ba bdun
NK118(se)002:5171: bal gos sha na nyi 'og dang //
NK118(se)002:5172: ras gos dang ni zar ma dang //
NK118(se)002:5173: ko tam pa dang d+au ku la //
NK118(se)002:5174: chos gos rgyun ni rnam pa bdun //
NK118(se)002:5176: de yang spu shin tu che ba dang kha tshar phun tshar ma bcad pa sogs ma yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5178: rgyu rung ba nyid legs par bkrus la /
NK118(se)002:5179: mi rung ba'i tshon chen brgyad spangs te rung ba'i tshon gsum gyis kha bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5180: de ltar yang rgya skyegs le brgan rtsi dang btsod //
NK118(se)002:5181: sman shing rtsi dang mthing shing mtshal //
NK118(se)002:5185: sngon po btsag dang ngur smrig rtsi //
NK118(se)002:5186: 'di dag rung ba'i tshon gsum ste //
NK118(se)002:5188: de la spyir btang du gos mtshon gyis dras pa zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:5189: mtshon gyis ma dras pa'i gos bcar bar mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5191: drub par 'os pa rnams drub par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:5192: dras shing drub pa chos gos nyid du byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5193: mthang gos dang bla gos dang snam sbyar la'o //
NK118(se)002:5194: dge slong ma'i shing nga dpung chad dang rdul gzan snam pa gang yang rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5195: zhes pas 'byor na de thams cad dras drub dang /
NK118(se)002:5196: ma 'byor na lhan thabs bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:5197: snam sbyar ma gtogs pa la thang thang po yang rung bar bshad do //
NK118(se)002:5198: gang dag snam sbyar la nges par dras drub dgos gsung ba mi rigs te /
NK118(se)002:5199: rgyu'i byin rlabs kyi sngags chog tu /
NK118(se)002:5200: yang na 'di la lhan thabs su bslan no //
NK118(se)002:5203: chos gos rlag pa nyid dang /
NK118(se)002:5204: chos gos 'tshig pa nyid la sogs pa'i rkyen de
NK118(se)002:5205: lta bu dag yod na snam sbyar la'ang dras shing
NK118(se)002:5206: drub pa chos gos nyid du byin gyis brlab po
NK118(se)002:5207: zhes bya ba'i nges pa med do //
NK118(se)002:5210: snam phran s+n+rel gzhi nyid dang lhag ma mnyam pa
NK118(se)002:5211: nyid dang dbus nas gzhan du glegs bu'i 'phro phyogs
NK118(se)002:5212: phyogs su lta ba nyid dang mtha' bskor ba nyid
NK118(se)002:5214: 'di la glegs bu'i 'phro zhes pa 'gyur skyon te /
NK118(se)002:5215: 'grel pa kha cig tu tshal bu'i 'phro zhes 'byung ba dag go //
NK118(se)002:5216: zhes rnam bshad dri med rgyan pa bzhed do //
NK118(se)002:5217: gsum pa dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:5220: mkho ba'i yo byad kyi gos rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5221: bzhi pa so so'i rnam gzhag la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5222: dang po 'tsho ba'i yo byad kyi gos la /
NK118(se)002:5228: bcas ldan dge slong gi lus 'tsho ba'i ched du
NK118(se)002:5229: gnang ba'i gos rung ba tshad ldan re rer nges
NK118(se)002:5230: pa gang zhig / rang ming gis byin gyis brlab rung gi rigs gnas /
NK118(se)002:5233: de'i byin rlabs chags rung gnyis /
NK118(se)002:5235: yo byad bcu gsum po gang rung tshad dang ldan par grub pa ste /
NK118(se)002:5248: dbyar gyi gos ras chen rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5250: rgyu'i byin brlabs 'bral spang khegs pa'i sngags rten te /
NK118(se)002:5251: chos gos gsum gang rung gi rgyur rung ba'i gos dang /
NK118(se)002:5252: khyim pa'i gos lta bu gang rung khru gang yan chad do //
NK118(se)002:5253: gsum pa so so'i rang bzhin las /
NK118(se)002:5254: snam sbyar ni snam phran dgu nas nyer lnga'i bar te /
NK118(se)002:5257: bcu gsum ma gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5260: bcu dgu gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5263: nyer lnga gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang lnga pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5264: tshad ni che bskor gsum dpangs su khru gsum dang srid du khru lnga /
NK118(se)002:5265: chung gsum de las khru phyed phyed phri ba /
NK118(se)002:5266: 'bring gsum de gnyis kyi bar ro //
NK118(se)002:5267: bla gos ni snam phran bdun dang glegs bu phyed dang gsum pa /
NK118(se)002:5268: tshad snam sbyar ltar gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:5269: mthang gos ni rnam phran lnga dang glegs bu phyed dang gnyis pa /
NK118(se)002:5270: tshad dpangs su khru do dang /
NK118(se)002:5272: tha na 'khor gsum khebs pas kyang rung zhing /
NK118(se)002:5273: lus sboom pas mi yogs na ral kha dpung chad bsnon par bshad do //
NK118(se)002:5279: khru'i don ni lus kyi cha bdun las gnyis so //
NK118(se)002:5281: sham thabs dang de'i gzan mthang gos dang tshad 'dra zhing /
NK118(se)002:5282: rdul gzan dang de'i gzan bla gos dang tshad 'dra ste /
NK118(se)002:5283: de dang de nyin mo dang mtshan mo mthang gos
NK118(se)002:5284: dang bla gos kyi 'og tu gyon pa'i gos yin
NK118(se)002:5285: pa'i phyir / gdong phyis srid dang zheng du khru gang pa /
NK118(se)002:5286: rnag gzan bla gos dang mnyam pa /
NK118(se)002:5287: skra bzed srid du khru gsum dang zheng du khru phyed dang gnyis pa /
NK118(se)002:5290: ras chen gsum gyi tshad ni ltung byed kyi skabs su bshad zin mod /
NK118(se)002:5291: 'on kyang gding ba'i 'jal byed rdul khru yin zhes gnyag dpon rin po che gsung zhing /
NK118(se)002:5292: dbyibs ni glegs bu phyed dang gnyis pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5294: 'tsho ba'i yo byad rnams so so rang ming gis nges par byin gyis brlab cing /
NK118(se)002:5295: khyad par chos gos gsum ni dngos med na rgyu'i byin brlabs dang /
NK118(se)002:5296: dngos sam rgyu'i byin brlab gang rung mi chags na rkyen dbang gis byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5297: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5298: dngos su 'chang 'bral gyi nyes pa khegs shing shan mi 'byung ba sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:5299: brgyud nas dngos zhen dang bral ba'i phan yon 'byung ste /
NK118(se)002:5300: 'og ma gnyis la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5301: gnyis pa lhag pa'i yo byad kyi gos la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5303: dge slong gi 'tsho mkho gang rung gi yo byad du gyur pa'i gos lhag po gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5304: gzhan ming nyid kyis brlab pa'am yid brtan te bcang rung gi rigs gnas /
NK118(se)002:5306: snam sbyar gnyis pa lta bu 'tsho ba'i yo byad
NK118(se)002:5307: gang rung gi dbyibs su grub pa'i lhag po dang
NK118(se)002:5308: / ska rags gnyis pa lta bu mkho ba'i yo byad kyi gos lhag po dag go //
NK118(se)002:5310: gzhan kho na'i ming gis brlab pa'am /
NK118(se)002:5311: yo byad rung ba ni mkhan po sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:5312: mi rung ba ni sbyin bdag la yid brtan te bcang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5313: gsum pa mkho ba'i yo byad kyi gos la'ang gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5315: 'tsho ba'i yo byad gang rung gi dbyibs su ma
NK118(se)002:5316: grub pa'i gos kyi khyad par khru gang yan chad
NK118(se)002:5318: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i ming gis brlabs te bcang rung gi rigs gnas /
NK118(se)002:5320: dar gos snam bu lta bu nor gyi 'du shes skye ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5321: zhwa dang ska rags sogs gos kyi 'du shes skye ba'i yo byad dag go //
NK118(se)002:5323: bdag dang tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa gnyis ka'i don du byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5324: lnga pa bcang tshul la bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:5326: spyir rab byung tshul ldan gyis bcang zhing /
NK118(se)002:5327: khyad par snam sbyar ni dge slong gis bcang ngo //
NK118(se)002:5328: bsam pa ji lta bus na /
NK118(se)002:5329: lus la rma dang gos la rma dkris kyis dgab pa sogs kyi 'du shes dang /
NK118(se)002:5330: spyir yo byad thams cad la mi rtag pas nyen pa'i bsam pas bcang ngo //
NK118(se)002:5332: spyir khyim pa'am mu stegs can dang /
NK118(se)002:5333: khyad par snam sbyar ni dge tshul man chad kyi rtags las 'phags par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:5334: rang nyid ston pa'i rnam thar gyi rjes su 'jug
NK118(se)002:5335: cing dge sbyong gi dran pa gso ba'i ched du
NK118(se)002:5336: bcang ba'o // mjug tu ji ltar sgrub pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5337: gos brnyings na lhan pa gdab pa sogs kyis bcos shing /
NK118(se)002:5338: bcos su mi rung na sbyin bdag gi bsod nams
NK118(se)002:5339: spel ba la sogs pa'i ched du sa dang gci
NK118(se)002:5340: ba sogs la bsres nas mchod rten dang gtsug lag
NK118(se)002:5341: khang gi ser kha la bslan par bshad do //
NK118(se)002:5342: gsum pa ko lpags kyi gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:5343: k+aa t+ya ya na'i slob ma gro zhun skyis bye
NK118(se)002:5344: ba nyi shu pas mtha' 'khob rdo can nas ston
NK118(se)002:5345: pa bltar 'ongs te zhus pas gnang ngo //
NK118(se)002:5346: de yang gnang bkag gi mtshams shes pa'i phyir dbus matha'i sa tshigs ni /
NK118(se)002:5347: sngar rab byung gi gzhir bshad pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:5348: spyir yul dbus su gnas mal skyob pa'i phyir ko lpags kyi lhwam tsam dang /
NK118(se)002:5349: gtsug lag khang las gzhan pa'i khyim du stan gzhan
NK118(se)002:5350: med na ko lpags la 'dug pa tsam gnang gi
NK118(se)002:5352: mtha' 'khob tu ni grang ba skyob pa'i phyir gnang
NK118(se)002:5353: bas lhwam dang mal stan gnyis ka bsten du rung
NK118(se)002:5354: zhing / de'i khyad par khra bo dang gser dngul
NK118(se)002:5355: gyi rgyan can sogs sgeg rdzas dang sgra sgrog pa'i
NK118(se)002:5356: mchil lhwam brten du mi rung /
NK118(se)002:5357: glang po che dang stag seng rta bong sogs kyi ko lpags bcang du mi rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5358: bye brag yul asma pa r+aan+tara ni ko lpags kyi
NK118(se)002:5359: gos ci dgar bsten pa sgrub pa'i bslab byar gsungs
NK118(se)002:5360: la / spyir chu la chab rom tsam chags pa'i
NK118(se)002:5361: yul du zhwa dang lhwam yu can gnyis ka gnang
NK118(se)002:5363: gnyis pa sman gyi gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:5364: ston pa gnyan yod na bzhugs pa'i tshe dge slong
NK118(se)002:5365: rnams ston ka'i nad kyis thebs nas rid pas sman
NK118(se)002:5367: de yang dus ma yin par ma zos pas rid
NK118(se)002:5368: pa na sman bzhir phye nas rjes su gnang ngo
NK118(se)002:5372: gang zag gang gis spyod pa /
NK118(se)002:5373: bzhag pa'i gnas rung khang brten tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:5375: log 'tsho dang bral zhing mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i sgo nas bsgrub par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5382: bcas ldan dge slong gis brten du rung ba'i sman gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5383: dri ro reg bya gsum gyi bdag nyid du gyur pa'i kham zas te /
NK118(se)002:5385: kham gyi zas ni 'dod pa na //
NK118(se)002:5386: skye mched gsum gyi bdag nyid do //
NK118(se)002:5397: bkres pa'i nad sel ba la gtso bor gnang ba'i sman gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5398: dge slong gis spyir btang la phyi dro longs spyod du mi rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5404: sna tshogs 'bras chan zan dang sha /
NK118(se)002:5405: phye dang khur ba bza' ba lnga //
NK118(se)002:5408: rtsa ba sdong bu me tog 'bras //
NK118(se)002:5409: lo ma yang ni bca' ba lnga //
NK118(se)002:5411: gnyis pa thun tshod du rung ba la /
NK118(se)002:5416: skom pa'i nad sel ba la gtso bor gnang ba'i sman gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5417: dge slong gis thun tshod kyi matha'i bar byin gyis brlabs nas longs spyad du rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5419: drang srong ke na'i bus btung ba'i rgyu brgyad phul te /
NK118(se)002:5421: chu shing 'bras dang ku shu go la dang //
NK118(se)002:5422: a shwat+tha dang u dum+ba ra dang //
NK118(se)002:5423: ba ru sha ka dang ni rgun 'brum dang //
NK118(se)002:5424: brgyad pa 'bra go dag ni yin par bshad //
NK118(se)002:5426: gzhan yang bcos pa'i tsh+wa ste rgun chang sogs kyi sangs po /
NK118(se)002:5427: 'bru'i tsh+wa ste nas chang gro chang sogs kyi shul nas byung ba'i sangs po /
NK118(se)002:5428: zho kha chu ste zho'i khu ba /
NK118(se)002:5429: dar ba'i dwangs ma ste chur khu /
NK118(se)002:5430: rtsa ba mo ste 'bras dang khre sogs btsos nas
NK118(se)002:5431: phabs ma btab par mnan pa'i tsad shu zhes bod
NK118(se)002:5433: de dag kyang btung ba mtshan nyid lnga ldan te /
NK118(se)002:5438: 'dam su nyag ma'i mdog lta bu'i btung ba rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5442: 'tsho bcangs las sbyar ba'i thun tshod du rung ba'i sman gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:5445: skyu ru ra'i khu ba shin tu sla ba lta bu'o //
NK118(se)002:5446: gsum pa zhag bdun pa la /
NK118(se)002:5450: rlung nad sel ba la gtso bor snang ba'i sman gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5451: dge slong gis zhag bdun pa'i matha'i bar byin gyis brlabs nas longs spyad du rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5456: bu ram gyi dbu ba ste /
NK118(se)002:5458: bu ram gyi kha shun bsdus pa'i phye ma hwags dang /
NK118(se)002:5459: de brdog por byas pa la kha ra sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:5460: zhun mar dang ngo bo 'dra ba bdud rtsi dang /
NK118(se)002:5461: 'bru mar dang 'dra ba nya sogs sems can lnga'i zhag bskol zhing btsags pa rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:5462: sa ga'i lhas mar gsar kyang zhag bdun bar bshad pa /
NK118(se)002:5464: zhag bdun pa ni mar dkar dang /
NK118(se)002:5467: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun no //
NK118(se)002:5472: 'dus pa'i nad sel ba la gtso bor gnang ba'i sman gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5473: ji srid nad de 'tsho'i bar byin gyis brlabs nas longs spyad du rung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5475: rtsa ba'i sman gla sgang dang yung ba lta bu /
NK118(se)002:5476: sdong bu'i sman tsan+dana dang sle tres lta bu /
NK118(se)002:5477: 'dab ma'i sman nim pa'i lo ma lta bu /
NK118(se)002:5478: me tog gi sman ba sha ka'i me tog lta bu /
NK118(se)002:5479: 'bras bu'i sman a bar skyur gsum lta bu ste /
NK118(se)002:5480: de dag kyang gtso bor zas kyi don du khyab par byed pa ma yin pa rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5482: spyi nad sel bar byed pas na sman /
NK118(se)002:5484: snga dro'i dus kho nar rung bas dus rung /
NK118(se)002:5485: rang ming gis dus kyi matha'i bar byin gyis brlab tu rung bas na thun tshod dang /
NK118(se)002:5488: bzhi pa brten tshul la gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:5490: mig sman gyi don lpags la sogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5492: dus rung gi sman snga dro'i dus kho nar brten du rung ba ste /
NK118(se)002:5493: nad par phan na dus min du brten pa'ang gnang zhing /
NK118(se)002:5494: rung dus las 'das na byin gyis brlabs kyang gsog
NK118(se)002:5495: 'jog mi khegs pa'i phyir byin brlab ma gsungs la
NK118(se)002:5496: / sman gzhan gsum byin gyis ma brlabs pa ni
NK118(se)002:5497: gang zag nad pa yin min thams cad la gnang
NK118(se)002:5498: / zhing / dus thams cad du brten du rung mod /
NK118(se)002:5499: 'on kyang byin gyis ma brlabs na byin len byas
NK118(se)002:5500: pa nyin thun gnyis mtshan thun gsum ste lnga po
NK118(se)002:5501: de dang de'i mthar gsog 'jog tu 'gyur bas de
NK118(se)002:5502: khegs pa'i phyir byin gyis brlabs dgos so //
NK118(se)002:5503: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i sman de ni nad pa kho nas brten du rung zhing /
NK118(se)002:5504: dus kyang spyir rang ming gi dus kyi matha'i bar dang /
NK118(se)002:5505: bye brag thun tshod kyi sman la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5506: rgyu dus rung las sbyar ba de mtshan gyi thun tha ma'i bar dang /
NK118(se)002:5507: zhag bdun pa las sbyar ba de brgyad pa'i skya
NK118(se)002:5508: rengs ma shar bar gsog 'jog tu mi 'gyur zhing
NK118(se)002:5509: / rgyu 'tsho bcangs las sbyar ba de la gsog 'jog 'byung mi srid do //
NK118(se)002:5510: 'o na byin gyis brlabs pa'i sman rang dus las
NK118(se)002:5511: ma 'das kyi bar du gsog 'jog mi 'byung bas
NK118(se)002:5514: ro gzhan du 'gyur na byin rlabs 'jig pas gsog 'jog tu 'gyur pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:5515: shan brdeg byed yod kyang der 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5516: ji ltar bsten pa'i cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:5517: bdag nyid la nad pa dang zas la sman gyi
NK118(se)002:5518: 'du shes bzhag ste dran shes dang ldan pas dkon
NK118(se)002:5519: mchog gsum rjes su dran pa'i sgo nas /
NK118(se)002:5520: zas la cha bzhir bgo bya ste //
NK118(se)002:5521: dang por lha la bshos gtsang 'bul //
NK118(se)002:5522: de rjes chos skyong srung ma la //
NK118(se)002:5523: gtor ma shin tu rgya cher bya //
NK118(se)002:5524: rang gis zos shing 'thungs pa yi //
NK118(se)002:5525: lhag ma 'byung po rnams la byin //
NK118(se)002:5526: zhes pa'i cho gas zas la ran par longs spyad de yon sbyong mdo bsngo rnams bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:5528: zhar byung sman snod lhung bzed byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5529: de dang de dbyung ba'i cho ga rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5530: gsum pa gang zag gang gis spyod pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5531: spyir btang du tshul khrims dang ldan pa'i rab byung myang 'das kyi bsam pa can gyis spyod cing /
NK118(se)002:5532: dmigs bsal pha ma dang slong ba po sogs la sbyin no //
NK118(se)002:5533: bzhi pa sman bzhag pa'i gnas rung khang brten tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:5535: rung ba nyid du byin gyis brlabs par btsos pa dang gnas pa dag ni phyi rol dang 'dra'o //
NK118(se)002:5536: zhes pas mtshams nang yin yang der rjen btsos dang
NK118(se)002:5537: zhag lon sogs byar rung bas na rung khang zhes
NK118(se)002:5538: bya'o // de yang khyim pa'i gnas khang dang gtsug
NK118(se)002:5539: lag khang nye 'khor dang bcas pa las phyi rol
NK118(se)002:5540: du gyur pa'i gnas su mtshams btsos dang zhag lon
NK118(se)002:5541: gyi nyes pa mi 'byung bas de dag tu rung
NK118(se)002:5542: khang byin gyis brlab mi dgos shing /
NK118(se)002:5543: de las gzhan gtsug lag khang nye 'khor dang bcas pa'i nang du ma zad /
NK118(se)002:5544: khyim pa'i gnas yin kyang der khyim pa mi sdod
NK118(se)002:5545: par dge slong nyid dbang ba'i khang pa yin na
NK118(se)002:5546: / rung khang byin gyis brlab dgos pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:5547: ji ltar byin gyis brlab pa'i tshul la bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:5548: dang po so phag 'grem pa'i dus su dge slong
NK118(se)002:5549: lag gi blas de'i 'gram rdo gtong ba na bteg
NK118(se)002:5550: pa'i mtha' las byung ba'i byin rlabs dang /
NK118(se)002:5551: gnyis pa rtsig pa'i 'go brtsams nas mjug ma zin
NK118(se)002:5552: pa'i bar gang yang rung ba'i dus su lag gi
NK118(se)002:5553: blas sems bsdus pa'i mtha' las byung ba'i byin rlabs
NK118(se)002:5554: dang / gsum pa rung khang du 'os pa'i khang
NK118(se)002:5555: pa de grub zin nas der dge slong gnas pa
NK118(se)002:5556: nyid dang ma bral ba'i dus su dge 'dun gyis
NK118(se)002:5557: gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis brlab pa dang
NK118(se)002:5558: dang / / bzhi pa sngar rung khang du byin
NK118(se)002:5559: gyis brlabs sam ma brlabs kyang rung ste gtsug lag
NK118(se)002:5560: khang stong par dge slong dag gsar du phyin pa'i
NK118(se)002:5561: tshe der sleb ma thag phral las byung ba'i byin
NK118(se)002:5562: dang / / brlab bya ba'o // phyi ma gnyis
NK118(se)002:5563: po 'di rung khang gsar du rtsig pa'am khang pa
NK118(se)002:5564: byas zin rung khang du sgrub pa gnyis ka la
NK118(se)002:5566: yang bdag po so so'i ba lang rnams lhas gcig
NK118(se)002:5567: tu 'jug pa ltar mtshams nang gcig tu gtsug lag
NK118(se)002:5568: khang du ma'i rung khang gi bya ba khang pa
NK118(se)002:5570: lung las ba lang gi lhas lta bu'i rung khang zhes gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:5571: gsum pa gnas mal gyi gzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:5572: w+aa ra n+aa s+air khyim bdag dge bzang gis ston
NK118(se)002:5573: pa la gtsug lag khang brtsig par zhus pas gnang
NK118(se)002:5575: phyag bya ba dang mi bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:5576: gtsug lag khang brtsig cing longs spyod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK118(se)002:5578: so so thar pa'i sdom pas mchog la rab tu byung bas phyag bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5581: khyim pas rab tu byung ba la'o //
NK118(se)002:5582: thams cad kyis sangs rgyas la'o //
NK118(se)002:5583: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK118(se)002:5586: ngos gcig gi dbus su dri gtsang khang bya ba nyid do //
NK118(se)002:5587: de'i mdun du sgo khang ngo //
NK118(se)002:5588: gru bzhi bzang ba nyid do //
NK118(se)002:5589: zhes sogs kyis gtsug lag khang brtsig pa'i cho ga dang /
NK118(se)002:5590: brtsigs nas sgor gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje dang
NK118(se)002:5591: sgo khang du 'khor ba'i 'khor lo cha lnga pa
NK118(se)002:5592: sogs ri mo 'dri ba'i tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:5593: gtsug lag khang yal bar mi dor ro //
NK118(se)002:5594: zhes sogs kyis ji ltar bskyang ba'i sgo nas gnas par bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5595: spyod lam ci 'dod pas lung dbog go //
NK118(se)002:5596: zhes sogs kyis der chos dang zang zing gi longs
NK118(se)002:5597: spyod la ji ltar spyod pa'i tshul rgyas par gsungs
NK118(se)002:5599: de ltar gnas khang dang gnas mal la mtha' gnyis
NK118(se)002:5600: spangs te chags med zhen med kyi tshul gyis spyod
NK118(se)002:5601: par gsungs shing / mdor na bde bar gnas pa'i
NK118(se)002:5602: rkyen gos dang sman dang gnas mal bsten pa'i skabs
NK118(se)002:5603: 'dir yongs su spyad pa rnam pa lnga shes par
NK118(se)002:5604: par gsungs shing / bya ste / ji skad du /
NK118(se)002:5605: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pas rab tu byung
NK118(se)002:5606: ba tshul khrims dang ldan pa la ni gos stong
NK118(se)002:5609: khang pa brtsegs pa lnga brgya pa yang 'os so //
NK118(se)002:5611: mi slob pa man chad kyi'o //
NK118(se)002:5612: so so'i skye bo la yang ngo //
NK118(se)002:5613: tshul khrims 'chal ba la ni ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:5614: le lo can la ni blangs pa dang nye bar spyad pa bu lon du 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:5617: mi slob pa ni bdag por spyod //
NK118(se)002:5618: slob pa byin pa spyod pa ste //
NK118(se)002:5619: bsam gtan klog dang ldan pa ni //
NK118(se)002:5620: rjes gnang spyod pas nyes pa med //
NK118(se)002:5621: lhag ma le los bcom pa yis //
NK118(se)002:5622: bdag nyid rnams ni bu lon spyod //
NK118(se)002:5623: khrims 'chal rnams ni nam du yang //
NK118(se)002:5624: gtsug lag khang sogs nyer spyod bkag /
NK118(se)002:5625: ces pa ltar mi slob pa'i gang zag gis gzhan gyi yo byad rang dbang ba'i tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:5626: slob pa 'phags pas rang la byin pa rnams longs spyad du rung ste /
NK118(se)002:5627: de dang des yon spyong nus pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5628: so skye khrims dag klong spong la brtson pa'i gang zag gis spyad kyang nyes pa med de /
NK118(se)002:5629: de ltar ston pas gnang ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5630: gal te tshul khrims dag kyang thos bsam sgom gsum
NK118(se)002:5631: mi nus pa'i le lo can gyis spyad du mi
NK118(se)002:5632: rung ste / gang blangs bu lon du 'phel nas skye ba phyi mar 'jal dgos pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5633: khrims 'chal gyis ni dad rdzas la nam yang spyod pa bkag ste /
NK118(se)002:5634: spyad na dmyal bar lhungs nas sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5635: de lta yang snying gi thur ma las /
NK118(se)002:5636: tshul khrims 'chal bas sa ni goms pa gang //
NK118(se)002:5637: zas ni kham gcig btung ba chu phor gang //
NK118(se)002:5638: tsam zhig dge 'dun rdzas la longs spyad na //
NK118(se)002:5639: log 'tsho yin te dmyal bar skye bar gsungs //
NK118(se)002:5641: gsum pa thams cad la khyab pa las kyi gzhi la lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:5653: bzhi bcu nyer gnyis nyi shu dang //
NK118(se)002:5654: bcu gnyis bcu gcig bcu dang dgu //
NK118(se)002:5655: brgyad drug lnga bzhi dgos pa yi //
NK118(se)002:5656: las ni rnam pa bcu gcig go //
NK118(se)002:5658: yul dbus su dge slong ma dbyung ba la pha
NK118(se)002:5659: tshogs nyi shu ma tshogs nyi shu ste bzhi bcu
NK118(se)002:5660: dgos pa sogs las bcu gcig po rang rang la
NK118(se)002:5662: mi 'dug par 'greng ba ma yin pa sogs kha skongs kyi chos dang ldan pa /
NK118(se)002:5663: mi mthun pa gnyis dang bral ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5665: spyir btang la kha skongs dang ldan zhing cho ga shes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5666: dmigs bsal la cho ga shes pa tsam mo //
NK118(se)002:5668: sems can ma yin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5671: mtshams che chung bcad pa sogs brgyad do //
NK118(se)002:5676: lhung bzed kha sbub sogs lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:5679: rdzogs pa'i rten la bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5682: chad pas bcad pa'i las gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:5683: 'di la bsko ba'i las ni med do //
NK118(se)002:5684: gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rten la bya ba ni /
NK118(se)002:5685: khang pa'i gnang ba ster ba sogs sbyin las nyer gcig /
NK118(se)002:5686: gsang ston bsko ba sogs bsko ba'i las drug /
NK118(se)002:5689: grangs su 'jug pa bzhi ste mi mthun pa'i las nyi shu rtsa gsum rnams so //
NK118(se)002:5694: sems can ma yin pa la bya ba dang mi
NK118(se)002:5695: mthun pa'i las la dge 'dun gyi 'du shes dang
NK118(se)002:5696: / sbyin pa dang bsko ba la yul gyi 'du shes gtso ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:5698: zhe thag pa nas las byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5699: gsum pa las kyi ngo bo la /
NK118(se)002:5703: las mkhan gyis chad lhag nor 'khrugs med pa'i cho ga byas shing chags pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5705: dge slong gis bya ba'i rigs brgya rtsa gcig yod de /
NK118(se)002:5707: btsun pa las du dag mchis /
NK118(se)002:5708: nye ba 'khor brgya rtsa gcig go //
NK118(se)002:5710: gsol ba'i las ni nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:5711: gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las ni bzhi bcu rtsa bdun no //
NK118(se)002:5712: gsol ba dang bzhi'i las ni sum cu'o //
NK118(se)002:5713: zhes pa'i bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:5714: bzhi pa nyams su myong ba ni /
NK118(se)002:5715: las kyi tshig thos shing don go ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5716: lnga pa chags pa'i dus ni /
NK118(se)002:5717: 'ba' zhig pa dang gsol gnyis kyi las la de dang de rdzogs ma thag tu dang /
NK118(se)002:5718: gsol bzhi'i las kyi brjod pa gsum pa la ngo bo bya byed gsum las /
NK118(se)002:5719: bya ba byed pa rdzogs ma thag tu las chags pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5720: gnyis pa shugs bstan rung mthun bsdus te bstan pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5721: mdor na ye nas gnang dang bkag pa med //
NK118(se)002:5722: byar rung dang nye mi rung zlog byed na //
NK118(se)002:5723: de dag spyod cig mi rung dang nye zhing //
NK118(se)002:5724: rung ba bzlog na kun tu spong zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)002:5726: dngos su ma smos pa'i gnang bkag gi bslab bya
NK118(se)002:5727: thams cad mdor bsdu na 'di nyid du 'dus te
NK118(se)002:5728: / gzhi gang la ston pas ye ste thog ma
NK118(se)002:5729: nyid nas dngos su gnang ba dang bkag pa'i gsal
NK118(se)002:5730: kha dod pa med pa rnams ni /
NK118(se)002:5731: gang zhig byar rung bar gsungs pa dang nye zhing
NK118(se)002:5732: mi rung ba las bzlog na de dag the tshom
NK118(se)002:5733: med par spyod par gyis shig /
NK118(se)002:5734: dper na dge tshul la dgag dbye gsungs pas mtshon nas gso sbyong bya dgos pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:5735: gang spyad du mi rung bar gsungs pa dang nye
NK118(se)002:5736: zhing rung ba las bzlog na de dag kun tu
NK118(se)002:5737: spongs shig / dper na srin bal la stan byed
NK118(se)002:5738: pa bkag pas de dang mnyam pa dang lhag pa
NK118(se)002:5739: la stan bya mi rung bar mthun pa bzhin no
NK118(se)002:5740: spongs shig / // de ltar yang lung phran tshegs las /
NK118(se)002:5741: bcom ldan 'das kyis yongs su mya ngan las 'da'
NK118(se)002:5742: ba'i dus de'i tshe nyid na dge slong rnams la
NK118(se)002:5743: bka' stsal pa / dge slong dag ngas khyed la 'dul ba rgya cher ni bstan na /
NK118(se)002:5744: mdor bsdus te ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:5745: 'on kyang mdor bsdus pa yang nyon cig /
NK118(se)002:5746: dge slong dag ngas khyed la gang zhig thog ma nyid nas gnang ba yang med /
NK118(se)002:5748: gal te rung ba dang nye ba yin zhing mi
NK118(se)002:5749: rung ba zlog par byed pa yin na ni rung
NK118(se)002:5750: ba yin par bzung bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5751: gal te mi rung ba dang nye ba yin zhing
NK118(se)002:5752: rung ba zlog par byed pa yin na mi rung
NK118(se)002:5753: ba yin pas kun tu spyad par mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5755: lnga pa skye ba'i lus rten ni /
NK118(se)002:5756: skye ba'i rten ni mu stegs mtshams med byas //
NK118(se)002:5757: sgra mi snyan dang za ma mtshan gnyis dang //
NK118(se)002:5758: ma ning rigs lnga mtshan gsum gyur pa dang //
NK118(se)002:5759: sprul pa ma gtogs gling gsum skyes pa yi //
NK118(se)002:5760: skyes pa bud med sdom pa'i rten du 'dod //
NK118(se)002:5762: las kyi sgrib pa shas che ba mu stegs can nam de zhugs pa /
NK118(se)002:5763: pha ma dgra bcom bsad pa dang dge 'dun gyi
NK118(se)002:5764: dbyen dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems
NK118(se)002:5765: kyi khrag 'byin pa ste mtshams med lnga byas pa
NK118(se)002:5767: rnam smin gyi sgrib pa shas che ba sgra mi snyan pa lta bu gnas rigs nyams pa /
NK118(se)002:5768: gang zhig grong pa'i chos med pa //
NK118(se)002:5769: de ni za ma zhes su brjod //
NK118(se)002:5770: ces pa ltar za ma dang /
NK118(se)002:5775: nyams pa ste ma ning rigs lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:5776: mtshan gnyis gcig car du byung ba /
NK118(se)002:5777: mtshan lan gsum du gyur pa sogs mtshan nyams pa /
NK118(se)002:5778: mi ma yin pa mi'i rnam par sprul pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5779: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba pa sogs ni 'gro
NK118(se)002:5780: ba nyams pa zhes de rnams sdom pa skye ba'i
NK118(se)002:5781: bar chad can yin pas na ma gtogs pa ste
NK118(se)002:5782: / de las gzhan shar nub lho'i gling gsum du
NK118(se)002:5783: skyes pa'i skyes pa dang bud med rnams so thar
NK118(se)002:5784: gyi sdom pa skyes ba dang gnas pa gnyis ka'i
NK118(se)002:5787: za ma ma ning sgra mi snyan //
NK118(se)002:5788: mtshan gnyis ma gtogs mi rnams la //
NK118(se)002:5789: sdom min sdom pa'ang de bzhin la //
NK118(se)002:5792: gling gsum skyes pa bud med las //
NK118(se)002:5793: 'gro ba gzhan la sdom pa bkag /
NK118(se)002:5795: drug pa nyams pa gso ba'i thabs la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:5797: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:5799: sdom pa thob nas ma nyams par bsrung zhing /
NK118(se)002:5800: gal te nyams na phyir bcos pa'i sgo nas dag par bya dgos te /
NK118(se)002:5802: gnyis ni rnam par byang bar 'gyur zhing /
NK118(se)002:5803: nyon mongs par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK118(se)002:5804: gnyis kyi zag pa 'phel bar mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK118(se)002:5806: ltung ba mi 'byin pa gang yin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5807: ltung ba byung nas chos bzhin du phyir 'chos pa gang yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5808: zhes gsungs pas gso tshul bshad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:5809: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:5810: sdom pa gtong ba'i rgyu dang /
NK118(se)002:5814: thun mong ma yin pa gnyis /
NK118(se)002:5816: gtong ba bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK118(se)002:5817: mtshan gnyis gcig car byung dang lan gsum gyur //
NK118(se)002:5818: rgya 'bras med bltas rtsa ba chad rnams lci //
NK118(se)002:5820: so thar gyi sdom pa spyi'i gtong rgyu ni bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:5821: brda 'phrod pa'i drung du bsam pa thag pa nas bslab pa phul bas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5822: yang dag par blangs pa dang 'gal ba'i rnam rig bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5824: sdom pa rang gi ngo bo /
NK118(se)002:5829: slob pa'i grogs rnams 'bul tshul gsungs pa ltar yin la /
NK118(se)002:5830: tshangs par spyad dka' 'o zhes sogs ni 'bul ba'i
NK118(se)002:5831: rgyu bstan pas nyams par byas pa yin gyis phul
NK118(se)002:5832: ba ma yin yang sdom pa gtong ba la khyad
NK118(se)002:5834: bslab pa ma phul bslab pa nyams par ma byas par //
NK118(se)002:5836: de bzhin du shi 'phos pas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5838: mtshan gnyis gcig car byung ba dang mtshan lan gsum gyur bas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5840: rgyu 'bras med lta'i log lta skyes pas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5841: dge ba'i rtsa ba chad pas sdom pa'i rten gzhi med pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5842: 'di ni theg pa che chung thams cad kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyur bshad pas shin tu lci ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5843: de ltar spyi'i gtong rgyu bzhi'i steng bsnyen gnas kyi gtong rgyu bsnan pas lngar bshad de /
NK118(se)002:5845: bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK118(se)002:5846: mtshan gnyis dag ni byung ba dang //
NK118(se)002:5847: rtsa ba chad dang mtshan 'das las //
NK118(se)002:5848: so so thar pa'i 'dul ba gtong //
NK118(se)002:5851: de dag ni mdor bsdu na gtong ba'i rgyu lnga yin no //
NK118(se)002:5854: bye brag so so'i gtong rgyu /
NK118(se)002:5855: spyi la 'dod pa mi 'dra ba'i khyad par /
NK118(se)002:5856: rtsa ltung gtong rgyu yin min las 'phros te sde lnga'i dngos gzhi mi bskyed pa'i rgyu bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5858: nyi shu ma lon bsnyen rdzogs rjes su shes //
NK118(se)002:5859: dge slong sdom gtong rten phyir khas blangs 'das //
NK118(se)002:5860: dge slob ma'o mtshan 'das bsnyen gnas kyi //
NK118(se)002:5861: sdom pa gtong rnams so sos thun mong min //
NK118(se)002:5863: lo nyi shu ma lon pa la lon par 'du shes nas bsnyen rdzogs blangs pa de /
NK118(se)002:5864: phyis nyi shu ma lon gong du de ltar ngo shes na /
NK118(se)002:5865: de'i tshe mngal shol gyi zla bas kha bskang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:5866: de ltar bskang yang ma tshang na bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5868: shes na ni de zhig go //
NK118(se)002:5869: gal te de skyes pa na ma lon pa'i 'o //
NK118(se)002:5870: mngal na gnas pa dang shol gyi zla ba dag dang yang bcas te'o //
NK118(se)002:5872: mi tshangs spyod bsten par byed pa'i phyir khas blangs pa dge slob ma'i sdom pa gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5873: bsten pa'i phyir gzhan la khas blangs pa na /
NK118(se)002:5876: mtshan mo matha'i skad cig ma 'das pas bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5877: de srid du 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:5878: de ltar gsum po sngar gyi spyi'i gtong rgyu bzhis gtong bar ma zad /
NK118(se)002:5879: rang rang gi gtong rgyu so sos sdom pa de
NK118(se)002:5880: dang de gtong bas na thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK118(se)002:5881: gtong tshul lo // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:5882: rtsa ltung byung dang dam chos nub na'ang gtong //
NK118(se)002:5883: kha che'i yul gyi bye brag smra ba rnams //
NK118(se)002:5884: sdom ldan rtsa ltung byung ba gnyis ldan na //
NK118(se)002:5885: nor ldan bu lon can bzhin 'dod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:5886: kha cig rtsa bzhi gcig spyad kun nyams zer //
NK118(se)002:5889: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung bas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5890: rgyud ngo tsha khrel med chen pos nyams pa'i phyir zer /
NK118(se)002:5891: gos dmar ba'i sde pa na re /
NK118(se)002:5892: lung gi dam chos nub pas gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5893: bslab pa'i mtshams rnam par bzhag pa med pa'i phyir zer /
NK118(se)002:5894: de la thogs med sku mched lung chos nub pa tsam gyis sdom pa sngar yong mi gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5895: rtogs pa'i dam chos ma nub pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5896: 'on kyang de tshe sngar med gsar skye med de /
NK118(se)002:5897: 'bogs byed kyi cho ga'i rnam gzhag med pa'i phyir gsung /
NK118(se)002:5898: kha che bye brag tu smra ba rnams na re /
NK118(se)002:5899: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung yang sdom pa mi gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:5900: phyogs gcig nyams pas sdom pa zad par gtong ba mi rigs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5901: de 'dra de sdom ldan dang tshul 'chal gnyis ka yin te /
NK118(se)002:5902: mi 'ga' zhig la nor yang ldan la bu lon yang chags pa bzhin no zhes 'dod /
NK118(se)002:5904: kha cig ltung bar gyur las smra //
NK118(se)002:5905: gzhan dag dam chos nub pa las //
NK118(se)002:5906: kha chen rnams ni byung ba la //
NK118(se)002:5907: bu lon nor bzhin gnyis su 'dod //
NK118(se)002:5910: pham pa sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:5911: pham pa byung ba'i dge slong la dge slong gi sdom pa'i rdzas tshang bar yod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5912: nyams tshul la ltos na kun nyams yin te /
NK118(se)002:5913: rtsa bzhi las srog gcod kyi pham pa 'chab bcas lta bu gcig spyad pa'i tshe /
NK118(se)002:5914: sdom pa mtha' dag dgos pa sgrub nus las nyams pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:5916: dge slong pham par gyur pa la ni sdom pa yod du zin kyang /
NK118(se)002:5917: de lta mod kyi dgos pa med pa nyid du 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:5918: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams dang lhan cig
NK118(se)002:5919: gnas pa dang longs spyod pa med pa'i phyir dang
NK118(se)002:5920: / sdom pa yang dag par blangs pa ni rnam par grol ba thob pa'i ched yin la /
NK118(se)002:5921: des rnam par grol ba thag ring du byas pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5922: des na de'i sdom pa ni med pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5925: dang po'i las can sems 'khrugs tshor bas gzir //
NK118(se)002:5926: sgrub par ma nus pa la nyes pa med //
NK118(se)002:5928: bshad ma thag pa ltar pham pa 'chab bcas kyis
NK118(se)002:5929: sdom pa gsor mi rung du song ba'i gang zag
NK118(se)002:5930: gis spyad kyang sde lnga'i dngos gzhi ji lta ba
NK118(se)002:5932: nyams pa dang ma chags pa gnyis ltung ba la sbyor na nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:5933: zhes pas nyes byas tsam las mi bskyed pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:5934: de bzhin du las dang po pas spyad kyang mi
NK118(se)002:5935: bskyed de / ston pa'i bcas pa dang ma 'brel ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5936: dge slong bzang sbyin la mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa ma byung ba bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:5937: sems 'khrugs tshor bas gzir nas sems rnal du ma phebs pas spyad kyang mi bskyed de /
NK118(se)002:5938: bsam pa rang bzhin du gnas pa ma yin pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:5939: smyon pas mi bsad pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:5940: sgrub ma nus pa'i gnas skabs su spyad kyang mi bskyed de /
NK118(se)002:5941: rmi lam du mi tshangs spyod spyad kyang pham pa mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:5942: des na de 'dra'i rten gyi gang zag gis ltung
NK118(se)002:5943: ba la spyad kyang dngos gzhi'i nyes pa ji lta
NK118(se)002:5944: ba bzhin bskyed pa med do //
NK118(se)002:5945: gnyis pa phyir bcos dngos la /
NK118(se)002:5947: de las 'phros nas rtsod pa phyir bcos /
NK118(se)002:5948: nyes ltung spyod pa'i thabs stobs bzhir 'du tshul /
NK118(se)002:5949: nyes dmigs shes pas nan tan du bsrung bar gdams pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5951: mi spro ba nan tur gyis phyir bcos pa dang /
NK118(se)002:5952: spro ba mthol bshags sogs kyis phyir bcos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5954: 'og tu gzhug cing bshung ba'i don gyis nan tur zhes bya ba ste /
NK118(se)002:5956: bsdigs dmad bskrad pa phyir 'gyed bzhi /
NK118(se)002:5958: gso dgag bzhag pa gnyis te bcu gsum mam /
NK118(se)002:5959: gnas dbyung bdun po gcig tu byas na nan tur bdun no //
NK118(se)002:5961: 'thab krol byed pa la bya ba 'di thong zhig
NK118(se)002:5962: mi gtong na gnas nas dbyung ngo zhes bsdigs pa'o
NK118(se)002:5963: // dmad pa ni lhag ma phyir mi 'chos par
NK118(se)002:5964: rgyun du byed pa la gang zag rang dbang can
NK118(se)002:5965: yin kyang gzhan la gnas chos shig ces smod pa'o
NK118(se)002:5966: // // bskrad pa ni khyim sun 'byin pa gnas de nas skrod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5967: phyir 'gyed ni khyim pa sogs la brnyas thabs byed
NK118(se)002:5968: pa la mdza' gcugs kyi dngos pos sbyangs na phyir
NK118(se)002:5970: ma mthong ba gnas nas dbyung ba /
NK118(se)002:5974: 'thab krol gyi rgyu nye bar sgrub pa /
NK118(se)002:5975: dge slong ma dang 'dris shing gnas pa /
NK118(se)002:5976: chos rnam par gtan la phab pas zhi bar ma gyur pa gnas nas dbyung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:5977: gdams ngag bzhag pas ma thul ba la dge 'dun
NK118(se)002:5978: dang lhan cig gso sbyong dang dgag dbye byed du
NK118(se)002:5979: mi 'jug pa ni de dang de bzhag pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5980: lhung bzed kha sbub ni spyir nan tur yin kyang
NK118(se)002:5981: yul khyim pa la bya ba yin pas 'dir mi
NK118(se)002:5982: bgrang ngo // de yang nan tur gang la /
NK118(se)002:5988: nan tur so so'i gzhi ma zhi bar yod cing
NK118(se)002:5989: dge 'dun bye 'gyur gyi dgag bya med pa'i gang
NK118(se)002:5992: dge 'dun mtshan nyid dang ldan pas so //
NK118(se)002:5994: dbyar gyi nang ma yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:5995: bzhi pa la sbyor ba gleng dran dang gzhams bsgo /
NK118(se)002:5997: rjes las kyi mjug sdud dang /
NK118(se)002:5998: 'di nyid du ltung ba phyir bcos par gyis shig /
NK118(se)002:5999: dge 'dun gyis khyod bag yangs su byed par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:6002: bya ba ngan pa rgyu bcas las bzlog pa dang ltung ba phyir bcos su gzhug pa'o //
NK118(se)002:6003: de ltar nan tur byas pa la brten nas bzod pa 'bul na /
NK118(se)002:6004: de rang bzhin du gnas pa thob pa'i phyir dge
NK118(se)002:6005: 'dun mtshan nyid dang ldan pas bzod pa blang ba
NK118(se)002:6006: ni / sbyor ba gsol btab sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:6008: mjug spro ba bskyed par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:6009: de yang nan tur bcu gsum las /
NK118(se)002:6010: dang po bcu gcig po sa gzhan na gnas pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:6011: gso dgag bzhag pa ni nan tur yin kyang sa gzhan na gnas pa ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:6012: gnyis pa spro ba mthol bshags sogs kyis phyir bcos pa las /
NK118(se)002:6015: lhag ma can gyi phyir bcos dang gsum /
NK118(se)002:6018: lhag med de ldan la ji ltar bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:6020: 'chab pa zhes grags gsang ste mi brjod pa //
NK118(se)002:6022: ltung ba byung ba gsod 'dod ni 'chab sems yin la /
NK118(se)002:6023: des kun nas bslangs te mi brjod par gsang ba'i
NK118(se)002:6024: lus ngag gi las ni 'chab pa'i ltung ba ste
NK118(se)002:6025: / de la'ang gang gis nyes par byed pa rig byed dang /
NK118(se)002:6026: gang nyes par bya ba'i ngo bo rig byed ma yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:6028: ltung ba dang ltung min gyi rnam dbye shes shing
NK118(se)002:6029: dran nus pa'i dge slong nyid las gzhan la mi
NK118(se)002:6030: 'byung zhing / spyir 'chab nyes tsam gyi dbang du
NK118(se)002:6031: byas na 'chab sems skad cig ma gcig skyes kyang
NK118(se)002:6032: ltung ba de 'chab bcas su 'gyur la /
NK118(se)002:6033: khyad par dge 'dun lhag ma'i spo spyod la zhag tu bcabs pa dgos te /
NK118(se)002:6034: nyin mtshan gyi mtha' ma yin pa la 'chab nyes mi 'byung ngo //
NK118(se)002:6037: pham pa 'chab bcas tshe 'dir gsor mi rung //
NK118(se)002:6039: bslab pa ma phul bar pham pa bzhi gang rung
NK118(se)002:6040: byung nas skad cig ma gcig bcabs kyang tshe 'dir
NK118(se)002:6041: ltung ba phyir bcos su yod pa ma yin te
NK118(se)002:6042: / rgyud gsor mi rung du song ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:6044: nyes rtsom byed dang khyim sun 'byin pa dang //
NK118(se)002:6045: 'dir ni gsum pa tshul khrims 'chal pa dag /'thab mo spangs te gan+di brdungs byas nas /
NK118(se)002:6046: chu shing rul ba bzhin du nges bskrad bya //
NK118(se)002:6048: nyes dmigs ni tshul 'chal dang lhan cig zhal lon
NK118(se)002:6049: du nyal na lo bye ba phrag bcu bzhi dang
NK118(se)002:6050: stong phrag bcu bzhir dmyal bar skye bar bshad do
NK118(se)002:6051: // gal te bskrad pa de sde snod 'dzin pa
NK118(se)002:6052: yin na dge 'dun dang lhan cig longs spyod du
NK118(se)002:6053: mi dbang yang gnas longs sbyin pa sogs kyis rjes
NK118(se)002:6055: de 'dra des bzod pa gsol ba'i dus su ma blangs na /
NK118(se)002:6056: de nas bzung ste gnas chos kyi rnyed pa'i rin
NK118(se)002:6057: thang rtsis nas tshad na dge 'dun la pham pa
NK118(se)002:6059: gnyis pa lhag med 'chab med ni /
NK118(se)002:6060: 'chab pa med na dngos po brjod pa yis //
NK118(se)002:6061: dge 'dun la bshags mthong sdom bar gyis 'dag /
NK118(se)002:6064: 'dir dge 'dun la bshags nas sdom pa slar nod
NK118(se)002:6065: pa lta bur gsungs pa ni sems tsam pa yan
NK118(se)002:6066: chod slar yang gsol bzhi'i las kyis dge slong gi
NK118(se)002:6067: sdom pa sbyin rjes chad pa las kyi bslab pa
NK118(se)002:6068: ster bar bzhed pa dang dgongs pa mthun nam snyam
NK118(se)002:6071: pham pa byung nas skad cig tsam yang ma bcabs
NK118(se)002:6072: pa la chad pa las kyi bslab pa sbyin te
NK118(se)002:6073: spyod pa'i sgo nas phyir bcos pa'o //
NK118(se)002:6075: des gnong 'gyod drag po dang bcas pas dge 'dun
NK118(se)002:6076: gyi drung du phyin nas rjes su bzung bar zhus
NK118(se)002:6077: te / sbyor ba gsol gdab sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:6078: dngos gzhi gsol bzhi'i las kyis bslab pa sbyin nas
NK118(se)002:6079: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dman pa'i spyod pa lnga
NK118(se)002:6080: dang du len zhing khyad par gyi spyod pa lnga
NK118(se)002:6082: gang gi tshe dgra bcom pa thob na de rang bzhin du gnas par 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:6083: 'khrul pa'i rgyu thams cad spangs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:6084: der ma zad rtsa ltung thun min byung ste bslab
NK118(se)002:6085: pa sbyin pa mtshan gyur na'ang bslab pa sbyang mi
