NK118(se)002:9251: 'doms kyang nyan du mi 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:9253: don mthun pa yis bag phab ste //
NK118(se)002:9256: gdul bya la gnas skabs su phan pa'i phyir zang zing dang /
NK118(se)002:9257: mthar thug gi phan pa'i rgyur chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9259: don de la yang nas yang du rjes su 'jug
NK118(se)002:9260: pa'i phyir phyi ma gsum ste bzhir grangs nges so
NK118(se)002:9261: / de ltar yang mdo sde rgyan las /
NK118(se)002:9262: sbyin mtshungs de ston len 'jug dang //
NK118(se)002:9263: bdag nyid rjes su 'jug rnams kyis //
NK118(se)002:9264: snyan par smra dang don spyod dang //
NK118(se)002:9265: don mthun nyid du 'dod pa yin //
NK118(se)002:9267: phan par byed pa'i thabs dang ni //
NK118(se)002:9269: de bzhin rjes su 'jug byed pas //
NK118(se)002:9270: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhir bshad do //
NK118(se)002:9272: yang chos kyi snod rung du sgrub pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9275: mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir yang bzhir nges te /
NK118(se)002:9277: dang pos snod gyur dngos po ste //
NK118(se)002:9278: gnyis pa yis ni mos pa yis //
NK118(se)002:9279: gsum pa yis ni sgrub pa ste //
NK118(se)002:9280: bzhi pas rnam par sbyong ba'o //
NK118(se)002:9282: des na 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gsum gyis bsdus
NK118(se)002:9283: pa'i sems can smin byed kyi thabs thams cad 'dir
NK118(se)002:9285: bsdus dang sdud par 'gyur ba dang //
NK118(se)002:9286: gang dag da ltar sdud byed pa //
NK118(se)002:9287: de kun de 'dra sdud lta bas //
NK118(se)002:9288: 'di ni sems can smin byed thabs //
NK118(se)002:9291: sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i sgo nas sems can la
NK118(se)002:9292: dngos sam brgyud pas phan bde sgrub pa thams cad
NK118(se)002:9293: yin yang / bsdu na bzhi po der 'du zhing //
NK118(se)002:9294: de yang 'khor du ma 'dus pa bsdu ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9295: 'dus pa smin par byed pa gnyis su bsdur rung ngo //
NK118(se)002:9296: gzhan las don byed tshul bcu gnyis su bsdus pa'ang snang ste /
NK118(se)002:9298: bya ba don dang ldan pa la grogs su 'gro ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9299: sems can sdug bsngal ba rnams kyi sdug bsngal sel ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9300: thabs mi shes pa rnams la rig pa ston pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9301: byas pa bzo zhing tshor te lan du phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9302: 'jigs pa rnams la bsrung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9303: sdug bsngal ba rnams kyi mya ngan sel ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9304: yo byad med pa rnams la yo byad stob pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9305: chos kyi 'khor legs par sdud pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9306: sems dang mthun par 'jug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9307: yang dag pa'i yon tan gyis dga' bar byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9308: legs par tshar gcod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9309: rdzu 'phrul gyis skrag pa dang 'dun par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:9310: zhes gsungs te sngar gyi bzhi po'i khog tu dngos shugs gang rung gis 'dus so //
NK118(se)002:9312: phyogs gnyis la ltos nas spang blang bya ba /
NK118(se)002:9313: 'jug ldog gi thabs dran shes bag yod gsum la sbyar ba /
NK118(se)002:9314: spyod lam thams cad dge bas dus 'da' ba la bslab pa'o //
NK118(se)002:9316: mthun phyogs kun slob mi mthun mtha' dag spang /
NK118(se)002:9319: gang gis ltung bar mi 'gyur ba //
NK118(se)002:9320: gnad kyis gnas rnams 'dis rig bya //
NK118(se)002:9321: zhes byang chub sems dpa'i bslab gzhi rgya chen rnams kyi gnad kyi gnas gang zhe na /
NK118(se)002:9323: bdag gi lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK118(se)002:9324: dus gsum dge ba skyes pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:9325: sems can kun la btang bar dang //
NK118(se)002:9326: de bsrung dag la spel ba'o //
NK118(se)002:9327: zhes pas gzhi gsum btang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9330: spel ba bzhis byang sems kyi sdom pa mtha' dag bsdus par bshad cing /
NK118(se)002:9331: ji ltar sgrub tshul kyang las dang po pas bsrung ba /
NK118(se)002:9333: ma dag sa bdun la gnas pas btang ba /
NK118(se)002:9334: dag pa sa gsum la gnas pas spel ba gtso bor sgrub par bshad de /
NK118(se)002:9335: rgyas par bslab btus nyid du blta bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:9336: 'dir ni de rnams kyi sgrub pa mthar phyin par 'grub pa'i man ngag bsdus pa ste /
NK118(se)002:9338: 'grub pa yang dag spong rnams te //
NK118(se)002:9339: zhes pas rdzogs byang sgrub pa'i mthun phyogs su gyur
NK118(se)002:9340: pa dge ba'i chos kun ma skyes pa rnams bskyed
NK118(se)002:9341: pa dang / skyes pa rnams gnas pa dang 'phel
NK118(se)002:9342: ba'i phyir dang por 'dun pa drag po bskyed nas
NK118(se)002:9344: phyi bshol med pa'i brtson 'grus brtsom /
NK118(se)002:9345: dge ba'i dmigs pa ma brjed par sems 'dzin cing yang dag par 'jog pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9346: de bzhin du rdzogs byang sgrub pa'i mi mthun phyogs
NK118(se)002:9347: su gyur pa sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos mtha'
NK118(se)002:9348: dag ma skyes pa mi bskyed cing skyes pa spang
NK118(se)002:9349: ba'i phyir 'dun pa sogs de ltar byed pa ste
NK118(se)002:9351: mi mthun phyogs dang gnyen po rnams //
NK118(se)002:9352: rnam pa thams cad yongs shes nas //
NK118(se)002:9353: de dag spang phyir brtson 'grus ni //
NK118(se)002:9354: rnam pa bzhi dag rab tu 'byung //
NK118(se)002:9356: gzhan yang byang chub kyi sems skyes pa de nyid
NK118(se)002:9357: bzung dag spel gsum gyi thabs la brtson pas bskyang
NK118(se)002:9359: de ltar dag gi sems 'di ni //
NK118(se)002:9360: legs bzung legs par bsrung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:9361: sems bsrung brtul zhugs ma gtogs pa //
NK118(se)002:9362: brtul zhugs mang pos ci zhig bya //
NK118(se)002:9364: de yang sems de nyid mi nyams par bzung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:9365: smon 'ju gi rang bzhin la sems gnas pa ste /
NK118(se)002:9366: mthun phyogs bslab par bya ba'i gnas so //
NK118(se)002:9367: sems de'i dri ma dag par byed pa ni /
NK118(se)002:9368: nyes spyod thams cad las bzlog par byed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:9369: mi mthun phyogs spong ba'i bslab bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9370: dge ba spel ba'i thabs ni /
NK118(se)002:9371: bdag gi bde ba dang gzhan gyi sdug bsngal barje ba la spel mar sbyong ste /
NK118(se)002:9374: bdag bde gzhan gyi sdug bsngal dag /
NK118(se)002:9375: yang dag barje bar ma byas na //
NK118(se)002:9376: sangs rgyas nyid du mi 'grub cing //
NK118(se)002:9377: 'khor ba na yang bde ba med //
NK118(se)002:9380: rtag tu dran dang shes bzhin bag yod bsten //
NK118(se)002:9383: bag yod pa dang ma bral zhing //
NK118(se)002:9384: dran pa dang ni shes bzhin dang //
NK118(se)002:9385: tshul bzhin du ni sems pas so //
NK118(se)002:9386: zhes pa ltar dus rtag tu bsrung sems mi brjed pa'i dran pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9387: rang rgyud la nyes pa byung ma byung rtog pa'i shes bzhin dang /
NK118(se)002:9388: 'jug ldog gi gnas la gzob pa lhur len pa'i
NK118(se)002:9389: bag yod dang gsum bsten pas sems bsrung bar bya
NK118(se)002:9391: sems bsrung 'dod pa rnams la ni //
NK118(se)002:9392: dran pa dang ni shes bzhin dang //
NK118(se)002:9393: srog la bab kyang srungs shig ces //
NK118(se)002:9394: bdag ni de ltar thal mo sbyor //
NK118(se)002:9397: bag yod bdud rtsi'i gnas te bag med pa //
NK118(se)002:9398: 'chi ba'i gnas su thub pas bka' stsal te //
NK118(se)002:9399: de bas khyod kyis dge chos spel slad du //
NK118(se)002:9400: gus pas rtag tu bag dang ldan par mdzod //
NK118(se)002:9403: 'gro 'dug za nyal spyod lam rnam pa bzhir //
NK118(se)002:9404: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo sde ltar //
NK118(se)002:9405: gang byed rigs mthun tshig gis smon lam 'debs //
NK118(se)002:9407: spyir spyod lam rnam bzhi'i dus thams cad du sgo
NK118(se)002:9408: gsum gyi spyod pa la brtags nas dran shes ma
NK118(se)002:9409: nyams pas / 'gro ba'i tshe mig gnya' shing gang tsam du blta zhing /
NK118(se)002:9410: gzhan dang 'phrad na 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis legs par 'ongs so zhes bsus te /
NK118(se)002:9411: snyan pa'i gtam gyis pha rol po'i yid dga' bar bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9412: 'dug pa'i tshe skyil krung drang por bsrangs te /
NK118(se)002:9413: 'chad nyan dang sgom pa sogs chos spyod bcu'i sgrub pa ci rigs pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9414: zas za ba'i tshe dkon mchog gsum rjes su dran
NK118(se)002:9415: pas phud dang gtor ma phul la chags sred spangs
NK118(se)002:9416: te / lus gso ba dang srin bu'i rigs la
NK118(se)002:9417: phan pa'i blos khams dang ting nge 'dzin la ji
NK118(se)002:9418: tsam 'phrod pa de tsam du longs spyad de zas
NK118(se)002:9419: kyi bsngo ba bya ba rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:9420: mtshan mo nyal ba'i tshe gzhogs g.yas phab la mgo byang du bstan nas nyal te /
NK118(se)002:9422: dkon mchog gsum sngas su dran pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9423: dge ba'i bya ba la ldang ba dang snang ba'i
NK118(se)002:9424: 'du shes bzhag nas chos nyid kyi ngang du blo
NK118(se)002:9426: nang par ldang ba na dkon mchog gsum dang byang chub kyi sems dran pas langs te /
NK118(se)002:9427: rmi lam du sdig pa mthong na 'phral du bshags shing dge na yi rang ba tsam byas nas /
NK118(se)002:9428: rang gzhan la phan par 'gyur ba'i chos spyod kyis dus 'da' bar bya ste /
NK118(se)002:9430: rgyal sras spyod tshe ji lta ji lta bur //
NK118(se)002:9431: dbang po'i spyod yul sna tshogs 'jug 'gyur ba //
NK118(se)002:9432: de lta de ltar rigs shing mthun tshig gis //
NK118(se)002:9433: sems can phan phyir de mngon 'du byed do //
NK118(se)002:9435: khyad par phal po che'i spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo sde las ji skad gsungs pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:9436: byang chub sems dpa' khang pa'i nang du 'jug pa'i
NK118(se)002:9437: sems can thams cad kyis thar pa'i grong khyer thob
NK118(se)002:9438: par gyur cig snyam du sems bskyed do //
NK118(se)002:9439: nyal ba'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi chos sku thob par /
NK118(se)002:9440: rmi lam rmi ba na chos thams cad rmi lam lta bur rtogs par /
NK118(se)002:9441: gnyid sad pa na ma rig pa las sad par /
NK118(se)002:9442: ldang ba na sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku thob par /
NK118(se)002:9443: gos gyon pa na ngo tsha dang khrel yod kyi gos gyon par /
NK118(se)002:9444: ska rags 'ching ba na dge ba'i rtsa ba dang 'brel bar /
NK118(se)002:9445: stan la 'dug pa na rdo rje'i gdan thob par /
NK118(se)002:9446: rgyab brten pa na byang chub kyi shing thob par /
NK118(se)002:9447: me gtong ba na nyon mongs pa'i bud shing bsreg par /
NK118(se)002:9448: 'bar ba na ye shes kyi me 'bar bar /
NK118(se)002:9449: g.yos zin pa na ye shes kyi bdud rtsi thob par /
NK118(se)002:9450: kha zas bza' ba na bsam gtan gyi zas thob par /
NK118(se)002:9451: phyir 'gro ba na 'khor ba'i grong las thar bar /
NK118(se)002:9452: skas la 'bab pa na sems can gyi don la 'khor bar 'jug par /
NK118(se)002:9453: sgo 'byed pa na thar pa'i grong gi sgo 'byed par /
NK118(se)002:9454: sgo gcod pa na ngan song gi sgo gcod par /
NK118(se)002:9455: lam du 'jug pa na 'phags pa'i lam du 'jug par /
NK118(se)002:9456: gyen la 'gro ba na sems can thams cad mtho ris kyi bde ba la 'god par /
NK118(se)002:9457: mthur la 'bab pa na ngan song gsum rgyun gcod par /
NK118(se)002:9458: sems can dang 'phrad pa na sangs rgyas dang mjal bar /
NK118(se)002:9459: rkang pa 'jog pa na sems can thams cad kyi don la 'gro bar /
NK118(se)002:9460: rkang pa 'degs pa na 'khor ba nas 'don par /
NK118(se)002:9461: rgyan dang ldan pa mthong na mtshan dpe'i rgyan thob par /
NK118(se)002:9462: rgyan med pa mthong na sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang ldan par /
NK118(se)002:9463: snod gang ba mthong na yon tan gyis gang bar /
NK118(se)002:9464: stong pa mthong na skyon gyis stongs par /
NK118(se)002:9465: sems can dga' ba mthong na chos la dga' bar /
NK118(se)002:9466: mi dga' ba mthong na 'dus byas kyi dngos po la mi dga' bar /
NK118(se)002:9467: sems can bde ba mthong na sangs rgyas kyi bde ba thob par /
NK118(se)002:9468: sdug bsngal ba mthong na sems can gyi sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar /
NK118(se)002:9469: nad pa mthong na nad las grol bar /
NK118(se)002:9470: drin du gzo ba mthong na sangs rgyas dang byang
NK118(se)002:9471: chub sems dpa' thams cad la drin lan ldon par
NK118(se)002:9472: / drin du mi gzo ba mthong na lta ba log pa la drin du mi bzo bar /
NK118(se)002:9473: rgol ba mthong na phas kyi rgol ba thams cad tshar gcod nus par /
NK118(se)002:9474: bstod pa mthong na sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la bstod par /
NK118(se)002:9475: chos kyi gtam byed pa mthong na sangs rgyas kyi spobs pa thob par /
NK118(se)002:9476: sku gzugs mthong na sangs rgyas thams cad mthong ba la sgrib pa med par /
NK118(se)002:9477: mchod rten mthong na 'gro ba thams cad kyi mchod rten du 'gyur bar /
NK118(se)002:9478: tshong byed pa mthong na 'phags pa'i nor bdun thob par /
NK118(se)002:9479: phyag 'tshal ba mthong na lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig
NK118(se)002:9480: rten gyis spyi gtsug bltar mi mngon pa thob par
NK118(se)002:9481: gyur cig snyam du sems bskyed par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9483: gsum pa don bsdu ba la /
NK118(se)002:9484: mkhas pa'i bzhed pa zlos pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9487: mkhyen rab dbang phyug klong chen rab 'byams ni //
NK118(se)002:9488: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi bsgom zhing //
NK118(se)002:9489: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug spyod //
NK118(se)002:9490: bsdu na dkar nag chos brgyad 'du zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)002:9492: tshad med bzhis blo sbyangs nas sems can gyi phan
NK118(se)002:9493: bde snying khong du chub pa ni smon pa'i bslab
NK118(se)002:9495: byang chub kyi sems mi 'dor ba nyid smon pa mi 'chor ba'i bslab byar bshad pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:9496: 'jug pa'i bslab bya phyin drug tu 'du tshul ni sngar bshad pa'i dkyus kyis go bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:9497: de dag kyang sems nyid ngal bso las /
NK118(se)002:9498: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi po bsgom //
NK118(se)002:9499: de yi mi mthun phyogs spang sems bsrung bya //
NK118(se)002:9500: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug spyad //
NK118(se)002:9501: de yi mi mthun phyogs spang brtson par bya //
NK118(se)002:9503: nag po'i chos bzhi spyad nas thun tshod 'das na smon sems gtong bar bshad la /
NK118(se)002:9504: de btang na 'jug sems kyang 'chor te /
NK118(se)002:9505: 'jug sems kyi rten smon sems yin pas /
NK118(se)002:9506: gyang med na ri mo med pa bzhin no snyam du dgongs nas /
NK118(se)002:9507: 'dir bsdu na chos brgyad du 'du bar 'phangs nas mdzad pa ste /
NK118(se)002:9509: mdor na nag po'i chos bzhi spang bya zhing //
NK118(se)002:9510: dkar po'i chos bzhi dag la nan tan bya //
NK118(se)002:9511: zhes pa'i skabs kyi 'grel pa'i mtshams sbyor du /
NK118(se)002:9512: da ni smon 'jug so so'i bsrung tshul bshad de /
NK118(se)002:9513: de yang dang por smon pa bsrung tshul la'ang /
NK118(se)002:9514: spang blang gi sgo nas bsrung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:9515: bslab pa ji snyed pa'i phyogs de dag gi rim pa /
NK118(se)002:9516: zhes 'byung bas 'jug pa gsal bar ma bsdus mod /
NK118(se)002:9517: de lta na'ang grub mtha' mdzod du srol gnyis kyi rtsa ltung gi dbye ba bshad nas /
NK118(se)002:9518: de ji ltar bsrung tshul 'chad pa'i skabs su /
NK118(se)002:9519: dran dang shes bzhin ma nyams pas nag po'i tshos bzhi dor nas /
NK118(se)002:9520: dkar po'i chos bzhi spyod pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9521: zhes pa 'dis bstan par dgongs nas de skad ces 'grel par mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:9523: 'dir ni phan dang bde ba rnams bya zhing //
NK118(se)002:9524: 'dir yang mi phan phyi mar gnod pa spang //
NK118(se)002:9525: srol gnyis bslab byar ma 'dus med ces smra //
NK118(se)002:9527: 'dir ni sems can la rjes su chags pa'i byams pas kun nas bslangs te /
NK118(se)002:9529: de thams cad gnas skabs su rang gzhan la phan
NK118(se)002:9530: zhing mthar thug bde ba sgrub pa'i thabs mkhas su
NK118(se)002:9531: 'gro ba'i phyir blang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:9532: zhe sdang gis kun nas blangs te khro rtsod kyis
NK118(se)002:9533: ni phan tshun gnyis ka'i rgyud ma rungs par byas
NK118(se)002:9534: pas tshe 'dir yang rang gzhan gnyis ka la mi
NK118(se)002:9535: phan te gnod pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:9536: phyi mar ni ngan song rnams las sdug bsngal che
NK118(se)002:9537: shos dmyal bar 'phen pas gnod pa'i phyi spang dgos
NK118(se)002:9538: par ma zad / 'dir bde ba ltar snang yang
NK118(se)002:9539: phyi mar gnod na nus pa ci yod kyis 'bad
NK118(se)002:9541: de ltar yang byang sa las /
NK118(se)002:9542: bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa'i nyes pa ni phal cher zhe sdang las 'byung gi /
NK118(se)002:9543: 'dod chags las 'byung ba ni ma yin par rig par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9544: zhes gang gsungs pa de la dgongs pa ni 'di yin par blta bar bya ste /
NK118(se)002:9545: byang chub sems dpa' sems can la rjes su chags
NK118(se)002:9546: shing sems can la byams pa'i dbang du byas nas
NK118(se)002:9548: de thams cad ni byang chub sems dpa'i bya ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:9549: mi bya ba ma yin la /
NK118(se)002:9550: bya bar rigs pa byed pa ni nyes par 'gyur ba mi rigs so //
NK118(se)002:9551: byang chub sems dpa' sems can rnams la sdang ba
NK118(se)002:9552: ni bdag dang gzhan rnams la phan par spyod pa
NK118(se)002:9553: ma yin la / de yang byang chub sems dpa'i bya ba ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:9554: de ltar bya ba ma yin pa byed pa ni nyes par 'gyur bar rigs so //
NK118(se)002:9556: de dag ji ltar slob pa'i thabs ni shing rta'i
NK118(se)002:9557: srol gnyis kyi bslab bya sngar bshad pa la ma
NK118(se)002:9559: lnga pa skye ba'i rten ni /
NK118(se)002:9560: skye ba'i rten ni lha klu 'phrog ma sogs //
NK118(se)002:9561: sdig can la yang skye bar klu sgrub bzhed //
NK118(se)002:9562: thogs med de'i rten so thar dgos zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)002:9563: spyir na sangs rgyas chos la dad byed cing //
NK118(se)002:9564: 'bras bu bla med byang chub la dad dang //
NK118(se)002:9565: rgyal sras spyod pa rgya mtshor dad byed na //
NK118(se)002:9566: byang sems skye bar dkon mchog t+aa lar gsungs //
NK118(se)002:9568: klu sgrub kyi lugs ltar na /
NK118(se)002:9569: brda shes don go la len 'dod yod na 'gro
NK118(se)002:9570: ba mtha' dag la skye bas rten gyi gang zag
NK118(se)002:9571: rgya che ste / sdig can sogs len pa po
NK118(se)002:9572: ji ltar dman yang smon pa'i sems bskyed tsam zhig
NK118(se)002:9573: nges par skye ba la dgongs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:9575: de'i tshe chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa na
NK118(se)002:9576: lha dang klu dang lha ma yin dang nam mkha'
NK118(se)002:9577: lding dang lto 'phye chen po bgrang ba las 'das
NK118(se)002:9578: pa dag gis bla na med pa yang dag par
NK118(se)002:9579: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK118(se)002:9581: 'phags pa thogs med kyi lugs ltar na /
NK118(se)002:9582: 'jug sdom ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i rten
NK118(se)002:9583: gling gsum gyi skyes pa bud med mtshan don byed
NK118(se)002:9585: so thar rigs bdun gang rung dang ldan pa'i rten la skye bar bshad pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:9587: so so thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK118(se)002:9588: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK118(se)002:9589: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK118(se)002:9590: skal ba yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK118(se)002:9592: byang sa'i lugs 'dir bslab pa'i grangs dang slob pa'i
NK118(se)002:9593: dus rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i 'jug sdom nyi tshe
NK118(se)002:9594: ba ma bshad pas sdom pa rgya chung ba ltar
NK118(se)002:9595: rten yang rgya chung ba yin par mngon no //
NK118(se)002:9596: de ltar na'ang srol gnyis po don la gnad gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:9597: rigs bdun sngon du song ma song gang yin kyang rung /
NK118(se)002:9598: sna gcig spong sems tsam yang med na byang sdom mi skye bas /
NK118(se)002:9599: don la nyes spyod spong bar dam 'cha' nus pa zhig nges par dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:9600: gzhan du na sems bskyed kyi bslab bya dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:9601: de bas bzhed pa spyir bshad na /
NK118(se)002:9602: gang len pa po'i 'gro ba'i sa pas bsdus pa ni lus rten yin la /
NK118(se)002:9603: 'dir gtso bo ni bsam pa'i rten te /
NK118(se)002:9604: dad sogs kyi blo khyad par can dngos su skyer rung ba nyid do //
NK118(se)002:9605: de ltar yang dkon mchog t+aa la'i mdo las /
NK118(se)002:9606: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i chos la dad gyur cig /
NK118(se)002:9607: byang chub bla na med la'ang dad gyur la //
NK118(se)002:9608: rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod la dad byed na //
NK118(se)002:9609: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyi sems skye'o //
NK118(se)002:9612: gang la skyes pa'i rten de'am tshe barjesa pa'i rten gzhan la'ang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:9613: gtong byed kyi rgyu gang yang ma byung na tshe
NK118(se)002:9614: barjesa te 'gro ba gang du skyes kyang byang sdom
NK118(se)002:9615: mi gtong bas / de'i dbang gis rang bzhin gyis
NK118(se)002:9616: nyes spyod la 'dzem zhing dge ba la ngang gis
NK118(se)002:9618: tshe 'phos pas brjed na'ang tshegs chung ngus dge ba'i
NK118(se)002:9619: bshes gnyen dang 'phrad nas sngar yod dran gso'i tshul
NK118(se)002:9620: du sdom pa nod par 'gyur gyi /
NK118(se)002:9621: gsar du yang dag par len dgos pa ni ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:9622: gtong byed kyi rgyu ma byung na rdzogs byang gi bar de srid du mi gtong ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:9623: drug pa nyams pa gso tshul la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:9625: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:9627: smon 'jug gi bslab bya ji snyed pa thams cad shes par byas nas mi nyams par bsrung zhing /
NK118(se)002:9628: gal te nyams na gso ba la 'bad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9629: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:9630: ltung ba'i rnam gzhag mu bzhir bstan pa /
NK118(se)002:9631: gnang bkag shes nas bslab tshul /
NK118(se)002:9634: gang gis rigs dang mi rigs ma brtags par //
NK118(se)002:9635: rtsom mam ldog gam btang snyoms 'jog kyang rung //
NK118(se)002:9636: 'os las 'das byed thams cad ltung ba'i sde //
NK118(se)002:9637: don chen bsgrub la chung btang gzugs brnyan te //
NK118(se)002:9638: nus pa'i yul min thams cad ltung ba med //
NK118(se)002:9639: mi nus der brtson de yi gzugs brnyan yin //
NK118(se)002:9641: gang zag gang gis bya ba gang la'ang blo'i nus
NK118(se)002:9642: pa ci yod kyis rung mi rung brtag dgos pa
NK118(se)002:9643: las / dgag sgrub rigs pa dang mi rigs pa ma brtags par /
NK118(se)002:9644: ldog par bya ba'i gnas la rtsom pa'am /
NK118(se)002:9645: brtsam par bya ba las ldog pa'am /
NK118(se)002:9646: 'jug ldog gi gzhi la btang snyoms su 'jog kyang rung ste ltung ba dang bcas pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:9648: brtags bzhin dpyad pas shes bzhin du bya bar 'os pa las 'das te /
NK118(se)002:9649: mnar sems kyis srog gcod pa lta bu mi rigs pa byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9650: ser snas mi sbyin pa lta bu rigs pa mi sgrub pa thams cad ltung ba'i sde yin no //
NK118(se)002:9651: don chen bsgrub phyir don chung gtong ba dper na sbyin pa byas pas tshul khrims 'chor na /
NK118(se)002:9653: gang zhig dga' ba'i yid kyis ni //
NK118(se)002:9654: lo brgyar sbyin pa byin pa bas //
NK118(se)002:9655: gang gis nyin gcig tshul khrims dag /
NK118(se)002:9656: bsrungs pa de ni khyad par 'phags //
NK118(se)002:9657: zhes pa ltar sbyin pa las tshul khrims mchog yin pas /
NK118(se)002:9658: de'i tshe sbyin pa gtong ba btang snyoms su 'jog pa lta bu'am /
NK118(se)002:9659: sdug bsngal dang yid mi bde ba chung ngus de
NK118(se)002:9660: dang de chen po'i gnyen por 'gro ba byis pa
NK118(se)002:9661: g.yang khar 'phyan pa mas brdung ba lta bu rnams
NK118(se)002:9662: ni ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan te don la ltung ba
NK118(se)002:9664: las dang po pas mgo dang mig sogs mi gtong
NK118(se)002:9665: ba lta bur rang gis nus pa'i yul min pas
NK118(se)002:9666: mi sgrub pa'am nus pa'i yul la 'jug ldog ma
NK118(se)002:9667: nor bar sgrub pa thams cad ltung med do //
NK118(se)002:9668: las dang po pas mgo ster ba lta bu rang
NK118(se)002:9669: gis nus pa'i yul min kyang der brtson par byed
NK118(se)002:9670: pa'am kun slong gnag na sbyor ba dkar yang ltung
NK118(se)002:9671: ba med pa'i gzugs brnyan te don la ltung ba
NK118(se)002:9672: yin no // de dag kyang tshul khrims gsum la dper sbyar na /
NK118(se)002:9674: zhe sdang gis srog gcod pa ltung ba /
NK118(se)002:9675: phan sems kyis gsod na ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK118(se)002:9676: snying rjes mi gsod pa ltung med /
NK118(se)002:9677: gzhan la phan kyang mi gsod pa ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK118(se)002:9679: ser snas mi sbyin pa ltung ba /
NK118(se)002:9680: phan sems kyis mi ster ba ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK118(se)002:9681: bsam pa dag pas ster ba ltung med /
NK118(se)002:9682: gzhan la gnod phyir ster ba ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK118(se)002:9684: nad g.yog ma byas pa ltung ba /
NK118(se)002:9685: don chen sgrub phyir nad g.yog ma byas pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK118(se)002:9686: brtse bas nad g.yog byed pa ltung med /
NK118(se)002:9687: nad g.yog gzhan yod bzhin du rang gi klog spong
NK118(se)002:9688: sogs don chen dor nas nad g.yog byas na ltung
NK118(se)002:9691: gzhan phyir phan na lus ngag mi dge bdun //
NK118(se)002:9692: gnang ba'i skabs yod don la dge ba yin //
NK118(se)002:9694: gzhan la phan pa'i thabs su 'gyur na /
NK118(se)002:9695: rang gi mi dge bcu'i nyes spyod sdom pa las lus ngag gi bdun gnang ba'i skabs yod de /
NK118(se)002:9696: 'di ltar mang po'i srog skyob phyir gshed ma gsod pa lta bu srog gcod dang /
NK118(se)002:9697: bkres pas srog la nyen pa skyob phyir 'byor ldan
NK118(se)002:9698: las brkus nas ster ba lta bu ma byin len
NK118(se)002:9699: dang / bud med 'dod pas gdungs te 'chi nges
NK118(se)002:9700: skyob phyir der spyod pa lta bu 'dod log dang
NK118(se)002:9701: dang / / gsod nges kyi skyes bu thar phyir sba ba lta bu rdzun dang /
NK118(se)002:9702: sdig grogs kyis bslus nas ngan 'gror khrid pa las
NK118(se)002:9703: ldog phyir de gnyis 'byed pa lta bu phra ma
NK118(se)002:9704: dang / mya ngan gyi non pa bsang ba'am gtam
NK118(se)002:9705: la dga' bas chos la 'jug pa'i dgos pa mthong
NK118(se)002:9706: na sgrung dang gtam rgyud sogs smra ba ngag 'khyal
NK118(se)002:9707: dang / dang / mi dge'i bya ba las ldog phyir bshe ba lta bu tshig rtsub ste /
NK118(se)002:9708: de rnams mi dge ba ltar snang yang don la dge ba yin pas bya bar gnang ste /
NK118(se)002:9709: sems kyi 'phen pa las gzhan pa'i dge sdig yod pa ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:9710: de ltar yang bzhi brgya pa las /
NK118(se)002:9711: bsam pas byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK118(se)002:9712: dge'am yang na mi dge ba //
NK118(se)002:9713: thams cad dge ba nyid 'gyur te //
NK118(se)002:9714: gang phyir sems de gtso bo'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:9717: dge slong rang gi pha rgan la //
NK118(se)002:9718: myur 'dod zhes ni bskul gyur nas //
NK118(se)002:9719: phul bas de ni shi gyur kyang //
NK118(se)002:9720: mtshams med sbyor ba ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:9721: bsam pa bzang pos mchil lhwam zhig /
NK118(se)002:9722: thub pa'i dbu la bzhag pa dang //
NK118(se)002:9723: de bzhin gzhan gyis bsal byas pa //
NK118(se)002:9724: gnyis kas rgyal srid thob par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:9725: de phyir bsam pa'i rtsa ba la //
NK118(se)002:9726: bsod nams sdig pa rnam par gnas //
NK118(se)002:9728: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK118(se)002:9729: snying rjer ldan zhing byams phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:9730: sems dge ba la nyes pa med //
NK118(se)002:9732: des na dge sdig gi las ni sems kyi 'phen
NK118(se)002:9733: pa nyid la rag las pa'i phyir yid kyi las
NK118(se)002:9734: gsum ni nam yang gnang ba med do //
NK118(se)002:9735: gsum pa la srol gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:9736: mgon po klu sgrub kyi lugs ni /
NK118(se)002:9737: thun 'das nyams na 'phags pa nam snying la //
NK118(se)002:9738: tho rangs gsol btab rmi lam ltung ba 'chags //
NK118(se)002:9739: lhag ma phung po gsum pa nyin mtshan du //
NK118(se)002:9740: lan gsum 'don pas gzhil ba klu sgrub lugs //
NK118(se)002:9742: spyir byang sems kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ni /
NK118(se)002:9743: rten gzhi smon sems btang ba /
NK118(se)002:9745: spong rkyen sdom pa phul ba gsum du 'du ba las /
NK118(se)002:9746: de yang sngar bshad kyi rtsa ltung bco brgyad dam
NK118(se)002:9747: nyi shu po thams cad spong ba ni dbang rnon
NK118(se)002:9749: dbang po 'bring rtul gnyis la ni /
NK118(se)002:9750: rang blo'i stobs dang sbyar ba'i so so'i bslab bya
NK118(se)002:9751: de dag bsrungs pas byang sems kyi bslab pa las
NK118(se)002:9754: byang chub sems ni bskyed bgyi zhing //
NK118(se)002:9756: de bzhin du ni bslabs pa la //
NK118(se)002:9757: rim pa bzhin du bslab par bgyi //
NK118(se)002:9758: zhes 'jug pa blo'i nus tshod dang sbyar te rim gyis bslab pa las /
NK118(se)002:9759: thog ma nyid nas bslab bya thams cad la slob par dam ma bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:9761: ltung ba spyi'i nyes dmigs la gsum las /
NK118(se)002:9762: dang po khas blangs nyams pas smad pa'i gnas su 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:9763: ston pa sangs rgyas bslus pas sangs rgyas mi mnyes /
NK118(se)002:9764: yul sems can bslus pas de dag mi mgu /
NK118(se)002:9765: rang bslus pas rang don nyams shing kun gyis smad pa'i gnas su 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:9766: gnyis pa ming don shor bas mi 'dod pa thams cad 'du ste /
NK118(se)002:9767: rgyal po rgyal srid nyams pa ltar tshe 'dir bkra
NK118(se)002:9768: mi shis shing 'chi khar mya ngan gyis gdung bar
NK118(se)002:9770: gsum pa nyes pa lci bas phyi ma ngan 'gror ltung zhing de las thar dka' ste /
NK118(se)002:9772: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis gsungs tshul du //
NK118(se)002:9775: khyad par rtsa ltung gi nyes dmigs ni /
NK118(se)002:9776: sngon bskyed pa'i byang sems kyi dge rtsa thams cad thal bar rlog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9777: de nyid kyis ni dkon mchog lha dang bcas pa bslus pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9778: des ni spyir ngan 'gro dang khyad par sems can dmyal ba chen por skye bar 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:9780: de dag rtsa ba'i ltung ba ste //
NK118(se)002:9781: sems can dmyal ba chen po'i rgyu //
NK118(se)002:9784: so thar las bsrung mi nus na 'bul ba bslab byar gnang mod /
NK118(se)002:9785: byang sdom phul na ni nyes pa ches lci bar 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:9786: rgyal ba sras bcas kyi spyan sngar 'gro ba'i phan
NK118(se)002:9787: bde sgrub par dam bcas pa nyid btang ba'i phyir
NK118(se)002:9789: bla na med pa'i bde ba la //
NK118(se)002:9790: bsam pa thag pas mgron gnyer nas //
NK118(se)002:9791: 'gro ba thams cad bslus byas na //
NK118(se)002:9794: sems can gcig gi bde ba yang //
NK118(se)002:9795: bshis na bdag nyid nyams 'gyur na //
NK118(se)002:9796: nam mkha'i ma lus mtha' klas pa'i //
NK118(se)002:9797: lus can bde bshig smos ci dgos //
NK118(se)002:9799: de ltar nyes dmigs bsam nas ltung bas ma gos par bya ba la 'bad du zin kyang /
NK118(se)002:9802: nyon mongs pa mang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9803: ma gus pa ste rgyu bzhis ltung ba byung na
NK118(se)002:9804: phyir bcos pa'i sgo nas nyes pa las ldang bar
NK118(se)002:9805: bya'o // de la thun 'das zhes pa ni /
NK118(se)002:9806: nyin la cha gsum mtshan la cha gsum ste thun
NK118(se)002:9807: drug tu phye ba'i nyin zhag gi drug cha'i mjug
NK118(se)002:9808: tu gnyen pos sleb na de'i tshul khrims rgyun mi
NK118(se)002:9809: chad cing rnam par dag par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:9810: de la snga dro lta bur thun snga ma'i thog
NK118(se)002:9811: tha bar gsum gang rung la ltung ba byung na
NK118(se)002:9812: / gung tshigs lta bu de ma thag gi thun
NK118(se)002:9813: phyi ma'i thog tha bar gsum gang rung de dang
NK118(se)002:9814: de'i dus su byang chub kyi sems dang ma bral
NK118(se)002:9815: ba nyid kyis bshags pas sor chud pa'i don no
NK118(se)002:9816: / // de ltar bshags tshad las ma 'das na
NK118(se)002:9817: rtsa ltung yang yang byung yang bshags pas sor chud
NK118(se)002:9818: par 'gyur bas phyir bcos su yod pa yin la
NK118(se)002:9819: / // / gal te bshags tshad las 'das na
NK118(se)002:9820: ni tshul khrims gtugs pa yin pas phyir bcos kyis
NK118(se)002:9822: bshags bsdams sngon du 'gro bas slar cho ga bzhin du blang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:9824: de lta na'ang 'dir sdom pa bskyar bar ma bshad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:9825: slar skye bas shor yang sla'o snyam du nan tan
NK118(se)002:9826: mi byed pa spang phyir bslab btus su dngos su
NK118(se)002:9827: ma gsungs pa bzhin du 'dir yang de ltar mdzad
NK118(se)002:9828: la / 'on kyang der nye ba 'khor gyi mdo
NK118(se)002:9829: drangs nas nyan thos dang byang sems kyi rtsa ltung
NK118(se)002:9830: byung ba bcos su yod med kyi khyad par bshad
NK118(se)002:9831: pas don gyis gsungs par mngon te /
NK118(se)002:9832: bcos su yod pa'ang nyes pa bshags pa dang sdom pa len pa las ma 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:9833: des na phyir bcos tshul la dbang po'i khyad par gyis gsum las /
NK118(se)002:9834: dbang 'bring lha'i rnal 'byor la nan tan du byed pa dag gis /
NK118(se)002:9835: rang gi yi dam gyi lha'i mdun du yan lag bdun pa byas la bshags pas ldang mod /
NK118(se)002:9836: rig sngags spyi'i lha 'phags pa nam mkha' snying po'i mdun du bshags par 'dod na /
NK118(se)002:9837: nyin mtshan gyis bar ma chod par bshags par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:9838: gang gi tshe ltung ba byung nas bzung khrus dang gtsang sbra bya /
NK118(se)002:9840: 'phags pa nam mkha'i snying po'i mtshan nas brjod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9841: 'phags pas bdag la zhal bstan te sdig pa dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK118(se)002:9842: zhes gsol ba drag tu btab pas /
NK118(se)002:9843: dngos sam rmi lam du skal pa dang 'tshams par
NK118(se)002:9844: de nyid kyi gzugs sam mi nas bya'i bar ci
NK118(se)002:9845: rigs pa'i gzugs kyis ltung ba las 'byin pa'i thabs
NK118(se)002:9847: gal te ston par mi byed na tho rangs langs
NK118(se)002:9848: la gtsang sbra dang bcas pas shar phyogs su bltas
NK118(se)002:9849: te / spos btul bas mchod cing /
NK118(se)002:9850: skya rengs skya rengs snying rje chen po legs pa
NK118(se)002:9851: chen po khyod dzam+bu'i gling du shar ma thag tu
NK118(se)002:9852: bdag la thugs rjes khyab par mdzod cig /
NK118(se)002:9853: nam mkha' snying po snying rje chen po dang ldan
NK118(se)002:9854: pa la yang bdag gi tshig gis myur du bskul
NK118(se)002:9855: te / thabs gang gis ltung ba myur du 'chags par 'dod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9856: theg pa chen po'i 'phags pa la thabs dang shes
NK118(se)002:9857: rab thob par 'gyur ba'i thabs de dag gi rmi
NK118(se)002:9859: zhes brjod nas nyal bas skya rengs 'char ba'i tshe
NK118(se)002:9860: rmi lam du nam snying gi gzugs skal ba bzhin
NK118(se)002:9861: ston pas ltung ba 'chags su 'jug go //
NK118(se)002:9862: dbang po dman pa dag gis ni stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9863: de la rten gyi stobs ni gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:9864: bshags yul gyi rten dge ba'i bshes gnyen nam de
NK118(se)002:9865: bzhin gshegs pa'i rten khyad par can mchod pa'i dbus
NK118(se)002:9866: su spyan drang zhing dmigs pas kyang mdun gyi nam
NK118(se)002:9867: mkhar rgyal ba sras bcas bsam pa'o //
NK118(se)002:9868: rang rgyud kyi rten ni skyabs sems yin pas sems
NK118(se)002:9869: can thams cad sgrol 'dod kyi snying rjes rdzogs byang
NK118(se)002:9870: gi sems dang ldan pas skyabs 'gro spyi dang /
NK118(se)002:9871: khyad par gtso rgyal mas 'jigs pa las skyob par gsol ba 'debs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:9872: rnam par sun 'byin pa'i stobs ni /
NK118(se)002:9873: sdig ltung dran zhing 'gyod pa drag pos ltung ba
NK118(se)002:9874: gang byung de dang de'i ming nas brjod de bshags
NK118(se)002:9875: pa'o // gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i stobs ni /
NK118(se)002:9876: sangs rgyas dang byang sems kyi mtshan bzung ba /
NK118(se)002:9877: sku gzugs dang mchod rten bzhengs pa /
NK118(se)002:9878: rten la phyag mchod dang skor ba bya ba /
NK118(se)002:9879: mdo rgyud zab mo klog pa'am kha ton bya ba /
NK118(se)002:9880: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yig brgya sogs sdig sbyong la basngagasa pa'i gzungs sngags bzlas brjod bya ba /
NK118(se)002:9881: stong pa nyid la mos pa zhes sdig pa'i ngo
NK118(se)002:9882: bo la ji lta bu gang na gnas so sor
NK118(se)002:9883: brtags nas mi dmigs pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog
NK118(se)002:9884: pa ste / de dag la gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i sgo drug ces grags so //
NK118(se)002:9886: phyin chad srog la bab kyang sdig pa'i las 'di
NK118(se)002:9887: dag mi bya'o zhes dam bcas nas nyes spyod kyi
NK118(se)002:9889: gzhan yang yul gyi khyad par sems can la gnod
NK118(se)002:9890: pa'i zhe sdang gi dang chos la gnod pa'i gti
NK118(se)002:9891: mug gi kun dkris lci ba gnyis dang /
NK118(se)002:9892: de las gzhan pa'i chags sems dang zhe sdang tsam
NK118(se)002:9893: gyi kun dkris rnams rim par theg chen gyi sdom
NK118(se)002:9894: ldan bcu tshogs dang lnga tshogs dang gang zag gcig
NK118(se)002:9895: gam gnyis la bshags par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9896: gal te de lta bu'i yul ma rnyed na thams cad dkon mchog gi drung du bshags so //
NK118(se)002:9897: khyad par nyin ma tshan dus drug tu sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:9898: so lnga la phyag byas nas bshags pa yi rang
NK118(se)002:9899: bsngo ba'i phung po gsum gyi mdo kha ton du
NK118(se)002:9900: byas pas rtsa ba las gzhan pa'am /
NK118(se)002:9901: brjod nges dang shes bzhin gyis ma zin pas phyir
NK118(se)002:9902: bcos ma grub pa'i ltung ba'i lhag ma rnams byang
NK118(se)002:9905: nyid dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK118(se)002:9906: phung po gsum pa gdon bya zhing //
NK118(se)002:9907: rgyal dang byang chub sems brten na //
NK118(se)002:9908: ltung ba'i lhag ma des zhi bya //
NK118(se)002:9910: dbang rnon gyi gang zag dam pa kha cig gis ni /
NK118(se)002:9911: thog mar sgyu ma rmi lam lta bu'i tshul gyis
NK118(se)002:9912: mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i spyan
NK118(se)002:9914: nyes pa de nyid kyi ngo bo la brtags shing
NK118(se)002:9915: dpyad pas dmigs med nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin
NK118(se)002:9916: du shes pa'i ngang la mnyam par gzhag pas nyes
NK118(se)002:9917: ltung thams cad las grol bar 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:9918: phyogs bcu rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK118(se)002:9920: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK118(se)002:9921: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK118(se)002:9922: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK118(se)002:9923: de ni 'gyod tshangs mchog yin no //
NK118(se)002:9925: de ltar dbang po'i khyad par gyis phyir bcos gsum
NK118(se)002:9926: du bsdus pa 'di ni nag po pa'i dgongs pa
NK118(se)002:9928: dman pa kha cig ni dngos por 'dzin pa'i dbang
NK118(se)002:9929: gis 'gyed cing yid la gcags pas gzhan gyi drung
NK118(se)002:9931: phyis sdom pas rim gyis nyes pa de las ring zhig na ldang ba yod do //
NK118(se)002:9932: bar ma kha cig ni rig sngags dang gsang sngags
NK118(se)002:9933: kyi lha byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha' snying po
NK118(se)002:9934: la sogs pa mnyes par byas te lha'i rjes su
NK118(se)002:9935: gnang ba thob pas ltung ba las ldang ngo //
NK118(se)002:9936: dam pa kha cig ni gang gis ltung bar brjod
NK118(se)002:9937: pa de nyid la byang chub kyi sems su shes
NK118(se)002:9938: pas tshegs med par gnas te ji ltar 'phags pa'i
NK118(se)002:9939: chos thams cad 'byung ba med par bstan pa zhes
NK118(se)002:9940: bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las gsungs pa
NK118(se)002:9942: byang chub sems dpa' gang gis las med cing rnam
NK118(se)002:9943: par smin pa med par shes pa des las kyi
NK118(se)002:9944: sgrib pa rnam par dag pa thob bo //
NK118(se)002:9946: gnyis pa 'phags pa thogs med kyi lugs la /
NK118(se)002:9947: gtong rgyu ngos bzung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9948: nyes ltung phyir bcos tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:9950: smon pa'i sems ni nag po'i chos bzhi spyad //
NK118(se)002:9951: sems can snying nas blos btang de gtong 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:9952: rgyun mi chad spyod ngo tsha khrel med dang //
NK118(se)002:9953: des mgu dga' dang de nyid yon tan du //
NK118(se)002:9954: lta ba kun dkris chen pos sdom pa 'joms //
NK118(se)002:9955: pham pa zhes brjod chung dang 'bring la min //
NK118(se)002:9957: rtsa ba sems can blos btang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:9958: yan lag nag po'i chos bzhi spyad na rten gzhi smon sems gtong la /
NK118(se)002:9959: de btang bas brten pa 'jug sems kyang btang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:9960: rnyed bkur gyi phyir bdag bstod gzhan smod sogs pham
NK118(se)002:9961: pa'i gnas lta bu'i chos bzhi rgyun mi chad du
NK118(se)002:9962: spyod pa dang / ngo tsha dang khrel yod chung ngu tsam yang mi bskyed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9963: des mgu zhing dga' bar byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:9964: de nyid la yon tan du blta ba ste yan
NK118(se)002:9965: lag bzhi tshang na kun dkris chen po'i ltung ba
NK118(se)002:9966: ste / sdom pa 'joms par byed pas na pham pa zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:9967: yan lag gang rung tshang la ngo tsha dang khrel
NK118(se)002:9968: yod cung zad skye zhing gzhan gyis bskul bas ldog
NK118(se)002:9970: yan lag gang rung de la ngo tsha cher bskyed
NK118(se)002:9971: cing gzhan rkyen la ma ltos par rang nyid kyis
NK118(se)002:9972: de las myur du ldog par byed na kun dkris
NK118(se)002:9973: chung ngu ste / de gnyis kyis sdom pa gtong ba ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:9974: 'o na gtan la dbab pa bsdu bar /
NK118(se)002:9975: gtong byed de gnyis gcig tu byas pa'i steng du bzlog zla sdom min skyes pa /
NK118(se)002:9977: kun dkris 'bring yan chod kyi bzhi tshang ba rnams
NK118(se)002:9978: bsnan nas gtong byed bzhir gsungs pa dang 'gal lo
NK118(se)002:9980: 'dir bshad kyi gtong byed gnyis ni byang sa'i dgongs
NK118(se)002:9981: pa ltar dbang po 'bring rtul gyi dbang du byas
NK118(se)002:9982: pa rags pa'i rnam gzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:9983: thabs mkhas kyi mdo ltar bslab btus kyi rtsa ltung
NK118(se)002:9984: bzhi po dbang 'bring gi rtsa ltung yin pa ltar
NK118(se)002:9985: / de dang cha 'dra ba byang sa'i bzhi yang
NK118(se)002:9986: dbang 'bring gi rtsa ltung du don gyis thob pa'i
NK118(se)002:9987: / phyir ro // des na bsdu bar zag pa
NK118(se)002:9988: 'bring pos spyad pa gtong byed du bzhed pa ni
NK118(se)002:9989: dbang rnon gyi dbang du mdzad pa ste /
NK118(se)002:9990: 'dis 'phags pa thogs med kyi lugs la'ang dbang rnon gyi sdom pa bzhed par mngon no //
NK118(se)002:9992: phas pham byung na slar blang 'bring ni gsum //
NK118(se)002:9993: tha ma gcig mdun dngos po brjod pas bshags //
NK118(se)002:9994: mthun pa'i gang zag med na yid kyi bsdam //
NK118(se)002:9995: rgya chen spyod pa'i ring lugs zla med do //
NK118(se)002:9998: kun dkris chen pos pham pa'i gnas lta bu'i rtsa ltung gis gtong bas /
NK118(se)002:9999: de dag byung na bshags bsdams dang bsag sbyangs la nan tan byas la /
NK118(se)002:10000: sdom pa slar blang bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:10001: grangs ni gsum las lhag pa bskyar du med par
NK118(se)002:10002: byang sa las bshad ces kun mkhyen chen po gsung
NK118(se)002:10003: ngo // kun dkris 'bring gis spyad pa'i pham 'dra rnams ni gang zag gsum yan chod dang /
NK118(se)002:10004: kun dkris chung ngus spyad pa'i rtsa ltung dang /
NK118(se)002:10005: de las gzhan pa'i nyes byas zhe drug la kun
NK118(se)002:10006: slong gi dbang gis nyon mongs can yin min dang
NK118(se)002:10007: ltung med du 'gyur ba'ang yod pas /
NK118(se)002:10008: de dag gang byung gang zag gcig yan chad kyi
NK118(se)002:10009: drung du bshags shing bsdams pas dag par 'gyur te
NK118(se)002:10010: / sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK118(se)002:10011: sdom pa slar yang blang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:10012: zag pa 'bring ni gsum la bshags //
NK118(se)002:10013: gcig gi mdun du lhag ma rnams //
NK118(se)002:10014: nyon mongs mi mongs bdag sems bzhin //
NK118(se)002:10016: de thams cad la bshags yul mthun pa'i gang zag
NK118(se)002:10017: med na rgyal ba sras bcas yid kyis bsam pa'i
NK118(se)002:10018: spyan sngar bshags shing bsdam par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10020: dum bu dang por legs par gsol byed pa //
NK118(se)002:10021: skyes bu rab yin 'bring ni gnyis la'o //
NK118(se)002:10022: dum bu thar mar gso ba tha ma ste //
NK118(se)002:10023: zhes spyir dus drug dang khyad par dus re re la cha gsum gsum du phye nas /
NK118(se)002:10024: de dang der gnyen pos sleb pa gang zag rab
NK118(se)002:10025: 'bring tha gsum gyi gso tshul yin par bshad do
NK118(se)002:10027: bsod nams rgyun chags su 'byung ba'i /
NK118(se)002:10028: sangs rgyas kyi sras su 'gyur ba'i /
NK118(se)002:10029: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i phan yon no //
NK118(se)002:10031: 'di 'dra'i byang chub sems kyi rtsis zin na //
NK118(se)002:10032: gnyid sogs bag med gyur la'ang bsod nams shugs /
NK118(se)002:10035: re zhig smon pa sems bskyed kyi dbang du byas na /
NK118(se)002:10036: 'di'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur ba lta zhog gi /
NK118(se)002:10037: gnas skabs su'ang 'khor lo sgyur ba dang lha'i dbang
NK118(se)002:10038: po sogs mtho ris kyi 'bras bu lan grangs du
NK118(se)002:10039: mar myong yang / mngon mtho'i 'bras bu 'byin pa'i nus pa nam yang zad par mi 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:10041: dge ba gzhan kun chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK118(se)002:10042: 'bras bu bskyed nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK118(se)002:10043: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK118(se)002:10044: 'bras bu sbyin pas mi zad 'phel bar 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:10046: 'jug sems kyi rtsis zin na ni 'bras bu mi zad pa 'byung bar ma zad /
NK118(se)002:10047: 'bras bu'i rgyu bsod nams kyang rgyun mi chad du
NK118(se)002:10048: 'byung bas smon pa dang khyad zhugs pa yin te
NK118(se)002:10050: byang chub smon pa'i sems las ni //
NK118(se)002:10052: ji ltar 'jug pa'i sems bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:10053: bsod nams rgyun chags 'byung ba min //
NK118(se)002:10054: gang nas bzung ste sems can khams //
NK118(se)002:10055: mtha' yas rab tu bsgral bya'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:10056: mi ldog pa yi sems kyis ni //
NK118(se)002:10057: sems de yang dag blangs gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:10058: de nas bzung ste gnyid log gam //
NK118(se)002:10059: bag med gyur kyang bsod nams shugs //
NK118(se)002:10060: rgyun mi chad par du ma zhig /
NK118(se)002:10061: nam mkha' mnyam par rab tu 'byung //
NK118(se)002:10063: phan par bsam pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK118(se)002:10064: sangs rgyas mchod las khyad 'phags na //
NK118(se)002:10065: sems can ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK118(se)002:10066: bde don brtson pa smos ci dgos //
NK118(se)002:10071: byang chub kyi sems skyes ma thag nas rgyal ba
NK118(se)002:10072: rnams kyi sras zhes ming 'pho zhing phyag bya ba'i
NK118(se)002:10075: byang chub sems bskyed gyur na skad cig gis //
NK118(se)002:10076: 'khor ba'i btson rar bsdams pa'i nyam thag rnams //
NK118(se)002:10077: bde gshegs rnams kyi sras zhes brjod bya zhing //
NK118(se)002:10078: 'jig rten lha mir bcas pas phyag rgyar 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:10080: gal te nyes pa dga' zhig byung yang smon sems
NK118(se)002:10081: ma btang na rigs kyi sgo nas nyan rang dgra
NK118(se)002:10083: byang sems kyi ming yang mi 'dor ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:10086: dper na rdo rje rin po che ni chag kyang gser gyi rgyan thams cad zil gyis gnon cing /
NK118(se)002:10087: rdo rje rin po che'i ming yang mi 'dor la /
NK118(se)002:10088: dbul ba yang rnam par bzlog go //
NK118(se)002:10089: de bzhin du rnam pa thams cad mkhyen par sems
NK118(se)002:10090: bskyed pa'i rdo rje rin po che nan tan dang
NK118(se)002:10091: bral yang / nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan thams cad zil gyis gnon cing /
NK118(se)002:10092: byang chub sems dpa'i ming yang mi 'dor la /
NK118(se)002:10093: 'khor ba'i dbul ba thams cad kyang rnam par bzlog go //
NK118(se)002:10096: grangs med gsum bdun so gsum byang chub thob //
NK118(se)002:10098: byang chub sems dpa' la'ang dbang po'i rim pas grol tshul gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:10099: rgyal po lta bu'am 'dod chen po'i sems bskyed ces
NK118(se)002:10100: rang grol nas gzhan sgrol bar 'dod pa'i byang sems
NK118(se)002:10102: bskal pa grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum thogs te /
NK118(se)002:10104: sa bcu re re la gsum gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:10105: gnyan pa lta bu'am ye shes dam pa'i sems bskyed
NK118(se)002:10106: ces rang dang 'gro ba mnyam du thar bar 'dod
NK118(se)002:10107: pa byang sems dbang 'bring rnams ni grangs med bdun
NK118(se)002:10108: thogs te / tshogs sbyor gnyis su gnyis re mthong lam du gcig /
NK118(se)002:10110: rdzi bo lta bu'am dpe med pa'i sems bskyed ces
NK118(se)002:10111: sems can thams cad bsgral nas rang nyid grol bar
NK118(se)002:10112: 'dod pa byang sems dbang rnon rnams ni grangs med
NK118(se)002:10114: dang po la mos spyod kyis tshogs sbyor gnyis rdzogs te /
NK118(se)002:10115: tshogs lam gsum du dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi //
NK118(se)002:10117: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi rnams bsgoms pas tshogs lam
NK118(se)002:10118: chen por gnas skabs kyi yon tan mngon shes lnga
NK118(se)002:10119: dang khyad par gyi 'bras bu chos rgyun gyi ting
NK118(se)002:10120: nge 'dzin thob / de nas sgom byung gtso bor
NK118(se)002:10121: gyur pa sbyor lam du nges 'byed yan lag bzhi
NK118(se)002:10122: nge 'dzin thob / ste / drod kyis kun nas
NK118(se)002:10123: nyon mongs pa dang rtse mos rnam byang gi gzung
NK118(se)002:10124: rtog bzod pas gang zag rdzas yod dang chos mchog
NK118(se)002:10125: gis btags yod bzhi spong zhing /
NK118(se)002:10126: dang po gnyis su dbang po lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:10127: phyi ma gnyis su de goms pas mi mthun phyogs kyis mi bardzi ba'i stobs lnga sgom mo //
NK118(se)002:10128: de nas 'phags lam la sa bcu las /
NK118(se)002:10129: grangs med gnyis pas ma dag sa bdun dang /
NK118(se)002:10130: gsum pas dag pa sa gsum rdzogs par byed /
NK118(se)002:10131: de'ang sa dang po mthong ba'i lam du chos nyid
NK118(se)002:10132: kyi bden pa mngon sum du mthong bas kun brtags
NK118(se)002:10133: blo bur gyi sgrib pa thams cad bcom nas skad
NK118(se)002:10134: cig gcig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgya bgrod pa
NK118(se)002:10135: sogs yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK118(se)002:10136: des byang chub kyi yan lag bdun nyams su len zhing sbyin pa'i phar phyin la gtso bor spyod /
NK118(se)002:10137: mthong ba'i don de spang bya lhan skyes spong ba'i
NK118(se)002:10138: gnyen por rgyun goms par byed pa sa gnyis pa
NK118(se)002:10139: nas bcu pa'i bar gyi sgom lam sa dgur rang
NK118(se)002:10140: skal gyi sgrib pa las grol ba'i glo bur rnam
NK118(se)002:10141: dag gi cha re thob pas sngar mthong lam gyi
NK118(se)002:10142: yon tan de nyid stong 'gyur sogs gong nas gong
NK118(se)002:10143: du 'phel zhing / de rnams su spyir 'phags lam yan lag brgyad sgom la /
NK118(se)002:10144: bye brag so sor tshul khrims nas ye shes kyi bar gyi phyin bcu la gtso bor spyod do //
NK118(se)002:10145: de ltar grangs med gsum gyis slob lam rdzogs nas
NK118(se)002:10146: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa mi skye ba'i
NK118(se)002:10147: chos can du byas pas de'i gnyen po la slob
NK118(se)002:10148: mi dgos par mi slob lam du phyin te bla
NK118(se)002:10149: na med pa'i byang chub brnyes pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:10150: de ltar yang sems nyid ngal bso las /
NK118(se)002:10151: de ltar byang chub phyogs chos sum cu bdun //
NK118(se)002:10152: slob pa'i lam bzhir bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs su /
NK118(se)002:10153: mi slob sa la mi gnas mya ngan 'da' //
NK118(se)002:10155: de la 'dir dbang rnon gyi grangs med gsum yang
NK118(se)002:10156: sems stobs shin tu che bas skad cig re re
NK118(se)002:10157: la bskal pa mang po'i tshogs bzlums par bshad pas
NK118(se)002:10158: grangs ji lta ba bzhin du gsog mi dgos par
NK118(se)002:10159: ma zad / mthong lam thob nas ni rang dbang 'byor ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:10160: ci dgar grol bar nus te /
NK118(se)002:10162: chos rnams la chos kyi mig rnams par dag pa
NK118(se)002:10163: thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po des 'dod
NK118(se)002:10164: na zhag bdun gyis kyang bla na med pa'i byang
NK118(se)002:10165: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya /
NK118(se)002:10167: de dag kyang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK118(se)002:10168: de la 'dod chen po'i sems bskyed pas ni grangs
NK118(se)002:10169: med sum cu rtsa gsum gyis 'khor ba las thar
NK118(se)002:10170: pa yin no // ye shes dam pa'i sems bskyed
NK118(se)002:10171: pas ni grangs med pa bdun gyis tshar phyin pa
NK118(se)002:10172: pa yin no // yin no // dpe med pa'i
NK118(se)002:10173: sems bskyed pas ni grangs med pa gsum gyis mngon
NK118(se)002:10174: par rdzogs pa byang chub pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:10180: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK118(se)002:10184: de ltar bshad zin nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:10185: byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi bslab bya bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10187: bstan bcos 'di la le'u lnga las /
NK118(se)002:10188: theg chen pha rol tu phyin pa dang thun mong
NK118(se)002:10189: pa'i bstan pa'i nyams len byang chub sems dpa'i sems
NK118(se)002:10190: bskyed kyi bslab bya srol gnyis kyi ring lugs ltar
NK118(se)002:10191: bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste le'u gsum pa'i
NK118(se)002:10193: nyes spyod rnyog bral rgya mtsho bsrubs las 'thon //
NK118(se)002:10194: legs spyod dge ba'i cha shas yongs su rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:10195: gzhan don spyod pa'i rgyu skar phreng bas mdzes //
NK118(se)002:10196: rgyal sras spyod mchog ston byed rmad byung gzhung //
NK118(se)002:10197: legs par 'grel pa'i ngag tshig kun+d+aa'i gnyen //
NK118(se)002:10198: lha dbang phyogs kyi sa 'dzin rtser 'dzegs nas //
NK118(se)002:10199: chos dkar bdud rtsi'i dpal 'dis 'gro kun gyi //
NK118(se)002:10200: srid zhi'i gdung sel bla na med gyur cig /
NK118(se)002:10201: na mo b+hat+t+aara ka sh+r+ai m+aam gu ra we /
NK118(se)002:10202: rang rig ye shes gzung 'dzin 'ching ba las //
NK118(se)002:10203: rnam par grol ba'i mi 'gyur mchog bde'i gar //
NK118(se)002:10204: grangs med rgyal ba'i 'khor lor bsgyur ba po //
NK118(se)002:10205: khyab bdag rdo rje slob dpon la btud nas //
NK118(se)002:10206: rnam dag lung gi nyi ma 'od po che //
NK118(se)002:10207: rnam dpyod rigs pa'i shing rta la chibs pa //
NK118(se)002:10208: rnam 'phrul man ngag rta bdun gyis drangs nas //
NK118(se)002:10209: rnam grol snang ba mchog gi dga' ston spro //
NK118(se)002:10210: gsum pa sngags kyi sdom pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:10211: ston pas gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde ji ltar gsungs tshul /
NK118(se)002:10212: de bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung tshul /
NK118(se)002:10213: de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10215: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang dbang ston pa des //
NK118(se)002:10216: 'og min chen por rgyud sde rgya mtsho gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10217: phyis nas 'bras spungs sogs su bzlas te bstan //
NK118(se)002:10219: bdag cag gi ston pa 'di nyid gzhi gdod ma'i
NK118(se)002:10220: dbyings su rig pa'i ye shes grol bas mngon par
NK118(se)002:10221: byang chub ste / sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK118(se)002:10222: med pa'i ngang la dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams
NK118(se)002:10223: cad dang dgongs pa ro cig tu bzhugs pa las
NK118(se)002:10224: byang chub ste / / rang snang shin tu rnam
NK118(se)002:10225: par dag pa rdo rje'i zhing khams 'og min chen
NK118(se)002:10226: byang chub ste / / por / ston pa longs
NK118(se)002:10227: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dpal kun tu bzang po rdo
NK118(se)002:10228: rje 'chang chen po nyid rgyal tshab zhi khro rigs
NK118(se)002:10229: lnga'i rnam pa dang bcas par snang bas /
NK118(se)002:10230: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i rang snang gi 'khor rgyal
NK118(se)002:10231: ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor tshad med pas yongs su
NK118(se)002:10233: chos ye shes 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa brjod du med pa nyid /
NK118(se)002:10234: dus gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dbyings su rang shar ba'i tshul gyis snang bar gyur to //
NK118(se)002:10235: de nyid kyi ngang las sa bcu rgyun mtha' la
NK118(se)002:10236: snang ba'i gzhan snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhing khams
NK118(se)002:10237: khyad par can gyi 'og min du ston pa rigs
NK118(se)002:10238: drug pa'i rnam pas 'khor sa matha'i byang chub sems
NK118(se)002:10239: dpa' rig pa 'dzin pa mchog rnams la /
NK118(se)002:10240: gsang sngags kyi rgyud dpag tu med pa dgongs pa
NK118(se)002:10241: brda'i gsung gis 'gro sgrol gyi bar du rgyun mi
NK118(se)002:10244: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK118(se)002:10245: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK118(se)002:10246: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK118(se)002:10247: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK118(se)002:10248: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK118(se)002:10250: de bzhin du byang sems sa dgu pa la snang ba'i 'og min tsam po dang /
NK118(se)002:10251: sa brgyad pa la snang ba'i btags pa'i 'og min
NK118(se)002:10252: rnams su'ang tshul de dang cha 'dra bas rgyud gsung
NK118(se)002:10253: zhing / de dag gi tshe drag po 'jigs byed
NK118(se)002:10254: sogs gdul bya gdug pa can rnams kyi don dpal
NK118(se)002:10255: he ru ka'i rnam par snang bas khro bo'i dkyil
NK118(se)002:10256: 'khor sprul bshad kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10257: zhing khams de rnams su bgrod par mi nus pa'i
NK118(se)002:10258: gdul bya dag pa rnams la bde ba can sogs
NK118(se)002:10259: rang bzhin sprul pa'i dag zhing rang dbang can rnams
NK118(se)002:10260: dang / gdul bya dag ma dag sna tshogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:10261: ngor 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i zhing rnams su dus gsum
NK118(se)002:10262: du gshegs bzhugs 'byon pa'i rdo rje 'chang gang 'dul
NK118(se)002:10263: zhi khro'i rol pa ma 'gags par snang bas dus
NK118(se)002:10264: dang tshad ma nges par gsungs pa ni dpag tu
NK118(se)002:10267: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK118(se)002:10268: so so 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK118(se)002:10269: de bzhin nyid las ma bcos kyang //
NK118(se)002:10270: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK118(se)002:10273: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10275: da ltar byung ba'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK118(se)002:10276: yang dang yang du gsung ba gang //
NK118(se)002:10278: de ltar thog ma med pa'i dus nas 'og min
NK118(se)002:10279: la sogs par bstan pa'i rgyud rnams phyis bzlas te
NK118(se)002:10282: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa zhing 'dir 'tshang rgya tshul
NK118(se)002:10283: bstan nas theg pa gsum bstan pa'i rjes su dpyid
NK118(se)002:10284: 'bring nag pa'i nya la dpal ldan 'bras spungs kyi
NK118(se)002:10285: mchod rten du / 'og tu chos dbyings gsung dbang
NK118(se)002:10286: dang steng du dpal ldan rgyu skar gyi dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:10287: sprul te 'dus pa'i 'khor la dbang bskur nas rnal
NK118(se)002:10288: 'byor dang rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud sde mtha' dag bstan
NK118(se)002:10289: mchod rten du / par bzhed de / dam pa dang po'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:10290: ston pas bya rgod phung po ru //
NK118(se)002:10291: shes rab pha rol phyin tshul bzhin //
NK118(se)002:10292: chos bstan dpal ldan 'bras spungs su //
NK118(se)002:10293: de bzhin gsang sngags tshul rab gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10295: yang snying po'i 'grel pa nyi 'od seng ges mdzad
NK118(se)002:10296: par rgyal bu don grub kyis btags pa'i lus dka'
NK118(se)002:10297: thub kyi gnas nee r+aany+dza na'i 'gram du bzhag nas
NK118(se)002:10298: / ye shes kyi lus 'og min du gshegs pa
NK118(se)002:10299: la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis mngon byang
NK118(se)002:10300: lngas byin gyis brlabs pas rdo rje dbyings chen por
NK118(se)002:10301: / sangs rgyas te / ri rab kyi rtse rdo rje nor bu'i khang pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10302: rgya mtsho'i 'gram du rim par byon nas yo ga'i rgyud rnams gsungs /
NK118(se)002:10303: de na o d+ai ya na dang sa ho ra'i
NK118(se)002:10304: yul du gshegs te in+d+ra b+h+au ti sogs la gsang
NK118(se)002:10305: ba'i rgyud sde thams cad bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:10306: slar btags pa'i lus la zhugs te rdo rje gdan du 'tshang rgya tshul bstan par bzhed cing /
NK118(se)002:10307: yang kha cig o t+y+aan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au
NK118(se)002:10308: tis ston pa'i nyan thos mkha' la 'phur te 'gro
NK118(se)002:10309: 'ong byed pa gzigs pa na thag ring bas cha
NK118(se)002:10310: ma phyed de / blon po la bya dmar po'i khyu 'di dag ci yin dris pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10313: sangs rgyas kyi nyan thos lags so byas pas /
NK118(se)002:10314: rgyal po sangs rgyas blta 'dod nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK118(se)002:10315: nangs par w+aa ra na s+ai nas bcom ldan 'khor
NK118(se)002:10316: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang bcas pa rdzu 'phrul
NK118(se)002:10317: gyis byon / der rgyal pos mchod nas 'tshang rgya ba'i thabs zhus pas /
NK118(se)002:10318: rab tu byung la bslab pa gsum rgyud la brten cig gsungs pas /
NK118(se)002:10319: dzam+bu'i tshal ni nyams dga' bar //
NK118(se)002:10320: wa skyes nyid du gyur kyang sla'i //
NK118(se)002:10321: 'dod yon spangs pa'i thar pa ni //
NK118(se)002:10322: nam yang mi 'dod goo ta ma //
NK118(se)002:10324: skad cig la nyan thos kyi tshogs rnams mi snang bar gyur te /
NK118(se)002:10325: 'di na gang zag brgyad med cing //
NK118(se)002:10326: nyan thos rang rgyal 'ga' yang med //
NK118(se)002:10327: byang chub sems dpa' rdzu 'phrul che //
NK118(se)002:10328: de dag de yi gzugs su sprul //
NK118(se)002:10329: zhes nam mkha' nas sgra 'byung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:10330: der ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor sprul nas rgyal po la dbang bskur bas /
NK118(se)002:10331: de nyid du zung 'jug gi sku 'grub ste /
NK118(se)002:10332: de la ston pas rgyud thams cad gtad par bzhed do //
NK118(se)002:10333: gzhan yang ri bo bya rkang can dang /
NK118(se)002:10335: lang+ka'i bdag po sgra sgrogs kyi gnas la sogs par
NK118(se)002:10336: ston pa nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po'i rnam par
NK118(se)002:10337: bsgyur ba'am / ma bsgyur ba chags bral gyi rnam
NK118(se)002:10338: pa ci rigs pas rgyud sde mang du gsungs so
NK118(se)002:10339: bsgyur ba'am / // des na rgyud gzhung gcig la'ang
NK118(se)002:10340: gdul bya'i snang bas gleng gzhi tha dad pa 'byung
NK118(se)002:10342: 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:10343: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK118(se)002:10344: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK118(se)002:10346: byang chub sems dang lha rnams dang //
NK118(se)002:10347: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10348: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK118(se)002:10349: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK118(se)002:10350: sprul sku 'khor los sgyur ba dang //
NK118(se)002:10351: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10352: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i tshe //
NK118(se)002:10356: phyag rdor dang ni zhu ba'i 'khor gyis bsdus //
NK118(se)002:10357: grub chen brgyad sogs rgya bod mkhas pas bkral //
NK118(se)002:10358: snga 'gyur ring lugs bka' gter grags pa dang //
NK118(se)002:10359: gsar ma'i bzhed srol dpag tu med na yang //
NK118(se)002:10360: rgyud sde spyi yi dam tshig 'dir 'chad do //
NK118(se)002:10362: spyir gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud rnams phyag na rdo rjes bsdus te /
NK118(se)002:10367: kla klo'i skad la sogs pa skad rigs dang yig
NK118(se)002:10368: rigs sna tshogs pas glegs bam la bkod par bshad
NK118(se)002:10369: de / ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:10370: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su gsang ba'i rgyud skal pa
NK118(se)002:10371: dang ldan pa'i sems can la sus 'chad par byed
NK118(se)002:10373: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad par byed do //
NK118(se)002:10375: in+d+ra b+h+au tis mdzad pa'i bde mchog rtsa rgyud kyi 'grel pa las /
NK118(se)002:10376: phyi dus rim par lung bstan sdud pa pos //
NK118(se)002:10377: ri bo mchog rab byang shar lha gnas mchog /
NK118(se)002:10378: lcang lo can gyi pho brang chen por ni //
NK118(se)002:10379: rgyud rnams ma lus sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs //
NK118(se)002:10380: bye ba phrag ni dgu bcu rtsa drug sogs //
NK118(se)002:10381: 'dus te rje btsun gsang ba'i bdag po la //
NK118(se)002:10382: gsol ba btab tshe 'di skad bdag thos zhes //
NK118(se)002:10383: rab tu gsungs pa gser gyi glegs bu la //
NK118(se)002:10384: beed+aur+ya yi zhun mas yi ger bkod //
NK118(se)002:10386: khyad par rgyud kyi zhu ba po gang yin dang /
NK118(se)002:10387: mjug tu gang la gtad pa de nyid sdud pa po yin pa shas che ste /
NK118(se)002:10388: rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa lta bu gang la gtad pa des bsdus par rgya mtsho las /
NK118(se)002:10389: 'khor gyi nang na skal mchog ldan //
NK118(se)002:10390: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /
NK118(se)002:10391: lag na rdo rjes bsdu bar mdzad //
NK118(se)002:10394: dus 'khor rtsa rgyud zla ba bzang pos /
NK118(se)002:10395: brtag gnyis rdo rje snying pos /
NK118(se)002:10397: rdo rje mkha' 'gro phag mos bsdus pa ltar ro //
NK118(se)002:10398: de ltar ston pa po dang sdud pa po tha dad du bstan kyang /
NK118(se)002:10399: nges pa'i don la ston 'khor rgyud tha dad du gyur pa ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:10400: bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:10401: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste //
NK118(se)002:10402: 'chad dang nyam pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NK118(se)002:10405: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje //
NK118(se)002:10406: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de //
NK118(se)002:10408: gal te mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po las /
NK118(se)002:10409: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum po dag /
NK118(se)002:10410: bcom ldan nges par gsungs lags na //
NK118(se)002:10411: rgyu 'bras lhun grub tu spyod cing //
NK118(se)002:10412: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK118(se)002:10413: nges pa'i theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NK118(se)002:10415: rgyu la mos pa rgyu chos kyi //
NK118(se)002:10416: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas na //
NK118(se)002:10417: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK118(se)002:10419: zhes pas rgyu'i theg pa'i sde snod gsum ston pas dngos su zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK118(se)002:10420: 'bras bu'i theg pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod
NK118(se)002:10421: rjes su gnang ba'i bka'o zhes mkhas pa dag gsung
NK118(se)002:10422: yang / dang po la shes rab snying po'i mdo lta bus ma nges /
NK118(se)002:10423: phyi ma la mtshan brjod du /
NK118(se)002:10424: de nas bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK118(se)002:10425: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rkang gnyis mchog /
NK118(se)002:10426: nyid kyi zhal nas ljags bzang ba //
NK118(se)002:10427: zhes sogs kyis ma nges rang lugs gdul bya dbang
NK118(se)002:10428: rnon skal ba mchog tu gyur pa rnams la thub
NK118(se)002:10429: pa'i dbang pos mi'i 'jig rten du'ang rgyud mang du
NK118(se)002:10430: gsung mod / de lta na'ang 'dir ma gsungs pa ltar bshad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:10431: re zhig gsang sngags kyi sgra mi'i 'jig rten du phal la ma grags pa'i dbang du mdzad cing /
NK118(se)002:10432: phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa ni yongs su grags pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10433: 'o na lha mi'i 'jig rten du ji ltar grags tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:10434: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:10439: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK118(se)002:10440: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK118(se)002:10441: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yin //
NK118(se)002:10442: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK118(se)002:10443: mi las skal ldan rigs can de //
NK118(se)002:10444: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK118(se)002:10445: sngon du bltas snang snang 'gyur te //
NK118(se)002:10446: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK118(se)002:10447: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK118(se)002:10448: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK118(se)002:10449: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:10450: zhes pa ltar thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK118(se)002:10451: dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga lang+ka'i yul gyi
NK118(se)002:10452: ri bo ma la ya'i rtser rang rang gi mngon
NK118(se)002:10454: gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pas gsang bdag
NK118(se)002:10455: mngon sum du byon nas rigs can lnga sogs rig
NK118(se)002:10456: 'dzin 'dus pa phal mo che la sngon 'og min
NK118(se)002:10458: sum cu rtsa gsum rnams su grags pa'i gsang ba'i theg pa nyid ston par mdzad cing /
NK118(se)002:10459: de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis gser
NK118(se)002:10460: gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya'i zhun mas bris nas
NK118(se)002:10461: dgongs pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la sbas so
NK118(se)002:10462: // de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i
NK118(se)002:10463: rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis
NK118(se)002:10464: pa la brten nas sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK118(se)002:10465: rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyud de'i glegs bam rnams mi yul du dngos su babs te /
NK118(se)002:10466: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa ra n+aa s+ai /
NK118(se)002:10467: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor /
NK118(se)002:10468: ma h+aa yo ga rnams sa hor gyi yul rgyal po dza'i khang steng /
NK118(se)002:10469: a nu yo ga rnams lang+ka'i yul du grags pa
NK118(se)002:10470: sing+ga la'i gling gi nags tshal du glegs bam dang
NK118(se)002:10471: bcas babs shing / a ti yo ga rnams ni
NK118(se)002:10472: nub phyogs o d+ai ya na'i yul du slob dpon
NK118(se)002:10473: chen po dga' rab rdo rjes dpal rdo rje sems
NK118(se)002:10474: dapa'am phyag na rdo rje la dngos su gsan pa
NK118(se)002:10475: ltar bsdu bar mdzad de glegs bam la bkod par
NK118(se)002:10476: bcas babs shing / bshad do // sgrub sde ni /
NK118(se)002:10477: sngon 'og min gsang ba mchog gi gnas su ston
NK118(se)002:10478: pa kun bzang che mchog he ru kas chos nyid
NK118(se)002:10479: kyi rang sgras gsungs pa'i rgyud rnams gsang bdag rdo
NK118(se)002:10480: rje chos kyis rang nyid tshom bu dgu'i dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:10481: gyi nang du snang bar mdzad nas thog mar ngag
NK118(se)002:10482: tu bsdus / de nas glegs bam la bkod de
NK118(se)002:10483: dgongs 'grel du lung lnga yang mdzad nas mkha' 'gro
NK118(se)002:10484: ma las kyi dbang mo che la gtad /
NK118(se)002:10485: des spyi dang bye brag gi rgyud rnams phye nas
NK118(se)002:10486: rin po che'i sgrom so sor bcug ste mchod rten
NK118(se)002:10487: bde byed brtsegs par gter du sbas pa /
NK118(se)002:10488: nam zhig gi tshe grub pa thob pa'i slob dpon brgyad kyis gter bsrung rnams la bka' bsgos pas /
NK118(se)002:10489: mkha' 'gro mas bka' bye brag gi sgrom bu brgyad po bka' babs kyi slob dpon brgyad la gtad /
NK118(se)002:10490: spyi rgyud kyi sgrom bu rin po che sna brgyad
NK118(se)002:10491: las byas pa rgya ma 'khrol bas slar de nyid
NK118(se)002:10492: du sbas / phyis kun 'dus rig 'dzin slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha bas spyan drangs te /
NK118(se)002:10493: rje 'bangs snying gi bu dagu'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la legs par gdams so //
NK118(se)002:10494: gsang sngags gsar ma'i grags tshod ltar na /
NK118(se)002:10495: o t+y+aan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au tis rgyud rnams glegs bam du byas shing /
NK118(se)002:10496: skye bo rnams la bstan pas yul de'i srog chags
NK118(se)002:10497: phra mo man chad thams cad kyis dngos grub thob
NK118(se)002:10499: de nas o t+y+aan gyi yul stongs pa mtshor gyur
NK118(se)002:10500: te klus gang ba la gsang bdag gis rgyud sde
NK118(se)002:10501: rnams gtad cing smin par mdzad pas /
NK118(se)002:10502: de dag rim gyis mir gyur nas mtsho 'gram du
NK118(se)002:10503: grong bcas te nyams su blangs pas grub pa thob
NK118(se)002:10504: / de rnams kyi bu dang bu mo rnams mkha'
NK118(se)002:10505: 'gro dang mkha' 'gro mar gyur pas o t+y+aan mkha'
NK118(se)002:10507: mtsho de yang skams te he ru ka'i lha khang rang byung zhig kyang byung bas /
NK118(se)002:10508: de'i dkor mdzod du rgyud kyi glegs bam rnams bzhugs pa las /
NK118(se)002:10509: phyis rgyal po ba su kalpa dang /
NK118(se)002:10511: ku ku ri pa sogs grub thob rnams kyis rgyud shas che ba zhig de nas blangs /
NK118(se)002:10512: de bzhin du sham+b+ha la sogs yul gzhan dag nas
NK118(se)002:10513: kyang blangs te rim gyis dar ro zhes 'dod do
NK118(se)002:10514: // de la gsar rnying gi khyad par ni /
NK118(se)002:10515: rgya gar na so sor phye ba med na'ang bod 'dir 'gyur snga phyis grags pa ste /
NK118(se)002:10516: sngon gyi pan+di ta sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:10518: o t+y+aan gyi slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK118(se)002:10519: pan chen bi ma la mi tra la sogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10520: lo ts+aa ba bee ro tsa na rma gnyags ska
NK118(se)002:10521: cog zhang gsum sogs kyis bsgyur ba nas bzung pan+di
NK118(se)002:10522: ta smri ti byon pa yan chad la bsgyur ba'i
NK118(se)002:10523: mdo rgyud dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa thams cad la
NK118(se)002:10524: rnying ma'am snga 'gyur zhes bya la /
NK118(se)002:10525: lo chen rin chen bzang po'i 'gyur 'go tshugs pa
NK118(se)002:10526: nas bzung lo che chung mar mal 'gos 'brog ra
NK118(se)002:10527: 'bro sogs kyis rgya bal gyi pan+di ta ci rigs
NK118(se)002:10528: spyan drangs te bsgyur ba rnams la gsar ma'am phyi
NK118(se)002:10530: 'gyur 'di gnyis la go dka' sla dang dbyings 'jal ba la rlabs che chung 'byung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:10531: sngon gyi lo pan rnams sangs rgyas byang sems kyi
NK118(se)002:10532: rnam 'phrul sha stag yin pas don ji lta ba
NK118(se)002:10533: bzhin du gtan la phab nas bsgyur bas tshig go
NK118(se)002:10534: sla zhing dbyings 'jal ba la rlabs che /
NK118(se)002:10535: phyis 'gyur gyi lo ts+aa ba dus der bod du
NK118(se)002:10536: grags chung ba'i chos re la 'dod pa'i dmigs btsugs
NK118(se)002:10537: te rgya bal thengs 'ga' re bskor nas sbyangs pa'i
NK118(se)002:10538: mkhas pa rnams kyis don ji lta ba bzhin du
NK118(se)002:10539: ma lhongs te sgra 'gyur gtso bor bton pas tshig
NK118(se)002:10540: sgrim zhing go dka' dbyings 'jal ba la rlabs chung
NK118(se)002:10541: ba ltar snang ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:10542: dper na gsang ba snying po'i rgyud rma gnyags kyi
NK118(se)002:10543: 'gyur dang thar lo'i 'gyur la bltas pas 'gyur snga
NK118(se)002:10544: phyi'i khyad par shes par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:10545: der ma zad snga 'gyur ni sngon 'phags yul du
NK118(se)002:10546: bstan pa grwa ma nyams pa'i dus su bsgyur bas
NK118(se)002:10547: thar lo'i gsar 'gyur bcu gsum tsam ma gtogs mdo
NK118(se)002:10548: thams cad dang bya rgyud shas che ba'i phyi rgyud
NK118(se)002:10549: dang 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa gsang 'dus mnyam sbyor sogs
NK118(se)002:10550: gsar ma dang thun mong pa'i rgyud kyang mang du
NK118(se)002:10551: 'gyur la / rgyud sde'i byung tshul gyi babs kyang mi 'dra ba med par gcig tu 'bab cing /
NK118(se)002:10552: phyis kyi lo pan rnams kyi spyod yul du ma gyur pa'i lung a nu /
NK118(se)002:10554: sgrub sde dang bcas pa'i rgyud mtha' yas pa zhig
NK118(se)002:10555: kyang gangs ljongs kyi gdul bya'i dpal du byon la
NK118(se)002:10556: / phyi 'gyur rnams ni phyis rgya gar du'ang dar
NK118(se)002:10557: nub ci rigs byung bas slad kyis yul tha dad
NK118(se)002:10558: nas grub thob 'ga' res dpe gsar du blangs te
NK118(se)002:10559: spyad pas lo rgyus mi mthun pa sna tshogs dang
NK118(se)002:10560: chos kyang bya spyod ci rigs las gtso bor rnal
NK118(se)002:10561: 'byor phyi nang thun mong ba tsam du snang ngo
NK118(se)002:10562: / // yang rnying ma bka' gter gyi khyad par ni /
NK118(se)002:10564: phyi rgyud sde gsum ka slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang
NK118(se)002:10565: ba'i lugs gtso che zhing sngon bshad sgrub kyi srol
NK118(se)002:10566: shin tu dar bar byung ngo //
NK118(se)002:10567: rnal 'byor nang pa la gsum gyi /
NK118(se)002:10568: ma h+aa yo ga las thun mong ma yin pa sgyu d+r+wa'i bskor rnams /
NK118(se)002:10569: rgyal po dzahns sras mo go ma de w+ai'i bar
NK118(se)002:10570: spyod pa'i nye rgyus rang rang gi tshom bu dang
NK118(se)002:10571: bcas pa rdo rje 'chang gi sar gshegs nas /
NK118(se)002:10572: sras mo'i slob ma sangs rgyas gsang bas bi ma la mi tra la bshad /
NK118(se)002:10573: de la lo tsa ba rma gnyags kyis gsan nas rim par gnubs dang zur la babs so //
NK118(se)002:10574: lung a nu yo ga rnams ni gnubs chen sangs
NK118(se)002:10575: rgyas ye shes kyis rgya bal gru sha'i yul gyi
NK118(se)002:10576: lo pan rnams la gsan pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:10577: a ti yo ga rnams ni /
NK118(se)002:10578: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rjes rjes su bzung ba 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin /
NK118(se)002:10580: de'i slob ma o t+y+aan sangs rgyas gnyis pa /
NK118(se)002:10582: lo chen bee ro tsa na gsum las rgya cher 'phel lo //
NK118(se)002:10583: de thams cad kyang spyi mdo las /
NK118(se)002:10584: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor dag /
NK118(se)002:10585: dgongs rig rna bar brgyud pa ste //
NK118(se)002:10586: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK118(se)002:10587: zhes pa ltar brgyud pa'i babs lugs gsum du bsdus nas 'chad do //
NK118(se)002:10590: shin tu zab pa'i mthar thug snying po rnams //
NK118(se)002:10591: spyir yang bod rnams gsar ngas che ba dang //
NK118(se)002:10592: snyigs ma'i 'gro la lhag par snying rje bas //
NK118(se)002:10593: mtha' dbus thams cad gter gyis bkang nas gzhag /
NK118(se)002:10594: las can bu dang 'phrad pa'i smon lam btab //
NK118(se)002:10595: zhes pa ltar ma 'ongs pa'i skal ldan rnams kyi
NK118(se)002:10596: don du bla rdzogs thugs gsum dang sgrub sde brgyad
NK118(se)002:10597: spyi bye brag gi zab chos rnams gter gnas so
NK118(se)002:10598: sor gter bsrung la gnyer gtad de sbas pa lo
NK118(se)002:10599: pan rje 'bangs sa chen po la bzhugs pa rnams
NK118(se)002:10600: dbang 'byor ba'i gang 'dul sprul pa'i skur bstan pas
NK118(se)002:10601: rim par spyan drangs te dus babs kyis 'gro don
NK118(se)002:10602: mdzad cing / brgyud pa'i babs lugs sngar ltar gsum gyi steng du /
NK118(se)002:10605: mkha' 'gro gtad bya ste gsum bsnan pas brgyud pa drug ldan gyi tha snyad 'byung yin no //
NK118(se)002:10606: de la spyir rgyud sde rnams dbang thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK118(se)002:10609: 'dzam bu gling gi gdod nas grub pa'i dur khrod
NK118(se)002:10610: brgyad du grub pa thob pa'i gdod nas grub pa'i
NK118(se)002:10611: lha'i slob dpon brgyad sogs kyis bzung nas gnas so
NK118(se)002:10613: de dag las mi'i 'gro ba'i bsod nams su cha
NK118(se)002:10614: shas tsam snang ba la rig 'dzin gyi sa mchog
NK118(se)002:10615: brnyes pa'i grub chen brgyad dang grub thob brgyad cu
NK118(se)002:10616: sogs rgya bod kyi mkhas grub du mas don la
NK118(se)002:10617: brton pa'i dgongs 'grel gyis legs par bkral zhing bshad
NK118(se)002:10618: sgrub kyis ji ltar bskyangs tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:10619: bye brag gsar rnying gi bzhed srol kyang mtha' yas pa zhig 'chad du yod na'ang /
NK118(se)002:10620: 'dir skabs don rgyud sde spyi'i dam tshig nyid bshad bya'i gtso bor snang bas /
NK118(se)002:10621: de dag gi rnam dbye ha cang mang na gtso
NK118(se)002:10622: bo'i don la sgrib cing yi ges kyang 'jogs pas
NK118(se)002:10623: de tsam mo // de ltar rdo rje theg pa'i chos sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa las /
NK118(se)002:10624: rang gi skal bas ji tsam zhig thob pa ni /
NK118(se)002:10625: bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum dang yang phur gshin
NK118(se)002:10626: rje gshed kyi bskor so so'i nang gses tha dad
NK118(se)002:10627: pa rnams kyi dbang lung man ngag bshad srol dang
NK118(se)002:10628: bcas pa ding sang rgyun yod do cog lta bu
NK118(se)002:10629: dang / gter ma bla rdzogs thugs gsum sgrub sde
NK118(se)002:10630: brgyad spyi bye brag gi dbang lung man ngag rgyun
NK118(se)002:10631: bzhugs pa phal mo che dang /
NK118(se)002:10632: de thams cad kyi rtsa ba rgyud 'bum dang bcas te /
NK118(se)002:10633: rnying ma bka' gter gyi chos tshul zab rgyas rgya mtsho lta bu rnams ni /
NK118(se)002:10634: rje bla ma dam pa bka' drin mtshungs pa med
NK118(se)002:10635: pa gter chen chos kyi rgyal po 'gro 'dul gter
NK118(se)002:10636: bdag gling pa mchog gi zhabs pad dad pa'i spyi
NK118(se)002:10637: bos rtag tu bsten pa'i bka' drin kho na las
NK118(se)002:10639: gsar ma ni rje bla ma dam pa las kyang mang zhig thob mod /
NK118(se)002:10640: gzhan du na bstan pa'i rtsa lag rig 'dzin mchog gi sprul pa'i sku kun bzang pad+ma phrin las /
NK118(se)002:10641: mkhas grub chos skyong rgyal mtshan /
NK118(se)002:10642: ding ri kun spangs pa blo gros brtan pa /
NK118(se)002:10643: grub pa'i dbang phyug blo gros rgya mtsho /
NK118(se)002:10644: yongs kyi bshes gnyen ngag dbang bstan 'dzin /
NK118(se)002:10645: kun dga' bstan pa dar rgyas sogs las dbang rjes
NK118(se)002:10646: gnang lung man ngag dang bcas pa mang du nos
NK118(se)002:10647: so // gsum pa de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa la bdun te /
NK118(se)002:10650: ma thob pa thob par byed pa /
NK118(se)002:10651: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba /
NK118(se)002:10656: ngo bo sgo gsum thabs shes kyis zin par //
NK118(se)002:10657: bsdams pa'i tshul khrims so so'i ring lugs bzhin //
NK118(se)002:10659: sngags sdom gyi ngo bo la /
NK118(se)002:10661: sdom byed thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyis /
NK118(se)002:10662: bsdam bya sgo gsum phra ba'i bag chags dang mtshan
NK118(se)002:10663: 'dzin gyi rtog pa sdom par byed pa'i sems pa
NK118(se)002:10664: sa bon dang bcas pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:10665: rang rgyu dbang bskur ba las gsar du thob pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK118(se)002:10668: thabs ni bde ba'i sdom pa ste //
NK118(se)002:10670: de la rgyud sde bzhi so so'i lugs ltar dbye na gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:10671: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum gyi dang /
NK118(se)002:10676: rnal 'byor rgyud gsum gyi sdom pa'i mtshan nyid rim bzhin /
NK118(se)002:10679: lag bcangs kyi bde ba gang rung lam du byas
NK118(se)002:10680: pa'i sgo nas chags pa de dang de dag par
NK118(se)002:10681: byed pa'i ye shes rang rgyud la 'dzin pa'i thabs
NK118(se)002:10682: shes khyad par can gyis sgo gsum gyi bag chags
NK118(se)002:10683: dang mtshan rtogs sdom par byed pa'i sems pa sa
NK118(se)002:10684: bon dang bcas pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:10685: rang rgyu rgyud sde rang la ltos pa'i dbang las thob pa'i tshul khrims /
NK118(se)002:10686: khyad par bla med kyi sngags sdom la /
NK118(se)002:10687: dbang po gnyis sbyor gyi bde ba lam du byas
NK118(se)002:10688: pa'i sgo nas chags pa de dag par byed pa'i
