NK118(se)002:10689: sogs gang zhig rang rgyud bla med kyi dbang las
NK118(se)002:10692: bum dbang las thob pa'i dang /
NK118(se)002:10693: dbang gong ma las thob pa'i sdom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10695: sbyor ba'i dus su rigs lnga spyi dang bye brag gi dam tshig khas blangs shing /
NK118(se)002:10696: dngos gzhi'i dus su bum dbang 'khor bcas bskur ba las gsar thob kyi tshul khrims gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:10697: thabs shes khyad par can bskyed rim gyis tha mal
NK118(se)002:10698: snang zhen gyi mtshan rtog sdom par byed pa'i sems
NK118(se)002:10700: btags pa ba brjod pa khas blangs kyis dang /
NK118(se)002:10701: mtshan nyid pa bsgom bya dbang la sa thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10703: rang thob byed kyi rgyu dbang gong ma gang rung
NK118(se)002:10704: bskur ba la brten nas mngon du gyur pa gya
NK118(se)002:10705: nom lhar zhen gyi mtshan rtog las skyob pa'i tshul
NK118(se)002:10706: khrims gang zhig / thabs shes khyad par can rang
NK118(se)002:10707: byin brlabs pas sems gsal stong gi ngo bor sdom
NK118(se)002:10708: pa'i sems pa gsang dbang gi /
NK118(se)002:10710: thabs shes khyad par can kun rdzob zhu bdes mtshon
NK118(se)002:10711: byed dpe'i ye shes bde stong gi ngo bor sdom
NK118(se)002:10712: pa'i sems pa sher dbang gi /
NK118(se)002:10714: thabs shes khyad par can 'pho med bde chen gyis
NK118(se)002:10715: zung 'jug lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mtshon bya
NK118(se)002:10716: don dam pa'i ngo bor sdom pa dbang bzhi pa'i
NK118(se)002:10718: de bas na dgyes rdor las /
NK118(se)002:10719: sangs rgyas kun gyi sdom pa ni //
NK118(se)002:10720: e wam rnam par rab tu gnas //
NK118(se)002:10721: e wam rnam pa'i bde chen po //
NK118(se)002:10722: dbang las yang dag shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:10723: zhes e wam gyis mtshon pa'i rnam kun mchog ldan
NK118(se)002:10724: gyi stong gzugs phyag rgya chen mos zhu bde drangs
NK118(se)002:10725: pas / 'dod chags chen po'i theg le'i 'gros las
NK118(se)002:10726: shar ba'i lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba stong gzugs
NK118(se)002:10727: dang ngo bo gcig tu gyur pa ni zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:10728: gi ye shes mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po
NK118(se)002:10729: zhes sangs rgyas kun gyi sdom pa ste /
NK118(se)002:10730: des spang bya 'dzag bde 'pho ba'i bag chags dang
NK118(se)002:10731: mtshan rtog las yid bde myur gyi sgo nas skyob
NK118(se)002:10732: pa'i phyir na / dbang bzhi pa'i sdom pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:10733: bum gsang sher dbang gsum yang mtshan rtog las yid
NK118(se)002:10734: skyob par byed pa'i bde chen gyi ye shes de
NK118(se)002:10735: 'dren byed kyi thabs ring ba dang nye ba dang
NK118(se)002:10736: shin tu nye ba gsum du rim par 'gyur ba
NK118(se)002:10737: yin no // 'o na lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK118(se)002:10738: shes de gdod ma nas lus can thams cad la
NK118(se)002:10739: gnas pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK118(se)002:10741: 'on kyang rang gnas kyi ye shes de ngos zin
NK118(se)002:10742: pa dang 'chal tshul gyi gnyen por 'gro ba dbang
NK118(se)002:10743: gong ma la ltos dgos te /
NK118(se)002:10745: gzhan gyis brjod min lhan cig skyes //
NK118(se)002:10746: gang du yang ni mi rnyed de //
NK118(se)002:10747: bla ma'i dus thabs bstan pa dang //
NK118(se)002:10748: bdag gi bsod nams las rig bya //
NK118(se)002:10750: yang sbyor ba'i dus rigs lnga'i sdom bzung lan gsum
NK118(se)002:10751: bzlas pa'i brjod pa gsum pa'i cha tha ma la
NK118(se)002:10752: gang bzung ba'i sdom pa de nyid thob bam mi
NK118(se)002:10753: thob ce na / dngos gtags ma phye ba'i dbang du byas na thob ste /
NK118(se)002:10755: sdom pa gsum la legs bkod nas //
NK118(se)002:10756: de la dkyil 'khor bstan par bya //
NK118(se)002:10758: rong zom chen pos mdzad pa'i sdom chog las kyang /
NK118(se)002:10759: thun mong pa'i sdom pa nos nas /
NK118(se)002:10760: de nas khyad par kyi sdom pa nos te /
NK118(se)002:10761: dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dbang thob par byas la /
NK118(se)002:10762: dngos grub kyi snod du gyur bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10765: so byang gi sdom chog las kyang de dang de'i sdom pa mi skye bar mtshungs te /
NK118(se)002:10766: de dang de la skye ba'i nus pa yod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10767: 'di la med pa'i lung rigs tshad ma med pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:10768: gzhan du na rgyal bas sdom chog gsungs pa'ang don med du thal lo //
NK118(se)002:10770: dbang ma thob par rigs lnga'i sdom pa bzung ba tsam gyis sngags sdom thob na /
NK118(se)002:10771: gang zag de 'dra de chos can /
NK118(se)002:10772: khyod la slob dpon smad pa la sogs pa'i rtsa ltung 'byung ba srid par thal /
NK118(se)002:10773: sngags sdom rgyud ldan gyi gang zag yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:10775: 'grel chen dri med 'od kyi rtsa ltung ston pa'i skabs las /
NK118(se)002:10776: gang dag rdo rje theg par gnas pa rnams la ste /
NK118(se)002:10778: zhes pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i nges pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10779: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zer na /
NK118(se)002:10781: smon pa sems bskyed kyi sdom pa thob pa de byang sdom rgyud ldan tsam yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:10782: de 'dra des smon sems ma btang na rgyal po
NK118(se)002:10783: la nges pa lta bu'i rtsa ltung bcu bzhi gang
NK118(se)002:10784: rung la spyad kyang smon sdom mi gtong ba bzhin
NK118(se)002:10785: no // des na rigs lnga'i sdom bzung gi skabs
NK118(se)002:10786: su dam tshig la gnas par smon pa tsam yin
NK118(se)002:10787: no // pas / dngos gzhi la ltos nas bsrung
NK118(se)002:10788: bar dbang ba'i dam tshig rnams rigs nges pa khas
NK118(se)002:10790: sngags sdom btags pa ba yin la /
NK118(se)002:10791: slar dbang bskur bas ye shes khong chud kyis thob pa ni sngags sdom mtshan nyid pa'o //
NK118(se)002:10792: de yang dbang bskur bas rang gnas kyi ye shes
NK118(se)002:10793: gsos thebs nas nus pa mthu can du gyur pa
NK118(se)002:10794: des gnyen po'i phyogs bzung nas /
NK118(se)002:10795: rang dang lhan cig gnas pa'i sbyang bya dang nus
NK118(se)002:10796: pa 'gran pa'i tshul gyis sun 'byin par byed la
NK118(se)002:10797: / gal te dbang dus su ye shes dngos su
NK118(se)002:10798: ma skyes kyang skye rung gi nus pa bzhag pa
NK118(se)002:10799: des dri ma sbyong ba dang yon tan skye ba'i
NK118(se)002:10800: 'go rtsom pa yin pas rgyud 'gyur ba'i khyad par
NK118(se)002:10801: / te / de la rgyud smin pa /
NK118(se)002:10803: dam tshig dang sdom pa thob pa zhes pa'i tha snyad thob cing /
NK118(se)002:10804: cho gas sems rgyud kyi yon tan dge ba'i sa
NK118(se)002:10805: bon gsos btab pa'i cha de sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK118(se)002:10806: gsang ba'i rdo rje gsum 'dzin pa'i cha nas dam
NK118(se)002:10808: rang rgyud sdom pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:10809: dper na bum pa nyid byas pa'ang yin la mi rtag pa'ang yin pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:10810: de ltar yang gsang snying gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK118(se)002:10811: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK118(se)002:10812: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK118(se)002:10813: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK118(se)002:10816: de ltar sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK118(se)002:10817: bdag gi rdo rje mchog gsum pos //
NK118(se)002:10818: log par mi gtong sdom pa'i dngos //
NK118(se)002:10819: sa gzhi lta bur gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:10821: yang sgyu 'phrul zhi khro lta bu'i dbang thob la ma nyams pa'i gang zag gis /
NK118(se)002:10822: slar de nyid dam sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor lta bu'i
NK118(se)002:10823: dbang thob pa'i tshe sngags sdom gsar thob yod dam
NK118(se)002:10824: med ce na / gsar thob kyi cha ni yod de /
NK118(se)002:10825: de 'dra de la bla mas dbang bskur ram /
NK118(se)002:10826: sdom ldan rang nyid kyis dbang blangs kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:10827: sngar rgyud la yod pa'i sngags sdom gyi rgyun de
NK118(se)002:10828: nyid phyis dbang bskur re re thob pa'i tshe gong
NK118(se)002:10830: ji tsam 'phel ba'i cha de gsar thob yin mod /
NK118(se)002:10831: 'on kyang thob bya dbang gi ngo bo rigs mthun
NK118(se)002:10832: phyin chad sdom pa rigs mi 'dra ba dang ngo
NK118(se)002:10833: bo tha dad du 'jug pa'ang med pas sdom pa
NK118(se)002:10834: dngos gzhi gsar thob med pa'i phyir dbang dang po
NK118(se)002:10835: de la smin byed kyi dbang zhes sngags sdom gsar
NK118(se)002:10836: du thob byed kyi dbang yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:10837: phyi ma rnams la'ang rang skal gyis smin par byas
NK118(se)002:10838: pa'i cha re yod kyang smin byed dang sdom pa
NK118(se)002:10839: gsar thob kyi tha snyad mi sbyor te /
NK118(se)002:10840: smin tshul de tsam zhig sangs rgyas ma thob pa'i bar du 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:10841: spyir gzhi lam 'bras gsum la ltos nas kyang sngags sdom gsum du bshad de /
NK118(se)002:10842: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK118(se)002:10843: ye shes kyi ngo bor sdom pa ni gzhi rgyud
NK118(se)002:10846: chos kun ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:10847: log rtog ye nas rnam par dag /
NK118(se)002:10848: de bas sdom pa rnam par dag /
NK118(se)002:10851: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes zhes brjod //
NK118(se)002:10852: rnam pa thams cad sdom pa gcig /
NK118(se)002:10854: de nyid rtogs pa'i thabs khyad par can smin grol
NK118(se)002:10855: gyi lam gyis mtshan rtog sdom par byed pa lam
NK118(se)002:10858: thabs ni bde ba'i sdom pa ste //
NK118(se)002:10860: chos thams cad rang snang gi ye shes kyi ngo bor sdom pa 'bras rgyud kyi sngags sdom ste /
NK118(se)002:10861: de nas chos kun sdom gcig pa'i //
NK118(se)002:10862: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes byar bshad //
NK118(se)002:10864: de ltar gsum gyi dang po btags pa ba dang /
NK118(se)002:10865: phyi ma gnyis mtshan nyid par bzhed de /
NK118(se)002:10867: gnyis pa dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:10868: rgyud sde bzhi'i lugs spyir dbye ba dang /
NK118(se)002:10869: bla med kyi lugs bye brag tu dbye ba'o //
NK118(se)002:10871: dbye ba bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med bzhir //
NK118(se)002:10872: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi so sor grangs nges par //
NK118(se)002:10873: dus kyi 'khor lor bshad pa gzhan du blta //
NK118(se)002:10876: bya spyod gnyis su rtsa ltung ma bshad pas byang
NK118(se)002:10877: sems kyi smon 'jug bslab bya las gzhan pa'i bsrung
NK118(se)002:10881: lnga po 'di ni rtsa ba'i ltung ba yin par bstan te /
NK118(se)002:10882: zhes rtsa ltung lnga bshad pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10884: ltung ba rtsa ba bzhi ni srog gi phyir yang yongs su nyams par mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10885: zhes rgyas par bshad pa rnams kyang byang sems kyi rtsa ltung yin par 'gyur la /
NK118(se)002:10886: de yin na byang sems kyi ltung ba'i grangs nges kyang nyams pa dang /
NK118(se)002:10887: bya spyod gnyis su rtsa ltung med na yan lag gi ltung ba'ang 'byung mi rigs la /
NK118(se)002:10889: mngon byang dang legs grub las sngags kyi 'dul ba gsungs pa dang yang 'gal bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:10890: der ma zad bya spyod gnyis kyi dbang bskur ba
NK118(se)002:10891: la brten nas de dang de'i sngags sdom thob pa
NK118(se)002:10894: rgyud sde gong ma gnyis la'ang sngags sdom skye ba'i nus pa med par 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:10895: de dang de'i dbang la sngags sdom skye ba'i nus pa yod med 'gro ldog mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:10896: des na dus 'khor 'grel chen las rgyud sde bzhi
NK118(se)002:10897: ka yang rtsa ltung bcu bzhi pa can du grangs
NK118(se)002:10898: 'dra bar gsungs pa ltar bshad par bya ba yin
NK118(se)002:10900: bya rgyud kyi rtsa ltung ni /
NK118(se)002:10902: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK118(se)002:10903: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK118(se)002:10904: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang ni //
NK118(se)002:10905: gsang sngags rig sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK118(se)002:10906: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK118(se)002:10907: rtag par theg pa chen po la //
NK118(se)002:10908: khyad par du ni mos par bya //
NK118(se)002:10909: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo dang //
NK118(se)002:10910: bla ma la yang gus par bya //
NK118(se)002:10911: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK118(se)002:10912: dus mtshams dag tu mchod par bya //
NK118(se)002:10913: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK118(se)002:10914: rtag tu glo bur mgron mchod bya //
NK118(se)002:10915: srog chags kun la byams pa'i sems //
NK118(se)002:10916: rab tu brtan pa nye bar gzhag /
NK118(se)002:10917: theg chen la ni dga' rnams kyis //
NK118(se)002:10918: bsod nams dag la nan tan skyed //
NK118(se)002:10919: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad pa yis //
NK118(se)002:10920: gsang sngags spyod la brtson par bya //
NK118(se)002:10921: gsang sngags rgyud las bstan pa yi //
NK118(se)002:10922: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:10923: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK118(se)002:10924: sngags dang phyag rgya mi sbyin no //
NK118(se)002:10925: gsang sngags rgyud ni legs bsrung zhing //
NK118(se)002:10926: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bya //
NK118(se)002:10927: zhes gsungs pa ltar bcu bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:10931: bla ma dang mched grogs la gus pa /
NK118(se)002:10932: 'das ma 'das kyi lha gzhan la mi sdang ba /
NK118(se)002:10933: rang gi lha dus tshigs su mchod pa /
NK118(se)002:10935: glo bur ba'i mgron mchod pa /
NK118(se)002:10937: sems can gyi don la brtson pa mi 'dor ba /
NK118(se)002:10939: dam tshig gzhan yang ci nus bsrung ba /
NK118(se)002:10940: snod min la sngags rgya mi sbyin pa /
NK118(se)002:10941: rang gi sngags rgyud bsrung zhing rtogs par bya ba rnams so //
NK118(se)002:10942: de dag gi log phyogs rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba'ang /
NK118(se)002:10944: ji skad bshad pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK118(se)002:10945: gal te nyams par gang gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:10946: de ni rang rigs snying po'i sngags //
NK118(se)002:10947: chig 'bum du ni bzlas brjod bya //
NK118(se)002:10948: yang na mes rmongs byed pa'i gzungs //
NK118(se)002:10949: stong du bzlas brjod byas kyang rung //
NK118(se)002:10950: yang na zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya //
NK118(se)002:10953: gnyis pa spyod rgyud kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:10955: rtsa ba bzhi spong ba ste /
NK118(se)002:10958: bcu po 'di dag byang chub sems dpa' gsang sngags
NK118(se)002:10959: kyi sgor spyod pa'i bslab pa thams cad kyi rtsa
NK118(se)002:10960: ba yin pas gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10964: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bzhi ni srog gi phyir yang yongs su nyams par mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10968: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyis //
NK118(se)002:10969: dam pa'i chos dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:10970: srog gi phyir yang da phyin chad //
NK118(se)002:10971: yongs su btang bar mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10972: khyod kyi ser sna dang ni gang //
NK118(se)002:10973: sems can gnod pa mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:10974: dam tshig 'di dag sangs rgyas kyi //
NK118(se)002:10975: brtul zhugs bzang po khyod la bshad //
NK118(se)002:10976: ces pas de bzhi'i ldog phyogs dam chos spong ba sogs bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:10977: 'o na mi dge bcu spong ni lha mi'i theg
NK118(se)002:10978: pa dang nyan rang la'ang yod pas sngags kyi khyad
NK118(se)002:10979: par gyi rtsa ltung du ci'i phyir 'jog ce na
NK118(se)002:10980: / 'dir byang sems sngags kyi sgor spyod pa rnams
NK118(se)002:10981: kyis 'dus ma byas pa'i tshul khrims kyi phung po
NK118(se)002:10982: bzung nas de'i dam tshig tu bcu po bzung bas
NK118(se)002:10985: gang dag 'das dang ma byon dang //
NK118(se)002:10986: gang yang da lta'i mgon po rnams //
NK118(se)002:10987: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa la //
NK118(se)002:10988: bslabs nas bla med byang chub ni //
NK118(se)002:10989: 'dus ma byas pa de thob bo //
NK118(se)002:10990: thabs dang mi ldan ye shes dang //
NK118(se)002:10991: bslab pa dag kyang bshad pa ni //
NK118(se)002:10992: dpa' bo chen pos nyan thos rnams //
NK118(se)002:10993: de la gzud pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK118(se)002:10995: gsum pa rnal 'byor rgyud kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:10996: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK118(se)002:10997: zhes sogs rigs lnga'i sdom bzung gi skabs su gsungs pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:10998: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi dam tshig la dkon mchog gsum skyabs gnas su 'dzin pa ste gsum /
NK118(se)002:10999: rdo rje'i rigs la rdo rje /
NK118(se)002:11002: slob dpon bzung ba ste bzhi /
NK118(se)002:11003: rin chen rigs la sbyin pa rnam bzhi gtong ba ste bzhi /
NK118(se)002:11004: pad+ma'i rigs la dam chos ma lus pa 'dzin pa ste gcig /
NK118(se)002:11005: las kyi rigs la sngar gyi sdom pa rnams ci nus 'dzin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11006: mchod pa'i las la 'bad pa ste gnyis de rnams sgrub pa'i bslab bya yin la /
NK118(se)002:11007: de las gzhan pa bcu bzhi ni //
NK118(se)002:11008: phas pham par ni rab tu bshad //
NK118(se)002:11009: spong ba dor bar mi bya ste //
NK118(se)002:11010: rtsa ba'i ltung ba zhes bshad do //
NK118(se)002:11011: zhes pa la ngos 'dzin mi mthun pa mang yang /
NK118(se)002:11012: 'dir sgrub pa'i bslab bya bcu bzhi po de las gzhan pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11013: de'i ldog phyogs bcu bzhi po de nyid rtsa ltung
NK118(se)002:11014: du slob dpon kun dga' snying po bzhed pa yin
NK118(se)002:11015: te / de nyid snang chen las /
NK118(se)002:11016: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK118(se)002:11017: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK118(se)002:11018: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa //
NK118(se)002:11019: zhes bya ba la sogs par phas pham pa bcu bzhi las ldog pa'i mtshan nyid can no //
NK118(se)002:11022: phyag rgya la sogs pa 'di dag gis ci zhig bya //
NK118(se)002:11023: zhes bya bas 'di yongs su spangs na pham par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:11025: bzhi pa rnal 'byor bla med kyi rtsa ltung bcu bzhi ni /
NK118(se)002:11026: kun la grags pa ltar te 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:11027: gnyis pa bla med kyi lugs bye brag tu dbye ba ni /
NK118(se)002:11028: bla med lugs la brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK118(se)002:11029: rigs lnga'i sdom pa rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang //
NK118(se)002:11030: sbom po dang ni rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK118(se)002:11032: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum gyi dbang las thob pa'i sngags sdom kyang yod mod kyi /
NK118(se)002:11033: bstan bcos 'dir khyad par du 'phags pa bla med
NK118(se)002:11034: kyi dbang las thob pa'i sngags sdom ston pa yin
NK118(se)002:11036: thog ma'i brtul zhugs dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK118(se)002:11037: zhes sogs kyis rgyas par 'chad pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:11039: gsum pa ma thob pa thob par byed pa la /
NK118(se)002:11042: dang po ma thob thob pa'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:11044: de la 'dir slob ma ji ltar dkri tshul gyi spyi don mdo tsam zhig bshad par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:11045: rgyud dag pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang 'brel bar dam tshig dang sdom pa 'dzin tshul /
NK118(se)002:11046: rgyud dag pa'i rten la smin byed kyi dbang bskur
NK118(se)002:11047: ba'i rim pas dam tshig dang sdom pa thob tshul
NK118(se)002:11048: / dam tshig dang sdom pas rgyud bsdams nas lam ji ltar sgom tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:11050: rgyud sde bzhi'i dam tshig dang sdom pa 'dzin pa dbang dang 'brel ba la nges par ltos pas /
NK118(se)002:11051: thog mar bya rgyud ltar na /
NK118(se)002:11052: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' la dgongs gsol sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:11054: bdag la byin gyis brlab par /
NK118(se)002:11055: dam tshig chen po'i dngos grub stsol bar gsol ba
NK118(se)002:11056: 'debs pa'i sgo nas 'dzin par dam tshig gsum bkod
NK118(se)002:11057: las gsungs so // spyod rgyud du bdag 'bul ba'i
NK118(se)002:11058: sdom pa sngar ltar blangs pa'i rjes su gnyis med
NK118(se)002:11059: kyi ye shes ngo shes par byas nas 'dzin pa
NK118(se)002:11060: dus gsum sgrib pa med pa'i ye shes kyi sdom
NK118(se)002:11061: pa zhes bya ba de 'dzin par mngon byang las
NK118(se)002:11062: las gsungs so // bshad do // de yang bya
NK118(se)002:11063: spyod kyi sdom chog de la thams cad rnal 'byor
NK118(se)002:11064: du sems bskyed pa'i don yang tshang zhing /
NK118(se)002:11065: ji ltar 'dzin pa'ang bya rgyud du de la 'jug
NK118(se)002:11066: pa'i tshul dang spyod rgyud du gnas pa'i tshul gyis
NK118(se)002:11068: yo ga'i rgyud du gang 'dzin rgyu'i sdom pa bsgrags te /
NK118(se)002:11069: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK118(se)002:11070: zhes sogs kyis len pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:11071: rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud du 'dzin tshul de dang 'dra ba las /
NK118(se)002:11072: khyad par dus kyi 'khor lor thog mar brtul zhugs nyer lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:11073: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rigs drug gi sdom pa 'dzin par bshad cing /
NK118(se)002:11074: rgyud gzhan rnams su rigs drug pa lnga pa'i khongs su gtogs par byas te /
NK118(se)002:11075: don grub la sdom pa thams cad 'dzin par bshad do //
NK118(se)002:11076: kha cig yo ga'i sdom pa bzung bas bla med kyi sdom pa'ang thob ste /
NK118(se)002:11077: de nyid rigs lnga'i sdom bzung gi cho ga 'dra ba'i phyir zer ba ma brtags pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11078: rigs lnga'i sdom bzung gi tshig tsam 'dra yang don mi 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:11079: 'di'i don 'og tu bla med kyi dam tshig 'chad pa las rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:11081: rgyud sde bzhi la dbang gi babs mi 'dra ba bzhi yod de /
NK118(se)002:11083: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /
NK118(se)002:11084: bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK118(se)002:11085: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK118(se)002:11086: spyod pa'i rgyud la rab tu gsal //
NK118(se)002:11087: phyir mi ldog pa yi ni dbang //
NK118(se)002:11088: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK118(se)002:11089: de ni drug pa'i bye brag dbang //
NK118(se)002:11090: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:11091: rnal 'byor bla ma yi ni mtshan //
NK118(se)002:11092: gsang ba yi ni dbang rgyal bshad //
NK118(se)002:11093: shes rab ye shes bla na med //
NK118(se)002:11094: bzhi pa de yang de bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:11095: zhes gsungs pas bya rgyud la 'jig rten las 'das
NK118(se)002:11096: pa'i rigs gsum gang rung gi dkyil 'khor du zhugs
NK118(se)002:11097: nas / gzugs dang dbang sngags bzla bzhin par dbang bum gyis chu'i dbang dang /
NK118(se)002:11098: rigs gang yin gyi dam tshig gi phyag rgyas cod pan gyi dbang /
NK118(se)002:11101: bkra shis rdzas brgyad byin pa rnams kyis dbang bskur ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11102: spyod rgyud la dkyil 'khor du bcug nas /
NK118(se)002:11103: chu dang cod pan gyi steng du /
NK118(se)002:11109: chos 'chad kyi rjes gnang sogs kyi dbang 'khor bcas bskur ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11112: slob dpon gyi dbang drug ste bcu gcig las /
NK118(se)002:11113: dang po la lnga'i chu dbang ni /
NK118(se)002:11114: dkyil 'khor du zhugs la dam tshig dang sdom pa bzung /
NK118(se)002:11116: me tog dor bas lhag pa'i lha nges par byas nas /
NK118(se)002:11117: gang bum gyi khrus sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:11118: lhag pa'i lha'i bum pa dang rnam rgyal sogs lha bum gyis chu'i dbang dang /
NK118(se)002:11119: rdo rje rin po che'i cod pan sogs rigs gang yin gyi cod pan dang /
NK118(se)002:11120: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdo rje sogs rigs kyi rdo rje dang /
NK118(se)002:11121: de rnams kyis mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK118(se)002:11122: lhag pa'i lha dang mthun pa'i ming dbang ste lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:11123: slob dpon gyi dbang drug ni /
NK118(se)002:11124: phyir mi ldog pa dam tshig gsum bzung ba /
NK118(se)002:11125: gsang dkyil du gsang ba'i 'jug pas zhugs shing mthong ba /
NK118(se)002:11126: lha dang dkyil 'khor gyi de kho na nyid /
NK118(se)002:11127: slob dpon gyi las rim rnams shes par bya ba /
NK118(se)002:11128: thun mong ma yin pa'i chos 'chad rjes gnang dang /
NK118(se)002:11131: gzengs stod de bcu gcig go //
NK118(se)002:11132: rnal 'byor bla med kyi dbang ni /
NK118(se)002:11133: sa bon 'debs pa la zhing sa sbyong dgos pa
NK118(se)002:11134: ltar rdul tshon sogs rgyu rten gyi dkyil 'khor bzhir
NK118(se)002:11135: bcug nas / 'bras bu sku bzhi'i rten 'brel sgrig pa'i phyir dbang bzhi bskur te /
NK118(se)002:11136: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK118(se)002:11137: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK118(se)002:11138: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK118(se)002:11139: rnam rtog dri ma dag bya'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:11140: dbang bskur rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK118(se)002:11142: de yang cung zad phye na /
NK118(se)002:11143: bum dbang la rig pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:11144: drug pa rdo rje 'chang gi dbang ste slob ma'i dbang drug gi steng /
NK118(se)002:11145: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang bcas pas bum dbang dngos gzhi la bdun dang /
NK118(se)002:11150: mchog dbang gong ma gsum dang bcu bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:11151: de ltar yang bshad rgyud rdor phreng las /
NK118(se)002:11152: dang po'i dbang ni gtso bo ste //
NK118(se)002:11153: gnyis pa gsang ba'i ming can no //
NK118(se)002:11154: gsum pa kun nas sbyor ba ste //
NK118(se)002:11155: bzhi pa don ni dam pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11156: gtso bo'i dbye ba bcu gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:11157: bcu gnyis pa ni gsang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11158: bcu gsum pa ni yang dag sbyor //
NK118(se)002:11159: bcu bzhi pa ni don dam ste //
NK118(se)002:11160: dbang bskur re re sa re'o //
NK118(se)002:11161: rnam pa gsum ni rgyu yi dbang //
NK118(se)002:11162: bzhi pa 'bras bur shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:11164: yang ye shes thig le las /
NK118(se)002:11165: rnal 'byor rgyud la mos pa las //
NK118(se)002:11166: dbang brgyad phye la byin par bya //
NK118(se)002:11167: rnal 'byor bla ma la mos la //
NK118(se)002:11168: bcu gcig bdag nyid byin par bya //
NK118(se)002:11169: zhes pa ltar bum dbang la brgyad du phye nas bcu gcig tu bsdus pa'am /
NK118(se)002:11170: dus 'khor las byis 'jug gi dbang bdun dang /
NK118(se)002:11171: dbang gong ma la 'jig rten pa gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:11172: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzhi pa ste bcu gcig tu bsdus pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11173: de ltar yang rtsa rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:11174: chu dang cod pan dar dang ni //
NK118(se)002:11175: rdo rje dril bu brtul zhugs dang //
NK118(se)002:11176: ming rgyal dbang ni rnam pa bdun //
NK118(se)002:11177: byis pa rnams ni bzung phyir yin //
NK118(se)002:11178: gsum pa 'jig rten kun rdzob dang //
NK118(se)002:11179: bzhi pa don gyi dam pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11180: bum pa gsang ba'i dbang dang ni //
NK118(se)002:11181: shes rab ye shes zhes bya dang //
NK118(se)002:11182: de nas shes rab chen po yi //
NK118(se)002:11183: ye shes zhes bya rdzogs pa dag /'gyur dang mi 'gyur bar chad can //
NK118(se)002:11184: bar chad med pa de las gzhan //
NK118(se)002:11186: gzhan yang sam+bu ti'i rgyu phyi mar rig pa'i dbang gi skabs su gos kyi dbang /
NK118(se)002:11187: mi g.yo bla med las gri zhags kyi dbang sogs
NK118(se)002:11188: grangs dang rnam pa mi 'dra ba mang du 'byung
NK118(se)002:11189: ste brjod par mi lang zhing /
NK118(se)002:11190: khyad par snga 'gyur bla med kyi rgyud thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs la /
NK118(se)002:11191: rgyud lung man ngag sgrub sde bzhi'i dbye bas /
NK118(se)002:11192: rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:11194: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK118(se)002:11195: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK118(se)002:11196: rim pa bzhin du byin par bya //
NK118(se)002:11197: zhes pa ltar dad pa can la dbu rgyan cod pan sogs phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK118(se)002:11199: bdag don nus pa la nyan sgom //
NK118(se)002:11200: gzhan don nus pa la 'chad phrin /
NK118(se)002:11201: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ste nus dbang lnga /
NK118(se)002:11202: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can gsum la zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11203: yang lung a nu yo ga la /
NK118(se)002:11205: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK118(se)002:11206: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK118(se)002:11207: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK118(se)002:11208: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:11209: zhes pa'i don rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs ltar bskur tshul gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:11210: rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa zab mo'i don
NK118(se)002:11211: la mos pa'i slob ma khyad par can la mdo
NK118(se)002:11212: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du rgyud kyi dngos bstan ltar
NK118(se)002:11213: chu bo bzhi rdzogs kyi dbang sum cu rtsa drug
NK118(se)002:11214: bskur ba dang / sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa
NK118(se)002:11215: rgya che ba la mos pa'i slob ma thun mong
NK118(se)002:11216: pa la mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs yan lag gi
NK118(se)002:11217: dkyil 'khor so sor phye nas bde ba gsal mdzad
NK118(se)002:11218: kyi las tho ltar theg pa thams cad 'dus pa'i
NK118(se)002:11219: mdo dbang rtsa ba so drug las yan lag rags
NK118(se)002:11220: pa brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur ba
NK118(se)002:11221: bskur ba dang / gnyis las / ding sang bla
NK118(se)002:11222: ma rnams kyi phyag bzhes su rgyud dang man ngag
NK118(se)002:11223: gi lugs de gnyis 'dor len gyi gnad kyis gcig
NK118(se)002:11224: tu dril nas bskur bar mdzad cing /
NK118(se)002:11225: de ltar mdzad pas gnas skabs su bya sla zhing /
NK118(se)002:11226: brgyud nas lugs gnyis gcig gis gcig mi nub par
NK118(se)002:11227: chabs gcig tu 'phel ba'i dgos pa khyad par can
NK118(se)002:11228: yod do // lugs de gnyis kas yo ga bzhi rdzogs dang /
NK118(se)002:11229: theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa la 'dra ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:11230: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK118(se)002:11231: bcu yis byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:11232: bcu gcig gsang ba nang par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:11233: bcu gsum bla ma chen por grags //
NK118(se)002:11234: gnyis kyis theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11236: des na mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs de yang theg
NK118(se)002:11237: brgyad sgos kyi cho gar so so nas btus te
NK118(se)002:11238: spyi'i cho gar byas pa ni ma yin gyi /
NK118(se)002:11239: 'dir mdo rang lugs kyi sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa nas /
NK118(se)002:11240: sa bcu pa rdzogs pa cir chib kyi bar non
NK118(se)002:11241: par bya ba'i ched du lha mi nas brtsams te
NK118(se)002:11242: a nu rang lugs kyi rdzogs rim mthar thug pa
NK118(se)002:11243: a ti'i bar la bya spyod so sor grangs pas
NK118(se)002:11244: dbang rim bcu byung ba de nyid bya spyod gcig
NK118(se)002:11245: tu bsdus nas theg dgu dang tshul 'dra bas the
NK118(se)002:11247: de ltu bu'i lam stegs kyi theg pa rnams so so'i lam dang 'dra rung du byung kyang /
NK118(se)002:11248: don la sngags kyi thabs mkhas kyis zin pas theg
NK118(se)002:11249: pa rang rang gi spangs thob dang rigs 'dra'i yon
NK118(se)002:11250: tan de dang de skye ba'i myur lam du'ang 'gro
NK118(se)002:11251: ba yin no // man ngag a ti yo ga'i dbang rnams ni /
NK118(se)002:11252: dbang gsum pa'i dpe'i ye shes la ltos mi dgos
NK118(se)002:11253: par thog ma nas don dam byang chub sems kyi
NK118(se)002:11254: dkyil 'khor du 'jug rung ba'i skal ldan la rdzogs
NK118(se)002:11255: pa chen po rig pa'i rtsal dbang bskur ba ste
NK118(se)002:11256: / slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i khog don las /
NK118(se)002:11257: zab pa don gyi dbang mchog ni //
NK118(se)002:11258: rig pa'i rtsal dbang thob pa ste //
NK118(se)002:11259: chos nyid rtogs pas dbang zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:11260: ye shes dbang bskur cod pan can //
NK118(se)002:11262: khyad par man ngag gi sde ltar na /
NK118(se)002:11264: spros bcas spros pa med pa dang //
NK118(se)002:11265: shin tu spros med rab spros med //
NK118(se)002:11266: dbang ni rnam pa bzhi yis kyang //
NK118(se)002:11267: skal ba ldan pa smin par bya //
NK118(se)002:11268: zhes pa'i dbang bzhis rim pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:11269: lus ngag yid gsum dang shes bya la rmongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyong /
NK118(se)002:11270: sku gsung thugs dang rang byung 'od gsal gyi nus pa 'jug /
NK118(se)002:11273: bde stong zung 'jug sgom zhing ka dag gi ye shes rtogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11274: mngon sum lhun grub kyi don nyams su len pa bzhi la dbang ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:11275: 'di ni dbang gong ma nyid la dbang bzhir phye
NK118(se)002:11276: ba yin pas bla med thun mong ba'i dbang bzhi
NK118(se)002:11277: dang grangs 'dra yang don mi 'dra bar shes dgos
NK118(se)002:11279: bla med thun mong gi dbang bzhi pa'i sngags sdom
NK118(se)002:11280: rgyud ldan zhig gis 'di nyid thob na sdom pa
NK118(se)002:11281: sngar med gsar thob kyang 'dod dgos te /
NK118(se)002:11282: bla med kyi cho ga gzhan rnams rgyas bsdus dang
NK118(se)002:11283: rnam grangs mi 'dra ba tsam las phan tshun gcig
NK118(se)002:11284: gi dod gcig gis thub pas mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:11285: de dag so so las thob pa'i sdom pa rnams kyang ngo bo gcig tu 'gyur mod /
NK118(se)002:11286: zhu bde lhan skyes kun rdzob pa dpe'i ye shes
NK118(se)002:11287: tsam la ngo sprod pa'i bzhi pa btags pa ba
NK118(se)002:11288: des don dam lhan skyes zung 'jug gi ye shes
NK118(se)002:11289: la 'jug pa'i thabs bzhi pa mtshan nyid pa 'di'i
NK118(se)002:11290: dod mi thub pas mtshungs pa ma yin pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:11291: ro // sgrub sde la spyi bka' bde 'dus ltar na /
NK118(se)002:11293: phyi dbang nang dbang gsang dbang dang //
NK118(se)002:11294: theg pa lta ba spyi 'byams dbang //
NK118(se)002:11295: rim gyis dbang ni rdzogs par bskur //
NK118(se)002:11296: zhes pa ltar phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi dbang dang bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:11297: gdul bya zhe sdang can sgrol ba lam du khyer
NK118(se)002:11298: ba'i phyir bum pa sogs phyi nang gi rdzas brgya
NK118(se)002:11299: rtsa brgyad la brten nas phyi dbang bskur ba /
NK118(se)002:11300: nga rgyal can lha lam du khyer ba'i phyir nang dbang lus la brten nas bskur ba /
NK118(se)002:11301: 'dod chags can sbyor ba lam du khyer ba'i phyir gsang dbang yum la brten nas bskul ba /
NK118(se)002:11302: gti mug can rnam rtog lam du khyer ba'i phyir
NK118(se)002:11303: de kho na nyid kyi dbang sems la brten nas
NK118(se)002:11304: bskur ba dang bzhi yin no //
NK118(se)002:11305: sgrub sde'i dgos bka' yang phur sogs la thun mong
NK118(se)002:11306: ba bla med spyi bka' ltar dbang bzhi bskur ba
NK118(se)002:11307: dang / zab khyad sgrub dbang gi lugs su bskur
NK118(se)002:11308: ba sogs mang ste thams cad brjod par mi nus
NK118(se)002:11309: dang / shing / spyi ldog nas bla med kyi dbang thams cad dbang bzhir 'du ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:11311: dang po bya ba'i rgyud ni /
NK118(se)002:11312: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK118(se)002:11313: rtogs pas kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re
NK118(se)002:11314: zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11315: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas sgyu 'phrul lam rim du /
NK118(se)002:11316: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK118(se)002:11317: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK118(se)002:11318: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK118(se)002:11319: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK118(se)002:11321: de'i lam gyi khyad par la /
NK118(se)002:11322: dpung bzang 'grel par spyod pa'i sgo bzhis bsdus te /
NK118(se)002:11324: dbang gis snod rung du byed pa /
NK118(se)002:11326: rigs gsum gang rung gi lha bsnyen pa /
NK118(se)002:11328: mtshan ma mthong nas rdzas dang sngags g.yog 'dzom pas
NK118(se)002:11329: brtson 'grus bar ma chad par bzlas brjod bya ba
NK118(se)002:11330: / grub pa'i mtha' 'bras bu'i spyod pa ni /
NK118(se)002:11331: de ltar bsgrubs pas rdzas lus longs spyod rnams 'dod
NK118(se)002:11332: pa'i lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i rig 'dzin nam
NK118(se)002:11334: rten de la brten nas sngags kyi phyin drug gi
NK118(se)002:11335: spyod pa sbyang pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyud
NK118(se)002:11336: sde 'dir bshad pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan nyid
NK118(se)002:11337: can gyi byang chub rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK118(se)002:11338: sa mngon du byed par 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:11340: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas sa //
NK118(se)002:11343: 'di'i mi tshe bdun yang rig 'dzin grub pas ring por 'tsho ba'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11344: gzhan las bya rgyud rang lam gyi bskal chen brgyad
NK118(se)002:11345: nas 'bras bu la sbyor bar bshad pa dang mi
NK118(se)002:11347: de ltar nges par byas nas rnal 'byor gyi ngo bor nyams su len tshul la /
NK118(se)002:11348: bya rgyud tsam po rnams su bdag lhar bskyed pa med pas /
NK118(se)002:11350: rang de'i 'khor du gtogs pa tsam gyi 'du shes bzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:11351: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i bya ba gtso bor gyur pas bsnyen pa bya ba ste /
NK118(se)002:11352: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus las /
NK118(se)002:11353: bdag nyid lha yi snyems pa med pa dang //
NK118(se)002:11355: 'on kyang bya rgyud khyad par can las bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa bshad de /
NK118(se)002:11357: de kho na nyid bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:11358: bdag gi de kho na nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:11359: rgyud 'dir gang lta bas gtan la dbab par bya
NK118(se)002:11360: ba'i gzhi sems nyid don dam stong gsal gyi ye
NK118(se)002:11361: shes yod med snang stong gi mtha' bzhi dang bral
NK118(se)002:11362: ba'i chos nyid du rtogs pa'i yon tan kun rdzob
NK118(se)002:11363: yongs su dag pa'i lha'i mtshan nyid du lta ba
NK118(se)002:11365: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba //
NK118(se)002:11366: rig phyir ye shes gzhan las min //
NK118(se)002:11367: rkyen bslang snang ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK118(se)002:11368: snang ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK118(se)002:11369: drug spyod rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK118(se)002:11370: mthong ba rnam par dag ces bya //
NK118(se)002:11372: lha'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:11374: dang po khrus byas rnal 'byor pas //
NK118(se)002:11375: rdo rje'i gdan la 'dug nas ni //
NK118(se)002:11376: mchod dang gsol bas lha drug bsgom //
NK118(se)002:11377: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK118(se)002:11378: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin no //
NK118(se)002:11379: zhes pas bdag gi de kho na nyid sgom pa stong pa'i lha /
NK118(se)002:11380: de nyid kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par sgom pa yi ge'i lha /
NK118(se)002:11381: de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags gzugs rang sgra sgrog pa sgra'i lha /
NK118(se)002:11382: sngags de nyid zla dkyil la 'dres nas slar yang
NK118(se)002:11383: sngags phreng bkod pa las 'od zer spro bsdus sangs
NK118(se)002:11384: rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te /
NK118(se)002:11385: zla ba sngags phreng dang bcas pa yongs su gyur
NK118(se)002:11386: pa las rigs gsum gyi lha de dang de'i gzugs
NK118(se)002:11387: su sgom pa gzugs kyi lha /
NK118(se)002:11388: de la rigs gang yin de dang de'i dam rgyas 'debs pa phyag rgya'i lha /
NK118(se)002:11389: gnas skabs kun tu ting nge 'dzin gyis lha'i 'du
NK118(se)002:11390: shes dang mi 'bral bar byed pa mtshan ma'i lha
NK118(se)002:11391: ste / rang gi lha sgom pa'i rnal 'byor drug go //
NK118(se)002:11393: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK118(se)002:11394: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du blta //
NK118(se)002:11395: zhes pa ltar rang gi mdun du yang dag pa'i
NK118(se)002:11396: smon lam gyi stobs las byung ba'i zhing khams pho
NK118(se)002:11397: brang dang bcas pa gsal btab pa'i nang du ye
NK118(se)002:11398: shes kyi lha spyan drangs nas bzhugs su gsol ba
NK118(se)002:11399: barje dang / rang nyid lhar bskyed pa bran gyi tshul du bltas te /
NK118(se)002:11400: mchod bstod dang rgyun bshags bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11401: bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:11402: rigs gsum so so'i bgrang phreng cho ga bzhin du 'du byas pa bzung ste /
NK118(se)002:11403: bdag mdun gnyis ka'i thugs kar zla dkyil la bzla
NK118(se)002:11404: bya'i sngags phreng rang sgra sgrog pa bkod pa la
NK118(se)002:11405: dmigs te / srog rtsol bsdams nas bzla ba spyi dang /
NK118(se)002:11407: gzhi bdag mdun lhar bsam pa /
NK118(se)002:11408: sems ni thugs kar zla dkyil bsam pa /
NK118(se)002:11409: sgra ni de'i steng sngags kyi sgra gdangs bsam la /
NK118(se)002:11410: srog rtsol bsdams nas mdun gyi lha zla ba sngags bcas la dmigs nas bzla ba dang /
NK118(se)002:11411: yang srog dbyung ba'i tshe rang gi lha zla ba sngags phreng la dmigs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11412: sngags bzla ba'ang skyon dang bral bar ma nyams par bzla zhing /
NK118(se)002:11413: des skyon mi rtog pa'i ngang du ngal bso ba ste /
NK118(se)002:11415: sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol //
NK118(se)002:11416: gsang sngags mi 'gyur gzhi la gnas //
NK118(se)002:11417: yan lag ma nyams gsang sngags bzlas //
NK118(se)002:11418: ngal na bdag la ngal bsos shig /
NK118(se)002:11420: bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:11422: gsang sngags mer gnas dngos grub ster //
NK118(se)002:11423: sgrar gnas rnal 'byor ster bar dran //
NK118(se)002:11424: sgra mthas thar pa ster bar byed //
NK118(se)002:11425: ces pas rang lhar gsal ba'i snying gar me 'bar
NK118(se)002:11426: ba'i nang du zla ba la sngags bkod nas srog
NK118(se)002:11427: bsdam pa'i sbyor bas bslab pa mer gnas te /
NK118(se)002:11428: zhi sogs las sgrub pa'i gazhi'o //
NK118(se)002:11429: de las sngags kyi yi ge rnams rang sgra dril
NK118(se)002:11430: bu'i sgra ltar grags par bsam nas srog bsdam pa
NK118(se)002:11432: zhi gnas skye ba'i rten gazhi'o //
NK118(se)002:11433: sngags kyi sgra tsam de yang dpyad cing gzhigs nas
NK118(se)002:11434: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngang la
NK118(se)002:11435: mnyam par 'jog pa sgra mtha' ste /
NK118(se)002:11436: de las lhag mthong 'char zhing thar pa'i nyer len du gyur pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11439: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK118(se)002:11440: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK118(se)002:11441: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11442: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK118(se)002:11445: gnyis ka la brten pa las grub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11447: lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK118(se)002:11448: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK118(se)002:11449: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK118(se)002:11450: zhes pas lta ba yo ga ltar blta zhing /
NK118(se)002:11451: spyod pa kri ya ltar gtsang sbra la gnas pa'i sgo nas /
NK118(se)002:11452: bsgom bya mngon par rtogs pa'i khyad par la /
NK118(se)002:11455: grub pa'i spyod pa gsum las /
NK118(se)002:11458: dbang gis snod rung du byed pa /
NK118(se)002:11459: nang gi 'jug pa'i spyod pa la /
NK118(se)002:11461: mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor gnyis gsungs pa'i tshul gyis bsgom bya'i lha la rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:11464: gzugs kyi lha dang gsum bshad pa'i re re la'ang gnyis gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:11465: yi ge la byang chub kyi sems dang sgra'i lha /
NK118(se)002:11466: phyag rgya la 'khor lo sogs dbyibs bcas dang chos
NK118(se)002:11467: 'byung thal khas mtshon pa'i stong nyid gzugs dbyibs med
NK118(se)002:11468: pa / gzugs la yongs su dag pa snying po'i don rang rig mngon sum gyis mthong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:11469: yongs su ma dag pa zhal phyag la sogs pa'i gzugs su rnam par rtog pas sgom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11470: de ltar shes par byas nas mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor sgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK118(se)002:11472: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK118(se)002:11473: de bzhin gzhi las gzhir gyur nyid //
NK118(se)002:11474: shin tu bsdams pas yid las ni //
NK118(se)002:11476: zhes pa ltar bdag gnas rnal 'byor bsrung ba sogs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK118(se)002:11477: yi ge dang po don dam byang chub kyi sems stong nyid kyi ngang las /
NK118(se)002:11478: de'i snang cha kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par sgom pa /
NK118(se)002:11479: yi ge gnyis pa de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra sgrog pa /
NK118(se)002:11480: de thams cad yongs su gyur pa las gzhi dang
NK118(se)002:11481: po bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa la sngags rgya la
NK118(se)002:11483: de nas gzhi gnyis pa rang gi mdun du lha
NK118(se)002:11484: bskyed pa'i thugs kar zla dkyil la sngags phreng bkod
NK118(se)002:11485: nas / srog bsdam zhing rtse gcig pa'i sbyor bas ting nge 'dzin brtan par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11486: gnyis pa mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK118(se)002:11487: phung sogs chos thams cad la mtha' bzhis rnam par
NK118(se)002:11488: dpyad pas skye med du rtogs pa 'jug pa'i sems
NK118(se)002:11489: / de rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bor mngon du gyur pa gnas pa'i sems /
NK118(se)002:11490: de ltar ma rtogs pa las snying rje chen pos rjes su 'jug pa ldang ba'i sems te /
NK118(se)002:11491: 'jug gnas ldang gsum gyis khyad par du byas pa'i don dam byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11492: de ltar rnal 'byor gnyis la goms pa las /
NK118(se)002:11493: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i ngang /
NK118(se)002:11494: mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis ka'i dngos grub 'grub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11495: gnyis pa sbyor ba'i spyod pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:11496: phyi ni bzlas brjod yan lag bzhi ldan gyi sgo
NK118(se)002:11497: nas mtshan ma'am grangs kyi bsnyen pa byed pa yin
NK118(se)002:11499: rang nyid sh+aakya thub pa gsal ba'i thugs kar zla
NK118(se)002:11500: ba la rnam snang bsgoms pa'i thugs kar zla dkyil
NK118(se)002:11502: srog bsdam zhing bzlas brjod rtse gcig pa'i mtshan nyid
NK118(se)002:11503: can gyi zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi ngo bor sgrub
NK118(se)002:11504: pa'o // gsum pa grub pa'i spyod pa la /
NK118(se)002:11505: thun mong ba bsnyen pa mthar phyin nas rdzas sngags la brten pa'i rig 'dzin sgrub pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11506: thun mong ma yin pa 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor la brten nas rlung gi sbyor ba bsgoms pa las /
NK118(se)002:11507: rdzu 'phrul dang mngon shes bsgrubs te rig pa 'dzin
NK118(se)002:11508: pa'i nang du 'gro ba sogs gnas skabs kyi 'bras
NK118(se)002:11509: bu grub cing / rten de la brten nas sngags
NK118(se)002:11510: kyi spyod pa spyad pas mi tshe lnga'am ji ltar
NK118(se)002:11511: 'gor na'ang bskal pa gsum mam gcig gis mthar thug
NK118(se)002:11512: gi 'bras bu rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa
NK118(se)002:11515: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang sar gnas //
NK118(se)002:11518: gnyis su med la mi tshe lngas sgrib gol //
NK118(se)002:11521: don dam par chos thams cad spros pa'i mtshan ma
NK118(se)002:11522: dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od gsal stong pa nyid
NK118(se)002:11523: du rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob
NK118(se)002:11524: rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar btags te /
NK118(se)002:11525: rtog pa bzang ngan blang dor gyi rtsol bas 'bras bu sgrub par 'dod pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11527: lhun grub mnyam pa ma rtogs pas //
NK118(se)002:11528: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK118(se)002:11529: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul lha //
NK118(se)002:11530: blang dor byed pa las kyi sa //
NK118(se)002:11532: de'i bsgom bya lam gyi khyad par la /
NK118(se)002:11535: rten gyi gang zag byang chub tu sems bskyed pa /
NK118(se)002:11537: bka' bzhin dam tshig sgrub pa /
NK118(se)002:11538: lam dang lam gyi ston pa sogs la dad pa
NK118(se)002:11539: dang ldan pa des ji ltar bsgom pa'i lam gyi
NK118(se)002:11540: chings ni / thob bya'i 'bras bu la dmigs nas /
NK118(se)002:11541: de'i nyer len gyi rgyu ni /
NK118(se)002:11542: thog mtha' med pa'i byang chub kyi sems 'od gsal
NK118(se)002:11543: ba so so rang gi rig pa'i bdag nyid lha
NK118(se)002:11544: sngags dkyil 'khor phyag rgya thams cad kyi 'char gzhir
NK118(se)002:11545: gyur pa'i sems kyi de kho na nyid rgyu'i rgyud
NK118(se)002:11546: ces bya ba de nyid yin la /
NK118(se)002:11547: rgyu de las 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i thabs kyi gtso bo ni gnyis kyis bsdus te /
NK118(se)002:11551: phyag rgya bzhi dang 'brel ba'i lha'i rnal 'byor sgom pa 'khor bcas te /
NK118(se)002:11552: de yang sku phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK118(se)002:11553: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i /
NK118(se)002:11555: phrin las las kyi phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor dang bzhis rim par /
NK118(se)002:11559: sgo lnga rnams kyi glo bur gyi 'khrul pa bsal nas /
NK118(se)002:11560: rang bzhin me long lta bu /
NK118(se)002:11563: bya grub ye shes bzhi mngon du byed cing //
NK118(se)002:11564: chos dbyings ye shes ni de thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:11565: de lta bu'i lha'i rnal 'byor sgom pa'i rim pa la /
NK118(se)002:11566: dbang rnon rnams sngon byung ston pa sangs rgyas nas
NK118(se)002:11567: dkyil 'khor sprul bshad dang phrin las mngon par 'du
NK118(se)002:11568: mdzad tshul dang mthun par rjes 'jug la'ang /
NK118(se)002:11571: las rgyal mchog ste ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas nyams su len pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11572: dbang rtul rnams bdag nyid rang rigs kyi lha dam tshig par sgom pa rnal 'byor /
NK118(se)002:11573: de la ye shes pa bcug ste ro gcig tu bya ba rjes su rnal 'byor /
NK118(se)002:11574: brtan g.yo thams cad rang rigs kyi lha'i rnal 'byor du bya ba thams cad rnal 'byor /
NK118(se)002:11575: de gsum sngon du song ba las sems rtse gcig
NK118(se)002:11576: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du gyur ba shin tu
NK118(se)002:11577: rnal 'byor te / rnal 'byor bzhi la brten nas nyams su len pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11579: sems kyi de kho na nyid mngon du rtogs pa so so rang rig pa'i ye shes te /
NK118(se)002:11580: de nyid dbang rnon byin brlabs dang sgom byung gi stobs kyis mngon du byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11581: dbang rtul thos sogs kyis brgyud de mngon du byed pa'i tshul lo //
NK118(se)002:11582: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i rim pa la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:11583: gtso bor ting nge 'dzin la brten nas 'das pa'i dngos grub dang /
NK118(se)002:11584: bzlas byed la brten nas dngos grub gnyis ka sgrub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11586: ting nge 'dzin gsum dang rnal 'byor bzhi gang la brten kyang rung /
NK118(se)002:11587: rang gi lha 'khor gsum yongs dag gi mchod pas mnyes par byas nas /
NK118(se)002:11588: gzhan don du phyag rgya sgrub /
NK118(se)002:11589: de grub nas phyag rgya'i las rab 'byams la sbyar /
NK118(se)002:11590: de nas mngon shes bsgrubs te rang rigs kyi 'khor
NK118(se)002:11591: lo dang mthun pa'i tshogs khang du lha grangs dang
NK118(se)002:11592: mnyam pa'i sgrub pa pos dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par
NK118(se)002:11593: byas te / 'dod yon gyi rol pa gnyis su
NK118(se)002:11594: med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi yan lag tu spyad
NK118(se)002:11595: pas lha mnyes shing dbang du gyur pa'i tshul gyis
NK118(se)002:11596: byas te / 'grub la / gal te ma 'grub
NK118(se)002:11597: na bskyar ba dang dpogs chog la brten nas 'grub
NK118(se)002:11598: byas te / 'grub la / pa'o // gnyis pa la /
NK118(se)002:11602: bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa'i mdun du'ang lha bskyed de /
NK118(se)002:11603: srog dang dbang po nang du bsdus nas snying po yid bzlas bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:11604: rlung phyir dbyung ba na mdun gyi lha la dmigs te bzla /
NK118(se)002:11605: nang du 'jug pa na bdag dang lha tha mi
NK118(se)002:11606: dad par byas la bzla ba ni kun rdzob dmigs
NK118(se)002:11607: bcas dang / bdag dang lha sngags kyis mtshon pa'i
NK118(se)002:11608: chos thams cad stong nyid nam mkha' lta bur dag
NK118(se)002:11609: pa'i ngang nas yid bzlas dang /
NK118(se)002:11610: phyir dbyung ba na lha'i mtshan ma tsam dran par bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:11611: slar srog rtsol nang du bsdus te sems rtse gcig
NK118(se)002:11612: pa'i ngo bor ro gcig tu bya ba don dam
NK118(se)002:11613: dmigs med kyi rdor bzlas te /
NK118(se)002:11614: de gnyis dbang rnon gyi bzla lugs so //
NK118(se)002:11616: dbang rtul gyi bzla lugs te /
NK118(se)002:11617: rang rigs kyi lha'i skyil krung bcas la /
NK118(se)002:11618: rigs gang yin gyi khu tshur bcas pa'i lag g.yon
NK118(se)002:11619: gyis rang rigs kyi phyag mtshan bzung ba gos kyis
NK118(se)002:11620: g.yogs g.yas pas rigs dang mthun pa'i bgrang phreng blangs
NK118(se)002:11621: te / rigs gang la shis pa'i sgra gdangs kyis bzla ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11622: de ltar rdor bzlas kyis 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub dang /
NK118(se)002:11623: tshig bzlas kyis rdzas dang mkha' spyod kyi rig 'dzin
NK118(se)002:11624: sogs 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub bsgrubs nas 'das pa'i
NK118(se)002:11626: mthar thug mi tshe gsum mam bcu drug gis phyag
NK118(se)002:11627: rgya chen po grub nas rim gyis rigs lnga stug
NK118(se)002:11628: po bkod pa'i sar mngon byang lnga'i thabs kyis ye
NK118(se)002:11629: shes lnga'i ngo bor 'tshang rgya bar 'dod de /
NK118(se)002:11631: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK118(se)002:11632: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK118(se)002:11634: yang yo ga'i nyams len gyi skabs 'dir thun khyad gnyis 'byung ste /
NK118(se)002:11635: spyod 'jug dang thun mong ba'i dbang du byas pa rang shar las /
NK118(se)002:11636: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK118(se)002:11637: spun dang grogs po'i tshul du 'dod //
NK118(se)002:11638: ces pa ltar zur lugs kyi snying po'i khog dbub
NK118(se)002:11639: rnams su yo ga'i bkol mdor smos pa bzhin no
NK118(se)002:11640: // yo ga khyad par ba'i dbang du byas na bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du bsgoms pa la /
NK118(se)002:11641: ye shes pa dgug bstim gnyis med du byed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11643: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings ngang //
NK118(se)002:11644: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang //
NK118(se)002:11646: bzhi pa rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud kyi nyams len ni /
NK118(se)002:11647: slob dpon ye shes grags pas /
NK118(se)002:11648: gzhan don phun tshogs sangs rgyas kyi //
NK118(se)002:11650: ces pa ltar gsang sngags kyi sgor spyad pa spyod
NK118(se)002:11651: pa'i gang zag rnams kyis 'dod don gnyer bya'i gtso
NK118(se)002:11652: bo ni gzhan don phun tshogs yin la /
NK118(se)002:11653: de'i rten ni rang don phun tshogs te /
NK118(se)002:11654: de ltar don gnyis mthar phyin pa'i byang chub ni thob bya 'bras bu'i rgyud do //
NK118(se)002:11655: de mngon du byed pa yang nyer len gyi rgyu dang /
NK118(se)002:11656: lhan cig byed rkyen tshang ba la rag lus pas /
NK118(se)002:11657: dang po'i dbang du byas nas gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud bzhag /
NK118(se)002:11658: gnyis pa'i dbang du byas nas thabs sam lam gyi rgyud bzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:11659: gsang snying gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK118(se)002:11660: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK118(se)002:11663: gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las kyang /
NK118(se)002:11664: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:11665: rgyun de rnam pa gsum du 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:11666: gzhi dang de yi rang bzhin dang //
NK118(se)002:11667: mi 'phrogs pa yi rab dbye bas //
NK118(se)002:11668: rang bzhin rnam pa rgyu yin te //
NK118(se)002:11669: gzhi ni thabs zhes bya ba yin //
NK118(se)002:11671: gsum gyis rgyud kyi don bsdus pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11673: de la sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK118(se)002:11674: par dag pa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ni
NK118(se)002:11675: dri ma sbyong ba'i gzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:11676: rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i gazhi'am rgyur gyur cing /
NK118(se)002:11677: rang bzhin 'gyur ba med par rgyun chags pas na gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK118(se)002:11678: de la ming gi rnam grangs /
NK118(se)002:11679: 'ching grol med pa'i don gyis gnas lugs /
NK118(se)002:11680: 'bras chos rnam gzhi la ye nas tshang bas bde gshegs snying po /
NK118(se)002:11681: sems kyi chos nyid de'i stong cha las chos sku
NK118(se)002:11682: dang snang cha las gzugs sku'i yon tan rdzogs par
NK118(se)002:11683: ldan yang dri ma las ma 'grol bar sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:11684: su mi 'gyur bas rang bzhin gnas rigs dang /
NK118(se)002:11687: dri ma dang 'brel yang rang gi ngo bo la
NK118(se)002:11688: gos ma myong bas rang bzhin rnam dag gam byang
NK118(se)002:11689: chub la sogs pa'i tha snyad btags shing /
NK118(se)002:11690: khyad par sngags kyi theg pa 'dir /
NK118(se)002:11691: phyi rgyud du bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK118(se)002:11692: thog mtha' med pa'i byang chub kyi sems la sogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11693: nang rgyud du ma h+aa yo ga bas rang rig
NK118(se)002:11694: pa byang chub kyi sems lhag pa bden pa dbyer
NK118(se)002:11695: med spyod yul dang bral ba'am /
NK118(se)002:11696: bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po /
NK118(se)002:11697: a nu yo ga bas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis
NK118(se)002:11698: su med pa'i sras bde ba chen po rtsa ba
NK118(se)002:11700: a ti yo ga bas 'od gsal byang chub kyi
NK118(se)002:11701: sems stong gsal 'gag med kyi gnas lugs ye shes
NK118(se)002:11702: gsum ldan du ye nas bzhugs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11703: de yang bla na med pa'i rgyud rnams su lus
NK118(se)002:11704: can rnams kyi snying ga chos kyi pho brang du
NK118(se)002:11705: rgyu rgyud kyi rten dwangs ma lnga'i dbus na brten
NK118(se)002:11706: pa sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i chos sku byang chub
NK118(se)002:11707: kyi sems bzhugs par bshad cing /
NK118(se)002:11708: 'byung lnga sems dang bcas pa'i dwangs ma drug kyang
NK118(se)002:11709: gnyis gnyis ro gcig tu 'jug pa'i don gyis shin
NK118(se)002:11710: tu phra ba'i sgo gsum gdod ma nas rdo rje
NK118(se)002:11711: mi shigs pa gsum gyi lha'i bdag nyid du gnas
NK118(se)002:11712: pa ste / sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK118(se)002:11713: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK118(se)002:11714: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK118(se)002:11715: mi shig thig le bde chen po //
NK118(se)002:11716: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK118(se)002:11717: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK118(se)002:11720: mi shigs ye shes thig le ni //
NK118(se)002:11721: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK118(se)002:11722: gcig dang du ma rnams spangs pa //
NK118(se)002:11723: sna tshogs snang la mtshon du med //
NK118(se)002:11726: lus la ye shes chen pos khyab //
NK118(se)002:11727: til 'bru la ni mar bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:11728: lus kyi skrag dang gzi mdangs ni //
NK118(se)002:11729: ye shes rlan gyis khyab par byed //
NK118(se)002:11732: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK118(se)002:11733: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spangs //
NK118(se)002:11734: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK118(se)002:11735: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11737: des na sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba de'ang khyad chos bzhi ldan te /
NK118(se)002:11738: zhing dang sku dang ye shes sogs 'bras bu'i chos mthun pa'i khyad par can /
NK118(se)002:11739: rang bzhin bde ba chen po /
NK118(se)002:11742: de nyid kyis 'khor 'das thams cad la khyad par
NK118(se)002:11743: med par khyab pas grol gzhi lhun grub kyi chos
NK118(se)002:11744: nyid rang la yod pa ni 'bras rgyud kyi nyer
NK118(se)002:11745: len gyi rgyur nges pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11747: dngos po rnams kyi stong pa nyid kyi ngo bo
NK118(se)002:11748: ni rang bzhin dang rnam pa zhes pa don gzhan
NK118(se)002:11749: ma yin te / rang gi ngo bo zhes pa'i don to //
NK118(se)002:11751: nye bar len pa'i byed pa po'i rdo rje 'dzin pa ste /
NK118(se)002:11752: gang 'di rnams kyi thog ma med pa'i dri mas
NK118(se)002:11753: ma gos pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa'i sangs
NK118(se)002:11754: rgyas nyid de / de kho na ni dri ma
NK118(se)002:11755: med pa nyid thob pa'i mtshan nyid can sangs rgyas
NK118(se)002:11756: rgyas nyid de / nyid kyi rgyu'o // zhes pa'i don to //
NK118(se)002:11758: rgyu rgyud rgyun chags pa de la rdo rje rtse mor rtsa ba'i rgyud ces bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:11759: 'bras rgyud ni rgyu rgyud de las byung zhing //
NK118(se)002:11760: de'i pha rol tu son pa sa mthar phyin pa'i rgyal ba ste rgyud phyi ma zhes bshad do //
NK118(se)002:11762: ci'i phyir 'dir ni rgyud phyi ma //
NK118(se)002:11763: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:11765: phyi ma zhes bya pha rol te //
NK118(se)002:11766: rgyud ni phyi mar brjod pa yin //
NK118(se)002:11767: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:11768: phyi ma snga ma las byung ba'i //
NK118(se)002:11769: de nyid gsang ba sbas zhes pa //
NK118(se)002:11770: rgyud ni phyi mar brjod pa yin //
NK118(se)002:11771: ci phyir rgyud dang phyi ma yin //
NK118(se)002:11772: sa mthar phyin pa'i rgyal ba mchog /
NK118(se)002:11773: srid pa'i btson ra las brgal yin //
NK118(se)002:11774: yang na gang zhig brgal gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:11775: rgyud ni phyi ma yin par bshad //
NK118(se)002:11777: de ltar rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don de nyid
NK118(se)002:11778: rtog ge rnam par 'khyams pa'i lung rig kyis gtan
NK118(se)002:11780: tha snyad kyi shes ngo las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:11783: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam //
NK118(se)002:11784: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK118(se)002:11785: rtogs par nus pa ma yin te //
NK118(se)002:11789: so so rang rig mtshan med spyod yul ni //
NK118(se)002:11790: brjod du med cing tha snyad yongs chad pas //
NK118(se)002:11791: rtsod dang bral ba don dam chos yin te //
NK118(se)002:11792: de ni rtog ge'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11794: 'o na gang gis gtan la dbab par bya zhe na /
NK118(se)002:11796: bye brag bsdus pas kun khyab gsum //
NK118(se)002:11797: zhes pas shin tu lkog gyur gyi don de nyid 'jal nus pa ni /
NK118(se)002:11798: kun khyab kyi tshad ma gsum las gzhan med de /
NK118(se)002:11799: rdo rje me long gi rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:11800: lung dang rigs pa man ngag gi //
NK118(se)002:11801: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal bas //
NK118(se)002:11802: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:11804: rgyal ba'i bka' dri ma med pa'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK118(se)002:11805: mkhas pas mdzad pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK118(se)002:11806: de gnyis dang rjes su mthun par skyes pa'i rig pa tshad ma gsum gyis gzhal bas /
NK118(se)002:11807: rtogs bya'i lta ba rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don
NK118(se)002:11808: de nyid gtan la phebs pa ni sngags rang gzhung
NK118(se)002:11810: de la phyi 'gyur ba'i mkhas pa phal che ba zhig /
NK118(se)002:11812: rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK118(se)002:11813: rdzun min bden min de bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:11814: thams cad chu yi zla ba ltar //
NK118(se)002:11816: zhes pa'i dgongs pa 'grel tshul las sngags kyi grub
NK118(se)002:11817: mtha' ni lta ba dbu ma la thabs khyad par
NK118(se)002:11818: du 'phags pas phye ba'o zhes bzhed mod /
NK118(se)002:11819: 'dir snga 'gyur gyi rang skad du thabs bzhin du lta ba'ang lhag ste /
NK118(se)002:11820: don dam par skye 'gag med pa dang /
NK118(se)002:11821: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad sgyu ma tsam du lta ba dbu ma pa dang mthun na'ang /
NK118(se)002:11822: sngags kyi khyad par kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bu
NK118(se)002:11823: de yang yongs su dag pa'i lha'i mtshan nyid du
NK118(se)002:11824: lta ba dang / bden pa gnyis kyang dbyer med par lta bas khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11825: de ltar yang kun mkhyen chen po yid bzhin mdzod du /
NK118(se)002:11826: de la dang po gnas lugs shes pa gces //
NK118(se)002:11827: theg pa'i dbang gis rnam pa mang na yang //
NK118(se)002:11828: nges pa'i snying po bden pa dbyer med de //
NK118(se)002:11829: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsang ba'i mdzod khang yin //
NK118(se)002:11831: kun rdzob tu lhar lta ba'ang /
NK118(se)002:11832: bya rgyud pas dag pa chos nyid kyi lha dang /
NK118(se)002:11833: yo ga bas de'i steng du mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen pos byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha dang /
NK118(se)002:11834: rnal 'byor bla na med pas de gnyis ka'i steng
NK118(se)002:11835: du lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du lta ba'i
NK118(se)002:11836: phyir na bden pa tha dad du 'dzin pa dor
NK118(se)002:11837: nas / don dam bden ngor ma zad /
NK118(se)002:11838: kun rdzob tu'ang snod bcud dag mnyam chen por gtan
NK118(se)002:11839: la 'bebs pas 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi lta ba
NK118(se)002:11840: zhes rgyu'i bla med kyi theg pa dbu ma pa
NK118(se)002:11841: las thabs kyi theg pa sngags kyi lta ba 'di
NK118(se)002:11843: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i rgyud tshig sangs rgyas gsang bas lam rim du drangs pa las /
NK118(se)002:11844: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK118(se)002:11845: don dam du ni dbyer med la //
NK118(se)002:11846: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK118(se)002:11847: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:11848: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK118(se)002:11849: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK118(se)002:11850: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK118(se)002:11851: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK118(se)002:11853: de bas na chos thams cad nges don 'ba' zhig gi snying por gtan la phab nas /
NK118(se)002:11854: lhun grub snying po'i khams kyi dri ma bsal ba
NK118(se)002:11855: tsam las rgyu 'bras tha dad du mi 'dod pas
NK118(se)002:11856: 'dus ma byas rang snang ba'i dkyil 'khor du shes
NK118(se)002:11857: par byas nas / de dang rjes su mthun pa'i
NK118(se)002:11858: lam bsgom zhing bsten pas sbyang bya'i dri ma gzhi
NK118(se)002:11860: sbyang gzhi snying po'i don ji lta ba bzhin mngon
NK118(se)002:11861: du gyur pa mthar thug pa ni grub pa 'bras
NK118(se)002:11862: bu'i rgyud do // de la gzhi'i steng gi dri
NK118(se)002:11863: ma sbyong byed thabs sam lam gyi rgyud de gang
NK118(se)002:11864: bu'i rgyud do // zhe na / smin grol gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:11866: bla med kyi skabs 'dir dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur ba ste /
NK118(se)002:11867: sngar bshad cing 'chad pa las kyang shes par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:11868: grol byed lam gyi ngo bo ni /
NK118(se)002:11869: gzhi sgrib bral du byed pa'i thabs khyad par can te /
NK118(se)002:11870: sbyang gzhi snying po nyid sgrib byed du gyur pa'i
NK118(se)002:11871: sbyang bya glo bur gyi dri ma sbyong bar byed
NK118(se)002:11873: 'khrul pa'i chos las nyon sdug bsngal gyi rnam par
NK118(se)002:11874: shar ba'i rigs rgyun de nyid lam bde ba chen
NK118(se)002:11875: por bsgyur te sgom pa'i don no //
NK118(se)002:11876: bsgyur tshul kyang gang shar gyi rang ngo la bsal
NK118(se)002:11877: bzhag med par bskyangs pas de'i rang bzhin dag snang
NK118(se)002:11879: de'i phyir sngags kyi theg pa 'dir kun 'byung bden pa'i rang bzhin lam bden dang /
NK118(se)002:11880: sdug bsngal bden pa'i rang bzhin 'gog bden du snang
NK118(se)002:11881: bas 'bras bu lam du byed pa'i phyir spong 'gegs
NK118(se)002:11882: sbyong ba'i lam las khyad par du 'phags so //
NK118(se)002:11884: sbyang bya 'khrul pa glo bur ba kun brtags dang /
NK118(se)002:11885: sa bon gyi cha gnyis la ltos nas sbyong byed bskyed rdzogs gnyis gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:11887: ut+pat+ti kra ma'i sgra las drangs na /
NK118(se)002:11888: ut+pat+ti zhes pa bcos pa'am brtags pa la 'jug la /
NK118(se)002:11889: gang las bcos shing gdams pa'i gzhi ni rdzogs rim ste /
NK118(se)002:11890: de'i skad dod nish+pan+na kra ma zhes pa'i nish+pan+na ni
NK118(se)002:11891: ma bcos pa'am grub pa dang rdzogs pa la 'jug
NK118(se)002:11892: cing / gnyis ka'i kra ma ni rim pa ste thabs sam lam gyi go rim du gyur pas /
NK118(se)002:11893: bcos shing brtags pa rjes dpag gi lha'i rnal 'byor 'khor bcas la bskyed rim dang /
NK118(se)002:11894: bcos ma dang bral ba mngon sum pa'i lha'i rnal
NK118(se)002:11895: 'byor gyi lam 'khor bcas la rdzogs rim zhes bya
NK118(se)002:11896: ste / gsang snying gi rgyud phyi ma kha che 'gyur las /
NK118(se)002:11897: lha yi rnam pa'i sbyor ba yi //
NK118(se)002:11898: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK118(se)002:11899: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad //
NK118(se)002:11900: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK118(se)002:11901: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes byar brjod //
NK118(se)002:11904: skye 'phags gnyis kyi lam gyi gnas skabs las /
NK118(se)002:11906: dri bcas de bzhin nyid kyi snang ba gang zhig
NK118(se)002:11907: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur ba'i lha sku
NK118(se)002:11908: snang stong / dbye na bskyed rdzogs gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:11911: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa bcos shing
NK118(se)002:11912: brtags pa las byung ba'i lha sku snang stong bskyed
NK118(se)002:11914: de yang khyad par gyi chos bzhi ldan te /
NK118(se)002:11915: cho ga'i khyad par rgyud las gsungs pa'i bskyed chog tshang ba /
NK118(se)002:11916: rang 'bras kyi khyad par sngags kyi mthu bskyed nus pa /
NK118(se)002:11917: ngo bo'i khyad par zhu bde dang stong nyid kyi rang bzhin /
NK118(se)002:11918: byed las kyi khyad par dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11919: rdzogs rim gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK118(se)002:11921: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa'i bcos min
NK118(se)002:11922: gyi lha sku snang stong mi brtan pa rgyu'i rdzogs
NK118(se)002:11923: rim gyi dang / de brtan pa 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim gyi mtshan nyid /
NK118(se)002:11924: de yang rdzogs rim ni khyad par gyi chos gsum ldan te /
NK118(se)002:11925: rgyu'i khyad par rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa /
NK118(se)002:11926: byed las kyi khyad par rtsa rlung thig le dbu mar dag byed /
NK118(se)002:11927: rnam pa'i khyad par lhan skyes kyi bde ba stong
NK118(se)002:11928: gzugs dang ngo bo gcig tu gyur pa'i bde stong
NK118(se)002:11929: ngo // rdzogs rim rgyud la skyes zin nas bskyed rim la slob mi dgos pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:11930: 'phags lam gyi dus kyi bskyed rim zhes pa mi 'byung bas /
NK118(se)002:11931: rdzogs rim zung 'jug ye shes kyi mtshan nyid la /
NK118(se)002:11933: mi slob pa'i ye shes gnyis /
NK118(se)002:11935: 'phags rgyud kyi ye shes gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:11936: zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan du gyur pa'i lha sku kha sbyor /
NK118(se)002:11938: dag pa gnyis ldan gyi ye shes mthar thug gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:11939: kha sbyor la sogs pa'i yan lag bdun ldan te /
NK118(se)002:11940: longs spyod rdzogs dang kha sbyor bde chen rang bzhin med //
NK118(se)002:11941: snying rjes yongs gang rgyun mi chad dang 'gog pa med //
NK118(se)002:11942: ces pa'i don de ba tsan+d+rasa shes rab ye shes gsal bar /
NK118(se)002:11943: longs spyod rdzogs pa ni rnam pa thams cad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11944: kha sbyor ni stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug go //
NK118(se)002:11945: bde chen ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11946: rang bzhin med pa ni skye ba med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11947: snying rjes des gang ni mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'o //
NK118(se)002:11948: rgyun mi chad pa ni rgyun gyi rtag pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11949: 'gag pa med pa ni chad pa med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:11951: 'dir 'bras bu'i rdzogs rim yin pa tsam gyis gzhi
NK118(se)002:11952: lam 'bras gsum gyi zlas phye ba'i 'bras bu yin
NK118(se)002:11955: ye shes kyi sku 'grub pa'i so skye'i lam gyi rdzogs rim bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:11956: rim pa gnyis kyi dgos pa ni /
NK118(se)002:11957: snod bcud tha mal du 'dzin pa spang zhing /
NK118(se)002:11958: lam ma dag sa bdun dang 'bras bu gzugs sku'i rten 'brel sgrig pa /
NK118(se)002:11959: khyad par rang gi dngos 'bras thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub par byed pa ni bskyed rim dang /
NK118(se)002:11960: 'pho ba'i bag chags kyi dri ma spong zhing /
NK118(se)002:11961: lam dag pa sa gsum dang 'bras bu lhan cig skyes sku'i rten 'brel sgrig pa /
NK118(se)002:11962: khyad par rang gi dngos 'bras mchog gi dngos grub
NK118(se)002:11963: 'grub par byed pa ni rdzogs rim gyi dgos pa
NK118(se)002:11964: ste / snying po'i rgyud phyi ma kha che 'gyur las /
NK118(se)002:11965: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK118(se)002:11966: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas thob //
NK118(se)002:11968: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas so //
NK118(se)002:11970: gal te bum dbang dang de'i lam bskyed rim gyis kyang mchog gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:11971: de dang de sa bdun dang gzugs sku'i rten 'brel sgrig byed du bshad pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK118(se)002:11972: de ltar bshad kyang des de dngos su thob mi dgos te /
NK118(se)002:11973: dper na de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas chos sku thob pa'i rten 'brel bsgrigs kyang /
NK118(se)002:11974: de tsam gyis chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:11975: des na bskyed rim gyis sa bdun dang gzugs sku'i
NK118(se)002:11976: ring rgyu tsam byed kyang dngos rgyu byed pa mi
NK118(se)002:11977: srid cing / brgyud rgyu la'ang med na mi 'byung ba'i rgyu ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:11979: skye ba kun rdzob dang 'chi ba don dam bden
NK118(se)002:11980: pa lam du byas nas de dang de rdzogs par
NK118(se)002:11981: sbyong ba la ltos nas bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim
NK118(se)002:11982: bstan te / ye shes rdo rje kun las btus las /
NK118(se)002:11983: skye ba kun rdzob bden pa zhes bya ste //
NK118(se)002:11984: 'chi ba yang ni don dam bden pa yin //
NK118(se)002:11985: bden gnyis 'di la rnam par nges byas nas //
NK118(se)002:11986: bshad pa gnyis kyi dbye ba gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:11988: yang gnas lugs kyi lam la 'jug pa'i sngon du rgyud sbyang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:11989: byang nas gnas lugs dngos sgom pa la ltos nas kyang bskyed rdzogs gnyis su bstan te /
NK118(se)002:11991: rnam rtog bag chags kyis bcings la //
NK118(se)002:11992: thog mar rtog pa'i cho ga bstan //
NK118(se)002:11993: rnam rtog rang bzhin shes pa na //
NK118(se)002:11994: mi rtog pa la 'jug par bya //
NK118(se)002:11997: bskyed pa'i rim la legs gnas shing //
NK118(se)002:11998: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod rnams la //
NK118(se)002:11999: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK118(se)002:12000: skas kyi rim pa lta bur gsungs //
NK118(se)002:12002: da ni rim pa gnyis kyi lam ji ltar nyams
NK118(se)002:12003: su len tshul gyi sgo mdo tsam zhig bstan par
NK118(se)002:12004: bya ste / de la bskyed rim ni /
NK118(se)002:12005: sbyang bya 'khor ba'i chos sna tshogs par snang ba
NK118(se)002:12006: 'di dag srid par skye ba blangs pa la brten
NK118(se)002:12007: nas 'char bas 'khor ba'i chos kyi gtso bo skye
NK118(se)002:12008: gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun nas /
NK118(se)002:12009: bskyed rim sgom tshul bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:12011: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:12012: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK118(se)002:12013: spros can spros dang spros pa med //
NK118(se)002:12014: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK118(se)002:12015: zhes pas sgong skyes sbyong ba ni //
NK118(se)002:12016: dbang rtul spros pa can gyi dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:12017: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bde chen byang chub sems
NK118(se)002:12018: kyi ngo bor zhu ba'i 'od kyi thig le las
NK118(se)002:12019: zhu ba glus bskul gyis slar bzhengs te dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:12020: gyi 'khor lo spro ba bdag sras gzhan sras kyi
NK118(se)002:12022: nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi nang du rang lha'i
NK118(se)002:12023: phyag mtshan sa bon dang bcas pa zhu zhing 'dres
NK118(se)002:12024: pa las spro bsdus lhar bskyed pa mngon byang lnga'i
NK118(se)002:12026: de ltar yang sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las /
NK118(se)002:12027: rang byung dngos dang mi 'gal zhing //
NK118(se)002:12028: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK118(se)002:12029: ma lus dkyil 'khor thig le rnams //
NK118(se)002:12030: bdag gi sras su bsgom par bya //
NK118(se)002:12032: gang gis gang la gsol btab pas //
NK118(se)002:12033: thugs rjes byin brlabs sbyangs byas nas //
NK118(se)002:12034: thugs zhugs 'dres par dbyer med na //
NK118(se)002:12035: sras gyur dgongs pa ci la gnas //
NK118(se)002:12036: zhes pas gzhan sras bstan no //
NK118(se)002:12037: mngon byang lnga ni dgyes rdor las /
NK118(se)002:12038: zla ba me long ye shes te //
NK118(se)002:12039: bdun gyi bdun pa mnyam pa nyid //
NK118(se)002:12040: rang lha'i sa bon phyag mtshan ni //
NK118(se)002:12041: so sor rtog par brjod par bya //
NK118(se)002:12042: thams cad gcig gyur nan tan nyid //
NK118(se)002:12043: rdzogs pa chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK118(se)002:12046: dbang 'bring dang spros pa 'bring gi dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:12048: dang po stong pa byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:12049: gnyis pa sa bon bsdu ba ste //
NK118(se)002:12050: gsum pa la ni gzugs rdzogs pa //
NK118(se)002:12051: bzhi pa la ni yi ge dgod //
NK118(se)002:12052: ces 'chi srid bar do dang bcas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12053: dri za'i sems khu khrag gi dbus su zhugs pa /
NK118(se)002:12055: btsas nas dbang po yul la sad pa'i rim pa ltar rdo rje bzhi'i cho gas bskyed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12056: 'dus pa'i rgyud phyi ma las kyang 'di dang tshig don 'dra bar 'byung zhing /
NK118(se)002:12057: yang de las bsdus pa cho ga gsum bskyed dang /
NK118(se)002:12058: lha mnga' 'byin gyis bskyed pa gzhan sras kyi 'khor spro ba lta bu la sogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12059: de ltar sgong skyes dang mngal skyes sbyong ba'i sgom
NK118(se)002:12060: tshul gnyis po 'di ni gtso bor ma h+aa yo
NK118(se)002:12061: ga'i dkyil 'khor rim bskyed kyi lugs so //
NK118(se)002:12062: drod gsher skyes sbyong ba ni /
NK118(se)002:12063: dbang rab spros med kyi dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:12064: bskyed sngags brjod pa tsam gyis snod bcud dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:12065: gyi 'khor lor gsal la ma 'dres par sgom pa
NK118(se)002:12066: ste / 'di ni bang mdzod 'khrul lde las /
NK118(se)002:12067: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni //
NK118(se)002:12068: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas pas //
NK118(se)002:12069: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i lha ru sgom //
NK118(se)002:12070: zhes pa ltar gtso bor a nu yo ga'i bskyed tshul dang mthun pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12072: dbang po yang rab shin tu spros med kyi dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:12073: lha skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12074: 'di ni gtso bor a ti yo ga'i snang srid
NK118(se)002:12075: gzhir bzhengs kyi dkyil 'khor sgom tshul dang mthun te
NK118(se)002:12077: ye nas lhun mnyam dkyil 'khor la //
NK118(se)002:12078: yin par shes nas sgom pa las //
NK118(se)002:12079: tha dad blo yis rim pa yis //
NK118(se)002:12080: spyan drangs gshegs gsol 'dir mi dgos //
NK118(se)002:12082: de ltar sgom tshul bzhis skye gnas rang rang gi bag chags sbyong ba gtso bo yin na'ang /
NK118(se)002:12083: gang rung re res gzhan gsum gyi bag chags kyang zhar la sbyong bar nus te /
NK118(se)002:12084: dper na mngal skyes sbyong byed cho ga gsum bskyed lta bu la mtshon na /
NK118(se)002:12085: gdan gyi nyi zla ni khu rdul /
NK118(se)002:12086: sa bon ni khu khrag gi dbus su dri za'i sems 'jug par phyogs pa /
NK118(se)002:12087: phyag mtshan ni pha ma'i 'du 'phrod kyi 'gyur bas
NK118(se)002:12088: lugs ldog gi khams lnga myong ba'i rim pas 'jug
NK118(se)002:12089: cing khu rdul sems gsum 'dres pa /
NK118(se)002:12090: spro bsdu ni 'byung lngas lus rim gyis grub pa /
NK118(se)002:12091: sku rdzogs pa ni dbang po rgyas nas btsas pa
NK118(se)002:12092: rnams te gtso bor mnga' skyes sbyong byed yin kyang
NK118(se)002:12093: / zhar la sgong skyes kyi dus su gzhan 'dra ba las /
NK118(se)002:12094: khyad par spro bsdus yongs su gyur pa'i 'od kyi gong bu ni sgo nga /
NK118(se)002:12095: de las lhar bskyed pa ni sgong khyim brdol nas skye ba /
NK118(se)002:12096: de bzhin du nyi zla drod gsher /
NK118(se)002:12097: sa bon phyag mtshan bar do'i rlung sems /
NK118(se)002:12098: spro bsdu dang sku rdzogs pa de gsum 'dus pa
NK118(se)002:12099: las drod gsher gyi dbus nas 'byung bzhi'i lus grub
NK118(se)002:12100: pa / rdzus skyes la gdan skye gnas /
NK118(se)002:12101: sa bon phyag mtshan bar do'i rlung sems /
NK118(se)002:12102: spro bsdu ni gnas lus la sred len /
NK118(se)002:12103: sku rdzogs pa ni lus skad cig gis 'grub pa mtshon no //
NK118(se)002:12104: de ltar bcud kyi sems can skye rim bzhi dang
NK118(se)002:12105: mthun par lha sgom pa bzhin du snod kyi 'jig
NK118(se)002:12106: rten chags rim dang bstun nas rten gzhal yas khang
NK118(se)002:12109: snod kyi rim pa byung tshul gyis //
NK118(se)002:12110: rim brtsegs gzhal yas gzhung bzhin bskyed //
NK118(se)002:12112: des na yar sangs rgyas kyi sku dang zhing khams kyi rnam pa lam byed dang /
NK118(se)002:12113: mar 'khor ba'i snod bcud kyi dri ma sbyong tshul du /
NK118(se)002:12114: de dang de'i rnam pa dang mthun pa'i rten dang
NK118(se)002:12115: brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo rdzogs par sgom
NK118(se)002:12116: pa yin la / de ltar dag pa lha'i rnam
NK118(se)002:12117: pa bsgoms pas ma dag pa'i snang ba dbyings su
NK118(se)002:12119: sgrub thabs kun tu bzang po las /
NK118(se)002:12120: tha mal rnam rtog rgyun las gzhan pa yi //
NK118(se)002:12121: srid pa'i sdug bsngal ci yang yod ma yin //
NK118(se)002:12122: de dang rnam pa 'gal bar gyur pa'i sems //
NK118(se)002:12123: 'dis ni mngon sum du ni rtog par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:12126: sangs rgyas gnas gzhi rdzogs byas nas //
NK118(se)002:12127: kun tu bzang po'i bde ba dngos //
NK118(se)002:12128: rnam pa lnga po bsgoms byas te //
NK118(se)002:12129: rang lhag lha yi sgrub thabs bya //
NK118(se)002:12130: de bzhin dkyil 'khor rnam bkod la //
NK118(se)002:12131: mchod bstod bdud rtsi myang sogs pa //
NK118(se)002:12132: rim pa 'di yis bsgos byas nas //
NK118(se)002:12133: yan lag drug gi sbyor bar 'dod //
NK118(se)002:12134: ces pa ltar ye shes lnga byang sems dang drug
NK118(se)002:12135: sangs rgyas kyi sar mthar phyin par bya ba'i don
NK118(se)002:12141: bdud rtsi myang ba 'od dpag med de yan lag drug rdzogs sgom par bzhed do //
NK118(se)002:12142: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyis skye 'chi so sor sbyong bar
NK118(se)002:12143: bshad pa yang bskyed sdud kyi rim pa'i dbang du
NK118(se)002:12144: byas pa ste / gzhan du na /
NK118(se)002:12146: srid pa rim par smin tshul du //
NK118(se)002:12147: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK118(se)002:12148: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK118(se)002:12149: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK118(se)002:12150: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK118(se)002:12151: skyes pa'i rim pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK118(se)002:12152: zhes pas gtso bor rdzogs rim gyi sbyang bya bstan kyang /
NK118(se)002:12153: 'chi bar skye gsum gyi bag chags la phra rags gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:12154: rags pa de bskyed rim gyis sbyong bar byed pa'ang yin pas 'di ltar /
NK118(se)002:12157: phyag rgya gcig pa phra rags dang /
NK118(se)002:12159: tshogs sgrub ste sbyong byed cho ga yan lag lngas /
NK118(se)002:12161: skye ba la'ang dri za'i sems mnga' du zhugs te lus chags nas skyes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12162: lus rdzogs nas bu tsha 'khor 'dab rgyas pa /
NK118(se)002:12163: blo gros smin nas bcang ris dang khe grags sgrub pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12164: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum gyis bag chags sbyong /
NK118(se)002:12165: yar sangs rgyas chos longs sprul gsum phrin las dang
NK118(se)002:12166: bcas pa'i rnam pa lam byed kyis rigs kyi nus
