NK118(se)002:12167: pa gsos btab nas 'bras bur rdzogs par byed /
NK118(se)002:12168: lam gong ma 'od gsal las snying rje chen po'i
NK118(se)002:12169: 'phen pas zung 'jug gi lhar ldang ba'i smin byed
NK118(se)002:12170: du 'gro zhing / dam tshig pa la ye shes
NK118(se)002:12171: pa bcug ste gnyis su med par byas pas ni
NK118(se)002:12172: du 'gro zhing / / tshor ba dang 'du shes
NK118(se)002:12173: rdzogs nas rgan rabs rnams dang blo nus 'dra bar
NK118(se)002:12174: byas shing sangs rgyas thams cad ye shes mnyam nyid
NK118(se)002:12175: du gyur pa dang lam gong ma'i tshe lta ba
NK118(se)002:12176: 'khor 'das dbyer med dang rjes su mthun pa'i nyams
NK118(se)002:12178: de ltar mnyam gzhag tu dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo sgom pa de'ang /
NK118(se)002:12179: tha mal gyi snang ba ldog pa'i don du lha'i rnam pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12180: tha mal gyi zhen pa ldog pa'i don du lha'i nga rgyal la bslab cing /
NK118(se)002:12181: nga rgyal de yang bzung 'dzin gyi snang ba las
NK118(se)002:12182: 'das te yang dag pa'i ye shes su sgyur ba'i
NK118(se)002:12183: don du sgyu ma lta bur 'char ba la bslab
NK118(se)002:12184: dgos so // bla med kyi lugs 'dir bdag bskyed
NK118(se)002:12185: kyi ye shes pa mi gshegs pas mthar dam ye
NK118(se)002:12186: dbyer med kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal du bsdu zhing
NK118(se)002:12187: dgos so // ldang bas ni / 'phyis nyin mtshams
NK118(se)002:12188: sbyor ba la ltos pa'i srid pa phyi ma rnams
NK118(se)002:12189: kyi bag chags thams cad sbyong ba dang rang bzhin
NK118(se)002:12190: chos sku'i ngang nas 'gro don mdzad pa mtshon no
NK118(se)002:12191: dgos so // ldang bas ni / // de ltar
NK118(se)002:12192: bskyed rim de nyid lam gyi gtso bo yin la
NK118(se)002:12193: dgos so // ldang bas ni / // / des
NK118(se)002:12194: skyon ngag gi zhen pa ldog cing lha'i thugs rgyud
NK118(se)002:12195: bskul ba'i phyir bzlas pa bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12197: skyon bcu spangs te rnam gsum gyis //
NK118(se)002:12198: bzlas pa grangs bzhin rdzogs par bya //
NK118(se)002:12201: sgra chen ma yin chung bar min //
NK118(se)002:12202: mgyogs par ma yin bul bar min //
NK118(se)002:12203: drag por ma yin zhan par min //
NK118(se)002:12204: yig 'bru yan lag nyams pa min //
NK118(se)002:12205: yengs pas ma yin smra bzhin min //
NK118(se)002:12206: glal sogs bar du chod pa min //
NK118(se)002:12208: rnam pa gsum ni bzla tshul te /
NK118(se)002:12211: phra mo gsum gyi bzla lugs so //
NK118(se)002:12212: gzhan las ni ngag gi dang /
NK118(se)002:12215: rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang bzhi bshad de /
NK118(se)002:12217: spro bsdu'am dam tshig gi dang /
NK118(se)002:12220: gnyis pa ni lha'i rnam pa dran pas so /
NK118(se)002:12222: de kho na nyid tsam sems pas so //
NK118(se)002:12224: brjod pa dang ni dmigs pa dang //
NK118(se)002:12225: brdar gyur dang ni don dam mo //
NK118(se)002:12227: grangs tshad ni spyir btang gtso bo la 'bum dang 'khor la khrir bshad pa mang yang /
NK118(se)002:12229: rdzogs ldan dus na gcig bzlas pa //
NK118(se)002:12230: gsum ldan dus na nyis 'gyur bzlas //
NK118(se)002:12231: gnyis ldan dus na sum 'gyur bshad //
NK118(se)002:12232: rtsod dus bzhi 'gyur du ni bzlas //
NK118(se)002:12233: sngags kyi grangs ni bzhi po yis //
NK118(se)002:12234: rgyun mi chad par gsang sngags bzla //
NK118(se)002:12235: zhes pa ltar dmigs gsal med pa rnams la dus 'gyur rtsis nas bzla ba'o //
NK118(se)002:12236: gzhan yang las sgrub cing bar chad zhi ba'i phyir gtor ma dang /
NK118(se)002:12237: zas kyi bya ba bsod nams kyi tshogs su bsgyur ba'i phyir bza' ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK118(se)002:12238: spyod pa rnam par dag pa'i phyir thun mtshams kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK118(se)002:12239: gnyid dge bar bsgyur ba'i phyir nyal ldang gi rnal 'byor te /
NK118(se)002:12240: de rnams ni mnyam bzhag las langs pa'i dus kyi bya ba yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:12244: las tshogs sgrub pa sogs gtso bor phyi la gzhol ba'i gang zag gi nyams su blang bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12245: de dag gis bskyed rim gyi lus bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:12249: de yang bskyed rim spros bcas mthar phyin pa zhig
NK118(se)002:12250: gis tshogs kyis spyod pa'i nye rgyu la spyad na
NK118(se)002:12251: 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub chen po 'dod pa dang
NK118(se)002:12252: gzugs kyi rig pa 'dzin pa mchog gi bar du
NK118(se)002:12255: spyir pha rgyud du rim lnga /
NK118(se)002:12256: ma rgyud du phyag rgya bzhi /
NK118(se)002:12257: gnyis med kyi rgyud du yan lag drug ces grags pa las /
NK118(se)002:12259: ngag dben rdo rje'i bzlas pas rlung sbyangs shing /
NK118(se)002:12260: sems dben gyis sems sbyangs nas /
NK118(se)002:12261: bdag byin brlabs pa'i rim pa rlung sems tsam las grub pa'i ma dag pa'i rgyu lus sgom zhing /
NK118(se)002:12262: de nyid ril 'dzin dang rjes gzhig gis 'od gsal du sbyangs nas /
NK118(se)002:12263: de las dag pa'i sgyu lus zung 'jug gi skur mngon du ldang ba ste /
NK118(se)002:12265: rdo rje bzlas dang sems la dmigs //
NK118(se)002:12266: bdag byin rlobs dang 'od gsal dang //
NK118(se)002:12269: bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs las kyang /
NK118(se)002:12270: sngags sems sgyu lus 'od gsal dang //
NK118(se)002:12273: sgrub sde'i bde gshegs 'dus pa las ni /
NK118(se)002:12276: bkod pa byang chub kyi sems lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhis sgo gsum sbyangs nas /
NK118(se)002:12278: bcud thig le'i rdzogs rim ste lnga la rim lngar
NK118(se)002:12279: bshad pas 'di dang sgom tshul rnam pa mi 'dra'o
NK118(se)002:12281: rlung la dbang thob pas pad+ma can sogs phyi las kyi phyag rgya /
NK118(se)002:12282: nang dam tshig gi phyag rgya gtum mo //
NK118(se)002:12283: snang ba chos kyi phyag rgya sgyu lus /
NK118(se)002:12284: phyag rgya chen po 'od gsal dang lhan cig skyes sbyor ro //
NK118(se)002:12285: chos drug gi dbang du byas na /
NK118(se)002:12286: rmi lam sgyu lus kyi yan lag /'pho ba dang bar do gnyis phyi ma'i mtshams sbyor te /
NK118(se)002:12287: rtsa ba bzhi las yan lag gsum du phye ba'o //
NK118(se)002:12288: 'dir dam rgya gtum mo la byed pa na ro pa sogs kyi dgongs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12289: mnga' bdag mee tri pa 'bras bu zung 'jug la
NK118(se)002:12290: dam rgyar bzhed pa ltar na so skye'i gnas skabs
NK118(se)002:12292: gzhan yang ma rgyud du mchog gi dbyibs sngags chos gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:12297: bsam mi khyab kyi rim lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:12298: dpyid thig la sogs pa'i rdzogs rim mtha' yas so //
NK118(se)002:12300: nyin mtshan gyi rnal 'byor la brten nas shes pa
NK118(se)002:12301: yul la 'jug pa 'gags pas rtags bcu'i stong gzugs
NK118(se)002:12302: mngon du gyur pa sor sdud /
NK118(se)002:12303: gsal la ngos bzung med pa'i stong gzugs kyi rang zhal rig pa shes rab dang /
NK118(se)002:12304: de las rtags snang rang sems su myong ba'i rtog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12305: de nyid mtshan med du rig pa'i dpyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12306: de las lus sems la dga' bde dang /
NK118(se)002:12307: yul rig 'dres pa'i bde ba ste yan lag lnga dang ldan pa'i bsam gtan /
NK118(se)002:12308: g.yas g.yon dang steng 'og gi rlung ro gcig tu bsre ba srog rtsol /
NK118(se)002:12309: 'khor lo lngar bum can grub nas rlung sems dbu ma'i thig ler thim par byed pa 'dzin pa /
NK118(se)002:12310: phyag rgya gsum gang rung la brten nas byang sems
NK118(se)002:12311: 'dul sbyong gis dbang po'i sgor mi 'dzag pa rjes
NK118(se)002:12312: dran / 'pho med gsum gyis las rlung nyi khri
NK118(se)002:12313: chig stong drug brgya rim gyis 'gags pa'i dbye bas
NK118(se)002:12314: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'ang de snyed thob pa ni
NK118(se)002:12315: ting nge 'dzin gyi yan lag ste /
NK118(se)002:12316: dus 'khor rtsa rgyud dang gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK118(se)002:12317: so sor sdud dang bsam gtan dang //
NK118(se)002:12318: srog rtsol de bzhin 'dzin pa dang //
NK118(se)002:12319: rjes su dran dang ting nge 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:12320: sbyor ba yan lag drug tu 'dod //
NK118(se)002:12323: sbyor ba yan lag drug gis bsnyen //
NK118(se)002:12329: snang ba gsum du bstan pa'i lam //
NK118(se)002:12330: kun gzhi lus dang phyag rgya che //
NK118(se)002:12331: rgyu rgyud thabs dang 'bras bu'i rgyud //
NK118(se)002:12332: ces snang ba gsum dang rgyud gsum gyi dkri tshul
NK118(se)002:12333: sogs lam 'bras kyi rtsa tho yang rgyas par bshad
NK118(se)002:12334: cing / khyad par tshangs pa'i thog gi lam sbyang ba'i thabs /
NK118(se)002:12335: rlung gi gzhu la me yi mda' //
NK118(se)002:12336: byang sems ham gi 'ben la brdeg /
NK118(se)002:12338: bskyar ba'i sbyor ba med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12339: zhes pa 'adi'ang khrid yig rnams su bla ma'i gsung gis zhes lung khungs ma smos kyang /
NK118(se)002:12340: rgyud 'di'i brtag pa bcu bzhi pa nas 'byung ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:12341: gzhan yang ma mo'i rgyud lung dang glang po che
NK118(se)002:12342: rab 'bogs kyi bkol rgyud sogs las lam 'bras kyi
NK118(se)002:12343: gdams pa'i gnad gsal bar bshad pa lta bu ni
NK118(se)002:12344: dgyes rdor rang gi rgyud ding sang bod 'dir grags
NK118(se)002:12345: pa rnams kyi dngos bstan las gsungs pa ma mthong
NK118(se)002:12346: ngo // khyad par thun mong ma yin pa snga 'gyur la /
NK118(se)002:12347: rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ltar na /
NK118(se)002:12349: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK118(se)002:12350: zhes pas shes rab rnam par grol ba'i lam dang /
NK118(se)002:12351: thabs kyi nges pa'i lam gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:12354: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK118(se)002:12355: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK118(se)002:12356: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK118(se)002:12357: ces pas rgyu rgyud de bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ngos bzung nas /
NK118(se)002:12358: gzhi de ltar yin par yid ches par byas la ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgrubs pas /
NK118(se)002:12359: gzhi ji lta ba bzhin mngon du snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:12362: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK118(se)002:12364: bar chad med sgrub rnam par smin //
NK118(se)002:12365: dbang sgyur phyag rgya lhun grub lam //
NK118(se)002:12366: mngon byas rim pa brjod par bya //
NK118(se)002:12367: zhes pas gzhi rgyud rang gnas kyi ye shes nyid gtan tshigs rnams kyis gtan la phebs pas /
NK118(se)002:12368: der mthong ni rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK118(se)002:12369: de ltar rtogs nas rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bsgom ste /
NK118(se)002:12370: sgo gsum gyi bya ba btang nas /
NK118(se)002:12371: 'jog thabs gnyis gang rung gis don dam 'od gsal
NK118(se)002:12372: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin mtshan mo'i
NK118(se)002:12373: gnyid 'thug gi 'od gsal dang sbrel te /
NK118(se)002:12374: mnyam par 'jog pa stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK118(se)002:12375: 'od gsal de'i ngang du sems 'gags pas stong gzugs
NK118(se)002:12376: kyi snang ba shar ba na nyin dus sad pa'i
NK118(se)002:12377: snang ba dang mtshan mo rmi lam gyi snang ba
NK118(se)002:12378: thams cad sgyu ma chu zla ltar mthong ba las
NK118(se)002:12379: dmigs med bde chen gyi snying rje ma 'gags par
NK118(se)002:12380: shar ba snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK118(se)002:12381: snang ba ris med las snying rje chen po'i 'phen
NK118(se)002:12382: pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyi rkyen gyis zhu bde
NK118(se)002:12383: dang mtshungs ldan du byung ba'i bcos min zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:12384: gi lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12385: de las mched de snang ba thams cad zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:12386: gi lhar mngon sum du spro ba spros bcas kyi
NK118(se)002:12387: rnal 'byor la brtan pa thob nas /
NK118(se)002:12388: nye rgyu'i spyod pa gsum gang rung spyad pas zag
NK118(se)002:12389: med rig pa 'dzin pa'i lam la sbyor bar byed
NK118(se)002:12392: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK118(se)002:12393: me rlung 'gro ba nam mkha'i ba //
NK118(se)002:12394: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK118(se)002:12395: zhes 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi
NK118(se)002:12396: sbyor bas dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed pa steng sgo
NK118(se)002:12398: snying ga lte mgrin spyi bo'i 'khor lo bzhir /
NK118(se)002:12400: kun tu bzang mo'am bde chen thig le'i /
NK118(se)002:12402: khyab brdal chen po'i man ngag bzhi rtsa rgyud le'u bcu gsum pa las 'byung ba ltar bsgoms pas /
NK118(se)002:12403: dwangs ma'i dwangs ma rnams 'khor lo bzhi'i lte ba'i
NK118(se)002:12404: dwangs ma g.yo byed dang bral ba'i 'od gsal la
NK118(se)002:12405: tshur thim pas / bde gsal rnam par mi rtog
NK118(se)002:12406: pa'i ye shes chen po gcig dang du ma med
NK118(se)002:12407: pa'i chos nyid mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i 'od gsal
NK118(se)002:12409: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag khyad par can no //
NK118(se)002:12410: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ni /
NK118(se)002:12411: mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas dbab bzung ldog khyab
NK118(se)002:12412: kyi sbyor bas dga' bzhi lugs 'byung ldog gis bde
NK118(se)002:12413: stong gi ye shes skyed par byed pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12414: lung a nu yo ga las /
NK118(se)002:12415: kun rdzob byang sems kyi nyams len steng 'og gi
NK118(se)002:12416: sgo la brten nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes 'dren
NK118(se)002:12417: pa'i thabs rgyud dang babs 'dra ba las /
NK118(se)002:12418: thabs lam rang gi sems bcu /
NK118(se)002:12420: dpe btags bcu dang sbyar nas 'bras bu la bgrod
NK118(se)002:12421: par spyi mdo'i ljon shing gi le'u las gsungs shing
NK118(se)002:12422: / don dam byang sems kyi nyams len rten can
NK118(se)002:12423: snying ga'i thig le la rlung sems kyi dwangs ma
NK118(se)002:12424: thams cad thim ste dbyings rig gnyis med bde chen
NK118(se)002:12425: gyi ye shes 'char bas khams gsum bde ba chen
NK118(se)002:12426: por grol bar byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12427: rten med mi g.yo gsum ldan gyis rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang bskyangs pas /
NK118(se)002:12428: yul chos nyid don gyi ye shes dang /
NK118(se)002:12429: yul can chos sku gzhi'i ye shes dbyer med pa'i
NK118(se)002:12430: rig pa dbyings dang ye shes zung 'jug rtsa ba
NK118(se)002:12431: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor mngon du rtogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:12432: thabs don gyi rjes su 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor rgyas
NK118(se)002:12434: theg pa thams cad kyi rtse mo a ti yo ga ni /
NK118(se)002:12435: bla med kyi rgyud thams cad kyi dbang bzhi pa'i
NK118(se)002:12436: rdzogs rim mthar thug pa nyid rtsal du bton pas
NK118(se)002:12437: skal ldan shin tu dbang rnon gyi spyod yul te
NK118(se)002:12438: 'di ltar snang srid snod bcud kyi snang ba thams
NK118(se)002:12439: cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes brjod bral
NK118(se)002:12440: chos kyi skur gtan la phab nas bsal bzhag med
NK118(se)002:12442: rang byung gi ye shes dang de las shar ba'i
NK118(se)002:12443: chos thams cad ye grol rang dag chos nyid kun
NK118(se)002:12444: tu bzang mo'i klong las 'gro sa gzhan med par
NK118(se)002:12445: gtan la phab nas chos nyid dmigs med bya rtsol
NK118(se)002:12446: dang bral ba'i ngang du skyong ba klong sde /
NK118(se)002:12447: khyad par man ngag gi sde la phyi nang gsang ba yang gsang bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:12448: 'dir yang gsang bla med kyi dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:12449: sems gzhi med rtsa bral ka dag tu gtan la phab nas /
NK118(se)002:12450: snang sems thams cad ye grol sor bzhag chen po khregs gcod kyis nyams su len pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12451: lhun grub lus kyi dkyil 'khor de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang mdzod sgo phye nas /
NK118(se)002:12452: rang gnas kyi ye shes 'od gsal lhun grub kyi
NK118(se)002:12453: dkyil 'khor du zhal lta ba thod brgal snang bzhi'i
NK118(se)002:12454: lam bsgoms pas / chos nyid zad pa'i tshe phung
NK118(se)002:12455: khams skye mched thams cad rang dag nas thob pa
NK118(se)002:12456: gsum gyi gzer thebs pas shes rab rang byung gi
NK118(se)002:12457: sgron ma mngon du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:12458: mdor na de thams cad kyang rdzogs rim dngos dang btags pa /
NK118(se)002:12460: khyab bya dang khyab byed rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:12461: de yang rang byin brlabs kyi rim pa rtsa rlung sems gsum la brten pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12462: de dag gi rgyas gdab tu gyur pa brjod min
NK118(se)002:12463: lhan cig skyes pa'i rim pa phyag rdzogs kyi rnal
NK118(se)002:12465: de rnams kyis rdzogs rim gyi lus bstan pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12466: go ba'i chings tsam las rtsa rlung thig le'i gnas
NK118(se)002:12467: lugs dang nyams su len pa'i man ngag gi gnad
NK118(se)002:12468: rnams ni zab don gsang sgrogs su 'gyur gyi dogs
NK118(se)002:12469: nas 'dir zhib par ma smos so //
NK118(se)002:12472: khyod kyi srog chags bsad par bya //
NK118(se)002:12473: zhes sogs dgongs te gsungs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12475: phyal ba sogs lta ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:12476: bza' ba'i dam tshig la sogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12483: phyogs las rnam rgyal gyi spyod pa sogs ming dang dbye sgo mang yang don 'dra'o //
NK118(se)002:12484: de ltar sdom pa 'dzin tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:12486: lam sgom tshul gsum gyi sgo nas so so'i dbye ba phyed pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:12487: rgyud sde bzhi rang rang gi smin grol gyis lam
NK118(se)002:12488: la ji ltar dkri ba'i khog mdo tsam 'phros don
NK118(se)002:12489: du bkod nas / da ni gzhung gi dkyus nyid la 'jug par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12490: de yang 'dir ni rnal 'byor bla med kyi rnam bzhag nyid ston te /
NK118(se)002:12491: 'chad pa las shes par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:12492: gnyis pa rgyas bshad sngags sdom thob byed dbang bskur gyi cho ga la /
NK118(se)002:12494: gang bskur bya dbang bzhi'i rnam bzhag /
NK118(se)002:12495: de ltar bskur ba'i bral thob kyi yon tan /
NK118(se)002:12496: sngags sdom thob mtshams ngos bzung ba /
NK118(se)002:12497: dam tshig khas blang pa sogs rjes kyi bya ba'o //
NK118(se)002:12499: rdul tshon dang ni de bzhin b+ha ga dang //
NK118(se)002:12500: kun rdzob don dam byang sems dkyil 'khor bzhir //
NK118(se)002:12502: de la man+da la'i sgra las /
NK118(se)002:12503: man+da ni snying po'am bcud dang /
NK118(se)002:12504: la ni 'dzin pa'am len pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12505: snying po'i yon tan gyi gzhi 'dzin cing len par byed pas na dkyil 'khor ro //
NK118(se)002:12507: rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:12508: de las skabs don ding sang gi gang zag phal cher smin byed du rung ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK118(se)002:12510: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK118(se)002:12511: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan nam sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK118(se)002:12512: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK118(se)002:12513: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:12514: dang po gsum ni rim par slob dpon rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK118(se)002:12517: slob ma sa matha'i byang sems dang /
NK118(se)002:12518: mthong sgom dang tshogs sbyor gyi yon tan mthar phyin
NK118(se)002:12519: pa rnams la gang du dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:12520: du sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las bshad pas 'phags pa
NK118(se)002:12521: rnams kyi spyod yul yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:12522: de las 'dir sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor la lhag pa
NK118(se)002:12523: ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan zhes pa ni sgyu
NK118(se)002:12526: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam gnas pas //
NK118(se)002:12527: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gsum 'phro zhing //
NK118(se)002:12528: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor sogs //
NK118(se)002:12529: rdo rje'i thig tshad dor tsam gyis //
NK118(se)002:12530: rgyang grags la sogs mtshan ma yi //
NK118(se)002:12531: dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gsal ldan pa //
NK118(se)002:12532: ting 'dzin lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan yin //
NK118(se)002:12535: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa rjes mthun tsam thob
NK118(se)002:12536: pa yan chad kyi slob dpon mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK118(se)002:12537: pas / skal ldan gyi slob ma lhag pa gzugs
NK118(se)002:12538: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba yin la
NK118(se)002:12539: pas / / de la'ang gdul bya'i dbye bas /
NK118(se)002:12540: skal dman 'jug pa la rdul tshon /
NK118(se)002:12542: rab tshom bu lta bu dmigs rten cung zad tsam la brten nas bskur rung ba yod de /
NK118(se)002:12543: bka' brgyad bde 'dus kyi dbang chog rtsa bar /
NK118(se)002:12544: dkyil 'khor gang du dbang bskur na //
NK118(se)002:12545: rab 'bring tha mar gsungs pa yi //
NK118(se)002:12546: me tog bris sku rdul tshon gsum //
NK118(se)002:12547: dkyil 'khor gsum du dbang bskur ro //
NK118(se)002:12549: de las kyang blo che ba'i skal ldan kha cig
NK118(se)002:12550: thog ma nas slob dpon gyi lus dkyil du 'jug
NK118(se)002:12552: lus dkyil la dkyil 'khor du 'du shes pa'i gang
NK118(se)002:12553: zag mkhas pa des phyi dkyil bsten dgos pa'i nges
NK118(se)002:12555: de ltar yang slob dpon dril bu pas /
NK118(se)002:12556: bcos ma gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor gang //
NK118(se)002:12557: de ni gdul bya'i dbang las 'dod //
NK118(se)002:12558: mkhas pa'i bsgrub bya de ma yin //
NK118(se)002:12560: de lta bu'i mkhas pa des bsgrub bya'i yul ni /
NK118(se)002:12563: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12565: dong sprugs kyi 'jug pa'i me tog dor ba'i skabs su'ang //
NK118(se)002:12566: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK118(se)002:12568: de'ang spyir gang zag gi khyad par gyis ltos sa
NK118(se)002:12569: gnyis la ltos nas 'jug tshul gnyis su 'gyur te
NK118(se)002:12570: / rkyen sad tshul la ltos nas gang la mos
NK118(se)002:12571: pa der thog ma nas 'jug rung ba yin cing
NK118(se)002:12572: / / zhugs nas de dang mthun pa'i lam sgom pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12573: rgyud smin tshul la ltos nas gang zag thams cad rim gyis pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:12574: de yang tshe 'di kho na la brtseg dgos pa'i nges pa mi snang yang /
NK118(se)002:12575: 'dir skal dman rim 'jug gi gang zag sngar rgyud
NK118(se)002:12576: ma smin pa smin par byed pa'i dbang du mdzad
NK118(se)002:12577: nas / da ltar gyi bla ma dam pa rnams
NK118(se)002:12578: kyi phyag bzhes su rdul tshon dang ras bris kyi
NK118(se)002:12579: dkyil 'khor gang rung du dbang bskur bar bzhed do
NK118(se)002:12580: nas / // de la ras bris su smin byed kyi dbang bskur rung ba'i khungs ni /
NK118(se)002:12581: mi g.yo bla med kyi rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:12582: yang na dkyil 'khor bri bya ba //
NK118(se)002:12583: ras bris tshul du bri bar bya //
NK118(se)002:12584: dkyil 'khor sngar bzhin bris byas nas //
NK118(se)002:12585: dbus su mi g.yo mthing nag bri //
NK118(se)002:12586: zhes sogs ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor bshad nas /
NK118(se)002:12587: de dang 'brel ba nyid du slob ma dbang bskur gyi cho ga rgyas par gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:12588: slob dpon dza ya se nas kyang /
NK118(se)002:12589: rdul tshon bri bar ma nus na //
NK118(se)002:12590: dkyil 'khor dang mnyam ras la ni //
NK118(se)002:12591: nges par bcom ldan he ru ka /
NK118(se)002:12592: phyag rgya'i gzugs dang bcas pa bri /
NK118(se)002:12594: gnyis pa skabs don ding sang gi gang zag phal cher smin byed du rung pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK118(se)002:12595: dbang bzhi la ltos nas rgyu rten gyi dkyil 'khor bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:12596: bum dbang la phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rdul tshon nam /
NK118(se)002:12597: de'i zlas drangs pa'i chu tshon ras bris dkyil 'khor /
NK118(se)002:12598: mchog dbang gsum la spyir bdag gi de kho na nyid nang lus rtsa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK118(se)002:12599: khyad par gsang dbang la sngags kyi de kho na nyid yi ge b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor /
NK118(se)002:12600: sher dbang la lha'i de kho na nyid kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK118(se)002:12601: dbang bzhi pa la ye shes kyi de kho na
NK118(se)002:12602: nyid don dam byang chub kyi sems snying po ye
NK118(se)002:12604: de ltar yang dril bu pas /
NK118(se)002:12605: ri mor gnas pa'i las dang ni //
NK118(se)002:12606: thig dang tshon dgye'i rim pa bstan //
NK118(se)002:12609: b+ha ga dkyil 'khor zhes byar bshad //
NK118(se)002:12610: byang chub sems kyang dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK118(se)002:12611: lus ni dkyil 'khor nyid du brjod //
NK118(se)002:12612: dkyil 'khor gsum du gsungs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:12614: gsang ba'i dbang po thig le'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:12615: yan lag kun gyi sgom las 'das //
NK118(se)002:12616: rtog pas brtags pa rnam par spangs //
NK118(se)002:12617: thig le yi ge'i cha las 'das //
NK118(se)002:12618: de ni dkyil 'khor bla na med //
NK118(se)002:12621: dkyil ni snying po zhes brjod de //
NK118(se)002:12622: byang chub sems ni bde chen po //
NK118(se)002:12623: len par byed pas dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK118(se)002:12627: phyi ma gsum ni mchog dbang gsum gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:12630: rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa ste //
NK118(se)002:12631: zhes sngon la dkyil 'khor du bcug nas dbang bskur
NK118(se)002:12632: bar gsungs pa'i gang du gzhug bya'i dkyil 'khor ni
NK118(se)002:12634: gnyis pa gang bskur bya dbang bzhi'i rnam gzhag ni /
NK118(se)002:12635: bum pa gsang ba shes rab bzhi pa'i dbang //
NK118(se)002:12636: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i slob bur rim par bskur //
NK118(se)002:12637: zhes pa'i don la lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:12644: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi snod rung du sgrub pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:12646: bya byed las gsum gyis shes par bya ba ste /
NK118(se)002:12647: byed pa po rdo rje slob dpon gyis /
NK118(se)002:12648: las ni rgyud sbyangs pa'i slob bu snod ldan la /
NK118(se)002:12649: byed pa rdzas sngags ting 'dzin gsum 'dzom pa'i cho ga khyad par can gyis /
NK118(se)002:12650: bya ba slob bu'i rgyud byin gyis brlabs pa'i khyad
NK118(se)002:12651: par las sems rgyud la gnas pa'i rang skal gyi
NK118(se)002:12652: dri ma ci rigs dag pa'am nyams smad par byas
NK118(se)002:12653: shing / thob bya rang gnas kyi ye shes ci rigs gsos thebs pa'i mthus /
NK118(se)002:12654: lam rim pa gnyis kyi ye shes mngon du skyes
NK118(se)002:12655: sam skye nges kyi nus rung du smin par byas
NK118(se)002:12656: pas rgyud 'gyur ba'i khyad par gang yin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12657: de ltar yang he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:12658: gang gis gang la dbang bskur bas //
NK118(se)002:12659: rgyud dag nus pa thob phyir dbang //
NK118(se)002:12661: gal te dbang dus der ye shes dngos su ma skyes kyang /
NK118(se)002:12662: dbang gis smin pa'i tshad du 'gro ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:12664: ji ltar rma dang zas la de dag gis //
NK118(se)002:12665: gzag dang spyad du rung bas smin 'dod ltar //
NK118(se)002:12666: de phyir rten 'dir phyogs gnyis zhi ba dang //
NK118(se)002:12667: yongs su spyad pa nyid du smin par bstan //
NK118(se)002:12668: zhes phar phyin theg par rten de nyid la mthong spang spang rung dang /
NK118(se)002:12669: mthong lam skye rung la smin pa'i tshad du 'jog pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:12670: sngags bla med kyi theg pa 'dir zhugs nas bar chad med par bsgrubs pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK118(se)002:12671: tshe 'di nyid la spang bya spang rung dang thob
NK118(se)002:12672: bya mchog gi dngos grub thob rung gi nus pa
NK118(se)002:12673: thob pa'i phyir / des na dbang thob pa nyid rgyud smin pa'i tshad de /
NK118(se)002:12674: chu lud drod gsher 'dzom dus zhing la sa bon thebs pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:12677: mngon par gtor ba'am blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK118(se)002:12678: sbyang bya'i dri ma gtor zhing /
NK118(se)002:12679: lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa 'jog pa'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:12681: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)002:12682: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK118(se)002:12684: bzhi pa la rgyu lam 'bras bu'i dbang gsum las /
NK118(se)002:12685: rgyu dus kyi dbang ni dang por bla ma las dngos su blang dgos te /
NK118(se)002:12686: de smin byed kyi dbang gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:12687: de yin na lam sgom pa'i sngon du thob dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:12689: phyis bla ma las sam sdom ldan rang nyid kyis blangs kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:12690: sngar rgyud smin zin pa'i dbang gi rgyun de nyid gong 'phel du byed pa'i dbang yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:12692: slob lam rdzogs pa'i rgyun matha'i dus su bskur te /
NK118(se)002:12693: des mthar thug gi 'bras bur sbyor byed kyi dbang yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:12694: rgyu dus kyi dbang la'ang bzhir nges pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:12695: sbyang bya dri ma bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:12696: sbyong byed bskyed rdzogs bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:12697: sbyangs 'bras sku bzhir nges pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:12699: gsang ba shes rab dbang bskur ni //
NK118(se)002:12700: tshangs par spyod pas blang mi bya //
NK118(se)002:12701: zhes dgongs pa can gyi gsung sgra ji bzhin par
NK118(se)002:12702: bzung nas rab byung la dbang de dang de mi
NK118(se)002:12703: bskur zer ba mi rigs te /
NK118(se)002:12704: rab byung thams cad bla med zab lam gyi snod ma yin par thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:12706: dus 'khor las sngags kyi rten mchog dge slong yin par gsungs pa dang 'gal lo //
NK118(se)002:12708: gang gis bskur ba'i slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:12709: gang la bskur ba'i slob ma /
NK118(se)002:12710: ji ltar bskur ba'i cho ga'o //
NK118(se)002:12713: slob dpon mtshan nyid brtag pa ni //
NK118(se)002:12714: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK118(se)002:12715: brtan zhing dul la g.yo sgyu med //
NK118(se)002:12716: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor ba shes //
NK118(se)002:12717: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK118(se)002:12718: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK118(se)002:12719: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs byin //
NK118(se)002:12720: theg pa che la rtag dga' ba //
NK118(se)002:12721: de ni slob dpon yin par gsungs //
NK118(se)002:12723: de nyid bcu ni rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:12724: phyir bzlog gnyis kyi cho ga dang //
NK118(se)002:12725: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK118(se)002:12726: kha sbyor byed pa'i cho ga dang //
NK118(se)002:12727: gtor ma rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang //
NK118(se)002:12728: drag shul sgrub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK118(se)002:12729: rab tu gnas dang dkyil 'khor sgrub //
NK118(se)002:12730: gsang ba'i de nyid bcu yin no //
NK118(se)002:12732: stang stabs 'dug stangs bzlas brjod dang //
NK118(se)002:12733: sbyin sreg mchod pa las sbyor dang //
NK118(se)002:12734: slar yang sdud pa'i rnam pa ni //
NK118(se)002:12735: phyi yi de nyid bcu yin no //
NK118(se)002:12736: zhes nang dang phyi'i de nyid bcu gsungs pa bla
NK118(se)002:12737: med dang rgyud sde 'og ma'i slob dpon gyis shes
NK118(se)002:12740: dus dang grangs dang mtshan ma yi //
NK118(se)002:12741: bsnyen pa rab tu rdzogs pa gces //
NK118(se)002:12742: zhes mtshan dus grangs gsum gang rung gi bsnyen pa
NK118(se)002:12743: kha skong gi sbyin sreg dang bcas pa sngon du
NK118(se)002:12744: song ba'i slob dpon la slob bus gsol ba 'debs
NK118(se)002:12745: na snod brtags te rung na gegs sbyang zhing bsrung
NK118(se)002:12746: ba byas la / rgyud sbyong ba'i man ngag kyang bstan nas /
NK118(se)002:12747: rang nyid lha la gnang ba zhu ba'i don du bsnyen pa kha gso ba la 'jug ste /
NK118(se)002:12748: 'di ni gzhan don gnyer ba'i slob dpon gyis 'da' mi rung ba'i dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:12750: dad brtson shes rab gtong phod che zhing sgom sgrub
NK118(se)002:12751: dang dam tshig la yid brton pa la sogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:12752: yon tan dang ldan pa ste /
NK118(se)002:12753: sgrub dang sgom la dga' ba dang //
NK118(se)002:12754: rtag tu bla ma la gus shing //
NK118(se)002:12755: dus gsum bla ma mchod byed pa //
NK118(se)002:12756: yon tan dang ldan slob ma yin //
NK118(se)002:12759: dad brtson brtul zhugs ldan pa snod //
NK118(se)002:12762: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:12763: dang po sa yi cho ga ste //
NK118(se)002:12764: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK118(se)002:12765: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK118(se)002:12767: nub dang po sa'i cho ga /
NK118(se)002:12769: gsum pa dngos gzhi'i cho ga'o //
NK118(se)002:12772: spyir gnam sa bar gsum gyi dpyad de sa'i gzhi la brtag pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12773: bye brag lto 'phye'i lto ba'i thad nas brkos la
NK118(se)002:12774: zug rngu bsal ba sogs kyis sa rang gi mtshan
NK118(se)002:12777: brtags pas rung bar mthong na snang ba dang mi
NK118(se)002:12778: snang ba'i sa bdag la rin 'jal zhing bden pa
NK118(se)002:12782: sbyang ba las me sngags phyag rgya //
NK118(se)002:12787: phyogs bzhi'i slob ma'i gsol gdab dang /
NK118(se)002:12788: slob dpon gyis mkha' khyab tu sad pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams bskul zhing bsdus nas /
NK118(se)002:12789: khro bo'i snyems pas bgegs la bka' bsgo zhing 'bar
NK118(se)002:12790: ba'i spyan dang rdo rjee'i 'gros kyis bskrad de sa
NK118(se)002:12791: gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlab pa'o
NK118(se)002:12794: seng ldeng phur bu sor brgyad pa //
NK118(se)002:12795: khro bor byin brlabs gdab par bya //
NK118(se)002:12796: zhes pas khro bcu'i phur bu phyogs mtshams brgyad dang /
NK118(se)002:12797: steng 'og gnyis shar gyi shar dang nub kyi nub tu gdab pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12798: de la dkyil 'khor khang pa rnying par rdul tshon
NK118(se)002:12799: la brten pa'i phyogs la'ang sa chog med pas chog
NK118(se)002:12800: mod / gnas khang gsar par ni ras bris la'ang sa chog byas na legs te /
NK118(se)002:12801: sa chog ni sa gzhi la dkyil 'khor bri ba kho na'i ched ma yin gyi /
NK118(se)002:12802: phyi nang gi bdud dang bar chad gzhom pa'i ched yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:12803: des na ras bris kyi phyogs la sa chog mtha'
NK118(se)002:12804: gcig tu mi dgos par 'dod pa la snying po
NK118(se)002:12805: med do // gnyis pa la lha bum slob ma'i sta gon gsum las /
NK118(se)002:12807: lha gnas so sor dri'i thig le tshom bu dang
NK118(se)002:12808: bcas pa bkod la lhar bskyed bstim mchod bstod dang
NK118(se)002:12809: snyan gsan dbab ste nam mkhar bteg nas bzhugs su
NK118(se)002:12810: gsol ba'o // 'di ni rdul tshon du ma zad ras bris kyi phyogs la'ang 'grub na legs te /
NK118(se)002:12811: snyan gsan dbab pa ni dkyil 'khor bri ba kho
NK118(se)002:12812: nar ma zad sgrub pa'i phyir yang yin pas so
NK118(se)002:12813: // de ltar gyi tshe man+dala lta bur tshom bu
NK118(se)002:12814: 'god pa'i phyag bzhes la 'brel med chen po'o zhes
NK118(se)002:12815: gsungs pa'ang don gyi gnad 'di ma rtogs pas nongs
NK118(se)002:12816: // pa yin no // bum pa sta gon ni /
NK118(se)002:12817: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bum pa lha grangs dang
NK118(se)002:12818: mnyam pa'am rnam rgyal dang las bum gnyis su bsdus
NK118(se)002:12819: kyang rung ste / chas su bcug la bum rdzas dang dri'i chus bkang ba bkod nas /
NK118(se)002:12820: rang rang gi lha'am rnam rgyal du dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs dang /
NK118(se)002:12821: las bum du las kyi lha gang yin bskyed bstim
NK118(se)002:12822: mchod bstod bzlas pa byas mthar 'od zhu bya ba'o
NK118(se)002:12823: // 'dir bla med spyi'i dbang du byas la /
NK118(se)002:12824: gzhan du snga 'gyur gyis mdo sgyu la sogs par las bum ni rdor dril /
NK118(se)002:12826: thig tshon dang bcas te yan lag rab gnas kyi cho ga zur du mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:12828: yol ba'i phyi rol du slob bus man+dala phul nas gsol ba btab pa la /
NK118(se)002:12829: spro ba bskyed cing nyan par bskul nas /
NK118(se)002:12830: ji ltar rigs pa'i sdom pa bzung ba rnams lhar
NK118(se)002:12831: bskyed de sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa la
NK118(se)002:12832: mchod / de nas dngos grub kyi mtshan ltas brtag pa'i phyir so shing dor ba dang /
NK118(se)002:12833: rmi lam brtag pa gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:12836: ku sha'i sngas stan rnams byin la /
NK118(se)002:12837: mi ldog pa'i don du chos kyang bshad nas /
NK118(se)002:12838: dngos gzhi rmi lam brtags la ngan na nang par bzlog pa'i cho ga bya ba rnams so //
NK118(se)002:12847: srad bu ring thung dkyil 'khor gyi nyis 'gyur la
NK118(se)002:12848: sbom phra sgo'i nyi shu cha dang ldan pa gnyis
NK118(se)002:12849: ye shes dang las kyi thig skud du byin gyis
NK118(se)002:12850: brlabs la / thig g.yog yum du gsal ba la gtad nas /
NK118(se)002:12851: thig chen brgyad bskor 'dug gi phyogs ma 'khrul bas steng gi nam mkhar ye thig gdab /
NK118(se)002:12852: de bzhin du sa la las thig cha dbye ba
NK118(se)002:12853: zlum bskor phyi nang dang bcas pa cho ga bzhin
NK118(se)002:12854: du bri'o // tshon gyis bri ba ni /
NK118(se)002:12855: rdul tshon dang lag pa byin gyis brlabs te thog mar dbus kyi phur khung dgang /
NK118(se)002:12856: de nas dbang ldan nas brtsams te rtsig pa sgo
NK118(se)002:12857: tshad gcig tsam bris pa 'phyis sbrel ba'i tshe pra
NK118(se)002:12859: thig ji ltar btab pa'i gzhi la tshon rim par bkye zhing /
NK118(se)002:12860: lha gnas rnams su rang rang gi gdan la so so'i sku phyag rgya chen po /
NK118(se)002:12862: thugs phyag mtshan nam rang mdog dang mtshungs pa'i thig le gang rung /
NK118(se)002:12864: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK118(se)002:12865: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK118(se)002:12866: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK118(se)002:12867: zhes pa'i rim pa ltar bris 'bur gang rigs 'jog pa'am tshon gyis bri bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12869: dkyil 'khor rgyan gyis legs par brgyan la dbang rdzas dang mchod rdzas rnams tshul bzhin du bsham pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12871: sbyor ba dkyil 'khor rab gnas dang /
NK118(se)002:12875: dkyil 'khor la sogs gang byas kyang //
NK118(se)002:12876: rab gnas ye shes mi ldan na //
NK118(se)002:12877: tshogs dang bri ba'i nus pa med //
NK118(se)002:12878: ces pa ltar rdul tshon du ma zad /
NK118(se)002:12879: ras bris kyi phyog la'ang dkyil 'khor gsar pa yin na rab gnas bya dgos so //
NK118(se)002:12881: bdag mdun tha dad pa'i sgrub tshul dang /
NK118(se)002:12882: tha mi dad pa'i sgrub tshul gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:12884: bdag mdun so sor bsgoms nas mi bsre bar tha dad du sgrub pa /
NK118(se)002:12886: thog mar bdag mdun so sor bsgoms pa bsres nas bum pa sgrub pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12887: thog ma nas bdag mdun bum gsum dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus te bsgoms la /
NK118(se)002:12888: bzlas pa'i tshe dzapa khang dbye ba'i cho gas so sor phye nas bzla zhing /
NK118(se)002:12889: khyad par bum pa la gzungs thag gtad de bzlas mthar 'od zhu bya ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:12890: yang bdag mdun so sor bsre ba'i phyogs la bdun
NK118(se)002:12891: bsres dang drug bsres sogs kyi tha snyad 'byung mod
NK118(se)002:12892: / rang lugs snga 'gyur ba'i phyogs la thog ma
NK118(se)002:12893: nas tha mi dad du sgom pa la phyag len
NK118(se)002:12895: dkyil 'khor gsar pa yin na rab gnas kyi tshe'am /
NK118(se)002:12896: ras bris rnying pa lta bu rab gnas mi dgos
NK118(se)002:12897: pa'i phyogs la dngos gzhi'i nyin dang po'i dus su
NK118(se)002:12898: / ting 'dzin dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK118(se)002:12899: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK118(se)002:12900: sngar sta gon gyi dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bteg pa
NK118(se)002:12901: gnyis bstim nas gsum bsres kyi tha snyad mdzad de
NK118(se)002:12902: / spyi mdo'i 'grel pa lung bstan ma las /
NK118(se)002:12903: de nas le'u bcu gnyis pa tshogs chen 'dus pa'i lugs kyi dkyil 'khor bri ba dang /
NK118(se)002:12907: mchod pa la sogs pa bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12909: gang ltar yang rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK118(se)002:12910: snang ngo der ma dag pa'i snod bcud kyi snang
NK118(se)002:12911: ba nub ste / rten dang brten par bcas pa'i
NK118(se)002:12912: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo 'char zhing zhen pas ma
NK118(se)002:12913: bslad par slob pa'i gnad kyis ting nge 'dzin bsgoms
NK118(se)002:12914: ba nub ste / la / mchod pa dang bstod pa sogs ci rigs par bya ba ste /
NK118(se)002:12915: de dag ni dkyil 'khor sgrub cing mchod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK118(se)002:12921: nus dang ldan pa'i ltas thob nas //
NK118(se)002:12923: zhes pas slob ma ji ltar 'jug pa'i cho gas bdag nyid zhugs te dbang blang ba'am /
NK118(se)002:12925: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK118(se)002:12926: ces pa ltar rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du 'jug
NK118(se)002:12927: pa'i tshul gyis rig pa'i me tog dor bas kyang
NK118(se)002:12928: bdag nyid 'jug pa'i go chod do //
NK118(se)002:12931: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK118(se)002:12932: zhes pa'i don la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:12933: phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12934: nang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12936: slob bu rnams dkyil 'khor khang pa'i phyi rol lam yol ba'i phyi rol du khrus byas /
NK118(se)002:12937: phyag dang man+dala sngon du 'gro bas gdong g.yogs te
NK118(se)002:12938: me tog gi phreng ba thogs la gsol ba gdab
NK118(se)002:12940: thun mong dang khyad par gyi sdom pa byin te /
NK118(se)002:12941: bden gnyis zung 'jug gi sems bskyed cing brtan par byas nas /
NK118(se)002:12942: dkyil 'khor khang pa'am yol ba'i nang du drang ba'i
NK118(se)002:12943: tshe sngags rgyas sgo bzhi phye nas las kyi rdo
NK118(se)002:12944: rjees khrid de tshad med bzhi'i 'jug pas zhus la
NK118(se)002:12947: sbyor ba dam la bzhag pa bzhis rgyud bsdams nas /
NK118(se)002:12948: dngos gzhi ye shes dbab pas bde stong gi ye
NK118(se)002:12949: shes dngos sam sne cung zad rnyed pa de nyid
NK118(se)002:12951: de nas lhag pa'i lha ngos 'dzin pa'i phyir me
NK118(se)002:12952: tog dor ba de nyid mgo bor bcings pas rigs
NK118(se)002:12954: mig phye nas dkyil 'khor bstan par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12955: de dag ni 'jug pa'i chos te /
NK118(se)002:12956: lha dang skal ba mnyam par byas pa'o //
NK118(se)002:12957: de ltar yang mnyam sbyor las /
NK118(se)002:12958: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yi //
NK118(se)002:12959: bsod nams rtag pa gang yin pa //
NK118(se)002:12962: gal te dam tshig dang sdom pa mi 'dzin pa
NK118(se)002:12963: sogs kyis dbang bskur du mi rung ba'i gang zag
NK118(se)002:12964: yin na'ang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa tsam zhig bya
NK118(se)002:12965: bar gnang ste / rtse mo las /
NK118(se)002:12966: gal te de ni snod min na //
NK118(se)002:12967: de la gzhug pa byin par bya //
NK118(se)002:12969: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i dkyil
NK118(se)002:12970: 'khor gyi rgyal po chen po 'dir ni ma lus
NK118(se)002:12971: shing lus pa med pa'i sems can gyi khams thams
NK118(se)002:12973: snod dang snod ma yin pa yongs su brtag par mi bya ste /
NK118(se)002:12974: gzhug pa tsam la mngon par zhen pas yongs su bzung bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:12975: de ci'i phyir zhe na sems can thams cad kyis
NK118(se)002:12976: mthong ba tsam gyi mod la phyir mi ldog pa
NK118(se)002:12979: dge ba'i rtsa ba ma bsags pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12980: rgyud yongs su ma smin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:12981: mos pa med pa mang du zin kyang mthong ba tsam gyis so //
NK118(se)002:12989: zhugs pa'i dkyil 'khor der dbang bskur bar man+dala sngon 'gros gsol ba btab la /
NK118(se)002:12990: dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su dbang stegs la slob bu bkod de /
NK118(se)002:12992: sku rdo rje sprul sku'i ngo bo bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang /
NK118(se)002:12993: de las sprul pa'i lha dang /
NK118(se)002:12994: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas spyan drangs pa'i lha ste /
NK118(se)002:12995: de thams cad kyang gdan gsum tshang ba'i rnam par bzhugs pa rnams kyis so //
NK118(se)002:12997: slob ma'ang dbang rdzas ltar rigs kyi lha so sor bskyed pa'am /
NK118(se)002:12998: yang na thams cad la lhag pa'i lha gang yin gyi rnam par bskyed pa gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:12999: snga 'gyur gyi dbang rnams su phyi ma ltar mdzad pa shas che /
NK118(se)002:13001: slob bu'i phung lnga dang nyon mongs pa lnga dag
NK118(se)002:13002: pa rigs lnga ye shes lngar byin gyis brlab pa'i
NK118(se)002:13003: phyir / dbang bskur ba po rnams kyis bum pa
NK118(se)002:13004: sogs dam ye dbyer med kyi rigs lngar bskyed pa
NK118(se)002:13005: dbang rdzas so so'i rnam par gyur pa nyid thogs
NK118(se)002:13006: phyir / te / sngags rgya ting 'dzin gsum dang ldan pas /
NK118(se)002:13007: bum chu spyi bor gtor zhing blugs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13008: dbu rgyan rigs lnga mgo la bcing ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13009: rdo rje lag g.yas su byin pa gsor zhing snying gar gtod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13010: dril bu g.yon du gtad pa dkrol zhing dkur 'dzin du 'jug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13011: me tog phog pa'i rigs kyi ming 'dogs pa ste rig pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK118(se)002:13012: dri bcas ye shes kyi khams thabs rdo rje sems
NK118(se)002:13013: dpa'i ngo bor byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir tha mal
NK118(se)002:13014: gyi spyod pa brtul nas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshul
NK118(se)002:13015: la 'jug pa rdo rje brtul zhugs kyi dbang thun
NK118(se)002:13016: mong dang / khyad par spyod pa'i brtul zhugs kyi
NK118(se)002:13017: dbang yod pa'i phyogs la de'ang bskur te slob ma'i
NK118(se)002:13018: mong dang / dbang drug go // de nas thabs
NK118(se)002:13019: byung rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang gi byin gyis brlabs
NK118(se)002:13020: te gzhan don gyi mthu dang ldan par bya ba'i
NK118(se)002:13023: phyag rgya sku'i dam tshig gsum byin pas phyi nang
NK118(se)002:13024: gi rdor dril kha sbyor las byung ba'i bde stong
NK118(se)002:13025: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ste bum dbang gi
NK118(se)002:13027: de'i yan lag tu rjes su gnang ba la sogs pa byin pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13028: de yang nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma rags pa sbyangs pas ye shes lnga thob par mos nas /
NK118(se)002:13029: phung po lnga gnas gyur thob pas 'bras bu rig
NK118(se)002:13030: lnga'i spangs rtogs kyi nus pa khyad par can rnams
NK118(se)002:13031: rig pa'i dbang lnga'i ngo bo dang /
NK118(se)002:13032: ye shes dang rdo rje lus mi shigs pa'i dri
NK118(se)002:13033: ma rags pa sbyangs nas gzung 'dzin dang gzung 'dzin
NK118(se)002:13034: rigs gsum gnas gyur thob pas thabs rdo rje sems
NK118(se)002:13035: dpa' dang thabs byung rdo rje 'chang gi spangs rtogs
NK118(se)002:13036: kyi nus pa khyad par can dag brtul zhugs dang
NK118(se)002:13037: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang gi ngo bo'o //
NK118(se)002:13038: de rnams kyi skabs kun tu bum chu'i bya ba
NK118(se)002:13039: rjes su 'gro bas bum pa'i dbang zhes bya zhing
NK118(se)002:13040: / bla med thun mong ba'i rig dbang lnga dang rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang 'di dag /
NK118(se)002:13041: sgyu 'phrul ba'i lugs kyi phan dbang dang nus dbang
NK118(se)002:13042: phyi ma gsum dang rim par dod mtshungs pa tsam
NK118(se)002:13043: yin mod / 'on kyang de dang de'i dod thub pa ni ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:13044: bla med thun mong ba'i lugs 'di'i bum dbang gi
NK118(se)002:13045: sbyang bya phung lnga dang nyon mongs lnga sogs theg
NK118(se)002:13046: pa spyi la grags pa ltar yin la /
NK118(se)002:13047: sgyu 'phrul ba'i lugs ni lam rim las /
NK118(se)002:13048: gnas rten rtsa dang thig le la //
NK118(se)002:13049: bcu dbang lnga gsum dbang rnams ldan //
NK118(se)002:13050: zhes phan nus gnyis kyang zab dbang ltar rlung sems
NK118(se)002:13051: rtsa dang thig le la brten pa'i lus dkyil zab
NK118(se)002:13052: mo dang 'brel ba'i phyir khyad par che'o //
NK118(se)002:13054: nam phyed kyi dus su dkyil 'khor gyi lhor man+dala
NK118(se)002:13055: dang rig ma mtshan ldan phul la gsol ba btab
NK118(se)002:13056: nas / gsung rdo rje longs spyod rdzogs sku'i ngo
NK118(se)002:13057: bo bla ma yab yum gyi lus dang yi ge
NK118(se)002:13058: b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas thams cad spyan
NK118(se)002:13059: drangs te bcug pa rjes chags kyis zhu ba rdo
NK118(se)002:13060: rje nor bu nas byon pa'i bdud rtsi byang chub
NK118(se)002:13061: kyi sems dkar dmar ni skal med la bstan du
NK118(se)002:13062: mi rung bas gsang ba zhes bya la /
NK118(se)002:13063: de nyid slob bu'i lce thog tu byin pa ni dbang bskur ba ste /
NK118(se)002:13064: ster lugs yab yum gyi mkha' gsang las dngos su len pa thabs dang shes rab kyi gsang dbang /
NK118(se)002:13065: yum gyi mkhar lhungs pa yab kyi lces blangs pa las sam /
NK118(se)002:13066: mi nus na me long yu ba can gyis blangs
NK118(se)002:13067: te bdud rtsi dang sbyar nas ster ba ni gnyis
NK118(se)002:13069: de mgrin pa nas 'phel bas lus gang /
NK118(se)002:13070: chan la phabs kyis thebs pa ltar byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK118(se)002:13071: ngag mi shigs pa'i dri ma rags pa sbyangs /
NK118(se)002:13072: gsung rdo rje'i spangs rtogs kyi nus pa khyad par can bzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:13073: sems gsal stong brjod bral gyi ye shes su rtogs
NK118(se)002:13074: pas dbyibs la lhar zhen gyi rtog pa dang bral
NK118(se)002:13075: ba ni gsang dbang thob pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13076: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK118(se)002:13077: tho rangs dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su man+dala dang gsol ba btab nas /
NK118(se)002:13078: bla ma dang lha gnyis su med pa chos kyi
NK118(se)002:13079: sku thugs rdo rje yab yum kha sbyor gyi ngo
NK118(se)002:13081: kun rdzob byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor du rten shes rab ma gtad nas /
NK118(se)002:13082: sangs rgyas thams cad slob ma yab yum la bcug
NK118(se)002:13083: ste snyoms par zhugs pas brten pa khams zhu ba'i
NK118(se)002:13084: byang chub kyi sems rgyun yas 'bab dga' bzhi'i 'gros
NK118(se)002:13085: kyis phyin pa rdo rje nor bu'i bum par 'dzag
NK118(se)002:13086: med du bzung ste zhu bde nyams su myong ba'i
NK118(se)002:13087: rkyen las snang mched thob gsum gyi rim pas rang
NK118(se)002:13088: bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i 'od gsal bde ba chen
NK118(se)002:13089: po'i ngor shar bas yid byin gyis brlabs te /
NK118(se)002:13090: thugs rdo rje'i spangs rtogs kyi nus pa khyad par can thob pa ni dbang gi ngo bo ste /
NK118(se)002:13091: rten shes rab ma las brten pa dga' bzhi'i ye
NK118(se)002:13092: shes bskyed pas na shes rab ye shes kyi dbang
NK118(se)002:13093: zhes bya'o // dbang bzhi pa tshig dbang rin po che ni /
NK118(se)002:13094: bla ma ngo bo nyid sku ye shes rdo rje'i
NK118(se)002:13095: bdag nyid can las don dam byang sems kyi dkyil
NK118(se)002:13097: de'ang sngar dbang gsum pa'i dus kyi yas babs kyi
NK118(se)002:13098: dga' bzhi rdzogs nas thabs kyis ldog pa las mas
NK118(se)002:13099: brtan gyi dga' bzhi'i mthar nyams su myong ba'i ye
NK118(se)002:13100: shes dang / rang sems lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK118(se)002:13101: shes ro gcig tu tshig tsam gyi brdas ngo sprad
NK118(se)002:13103: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lhan cig skyes pa'i de
NK118(se)002:13104: kho na nyid sku dang ye shes zung du 'jug
NK118(se)002:13105: pa dbyer med bde ba chen po mchog gi ting
NK118(se)002:13106: nge 'dzin rgyud la skyes pa don gyi bzhi pa
NK118(se)002:13107: / ye shes ngos ma zin na las rgya la
NK118(se)002:13108: brten nas nyams myong 'dren pa brten can gyi bzhi
NK118(se)002:13109: / pa / de lam du goms par byed pa lam gyi bzhi pa /
NK118(se)002:13110: dga' bzhi'i 'gros re re la'ang dga' chung bzhi bzhir phye ba'i bcu drug gi /
NK118(se)002:13112: de nas re res sbyor mthong dang /
NK118(se)002:13114: tha ma bcu drug pa mi slob lam ste /
NK118(se)002:13115: yas babs rgyu dang mas brtan 'bras bu'i sa lam dang sbyar te /
NK118(se)002:13116: mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu drug pa'i mthar khu
NK118(se)002:13117: rdul steng 'og tu thim pa'i skad cig la rlung
NK118(se)002:13118: 'gags pas / de gsum gyi 'gyur ba myong ba'i shes rig kyang rgyun chad de /
NK118(se)002:13119: sku bzhi mngon du byed pa ni 'bras bu'i bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13120: de ltar yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK118(se)002:13121: gnas ni ye shes bcu drug po //
NK118(se)002:13122: tshogs sbyor la sogs dang po nas //
NK118(se)002:13123: mthar phyin sangs rgyas sa nyid de //
NK118(se)002:13124: gnas bzhi de bzhin dbye ba las //
NK118(se)002:13125: gnyis pa'i gnyis pa rab dga' sogs //
NK118(se)002:13126: pha rol phyin dang sa mtshan nyid //
NK118(se)002:13127: mtshungs phyir rdzogs par bshad pa yin //
NK118(se)002:13129: gsum pa de ltar bskur ba'i bral thob kyi yon tan ni /
NK118(se)002:13130: sad rmi gnyid 'thug snyoms 'jug gnas skabs bzhis //
NK118(se)002:13131: bskyed pa'i sgo gsum shes bya'i dri ma sbyang //
NK118(se)002:13132: bskyed rim gtum mo dpe don ye shes gnyis //
NK118(se)002:13133: sgom dang sku bzhi thob pa'i nus rung bya //
NK118(se)002:13135: dbang bzhi bskur bas dri ma gang dag na //
NK118(se)002:13136: bum dbang gis gnas skabs bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:13138: de'i snang ba lus phung sogs rags pa'i chos yin
NK118(se)002:13139: pas sgo gsum las lus kyi thig le'i sgrib pa
NK118(se)002:13140: dag cing / bdud bzhi las phung po'i bdud 'joms par byed do //
NK118(se)002:13141: de bzhin du gsang dbang gis rmi lam gyi gnas skabs dang /
NK118(se)002:13142: de yid ngor snang bas phra zhing /
NK118(se)002:13143: de nyid thig le rlung gis bskyod pa las snang
NK118(se)002:13144: ba'am brjod 'dod kyi rtog pa dang 'brel bas ngag
NK118(se)002:13145: gi thig le dang nyon mongs pa'i bdud /
NK118(se)002:13146: sher dbang gis gnyid 'thug gi gnas skabs dang /
NK118(se)002:13147: de tshogs drug rags pa 'gags pa'i rnam rtog yin pas yid kyi thig le dang /
NK118(se)002:13149: dbang bzhi pas snyoms 'jug gi gnas skabs dang /
NK118(se)002:13150: de 'dzag bde'i sred pa yin pas /
NK118(se)002:13151: sher sgrib ches phra ba 'pho ba'i thig le'i sgrib pa dang lha'i bu'i bdud de /
NK118(se)002:13152: de dang de dag cing 'joms par byed do //
NK118(se)002:13153: gzhan yang gser 'od dam pa las /
NK118(se)002:13154: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:13155: las kyi sgrib pa rnam par dag pas sprul pa'i skur snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:13156: ye shes kyi sgrib pa rnam par dag pas chos kyi sku snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:13158: thob bya sku bzhi ngo bo'i sgo nas dbyer med kyang /
NK118(se)002:13159: dag pa'i ldog cha nas de dang der btags pa ltar na /
NK118(se)002:13162: ye shes te shes bya'i sgrib pa la phra rags gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:13163: sher dbang gis shes sgrib rags pa /
NK118(se)002:13164: dbang bzhi pas shes sgrib phra ba 'pho ba'i bag
NK118(se)002:13165: chags kyi sgrib pa rnams gtso bor sbyong bar byed
NK118(se)002:13166: cing / der ma zad dbang dang po gsum gyis sgo gsum so sor sbyangs nas /
NK118(se)002:13167: bzhi pas cha mnyam sbyong bar bshad pa'ang snang ste /
NK118(se)002:13168: de'i cha mnyam ni khu rdul rlung gsum las 'khor
NK118(se)002:13169: ba'i lus ngag yid gsum dang bde sdug btang snyoms
NK118(se)002:13170: rnams 'char bas dkar dmar rlung la cha mnyam du
NK118(se)002:13171: 'jug pa'i sems dang bcas par 'pho ba'i bag chags
NK118(se)002:13172: la 'jog dgos pas gnad gcig go //
NK118(se)002:13173: lam gang sgom pa la dbang na /
NK118(se)002:13174: bum dbang gis phyi nang gi bskyed rim las tshogs
NK118(se)002:13175: dang bcas pa bshad sgrub nyan pa la dbang zhing
NK118(se)002:13176: yul snang stong zung 'jug tu 'char ba'i nyams skye
NK118(se)002:13177: bar byed / de bzhin du gsang dbang gis rang
NK118(se)002:13178: byin brlabs pa gtum mo dang sgyu lus sgom pa
NK118(se)002:13179: la dbang zhing sems gsal stong gi nyams skye /
NK118(se)002:13180: sher dbang gis las dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK118(se)002:13181: la brten pa'i dpe'i ye shes sgom zhing zhu bdes
NK118(se)002:13182: lus bde stong gi nyams skye /
NK118(se)002:13183: dbang bzhi pas don gyi ye shes phyag rdzogs sgom pa la dbang zhing /
NK118(se)002:13184: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin don dam 'od gsal
NK118(se)002:13185: mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po rang
NK118(se)002:13186: rig gi ngo bor pra phab pa ltar mthong ba'i
NK118(se)002:13189: dbang gi sa bon rgyud la thebs pa de lam
NK118(se)002:13190: rim pa gnyis kyis bskyangs pas dngos brgyud ci rigs
NK118(se)002:13191: kyi sgo nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku gsung
NK118(se)002:13192: thugs ye shes rdo rje'i bdag nyid sku bzhi thob
NK118(se)002:13193: pa'i nus rung du byas pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:13194: bzhi pa sngags sdom thob mtshams ngos bzung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13195: dang po gnas gsum rdo rje gsum bskyed nas /
NK118(se)002:13196: tha ma dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe //
NK118(se)002:13199: sdom pa skye ba'i dang po ni /
NK118(se)002:13200: slob ma'i lus ngag yid gsum rdo rje ga sum
NK118(se)002:13201: du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus nas 'go brtsams te
NK118(se)002:13202: / skyes zin pa'i tha ni rgyud sde bzhi rang
NK118(se)002:13203: rang gi dbang gi mtha' ba rten rdzogs zin pa'i
NK118(se)002:13205: rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la rang gi dbang dngos
NK118(se)002:13206: gzhi'i cho ga grub pa na rang rang la ltos
NK118(se)002:13207: pa'i slob dpon du dbang bskur ba rdzogs pas de
NK118(se)002:13209: bla med la bum dbang gi mthar bskyed rim gyi
NK118(se)002:13210: sngags sdom sogs dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs par thob
NK118(se)002:13211: pa'i tshe bskyed rdzogs rang rang la ltos pa'i sdom
NK118(se)002:13212: pa mtha' dag thob zin pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:13213: de'i tshe de 'dra ba de dbang rang rang la
NK118(se)002:13214: ltos pa'i rtsa ltung de dang de bskyed pa'i rten
NK118(se)002:13216: gang dag bla med kyi sngags sdom yongs rdzogs bum dbang dngos gzhi'i dus su thob zin pas /
NK118(se)002:13217: dbang gong ma gsum la dam tshig gsar thob re
NK118(se)002:13218: re las sdom pa gsar thob med do zhes gsungs
NK118(se)002:13220: bla ma btsal la dbang bzhi blang //
NK118(se)002:13221: de yis sdom pa gsum ldan 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:13222: zhes pa dang 'gal ba spang daka'o //
NK118(se)002:13223: lnga pa dam tshig khas blang ba sogs rjes kyi bya ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13225: khas blangs sdom dang dam tshig bslab la 'bad //
NK118(se)002:13227: de ltar snod dang 'tshams par dbang ji tsam zhig
NK118(se)002:13228: bskur ba de dang de'i cho ga rdzogs pa'i mtha'
NK118(se)002:13229: rten du dam tshig rgyas par bsgrags nas /
NK118(se)002:13230: bsdus te khas blang bas bzung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13231: bzung nas kyang sdom pa dang dam tshig gi blang
NK118(se)002:13232: dor rnams tshul bzhin du bslab pa la 'bad par
NK118(se)002:13233: bya zhing / gzhan yang yon stob pa dang dkyil
NK118(se)002:13234: 'khor gshegs bsdu sogs rjes kyi bya ba rnams so
NK118(se)002:13235: so'i cho ga bzhin du bya ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:13236: bzhi pa thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba la /
NK118(se)002:13239: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:13240: zhes pas sngags sdom dang por thob pa tsam gyis mi chog gi /
NK118(se)002:13241: de bar du mi nyams par bsrung ba'i lhag bsam khyad par can gyis bsrung bar bya dgos te /
NK118(se)002:13242: dam tshig dang sdom pa ni sngags kyi bslab pa thams cad kyi gzhi rten yin pas /
NK118(se)002:13243: de nyams na bslab pa thams cad don med par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:13244: dper na srog gi dbang po 'gags na dbang po thams cad 'gag par 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:13245: de bas na gsang snying las /
NK118(se)002:13246: sngags 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK118(se)002:13248: de yang bsrung thabs shes pa la rag las pas 'dir de bshad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:13249: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:13250: brtul zhugs nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK118(se)002:13252: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi /
NK118(se)002:13253: yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba /
NK118(se)002:13254: khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13255: dang po la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:13257: thog ma'i brtul zhugs dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK118(se)002:13259: thog mar dam tshig dang sdom pa thams cad kyi
NK118(se)002:13260: gzhi rten du gyur pa rdo rje sems dpa'i dam
NK118(se)002:13261: tshig gi yan lag brtul zhugs nyer lnga po 'di
NK118(se)002:13262: ni dus kyi 'khor lo las gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:13264: 'tshe dang mi ldan gzhan gyi bud med spang bya /
NK118(se)002:13266: de ltar srid pa'i bdag po dag gi brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK118(se)002:13268: 'di dag ye shes phab pa'i rjes su ster ba
NK118(se)002:13269: ni dbang dngos gzhi ma thob na'ang ye shes 'bebs
NK118(se)002:13270: pa'i rim pa dngos dang mos sgom gang thob kyang
NK118(se)002:13272: rgyas bshad la lnga tshan lnga las /
NK118(se)002:13273: dang po sdig pa lnga spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13274: gsod rdzun rku dang 'dod log chang 'thung ba //
NK118(se)002:13275: spang bya bslab pa'i gzhi lnga spang zhes gsungs //
NK118(se)002:13277: srog chags phra mo yan chad kyi srog gcod pa
NK118(se)002:13278: lta ci smos skad cig tsam mnar sems pas 'tshe
NK118(se)002:13280: rang 'dod kyis gzhan bslu ba'i bsam pas rdzun smra ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13281: dud 'gro yan chad kyis bdag tu bzung ba'i gzhan nor rku ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13282: gzhan gyis bdag tu bzung ba'i bud med bsten pa sogs 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13283: nyes pa bskyed pa'i gzhi chang gi btung bas myos
NK118(se)002:13284: par byed pa dang lnga ni 'khor ba'i gnas su
NK118(se)002:13285: 'ching byed dam po rdo rje'i zhags pa dang mtshungs
NK118(se)002:13286: shing rang gzhan gyi bde dge thams cad 'joms par
NK118(se)002:13287: byed pas na de rnams phyogs mthun char gtogs dang
NK118(se)002:13288: bcas pa spang bar bya dgos la /
NK118(se)002:13289: de lnga bsrung nus shing 'dod na brtul zhugs lhag
NK118(se)002:13290: ma nyi shu sbyin par bya ba yin pas bslab
NK118(se)002:13291: pa'i gzhi lnga zhes gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:13292: gnyis pa nye ba'i sdig pa lnga spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13293: cho lo kha na ma tho'i zas za dang //
NK118(se)002:13294: ngan tshig 'byung po lha min chos bslab pa //
NK118(se)002:13295: rnam pa lnga ni bya ba min lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:13297: sho dang mig mngas sogs cho lo rtse ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13298: bza' ba dang rin gyi don du bsad pa'i sha
NK118(se)002:13299: sogs kha na ma tho ba chos dang mi mthun
NK118(se)002:13300: pa'i zas za bas 'tsho ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13301: nyon mongs pa can gyis kun nas bslangs pa'i dmag
NK118(se)002:13302: 'khrug dang tshong gi gtam sogs ngag 'khyal sna tshogs
NK118(se)002:13303: pa'i tshig ngan smra ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13304: rig byed las byed pa'i pha mes kyi mtshun gsol
NK118(se)002:13305: ba sogs kyis spyod pa dang grol bar lta ba
NK118(se)002:13306: dang phyugs kyis mchod sbyin bya ba 'byung po'i chos
NK118(se)002:13307: dang / rang gis bsad pa'i sha ma gtogs las
NK118(se)002:13308: kyis shi ba'i sha mi za zhing gos dkar po
NK118(se)002:13309: dang bya gag gi btung ba 'ba' zhig bsten pa
NK118(se)002:13310: sogs lha min gyi chos lugs kla klo'i chos te
NK118(se)002:13311: dang / / bya ba ngan pa de rnams kyis
NK118(se)002:13312: dus 'das na dge ba'i phyogs nyams par byed pa'i
NK118(se)002:13313: dang / / phyir / nye ba'i sdig pa lnga
NK118(se)002:13314: zhes grags pa bya bar rigs pa ma yin pas
NK118(se)002:13316: gsum pa gsod pa lnga spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13317: ba lang byis pa skyes pa bud med dang //
NK118(se)002:13318: mchod rten bsnun pa gsod pa lnga ru grags //
NK118(se)002:13320: rkang pa dang po'i gsod pa bzhi po 'di rnams
NK118(se)002:13321: sngar gyi 'tshe ba'i nang du 'du na'ang 'dir logs
NK118(se)002:13323: mu stegs byed mang po zhig spyir 'tshe ba sdig
NK118(se)002:13324: pa yin kyang dge bar 'dod pa'i skabs yod pa
NK118(se)002:13327: mtho ris 'dod pa'i mchod sbyin gyi don du ba lang gsod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13328: ma mo mchod pa la byis pa gsod pa /
NK118(se)002:13329: mi'i mchod sbyin skyes pa'i don du skyes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13330: bud med kyi don du bud med gsod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13331: lha mi'i bla ma gsod pa zhes sangs rgyas sras
NK118(se)002:13332: bcas kyi sku gzugs dang bka'i glegs bam dang mchod
NK118(se)002:13333: rten rnams bsnun te bshig pa la gsod pa'i sgras
NK118(se)002:13334: btags pa 'di ni kla klo rnams chos su 'dod
NK118(se)002:13335: pa dgag pa'i don du ma zad shin tu sdig
NK118(se)002:13337: de ltar gsod pa lnga las ldog par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:13338: bzhi pa 'khu ba lnga spang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13339: dge grogs rje bo sangs rgyas dge 'dun dang //
NK118(se)002:13340: bla mar khong khro sgom rnams 'khu ba lnga //
NK118(se)002:13342: chos dang 'jig rten gang rung gis sbrel ba'i mnyam por 'grogs pa'i dge grogs dang /
NK118(se)002:13343: lugs gnyis kyis bkur bar 'os pa'i rje bo rgan rabs sogs dang /
NK118(se)002:13344: lha mi'i bla ma sangs rgyas dang /
NK118(se)002:13346: yid brtan par 'os pa'i yul mkhan slob sogs bla ma ste /
NK118(se)002:13347: yul lnga po de la khong khro sgom zhing 'khang ba ni 'khu ba lnga ste spang bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:13351: 'khu ba lnga lnga ste nyi shu po 'di rnams
NK118(se)002:13352: kyi 'phral spyod lam gyi sgo nas spang zhing ldog
NK118(se)002:13353: pa la 'bad par bya ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:13354: lnga pa chags pa lnga bsrung ba ni /
NK118(se)002:13355: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya yul lnga la //
NK118(se)002:13356: mig dang rna ba sna lce lus dbang lnga //
NK118(se)002:13357: zhen par mi byed brtul zhugs nyer lnga'o //
NK118(se)002:13359: mig gi dbang po yul gzugs la chags pa nas lus dbang reg bya la chags pa'i bar te /
NK118(se)002:13360: dbang shes kyi rjes su 'brang ba'i rnam rtog yul lnga la zhen pas chags pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13361: de rnams ni yang srid 'phen nus kyi las su rdzogs pas spang bar bya dgos mod /
NK118(se)002:13362: 'on kyang so skye 'dod khams pas rtsa ba nas ldog par mi nus na'ang /
NK118(se)002:13363: nyin re bzhin thun gsum la sogs par bcad nas gnyen po sgom pa la 'bad par bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:13364: gnyen po'ang bskyed rim gyis yul dbang lha skur bsgyur ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13365: rdzogs rim so sor sdud pa'i rnal 'byor gyis dbang po lnga yul lnga la 'jug pa gcod pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13366: de ltar brtul zhugs kyi gtso bo chags pa lnga spong thabs ni sor sdud yin la /
NK118(se)002:13367: de rdo rje sems dpa'i lam du bshad pa ltar
NK118(se)002:13368: 'dir yang srid pa'i bdag po rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK118(se)002:13369: brtul zhugs nyer lnga zhes rgyud 'grel las gsungs te
NK118(se)002:13370: / de dag las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pas dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:13371: sgo gsum de'i ngo bor son pa nyid kyis na brtul zhugs so //
NK118(se)002:13372: gnyis pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:13375: dang po la'ang bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:13377: thun mong gyur pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa lnga //
NK118(se)002:13379: 'di dag rnal 'byor phyi ma'i gzhung du bshad pa las don 'phags kyang sgra mthun par 'byung zhing /
NK118(se)002:13380: der ma zad smon 'jug gi sems bskyed dang tshul
NK118(se)002:13381: khrims gsum sogs theg pa chen po spyi'i bslab bya
NK118(se)002:13382: dang yang 'dra bar byung bas na thun mong pa
NK118(se)002:13383: ste / gzhi de las 'dir rdo rje theg pa mchog gi dgongs pa ltar 'chad par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:13384: de la rig bye brag pa'i rnal 'byor pas kyang rigs lnga ka'i sdom pa bsrung dgos mod /
NK118(se)002:13385: de ltar na'ang rang rigs gang yin gyi sdom pa
NK118(se)002:13386: la gtso bor bslab dgos pas rigs lnga so so'i
NK118(se)002:13387: sdom pa'am dam tshig tu grags so //
NK118(se)002:13388: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:13389: smon 'jug gnyis dang tshul khrims rnam pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:13390: slob pa sangs rgyas rnal 'byor sdom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13391: rdor dril phyag rgya bla ma bzung rdo rje //
NK118(se)002:13392: nor chos mi 'jigs byams sbyin rin chen 'byung //
NK118(se)002:13393: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg 'dzin pad+ma'i rigs //
NK118(se)002:13394: mchod gtor las rim 'dzin pa las kyi'o //
NK118(se)002:13396: de la thog mar de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs rnam snang gi sdom pa ni /
NK118(se)002:13398: smon pa dang 'jug pa'i sems bskyed nas /
NK118(se)002:13401: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims rnams so so'i mtshan nyid tshang bar brtan por bzung zhing /
NK118(se)002:13402: de thams cad kyi rten du thun mong ma yin
NK118(se)002:13403: pa'i dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba ste
NK118(se)002:13404: / sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad ni gtso bor sku'i rigs yin la /
NK118(se)002:13405: sku ni 'bras chos thams cad kyi rten yin pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:13406: spyir tshul khrims ni yon tan kun gyi rten gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:13407: sdom pa de thams cad kyi rten ni skyabs 'gro yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13409: ji lta dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK118(se)002:13410: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'i //
NK118(se)002:13411: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK118(se)002:13412: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13413: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK118(se)002:13414: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK118(se)002:13415: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK118(se)002:13416: so so brtan por bzung bar bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13417: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK118(se)002:13418: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK118(se)002:13419: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor las byung ba'i //
NK118(se)002:13420: sdom pa deng nas brtan por bzung //
NK118(se)002:13421: zhes khas blang bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13423: bde stong dbyer med kyi byang sems dang sems nya
NK118(se)002:13424: da gdod nas rnam par dag pa dkon mchog gsum
NK118(se)002:13425: gyi rang bzhin du bzung ba'o //
NK118(se)002:13426: de yang rnal 'byor phyi pa man chad dam rdo
NK118(se)002:13427: rje slob dpon gyi dbang mi bskur na rdo rje'i
NK118(se)002:13428: rigs sogs rigs gzhan gyi cho ga med kyang rung
NK118(se)002:13429: bar a b+ha y+aa ka ra bzhed do //
NK118(se)002:13430: de nas rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa'i sdom pa ni /
NK118(se)002:13431: phyi rdzas kyi rdo rje dang dril bu tshad dang
NK118(se)002:13432: ldan pa bzung nas rang nyid lha sku phyag chen
NK118(se)002:13435: de nyid kyis ni rdo rje bzung //
NK118(se)002:13436: chos kyi dril bu dkrol bar bya //
NK118(se)002:13437: dam tshig gis ni phyag rgya cher //
NK118(se)002:13438: byin gyis brlabs nas snying po bzla //
NK118(se)002:13440: nang gi rdor dril ni thabs yab kyi nor bu
NK118(se)002:13441: rdo rje dang shes rab yum gyi pad+ma dril bu
NK118(se)002:13442: ste / phyag rgya ni phan tshun rgyas btab nas mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK118(se)002:13443: de bzhin du gsang ba khams dkar dmar gnyis 'bar 'dzag gis zung du 'jug pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13444: de kho na nyid mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen dang
NK118(se)002:13445: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid ni rdor dril
NK118(se)002:13446: dang / de dag zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes kyi sku ni phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK118(se)002:13447: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid
NK118(se)002:13448: kyi rdo rje dang dril bu dang phyag rgya gsum
NK118(se)002:13449: 'dzin cing / de dag gi de kho na nyid
NK118(se)002:13450: phyin ci ma log par ston par byed pa'i rdo
NK118(se)002:13451: rje slob dpon yang bsnyen bkur la sogs pas chos
NK118(se)002:13452: kyi don du yang dag par bzung zhing bsten par
NK118(se)002:13453: 'dzin cing / bya ste / rdo rje rigs mchog chen po la //
NK118(se)002:13454: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK118(se)002:13455: yang bdag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13456: slob dpon dag kyang bzung bar bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13458: mi bskyod pa gtso bor thugs kyi rigs yin la /
NK118(se)002:13459: thabs shes khyad par can dang /
NK118(se)002:13460: de ston byed ni byang chub kyi sems kyi ngo bo dang /
NK118(se)002:13461: de'i lhan cig byed rkyen yin pas 'di las nam
NK118(se)002:13462: yang mi g.yo ba'i phyir mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig
NK118(se)002:13463: tu gzhag go // rin chen rigs rin 'byung gi dam tshig ni /
NK118(se)002:13464: phyi ltar na zang zing nor gyi sbyin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13466: mi 'jigs pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13467: de'i rtsa ba sems can thams cad kyis bla na
NK118(se)002:13468: med pa'i bde ba thob par gyur cig snyam pa
NK118(se)002:13469: byams pa chen po'i sbyin pa dang bzhi po nyin
NK118(se)002:13470: re bzhin yang dus drug tu sbyin par bya ba
NK118(se)002:13471: dang / nang ltar na sbas don rjes chags kyi
NK118(se)002:13472: mes byang sems dbab ldog gi dga' bzhi'i ye shes
NK118(se)002:13473: dang / sbyin pa ste / rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK118(se)002:13474: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK118(se)002:13475: nyin re bzhin yang dus drug tu //
NK118(se)002:13476: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK118(se)002:13478: de yang rin 'byung ni gtso bor rin chen rigs yin la /
NK118(se)002:13479: rin po che las dgos 'dod 'byung ba ltar sbyin
NK118(se)002:13480: pa bzhi yang dgos 'dod ster ba'i ngo bo yin
NK118(se)002:13481: pas / de nyid rin 'byung gi sdom par bzhag go //
NK118(se)002:13482: pad+ma'i rigs 'od dpag med kyi dam tshig ni /
NK118(se)002:13483: dngos bstan ltar na phyi nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13484: nang bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi theg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13485: gsang ba bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi theg pa dam pa'i chos ma lus pa 'dzin zhing /
NK118(se)002:13486: sbas don rlung dbu mar bcings pas gzhom med kyi gsung sgrub pa ste /
NK118(se)002:13487: byang chub chen po las byung ba'i //
NK118(se)002:13488: pad+ma'i rigs chen dag pa la //
NK118(se)002:13489: phyi nang gsang ba theg pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:13490: dam pa'i chos ni ma lus bzung //
NK118(se)002:13492: de nyid pad+ma'i rigs kyi sdom par 'jog ste /
NK118(se)002:13493: 'od dpag med gsung gi rigs yin pa ltar dam
NK118(se)002:13494: pa'i chos kyang dang por lung las brtsams pas gsung
NK118(se)002:13495: gi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13496: las kyi rigs don grub kyi dam tshig ni /
NK118(se)002:13497: phyi ltar na sngar gyi sdom pa de thams cad
NK118(se)002:13498: dang ldan pa'i steng du phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod
NK118(se)002:13499: pa dang gtor ma sbyin sreg sogs las kyi rim
NK118(se)002:13500: pa thams cad kyang ci nus su 'dzin cing /
NK118(se)002:13501: sbas don de thams cad zung 'jug e wam gyi
NK118(se)002:13502: sdom pas rgyas 'debs pa dang zhu bdes phung khams
NK118(se)002:13503: dbang yul gyi lha rnams tshim par mchod pa ste
NK118(se)002:13504: / las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK118(se)002:13505: sdom pa thams cad ldan par ni //
NK118(se)002:13506: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13507: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13509: de nyid don grub kyi sdom par 'jog ste /
NK118(se)002:13510: don yod grub pa ni las thams cad pa dang las rigs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13511: de dag kyang dus kyi 'khor lor rigs drug tu phye ste /
NK118(se)002:13513: 'dod pa'i rdo rje la ni rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya bla ma dag kyang bzung bar bgyi /
NK118(se)002:13514: rin chen la ni sbyin pa sbyin bgyi 'khor lo
NK118(se)002:13515: 'di la rgyal ba mchog gi dam tshig bskyang bar
NK118(se)002:13516: bgyi // ral gri la ni mchod pa bgyi ste
NK118(se)002:13517: gsal bar chu skyes rigs la sdom pa dag ni
NK118(se)002:13518: bgyi // bskyang bar bgyi // sems can rnams ni
NK118(se)002:13519: thar pa'i slad du rgyal ba bskyed mdzad rigs la
NK118(se)002:13520: byang chub bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK118(se)002:13521: zhes pa ltar rnam snang dang 'od dpag med ma gtogs phal cher 'dra ste /
NK118(se)002:13522: mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig gsum bzung ba rtsa bar bzhag nas /
NK118(se)002:13523: lhag ma rnams tshogs gsum gyis bsdus te /
NK118(se)002:13524: bsod nams kyi tshogs ni yul dman pa la brten
NK118(se)002:13525: pa rin chen rigs kyii sbyin pa bcu ster ba
NK118(se)002:13526: dang / yul mchog la brten pa las rigs kyi mchod pa sgrub pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13527: tshul khrims kyi tshogs ni pad+ma'i rigs la 'dzag med kyi tshul khrims sgrub pa dngos dang /
NK118(se)002:13528: de'i rgyur rnam snang gi rigs la sha lnga bdud rtsi bsten pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13529: ye shes kyi tshogs ni rdo rje sems dpa'i rigs
NK118(se)002:13530: kyi stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa'i byang chub
NK118(se)002:13532: 'o na rdo rje'i rigs tshogs gsum gang du 'du zhe na /
NK118(se)002:13533: dam tshig gsum la bskyed rdzogs kyi lugs so sor
NK118(se)002:13534: phye ba rim par bsod nams dang ye shes kyi
NK118(se)002:13535: tshogs dang / slob dpon gyi dam tshig ni tshogs gsum ka la sbyar ro //
NK118(se)002:13536: gnyis pa khyad par gyi rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni /
NK118(se)002:13537: khyad par srog gcod rdo rje'i rigs yin te //
NK118(se)002:13538: zhing bcu tshang dang rlung dang rtog pa yin //
NK118(se)002:13539: rin chen rigs la ma byin len pa ni //
NK118(se)002:13540: nor dang bud med theg chen zab mo'i chos //
NK118(se)002:13541: rang dang gzhan don sgrub la dgongs pas gsungs //
NK118(se)002:13542: pad+ma'i rigs la las chos dam tshig dang //
NK118(se)002:13543: phyag rgya che ste bud med bsten par gsungs //
NK118(se)002:13544: las kyi rigs la rdzun du smra gsungs pa //
NK118(se)002:13545: bdag dang sems can mi dmigs bden med ston //
NK118(se)002:13546: 'khor lo'i rigs la chang dang sha lnga dang //
NK118(se)002:13547: yul kun bsten gsungs phyi nang gsang ba'i theg /
NK118(se)002:13548: rim pa ma nyams spyod pa bla med lugs //
NK118(se)002:13550: 'di ni thun mong ma yin pa rnal 'byor bla med la gnas pa rnams kyi dam tshig ste /
NK118(se)002:13551: rten gyi gang zag rigs lnga so so'i rnal 'byor
NK118(se)002:13552: la brtan pa thob cing nus pa rnyed pas rang
NK118(se)002:13553: gzhan gyi don du 'gyur na sgra ji bzhin par
NK118(se)002:13554: spyod pa drang don bskyed rim pa'i dam tshig dang
NK118(se)002:13555: / sgra bsgyur te dgongs pa can du gsungs pa'i
NK118(se)002:13556: don de nyid sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa nges
NK118(se)002:13557: don gyi gsal byar byas te dbang gong ma'i dam
NK118(se)002:13558: tshig dang sdom pa rdzogs rim la sbyar bar bya
NK118(se)002:13559: ba yin pas na khyad par zhes bstan to //
NK118(se)002:13560: 'dir srog gcod pa ni zhe sdang rnam par dag
NK118(se)002:13561: pa rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig ste
NK118(se)002:13563: drang don ltar na zhing bcu tshang ba'i dgra bo
NK118(se)002:13564: drag po'i las kho nas ma gtogs 'dul bar mi
NK118(se)002:13565: nus pa rnams kyi las ngan gyi rgyun gcod phyir
NK118(se)002:13566: mngon spyod kyi las kyis bsad par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:13568: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed dang //
NK118(se)002:13569: bla mar smod brtson ma rungs dang //
NK118(se)002:13570: rtag tu sems can gnod brtson pa //
NK118(se)002:13571: mkhas pas sgrims te bsad par bya //
NK118(se)002:13573: de 'dra de srog bcad pa ltar snang yang rtogs
NK118(se)002:13574: goms kyi blo ngor gcad bya gcod byed bcad do
NK118(se)002:13575: ba'i 'du shes ma grub pas nye pas gos par
NK118(se)002:13577: yod med dbu ma mi dmigs shing //
NK118(se)002:13578: sgyu ma mig yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK118(se)002:13579: srog med srog kyang bcad du med //
NK118(se)002:13580: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK118(se)002:13582: nges pa'i don du srog ni ro rkyang gi rlung yin la /
NK118(se)002:13583: de bcad pa ni bum can la sogs pa'i thabs
NK118(se)002:13584: kyis bkag pas dbu mar srog rengs pa mthar thug
NK118(se)002:13585: gtsug tor du rlung sems brtan pa ste /
NK118(se)002:13587: srog rlung nges par 'gags pa na //
NK118(se)002:13589: byang chub sems ni 'gags pa yis //
NK118(se)002:13592: rnal 'byor pa kun sangs rgyas nyid //
NK118(se)002:13594: yang na srog ni rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pa'i sems yin la /
NK118(se)002:13595: de skye ba med par byas pa ni bsad pa ste /
NK118(se)002:13597: sems gcig srog chags gsod pa ni //
NK118(se)002:13598: gang phyir srog ni sems su brjod //
NK118(se)002:13600: ma byin par len pa ni nga rgyal rnam par
NK118(se)002:13601: dag pa rin po che'i rigs rin chen 'byung ldan
NK118(se)002:13604: drang don gzhan la phan par 'gyur na sngags kyi mthus gzhan nor 'phrog par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:13606: 'jungs pa rnams las nor blangs la //
NK118(se)002:13607: sems can bkren la sbyin par bya //
NK118(se)002:13608: de phyir mi yi bdag po dang //
NK118(se)002:13609: phyug po rnams kyi nor 'phrog go //
NK118(se)002:13611: de ltar ma byin par blangs pa ltar snang yang
NK118(se)002:13612: rtogs goms kyi blo la ltos nas nyes pas gos
NK118(se)002:13614: 'phrul dag'i lha'i longs spyod ltar rdzas dang nor bdag
NK118(se)002:13615: kyang bdag nyid las don la tha dad ma yin
NK118(se)002:13617: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK118(se)002:13618: 'phrul dag'i tshul te tha dad min //
NK118(se)002:13619: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:13620: blangs med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK118(se)002:13622: nges don la sngags kyi ye shes bsgrub pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:13623: pa ra stri'i sgra las mchog gam gzhan nam pha
NK118(se)002:13624: rol gyi bud med dgug pa'i thabs kyis /
NK118(se)002:13625: phrogs pa las byang chub kyi sems dkar dmar yang rlung gi stobs kyis ma byin par blang ste /
NK118(se)002:13627: btsun mo'i khu ba ma byin blang //
NK118(se)002:13628: gzhan gyi bud med rang mtshungs mdzes //
NK118(se)002:13630: yang na don dam pa'i btsun mo stong pa nyid yin la /
NK118(se)002:13631: de'i khu ba gnyis med kyi ye shes nyid gzhan
NK118(se)002:13632: gyis ma byin par rang gis lam bsgoms pa'i stobs
NK118(se)002:13633: kyis thob pas theg chen zab mo'i chos don gnyis
NK118(se)002:13634: sgrub pa la mnga' dbang 'byor ba ste /
NK118(se)002:13636: gang phyir theg pa chen po 'di //
NK118(se)002:13637: gang gis kyang ni byin ma lags //
NK118(se)002:13638: de nyid rtogs pas ma byin blang //
NK118(se)002:13640: phyag rgya bzhi bsten pa ni 'dod chags rnam par
NK118(se)002:13641: dag pa pad+ma'i rigs 'od dpag med kyi dam tshig
NK118(se)002:13643: 'dzag med kyi ye shes bsgrub pa'i phyir rdo rje las /
NK118(se)002:13644: sangs rgyas rnams kyi mnyes bya dang //
NK118(se)002:13645: dam tshig rnams ni bsrung ba dang //
NK118(se)002:13646: gsang sngags rig pas sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:13647: gzhan gyi bud med bsten par bya //
NK118(se)002:13648: zhes pas mchog gam pha rol lam gzhan gyi bud
NK118(se)002:13649: med kyi sgra phyag rgya bzhi ka la 'jug pas
NK118(se)002:13650: / rtogs goms kyi gdengs dang ldan pa'i gang zag gis gnyis med du shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13651: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi bsgom pa dang /
