NK118(se)002:13652: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum gyis zin pa'i sgo nas dngos rig las kyi phyag rgya bsten pa ste /
NK118(se)002:13654: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK118(se)002:13655: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK118(se)002:13656: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK118(se)002:13657: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK118(se)002:13659: de bzhin du yid rig chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK118(se)002:13660: gtum mo dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK118(se)002:13661: de gsum la bsten nas zhu bde dpe'i ye shes
NK118(se)002:13662: kyis 'dzag med sgrub pa gsum la drang nges gnyis
NK118(se)002:13664: mchog gi bud med rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong
NK118(se)002:13665: nyid dang mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen kha sbyor las
NK118(se)002:13666: lhan skyes mchog gi bde stong don gyi ye shes
NK118(se)002:13667: sgrub pa ni nges don nyid do //
NK118(se)002:13669: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan ma //
NK118(se)002:13670: stong nyid shes rab mdzes ma nyid //
NK118(se)002:13671: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK118(se)002:13672: de nyid ma bsten 'tshang mi rgya //
NK118(se)002:13674: rdzun smra ba ni phrag dog rnam par dag pa
NK118(se)002:13675: las kyi rigs don yod grub pa'i dam tshig ste
NK118(se)002:13677: drang don gzhan la phan par 'gyur na rdzun smra bar bya ste /
NK118(se)002:13679: sems can rnams la phan spyod pa //
NK118(se)002:13680: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK118(se)002:13681: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:13682: rdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK118(se)002:13684: de ltar rdzun smras pa ltar snang yang rtogs goms
NK118(se)002:13685: kyi blo la ltos nas nyes pas gos par mi
NK118(se)002:13686: 'gyur te / bdag dang sems can mi dmigs pas
NK118(se)002:13687: chos thams cad btags pa tsam las bden par ma
NK118(se)002:13688: grub par rtogs pa na de la ltos pa'i rdzun
NK118(se)002:13691: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK118(se)002:13692: ming dang tshig tu btags pa rdzun //
NK118(se)002:13693: rdzun nyid la ni rdzun spyod pas //
NK118(se)002:13694: rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK118(se)002:13696: nges don du sems can thams cad 'khor ba las
NK118(se)002:13697: bsgral bar bya'o zhes pa ni rdzun tshig smra ba
NK118(se)002:13698: ste / bsgral bya sems can dang sgrol bar byed
NK118(se)002:13699: pa po bdag kyang don dam par ma grub pa'i
NK118(se)002:13700: ste / phyir / de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:13701: 'jig rten bsgral ba zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)002:13702: rdzun gyi tshig ni rab tu bsgrag /
NK118(se)002:13704: 'jam dpal gyi bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK118(se)002:13705: bdag dang sems can mi dmigs la //
NK118(se)002:13706: 'khor ba las sgrol rdzun gyi tshig /
NK118(se)002:13709: snying ga'i 'khor lor rlung thim pas rang snang la
NK118(se)002:13710: gzhom med kyi sgra rnam pa thams cad par shar
NK118(se)002:13712: de las gzhan snang du sems can rnams la chos
NK118(se)002:13713: sgo sna tshogs pa cig car du ston pa drang
NK118(se)002:13714: don du gsungs pa'ang yod de /
NK118(se)002:13716: gang gis srog rlung zos pa na //
NK118(se)002:13717: cig car 'gro kun skad kyis ni //
NK118(se)002:13718: gang dang gang la de dang de //
NK118(se)002:13719: mthun pa'i chos ston rdzun pa'i tshig /
NK118(se)002:13721: sha lnga dang chang dang yul kun bsten pa ni
NK118(se)002:13722: gti mug rnam par dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK118(se)002:13723: rigs rnam snang gi dam tshig ste /
NK118(se)002:13725: drang don du rigs kyi dregs shing nga rgyal dang
NK118(se)002:13726: gtsang dme'i rtog pa gzhig pa'i slad du yul dbus
NK118(se)002:13727: su bza' ba'i don du gsod par mi byed pa'i
NK118(se)002:13728: sha lnga gnang ba ltar rang gi las kyis shi
NK118(se)002:13729: ba'i sha rnams dam tshig gi rdzas su rung bas
NK118(se)002:13731: myos pa'i skyon med na chang yang btung ste /
NK118(se)002:13733: de la ga bur rgyu yi phyir //
NK118(se)002:13734: sha ni bza' ba nyid du bya //
NK118(se)002:13735: khyad par du yang chang nyid do //
NK118(se)002:13737: de bzhin du bdud rtsi lnga dang gzugs sogs yul
NK118(se)002:13738: rnams la ci dgar spyod pa'i bde ba bsten pa
NK118(se)002:13739: rjes su gnang ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:13740: nges don du sha lnga bza' ba ni dbang po lnga'i dwangs ma 'ching ba /
NK118(se)002:13741: chang 'thung ba ni yas 'bab kyi lhan skyes zhu bde 'dzag med du 'ching ba /
NK118(se)002:13742: bdud rtsi lnga ni 'byung lnga'i dwangs ma bcings pa
NK118(se)002:13743: las zhu ba'i thig le rdul phra rab kyi tshogs
NK118(se)002:13745: yul kun bsten pa ni bshang gci khu ba'i dwangs ma lte bar lugs ldog tu brtan pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13746: yang na de dag bsten pa ni rnam par rtog
NK118(se)002:13747: pa thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su ro
NK118(se)002:13750: rnam rtog dang ni kun rtog gi //
NK118(se)002:13751: dngos dang dngos med sogs 'khrul pa //
NK118(se)002:13752: rnam rtog d+r+wa ba'i sa bon tshogs //
NK118(se)002:13753: rnam par mi rtog pa yis bza' //
NK118(se)002:13754: snying rje'i snod kyi mchog tu ni //
NK118(se)002:13755: ye shes chen po mnyam gzhag nas //
NK118(se)002:13756: btung zhing rtag tu btung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:13757: phyag rgya'i dam tshig ces su bshad //
NK118(se)002:13760: nges par rdo rje'i rigs la srog gcod bya ste ral gri la yang bden pa min pa'i tshig /
NK118(se)002:13761: rin chen la ni gzhan nor 'phrog bya mchog gi
NK118(se)002:13762: pad+ma'i rigs nyid la yang gzhan gyi bud med 'phrog
NK118(se)002:13763: / chang dang sgron ma sangs rgyas rnams dang bzang
NK118(se)002:13764: po'i yul rnams mtha' dag 'khor lo la ni bsten
NK118(se)002:13765: / par bya // g.yung mo la sogs mtha' dag
NK118(se)002:13766: bud med rnams ni gri gug la yang mkha' yi
NK118(se)002:13768: sems can don gyi slad du nor dang bcas pa'i
NK118(se)002:13769: lus 'di sbyin par bya ste khyod kyis bsrung mi
NK118(se)002:13770: bya // zhes drang nges phye nas gsungs pa ste /
NK118(se)002:13771: 'dir gri gug gi rigs la drang don bud med la mi smod cing rang lus gtong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13772: de nges don du 'dzag med kyi tshangs spyod la
NK118(se)002:13773: gnas par bshad pa ma gtogs gzhan lnga po phal
NK118(se)002:13774: cher don 'dra'o // de ltar dam tshig dang sdom pa de rnams kyi go rim yang /
NK118(se)002:13775: thog mar brtul zhugs nyer lnga bstan te /
NK118(se)002:13776: de'i lnga tshan dang po bzhi sems can la gnod
NK118(se)002:13777: pa shas che ba dang lnga pa yul la dbang
NK118(se)002:13778: po zhen pa'ang nyon mongs pa skye ba'i rgyu yin
NK118(se)002:13779: pas phyi mtshan nyid dang nang kri yog sde gsum
NK118(se)002:13780: gyi theg pas kyang don la spang dgos pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:13781: / de rjes rigs lnga'i dam tshig thun mong pa bstan te /
NK118(se)002:13782: de'i dngos bstan phyi bshad ltar na rnal 'byor rgyud kyi theg pa dang sgra mthun pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:13783: de rjes khyad par gyi rigs lnga'i dam tshig rnams bstan te /
NK118(se)002:13784: de'i drang nges kyi bshad tshul gnyis ka gsang ba
NK118(se)002:13785: bla na med pa rdo rje theg pa'i khyad chos
NK118(se)002:13786: yin pa'i phyir / des na gdul bya rnams 'jug
NK118(se)002:13787: pa'i go rim ma nyams pa'i sgo nas dkri zhing
NK118(se)002:13788: spyod pa ni rnal 'byor bla med kyi lugs su
NK118(se)002:13789: yin pa'i phyir / shes par bya'o // gsum pa
NK118(se)002:13790: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi la bstan bshad gnyis
NK118(se)002:13791: yin pa'i phyir / shes par bya'o // las / mdor bstan ni /
NK118(se)002:13792: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi bstan pa ni //
NK118(se)002:13794: de la spyir thun mong gi rang bzhin la /
NK118(se)002:13800: dbang bzhi so so la ltos pa'i rtsa ltung ngos bzung ba dang drug go //
NK118(se)002:13802: lus ngag yid gsum gyi nang nas yid gtso bor gyur pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:13803: mi dge ba gzugs can du 'dod pa sh+aakya'i sras ma yin par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13804: 'on kyang lus ngag grogs su dgos pa'i ltung ba'ang
NK118(se)002:13805: yod pas sgo gsum gyi bsrung bya zhes bya ste
NK118(se)002:13807: gsang sgor zhugs pa thams cad kyis //
NK118(se)002:13808: sgo gsum rang gi bsrung bya la //
NK118(se)002:13809: rgyal po'i bka' rtags ji lta bar //
NK118(se)002:13810: mi 'bral sdom pa de ngo bo //
NK118(se)002:13813: sngags bla med kyi sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs kyi nyes pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:13814: spyad na gang blangs pa'i sdom pa rtsa ba nas gtong byed kyi rigs gnas so //
NK118(se)002:13816: m+au la pat+ti'i sgra las rtsa ba'i ltung ba zhes pa ljon shing gi rtsa ba dang 'dra ste /
NK118(se)002:13817: brtan na yal ga lo 'dab rgyas shing bton na thams cad bskams par 'gyur ba ltar /
NK118(se)002:13818: bsrungs na lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad bskyed pa'i rtsa ba yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:13819: ma bsrungs na ngan 'gror ltung bas sdug bsngal gyi yang rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13821: nges tshig skyon yon skabs kyis sgyur //
NK118(se)002:13828: bsam pa'i yan lag dang lnga /
NK118(se)002:13830: gang zag sngags kyi sdom pa dang ldan zhing shes pa rang bzhin du gnas pa zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:13831: sdom pa dang mi ldan na rang bzhin gyi kha
NK118(se)002:13832: na ma tho ba tsam las bcas ltung mi bskyed
NK118(se)002:13833: pa'i phyir dang / dran pa nyams na ltung ba
NK118(se)002:13834: mi skyed par theg pa thams cad dgongs pa mthun
NK118(se)002:13835: pa'i phyir dang / pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:13836: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po gang la brten nas 'byung ba'i yul te /
NK118(se)002:13837: rtsa ltung dang po'i yul bla ma dam pa yin pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:13839: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi'am rgyu drug ste /
NK118(se)002:13840: rtsa ba'i sa bcad drug par 'chad do //
NK118(se)002:13842: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po gang rung yan lag tshang bar spyad na /
NK118(se)002:13843: yid kho nas rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba rnams thun
NK118(se)002:13844: mtshams gcig gi nang du gnyen pos ma slebs pa
NK118(se)002:13845: dang / ngag dang 'brel ba rnams pha rol po gang yang rung bas go ba dang /
NK118(se)002:13846: lus dang 'brel ba rnams bya ba de byas zin pa na rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba yin la /
NK118(se)002:13847: sgo gsum gang rung gcig la ltos pa'i rtsa ltung gcig byung zin nas /
NK118(se)002:13848: 'phyis cig shos de byas kyang rtsa ltung gnyis par mi 'gyur mod /
NK118(se)002:13849: nyes pa lci ba'i yan lag tu ni 'gro ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:13851: ltung ba so so'i yul de la de yin par 'du shes ma 'khrul ba'o //
NK118(se)002:13853: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:13854: de las mang mi dgos shing nyung na mi 'du ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:13856: sngags kyi dngos grub kyi rtsa ba bla ma dang /
NK118(se)002:13857: de la brten nas lung gi chos dang /
NK118(se)002:13858: chos sgrub pa'i grogs spangs pa sogs gnyen po sngags kyi go rim dang /
NK118(se)002:13859: snga ma snga ma lci zhing phyi ma phyi ma
NK118(se)002:13860: yang bas lci yang gi go rim yang yin no
NK118(se)002:13862: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi las gtso che ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK118(se)002:13863: ltung ba bcu gsum pa dang lnga pa rgyu 'bras
NK118(se)002:13864: su byas nas gsang dbang dang sher dbang gi dang
NK118(se)002:13865: / khyad par sher dbang gi bcu bzhi pa /
NK118(se)002:13866: dgu pa dang bcu gcig pa dbang bzhi pa'i /
NK118(se)002:13867: lhag ma dgu po bum dbang dang 'gal ba'i rtsa ltung yin zhing /
NK118(se)002:13868: dbang phyi ma phyi ma'i tshe na snga ma snga
NK118(se)002:13869: ma thun mong dang dbang rang skabs kyi de nyid
NK118(se)002:13871: des na bum dbang tsam thob pas rang gi dgu po spyad na rtsa ltung du 'gyur gyi /
NK118(se)002:13872: de la gzhan pa lnga la spyad kyang rtsa ltung dngos su mi 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:13873: de dag spong ba'i sdom pa ma thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:13874: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la bcu bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:13876: slob dpon rnam gsum snying nas smod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:13877: brnyas dang thugs dkrugs ltung ba'i sgo kun las //
NK118(se)002:13878: shin tu lci phyir 'di nyid dang por bshad //
NK118(se)002:13880: spyir slob dpon drug bshad pa sogs yod pas ltung
NK118(se)002:13881: ba byed pa po rang nyid sngags sdoom dang ldan
NK118(se)002:13882: pa dgos kyi / yul bla ma'i ngos nas sngags chos kho nas sbrel ba zhig mi dgos kyang /
NK118(se)002:13883: 'dir khyad par gyi slob dpon ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:13884: bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:13885: rgyud dgrol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK118(se)002:13888: man ngag byin pa'i bka' drin gsum ldan nam //
NK118(se)002:13889: gnyis ldan nam gcig ldan gang rung la /
NK118(se)002:13890: zhe sdang ngam phrag dog gi dbang gis snying thag
NK118(se)002:13891: pa nas sma 'bebs par 'dod pas gang gis 'khu
NK118(se)002:13892: zhing 'phya ba'i sgo nas smod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13893: bkur sti mi byed par brnyas pa sogs kyis thugs
NK118(se)002:13894: 'khrugs te mi mnyes par byas pa de ni rtsa
NK118(se)002:13896: rdo rje slob dpon ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo yin pas yul gnyan par ma zad /
NK118(se)002:13897: rang nyid kyi lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams
NK118(se)002:13898: cad de nyid mnyes pas rjes su bzung ba la
NK118(se)002:13900: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i nang nas nyes pa shin tu lci bas dang por bzhag ste /
NK118(se)002:13901: gang phyir rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK118(se)002:13902: dngos grub slob dpon rjes 'brang gsungs //
NK118(se)002:13903: de bas de la brnyas pa ni //
NK118(se)002:13904: rtsa ba'i ltung ba dang por bshad //
NK118(se)002:13906: des na ci mdzad yon tan du blta ba dang
NK118(se)002:13907: ci mnyes sgrub pa'i spyod pa la bslab par bya'o
NK118(se)002:13909: blang dor gnas ston bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' //
NK118(se)002:13910: bla mas gsungs shing rang gis go bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:13911: khyad gsod mi mthun spyod 'brel bka' 'das gnyis //
NK118(se)002:13913: gdul bya la blang dor gyi gnas ston pa sde
NK118(se)002:13914: snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'am drug gis bsdus pa'i
NK118(se)002:13915: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' thams cad dang /
NK118(se)002:13916: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i 'jug ldog gi bslab
NK118(se)002:13917: bya bla ma dam pas rang la 'doms par mdzad
NK118(se)002:13918: pa gang yin kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:13919: de dang des gsungs pa'i don go bzhin du khyad
NK118(se)002:13920: gsod kyi blos bka' las 'das te mi mthun par
NK118(se)002:13921: spyod pa'am / de dang 'brel ba gzhan la bshad kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:13922: dngos grub thams cad sangs rgyas dang bla ma'i bka'i rjes su 'gro zhing /
NK118(se)002:13923: de las 'das pa ni bla ma la brnyas pa'i
NK118(se)002:13924: 'og nas nyes pa che bas rtsa ltung gnyis par
NK118(se)002:13926: spyi ring nye dang nang 'dres spun la khros //
NK118(se)002:13927: 'khon 'dzin phrag dog brnyas sogs gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13929: yul ni spyi'i mched sems can thams cad /
NK118(se)002:13930: ring ba'i mched sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhugs so cog /
NK118(se)002:13931: nye ba'i mched sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa /
NK118(se)002:13932: de las kyang khyad par nang 'dres pa'i mched bla
NK118(se)002:13933: ma gcig gis bsdus pa pha gcig pa'i spun dang
NK118(se)002:13934: / de'i shugs kyis dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus pa ma gcig pa'i spun te /
NK118(se)002:13935: de bzhin snga ma snga ma las phyi ma phyi ma nye zhing /
NK118(se)002:13936: khyad par nang 'dres la'ang ma gcig pa las pha gcig pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13937: de gnyis ka gcig pa la'ang dbang thob pa'i dus snga phyi yod na spun rgan gzhon dang /
NK118(se)002:13938: dus gcig pa mtshe ma lta bu rnams phyi rim gyis nye la /
NK118(se)002:13939: de yang dbang bzhi ka rdzogs par thob pa'i spun rnams shin tu nye ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:13940: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK118(se)002:13941: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK118(se)002:13942: gang yang bdag las gzhan med cing //
NK118(se)002:13943: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK118(se)002:13944: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:13945: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK118(se)002:13946: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK118(se)002:13947: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK118(se)002:13948: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK118(se)002:13951: sems can kun gyi yid khyab par //
NK118(se)002:13952: rdo rje sems dpa' rang nyid bzhugs //
NK118(se)002:13953: de ltar bsam nas rnal 'byor gyi //
NK118(se)002:13954: dbang pos gang la'ang ba rnyas mi bya //
NK118(se)002:13956: sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs kyis rim pa rnam par gzhag pa las /
NK118(se)002:13957: bstan dang rdo rje'i theg pa la //
NK118(se)002:13958: zhugs pa thams cad spun du brjod //
NK118(se)002:13959: kun kyang ye shes ldan pas na //
NK118(se)002:13960: rdo rje sems dpa'i rdo rje'i spun //
NK118(se)002:13961: dkyil 'khor slob dpon rig ma gcig /
NK118(se)002:13962: dbang bzhi dag gi bye brag gis //
NK118(se)002:13963: nye dang khyad par bye brag go //
NK118(se)002:13965: de ltar spun de rnams la yid kyis khros shing
NK118(se)002:13966: 'khon zhe la 'dzin pa dang phrag dog gi bsam
NK118(se)002:13967: pas lus ngag gis brnyas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:13968: skyon brjod pas de'i sems sun phyung na rtsa ltung gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13969: de'ang nang 'dres pa'i spun yin na rdo rje nang
NK118(se)002:13970: dme yin pas shin tu lci zhing sbyang dka' ba'i
NK118(se)002:13972: sems can bde ba kun dang bral na bsam //
NK118(se)002:13973: snying nas byams pa btang ba bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13975: yul sems can gang yang rung ba bde ba dang
NK118(se)002:13976: bral zhing sdug bsngal dang 'phrad na ci ma rung
NK118(se)002:13977: snyam du khro bo'i bsam pas snying thag pa nas
NK118(se)002:13978: byams pa btang ba rtsa ltung bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:13980: 'dod chags sems kyis gnas skabs ma yin par //
NK118(se)002:13981: bsam zhing khu ba 'byin dang sems can la //
NK118(se)002:13982: byang chub sems bskyed btang ba lnga pa yin //
NK118(se)002:13984: bskyed rim pas sems can thams cad kyi don du
NK118(se)002:13985: rdzogs pa'i byang chub don gnyer gyi smon sems btang
NK118(se)002:13986: ba dang / de ma btang na'ang 'jug pa'i rtsa
NK118(se)002:13987: ltung thun mong ba spyad pas 'jug sems btang ba
NK118(se)002:13988: ba dang / spyi dang / khyad par gsang dbang
NK118(se)002:13989: gi lam pas skyug bro'i dbang gis thabs shes kyi
NK118(se)002:13991: shes rab ye shes kyi lam pas gsang dbang bskur
NK118(se)002:13992: ba'i rdzas dang bdud rtsi ril bu sgrub pa'i ched
NK118(se)002:13993: sogs gnang ba'i gnas skabs bdun ma yin par mi
NK118(se)002:13994: 'gyur ba'i bde ba la ma dad cing zhu bde
NK118(se)002:13995: 'gyur med la dgos med du bsams nas 'dod chags
NK118(se)002:13996: sam bslab pa khyad gsod kyis bsam bzhin du khu
NK118(se)002:13997: ba 'byin pas nor bu'i phyir lhungs na rtsa ltung
NK118(se)002:13998: lnga pa'o // de la gnang ba'i gnas skabs bdun ni /
NK118(se)002:13999: gsang ba'i dbang dang gsum pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14000: ro mnyam pa dang lha mchod dang //
NK118(se)002:14001: rigs brgyad spel dang ril bu dang //
NK118(se)002:14002: 'chi ltas brtag pa'i dus yin te //
NK118(se)002:14005: lam 'tshol mu stegs lam zhugs nyan rang dang //
NK118(se)002:14006: lam chen theg chen grub mthar smod na drug /
NK118(se)002:14008: mu stegs kyi grub mthar bshad pa'i dkar chos rnams
NK118(se)002:14009: kyang lam gyi rten mtho ris sgrub pas ngan 'gro
NK118(se)002:14010: las nges 'byung gi lam 'tsho ba'i phyir dang nang
NK118(se)002:14011: pa sangs rgyas pa las nyan rang ni 'khor ba
NK118(se)002:14012: las nges par 'byung ba'i lam la zhugs pa dang
NK118(se)002:14013: / mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba'i lam chen
NK118(se)002:14014: po la zhugs pa theg chen pha rol tu phyin
NK118(se)002:14015: / pa ste / de thams cad kyang gsang snying las /
NK118(se)002:14016: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK118(se)002:14017: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK118(se)002:14018: zhes sngags kyi theg pa'i lam stegs su 'gyur bas mthar thug theg pa gcig tu grub pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:14019: theg pa gong ma la drang ba'i ched sogs ma
NK118(se)002:14020: yin par mchog dman du bzung nas sdang sems kyis
NK118(se)002:14021: smad na rtsa ltung drug pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14022: de la 'dir gzhan gyi grub mtha' mu stegs pa'i dkar chos la ngos 'dzin pa ni /
NK118(se)002:14023: spyir mu stegs pa'i gzhung dkar chos ma yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:14024: der bshad pa'i dkar chos ni sangs rgyas pa'i yang
NK118(se)002:14025: dkar chos yin pas smad na ltung bar 'gyur dgos
NK118(se)002:14026: te / rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK118(se)002:14027: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK118(se)002:14028: mu stegs can la smad mi bya //
NK118(se)002:14031: grub pa'i mtha' yi blo bskyed phyir //
NK118(se)002:14032: phyi rol pa yang lam 'tshol zhugs //
NK118(se)002:14033: de phyir de la smad mi bya //
NK118(se)002:14034: lam zhugs nyan thos smos ci dgos //
NK118(se)002:14037: snod dang cho ga ma byas ma rdzogs dang //
NK118(se)002:14038: nyams dang zab mos 'jigs lngar gsang sgrogs bdun //
NK118(se)002:14040: snod kyis ma smin pa logs sred can dang /
NK118(se)002:14041: cho ga ma byas pas ma smin pa bum dbang ma thob pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14042: cho ga ma rdzogs pas ma smin pa mchog dbang gsum ma thob pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14043: nyams pas ma smin pa rtsa ltung byung nas 'gyod pas phyir mi 'chos dang /
NK118(se)002:14044: zab mos 'jigs pa nyan rang sogs dbang po ma smin pas zab don la skrag pa ste /
NK118(se)002:14045: de ltar yul rnam pa lnga la 'dul ba'i dus
NK118(se)002:14046: dang bstan bya de la ltos pa'i snod kyi skabs
NK118(se)002:14047: ma yin par gsang sngags kyi thun mong ma yin
NK118(se)002:14048: pa'i rdzas dang spyod pa dang chos zab don gyi
NK118(se)002:14050: des kyang go bzhin ma dad pa skyes na rtsa ltung bdun pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14052: phung lnga sangs rgyas lnga la brnyas pa yis //
NK118(se)002:14053: smon dang gdung ba bskyed na brgyad pa yin //
NK118(se)002:14055: rdo rje phung po yan lag ni //
NK118(se)002:14056: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK118(se)002:14057: zhes pa ltar phung po lnga'i rang bzhin rigs lnga'i
NK118(se)002:14058: sangs rgyas yin pa ltar dbang dus su ngo sprad
NK118(se)002:14059: nas / de 'dod yon gyis mnyes par mchod pas rten bde ba 'phel /
NK118(se)002:14060: des brten pa ye shes mngon du 'gyur ba yin pa las /
NK118(se)002:14061: phung po kun 'byung gi gtso bor bzung ste /
NK118(se)002:14062: lha'i khyad par sgrub pa sogs kyi dgos pa med
NK118(se)002:14063: par rang lus mi gtsang ngo zhes ngag gis smad
NK118(se)002:14064: cing sems kyis de ltar bzung nas brnyas pa'am yan
NK118(se)002:14065: lag gcod pa sogs kyi dka' spyad dang smyung gnas
NK118(se)002:14066: sogs dka' thub kyis lus la gdung ba bskyed par
NK118(se)002:14067: byed na rtsa ltung brgyad pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14069: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rang bzhin dag pa la //
NK118(se)002:14070: dkri bar the tshom za ba dgu par bshad //
NK118(se)002:14072: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis
NK118(se)002:14073: rnam par dag pas dbyer mi phyed pa'i zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:14074: 'od gsal byang chub kyi sems bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK118(se)002:14075: snying po gdod ma'i gnas lugs su bzhugs par bshad
NK118(se)002:14076: pa ni lam la dkri ba'i ched du spro ba
NK118(se)002:14077: bskyed pa tsam las don la de ltar ma yin
NK118(se)002:14078: snyam du the tshom za bas yid ma ches te
NK118(se)002:14079: ma dad na rtsa ltung dgu pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14081: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu tshang ba nus bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:14082: mi sgrol ba dang byams par byed na bcu //
NK118(se)002:14084: de la yul ni gsal bkra las /
NK118(se)002:14085: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK118(se)002:14086: dam nyams log dang 'khu ba dang //
NK118(se)002:14088: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK118(se)002:14089: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK118(se)002:14090: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK118(se)002:14091: zhes pas spyir bstan pa la gnod pa byed pa'i dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra dang /
NK118(se)002:14092: khyad par bla ma'i sku dgra dang /
NK118(se)002:14093: sngags kyi dam tshig nyams nas gso bar mi byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14094: sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa las phyir log ste spong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14095: bla ma dang mched la zhe sdang bas 'khu ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14096: sngags spyod la 'du bar mi dbang bzhin du rku thabs kyis 'dus pa'i nang du 'ongs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14097: sems can yongs la gnod pa'i las byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14098: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i dgrar gyur pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14099: mi dge ba'i las 'ba' zhig la 'jug pa'i spyod
NK118(se)002:14100: pa ngan pa'i ngang tshul can te sdug bsngal gyi
NK118(se)002:14101: rgyu la spyod pa dgu dang /
NK118(se)002:14102: sdug bsngal dngos la spyod pa ngan song gsum po gcig tu bsdoms pas bcu ste /
NK118(se)002:14103: de ltar bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa de rnams
NK118(se)002:14104: mngon spyod kyi las kyis sgrol bar nus bzhin du
NK118(se)002:14105: yal bar dor nas mi sgrol ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14106: de las kyang khyad par bla ma dang bstan 'gror
NK118(se)002:14107: 'tshe ba'i gdug pa can de dag log pa'i sred
NK118(se)002:14108: pas rang gi mdza' bor byas nas tha mal pa'i
NK118(se)002:14109: byams pa byed na rtsa ltung ste /
NK118(se)002:14110: des na lus ngag gi byams pa mi byed par ma zad /
NK118(se)002:14111: 'phral du bzod pa bsgom pa'ang mi bya ste /
NK118(se)002:14113: gdug pa rnams la bzlog ste bya //
NK118(se)002:14114: dngos sam yang na sngags dang gzhan //
NK118(se)002:14116: sman gyis kyang ni bya ba ste //
NK118(se)002:14118: der ma zad g.yo sgyus byams pa ltar ston pa
NK118(se)002:14119: kha 'jam la zhe gdug par byed na'ang rtsa ltung
NK118(se)002:14120: du 'gyur bar dus 'khor las bshad do //
NK118(se)002:14122: ming sogs bral la dngos dang dngos med rtog /
NK118(se)002:14123: rtog ges 'jal bar byed na bcu gcig pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14125: ming sogs mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba'i don dam bden pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14126: de rtogs pa'i thabs rnam par mi rtog pa'i lam
NK118(se)002:14127: la the tshom za bas so so rang rig las
NK118(se)002:14128: gzhan du rtog ge'i rigs pas dngos po'am dngos med
NK118(se)002:14129: gang rung du sgro 'dogs pas rtog cing zhen par
NK118(se)002:14130: byed na rtsa ltung bcu gcig pa ste /
NK118(se)002:14132: chos nyid tshad ni bzung mi bya //
NK118(se)002:14135: chos la tshad mas gzhal mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:14138: dad gsum ldan pa'i sems can don mi byed //
NK118(se)002:14139: sems mi bsrung dang bslu ba bcu gnyis pa //
NK118(se)002:14141: bla ma dang dkon mchog gi yon tan la dang
NK118(se)002:14142: ba dang 'dod pa dang yid ches kyi dad pa
NK118(se)002:14143: gsum dang ldan pa'i sems can chos 'dod cing sbyin
NK118(se)002:14144: du rung ba la mi ster ba lta bu de'i
NK118(se)002:14145: don byed nus kyang mi byed pas sam /
NK118(se)002:14146: de'i sems dang 'gal ba mi bsrung bar mi dad
NK118(se)002:14147: par rigs pa'i spyod pa bstan pa dang chags sdang
NK118(se)002:14148: gis skyon brjod pa'am g.yo sgyus bslus kyang rung ste
NK118(se)002:14149: / de nyid kyi sems sun phyungs nas dad 'dun log na rtsa ltung bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14151: skabs babs yo byad longs spyod dam tshig rdzas //
NK118(se)002:14152: dus tshod 'brel kyang mi sten bcu gsum pa //
NK118(se)002:14154: sngags kyi spyod pa'i dus su tshogs 'khor rim dpa'
NK118(se)002:14155: bo dang dpa' mo'i ston mo gang yin kyang rung
NK118(se)002:14156: ste / de dang de'i tshe brten pa skabs su
NK118(se)002:14157: babs pa'i dam tshig gi rdzas rdor dril gos rgyan
NK118(se)002:14158: sogs bcang ba'i yo byad dang /
NK118(se)002:14159: phyi nang gi sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga chang sogs bza' btung gi longs spyod dang /
NK118(se)002:14160: bro gar glu tshig rig ma sogs spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel kyang /
NK118(se)002:14161: nyan thos kyi brtul zhugs la 'chel ba la sogs pas the tshom za ba'am /
NK118(se)002:14162: mi gtsang ba dang nyes dmigs kyi bsam pas mi brten zhing spangs na rtsa ltung bcu gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14164: spyi dang bye brag la ltos shes rab ma //
NK118(se)002:14165: ngos lkog snying tshig smad go bcu bzhi pa //
NK118(se)002:14167: yul bud med gcig gam du ma'ang rung ste rigs 'ded pa'i sgo nas spyi dang /
NK118(se)002:14168: bye brag spyod pa'i dus yin na rang gi brten
NK118(se)002:14169: byar 'gyur nges la ltos pa'i bud med shes rab
NK118(se)002:14170: chos 'byung gi rang bzhin can de dag la ngos
NK118(se)002:14171: sam lkog tu zhe thag pa nas snying tshim pas
NK118(se)002:14172: brnyas thabs dang smod tshig brjod pa gzhan gyis go
NK118(se)002:14173: na rtsa ltung bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14174: de yang 'dir yul gyi bud med bla med kyi sdom ldan ma yin pa zhig dgos te /
NK118(se)002:14175: sngags sdom dang ldan pa'i bud med ni rang gi
NK118(se)002:14176: bla ma'am spun las mi 'da' bas rtsa ltung dang
NK118(se)002:14177: po dang gsum par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:14178: bzhi pa yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba la bstan bshad bsdu gsum las /
NK118(se)002:14180: da ni yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba bshad //
NK118(se)002:14186: sngags bla med kyi sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs kyi nyes pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:14187: spyad na sdom pa'i yan lag nyams byed kyi rigs gnas so //
NK118(se)002:14189: rtsa ba bcu bzhi dang rjes su mthun pas yan lag dang /
NK118(se)002:14190: sdom pa gtong byed kyi pham pa ma yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:14191: dngos grub myur du 'grub pa la gegs byed pa'i phyir lci bas sbom po zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:14192: shing gi yal ga chad na sbom po nyams pa
NK118(se)002:14193: las slar mi skye ba ma yin pa bzhin no
NK118(se)002:14195: sbom po'i ltung ba brgyad las /
NK118(se)002:14196: thog ma gsum rang rgyud smin byed kyi yan lag dang /
NK118(se)002:14197: phyi ma lnga gzhan rgyud smin byed kyi yan lag go //
NK118(se)002:14199: sbom po brgyad bshad pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14200: 'chad tshul gzhan rnam grangs su 'phros pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14202: dbang dang dam tshig ma smin rig ma bsten //
NK118(se)002:14203: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus su lus thang rtsod //
NK118(se)002:14204: ma gsungs rig mar rang stobs bdud rtsi len //
NK118(se)002:14205: snod ldan slob mar gsang sngags mi ston dang //
NK118(se)002:14206: dad ldan chos 'dri ba la chos gzhan ston //
NK118(se)002:14207: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK118(se)002:14208: rnal 'byor ye shes mi ldan sngags par rlom //
NK118(se)002:14209: snod min la bshad yan lag ltung ba brgyad //
NK118(se)002:14211: dbang gis rgyud ma smin cing dam tshig dang mi
NK118(se)002:14212: ldan pa'i rig ma bsten pa tsam las dang po'o
NK118(se)002:14213: // tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i gral du bla ma'am /
NK118(se)002:14214: rdo rje spun la mnar sems med par lus ngag
NK118(se)002:14215: gis rtsod rdeg dang kha shags tsam byas na gnyis
NK118(se)002:14216: pa'o // rgyud las gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid ma tshang
NK118(se)002:14217: ba'i rig ma phal pa las ril bu'am bde ba'i
NK118(se)002:14218: rgyur bdud rtsi cho ga bzhin du ma yin par
NK118(se)002:14219: rang stobs kyis len pa gsum pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14220: snod rung don du gnyer ba'i slob mar gsang sngags
NK118(se)002:14221: kyi chos dpe mkhyud kyis mi ston pa bzhi pa'o
NK118(se)002:14222: // dad ldan chos don gnyer gyis dus su 'dri
NK118(se)002:14223: ba la chos de mi ston par gzhan ston pa
NK118(se)002:14224: // lnga pa'o // sngags kyi lta spyod la skur
NK118(se)002:14225: pa 'debs pa'i nyan thos dngos sam rtog ge ba'i
NK118(se)002:14226: nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad pa drug pa'o
NK118(se)002:14227: // lnga pa'o // // gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor
NK118(se)002:14228: de kho na nyid kyi ye shes dang mi ldan
NK118(se)002:14229: par rang nyid sngags 'chang rdo rje 'dzin par smra
NK118(se)002:14230: zhing rlom pa ni bdun pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14231: nang gi snod ma yin pa'i gang zag 'dod cing
NK118(se)002:14232: don du gnyer ba tshogs bshad bstan bya'i yul la
NK118(se)002:14233: zab don dus ma yin par bshad pa brgyad pa'o
NK118(se)002:14234: // de dag kyang slob dpon dpa' bos /
NK118(se)002:14235: rab tu bde ba 'phrog byed pa //
NK118(se)002:14236: yan lag nyes pa nga yis bshad //
NK118(se)002:14237: dam tshig dag dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK118(se)002:14238: rig ma bsten par dga' ba ni //
NK118(se)002:14239: yan lag nyes pa dang po yin //
NK118(se)002:14240: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK118(se)002:14242: bsnyen sogs ma byas dbang rab las sogs 'jug /
NK118(se)002:14243: phyi chos mos la lus kyi phyag rgya bstan //
NK118(se)002:14244: sdom pa gnyis kyi bcas las dgos med 'da' //
NK118(se)002:14246: bsnyen sgrub ma byas par slob ma la dbang bskur
NK118(se)002:14247: ba dang rab gnas dang sbyin sreg gi las la
NK118(se)002:14248: bsam pas 'jug cing sbyor bas zhugs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14249: zab mo la skrag pa'i rigs ma yin kyang phyi'i
NK118(se)002:14250: chos la mos pa'i gang zag la dgos pa med
NK118(se)002:14251: par lus kyi phyag rgya bstan pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14252: sdom pa 'og ma so byang gnyis thob pa'i sngags
NK118(se)002:14253: pas phyi dro'i kha zas za ba lta bu de
NK118(se)002:14254: dang de'i bcas pa las tshogs 'khor dang sbyin sreg
NK118(se)002:14255: sogs dgos pa khyad par can med par 'da' bar
NK118(se)002:14256: byed pa ste / de sogs sbom po'i ngos 'dzin
NK118(se)002:14257: dang go rim mi gcig pa mang du snang mod
NK118(se)002:14258: byed pa ste / / gzhung 'dir bsdu bar mdzad
NK118(se)002:14259: pa'i sbom po brgyad ni 'jigs bral dpa' bo dang
NK118(se)002:14260: dam tshig rgya mtsho la sogs pa'i dgongs pa dang
NK118(se)002:14261: byed pa ste / / mthun la / rje btsun
NK118(se)002:14262: rin po che'i 'khrul spong las ni bshad ma thag
NK118(se)002:14263: pa'i gsum po rim par sbom po brgyad pa dang
NK118(se)002:14264: bdun pa dang dgu par mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:14265: des na 'khrul spong gi dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang go rim ni 'di yin te /
NK118(se)002:14267: yan lag dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK118(se)002:14268: dam tshig dad dang mi ldan pa'o //
NK118(se)002:14269: rig ma bsten par dga' ba dang //
NK118(se)002:14270: tshogs kyi 'khor lor rtsod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14271: gsang ba'i chos ni ston pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14272: sems can dad dang ldan pa la //
NK118(se)002:14273: dam chos gzhan du ston pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14274: nyan thos dag tu rlom byed pa'i //
NK118(se)002:14275: nang du zhag bdun gnas pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14276: sbyor ba nges par ma byas par //
NK118(se)002:14277: skal min gsang ba ston pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14278: gang zhig phyag rgya mi mkhas la //
NK118(se)002:14279: lus kyi phyag rgya ston pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14280: bsnyen sogs dag par ma byas par //
NK118(se)002:14282: sdom pa gnyis kyi bcas pa la //
NK118(se)002:14283: dgos pa med par 'da' ba rnams //
NK118(se)002:14285: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:14286: zhes sogs sbom po'i ltung ba du ma rnams //
NK118(se)002:14287: yod kyang nyes pa chung zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK118(se)002:14289: de sogs sbom po'i ltung ba grangs mtha' gcig tu ma nges pa du ma dang /
NK118(se)002:14290: yan lag gang rung ma tshang ba'i nyes byas sogs
NK118(se)002:14291: mang du yod kyang nyes pa chung bar bshad pas
NK118(se)002:14294: ltung ba sbom po rnams ni du ma ste /
NK118(se)002:14295: de rnams la chad pa shin tu chung bar 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:14298: lnga pa khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa las /
NK118(se)002:14301: khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK118(se)002:14304: ma h+aa yo ga man chad du bshad pa'i gsar
NK118(se)002:14305: rnying thun mong pa'i dam tshig rnams bstan zin nas
NK118(se)002:14306: / da ni gsar ma'i rgyud rnams su ma grags pas khyad par ba ste /
NK118(se)002:14307: rdzogs pa chen po gtso bor byas pa'i snga 'gyur
NK118(se)002:14308: gyi rgyud rnams su gsungs pa'i lugs srol dag 'chad
NK118(se)002:14309: par bya'o // de la thog mar spyi'i don cung zad bshad na /
NK118(se)002:14314: bsrung bya'i don sngags kyi brtul zhugs bzang po las
NK118(se)002:14315: mi 'da' bar sdom pa'i lhag bsam khyad par can
NK118(se)002:14316: sa bon dang bcas pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:14317: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rigs gnas so //
NK118(se)002:14319: sa ma ya'i sgra dngos su yal gam bcas pa'i
NK118(se)002:14320: tha tshig la 'jug pas ji ltar bcas pa las
NK118(se)002:14321: 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pas dam tshig ste
NK118(se)002:14323: 'da' dka' rdo rje dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK118(se)002:14325: de la bsrungs ma bsrungs kyi khe nyen gyis dam tshig tu bzhag pa'ang yod de /
NK118(se)002:14326: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:14327: mi 'da' dam pa mchog gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:14328: 'das par gyur na tshig par bshad //
NK118(se)002:14331: bsrung du med pa gcig car ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:14332: bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:14334: chos thams cad ye nas blang dor med par rtogs
NK118(se)002:14335: pas spang blang bsrung mtshams las 'das pa'i dam tshig
NK118(se)002:14336: ste / kun byed rgyal po las /
NK118(se)002:14338: kun byed nga yi dgongs pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK118(se)002:14339: ma yengs dran pas dngos po ye shes su //
NK118(se)002:14340: ma bcos sus kyang ma byas rang byung ste //
NK118(se)002:14341: rig pas dbang sgyur bsrung dang mi srungs med //
NK118(se)002:14344: bsrung bya bsrung du med pa ni //
NK118(se)002:14345: chos nyid dam tshig dam pa yin //
NK118(se)002:14349: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK118(se)002:14350: kun gyi thun mong ma yin phyir //
NK118(se)002:14351: mos pa chung ngu thams cad la //
NK118(se)002:14352: bsrung ba'i mtshams dag bzung bar byos //
NK118(se)002:14358: bsrung zhing bsdam par bya ba dag /
NK118(se)002:14359: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa yi //
NK118(se)002:14360: rnam par dbye bas bzung bya ste //
NK118(se)002:14365: so byang dang phyi rgyud kyi sdom pa'i bsrung mtshams su grags pa'i dam tshig rnams te /
NK118(se)002:14367: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:14368: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams las //
NK118(se)002:14369: bsrung bar bya ba gang gsungs pa //
NK118(se)002:14370: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK118(se)002:14373: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:14374: yan lag lnga tshan lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:14376: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK118(se)002:14377: bsrung dang spyad dang yid 'ong dang //
NK118(se)002:14378: mi 'dor shes bya sgrub pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14379: zhes nyi shu rtsa brgyad du gsungs pa ni /
NK118(se)002:14380: gzhung don rgyas bshad kyi skabs su 'chad 'gyur ba las shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:14383: gzhung don lhag pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK118(se)002:14384: rab tu lhag par bsrung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:14385: gcan gzan rgyal po'i khri mi zhig /
NK118(se)002:14386: za ma tog tu dug mi blug /
NK118(se)002:14387: rin chen lcug phran mi 'breg cing //
NK118(se)002:14388: zhun khol lta bu mi btung ste //
NK118(se)002:14390: bug brdol snod du bcud mi blug /
NK118(se)002:14391: don dang mi ldan rdzas mi brten //
NK118(se)002:14392: shel sgong 'dam du bsub mi bya //
NK118(se)002:14393: ma dag snod du dag pa min //
NK118(se)002:14394: yid bzhin nor bu mi 'brog ste //
NK118(se)002:14395: khyung chen gshog pa ya mi 'bral //
NK118(se)002:14396: gnam lcags ngur mo'i mtshon mi rdeg /
NK118(se)002:14397: gcan gzan rol pa'i lhag mi spyad //
NK118(se)002:14398: rdo rje brag chen mi gzhig cing //
NK118(se)002:14399: ra ba d+r+wa ba'i mtshams mi 'dral //
NK118(se)002:14400: sgron me rlung gis bsad pa min //
NK118(se)002:14401: ye shes chu rgyun gcod pa spang /
NK118(se)002:14402: bka' rtags phyag rgya mi dbyi zhing //
NK118(se)002:14403: rdo rje pha lam mkhar mi ldog /
NK118(se)002:14404: gtsug gi nor bu dma' mi dbabs //
NK118(se)002:14405: 'di dag bsrung bar bya ba ste //
NK118(se)002:14406: lhag par gces pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK118(se)002:14407: zhes spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig la gnas
NK118(se)002:14408: pa'i rnal 'byor pas sgrub pa la sogs pa'i skabs
NK118(se)002:14409: su bsrung ba lhag par bstan pa'i dam tshig nyi
NK118(se)002:14410: shu ldem dgongs kyi sgras bshad pa ste /
NK118(se)002:14412: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la mi 'tshe zhing bka' mi gcog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14413: bla ma'i yum la mi spyod dang /
NK118(se)002:14414: dad pa can gyi tshogs mi bcag pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14415: dkon mchog dang mkhas pa'i dkor la mi 'bag cing chang myos par mi 'thung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14416: rdo rje spun gyi yum la mi spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14417: mtshan ngan gyi gzungs ma mi bsten pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14418: mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i dam rdzas mi bsten pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14419: mkhas pa'i yon tan la mi smod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14420: snod min la gsang chos mi ston pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14421: mtshan ldan gyi gzungs ma dang snod ldan gyi slob ma mi spang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14422: don bde stong dang rtags yab yum mi 'bral ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14423: mched bkyal kha tsam du'ang nang 'thab mi byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14424: gzhan gyis spyad pa'i lhag mi spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14425: bla ma'i gdan sa mi rlam pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14426: rang gzhan gyi mtshams mi 'dral ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14427: ting nge 'dzin bying rgod kyi dbang du mi gtong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14428: bzlas pa dang cho ga mi tshig gis bar mi gcod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14429: dbang rtags kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' zhing brda' mi brjed par bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14430: rnal 'byor pa'i dkyil 'khor mi dkrug cing skye bo'i mthu ldog mi byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14431: slob dpon gtsug tu 'khur ba las nyams par mi bya ba rnams so //
NK118(se)002:14436: bsrung bya'i don khyad par can las mi 'da' bar
NK118(se)002:14437: sdom pa'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa gang
NK118(se)002:14438: zhig rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i rigs
NK118(se)002:14439: gnas so // de ltar yang gsang snying gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK118(se)002:14440: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK118(se)002:14441: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK118(se)002:14442: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK118(se)002:14446: yan lag gi dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:14448: rtsa ba bla ma'i sku gsung thugs gsum la //
NK118(se)002:14449: dgu dgur phye ba nyi shu rtsa bdun dang //
NK118(se)002:14451: rtsa ba rdo rje gsum gyi dam tshig la bla
NK118(se)002:14452: ma zhes sbyar ba ni rang gi sgo gsum sangs
NK118(se)002:14453: rgyas kun 'dus bla ma'i rdo rje gsum dang dbyer
NK118(se)002:14454: mi phyed par sdom pas sam /
NK118(se)002:14455: yang na gu ru'i sgra las lci ba ste nyams na sbyang dka' ba'i don no //
NK118(se)002:14456: 'di ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po man ngag
NK118(se)002:14457: sde'i lugs kyi dam tshig rnam par gzhag pa yin
NK118(se)002:14458: pas / rdzogs pa chen po'i dam tshig ni bsrung
NK118(se)002:14459: mtshams las 'das pa'i phyir na 'da' nyams med kyang
NK118(se)002:14460: pas / / lam nyams su len pa'i gang zag las /
NK118(se)002:14461: dang po pa rnams kyis rang rgyud dag par bya
NK118(se)002:14462: phyir sgo gsum rdo rje gsum gyi dam tshig las
NK118(se)002:14465: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa las /
NK118(se)002:14466: 'gro ba'i smin so gsum dag las //
NK118(se)002:14467: sngags kyi dam tshig gsum du bshad //
NK118(se)002:14468: de la khyad par nges phye ba //
NK118(se)002:14469: sku dang gsung dang thugs dag las //
NK118(se)002:14470: re re la yang dgu dgu ste //
NK118(se)002:14471: 'jug dang las kyi rnam pas shes //
NK118(se)002:14473: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs la phyi nang gsang gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:14474: de re re la'ang gsum gsum du phye bas nyi shu rtsa bdun las /
NK118(se)002:14475: dang po sku'i dam tshig gsum tshan gsum gyi /
NK118(se)002:14476: phyi'i phyi nang gsang gsum ni /
NK118(se)002:14481: pha ma rdo rje spun sring dang rang lus la smod pa /
NK118(se)002:14482: chos dang gang zag la smod pa //
NK118(se)002:14483: rang lus la rdeg 'tshog dang dka' thub kyis brnyas shing gdung ba rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14485: rdo rje spun sring gi lus la rdeg par gzas shing rgyan la smod pa /
NK118(se)002:14486: rdo rje mched lcam la rdeg pa dang bla ma'i yum la gtses pa /
NK118(se)002:14487: bla ma'i grib mar 'gongs pa dang spyan sngar lus ngag gi spyod pa bag med rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14488: gnyis pa gsung gi dam tshig gsum tshan gsum gyi /
NK118(se)002:14492: gzhan gyi zher 'debs kyi tshig smra ba rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14496: gnas lugs sgom par byed pa rnams la gshe skur 'debs pa spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14498: rdo rje spun sring gi tshig /
NK118(se)002:14499: bla ma'i phyag rgya dang nye 'khor gyi tshig /
NK118(se)002:14500: bla ma'i gsung rnams la brnyas shing gcog pa rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14501: gsum pa thugs kyi dam tshig gsum tshan gsum gyi /
NK118(se)002:14507: spyod pa log pa bag med /
NK118(se)002:14508: sgom pa log pa bying rgod dang gol sgrib /
NK118(se)002:14509: lta ba log pa rtag chad mthar 'dzin rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14511: nyin zhag gi thun re re bzhin lta sgom spyod gsum yid la ma byas pa /
NK118(se)002:14512: yi dam gyi lha yid la ma byas pa /
NK118(se)002:14513: bla ma'i rnal 'byor dang mched lcam la brtse gdung yid la ma byas pa rnams spang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14514: de dag gis gzhung don dngos bstan bkral zin nas /
NK118(se)002:14515: da ni 'phros don rgyud lung gnyis su ji ltar
NK118(se)002:14516: gsungs pa'i rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum mdo tsam bshad
NK118(se)002:14517: par bya ste / de la spyi mdo las /
NK118(se)002:14518: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK118(se)002:14522: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK118(se)002:14523: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK118(se)002:14524: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK118(se)002:14525: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK118(se)002:14526: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK118(se)002:14527: sgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK118(se)002:14528: ces gsungs pa'i lnga po'ang rtsa ba gsum du 'du ste /
NK118(se)002:14529: 'di dag ma nyams na yan lag nyams kyang rim gyis sor chud par 'gyur bas rtsa ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14530: de yang bla ma dang mched la bsrung ba ni
NK118(se)002:14531: phan 'dogs pa dang gnod pa spang ba'i gzhi'i gtso
NK118(se)002:14532: bo lus yin pas sku'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:14533: sngags rgya rgyun mi gcod pa ni bzlas brjod kyi
NK118(se)002:14534: yan lag tu gtogs pas gtso bor ngag yin pa'i
NK118(se)002:14535: phyir gsung du bsdu bar rgyud dang sgrub sde gnyis
NK118(se)002:14537: sgyu 'phrul ba gsang bcu mi smra ba ngag yin
NK118(se)002:14538: kyang gang gsang ba ni thugs la gnas pas gtso
NK118(se)002:14539: bo sems kyi chos yin pa'i phyir thugs su bsdu
NK118(se)002:14541: gsang bar bya ba 'di rnams kyang //
NK118(se)002:14542: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:14543: zhes gsum kas bsdus par gsungs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14544: byang chub sems gsum sgom pa ni //
NK118(se)002:14545: rdo rje thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:14546: zhes byang sems thugs su bsdu bar gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:14547: de las 'dir byang sems dang gsang ba mi smra
NK118(se)002:14548: ba gnyis ka thugs kyi dam tshig tu bsdus na
NK118(se)002:14549: bde ste / rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum du bsdu ba'i skabs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:14551: byang sems rnam gnyis slob dpon drug /
NK118(se)002:14552: mched bzhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi //
NK118(se)002:14553: gsang bcu rtsa bar shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:14555: dang po sku'i dam tshig gi yul ni gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:14557: rgyud grol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK118(se)002:14558: bla ma nyid dang lhan cig grogs //
NK118(se)002:14559: lus ngag yid kyis bkur ba ni //
NK118(se)002:14560: rdo rje sku yi dam tshig go //
NK118(se)002:14562: de las bla ma bkur ba la /
NK118(se)002:14563: yul gyi dbye ba spyir kun gyis dam par bkur zhing bka' drin thob pa spyi'i slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:14564: rang byung gi mkhan po lta bu chos sgor 'dren pa'i slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:14565: dam tshig 'bogs shig dbang bskur ba po dam tshig dbang gi slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:14566: nyes ltung bshags yul du gyur pa nyams chags skong ba'i slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:14567: chos 'chad pa'i slob dpon lta bu shes rgyud 'grol ba'i slob dpon /
NK118(se)002:14568: zab mo'i gdams pa ston pa'i bla ma lta bu man ngag lung gi slob dpon dang drug ste /
NK118(se)002:14570: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK118(se)002:14571: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK118(se)002:14572: man ngag lung gi slob dpon rnams //
NK118(se)002:14573: zhes pa'i slob dpon drug ji ltar bkur tshul gyi dpe yang rim bzhin de nyid las /
NK118(se)002:14574: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK118(se)002:14575: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK118(se)002:14576: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul bltas te //
NK118(se)002:14578: khyad par zhi rgyud las gsungs pa ltar dbang bskur /
NK118(se)002:14580: man ngag nod pa'i slob dpon gsum ni /
NK118(se)002:14583: dkon mchog bzhi par blta ba gang rung gis sgo
NK118(se)002:14584: gsum g.yo zol med pas thugs ci mnyes dang bka'
NK118(se)002:14585: ci gsung sgrub pa'i sgo nas bkur bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:14586: gnyis pa mched la byams par bya ba ni /
NK118(se)002:14587: sngar bshad pa ltar spyi ring nye ba 'dres pa'i mched bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:14588: de rnams las kyang yang dag lam du zhugs pa'i mched phyi ma gsum dang /
NK118(se)002:14589: de'i nang nas kyang 'dres pa'i mched lhag par yang
NK118(se)002:14590: gnyan par shes pa'i rim pas rtag tu mi 'bral
NK118(se)002:14591: zhing phan 'dogs pa'i lhag bsam gyis brtse zhing gdung
NK118(se)002:14594: rdo rje spun la gdung sems kyang //
NK118(se)002:14596: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la //
NK118(se)002:14597: rngan dang bcas pa'i sems tsam yang //
NK118(se)002:14598: rtag tu spang bar bya ba yin //
NK118(se)002:14599: brtse zhing gdung ba'i shugs phyung la //
NK118(se)002:14600: gcig la gcig ni mig bzhin blta //
NK118(se)002:14601: mdor na srog la'ang mi chags par //
NK118(se)002:14602: spun dang mi sring dgos pa sgrub //
NK118(se)002:14603: ci'i phyir rdo rje spun rnams ni //
NK118(se)002:14604: 'di nas byang chub bar dag tu //
NK118(se)002:14608: gnyis pa gsung gi dam tshig ni /
NK118(se)002:14610: rang gi yi dam lha mchog gi //
NK118(se)002:14611: sngags dang phyag rgya rab 'dzin pas //
NK118(se)002:14612: dus kun tu ni rgyun mi gcod //
NK118(se)002:14613: rdo rje gsum gyi dam tshig yin //
NK118(se)002:14616: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK118(se)002:14617: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK118(se)002:14618: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK118(se)002:14619: zhes pas yul sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi brtson
NK118(se)002:14620: pa rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam nyin mtshan
NK118(se)002:14621: gyi thun la gnas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14622: 'bring gis zla ba ngo rer dus drug gam bzhi la sogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14623: tha mas kyang lo zla'i dus mchod kyi rgyun ma chag par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:14625: rang gi sgo gsum yi dam gyi //
NK118(se)002:14626: sku gsung thugs su mngon sbyar la //
NK118(se)002:14627: rtag tu bzlas pa byed pa ni //
NK118(se)002:14628: byang chub gzungs la zhugs pa yin //
NK118(se)002:14629: rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam //
NK118(se)002:14630: nyin gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK118(se)002:14631: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK118(se)002:14632: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK118(se)002:14633: dus bzhi'i bar du mi gcad cing //
NK118(se)002:14634: tha mar brtson pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK118(se)002:14635: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK118(se)002:14636: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed pa //
NK118(se)002:14637: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK118(se)002:14638: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //
NK118(se)002:14641: gsum pa thugs kyi dam tshig la gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:14642: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems mi spang ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK118(se)002:14643: yul lhag pa don dam dang lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis yin la /
NK118(se)002:14644: de mi spong ba'i tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:14645: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'i gnas lugs rtogs pa lta ba'i dam tshig /
NK118(se)002:14646: de nyid spang thob med par mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu la dmigs pa smon pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14647: de sgrub pa'i phyir rang gnas kyi ye shes dang
NK118(se)002:14648: rjes su mthun par sgo gsum spyod yul dang bcas
NK118(se)002:14649: pa'i snang ba thams cad lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK118(se)002:14650: phyag rgya las mi 'da' bas gang shar dag pa'i
NK118(se)002:14651: snang bar lam du khyer ba 'jug pa'i sems la
NK118(se)002:14654: ji ltar smon dang 'jug pa yis //
NK118(se)002:14655: byang chub sems gsum sgom pa ni //
NK118(se)002:14658: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK118(se)002:14659: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK118(se)002:14660: snang stong gnyis med rdo rje'i sku //
NK118(se)002:14661: byas mthong zos pa thams cad kyang //
NK118(se)002:14662: sems phyir gang yang byas snang med //
NK118(se)002:14663: dran dang shes bzhin sngon btang la //
NK118(se)002:14664: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK118(se)002:14665: theg chen sngags par ci yis chud //
NK118(se)002:14667: gzhan las bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum mi spang bar bshad pa dang yang gnad gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:14669: 'di ltar sangs rgyas dang dge 'dun ni ye shes kyi bye brag yin la /
NK118(se)002:14670: chos ni de'i chos nyid yin pas /
NK118(se)002:14671: de bas na ye shes dang chos nyid ni kun
NK118(se)002:14672: rdzob tsam du chos dang chos can bdag nyid gcig
NK118(se)002:14674: don dam par spros pa zhi ba'i phyir gnyis su med de /
NK118(se)002:14675: de lta bu'i don gyis byang chub kyi sems yin no //
NK118(se)002:14676: de'i rtags kyi phyag rgya ni lha'i sku ste de
NK118(se)002:14677: bas na lha'i sku gcig pu bsgoms pas gzhung las
NK118(se)002:14678: / dkon mchog gsum dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:14679: lha dang bla ma de bzhin te //
NK118(se)002:14680: zhes gang gsungs pa'i bla ma ma gtogs pa gsum 'dus par gyur pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:14682: gnyis pa gsang ba mi smra ba la /
NK118(se)002:14684: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14685: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK118(se)002:14687: zhes pas gang gsang bya la ltos nas de rnams kyi bye brag dbye shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:14690: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK118(se)002:14691: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK118(se)002:14695: lta zab spyod pa barlanga po dang //
NK118(se)002:14696: lha'i ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK118(se)002:14697: spyi gsang rna ma pa bzhi yin no //
NK118(se)002:14698: zhes pa'i lta ba zab mo ni blo dman dbang po ma smin pa rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:14699: spyod pa ni gsar du zhugs pa rnams la gsang ngo //
NK118(se)002:14700: yi dam gyi lha'i mtshan dang /
NK118(se)002:14702: de grub pa'i rtags rnams ni ma 'dres pa la bstan na dam tshig nyams shing /
NK118(se)002:14703: 'dres pa la'ang rang dgar bstan na dngos grub nyams par gsungs pas thams cad du gsang bar bya'o //
NK118(se)002:14706: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK118(se)002:14707: bar du gsang la bsgrub par bya //
NK118(se)002:14708: zhes pas gang du 'du ba'i gnas dang /
NK118(se)002:14709: 'du ba'i dus sogs tshogs sgrub gsang ba'i spyod pa la zhugs pa'i bar de srid du gsang ngo //
NK118(se)002:14711: thun mong ma yin pa'i sngags kyi spyod pa dang
NK118(se)002:14712: dam rdzas mched kyi ngan spyod sogs mthong thos su
NK118(se)002:14715: bla ma dang mched kyis gsang bar bka' rgyas btab pa rnams so //
NK118(se)002:14716: de ltar yang zhi rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:14717: gzhan yang slob dpon mched lcam gyis //
NK118(se)002:14718: gsang bar bsgrags dang gnas skabs su //
NK118(se)002:14719: de ltar 'os pa shin tu gsang //
NK118(se)002:14721: de ltar gsang ba bcu po rang rang gi yul
NK118(se)002:14722: dang dus kyi dmigs nges pas shin tu gsang bar
NK118(se)002:14723: bya'o // de yang byang sems dang sngags rgya gnyis
NK118(se)002:14724: yon tan khyad par can sgrub pa'i dam tshig yin
NK118(se)002:14725: bya'o // la / bla ma bkur zhing mched la
NK118(se)002:14726: byams pa gnyis ni thugs dang 'gal ba bsrung ba
NK118(se)002:14727: bya'o // la / dang / gsang ba mi sgrog
NK118(se)002:14728: pa de'i grogs su bsrung bar bya ba gtso che
NK118(se)002:14729: bas bsrung ba'i dam tshig go zhes rong zur gyi
NK118(se)002:14732: dngos grub kyi rtsa ba bla ma yin la /
NK118(se)002:14733: de mnyes na dngos grub 'byung bas bla ma bsten pa sgrub pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK118(se)002:14735: sgrub pa'i dam tshig chen po ni //
NK118(se)002:14736: lha dang bla ma mi spang zhing //
NK118(se)002:14737: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK118(se)002:14738: ces gsungs pas so zhes bzhed /
NK118(se)002:14739: de ltar sku gsung thugs re re la'ang gsum gsum du gyur te /
NK118(se)002:14740: bla ma bkur ba lta bu la lus kyis bkur /
NK118(se)002:14742: yid kyis gus par bya ba bzhin du gzhan la'ang rigs 'gre ba'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:14743: mdor na 'gro ba thams cad gdod ma nas rang
NK118(se)002:14744: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas sangs rgyas thams cad
NK118(se)002:14745: kyi sku gsung thugs dang dbyer mi phyed pa rdo
NK118(se)002:14746: rje'i bdag nyid ni chos kun gyi srog dang bslab
NK118(se)002:14747: pa thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa mnyam pa chen
NK118(se)002:14749: de nyid shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyis rtogs
NK118(se)002:14750: shing goms par byas pa las dngos grub thams cad
NK118(se)002:14751: 'byung ba'i phyir shin tu brtson pas bsrung bar bya'o
NK118(se)002:14752: // de ltar yang snying po las /
NK118(se)002:14753: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK118(se)002:14754: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK118(se)002:14756: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK118(se)002:14757: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK118(se)002:14758: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:14760: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:14762: yan lag dam tshig nyi shu rtsa lnga ni //
NK118(se)002:14763: zhes pas rtsa ba'i grogs sam thabs su gyur pa
NK118(se)002:14764: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan lngar phye bas
NK118(se)002:14768: mi 'dor shes bya sgrub pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14771: spyad pa lnga dang mi spang lnga //
NK118(se)002:14772: dang du blang dang sgrub de bzhin //
NK118(se)002:14773: shes bya lnga rnams thun min bshad //
NK118(se)002:14775: rgyas bshad la lnga tshan lnga las /
NK118(se)002:14776: dang po spyad par bya ba lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14777: ta na ga na ma byin len dang rdzun //
NK118(se)002:14778: ngag 'khyal rnams ni spyad par bya ba lnga //
NK118(se)002:14780: 'di dag rang don gyi zhen 'khris med cing thabs
NK118(se)002:14781: la mkhas pas gzhan don du 'gyur na spyad par
NK118(se)002:14782: bya ste / zhing bcu sgrol ba'i phyir srog gcod pa nas //
NK118(se)002:14783: slob bu ma rungs pa'i rgyud 'chos pa'i phyir ngag
NK118(se)002:14784: 'khyal las zhe gcod kyi barlanga tshig sma ba'i bar
NK118(se)002:14787: sbyor sgrol ma byin len pa dang //
NK118(se)002:14788: rdzun dang ngag barlanga brjod pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:14789: thabs mchog nges pas zin pa yin //
NK118(se)002:14790: gnas skabs dag tu shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:14792: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las kyang /
NK118(se)002:14793: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK118(se)002:14794: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:14796: sbas don du srog ni rlung ste dbu mar 'gog
NK118(se)002:14797: pa'am gzung 'dzin rtog pa'i srog rang rig pa'i ye
NK118(se)002:14799: btsun mo'i shu dra ma byin par len pa /
NK118(se)002:14800: kha sbyor las zhu bde 'gyur med sgrub pa'i 'dod spyod /
NK118(se)002:14801: 'khor ba med snang las 'gro ba sgrol ba'i rdzin tshig /
NK118(se)002:14802: brjod med rtogs pas gab sbas med par smra ba'i barlangasa tshig rnams so //
NK118(se)002:14803: gnyis pa mi spang ba lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14804: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal dang //
NK118(se)002:14805: phrag dog lnga ni mi spang dam tshig lnga //
NK118(se)002:14808: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK118(se)002:14809: zhes yang log gnyis su bshad pa las /
NK118(se)002:14811: dug lnga rang mtshan pa rnams yin la /
NK118(se)002:14812: de yang nyan thos pa ltar dgrar bltas nas mi spong ngo //
NK118(se)002:14814: chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong pas
NK118(se)002:14815: spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir mi spang ste
NK118(se)002:14816: / smig rgyu la chu rags mi dgos pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:14817: de ltar yang rdo rje las /
NK118(se)002:14818: nyon mongs rnams ni sgyu d+r+wa ngo bos stong //
NK118(se)002:14819: rang gis mi rtag rang bzhin shes pas grol //
NK118(se)002:14821: yang thabs kyis zin na spyad kyang mi 'ching bar
NK118(se)002:14822: ma zad rnam par grol ba'i myur lam yin pas
NK118(se)002:14824: rna bar chu zhugs pa chus 'gugs pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:14826: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che //
NK118(se)002:14827: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK118(se)002:14828: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis //
NK118(se)002:14829: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:14831: nyon mongs pa lnga ye nas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas kyang mi spang ste /
NK118(se)002:14832: snum 'dod pas til 'bru sgrub pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:14834: gti mug zhe sdang nga rgyal dang //
NK118(se)002:14835: 'dod chags phrag dog chen po ni //
NK118(se)002:14836: bsrung ba med pa'i sdom pa can //
NK118(se)002:14837: de ni dam tshig rdo rje yin //
NK118(se)002:14838: zhes pa'i 'grel par slob dpon chen po pad+mas /
NK118(se)002:14839: gti mug ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig ste /
NK118(se)002:14841: ma rig pa ni spang du med /
NK118(se)002:14842: rig pa ni sgrub tu med de /
NK118(se)002:14843: chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:14844: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14846: rang bzhin shes pas mi spang ste //
NK118(se)002:14847: rang rig ye shes nyid yin no //
NK118(se)002:14849: sbas don yang dag pa'i dug lnga ste /
NK118(se)002:14850: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rdzogs pas lta
NK118(se)002:14851: ba la phyogs ris dang spyod pa la blang dor
NK118(se)002:14852: gyi 'byed pa med pa'i gti mug /
NK118(se)002:14853: de ltar ma rtogs pa la dmigs pa med pa'i
NK118(se)002:14854: snying rje chen pos rjes su chags pa'i 'dod chags
NK118(se)002:14855: / rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'i zhe sdang /
NK118(se)002:14856: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba gshongs su mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal /
NK118(se)002:14857: gnyis 'dzin gyi lta spyod mnyam nyid kyi klong du
NK118(se)002:14858: mi shong ba'i phrag dog rnams rtogs goms kyi thabs
NK118(se)002:14860: gsum pa dang du blang ba lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14861: drin chen dri chu rak+ta m+aam sa dang //
NK118(se)002:14862: rdo rje zil pa dang du blang ba lnga //
NK118(se)002:14864: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14868: byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa'i rdzas khyad par can
NK118(se)002:14869: yin pas mi dor bar dang du blang bar bya'o
NK118(se)002:14871: chos thams cad ye nas blang dor med pa'i chos
NK118(se)002:14872: nyid kyi rol pa yin pas gtsang dme'i rtog pa
NK118(se)002:14873: med pa'i phyir dang du blang ste /
NK118(se)002:14875: bdud rtsi ye nas dag pa'i chos //
NK118(se)002:14876: blang dor med pa kun las 'das //
NK118(se)002:14877: ye bsrung chen po'i dam tshig tu //
NK118(se)002:14878: mkhas pas dang du blang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:14880: nad lnga sel zhing thun mong gi yon tan lnga
NK118(se)002:14881: 'byung ba dang rigs lnga ye shes lnga sgrub pa'i
NK118(se)002:14882: dam rdzas khyad par can yin pas kyang dang du
NK118(se)002:14883: blang ste / byang sems dkar pos tsha ba'i nad
NK118(se)002:14884: sel ba dang mi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa'i yon
NK118(se)002:14885: tan 'byung zhing rdo rje'i rigs me long lta bu'i
NK118(se)002:14887: de bzhin du rak+tasa grang nad sel /
NK118(se)002:14890: dri chen gyis dug nad sel /
NK118(se)002:14896: sha chen gyi dwangs mas mdze nad sel /
NK118(se)002:14898: rin chen rigs mnyam nyid ye shes so //
NK118(se)002:14899: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK118(se)002:14900: nad lnga bsal phyir blang ba dang //
NK118(se)002:14901: gtsang dme'i rtog pa sbyang phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:14902: thun mong dgos pa lnga phyir dang //
NK118(se)002:14903: rigs lnga grub pa'i yon tan dang //
NK118(se)002:14904: sdug bsngal las grol dngos grub thob //
NK118(se)002:14906: sbas don du phung lnga'i dwangs ma 'dzag med du 'ching bas dang du blang ba'o //
NK118(se)002:14907: bzhi pa shes par bya ba lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14908: phung lnga 'byung lnga yul lnga dbang po lnga //
NK118(se)002:14909: kha dog lnga rnams lha ru shes pa lnga //
NK118(se)002:14911: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pas phung po lnga de bzhin gshegs pa yab lnga /
NK118(se)002:14913: dbang po dang dbang shes lnga sems dpa'/
NK118(se)002:14915: kha dog lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga sogs lnga
NK118(se)002:14916: tshan gyi rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK118(se)002:14917: kyi dkyil 'khor du shes rab kyis sgro 'dogs bcad
NK118(se)002:14918: nas shes par byed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:14920: dang por shes par bya ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK118(se)002:14921: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rnam pa lnga //
NK118(se)002:14922: rnam shes dbang po yul la sogs pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:14923: lha dang dkyil 'khor rang bzhin shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:14925: lnga pa bsgrub par bya ba lnga ni /
NK118(se)002:14926: de bzhin gshegs dang rdo rje rin po che //
NK118(se)002:14927: pad+ma las rigs bsgrub bya lnga rnams ni //
NK118(se)002:14928: dus tshod 'brel ba'i spyod pas dgongs pa blang //
NK118(se)002:14930: shes par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga po de rtogs
NK118(se)002:14931: goms kyi sbyor bas rang rgyud la tshul bzhin du
NK118(se)002:14932: sgrub pa'i thabs la brtson par byed pa ste /
NK118(se)002:14934: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK118(se)002:14936: don yod pa dang rnam snang mdzad //
NK118(se)002:14937: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin te //
NK118(se)002:14938: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK118(se)002:14939: phrin las lnga yis rab tu sgrub //
NK118(se)002:14941: de la shes par bya ba lta ba'i dam tshig /
NK118(se)002:14942: de ltar rtogs nas sgrub par byed pa sgom pa'i dam tshig /
NK118(se)002:14943: spyad dang mi spang dang du blang ba gsum po
NK118(se)002:14944: phyi bshad ltar na spyod pa'i dam tshig gtso che
NK118(se)002:14945: ba yin la / de bas na las dang po pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14946: nyams myong cung zad skyes pa sogs lta dgongs kyi
NK118(se)002:14947: gdengs dang tshogs dben la sogs pa'i yul dus kyi
NK118(se)002:14948: gnas skabs brtsis nas dus tshod dang 'brel ba'i dgongs
NK118(se)002:14949: pa blangs te rim pa ma nor bar spyad par
NK118(se)002:14951: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:14952: de sogs dam tshig rnam gzhag mang gsungs pa //
NK118(se)002:14953: rtsa ba yan lag bcas 'dir ma 'dus med //
NK118(se)002:14954: mdor na rang lus rdo rje gsum shes na //
NK118(se)002:14955: sngags kyi dam tshig sa ya 'bum sde 'dus //
NK118(se)002:14957: gong du ji skad bshad pa des mtshon te sogs khongs nas /
NK118(se)002:14958: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud snying po las rtsa ba dang
NK118(se)002:14959: yan lag gi dam tshig bco lnga las rnam grangs
NK118(se)002:14960: sum brgya drug cur spros pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14961: bshad rgyud rgyas pa'i le'u don gnyis par spong ba
NK118(se)002:14962: rdo rje la sogs pa'i gtso bor shes par bya
NK118(se)002:14963: ba'i dam tshig dgu bcu rtsa bdun dang /
NK118(se)002:14964: spyi mdo'i le'u re drug par /
NK118(se)002:14965: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK118(se)002:14966: thun mong gi nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK118(se)002:14973: lta ba'i dam tshig ste dgur phye ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14974: gzhan yang rgyud sde so sor rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i bsrung ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:14975: ting nge 'dzin dang spyod lam dang bza' ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:14976: mi 'bral ba'i yo byad kyi dam tshig sogs dam tshig gi rnam gzhag mang po zhig gsung na'ang /
NK118(se)002:14977: de thams cad rtsa ba dang /
NK118(se)002:14978: yan lag gi dam tshig tu ma 'dus pa med de /
NK118(se)002:14979: gang spyad na sngags sdom gtong ba'i rigs dang /
NK118(se)002:14980: mi gtong na'ang yan lag nyams par byed pa'i rigs gnyis su 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:14981: 'o na gsar rnying thun mong ba'i rtsa ltung bcu
NK118(se)002:14982: bzhi dang snga 'gyur ba'i khyad par gyi rtsa ba'i
NK118(se)002:14983: dam tshig lnga po mi 'gal lam snyam na /
NK118(se)002:14985: bcu bzhi po lnga po'i khongs su 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:14987: bla ma bkur ba'i nang du rtsa ltung dang po /
NK118(se)002:14990: bla ma la brnyas pa ni bkur ba'i mi mthun phyogs dang /
NK118(se)002:14991: bka' 'das ni de'i gsung las 'gongs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:14992: rang gzhan gyi grub mtha' la smod pa'ang bka' 'das kyi nang tshan yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:14993: mched la byams pa'i nang du gsum pa /
NK118(se)002:14998: rdo rje spun la khros pa ni /
NK118(se)002:14999: mched bye brag pa la byams pa'i mi mthun phyogs dang /
NK118(se)002:15000: sems can la byams pa spong ba /
NK118(se)002:15002: bud med la smod pa rnams spyi'i mched la byams pa spong ba'i mi mthun phyogs dang /
NK118(se)002:15003: bcu pa'ang tha mal gyi byams pa ltar snang bas
NK118(se)002:15004: don la 'dul nus na'ang mi 'dul bas byams pa
NK118(se)002:15006: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems mi spong ba rtogs goms kyi dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:15007: sngags rgya rgyun mi bcad pa'ang de'i sgom pa'i dam
NK118(se)002:15008: tshig ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs yin pas de gnyis
NK118(se)002:15013: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos la the tshom za ba /
NK118(se)002:15014: ming sogs bral ba der rtog /
NK118(se)002:15015: phung lnga sangs rgyas yin tshul nas lta ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:15016: phyi ma gnyis kyi phyogs gcig rnam par mi rtog pa'i lam la rtog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15017: ye shes skye ba'i rgyu phung po la mi mchod pa gnyis dang /
NK118(se)002:15018: bskyed rdzogs so so'i lam pas chos kyi rtsa ba
NK118(se)002:15019: byang chub kyi sems spyi dang khyad par ba spong
NK118(se)002:15020: ba rnams sgom pa'i dam tshig yin pa'i phyir ro
NK118(se)002:15021: // gsang ba'i don phyir mi smra ba'i nang du /
NK118(se)002:15022: bdun pa ma smin pa la gsang ba sgrog pa dngos su 'du zhing /
NK118(se)002:15023: bcu gsum pa dam rdzas ji bzhin mi bsten pa'ang /
NK118(se)002:15024: gsang spyod kyis bsten bya yin pa'i phyogs nas gsang
NK118(se)002:15025: bar 'os pa'i nang du 'du bas 'dir bsdu ba'am
NK118(se)002:15026: / yang na bcang ba dang bza' ba dang glu
NK118(se)002:15027: gar sogs spyod pa'i yo byad rnams sgom pa'i grogs
NK118(se)002:15028: su bstan bya yin pas sngags rgya'i khongs su bsdus
NK118(se)002:15030: de thams cad mdor bsdu na /
NK118(se)002:15032: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK118(se)002:15033: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar rang gi rdo rje'i lus
NK118(se)002:15034: gnyug ma'i rtsa rlung thig le ye shes dang bcas
NK118(se)002:15035: pa gdod ma nas sku gsung thugs dbyer med ye
NK118(se)002:15036: shes rdo rje'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa nyid shes
NK118(se)002:15037: rab kyis sgro 'dogs chod de rtogs par gyur pa
NK118(se)002:15039: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK118(se)002:15040: bsrung dang spyad dang yid 'ong dang //
NK118(se)002:15041: mi 'dor shes bya bsgrub pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15042: med dang phyal ba gcig pu dang //
NK118(se)002:15043: lhun gyis grub pa rnam pa bcu //
NK118(se)002:15045: zhes 'phro gzhi rtsa ba bcu las sa ma ya 'bum sder spros pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15047: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK118(se)002:15048: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK118(se)002:15049: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed pa'i //
NK118(se)002:15050: rtog 'dul dam tshig de snyed spro //
NK118(se)002:15051: zhes bsam gyis mi khyab par spros pa de thams
NK118(se)002:15052: cad 'dus shing rnam par dag par 'gyur ba yin
NK118(se)002:15053: no // lnga pa skye ba'i rten ni /
NK118(se)002:15054: skye ba'i rten ni nyin bzhin bram ze gsod //
NK118(se)002:15055: mtshams med lnga byed la sogs kun la'o //
NK118(se)002:15057: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyis gsar du bsgrubs pas mchog 'grub pa'i rten ni /
NK118(se)002:15058: gtso bor khams drug ldan gyi mi yin par bshad de /
NK118(se)002:15060: skye ba 'di'i zhes pa mi'i skye ba la sangs
NK118(se)002:15061: rgyas nyid kyi 'bras bu rab tu ster ba rgyud
NK118(se)002:15062: kyi rgyal po'o // lha la sogs pa 'gro ba lnga'i skye ba la ni ma yin no //
NK118(se)002:15064: 'o na tshogs gnyis bsags pa sngon du song ba'i
NK118(se)002:15065: mi'i rten can zhig gi dbang du byas pa yin
NK118(se)002:15066: nam snyam na / ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:15067: mtshon rtul pos shing sdong chod pa la yun ring
NK118(se)002:15068: thogs pa de mtshon rnon pos skad cig la chod
NK118(se)002:15069: pa ltar mtshan nyid theg pas tshe rabs mang por
NK118(se)002:15070: tshogs bsags nas 'bras bu sgrub dgos pa de sngags
NK118(se)002:15071: kyi theg pa 'dir sngon bsags rgyab can ma yin
NK118(se)002:15072: par ma zad / theg pa gzhan du spangs pa'i
NK118(se)002:15073: gdul bya mtshams med sogs sdig pa rngams po che'i
NK118(se)002:15074: las byed bzhin pa zhig yin kyang /
NK118(se)002:15075: dbang rnon sems stobs che na sngags lam gyis skye ba 'di la sangs rgyas nyid 'grub ste /
NK118(se)002:15076: thabs zab cing mang ba'i gnad kyis so //
NK118(se)002:15077: de ltar yang dam pa dang po'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:15078: gdol pa smyig mkhan la sogs dang //
NK118(se)002:15079: mtshams med lnga ni byed pa rnams //
NK118(se)002:15080: sngags kyi spyod pa rjes spyad na //
NK118(se)002:15084: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15085: mtshams med lnga ni byed pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15086: chom rkun las kyis longs spyod pa //
NK118(se)002:15088: sdig pas gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:15091: sems can mtshams med la sogs pa'i //
NK118(se)002:15092: sdig pa chen po byed pa yang //
NK118(se)002:15093: rdo rje theg pa rgya mtsho der //
NK118(se)002:15094: theg pa mchog ni 'di la grub //
NK118(se)002:15095: snying nas slob dpon smod pa dag /
NK118(se)002:15098: 'on kyang skal ldan las 'phro can bsags pa yang rab yin na ni /
NK118(se)002:15099: mi'i rten can kho na dgos pa'i nges pa med de /
NK118(se)002:15100: rgyud sde rnams las lha dang lha min sogs rgyud mnyan pa'i snod du bsdus pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15101: gsang bdag gis sngags kyi theg pa gsungs pa'i gdul
NK118(se)002:15102: bya'i gtso bo d+r+wa ma lnga las li tsa b+ai
NK118(se)002:15103: ma gtogs gzhan bzhi po mi'i rten can ma yin
NK118(se)002:15104: pa'i phyir dang / o t+yan gyi gnas su klu
NK118(se)002:15105: rnams la dbang bskur bas grol bar bshad pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:15106: pa'i phyir dang / dang / nyan rang dgra bcom
NK118(se)002:15107: lhag med du zhugs pa rnams kyang sku tshe'i 'du
NK118(se)002:15108: byed btang ste yid lus kyis sngags kyi theg par
NK118(se)002:15109: 'jug pa yod dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:15110: drug pa nyams pa gso tshul la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK118(se)002:15112: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK118(se)002:15114: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams ma nyams par bsrung zhing /
NK118(se)002:15115: gal te nyams na gso ba la 'bad dgos pas de'i tshul bshad ces sbrel lo //
NK118(se)002:15116: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:15120: ltung ba'i rgyu gnyen po dang bcas pa /
NK118(se)002:15121: ltung ba lci yang gi ldang tshad /
NK118(se)002:15123: bshags tshad 'das pa gsor rung mi rung gi dbye ba /
NK118(se)002:15124: phyir bcos bya tshul dngos so //
NK118(se)002:15126: ltung mtshams mi shes bla ma sogs mi gus //
NK118(se)002:15127: bag med spyod cing nyon mongs mang ba bzhi //
NK118(se)002:15128: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhir thogs med bzhed //
NK118(se)002:15129: de yi gnyen por bslab byar bslab pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15130: kun la gus bskyed rtag par dran shes bsten //
NK118(se)002:15131: nyon mongs gang che'i gnyen por 'bad de bslab //
NK118(se)002:15132: spang bya bzhi'i steng brjed ngas dran mi gsal //
NK118(se)002:15133: gnyis bsnan dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug ces //
NK118(se)002:15134: dpal ldan sdom pa'i rgyud las gsal bar gsungs //
NK118(se)002:15137: ltung ba'i rgyu yang rnam bzhi ste //
NK118(se)002:15138: mi shes pa dang bag med dang //
NK118(se)002:15139: nyon mongs mang dang ma gus pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15141: dam tshig la bslab par 'dod kyang ltung ba so so'i blang dor gyi mtshams mi shes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15142: shes kyang bla ma dang des 'doms pa'i bslab bya'i
NK118(se)002:15143: gnas la ma gus pas 'jug par mi byed pa
NK118(se)002:15144: dang / spyir gus kyang nyes dmigs ma mthong ba'am
NK118(se)002:15145: dran shes med pas 'dzem bag mi byed par spyod
NK118(se)002:15146: dang / pa dang / 'dzem bag cung zad skyes
NK118(se)002:15147: kyang dug gsum shas che bas sems nyon mongs pa'i
NK118(se)002:15148: dbang du thal ba nyon mongs pa mang ba ste
NK118(se)002:15149: dang / pa dang / / ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi dang /
NK118(se)002:15150: de'i steng du brjed ngas dang dran pa mi gsal ba gnyis bsnan pas drug ste /
NK118(se)002:15152: mi shes pa dang bag med dang //
NK118(se)002:15153: nyon mongs mang dang ma gus dang //
NK118(se)002:15154: brjed ngas dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK118(se)002:15155: 'di drug dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu //
NK118(se)002:15157: de dag gi gnyen po ji ltar bsten tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:15158: ltung ba'i mtshan nyid mi shes pa'i gnyen por bslab
NK118(se)002:15159: bya rnams legs par bslabs te blang dor gyi gnas
NK118(se)002:15160: rnams shes pas bsrung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15161: ma gus pa'i gnyen por phan yon la brod pa
NK118(se)002:15162: dang bcas te bla ma dang des 'dams pa'i bslab
NK118(se)002:15163: bya kun la gus pa bskyed nas bsrung ba dang
NK118(se)002:15164: / bag med kyi gnyen por dgra nyen che sar
NK118(se)002:15165: zon byed pa ltar nyes dmigs la 'jigs pas sems
NK118(se)002:15167: nyon mongs pa gang skyes de dang de'i phyi nang gi gnyen po bskyed nas bsrung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15168: brjed nges kyi gnyen por gnang bkag gi mtshams mi
NK118(se)002:15169: brjed par yid la byed pa'i dran pa nyin mtshan
NK118(se)002:15170: du sems zhing bshags bsdams byed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15171: dran pa mi gsal ba'i gnyen por dam tshig las
NK118(se)002:15172: 'das ma 'das rtog dpyod kyis blang dor la 'jug
NK118(se)002:15173: pa'i shes bzhin gyi bya ra 'dzugs pa rnams dang
NK118(se)002:15174: / gzhan yang nyams na bdag nyid ngan no snyam
NK118(se)002:15175: du rang la brten nas 'dzem pa'i ngo tsha shes
NK118(se)002:15176: / pa dang / nyams na gzhan khrel nas smad
NK118(se)002:15177: pa'i gnas su 'gyur ro snyam du gzhan la brten
NK118(se)002:15178: pa'i khrel yod sogs kyi sgo nas 'bad pas bsrung
NK118(se)002:15179: / pa dang / bar bya ste / sdom 'byung las /
NK118(se)002:15180: ci ste dngos grub mchog 'dod na //
NK118(se)002:15181: srog ni yongs su gtong yang sla //
NK118(se)002:15182: 'chi ba'i dus la babs kyang sla'i //
NK118(se)002:15183: rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar bya //
NK118(se)002:15186: kun la yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug gam //
NK118(se)002:15187: kun slong nyon mongs gang 'gal der shes dang //
NK118(se)002:15188: lus ngag sbyor byas dngos gzhi bar chod pa //
NK118(se)002:15189: ma 'khrul spyad dang 'gyod med bshags tshad 'das //
NK118(se)002:15190: pham pa zhes brjod dngos gzhi ma tshang na //
NK118(se)002:15191: thun 'das ltung ba zhes brjod lhag ma ltar //
NK118(se)002:15192: rim pas dman na sbom po ltung byed dang //
NK118(se)002:15193: nyes byas ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:15195: ltung ba kun la yan lag bzhi ldan nam bdun ldan te /
NK118(se)002:15196: de yang gang la ltung ba 'byung ba'i yul dang /
NK118(se)002:15197: de yin la der 'du shes pa'i bsam pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15198: spun la khro ba lta bu la zhugs pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15199: sgo gsum gang gis grub pa'i las lam rdzogs par
NK118(se)002:15200: spyad pa mthar thug ste yan lag bzhi ldan nam
NK118(se)002:15202: kun slong nyon mongs pa drag pos bslang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15203: gang la brten nas dam tshig dang 'gal bar 'gyur pa'i yul de la der shes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15204: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi las lnga pa khyad par ba
NK118(se)002:15205: kun+da 'dor ba lta bu lus kyi sbyor ba'i grogs
NK118(se)002:15206: la ltos pas bya ba de zin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15207: bdun pa gsang sgrogs lta bu ngag gi sbyor ba'i
NK118(se)002:15208: grogs la ltos pas brjod cing de pha rol gyis
NK118(se)002:15209: go na dngos gzhi ste rtsa ltung du grub pa
NK118(se)002:15210: dang / dgu pa lta bu yid kyis 'grub pa
NK118(se)002:15211: rnams nyin mtshan gyi drug cha'i nang du gnyen pos
NK118(se)002:15212: ma sleb par thun tshod kyis bar chod pa dang
NK118(se)002:15213: dang / / 'du shes ma 'khrul bas spyad pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15214: des mgu bas 'gyod pa med pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15215: bshags tshad rang rang gi dus las 'das pa ste /
NK118(se)002:15216: de ltar yan lag bdun tshang bar spyad na sngags
NK118(se)002:15217: sdom gtong bas shin tu lci zhing mi mthun phyogs
NK118(se)002:15218: kyis gnyen po bcom pas pham pa zhes brjod do
