NK118(se)002:15219: // yang rtsa ltung gang rung gnyen po dang spel
NK118(se)002:15220: nas skyes pa lta bu dngos gzhi ma tshang zhing
NK118(se)002:15221: ma bshags par thun tshod 'das na ltung ba zhes
NK118(se)002:15222: brjod de so thar gyi dge 'dun lhag ma ltar
NK118(se)002:15224: de bzhin du rim pas nyes pa dman na zhes sbyar te /
NK118(se)002:15225: pham pa'i sder gtogs yan lag ma tshang ba nyon mongs pa can ni sbom po dang /
NK118(se)002:15226: yan lag gi ltung ba gzhan thams cad ni ltung byed dang /
NK118(se)002:15227: phyogs mthun gyi nyes pa phra mo rnams ni nyes byas dang 'dra'o //
NK118(se)002:15228: gal te rdo rje'i mched la phan pa'i sems kyis
NK118(se)002:15229: khros pa lta bu ni ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan te
NK118(se)002:15231: de ltar yang slob dpon mtsho skyes kyi rnam thar bsdus pa las /
NK118(se)002:15232: dngos grub thams cad gzhir gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:15233: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag go //
NK118(se)002:15235: tshad ldan ltung bar bshad pa yin //
NK118(se)002:15236: yan lag gtso bo dus 'das pa //
NK118(se)002:15237: lci ba zhes ni bshad pa ste //
NK118(se)002:15238: sbyor ba ma rdzogs sbom po'o //
NK118(se)002:15239: yan lag phra ba nyes byas so //
NK118(se)002:15240: phra mo'i phra mo dkyil 'khor gcig /
NK118(se)002:15243: na dang dbang nyams bya ba gzhan gyis dang //
NK118(se)002:15244: don chen skye med brtan dang dgos ldan dang //
NK118(se)002:15245: nus rnyed gnang dang bka' bsgo bar chad las //
NK118(se)002:15246: nyes pa med ces snying po rgyan las gsungs //
NK118(se)002:15248: de dag kun la rang nyid na ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15249: dbang nyams zhes pas rang dbang nyams pa'am dbang thob pa las nyams pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15250: bya ba gzhan don de bas che bar 'byung ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15251: gzhan don du 'gyur ba'am don chen po mthong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15252: skye ba med pa'i don brtan pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15253: gzhan drang ba sogs kyi dgos pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15254: rtogs goms kyi nus pa rnyed pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15255: lhag pa'i lha lta bu yul khyad par can gyi gnang ba thob pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15256: bka' bsgo ba ste bla ma'i lung dang /
NK118(se)002:15257: srog gi bar chad 'byung ba las nyes med du bstan te /
NK118(se)002:15259: na dang dbang nyams bya ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15260: gzhan gyi don dang don chen dang //
NK118(se)002:15261: skye med brtan pa dgos ldan dang //
NK118(se)002:15262: nus pa rnyed dang gnang ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15263: bka' bsgo ba dang bar chad las //
NK118(se)002:15264: nyes pa med par shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:15267: de ltar nyin mtshan thun la lan drug tu //
NK118(se)002:15268: spang blang dam tshig gnas la sgrims te dpyad //
NK118(se)002:15269: drug cha 'das na thun tshod 'das zhes bya //
NK118(se)002:15270: zhag gcig zla gcig lo gcig lo gnyis 'das //
NK118(se)002:15271: 'gal nyams 'das ral zhes brjod de dag kyang //
NK118(se)002:15272: snying nas bshags na gsor rung phyi rim lci //
NK118(se)002:15273: lo gsum 'das na gsor mi rung ba yin //
NK118(se)002:15275: de ltar nyin zhag gi drug cha'i thun re re
NK118(se)002:15276: bzhin yang spang bya dang blang bya'i dam tshig gi
NK118(se)002:15277: gnas rnams las 'gal lam ma 'gal legs par sgrims
NK118(se)002:15279: nyin mtshan gyi drug cha'i nang du gnyen pos ma
NK118(se)002:15280: sleb na thun tshod 'das pa zhes bya ba dang
NK118(se)002:15281: / zhag gcig gis bar ma chod na 'gal ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15282: zla bas bar ma chod pa tshun chad nyams pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15283: lo gcig tshun chad 'das pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15284: lo gnyis sam gsum tshun chad ral ba zhes dus
NK118(se)002:15285: la ltos nas nyes pa phyi rim gyis lci ba
NK118(se)002:15286: ste / de tshun chad snying nas brtson pa chen pos bshags na ldang la /
NK118(se)002:15287: lo gsum 'das pa phan chad ni gsor mi rung ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:15288: dam tshig bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:15289: spyir na dam tshig khyad par ral //
NK118(se)002:15290: dus las khyad par nges phye ba //
NK118(se)002:15291: dam las 'gal zhes nyes byas gang //
NK118(se)002:15292: zhag gis bar ma chod par ni //
NK118(se)002:15293: dmigs pa'i yul la bshags byas na //
NK118(se)002:15294: des ni sor yang chud pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15295: nyams zhes zla bas ma chod par //
NK118(se)002:15296: 'gyod pa drag pos bshags pas so //
NK118(se)002:15297: dam las 'das pa lo dag gis //
NK118(se)002:15298: bar du ma chod bshags pas so //
NK118(se)002:15299: lo ni gnyis dang gsum dag las //
NK118(se)002:15300: dam tshig ral ba zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)002:15301: mchog tu drag na gso ru rung //
NK118(se)002:15302: lo gsum dag las 'das pa ni //
NK118(se)002:15303: de nas gso ru mi rung ste //
NK118(se)002:15304: gal te blangs na gnyis ka 'tshig /
NK118(se)002:15305: nges par sa spyod sdug bsngal la //
NK118(se)002:15306: rgyun du spyod pa kho na'o //
NK118(se)002:15308: de yang ngo bo la ltos pa rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15309: dus la ltos pa thun 'das 'gal nyams sogs kyis bshags bya'i lci yang shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:15312: nyams par gyur pa gang zhe na //
NK118(se)002:15313: kun tu nyams pa chen po dang //
NK118(se)002:15314: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK118(se)002:15315: de bzhin zlas nyams zhar nyams lnga //
NK118(se)002:15316: zhes pa'i kun tu nyams pa ni yul ches gnyan
NK118(se)002:15317: pa la kun dkris drag pos spyad pa'am lan grangs
NK118(se)002:15318: mang du byung ba dang dus 'das ral la sogs
NK118(se)002:15319: pa yin la / zlas nyams ni nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15320: zhar nyams ni gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal ba'i nyes pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15321: lnga pa phyir bcos bya tshul dngos la bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:15322: dbang bzhi la ltos pa'i gso thabs /
NK118(se)002:15323: dus 'das la ltos pa'i gso thabs /
NK118(se)002:15324: snying po rgyan las bshad pa'i phyir bcos nyer lnga /
NK118(se)002:15325: yo ga gsum ka'i rnal 'byor spyi khrus kyis gso ba'o //
NK118(se)002:15327: dbang bdun thob la lha grangs re re la //
NK118(se)002:15328: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong byas pas sbyang //
NK118(se)002:15329: bum gsang thob nyams sngon du chad las sbyang //
NK118(se)002:15330: de rjes dkyil 'khor zhugs la dbang bzhi len //
NK118(se)002:15331: sher dbang tshig dbang thob nyams bskyed rim dang //
NK118(se)002:15332: 'pho med tshul khrims rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15333: rang rgyud byin rlabs ma gtogs gzhan mi 'dag /
NK118(se)002:15335: de yang dbang thob mtshams tha dad pa'i dbang gis /
NK118(se)002:15336: de la ltos pa'i ltung ba sbyong ba'i thabs kyang tha dad du dus kyi 'khor lor gsungs te /
NK118(se)002:15337: 'di ltar bum dbang bdun tsam thob pas dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:15338: gyi lha grangs re re'am gtso bo'i bzlas pa stong
NK118(se)002:15339: phrag sum cu rtsa drug gis sbyang zhing /
NK118(se)002:15341: de'i steng du slob dpon gyis gsungs pa'i chad las kyi brtul zhugs spyad pas sbyong /
NK118(se)002:15342: sher dbang yan chad thob pas dben pa'i gnas su
NK118(se)002:15343: bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa 'ba' zhig gis rang rgyud byin
NK118(se)002:15345: de gsum kas kyang sbyangs pa las dag pa'i mtshan
NK118(se)002:15346: ma mthong ba na slar dkyil 'khor du zhugs te
NK118(se)002:15347: sdom pa bzung zhing dbang blang bar bya ba yin
NK118(se)002:15348: la / de'i tshe sngar gyi dbang thob pa'i bslab
NK118(se)002:15349: gral dang rnyed bkur len pa sogs mi bya bar
NK118(se)002:15350: la / gsungs so // gnyis pa ni /
NK118(se)002:15351: 'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog pas bskang //
NK118(se)002:15352: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor sogs dang //
NK118(se)002:15353: ral na rang gi srog gis gso bar bshad //
NK118(se)002:15357: nyams na rang gi bdog pas bskang //
NK118(se)002:15358: 'das na bu dang chung ma dang //
NK118(se)002:15359: nye 'khor lus dang ngag dag dang //
NK118(se)002:15360: yid dang bdog par bcas pas bskang //
NK118(se)002:15361: ral na rang gi srog gis bskang //
NK118(se)002:15363: ral ba la srog gis bskang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:15364: bla ma dang bstan pa lta bu'i ched du rang
NK118(se)002:15365: srog blos btang ba'i brtson pa drag pos bskang zhing
NK118(se)002:15366: / de thams cad kyi rjes su tshogs 'khor dang
NK118(se)002:15367: 'brel bar spyir bla ma dang khyad par bla ma'am
NK118(se)002:15368: spun la nyams na gang las nyams pa de'i drung
NK118(se)002:15369: du'am de dag med na sku gzugs la sogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:15370: mdun du 'gyod sems dang bcas pas bshags shing phyis
NK118(se)002:15371: sdom pa'i brtul zhugs la gnas par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:15373: las dang rdzas dang 'dun pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15374: ting nge 'dzin dang de nyid do //
NK118(se)002:15375: zhes bskang thabs lngar bshad pa'i las kyis bskang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:15376: sbyin sreg gam bzlas brjod kyis bskang ba ste /
NK118(se)002:15377: grangs ni kun tu nyam pa la khri phrag bcu gsum /
NK118(se)002:15378: rtsa ba nyams par stong phrag lnga bcu nga gsum /
NK118(se)002:15379: yan lag la brgya phrag nga gsum /
NK118(se)002:15380: zlas nyams la lnga brgya dang sum cu /
NK118(se)002:15381: zhar nyams la lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo //
NK118(se)002:15383: rigs lnga gang gi dam tshig nyams pa'i khyad par las /
NK118(se)002:15384: yul rnyed na dmangs gdol so sor phye ba'i mi
NK118(se)002:15385: rigs lnga'i bla ma dngos sam mos pa de bzhin
NK118(se)002:15386: gshegs pa lnga'i rang bzhin can la rdzas rin chen
NK118(se)002:15387: lnga las rigs dang mthun pa'i rin po che 'phangs
NK118(se)002:15388: pa med par stob pas skong zhing /
NK118(se)002:15390: dang ba dang 'dod pa'i dad pas nyes byas la
NK118(se)002:15391: gnong 'gyod drag pos gdung ba'i nga ro dang bcas
NK118(se)002:15393: mi dag sdig pa'i bag chags rnams //
NK118(se)002:15394: gdung ba'i glu dang bcas te bshags //
NK118(se)002:15396: ting nge 'dzin gyis bskang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:15397: stobs bzhi tshang ba'i sgo nas bshags pas yul gyi
NK118(se)002:15398: gnas gsum las 'od zer rang nyid la phog pas
NK118(se)002:15399: sdig sgrib nyams chag thams cad sbyangs par bsam pa
NK118(se)002:15400: ste / de yang ting nge 'dzin gyis mes sreg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15401: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis mun pa bsal ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15402: spyod pa rlabs po che'i chus bkru ba la sogs pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15403: de kho na nyid kyis bskang ba ni /
NK118(se)002:15405: shes rab chen pos rgyud kyi bag chags thams cad rang bzhin med par shes pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15406: zhes pas 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i shes rab sgom
NK118(se)002:15407: pa ni sdig sbyong rnams kyi nang nas phul du
NK118(se)002:15408: byung ba'o // khyad par rtsa ba dang yan lag so so'i bskang thabs kyang rngam glog las /
NK118(se)002:15409: dam tshig nyams par gyur pa na //
NK118(se)002:15410: mgon btsun mnyam pa'i don rtogs na //
NK118(se)002:15411: de nyid skong ba'i gnas su 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15412: bla ma spun la smad gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15413: tshe 'di nyid la mnyes byas te //
NK118(se)002:15414: mthong bshags drag pos 'gyod byas na //
NK118(se)002:15415: de ni skong ba'i mchog tu 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15416: gal te bdag gam bla ma spun //
NK118(se)002:15417: ma bskang bar du tshe 'phos na //
NK118(se)002:15418: de ni bskang ba'i tshad las 'das //
NK118(se)002:15419: gsung gi tha tshig ral gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15420: rdo rje chos su bdag bsgoms te //
NK118(se)002:15422: thugs kyi dam tshig ral gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15423: rdo rje sems dpar bdag bsgoms la //
NK118(se)002:15424: lo gsum bar du mi smra bar //
NK118(se)002:15425: bsam gtan sbyor ba rab tu bya //
NK118(se)002:15426: yan lag tha tshig ral gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15427: so so rang rang rigs kyis bskang //
NK118(se)002:15428: zhes rang gi sgo gsum dang sbyar nas sku gsung thugs kyi nyams chag skong tshul gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:15430: snying po rgyan las gso ba'i cho ga ni /
NK118(se)002:15431: tshogs zhing la bshags dral ba'i sngags rgya dang //
NK118(se)002:15432: bkru ba'i rim pa gtum mo'i mes sreg dang //
NK118(se)002:15433: mi dmigs bsgom dang dbang bzhi blang ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15434: tshogs su zhu dang rten la smre ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15435: man+dala 'bul dang mchod rten bya ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15436: me la sbyang dang gtor ma gtong ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15437: gsang sngags bzla dang zab mo'i bsam gtan dang //
NK118(se)002:15438: srog skyob bka' klog bla ma brten pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15439: bdag 'jug rgyal ba'i yig brgya dus bzang bzla //
NK118(se)002:15440: phung po gsum pa rdor sems bla ma dang //
NK118(se)002:15441: thig le phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgom pas so //
NK118(se)002:15443: tshogs zhing spyan drangs pa'i drung du bshags sdom bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15444: yo gar bshad pa'i dral ba'i sngags rgyas sbyong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15445: phyi bum chu dang nang nam mkha'i dbang lha las
NK118(se)002:15446: rig dbang lnga len pa sogs bkru ba'i rim pa
NK118(se)002:15447: dang / gtum mo'i mes lte ba'i kam yig sreg pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15448: 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i shes rab bsgom pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15449: bla ma las sam bdag 'jug gis dbang bzhi blang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15450: tshogs 'khor ram dpa' bo dpa' mo'i ston mos mchod nas bshags sdom bya ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15451: rten gsum rab gnas can gyi drung du yan lag
NK118(se)002:15452: bdun pa sngon du 'gro bas smre sngags kyis bshags
NK118(se)002:15453: pa dang / man+dala gyis mtshon te lus longs dge tshogs thams cad phul la bshags pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15454: mchod rten tshad ldan bzhengs pa'am s+aats+tsha gdab pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15455: zhi ba'i sreg blugs rgyas pa'am za byed rdo rje
NK118(se)002:15456: mkha' 'gro'i sbyin sreg lta bu mes sbyang ba dang
NK118(se)002:15457: / gtor ma sbyangs rtogs sbar gsum gyis byin gyis
NK118(se)002:15458: brlabs pa 'khor 'das thams cad 'khor lo'i dbang phyug
NK118(se)002:15459: gi rnam par sad pa la dbul zhing 'dod don
NK118(se)002:15460: / gsol ba dang / rang gi lhag pa'i lha'i gsang sngags bzla ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15461: zab mo'i bsam gtan zhi lhag gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15463: mdo rgyud zab mo'i bka' klog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15464: bla ma gtsug gi nor bu ltar bsten pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15465: snying gar dam tshig rdo rje don grub yab yum
NK118(se)002:15466: bsgoms pa'i thugs ka'i sa bon las bdud rtsi'i rgyun
NK118(se)002:15467: babs sdig sgrib sbyong bar bsam la +aahkham h+aum zhes
NK118(se)002:15468: pa'i bsnyen pa sngon du 'gro bas lus dkyil lam
NK118(se)002:15469: phyi dkyil gang rung du bdag 'jug blang ba dang
NK118(se)002:15470: / rten byin can la bskor ba byed pa'am drung
NK118(se)002:15471: du 'dug nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i yig brgya stong
NK118(se)002:15473: yar ngo'i brgyad dang bco lnga'i dus bzang po la
NK118(se)002:15474: sdig sbyong la basngagasa pa'i gzungs sngags byin can mang
NK118(se)002:15476: phung po gsum pa'i mdo nyin mtshan dus drug tu gdon pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15477: spyi bor bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' bsgoms la
NK118(se)002:15478: sdig sgrib bkru ba'i dmigs pas yi ge brgya pa
NK118(se)002:15479: bzla ba dang / rang gnyug ma'i lhar gsal ba'i
NK118(se)002:15480: spyi bor bla ma rdo rje 'chang bsgoms pa'i gnas
NK118(se)002:15481: gsum du 'bru gsum gsal ba la dmigs nas srog
NK118(se)002:15482: rtsol bsdams te 'bru gsum gyi yid bzlas bya ba
NK118(se)002:15484: rang lus lhar gsal ba la rtsa 'khor gsal btab
NK118(se)002:15485: ste rlung bum can dang sbyar nas dpyid thig gi
NK118(se)002:15486: 'bar 'dzag bsgom pa thig le'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK118(se)002:15487: rtsa 'khor lnga'i lte bar rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan phra
NK118(se)002:15488: mo gsal ba la sems bzung ste mgon po lnga'i
NK118(se)002:15489: rlung gcun pa phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15491: glang chen rab 'bog rgyud las gsungs pa yi //
NK118(se)002:15492: rnal 'byor spyi khrus 'gyod tshangs dong sprug gi //
NK118(se)002:15493: bshags pas mi 'dag med phyir nyams su blang //
NK118(se)002:15495: glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud las rtog pa
NK118(se)002:15496: gcig khol du phyung ba kalpa dum bu'i rgyud dri
NK118(se)002:15497: med bshags rgyud las ji skad gsungs pa ltar /
NK118(se)002:15498: yo ga rnam pa gsum gyi sgor zhugs pa'i rnal
NK118(se)002:15499: 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag skong zhing rtog sgrib
NK118(se)002:15500: sbyong ba'i spyi khrus rmad du byung ba na raka
NK118(se)002:15501: dong sprug gi man ngag la brten nas /
NK118(se)002:15504: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi bskang bshags gsum nya
NK118(se)002:15505: stong tshes brgyad la byas na de tshun chad kyi
NK118(se)002:15506: nyams chag thams cad sos par gsungs shing /
NK118(se)002:15507: de ltar ma grub na'ang phyag gi bkol byang tsam
NK118(se)002:15508: rgyun du yi dam du bgyis pas kyang nyams chag
NK118(se)002:15511: gang gis sgyu 'phrul zhi khro yi //
NK118(se)002:15512: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag btsal na //
NK118(se)002:15513: nyams chag kun kyang byang 'gyur te //
NK118(se)002:15514: mtshams med lnga yi sdig kyang 'byang //
NK118(se)002:15515: na raka gnas kyang dong sprugs te //
NK118(se)002:15516: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK118(se)002:15518: gong gi dkyil 'khor gyi lha de rnams kyi mtshan
NK118(se)002:15519: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyis thos pa tsam gyis
NK118(se)002:15520: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag
NK118(se)002:15523: mdor na rmi lam du bla ma dang lhas legs so ster ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15526: ri bo chen po'i rtser 'dzegs pa /
NK118(se)002:15527: nyi zla shar ba sogs sdig ltung dag pa'i rtags
NK118(se)002:15528: ma byung gi bar de srid du stobs bzhi tshang
NK118(se)002:15529: ba'i bshags pa la 'bad par bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:15530: de yang yan lag tshang ba'i rtsa ltung ni bshags
NK118(se)002:15531: pas dag pa'i rtags byung ba dang slar dkyil 'khor
NK118(se)002:15532: du zhugs nas dbang blang bar bya ba khyad par
NK118(se)002:15533: ro // gnyis pa phyir bcos ma byas pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK118(se)002:15534: ma bshags tshe 'dir yid mi 'ong bas mnar //
NK118(se)002:15535: phyi ma rdo rje dmyal ba zhes bya ba //
NK118(se)002:15536: mnar med do zla med pa'i gnas su skye //
NK118(se)002:15538: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa ma bshags na tshe
NK118(se)002:15539: 'dir yang dbang sdud sgrubs pas yul dgrar ldang ba
NK118(se)002:15540: ltar sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur ba sogs
NK118(se)002:15541: mi 'dod pa thams cad rdo khab len gyis lcags
NK118(se)002:15542: phye len pa bzhin du 'du zhing /
NK118(se)002:15543: phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal bar ltung nas bskal pa
NK118(se)002:15544: du mar 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing sdug bsngal
NK118(se)002:15547: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15548: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15549: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i //
NK118(se)002:15553: gal te nyams par gyur pa na //
NK118(se)002:15554: chad pa'i skye gnas dmyal chen brgyad //
NK118(se)002:15555: mi bzad sdug bsngal drag po yis //
NK118(se)002:15559: rtsa kun nyams pa'i 'chal pa dag /
NK118(se)002:15560: gso la nye bar mi brtson pa //
NK118(se)002:15561: rdo rje dmyal bar de ltung ste //
NK118(se)002:15562: dmyal ba phal pa thams cad kyi //
NK118(se)002:15563: sdug bsngal gcig tu bsdoms pas ni //
NK118(se)002:15564: de yi 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK118(se)002:15565: sangs rgyas stong gi 'od zer dang //
NK118(se)002:15566: byang chub sems dpa'i phrin las kun //
NK118(se)002:15567: rgyun du mdzad kyang phan mi 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15568: bskal pa ther 'bum la sogs su //
NK118(se)002:15571: se gol gcig gis phyin par byed //
NK118(se)002:15572: de bas shin tu nan tan gyis //
NK118(se)002:15574: rtsa ltung gi gzhung las kyang /
NK118(se)002:15575: gzhan du dam tshig las nyams na //
NK118(se)002:15576: nyams pa bdud kyis bzung bar 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15577: de nas sdug bsngal myong 'gyur zhing //
NK118(se)002:15578: thur du bltas te dmyal bar 'gro //
NK118(se)002:15580: rtsa ltung can des rang nyid nyams par ma zad
NK118(se)002:15581: gzhan la zlas nyams kyi nyes pa'ang ngang gis ster
NK118(se)002:15584: rtsa ba nyams pa'i 'chal pa dag /
NK118(se)002:15585: gso la nye bar mi brtson dang //
NK118(se)002:15586: skad cig yul tsam smra ma byed //
NK118(se)002:15587: nyams gyur nyes pa brjod mi lang //
NK118(se)002:15590: ji ltar 'o ma rul ba dag /
NK118(se)002:15591: rul bas 'o ma kun rul ltar //
NK118(se)002:15592: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK118(se)002:15593: rnal 'byor can kun ma rungs byed //
NK118(se)002:15595: der ma zad rmi lam du nyes pa byas pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15596: gzhan ci zer brtag pa'am gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal
NK118(se)002:15597: ba'i zhor nyams byung yang de ma thag ma bshags
NK118(se)002:15598: na nyes pa chen por 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:15600: bla ma dang ni nye ba'i 'khor //
NK118(se)002:15601: rdo rje spun dang sring mo la //
NK118(se)002:15602: ngan smras tshig gi zur tsam yang //
NK118(se)002:15603: barda'am dngos por brjod mi bya //
NK118(se)002:15604: gal te rmi lam dag tu yang //
NK118(se)002:15605: byung na yid kyis bshags par bya //
NK118(se)002:15606: dngos dang zhe yis byas pa dang //
NK118(se)002:15607: gal te dran pas ma zin par //
NK118(se)002:15608: thal bar gyur kyang ma bshags na //
NK118(se)002:15609: thur du bltas te dmyal bar 'gro //
NK118(se)002:15611: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK118(se)002:15612: tshe 'dir dngos grub mi 'grub cing phyi ma ngan 'gror ltung ste /
NK118(se)002:15614: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15615: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK118(se)002:15618: de las sngags pas yongs 'das na //
NK118(se)002:15621: bstir med spyi'u tshugs dmyal bar 'gro //
NK118(se)002:15622: sbom po ltung byed nyes dmigs kyang //
NK118(se)002:15623: de dang 'dra bar shes par bya //
NK118(se)002:15624: zhes rtsa ba dang yan lag gi ltung ba gnyis
NK118(se)002:15625: kas dmyal bar skye ba 'dra ba lta bur gsungs
NK118(se)002:15626: na'ang / sdug bsngal che chung dang mnar yun ring thung gi khyad par che'o //
NK118(se)002:15628: ma nyams ring mtha' skye ba bcu drug gam //
NK118(se)002:15629: myur na tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha bar do ru //
NK118(se)002:15630: thun mong grub pa brgyad dam dbang phyug brgyad //
NK118(se)002:15631: mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor bdun ldan thob //
NK118(se)002:15632: de phyir rang gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK118(se)002:15634: spyir dam tshig ni yon tan thams cad skye ba dang gnas pa'i gzhi rten du gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:15636: ji ltar sa gzhi gshin pa la //
NK118(se)002:15637: brten nas sa bon btab pa las //
NK118(se)002:15638: 'bras bu smin par gyur pa yis //
NK118(se)002:15640: chos rnams kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK118(se)002:15641: dam tshig 'di la gnas pa na //
NK118(se)002:15642: bla med byang chub rnam smin pas //
NK118(se)002:15645: khyad par gnas skabs su'ang bsam pa'i don thams cad ji lta ba bzhin du 'grub pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15646: kun gyi yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15647: 'jig rten gyi lha chen po rnams kyi bkur gnas thob pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15648: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bo rnal
NK118(se)002:15649: 'byor ma rnams kyis sras dang spun du dgongs pas
NK118(se)002:15651: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi spyod yul la zhugs
NK118(se)002:15652: pas rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa la rim gyis sbyor
NK118(se)002:15655: rgyal ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa de //
NK118(se)002:15657: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK118(se)002:15658: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis brlab //
NK118(se)002:15659: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK118(se)002:15660: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK118(se)002:15663: gsang sngags rdo rje'i dam la gnas //
NK118(se)002:15664: de yis smon pa kun 'grub cing //
NK118(se)002:15665: lha rnams kyis kyang rtag tu bsrung //
NK118(se)002:15666: rgyal ba rgyal mchog sras bcas kyis //
NK118(se)002:15667: bu bzhin dgongs pa dam par mdzad //
NK118(se)002:15668: ting 'dzin yon tan dpag yas shing //
NK118(se)002:15669: kun bzang rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK118(se)002:15671: de yang dam tshig rnam par dag cing lam rim
NK118(se)002:15672: pa gnyis la 'bad pas dbang po rno na tshe
NK118(se)002:15673: 'dir mchog gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur te /
NK118(se)002:15674: rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:15675: bla med sngags kyi dngos grub gang //
NK118(se)002:15676: shin tu brtson pas gang bsgrubs pa //
NK118(se)002:15677: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas te //
NK118(se)002:15678: gdul bya'i zhing du mdzad pa ston //
NK118(se)002:15679: grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK118(se)002:15680: zab mo'i nye lam mthar thug pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15683: 'chi khar don gyi 'od gsal mngon du byas nas bar dor zung 'jug gi skur ldang ste /
NK118(se)002:15684: de yang rten gyi gang zag de dpe'i 'od gsal mngon du gyur pa zhig yin na /
NK118(se)002:15685: de 'chi kha'i gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal dang phrad
NK118(se)002:15686: pas don gyi 'od gsal du gyur nas slob ma'i
NK118(se)002:15688: gal te don gyi 'od gsal mngon du gyur pa zhig yin na /
NK118(se)002:15689: de gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal dang 'dres pas yang
NK118(se)002:15690: dag pa'i mtha' mngon du byas te mi slob pa'i
NK118(se)002:15691: zung 'jug gi skur ldang ba'i sgo nas 'tshang rgya
NK118(se)002:15692: ba yin cing / tha ma bar do nas rang
NK118(se)002:15693: bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du dbugs dbyung ste grol bar
NK118(se)002:15694: ba yin cing / 'gyur ro // gal te tshe
NK118(se)002:15695: 'dir lam rim pa gnyis la 'bad par ma byas
NK118(se)002:15696: kyang dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK118(se)002:15698: bdun nam ji ltar 'gor na'ang skye ba bcu drug las mi 'gyangs par 'grub ste /
NK118(se)002:15700: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK118(se)002:15701: skye dang skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:15702: de yi skye ba bdun la ni //
NK118(se)002:15703: ma bsgoms par yang dngos grub thob //
NK118(se)002:15704: gal te dam tshig sdom la gnas //
NK118(se)002:15705: skye 'dir las dbang gis ma grub //
NK118(se)002:15706: skye ba gzhan du dngos grub thob //
NK118(se)002:15708: pad+ma badz+ra gyi dam tshig lnga pa las /
NK118(se)002:15709: gal te ltung ba med gyur na //
NK118(se)002:15710: skye ba bcu drug dag la 'grub //
NK118(se)002:15712: 'o na bsgrub bya'i dngos grub de gang zhe na /
NK118(se)002:15716: dang po la'ang chung 'bring che gsum las /
NK118(se)002:15717: chung ngu ni las chen brgyad de /
NK118(se)002:15726: rgyas pa yang dag par 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:15730: gang phyir des ni dka' ba min //
NK118(se)002:15731: mig sman dang ni rkang mgyogs dang //
NK118(se)002:15732: ral gri dang ni sa 'og grub //
NK118(se)002:15733: ril bu dang ni mkha' spyod nyid //
NK118(se)002:15734: mi snang ba dang bcud kyis len //
NK118(se)002:15735: gang phyir des ni rdo rje 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:15736: mnyes par byas las myur du thob //
NK118(se)002:15738: chen po ni dbang phyug gi yon tan brgyad de /
NK118(se)002:15740: gzugs phra reg pa yang ba dang //
NK118(se)002:15741: khyab pa yang dag thob pa nyid //
NK118(se)002:15742: rab tu gsal ba nyid brtan pa //
NK118(se)002:15743: dbang phyug nyid dang 'dod dgur sgyur //
NK118(se)002:15745: 'di dag la thun mong gi dngos grub ces bya ste /
NK118(se)002:15747: mig sman la sogs dngos grub rnams //
NK118(se)002:15748: tha mal pa zhes bshad pa yin //
NK118(se)002:15749: zhes pas phyi rol pa la'ang yod cing /
NK118(se)002:15750: bskyed rim kho nas kyang 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub
NK118(se)002:15751: mchog 'og min gyi srid pa'i mthar thug pa'i bar
NK118(se)002:15753: de yang sngags sam ting nge 'dzin tsam gyi mthus
NK118(se)002:15754: chang gi ro sgyur ba dang dug zhi ba la
NK118(se)002:15755: sogs pa'i drod ma thob pa de srid du las
NK118(se)002:15756: dang po pa zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:15757: las phran tshegs kyi sgo nas ji ltar rigs pa'i gzhan don byed pa ni yod do //
NK118(se)002:15758: bskyed rim la brtan pa cung zad thob nas sngags
NK118(se)002:15759: kyis rdzas byin gyis brlab par nus pa'i drod tshad
NK118(se)002:15760: rnyed pa des ral gri sogs rdzas kyi rig 'dzin
NK118(se)002:15762: lus de nyid kyis lha dang mi'i gnas rnams su
NK118(se)002:15763: lus mngon du snang bas rgyu zhing rig sngags kyis
NK118(se)002:15765: bskyed rim brtan pas spyod pa'i nye rgyu las kyi
NK118(se)002:15766: phyag rgya la brten nas 'dod pa'i lha dang skal
NK118(se)002:15767: ba mnyam pa phra yang gi yon tan brgyad ldan
NK118(se)002:15768: thob pa 'dod pa'i rig pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15769: ye rgya la brten nas dbang po rno rtul gyis
NK118(se)002:15770: mi'i rten rags pa'am 'dod pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rten
NK118(se)002:15771: las gzugs kyi rig 'dzin du gnas sgyur bar byed
NK118(se)002:15772: cing / 'dod pa'i rig 'dzin ni mi rnams kyi nang du 'ong yang mi mthong la /
NK118(se)002:15773: gzugs kyi rig 'dzin ni 'ong ba'ang med mod /
NK118(se)002:15774: 'on kyang sprul pa du mas sems can gyi don byed cing /
NK118(se)002:15775: rang nyid kyang rten des rdzogs rim la zhugs nas mchog gi dngos grub sgrub par byed do //
NK118(se)002:15776: des na rdzogs rim gyi rtogs pa skyes rung ma
NK118(se)002:15777: skyes rung bskyed rim brtan na tshogs lam bgrod cing
NK118(se)002:15778: / bskyed rim ma bsgoms par rdzogs rim gyis tshogs lam dang drod 'bring tsam bgrod na'ang /
NK118(se)002:15779: drod chen po thob pa la rim gnyis zung 'jug
NK118(se)002:15780: tu sgom pa gces pa yin no zhes bzhed do
NK118(se)002:15783: 'khor lo bzhi po'i rlung sems las rung tshe //
NK118(se)002:15784: lam bzhi'i yon tan rim gyis 'char ba ste //
NK118(se)002:15785: dbu ma'i mdud pa gnyis gnyis grol ba las //
NK118(se)002:15786: sa bcu'i yon tan nang nas 'char bar bzhed //
NK118(se)002:15787: ces lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo la sogs te
NK118(se)002:15788: 'khor lo bzhi'i rlung sems las su rung ba las
NK118(se)002:15789: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom gyi lam bzhi'i yon tan 'char
NK118(se)002:15790: zhing / dbu ma la ro rkyang gi mdud pa
NK118(se)002:15791: nyi shu rtsa gcig yod pa'i gnyis gnyis grol ba
NK118(se)002:15792: na sa bcu po re re'i yon tan 'char la
NK118(se)002:15793: zhing / / tha ma grol bas sangs rgyas kyi sa 'grub par bzhed /
NK118(se)002:15794: dus 'khor du las rlung brgya phrag bco brgyad pa
NK118(se)002:15795: re re 'gags pa las mi 'gyur ba'i skad cig
NK118(se)002:15796: ma de snyed re mngon du byed la /
NK118(se)002:15797: gang gi tshe rlung nyi khri chig stong drug brgya
NK118(se)002:15798: 'gags pas rtsa thams cad grol nas thig le rnam
NK118(se)002:15799: pa kun gyi mchog dang ldan pa nam mkha' dang
NK118(se)002:15800: mnyam pa na sa bcu gnyis pa'i dbang phyug chen
NK118(se)002:15802: de ltar bshad pa'i sa bcu'i rnam gzhag de dag
NK118(se)002:15803: mkhas pa phal cher 'phags pa'i sa mtshan nyid par
NK118(se)002:15804: bzhed pa dang / yang mkhas mcho 'ga' zhig /
NK118(se)002:15805: dbang thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes kyi sku 'grub pa la /
NK118(se)002:15806: de'i snga logs su dus sbyor bcu gnyis 'gags zin
NK118(se)002:15807: pa zhig dgos pas 'phags lam gyi sa bcu ma
NK118(se)002:15808: yin mod // 'o na gang zhe na /
NK118(se)002:15809: mi 'gyur ba'i ye shes kyi skad cig ma nyi
NK118(se)002:15810: khri chig stong drug brgya po thams cad rim lnga'i
NK118(se)002:15811: rim pa bzhi pa'i 'od gsal dang /
NK118(se)002:15812: sbyor drug gi ting nge 'dzin gyi sa zhes bshad pa de nyid yin la /
NK118(se)002:15813: de las 'phags lam mngon du brnyes pa ni zung 'jug gam ye shes kyi sku ste /
NK118(se)002:15814: de la sangs rgyas zhes btags pa'o zhes gsung ngo //
NK118(se)002:15815: gang ltar yang lam rim par bgrod tshul ni /
NK118(se)002:15817: ye shes la ches dbang ba dang /
NK118(se)002:15818: de nyid spyod pas mthar phyin nas lta stangs rnams
NK118(se)002:15819: thogs med du grub cing chos rgyun gyi ting nge
NK118(se)002:15820: 'dzin thob pas sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku las mngon
NK118(se)002:15821: du gdams ngag nyan pa rnyed de /
NK118(se)002:15822: de dag rim par dran pa nyer bzhag /
NK118(se)002:15824: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa can bzhis bsdus pa'i tshogs lam chung 'bring che gsum yin la /
NK118(se)002:15825: de nas rdzogs rim dngos kyi zhu bde mthar thug pa dbang po lnga'i rang bzhin drod rtse dang /
NK118(se)002:15826: stobs lnga'i rang bzhin bzod pa chos mchog ste sbyor lam bzhi las /
NK118(se)002:15827: phyi ma gsum du dag pa'i ye shes kyi sku ma thob kyang /
NK118(se)002:15828: nyin mtshan gyi snang ba dang mnyam rjes kun tu
NK118(se)002:15829: snang stong sgyu ma lta bu'i lha sku khor yug
NK118(se)002:15830: tu 'byung bas sgyu lus rlung sems tsam gyi sku
NK118(se)002:15831: mngon du mdzad pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:15832: de dag ni mos pas spyod pa'i sa'o //
NK118(se)002:15833: de nas sgyu lus rlung sems kyi sku yang spyod
NK118(se)002:15834: pa'i nye rgyu la brten nas mthong lam gyi mngon
NK118(se)002:15835: byang lngas 'od gsal du bcug ste /
NK118(se)002:15836: don dam so so rang rig bde stong gi 'od
NK118(se)002:15837: gsal mngon sum du mthong ba ni dang por byang
NK118(se)002:15838: chub yan lag mthong ba'i lam rab tu dga' ba'i
NK118(se)002:15839: sa ste / rnam pa dga' ba'i rang bzhin bden pa bcu drug go //
NK118(se)002:15840: 'di la sgyu 'phrul zur lugs kyi bla ma rnams kyi bshad bgros la /
NK118(se)002:15841: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang blo'i nus stobs
NK118(se)002:15842: che chung gis 'byung ba snyigs ma'i lus 'od gsal
NK118(se)002:15843: ye shes kyi mes sbyong bar ma nus pa rnam
NK118(se)002:15845: sbyong bar nus pas skye 'jig med pa dwangs ma'i
NK118(se)002:15846: lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa
NK118(se)002:15849: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK118(se)002:15850: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK118(se)002:15851: zhes bshad pa'i phyir zhes gsung la /
NK118(se)002:15852: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po ni /
NK118(se)002:15853: lus tha mal dang sems lhar smin pa rnam smin rig 'dzin tshogs sbyor la gnas pa ste /
NK118(se)002:15854: de che mchog ma thob par 'das na bar dor phyag rgya chen po thob ste /
NK118(se)002:15855: lus dor ba dang sems lha skur smin zin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:15856: gal te rten des chos mchog thob na tshe dbang la dngos su sbyor te /
NK118(se)002:15857: lus chos mchog gi rten gang yin pa'i rnam pa
NK118(se)002:15858: de nyid dwangs ma'i lus rdo rje'i skur gyur cing
NK118(se)002:15859: sems mthong lam skyes pa'o zhes gsung ngo //
NK118(se)002:15860: de la rang gi ye ge snga ma rnams su
NK118(se)002:15861: lam rim che chung gi dngos bstan dang sbyor nas
NK118(se)002:15862: zur lugs ltar bkod pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:15863: de'i bka' srol 'chad pa'i tshe de'i lugs su 'chad dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:15864: 'on kyang mdo sngags spyi gzhung gi bshad bgros dang
NK118(se)002:15865: bstun na lugs phyi ma 'di nyid 'chad bde bar
NK118(se)002:15866: snang ngo // de nas mthong lam 'od gsal de
NK118(se)002:15867: las langs pa'i zung 'jug ye shes sgyu ma'i sku
NK118(se)002:15868: can phyag chen rig 'dzin gyis bsdus pa slob pa'i
NK118(se)002:15869: zung 'jug rnam pa dgu ni dri ma med pa
NK118(se)002:15870: sogs sa lhag ma dgu ste sgom pa'i lam mo
NK118(se)002:15871: snang ngo // // de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK118(se)002:15872: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK118(se)002:15873: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha /
NK118(se)002:15874: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK118(se)002:15875: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK118(se)002:15876: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK118(se)002:15878: zhes pas sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i bar bzhi la rdo rje'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK118(se)002:15879: rtogs pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bus rang sa'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:15880: sa drug par sher phyin gtso bor spyod cing chos 'khor bskor ba'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:15881: sa bdun pa'ang thabs mkhas pa 'khor lo ltar gyur
NK118(se)002:15882: pas sa de gnyis su 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin zhes
NK118(se)002:15883: bya'o // brgyad par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la dbang thob pas rin po che'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK118(se)002:15884: dgu par chags pa med pas zhing sbyong zhing don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK118(se)002:15885: bcu par phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems can
NK118(se)002:15886: gyi don byed pa'i phyir ral gri'i rig 'dzin no
NK118(se)002:15887: // de yang sa bcu tsam sgom lam phyag rgya'i rig 'dzin du bsdus nas /
NK118(se)002:15888: rgyun matha'i ye shes dag las rnam grol lam dang /
NK118(se)002:15889: khyad par lam ni mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin te /
NK118(se)002:15890: yan lag bdun dang ldan pa'i ye shes gong ma'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15891: de ltar sgom lam rgyun mtha' dang bcas pa 'phags lam yan lag brgyad kyi rang bzhin yin la /
NK118(se)002:15892: sa bcu po de rnams su pha rol tu phyin pa bcu la spyod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15893: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis la sogs pa ni mdo sde bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK118(se)002:15894: de la sa bcu rgyun matha'i snga logs kyi bar
NK118(se)002:15895: du'ang bem chos las 'das pa'i dkar dmar rlung gsum
NK118(se)002:15896: dang / de gsum la cha mnyam du 'dres pa'i
NK118(se)002:15897: yid dang bcas shes pa tsam du rig pa yod
NK118(se)002:15898: pa'i phyir na gnyis snang ma 'gags pas /
NK118(se)002:15899: de sbyong byed sa bcu rgyun mthar 'dod chags chen po'i lam gyis 'bras bu'i dbang bskur te /
NK118(se)002:15900: dbang gsum pa dang bzhi pa'i rjes chags las mthar
NK118(se)002:15901: thug 'bras bu'i mngon byang lngas khu rdul rlung gsum
NK118(se)002:15902: 'gags pa na 'gyur bde myong ba'i shes rig kyang
NK118(se)002:15903: rgyun chad de / sku bzhi ye shes lnga'i bdag
NK118(se)002:15904: nyid mi slob pa'i zung 'jug mngon du brnyes pa'o
NK118(se)002:15905: rgyun chad de / // de ltar zung 'jug gi
NK118(se)002:15906: sku nyid la ldog chas phye na kha sbyor yan
NK118(se)002:15908: zung 'jug sgrib pa thams cad dang bral ba yang
NK118(se)002:15909: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de'i gsung rnam pa
NK118(se)002:15910: thams cad pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK118(se)002:15911: sku rnam pa thams cad pa shes bya'i snang brnyan yod dgur 'char ba ni kha sbyor dang /
NK118(se)002:15912: bde chen ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa med pa'i
NK118(se)002:15913: zag med mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen la rol pa
NK118(se)002:15914: dang / rang bzhin med pa ni med dgag gi
NK118(se)002:15915: mtshan nyid can gyi dpyad mtha' las rnam par grol
NK118(se)002:15916: ba'i rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa so so rang
NK118(se)002:15917: rig pa'i mtshan nyid can dang /
NK118(se)002:15918: snying rjes yongs gang ni yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK118(se)002:15919: ltar gzhan gyi don 'bad med lhun grub tu 'byung
NK118(se)002:15920: ba dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje dang /
NK118(se)002:15921: rgyun mi chad pa ni thugs rje chen po de
NK118(se)002:15922: nyid nam du'ang rgyun chad pa med par 'jug pas
NK118(se)002:15923: rtag pa dang / 'gog pa med pa ni sems
NK118(se)002:15924: can so so'i mos pa dang dbang po ji lta
NK118(se)002:15925: ba bzhin du gzungs sku'i snang brnyan dang chos kyi
NK118(se)002:15926: sgo mtha' yas pa 'gog pa med par 'char ba'o
NK118(se)002:15927: rtag pa dang / // de yang dang po bzhis rang don phun tshogs dang /
NK118(se)002:15928: phyi ma gsum gyis gzhan don phun tshogs rdzogs par
NK118(se)002:15929: bstan pas na don gnyis ma btsal bar lhun gyis
NK118(se)002:15930: grub pa'i phyir / bla na med pa mchog gi 'bras bu mthar phyin par gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:15931: snying po'i khog gzhung gsal sgron las /
NK118(se)002:15932: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK118(se)002:15937: mdzad pa phrin las kyi rnam gzhag rgyas par bshad du yod kyang /
NK118(se)002:15938: mdo tsam le'u dang por bshad zin pas 'dir zlos te ma brjod do //
NK118(se)002:15939: de ltar bshad nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:15940: gsang sngags rig 'dzin sdom pa'i rim par phye ba ste bzhi pa'o //
NK118(se)002:15942: bstan bcos 'di la le'u lnga las /
NK118(se)002:15943: rdo rje theg pa thun mong ma yin pa'i bstan
NK118(se)002:15944: pa'i nyams len gsang sngags rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom
NK118(se)002:15945: pa'i don rnam par gzhag pa bslab bya dang bcas
NK118(se)002:15946: pa bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste le'u bzhi
NK118(se)002:15948: legs gsung rgyud sde'i dgongs don ji lta bar //
NK118(se)002:15949: legs lam gsang bar ston pa'i gzhung bzang gang //
NK118(se)002:15950: legs par phye ba'i rnam 'grel chu 'dzin las //
NK118(se)002:15951: legs bshad bdud rtsi'i char rgyun ci yang 'bab //
NK118(se)002:15952: rgyud lung man ngag chu gter srubs las 'thon //
NK118(se)002:15953: dbang bzhi'i dkyil 'khor rim gnyis 'od stong can //
NK118(se)002:15954: chos dbyings yangs pa'i mkha' la rtag 'char bas //
NK118(se)002:15955: lhan skyes bde chen snang ba'i dpal 'bar shog ///
NK118(se)002:15956: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK118(se)002:15957: rnam dag legs pa'i lam ston rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK118(se)002:15958: de bstan bshad sgrub kyis 'dzin bshes gnyen tshogs //
NK118(se)002:15959: khyad par bdag brgyud sdom gsum bka' drin gyis //
NK118(se)002:15960: smin mdzad rtsa ba'i bla mar phyag bagyi'o //
NK118(se)002:15961: sbyang gzhi bde gshegs snying po'i gnas lugs shes //
NK118(se)002:15962: sbyangs 'bras rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas go 'phang 'dod //
NK118(se)002:15963: sbyang bya'i dri ma 'dor las gzhan med na //
NK118(se)002:15964: sbyang thabs sdom gsum lam 'dir cis mi 'jug /
NK118(se)002:15965: gsum pa sdom pa gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud
NK118(se)002:15966: la 'gal med du nyams su len tshul gyis mtha'
NK118(se)002:15967: dpyad pas don bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK118(se)002:15968: brjod bya'i lus ngos bzung ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan /
NK118(se)002:15969: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'i sgo nas mtha' dpyad /
NK118(se)002:15970: sdom gsum nyams su len tshul bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK118(se)002:15972: de lta'i sdom gsum gang zag rgyud gcig la //
NK118(se)002:15973: rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos yongs su rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:15974: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK118(se)002:15975: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gang gtsor spyad //
NK118(se)002:15977: de ltar so byang sngags kyi sdom pa gsum po
NK118(se)002:15978: de rim par nod pa'i gang zag gi rgyud la
NK118(se)002:15980: de gtan la 'bebs par byed pa la 'dir don
NK118(se)002:15981: drug tu bsdus nas gsungs pas kun mkhyen chos kyi
NK118(se)002:15982: rgyal po dri med 'od zer dang yang dgongs pa
NK118(se)002:15985: nyan thos byang chub sems dang rig pa 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:15986: sdom pa gsum po dag dang ma 'gal bar //
NK118(se)002:15987: rang rgyud sdom zhing gzhan phan ci 'grub dang //
NK118(se)002:15988: cir snang dag pa'i lam du bsgyur bar bya //
NK118(se)002:15989: zhes pa'i don 'grel pa shing rta rnam dag tu 'chad pa na /
NK118(se)002:15992: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la gsum ldan du bsrung ba la /
NK118(se)002:15997: sdom pa gsum gnad kyis mi 'gal ba /
NK118(se)002:15998: dus skabs kyis gtso bor gang 'gyur bya ba dang drug go //
NK118(se)002:16000: gnyis pa la don drug las /
NK118(se)002:16001: dang po rang ldog ma 'dres pa ni /
NK118(se)002:16002: de yang blang yul bsam pa cho ga rnams //
NK118(se)002:16003: so sor nges phyir rang ldog ma 'dres yin //
NK118(se)002:16005: de yang sdom pa gsum po de rang gang las blang ba'i yul /
NK118(se)002:16006: gang gis len pa'i bsam pa /
NK118(se)002:16007: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga tha dad pa'i sgo nas /
NK118(se)002:16008: ji srid blangs pa'i dus kyang so sor nges pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16009: ngo bo gnas gyur kyang ldog pa la gzhi mthun
NK118(se)002:16010: mi srid pas rang rang gi ldog cha ma 'dres
NK118(se)002:16011: par yod de / thob la ma nyams par so sor gnas pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16013: so thar ni ji srid 'tsho'i bar dang /
NK118(se)002:16014: byang sdom ni snying po byang chub kyi bar du khas blangs kyi /
NK118(se)002:16015: sngags sdom thob dus de dang de nyams rkyen dang gtong rgyur ma bshad pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16016: dper na bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pas cho
NK118(se)002:16017: ga nyan thos kyi lugs ltar blangs pa'i theg chen
NK118(se)002:16018: so thar ram / nyan thos kyi dge slong gi
NK118(se)002:16019: sdom pa nyid slar sems bskyed blangs pas der gnas
NK118(se)002:16020: gyur pa'i rgyud kyi so thar gyi sdom pa gang
NK118(se)002:16022: de la kun slong byang chub kyi sems kyi ldog pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16023: sdom pa'i ldog pa gnyis yod pa las /
NK118(se)002:16024: snga ma tshe 'phos pa'i dus su mi gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:16025: de byang sems kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16026: phyi ma sdom pa khas blangs pa'i dus kyi ldog cha ni tshe 'phos pa'i dbang gis gtong ste /
NK118(se)002:16027: dge slong gi sdom pa de ji srid 'tsho'i mtha' can gyi sdom pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16028: de ltar yang rab dbye las /
NK118(se)002:16029: theg chen so so thar yin yang //
NK118(se)002:16030: dge slong la sogs sdom pa yi //
NK118(se)002:16031: ldog pa shi ba'i tshe na gtong //
NK118(se)002:16032: byang chub sems kyi ldog pa dang //
NK118(se)002:16035: gnyis pa dgag dgos yongs rdzogs ni /
NK118(se)002:16036: dgag bya nyon mongs dgos pa mi 'ching bar //
NK118(se)002:16037: rang rang lam gyi ngos nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK118(se)002:16038: spong bsgyur lam du byed pa so so yang //
NK118(se)002:16039: nyon mongs rang mtshan spong bar mkhas rnams mthun //
NK118(se)002:16041: sdom pa gsum kas rang rgyud kyi mi dge ba sdom par gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:16043: chos gang zhig dngos dang brgyud nas kun tu 'dod chags pa'i rgyur 'gyur ni /
NK118(se)002:16044: kun tu 'dod chags dang bral bar mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos ma yin /
NK118(se)002:16046: ston pa'i bstan pa ma yin par shes par byos shig /
NK118(se)002:16047: chos gang zhig dngos dang brgyud nas kun tu 'dod chags dang bral ba'i rgyur 'gyur gyi /
NK118(se)002:16048: kun tu 'dod chags pa'i rgyur mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos yin /
NK118(se)002:16050: ston pa'i bstan pa yin par shes par byos shig /
NK118(se)002:16051: ces zhe sdang la sogs pa'i bar du rgyas par gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:16052: de yang mi tshangs spyod lta bu nyan thos pas
NK118(se)002:16053: spyod pa'i nus pa yod bzhin du mi spyod pa
NK118(se)002:16054: dang / sdom pa gong ma gnyis kyi thabs kyis
NK118(se)002:16055: zin pas spyad pa gnyis dgag bya nyon mongs pa
NK118(se)002:16056: dang / spong ba dang / dgos pa nyon mongs pa des mi 'ching bar gnad gcig ste /
NK118(se)002:16057: de gnyis ka la 'dod pa'i dri mas ma gos par mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16058: des na rang rang gi lam rnam pa mi 'dra
NK118(se)002:16059: ba ltar snang yang don gnad gcig pa'i ngos nas
NK118(se)002:16060: dgag dgos yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:16061: 'di ltar nyan thos pa bden pa gnyis ka rdzas
NK118(se)002:16062: yod du blta bas so thar gyis nyon mongs pa
NK118(se)002:16063: spong ba dang / byang chub sems dpas kun rdzob
NK118(se)002:16064: rdzas yod du bltas te nyon mongs pa chos nyid
NK118(se)002:16066: gsang sngags pas nyon mongs pa lnga'i rang bzhin ye shes lngar bltas te lam du byed pas na /
NK118(se)002:16067: de gsum gnyen po'i rnam pa so so ba ltar snang yang /
NK118(se)002:16068: don nyon mongs pa rang mtshan pa spong bar gcig pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16072: sngags kyis btab ste za ba gsum kas kyang dug
NK118(se)002:16073: gis mi 'chi ba'i dgos pa sgrub par gcig pa
NK118(se)002:16074: bzhin no // gsum pa ngo bo gnas 'gyur ni /
NK118(se)002:16075: so thar kun slong sems bskyed kyis zin na //
NK118(se)002:16076: nyes spyod sdom pa zhes bya'i tshul khrims yin //
NK118(se)002:16077: dbang thob rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sdom par 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:16078: de phyir ngo bo gnas 'gyur yin no zhes //
NK118(se)002:16079: 'bum phrag lnga pa'i lung gis gsal bar grub //
NK118(se)002:16081: de la spyir snga phyir byon pa'i chen po dag /
NK118(se)002:16082: sdom pa gsum ngo bo tha dad du 'dod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16083: gnas gyur ngo bo gcig tu 'dod pa'i lugs gnyis /
NK118(se)002:16085: gong mas 'og ma zil gnon du 'dod pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16086: 'og ma gong ma'i rten du byas te rten brten par 'dod pa'i lugs gnyis /
NK118(se)002:16088: skar zla nyi gsum gyi dpes gong mas 'og ma
NK118(se)002:16089: zil gyis mnan nas kun gzhi la bag la nyal
NK118(se)002:16091: 'og ma mngon gyur du mi gnas par bzhed pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16093: byang sems sdom ldan gyi rgyud la dge slong gi
NK118(se)002:16094: sdom pa mngon gyur med kyang kun gzhi la de'i
NK118(se)002:16095: bag la nyal yod pa tsam gyis dge slong gi
NK118(se)002:16097: chod na sems can thams cad chos can /
NK118(se)002:16099: kun gzhi la dge slong gi bag chags yod dgos pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16100: der ma zad dge slong gi sdom pa phul ba'i gang zag chos can /
NK118(se)002:16101: khyod kyi rgyud la dge slong gi sdom pa yod par thal /
NK118(se)002:16102: de'i shes rgyud la sdom pa'i bag chags 'brang ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16104: nyi ma'i 'od zer gyi 'og tu zla ba dang
NK118(se)002:16105: skar ma'i 'od sgrib byed kyi thun mong ma yin
NK118(se)002:16106: pa'i mun pa srid par thal /
NK118(se)002:16107: sdom pa gsum nang ma 'dom pa'i tshe gong ma'i
NK118(se)002:16108: bcas pa las gzhan pa'i 'og ma'i bcas 'gal gyi
NK118(se)002:16109: ltung ba thun mong ma yin pa du ma zhig
NK118(se)002:16112: snod dwangs par chu rnyog med blugs pa'i nang du
NK118(se)002:16113: mrgad lta bu bcug pa na snod dang chu gnyis
NK118(se)002:16114: ka rin po che'i kha dog tu 'gyur bas rin
NK118(se)002:16115: po che'i yan lag tu gyur kyang /
NK118(se)002:16116: de gsum rten brten pa'i tshul du rdzas tha dad
NK118(se)002:16117: pa bzhin du gong mas zin pa na 'og ma
NK118(se)002:16118: yan lag tu 'gyur ba las rdzas tha dad pa'o
NK118(se)002:16119: zhes bzhed / de yang mi 'thad de /
NK118(se)002:16120: snod de chu dang nor bu gnyis ka'i rten du
NK118(se)002:16121: med mi rung ba bzhin du sdom pa gong ma
NK118(se)002:16122: gnyis kyi rten du so thar nges par dgos par
NK118(se)002:16123: 'gyur la / de ltar na gong ma gnyis kyang
NK118(se)002:16124: rten gling gsum gyi skyed pa bud med kho na
NK118(se)002:16125: las gzhan la skye ba med par thal zhing /
NK118(se)002:16127: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pas gzhan don du 'gyur
NK118(se)002:16128: nges par mthong nas dge slong gi bslab pa phul
NK118(se)002:16129: ba'i tshe / de'i rgyud kyi dge slong gi sdom pa chos can /
NK118(se)002:16130: khyod phul bas sdom pa gong ma gnyis kyang gtong bar thal /
NK118(se)002:16131: khyod sdom pa gong ma gnyis kyi skye ba dang gnas pa'i rten yin pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:16132: rten btang na brten pa gtong ba'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:16133: rten snod med na de la brten pa'i chu dang nor bu'ang med dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16134: zil gnon dang rten brten par 'dod pa gnyis ka'i skyon thun mong ba ni /
NK118(se)002:16135: sdom pa gsum ngo bo rdzas tha dad du 'dod pa de ltar na /
NK118(se)002:16136: gtso sems gcig gi 'khor du sems byung sems pa
NK118(se)002:16137: rigs mthun ngo bo tha dad pa gsum cig car
NK118(se)002:16138: yod par thal ba'i phyir mi 'thad do //
NK118(se)002:16139: des na rang lugs gzhung 'di'i dgongs pa ni /
NK118(se)002:16140: sdom pa gsum gnas gyur ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du bzhed pa yin cing /
NK118(se)002:16141: lugs 'di ni snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK118(se)002:16142: ba la sogs pa nas gsal bar bstan pa ltar
NK118(se)002:16143: / lo ts+aa ba rong zom chos kyi bzang po /
NK118(se)002:16144: zur lugs kyi bla ma phal che ba dang /
NK118(se)002:16145: de'i bshad bgros rtsal 'don gyis 'chad pa po snar ston seng ge 'od /
NK118(se)002:16146: khyad par kun mkhyen chen po dri med 'od zer /
NK118(se)002:16147: bdag cag gi rtsa ba'i bla ma rje gter chen
NK118(se)002:16148: chos kyi rgyal po sogs snga 'gyur gyi mkhan grub
NK118(se)002:16149: rnams dang / gsar ma'i lo chen rin chen bzang po /
NK118(se)002:16150: 'jam pa'i dbyangs bdag nyid chen po sa skya pan+di ta rjes 'brangs dang bcas pa rnams te /
NK118(se)002:16151: gsar rnying gi mkhas grub 'gran zla bral ba rnams
NK118(se)002:16152: kyi dgongs pa rma med pa yin pas mkhas pa'i
NK118(se)002:16155: snga ma snga ma phyi ma phyi mar gnas gyur pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK118(se)002:16157: nyon mongs pa rang ga mas spyad pa'i sgo gsum gyi las kyis 'khor bar 'ching mod /
NK118(se)002:16158: de nyid shes rab dang snying rje phyogs gcig gis
NK118(se)002:16159: bzung nas nyes spyod spong ba'i sdom pa la zhugs
NK118(se)002:16160: pa na ngan 'gro las thar nas mtho ris dang
NK118(se)002:16161: thar pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba ni nyan thos kyi so
NK118(se)002:16162: thar / de nyid thabs dang shes rab che po'i
NK118(se)002:16163: bsam pas zin nas gzhan don gyi bya ba la
NK118(se)002:16164: zhu gas pa na byang chub chen por grol ba'i
NK118(se)002:16166: de nyid kyang thabs shes chen po'i yang chen pos
NK118(se)002:16167: yongs su zin par spyad pa na bla na med
NK118(se)002:16168: pa'i byang chub chen por 'bad rtsol med par lhun
NK118(se)002:16169: gyis grub pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba ni sngags sdom mo
NK118(se)002:16172: rdo yi rigs kyi bye brag cig /
NK118(se)002:16173: bzhu bas lcags dang zangs dngul 'byung //
NK118(se)002:16174: zhes sogs sngar drangs pa ltar rigs can gsum gyi
NK118(se)002:16175: sdom pa sngags sdom du 'gyur tshul gsungs pa ltar
NK118(se)002:16176: ram / yang na gsang ba spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK118(se)002:16177: dper na rdo las zangs su 'gyur //
NK118(se)002:16178: zangs las gser gyi rnam pa ste //
NK118(se)002:16179: zangs kyi dus na rdo med la //
NK118(se)002:16180: gser du gyur pas zangs mi snang //
NK118(se)002:16181: rig 'dzin nang gi dge slong la //
NK118(se)002:16182: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK118(se)002:16183: gnyis po gnas pa nyid du ni //
NK118(se)002:16184: sangs rgyas nyid kyis ma gsungs so //
NK118(se)002:16185: zhes lo chen rin bzang gi spyi rnam dang /
NK118(se)002:16186: kun mkhyen chen pos shing rta rnam dag tu drangs pa ltar 'chad de /
NK118(se)002:16187: dper na zangs rdo bzhu bas zangs su 'gyur la /
NK118(se)002:16188: de la gser 'gyur gyi rtsis btab pas gser du 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK118(se)002:16189: nyan thos ltar dman sems kyis blangs pa'i so thar gyi sdom pa de'ang /
NK118(se)002:16190: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pas zin pa na dman
NK118(se)002:16191: sems btang yang rang gi ngo bo gzhan gnod gzhi
NK118(se)002:16192: bcas spong ba'i ldog cha de byang chub sems dpa'i
NK118(se)002:16193: nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims su gnas gyur la
NK118(se)002:16194: / de gnyis kas dbang thob pa na mnyam pa
NK118(se)002:16195: chen po'i thabs kyis ma zin pa'i tha mal snang
NK118(se)002:16196: zhen gyi ldog cha re yod pa de btang nas
NK118(se)002:16197: / / so thar gyi gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong
NK118(se)002:16198: ba dang byang sdom gyi gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'i
NK118(se)002:16199: ldog cha gnyis po de rdzas gong 'phel gyi tshul
NK118(se)002:16200: gyis mnyam pa chen po'i thabs khyad par can gyis
NK118(se)002:16201: zin pa'i sngags kyi nyes spyod sdom pa dang rigs
NK118(se)002:16202: lnga spyi'am rnam snang gi dam tshig tu gnas gyur
NK118(se)002:16203: / / pa yin no // des na sgo gsum
NK118(se)002:16204: gyi bya ba gzhi gcig la'ang thabs che chung gis
NK118(se)002:16205: gong ma gong mar gnas gyur te /
NK118(se)002:16206: rig 'dzin sngags kyi rang dus na so byang zhes rdzas gzhan tha dad pa med de /
NK118(se)002:16207: sngags kyi sdom rdzas su ngo bo gnas gyur du yod pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16208: de yang gzhi gcig la dper mtshon na /
NK118(se)002:16209: so byang sngags kyi dus su thob pa'i srog gcod
NK118(se)002:16210: spong ba'i sems pa gsum po de snga ma phyi
NK118(se)002:16211: mar gnas gyur te ngo bo gcig pa bzhin dang
NK118(se)002:16212: / gzhan don du bskal pa grangs med gsum na
NK118(se)002:16213: rdzogs byang tsam thob 'dod kyi sem sa pa dang
NK118(se)002:16214: / / sngags kyi rdzogs byang tshe gcig gis thob
NK118(se)002:16215: par 'dod pa'i sems pa gnyis snga ma phyi mar
NK118(se)002:16216: gnas gyur te ngo bo gcig pa bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:16217: de lta na'ang sdom pa gsum gyi sems pa ldog
NK118(se)002:16218: pa tha dad pa gsum po de rnams skye 'jig
NK118(se)002:16219: gnas gsum dus gcig pa ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:16220: dang po ji ltar blangs pa ltar gnas 'jig byed pa'i rang ldog ma 'dres pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:16221: gsum ldan gyi rgyud kyi sdom pa snga ma rnams phyi ma dang ngo bo gcig kyang /
NK118(se)002:16222: phyi ma snga ma dang gnas gyur ngo bo gcig pa ma yin te /
NK118(se)002:16223: snga ma snga ma las phyi ma phyi ma rgya che ba'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:16224: phyi ma blangs tshe sngar gyi sdom pa'i rdzas rgyun
NK118(se)002:16225: ma yin pa'i sdom rdzas gsar pa du ma zhig
NK118(se)002:16226: skye ba yod dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16227: de la kha cig na re /
NK118(se)002:16228: gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud kyi dge slong gi sdom pa chos can /
NK118(se)002:16229: de'i rgyud kyi byang sdom dang sngags sdom du thal /
NK118(se)002:16230: de dang der gnas gyur pa'i phyir zer na /
NK118(se)002:16231: de'i lan la khyab pa ma nges pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16234: khyod kyi de la khyab pa ma nges pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:16235: snga ma phyi mar gnas gyur kyang de de yin mi dgos pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16236: kun gzhi dang nyon yid sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK118(se)002:16237: su gnas gyur kyang de de ma yin pa bzhin
NK118(se)002:16239: dngos po gzhir byas kyi steng du khyod kyi khyab pa de 'gal ba yin te /
NK118(se)002:16240: gzhon nu rgan por gnas gyur kyang de dang de 'gal ba bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:16241: gzhan yang gnas gyur pa'i tshe de der ston pa yin na /
NK118(se)002:16242: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa sngags sdom du gnas gyur pa'i tshe /
NK118(se)002:16243: nyan rang gnyis kyi sdom pa chos can /
NK118(se)002:16244: theg chen gyi sdom par thal /
NK118(se)002:16245: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16246: zhes pa la lan med do //
NK118(se)002:16247: dpes kyang de gsum gzhi mthun pa mi srid par ston te /
NK118(se)002:16248: lcags zangs dngul gsum 'gyur rtsis gser du gyur pa'i tshe de gsum der gnas gyur kyang /
NK118(se)002:16249: de gsum de yin pa mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16250: gzhan yang gsum ldan gyi rgyud kyi so byang gnyis
NK118(se)002:16251: de'i rgyud la yod cing der gnas gyur pas sngags
NK118(se)002:16253: dge slong gi rgyud kyi dge bsnyen dang dge tshul /
NK118(se)002:16254: sngags pa'i rgyud kyi bskyed rdzogs kyi sdom pa rnams
NK118(se)002:16255: kyang de der 'dod dgos par thal ba bzlog tu
NK118(se)002:16256: med do // de ltar bshad pa'i grub don la gnyis te /
NK118(se)002:16260: snga ma snga ma phyi ma phyi mar gnas gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16261: nyes spyod sdom pa'i spong sems snga ma rnams phyi mar dang /
NK118(se)002:16262: dge ba chos sdud dang sems can don byed kyi
NK118(se)002:16263: tshul khrims sngar byang sems kyi theg pa thob pa
NK118(se)002:16264: de dag / phyis sngags kyi theg par thob pa de dang der gnas gyur pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16266: gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud kyi gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong ba'i sems pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16267: gzhan don sems can la phan bde sgrub pa'i sems pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16268: rig pa 'dzin pa'i dam tshig mtha' dag la slob
NK118(se)002:16269: pa'i sems pa gsum po de ngo bo gcig pa
NK118(se)002:16270: yin te / de'i rgyud kyi gzhan la phan pa
NK118(se)002:16271: sgrub pa'i sems pa de ka gnod pa spong ba'i
NK118(se)002:16272: sems pa dang sngags kyi dam tshig la slob pa'i
NK118(se)002:16273: sems pa yang yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK118(se)002:16274: de bzhin du cig shos gnyis kyang phan tshun du gcig la gcig yin pas /
NK118(se)002:16275: de gsum gyi ldog pa la gzhi mthun mi srid kyang /
NK118(se)002:16276: ngo bo la gzhi mthun srid pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16277: bzhi pa yon tan yar ldan ni /
NK118(se)002:16278: 'jig rten rnal 'byor rnal 'byor blo khyad kyis //
NK118(se)002:16279: gong ma gong mas gnod phyir 'og ma yi //
NK118(se)002:16280: yon tan yar ldan 'og ma zil gyis gnon //
NK118(se)002:16285: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyis //
NK118(se)002:16286: gong ma gong ma rnams kyis gnod //
NK118(se)002:16287: ces gsungs pa ltar rten gyi gang zag blo na
NK118(se)002:16288: 'phar ba'i stobs kyis 'og ma'i yon tan rnams gong
NK118(se)002:16289: mar 'dus shing rnam par dag pas na /
NK118(se)002:16290: sngags kyi dam tshig ma nyams par thub na so
NK118(se)002:16291: byang gi bsrung bya rnams zhar la thub pas logs
NK118(se)002:16294: so byang gi bslab bya mtha' dag sngags kyi spyi'i dam tshig dang /
NK118(se)002:16295: khyad par rigs lnga'i dam tshig las rnam snang dang
NK118(se)002:16296: don grub kyi dam tshig tu 'dus pa gang zhig
NK118(se)002:16297: / rtsa ltung gnyis pa'i nang du'ang 'du ba'i phyir te /
NK118(se)002:16298: bre gsum gyi nang du bre do 'du ba bzhin no //
NK118(se)002:16299: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK118(se)002:16300: theg chen dam tshig la gnas na //
NK118(se)002:16302: bsrung ba med par thub pas na //
NK118(se)002:16303: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK118(se)002:16306: de yang so thar gyis gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong
NK118(se)002:16307: ba de nyid byang sdom gyis gzhan la phan 'dogs
NK118(se)002:16309: de gnyis ka'ang sngags kyis sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa
NK118(se)002:16310: bsgrubs te mnyam pa chen po'i ngang nas gzhan don
NK118(se)002:16311: rtsol med du mdzad pa'i thabs mkhas kyi nang du
NK118(se)002:16312: yon tan yar ldan gyi sgo nas tshang zhing 'dus
NK118(se)002:16313: la rnam par dag pa yin te /
NK118(se)002:16315: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK118(se)002:16316: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK118(se)002:16317: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK118(se)002:16318: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK118(se)002:16320: ji bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK118(se)002:16321: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK118(se)002:16322: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK118(se)002:16324: mdor na sngags kyi sdom pa gtso bor nyams su
NK118(se)002:16325: blangs pas 'og ma gnyis kyi dgag bya dang dgos
NK118(se)002:16326: pa'ang yar ldan gyi tshul du rdzogs pa yin te
NK118(se)002:16327: / dper na sngags kyi dbang gsum pa'i nyams len
NK118(se)002:16328: sbyor ba'i dam tshig lta bu la'ang rang rgyud kyi
NK118(se)002:16329: chags pa dang ma bral na sngags kyi lam du
NK118(se)002:16330: / mi 'gro mod / rtogs goms kyi gdengs kyis
NK118(se)002:16331: tha mal gyi 'dzin pa dang bral zhing thig le
NK118(se)002:16332: 'dzag med du brtan na mi tshangs spyod kyi pham
NK118(se)002:16334: dgag bya nyon mongs pa zil gyis non pas 'dod chags rang mtshan pa las log pa gang zhig /
NK118(se)002:16335: dgos pa nyon mongs pa'i bag chags mi gsog gi
NK118(se)002:16336: steng du bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs
NK118(se)002:16338: so byang gi tshul khrims dang sdom pa thams cad
NK118(se)002:16339: phun sum tshogs pas yon tan yar ldan du 'gyur
NK118(se)002:16340: ba'i phyir te / de nyid las /
NK118(se)002:16341: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK118(se)002:16342: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyad kyang //
NK118(se)002:16343: byas la mi gsog tshogs 'gyur te //
NK118(se)002:16344: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK118(se)002:16346: lnga pa sdom pa gsum gnad kyis mi 'gal ba ni /
NK118(se)002:16347: 'du shes gsum gyis 'khrig na rnal 'byor de //
NK118(se)002:16348: yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug ma tshang bas //
NK118(se)002:16349: rmi lam ji bzhin gnad kyis 'gal mi srid //
NK118(se)002:16352: sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong mar 'dus pa mi 'thad de /
NK118(se)002:16354: so thar gyi pham pa bzhi cha bcas spong ba dang /
NK118(se)002:16355: byang sdom gyis sems can la 'tshe ba cha bcas
NK118(se)002:16356: las ldog nas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'i ldog cha
NK118(se)002:16357: gnyis po de / 'dir sngags sdom gyi spyad par
NK118(se)002:16358: bya ba'i dam tshig lnga dang dngos su 'gal bar
NK118(se)002:16360: de ltar 'og ma dang rnam pa 'gal ba ltar
NK118(se)002:16361: snang yang lta ba rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin goms
NK118(se)002:16362: pa dang thabs mkhas kyi spyod pas zin pa'i gnad
NK118(se)002:16363: kyis mi 'gal bar 'og ma'i sdom pa yar ldan
NK118(se)002:16365: rgyu mtshan nyan thos kyi dge slong la pham pa
NK118(se)002:16366: bzhi 'chab bcas byung na so thar gyi sdom pa
NK118(se)002:16369: bdag dang yul lha yab yum du gsal ba lha'i 'du shes dang /
NK118(se)002:16370: mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara shes pa sngags kyi 'du shes kyis gzhi'i yan lag ma tshang /
NK118(se)002:16371: thabs 'dis bde ba chen po'i ye shes bsgrub par
NK118(se)002:16372: bya'o snyam pa chos kyi 'du shes kyis bsam pa'i
NK118(se)002:16374: byed pa sdom pa'i thabs mkhas kyi spyod pas zin
NK118(se)002:16375: cing chags pa'i ro ye shes su gsal bas sbyor
NK118(se)002:16376: ba dang mthar thug gi yan lag ma tshang ba'i
NK118(se)002:16377: phyir dang / chos thams cad sems nyid kyi rang
NK118(se)002:16378: snang du shes pas rmi lam du spyad pa ltar
NK118(se)002:16379: nyes pas mi gos shing 'dzag med kyi ye shes
NK118(se)002:16380: 'grub pa sogs kyi don du 'gyur bas dgag dgos
NK118(se)002:16381: gnad gcig pa'i phyir mi 'gal te /
NK118(se)002:16383: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK118(se)002:16384: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK118(se)002:16385: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK118(se)002:16386: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK118(se)002:16388: de la kha cig na re /
NK118(se)002:16390: mi tshangs spyod la ni dngos po gtso bas lpags
NK118(se)002:16391: rim las 'das pa'i phyir pham pa byung ngo zhe
NK118(se)002:16392: na / de ni thabs la mi mkhas shing shes rab med pa'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16393: yang dag par na sngags med pa'i dug gis 'chi
NK118(se)002:16394: yang sngags dang ldan pa la nyes pa med pa
NK118(se)002:16395: bzhin du thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa
NK118(se)002:16397: 'di mkha' gsang sngags kyi 'du shes kyis byin gyis
NK118(se)002:16398: brlabs pas 'da' bya'i dngos po ma grub pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:16399: dang / sgyu ma'i skyes bus mig yor du snang
NK118(se)002:16400: ba'i bud med la sbyor ba brtsams pa bzhin bdag
NK118(se)002:16401: gzhan yang ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16402: de ltar yang de nyid las /
NK118(se)002:16403: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK118(se)002:16404: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK118(se)002:16405: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK118(se)002:16406: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK118(se)002:16408: ye shes rgyas pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK118(se)002:16409: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mkhan po dag /
NK118(se)002:16410: rang gis sprul pa'i sgyu ma la //
NK118(se)002:16411: dge dang mi dge 'du byed pa //
NK118(se)002:16412: nyes pa gang gis mi gos ltar //
NK118(se)002:16413: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par spyod //
NK118(se)002:16415: der ma zad dge slong ma ser skya bzang mo
NK118(se)002:16416: la rgyal po ma skyes dgras 'dod pa lan mang
NK118(se)002:16417: du spyad kyang dge slong ma la 'dod chags kyi
NK118(se)002:16419: las des pham pa bskyed mi nus par nyan thos
NK118(se)002:16420: kyi theg par yang gsungs na theg chen du lta
NK118(se)002:16422: de bzhin du srog gcod la'ang /
NK118(se)002:16423: bsgral bya mig yor lta bur shes pas gzhi ma tshang /
NK118(se)002:16424: de'i sdug bsngal bral 'dod kyi snying rjes bslangs pas bsam pa ma tshang /
NK118(se)002:16425: gsod par byed pa po bdag sgyu ma'i skyes bu
NK118(se)002:16426: lta bus bsad bya mig yor ltar srog dang skyes
NK118(se)002:16427: bur 'dzin pa med pas de bcad pa'ang med pa'i
NK118(se)002:16429: rjes mnar sems kyi yi rang med pas mthar thug ma tshang ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16430: nyes pas mi gos shing bsgral bya'i las ngan rgyun
NK118(se)002:16431: gcod pa'i thabs mkhas kyis tshogs rdzogs par 'gyur bas
NK118(se)002:16432: dgag dgos gnad gcig pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16434: yod med dbu ma mi dmigs shing //
NK118(se)002:16435: sgyu ma mig yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK118(se)002:16436: srog med srog kyang bcad du med //
NK118(se)002:16437: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK118(se)002:16439: ma byin par len pa la'ang /
NK118(se)002:16440: bdag gzhan gnyis med du rtogs te rang snang gi
NK118(se)002:16441: rdzas 'phrul dag'i longs spyod ltar len pas don la
NK118(se)002:16442: blangs pa med pa'i phyir gzhi bsam sbyor ba ma
NK118(se)002:16443: tshang la / thob bya thob byed kyi zhen pa
NK118(se)002:16444: las grol bas mthar thug thob blo yang ma grub
NK118(se)002:16445: pa'i phyir dgag dgos gnad gcig pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16447: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK118(se)002:16448: 'phrul dag'i tshul te tha dad min //
NK118(se)002:16449: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:16450: blangs med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK118(se)002:16452: rdzun smra ba'i tshe yang chos thams cad bden par ma grub pas /
NK118(se)002:16453: de la ltos pa'i rdzun pa'ang ma grub pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:16454: na gzhi pha rol po la rdzun pa'i 'du shes
NK118(se)002:16455: kyis smras shing des go ba'ang ma dmigs pa'i phyir
NK118(se)002:16456: / smras kyang nyes pas mi gos shing ji ltar
NK118(se)002:16457: phan pa ltar smras pas dgag dgos gnad gcig pa
NK118(se)002:16459: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK118(se)002:16460: ming dang tshig tu btags pa rdzun //
NK118(se)002:16461: rdzun nyid la ni rdzun spyod pas //
NK118(se)002:16462: rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK118(se)002:16465: de thams cad kyi skabs su /
NK118(se)002:16466: bdag nyid sdom ldan yin pa /
NK118(se)002:16467: yul de yin la yin par ma 'khrul ba /
NK118(se)002:16468: sbyor ba brtsams shing mthar thug grub pa zhig dgos pa las /
NK118(se)002:16469: 'dir rtogs goms kyi thabs kyis thams cad lhar shes
NK118(se)002:16470: pa'i phyir nyan thos kyi sdom pa dang 'gal ba
NK118(se)002:16471: med do // de bzhin du gzhan la phan 'dod
NK118(se)002:16472: kyi snying rje dang thabs khyad par can gyis zin
NK118(se)002:16473: pas byang sdom dang yang 'gal ba med de /
NK118(se)002:16474: de gnyis dang ldan pa ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams la'ang gnang ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16475: nyes pas mi gos kyi steng du phan yon tshad
NK118(se)002:16476: med pa thob pas dgag dgos gnad gcig pa yin
NK118(se)002:16478: gang dag sems can don 'gyur ba'i //
NK118(se)002:16479: thabs de rgyal sras bslab pa'i mchog /
NK118(se)002:16480: sprin las char chen babs pa yis //
NK118(se)002:16481: lo tog phun sum tshogs par byed //
NK118(se)002:16483: mdor na sdom pa gsum ka la skyon dang nyes pa bskyed na 'gog cing /
NK118(se)002:16484: yon tan dang dge ba bskyed na bya bar gnang ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16485: don gcig pas gnad kyis mi 'gal ba yin no //
NK118(se)002:16486: drug pa dus skabs kyis gtso bor gang 'gyur spyad pa ni /
NK118(se)002:16487: sdig to mi dge'i phyogs dang tshogs pa'i gseb //
NK118(se)002:16488: 'og ma gtsor byed 'dod pas dben pa dang //
NK118(se)002:16489: spyod pa'i dus dang dben par gsang sngags spyad //
NK118(se)002:16490: nang ma 'dom na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bsrung //
NK118(se)002:16491: 'dom na dgag dgos brtsi zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK118(se)002:16492: las dang po dang rnal 'byor grub thob dang //
NK118(se)002:16493: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod pa gang yin pa //
NK118(se)002:16494: dus tshod 'brel bar dgos zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK118(se)002:16496: sdig to mi dge ba'i phyogs rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:16497: tshogs pa'i gseb tu sdom pa 'og ma nyan thos kyi lugs bzhin du gtso bor bsrung dgos te /
NK118(se)002:16499: phyi ru nyan thos spyod pa skyong //
NK118(se)002:16500: nang du 'dus pa'i don la dga' //
NK118(se)002:16502: sangs rgyas gnyis pa slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i zhal nas /
NK118(se)002:16503: phyi ltar lag len mdo sde'i lugs su spyad //
NK118(se)002:16504: rgyu 'bras spang blang zhib pa'i dgos pa yod //
NK118(se)002:16506: byang sa'i tshul khrims le'ura yang /
NK118(se)002:16507: 'dul ba'i nang khrims bsrung na nyes pa med do //
NK118(se)002:16508: zhes yang yang gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16509: yang theg pa chen por gzhan don du 'byung nges
NK118(se)002:16510: na gnang ba rang 'dod kyis dben pa'i ltung ba
NK118(se)002:16511: lus ngag gi bcas pa rnams dang /
NK118(se)002:16512: gsang spyod kyi dus dang dben pa'i gnas su gsang sngags gtso bor bsrung ste /
NK118(se)002:16513: de'i tshe 'og ma nyams pa snyam byed kyang de ni ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16515: thugs rje mnga' bas ring gzigs pas //
NK118(se)002:16516: bkag pa rnams kyang de la gnang //
NK118(se)002:16519: rnam shes ngan pas brten byas na //
NK118(se)002:16521: de nyid mkhas pas brten byas na //
NK118(se)002:16522: 'dod pas thar pa rab tu sgrub //
NK118(se)002:16524: rang lhar sbyong ba'i bdag nyid kyis //
NK118(se)002:16525: 'gro ba'i don byed brtson ldan pas //
NK118(se)002:16530: nang ltar gsang sngags thun mong lugs su spyad //
NK118(se)002:16531: bskyed rdzogs don dang 'brel ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK118(se)002:16532: gsang bar gsang chen a ti'i lugs su spyad //
NK118(se)002:16533: tshe gcig 'od skur grol ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK118(se)002:16536: 'jig rten ma dad gyur pa'i cha //
NK118(se)002:16537: mthong dang dris te spang bar bya //
NK118(se)002:16538: zhes pas gzhan ma dad par 'gyur ba'i cha sdom
NK118(se)002:16539: pa gsum ka mthun pa rnams 'bad pas bsrung zhing
NK118(se)002:16540: / gal te gzhan 'jug pa'i rgyur 'gyur na theg
NK118(se)002:16541: pa chen po las gnang bas dgag dgos shes par
NK118(se)002:16542: / bya'o // de dag kyang rab dbye'i theg chen so thar gyi skabs su /
NK118(se)002:16543: 'di la sdig to mi dge'i phyogs //
NK118(se)002:16544: phal cher nyan thos lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK118(se)002:16546: byang chub sems dpa'i lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK118(se)002:16547: 'jig rten ma dad gyur pa'i cha //
NK118(se)002:16548: gnyis ka mthun rnams 'bad pas bsrung //
NK118(se)002:16550: theg chen so sor thar la gnang //
NK118(se)002:16552: tshogs dben gang yin kyang rung ste /
NK118(se)002:16553: sdom pa gsum gyi ltung ba nang ma 'dom pa'i
NK118(se)002:16554: dus su ni rang rang so so'i lugs ltar ma
NK118(se)002:16555: 'dres yongs rdzogs su bsrung bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:16556: gal te 'dom na dgag dgos brtsi ste /
NK118(se)002:16557: gang gi lugs la'ang nyes pa bskyed pa'i cha thams cad dgag bya yin pas dgog cing /
NK118(se)002:16558: yon tan nam dge ba'i cha bskyed na bslabs pa'i dgos pa yin pas spyad par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:16559: gnang bkag dang spyir btang dmigs bsal gyi gnad rnams ma 'dres par shes pa gal che'o //
NK118(se)002:16560: de yang gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pas spyod pa
NK118(se)002:16561: kha na ma tho ba med cing dus tshod dang
NK118(se)002:16562: 'brel bar sbyong dgos pas gnas skabs so so'i blang
NK118(se)002:16563: dor kyang shes par bya ste /
NK118(se)002:16564: las dang po pas so thar gyi dgag bya gtso bor bsrung zhing /
NK118(se)002:16565: brtan pa thob nas bzung blo na 'phar ba'i rim
NK118(se)002:16566: pa ltar gong ma gong ma'i dgos pa gtso bor
NK118(se)002:16567: sgrub ste / 'di ltar rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16569: thams cad mkhyeen pa'i gnas skabs kyi spyod pa rnams ma 'dres par blang dor bya'o //
NK118(se)002:16570: de ltar yang dus 'khor 'grel chen las /
NK118(se)002:16571: de'i phyir las dang po pas rnal 'byor pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:16572: rnal 'byor pas grub pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:16573: grub pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK118(se)002:16575: gsum pa sdom gsum nyams su len tshul bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo nas 'jug bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:16576: yon tan gzhi rten so thar gang nus steng //
NK118(se)002:16577: byang chub sems bskyed sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK118(se)002:16578: smin byed dbang thob sdom gsum mig ltar bsrung //
NK118(se)002:16579: gdan gsum lha ru shes pa'i bskyed rim dang //
NK118(se)002:16580: mtshan bcas mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim sgom //
NK118(se)002:16581: nye rgyu'i spyod pas rim bzhin mtshams sbyar na //
NK118(se)002:16582: 'adi'am 'chi kha dang ni bar do du //
NK118(se)002:16583: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du rdzogs 'tshang rgya //
NK118(se)002:16585: rgyal ba'i gsung rab kyi don thams cad sdom pa gsum gyi nyams len du 'du ste /
NK118(se)002:16586: 'di ltar nyan thos dang thun mong ba'i lam 'khor
NK118(se)002:16587: ba la skyo shas dang nges 'byung gis kun nas
NK118(se)002:16588: bslangs te / spong ba bzhi'am bdun ldan gyi so
NK118(se)002:16589: so thar pa rigs brgyad gang nus blangs la lus
NK118(se)002:16590: ngag gi nyes spyod las ldog par bya /
NK118(se)002:16591: de'i steng du mkha' khyab kyi sems can thams cad gdod nas rnam par dag kyang /
NK118(se)002:16592: de ltar ma rtogs pas sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang
NK118(se)002:16593: 'bras bur spyod pa rnams la bcos min gyi byams
NK118(se)002:16594: pa dang snying rjes kun nas bslangs te /
NK118(se)002:16595: gzhan don du smon pa dang 'jug pa'i bdag nyid
NK118(se)002:16596: can gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas tshul
NK118(se)002:16597: khrims gsum la bslab par bya /
NK118(se)002:16598: de ltar so byang gnyis kyis rgyud sbyangs rjes rgyu
NK118(se)002:16599: rten gyi dkyil 'khor bzhin zhugs nas sku bzhi'i rten
NK118(se)002:16600: 'brel bsgrig phyir dbang bzhi bskur bas sdom pa gsum
NK118(se)002:16602: sdom pa rang rang gi bslab bya rnams dgag dgos
NK118(se)002:16603: kyi gnad shes pa'i sgo nas mig gi 'bras bu
NK118(se)002:16604: ltar gces spras kyis bsrung bar bya zhing /
NK118(se)002:16605: smin zin grol bar bya ba'i phyir lam rim pa gnyis la 'jug ste /
NK118(se)002:16606: de yang rten gyi dkyil 'khor bzhi ka la de bzhin gshegs pa dang gshegs ma /
NK118(se)002:16608: khro bo dang khro mo ste gdan gsum tshang bar
NK118(se)002:16609: shes pas sbyang gzhi sbyong byed ngo 'phrod pa'i sgo
NK118(se)002:16610: nas ma dag pa'i snang ba dbyings su sbyong ba'i
NK118(se)002:16611: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo sgom pa bskyed rim dang
NK118(se)002:16612: / rdzogs rim mtshan bcas rang byin gyis brlab pa'i
NK118(se)002:16613: rim pa rtsa rlung thig le la gnad du bsnun
NK118(se)002:16614: / pa'i thabs dang / de dag gi rgyas gdab
NK118(se)002:16615: tu gyur pa mtshan med rang byung gi ye shes
NK118(se)002:16616: sems nyid 'od gsal du ngo sprod pa de kho
NK118(se)002:16617: na nyid kyi rdzogs rim rnams legs par bsgom zhing
NK118(se)002:16618: / pa'i thabs dang / / nye rgyu'i spyod pa
NK118(se)002:16619: spros bcas spros med shin tu spros med gsum spyad
NK118(se)002:16620: pas dbang po rab tshe 'dir zung 'jug gi sku
NK118(se)002:16621: / pa'i thabs dang / / 'grub / 'bring 'chi kha'i 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi skur ldang /
NK118(se)002:16622: tha ma bar do nas bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK118(se)002:16623: mngon par dga' ba la sogs pa rang bzhin sprul
NK118(se)002:16624: sku'i zhing bgrod de rdo rje mi bskyod pa la
NK118(se)002:16625: sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rang rigs kyi 'khor
NK118(se)002:16626: dang bcas pa rnams rim pa ji lta ba bzhin
NK118(se)002:16629: byang chub tu lung bstan pa dang /
NK118(se)002:16630: dbugs dbyung ba thob nas gdod ma'i dbyings su rdzogs sangs rgyas te /
NK118(se)002:16631: don gnyis mthar phyin par 'gyur ro //
NK118(se)002:16632: de ltar yang sgyu 'phrul mngon byang las /
NK118(se)002:16633: dag pa sa yi dbang nyid phyir //
NK118(se)002:16634: ston pa lnga dag chos rab lnga //
NK118(se)002:16635: ye shes lnga yongs rdzogs pa las //
NK118(se)002:16636: rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK118(se)002:16638: de ltar bshad nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK118(se)002:16639: sdom gsum spyir bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste lnga pa'o //
NK118(se)002:16641: bstan bcos 'di la le'u lnga las /
NK118(se)002:16642: 'dis sdom pa gsum po spyir gang zag gcig gi
NK118(se)002:16643: rgyud la 'gal med du nyams su len tshul gyi
NK118(se)002:16644: mtha' dpyad nas bshad pa'i rim par phye ba ste
NK118(se)002:16647: gzhan gnod spong dang gzhan phan sgrub pa'i thabs //
NK118(se)002:16648: so byang rnam gnyis sngags kyi sdom rdzas su //
NK118(se)002:16649: gnas gyur rang ldog ma 'dres ngo bo gcig /
NK118(se)002:16650: gnang bkag 'gal med nyams su len pa'i tshul //
NK118(se)002:16651: legs par bkra ba'i ngag tshig legs bshad las //
NK118(se)002:16652: thob pa'i dge tshogs dbang thob byang sems dang //
NK118(se)002:16653: lhan cig chos la spyod pas lhan skyes kyi //
NK118(se)002:16654: bde chen dpal mnga' bde ldan mgon gyur cig ///
NK118(se)002:16655: gsum pa bshad pa rdzogs pa'i bya ba la bzhi ste /
NK118(se)002:16656: rtsom pa'i rgyu brtse ba'i snying rje /
NK118(se)002:16659: des thob dge ba bsngo ba'o //
NK118(se)002:16661: ding sang ma sbyangs mu cor smra ba brgyas //
NK118(se)002:16662: rang gi ye shes rdul tsam ma rtogs par //
NK118(se)002:16663: rang bzo'i cho gas rmongs rnams tshim pa'i dus //
NK118(se)002:16664: skyabs de bsam kyin snying nas mchi ma bku //
NK118(se)002:16666: sngon gyi mkhas grub rnams ni gshegs /
NK118(se)002:16667: de dag gi gzhung lugs rnams kyang rim gyis nub
NK118(se)002:16668: pas snyigs ma las kyang snyigs mar gyur pa ding
NK118(se)002:16669: sang gi dus bstan pa nyams smad par gyur pa
NK118(se)002:16670: la thugs skyo ba'i shugs kyis gdul bya la snying
NK118(se)002:16671: rje'i kun slong g.yos pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16673: da lta'i dus 'dir rang gis gzhung lugs rnams la
NK118(se)002:16674: thos bsam gyi sgo nas legs par ma sbyangs shing
