NK118(se)002:16675: / sgom pa nyams len gyi sgo nas rang gi
NK118(se)002:16676: ye shes 'dir bstan gyi cha tsam yang ma rtogs
NK118(se)002:16677: par blun po mkhas rlom gyi mngon pa'i nga rgyal
NK118(se)002:16678: can dag gzhan la mu cor gyi kha zer ba
NK118(se)002:16679: / dang / zog po grub rlom can mang pos
NK118(se)002:16680: rang bzo'i ngan rtog gis bslad pa'i cho gas rmongs
NK118(se)002:16681: pa rnams mgo bskor ba la skyabs su brten pa'i
NK118(se)002:16683: bsam kyin snying nas mya ngan gyi mchi ma bku ba'i gnas su gyur pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16685: mdo sngags lam rnams mu med 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:16686: tshangs la ma nor lam 'di rgyal bas gsungs //
NK118(se)002:16687: gangs can 'di na de dag phyogs rer 'dzin //
NK118(se)002:16688: gcig tu sems kyang sdom gsum ming tsam lus //
NK118(se)002:16690: rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK118(se)002:16691: mtha' yas mu med pa'i gdul bya'i 'gro ba rnams 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16692: so so'i blo'i rim pa ltar mdo sngags kyi gzhung
NK118(se)002:16693: lam dpag tu med pa zhig gsungs pa thams cad
NK118(se)002:16694: kyang / gang zag gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i thabs tshang
NK118(se)002:16695: la ma nor ba'i rnam dag legs pa'i lam 'dir
NK118(se)002:16696: kyang / 'du mod / 'on kyang mdo sngags kyi
NK118(se)002:16697: gzhung lugs so so'i dgongs don zab cing barlinga bas
NK118(se)002:16698: gcig tu sdud ma shes te /
NK118(se)002:16699: de'i phyir gangs can 'di na 'dul ba dang gsang
NK118(se)002:16700: sngags dag 'gal lo zhes g.yag zhar gyi r+ts+wa ltar
NK118(se)002:16702: gal te gcig tu bsdu bar sems pa rnams kyis
NK118(se)002:16703: kyang sdom pa gsum so so'i 'bogs chog gi lag
NK118(se)002:16704: len ltar snang tsam las gnang bkag gi bslab bya
NK118(se)002:16705: spyir btang dmigs bsal gyi gnas rnams lung rigs man
NK118(se)002:16706: ngag dang mi 'gal bar 'chad mi shes pas ming
NK118(se)002:16707: tsam du lus par zad do //
NK118(se)002:16709: 'di ni mkhas grub du ma'i legs bshad las //
NK118(se)002:16710: sgrims po'i blo yis phyogs gcig dag tu bkod //
NK118(se)002:16711: de phyir nongs pa'i dri ma med snyam rlom //
NK118(se)002:16713: tshul de dag mthong nas bstan bcos 'di ni phyogs
NK118(se)002:16714: 'dzin gyi blo dang rang bzo spangs te mdo rgyud
NK118(se)002:16715: kyi don ji lta ba bzhin du gtan la 'bebs
NK118(se)002:16716: par byed pa mkhas grub du ma'i legs bshad las
NK118(se)002:16717: ji skad bstan pa rnams la sgrims po'i blos brtags
NK118(se)002:16718: shing dpyad nas / mdo rgyud kyi dgongs don rnams
NK118(se)002:16719: lung rigs man ngag dang mi 'gal bar phyogs gcig
NK118(se)002:16720: tu bsdus te bkod pa yin la /
NK118(se)002:16721: de yang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa phyin ci ma log
NK118(se)002:16722: par legs par bshad pa'i phyir ma rtogs pa dang
NK118(se)002:16723: log rtog gis nongs pa'i dri ma med snyam du
NK118(se)002:16724: rlom mo zhes gsung gsang mthon pos 'doms shing bzod
NK118(se)002:16725: par gsol ba ma mdzad do //
NK118(se)002:16727: dge des kun bzang go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK118(se)002:16729: bstan bcos 'di brtsams pa las byung ba'i dge ba mchog tu gyur pa des /
NK118(se)002:16730: mkha' khyab kyi 'gro ba thams cad 'bad rtsol med
NK118(se)002:16731: par de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang
NK118(se)002:16732: ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i bdag nyid dpal kun
NK118(se)002:16733: tu bzang po'i go 'phang myur du thob par shog
NK118(se)002:16734: cig pa'o // gsum pa bstan bcos ji ltar brtsams pa'i mdzad byang ni /
NK118(se)002:16735: ces sdom gsum rnam nges tshig gis rim par phye
NK118(se)002:16736: ba 'di gangs ri'i phreng bas bskor ba'i yul ljongs
NK118(se)002:16737: lho phyogs kyi rgyud du byung ba'i nges par 'byung
NK118(se)002:16738: ba'i bsam pa can mnga' ris kyi pan+di ta pad+ma
NK118(se)002:16739: dbang gi rgyal pos bkod pa /
NK118(se)002:16740: phyogs dus thams cad du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK118(se)002:16741: po'i bstan pa la bya ba byed nus par gyur
NK118(se)002:16743: sdom pa gsum gyi don sgro skur dang bral bar
NK118(se)002:16744: gtan la phab pas na rnam par nges pa ste
NK118(se)002:16746: de yang tshig ni mkhan po thu mis /
NK118(se)002:16747: yi ge'i khongs nas ming byung ste //
NK118(se)002:16748: ming gi khongs nas tshig byung la //
NK118(se)002:16749: tshig gis don rnams ston byed pa //
NK118(se)002:16750: zhes pa ltar yi ge 'dus pa las ming /
NK118(se)002:16752: de 'dus pa las tshigs su bcad pa 'dus pa'i
NK118(se)002:16753: gzhung tshogs le'u rim par phye ba lnga'i bdag nyid
NK118(se)002:16755: de mdzad pa po su zhig ce na /
NK118(se)002:16756: gangs ri'i phreng bas bskor ba bod kyi yul las
NK118(se)002:16757: bye brag lho phyogs kyi rgyud mnga' ris glo bo
NK118(se)002:16759: yon tan gyi khyad par shes rab dang snying rjes
NK118(se)002:16760: srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba bla
NK118(se)002:16761: na med pa'i byang chub don gnyer gyi bsam pas
NK118(se)002:16762: kun nas bslangs te sbyor ba gzhan don sgrub pa'i
NK118(se)002:16763: thabs la mkhas pa can rig pa'i gnas lnga thugs
NK118(se)002:16765: mtshan brjod par dka' ba pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje
NK118(se)002:16766: grags pa rgyal mtshan dpal bzang pos gsung rab dgongs
NK118(se)002:16767: 'grel dang bcas pa'i don ji lta ba bzhin du
NK118(se)002:16768: rtsom par mdzad pas na thar 'dod kyi skyes bu
NK118(se)002:16769: rnams kyi spyi bos blang bar 'os te /
NK118(se)002:16771: gang zhig rgyal ba ston pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK118(se)002:16772: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK118(se)002:16773: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK118(se)002:16774: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK118(se)002:16776: de ltar bstan bcos bkod pa'i dge ba ci yod
NK118(se)002:16777: pa des phyogs bcu dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK118(se)002:16778: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du theg pa kun
NK118(se)002:16779: gyi rtse mor son pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK118(se)002:16780: po a ti yo ga'i bstan pa la bshad sgrub
NK118(se)002:16781: kyi bya ba rlabs po che byed nus par gyur
NK118(se)002:16782: cig ces smon lam du mdzad pa ni bsngo ba
NK118(se)002:16783: rnams kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK118(se)002:16784: smon lam thams cad kyang dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin par bsngosa na 'du bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK118(se)002:16786: rgyal ba kun gyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK118(se)002:16787: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK118(se)002:16788: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyong ba yang //
NK118(se)002:16789: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par shog /
NK118(se)002:16790: ces gsungs pa dang tshul mthun pa yin no //
NK118(se)002:16791: de ltar legs bshad 'dul ba'i rtsa ba brtan //
NK118(se)002:16792: gzhan phan byang sems ngo mtshar lo 'dab rgyas //
NK118(se)002:16793: gsang chen smin grol 'bras bus yongs gang ba'i //
NK118(se)002:16794: rnam 'grel dpag bsam snye ma 'di long zhig /
NK118(se)002:16795: mtshungs med rnam dpyod stobs rgyas rta bdun gyis //
NK118(se)002:16796: drangs pa'i lung rig shing rta la chibs nas //
NK118(se)002:16797: legs bshad 'od stong spro bzhin 'dir shar gyis //
NK118(se)002:16798: rgyal bstan pad+mo'i ge sar rgod min nam //
NK118(se)002:16799: deng bdag 'byung lus rga bas dam bcings kyang //
NK118(se)002:16800: sems kyi khye'u chung lang tsho ma nyams pas //
NK118(se)002:16801: rnam dpyod me long ngos la tshig don gzugs //
NK118(se)002:16802: 'phos pas za 'og thags la ngal bso sbyin //
NK118(se)002:16803: skye bar goms pa'i shes rab mthu chung zhing //
NK118(se)002:16804: dad brtson snying stobs goms shugs dman gyur kyang //
NK118(se)002:16805: yongs 'dzin dam pa'i thugs rje'i phyag bzang gis //
NK118(se)002:16806: drangs pas legs bshad smra ba'i spobs pa thob //
NK118(se)002:16807: gang bshad 'di ni mdo rgyud snying po'i don //
NK118(se)002:16808: thar 'dod skal ldan skye bo 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK118(se)002:16809: blang dor gsal bar byed pa'i sgron me ste //
NK118(se)002:16810: 'dod ster dpag bsam snye ma 'di yin no //
NK118(se)002:16811: ji ltar gting mtha' gzhal daka'i chu gter che //
NK118(se)002:16812: nyam chung ri bong rkyal gyis chod min ltar //
NK118(se)002:16813: gzhung don rtogs dka' bdag blo mthu zhan phyir //
NK118(se)002:16814: nongs par gyur gang dam pa rnams la bshags //
NK118(se)002:16815: de ltar bshad las dge ba gang thob des //
NK118(se)002:16816: bdag gzhan srid zhi'i chu gter las sgrol nas //
NK118(se)002:16817: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK118(se)002:16818: thar mchog kun bzang go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK118(se)002:16819: lung rig man ngag rjes 'gro'i rnam bshad 'di //
NK118(se)002:16820: dbang phyug ral pa'i rgyan gyur dkyil 'khor ltar //
NK118(se)002:16821: chos sgra'i snang bas phyogs kun yongs khyab ste //
NK118(se)002:16822: 'gro kun gdung sel phan bde'i dpal 'bar shog /
NK118(se)002:16823: gnas skabs su yang 'jig rten khams ma lus //
NK118(se)002:16824: lha yul ji bzhin dga' skyid bde bas 'tsho //
NK118(se)002:16825: khyad par bstan 'dzin skyes bus yongs gang nas //
NK118(se)002:16826: bstan pa dri med dar zhing rgyas pa shog /
NK118(se)002:16827: bdag kyang tshe rabs kun tu snga 'gyur gyi //
NK118(se)002:16828: bshad sgrub nyi zla'i snang ba rab bzung nas //
NK118(se)002:16829: thub bstan gling bzhi'i khyon 'dir rtag 'char bas //
NK118(se)002:16830: phan bde'i pad+mo 'dab brgya 'byed par shog /
NK118(se)002:16831: ces sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i bstan bcos kyi
NK118(se)002:16832: 'grel pa legs bshad ngo mtshar dpag bsam gyi snye
NK118(se)002:16834: sngar ming don mthun pa'i grogs mchog hor bla ma
NK118(se)002:16835: dge slong bstan 'dzin 'gyur med kyis bskul nas rang
NK118(se)002:16836: lo nyi shu rtsa bdun pa lcags pho spre'u'i lo
NK118(se)002:16837: le'u gnyis pa so thar gyi skabs las dge slong
NK118(se)002:16838: pha'i sde lnga yan chad 'bru 'grel du brtsams pa
NK118(se)002:16839: zhig yod na'ang / de dus blo gros ma smin
NK118(se)002:16840: pas dmar nag spel ba tsam gyi yi ge la
NK118(se)002:16841: don med par mthong nas slar 'phro'i rtsom 'dun bskyungs
NK118(se)002:16842: zhig yod na'ang / pa las / phyis mdo sngags
NK118(se)002:16843: kyi gzhung lugs smra ba rab 'byams pa phrin las
NK118(se)002:16844: rab 'phel gyis sdom gsum la bstan bcos rab rang
NK118(se)002:16845: gzhung ngam gzhan 'grel gang rigs su byas pa dang
NK118(se)002:16846: tha na'ang gnas 'gyur tsam la rang lugs kyi grub
NK118(se)002:16847: matha'i gnad 'khrol ba zhig cis kyang brtsam dgos zhes
NK118(se)002:16848: ring mo nas yang yang bskul ba dang /
NK118(se)002:16849: khyad par dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi
NK118(se)002:16850: gzugs rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag bka'
NK118(se)002:16851: drin mnyam med rje bla ma dam pa gter chen
NK118(se)002:16852: chos kyi rgyal po'i bka' lung lci bas sdom gsum
NK118(se)002:16853: rnam nges kyi bstan bcos legs bshad rmad du byung
NK118(se)002:16854: ba 'di nyid kyi zhabs tog la dmigs shing rang
NK118(se)002:16855: gi blo gros kyang goms par bya ba'i phyir 'grel
NK118(se)002:16856: pa mtha' chod pa zhig 'phral du rtsom par gyis
NK118(se)002:16857: zhes stsal ba gus pa'i gtsug gis mchod de rtsom
NK118(se)002:16859: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i mnga' bdag mkhyen brtse nus pa'i
NK118(se)002:16860: dbang phyug chen po rdo rje brag rig 'dzin mchog
NK118(se)002:16861: gi sprul pa'i sku'i zhal snga nas kyang sdom gsum
NK118(se)002:16862: la 'grel pa byas pa ni snga 'gyur bstan pa'i
NK118(se)002:16863: gso sman du 'gyur ro zhes dbugs dbyung ba'i bka'
NK118(se)002:16864: stsal thob pas kyang yid spro bar gyur cing /
NK118(se)002:16865: sgra snyan sdeb sbyor rtsis skar nag la blo byang
NK118(se)002:16866: ba'i rig byed pa dge slong o t+y+aan dpal 'byor
NK118(se)002:16867: gyis kyang rtsom gdan gyi bri gzhi'i rkyen sbyar ba
NK118(se)002:16869: gnyos kyi dge slong rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais rang lo
NK118(se)002:16870: lnga bcu nga lnga pa'i thog tu son pa kun
NK118(se)002:16871: 'dzin gyi lo dbo zla ba'i tshes dgu res gza'
NK118(se)002:16872: pa wa sangs rgyu skar nabs so dang rtse ba'i
NK118(se)002:16873: phyi dro seng ge'i dus sbyor la yon tan rin
NK118(se)002:16874: po che'i 'byung gnas o t+y+aan smin grol gling gi
NK118(se)002:16875: gtsug lag khang chen por sbyar ba'o //
NK118(se)002:16876: 'dis kyang bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa
NK118(se)002:16877: rgya che rgyun mi chad pa 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur
NK118(se)002:16879: zla med ston pa rdzogs sangs rgyas de yis //
NK118(se)002:16880: rang gis brnyes pa'i chos kyi rgyal thabs la //
NK118(se)002:16881: 'god phyir gdul bya'i skal ba dang 'tshams par //
NK118(se)002:16882: theg gsum chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong bstan //
NK118(se)002:16883: srid mtsho nyam nga'i grong las ring brgal nas //
NK118(se)002:16884: rnam grol rin chen len pa gru yi rten //
NK118(se)002:16885: so thar byang sems rig 'dzin sdom pa yi //
NK118(se)002:16886: mthun pa'i rlung gis bskul ba nyid la rag /
NK118(se)002:16887: dang po blang yul mkhan slob dge 'dun las //
NK118(se)002:16888: srog 'tsho'i bar du gzhan gnod las ldog pa //
NK118(se)002:16889: bdag don nyid du dgra bcom rjes slob tshul //
NK118(se)002:16890: 'bras bu myang 'das rnam gnyis thob phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16891: gnyis pa slob dpon nyid dam rten las kyang //
NK118(se)002:16892: byang chub bar du tshul khrims rnam pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:16893: gzhan don nyid du byang sems rjes slob tshul //
NK118(se)002:16894: 'bras bu sa bcu'i go 'phang thob phyir ro //
NK118(se)002:16895: gsum pa bla ma dkyil 'khor 'khor lo las //
NK118(se)002:16896: nam mkha' ji srid gnyis don ye shes kyi //
NK118(se)002:16897: 'khor lor rgyas 'debs sangs rgyas rjes slob tshul //
NK118(se)002:16898: 'bras bu rdo rje 'chang gi sa thob phyir //
NK118(se)002:16899: gang yang srid pa'i 'dod chags dug chen khams //
NK118(se)002:16900: spong sbyong lam du byed pa'i khyad par gyi //
NK118(se)002:16901: thabs las nyon mongs rang mtshan nyid spong bar //
NK118(se)002:16902: rnam dbyer med phyir don gyi dgongs pa mthun //
NK118(se)002:16903: de yang rgyud gcig nyid la sdom pa gsum //
NK118(se)002:16904: mtshan nyid drug ldan ngo bo gcig tu gnas //
NK118(se)002:16905: len cing rten dang phyir 'chos 'khrul med du //
NK118(se)002:16906: spyod pa sde snod gsung rab shes la rag /
NK118(se)002:16907: gang yang gzhung mang gis dub ngal bso'i skyes //
NK118(se)002:16908: tshig nyung don rgyas sdom gsum rnam nges kyi //
NK118(se)002:16909: legs bshad rin chen shes bya'i chu klung kun //
NK118(se)002:16910: 'khyil ba pan chen mkhyen pa'i mtsho las byung //
NK118(se)002:16911: de yi tshig don ma 'dres mtshar po'i gzugs //
NK118(se)002:16912: ji bzhin gsal byed 'grel pa nor bu yi //
NK118(se)002:16913: me long nyid dam legs bshad 'dod 'jo'i phyir //
NK118(se)002:16914: ngo mtshar dpag bsam snye mar lhun gyis grub //
NK118(se)002:16915: gang de mkhas btsun bzang pos mngon mtho'i bshes //
NK118(se)002:16916: chos dpal rgya mtsho'i rnam dpyod nor bu'i tog /
NK118(se)002:16917: mchod las chos char 'bebs byed rigs kyi gcung //
NK118(se)002:16918: kun dga' tshul khrims blo gsal 'dod 'jo'i dpyid //
NK118(se)002:16919: bri brkos byed po o rgyan dpal 'byor dang //
NK118(se)002:16920: o rgyan tshogs gnyis rdo rje chos bzang rnams //
NK118(se)002:16921: sor 'phrul gcig las 'bad med du ma ru //
NK118(se)002:16922: 'char ba'i ngo mtshar par gyis mtshon pa gang //
NK118(se)002:16923: sgrub byed do dam dge slong rab 'phel dang //
NK118(se)002:16924: rig byed 'tsho rkyen 'dod ster gnyer gyi las //
NK118(se)002:16925: 'dzin pa ngag dbang rab brtan gyis mtshon te //
NK118(se)002:16926: las byed kun gyis bsam sbyor mthun par zhugs //
NK118(se)002:16927: 'dis thob dge tshogs shing rta'i bgrod pa yis //
NK118(se)002:16928: sku gsum lang tsho 'bar ba'i nyi ma ni //
NK118(se)002:16929: phan bde'i snang ba 'gyed la 'drongs pa'i dpal //
NK118(se)002:16930: mtha' yas 'gro ba kun la gsal gyur cig /
NK118(se)002:16931: thar 'dod rnams kyis bslab par bya ba'i gnas ni
NK118(se)002:16932: sdom pa gsum gyi bslab bya la nan tan snying
NK118(se)002:16933: por bya ba las gzhan du med la /
NK118(se)002:16934: ji bzhin pa rang rgyud la 'byor ba yang sde snod kyi gsung rab rnams la ltos shing /
NK118(se)002:16935: de dag so sor bslab par mi nus pa rnams
NK118(se)002:16936: kyi don du sdom pa gsum gyi brjod bya gzhung
NK118(se)002:16937: tshan gcig gis ston pa'i bstan bcos sngon gyi mkhas
NK118(se)002:16938: pa rnams kyis mdzad pa 'ga' zhig 'dug mod /
NK118(se)002:16939: so byang gnyis la khas len mi 'dra ba'i khyad
NK118(se)002:16940: par re gnyis tsam las brjod bya'i don 'dra yang
NK118(se)002:16941: / sngags sdom gnas 'gyur dang bcas pa la sngags
NK118(se)002:16942: gsar rnying gi dbang las mi 'dra ba'i khyad par
NK118(se)002:16943: che ba la dgongs nas pan chen pad+ma dbang gi
NK118(se)002:16944: rgyal pos sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i gzhung legs
NK118(se)002:16945: bshad snying por dril ba mdzad kyang /
NK118(se)002:16946: 'grel pas ma bshad na rtogs dka' bas blo gsal
NK118(se)002:16947: don gnyer rnams la phan pa'i ched du gcung mkhan
NK118(se)002:16948: chen lo ts+aa ba nyid la rtsom par bskul ba
NK118(se)002:16949: bzhin rdo rje brag rig 'dzin mchog sprul dam pas
NK118(se)002:16950: kyang rang lugs 'dzin pa rnams la shin tu mkho
NK118(se)002:16951: ba yong 'dug pas rtsol ba bskyed pa legs so
NK118(se)002:16952: zhes pa'i gsung gis rkyen byas myur du grub pa'i
NK118(se)002:16953: brtsam gdan las thog mar phab pa'i glegs bam rtsom
NK118(se)002:16954: phud du phul bar shin tu dgyes pa'i dbugs dbyung
NK118(se)002:16955: dang / da cha par zhig byung na don gnyer
NK118(se)002:16956: mtha' dag gis 'grub sla zhing phan che ba 'dug
NK118(se)002:16957: pas rtsol ba bskyed cig par bka' phrin stsal ba
NK118(se)002:16958: las gcung kun dga' tshul khrims rgya mtshos 'bad rtsol
NK118(se)002:16959: chen pos par du bsgrubs pa'i snying stobs 'khur du
NK118(se)002:16960: bzung ba'i tshe par byang du rig pa 'dzin pa
NK118(se)002:16961: 'gyur med rdo rjes sa mo glang gi lo la
NK118(se)002:16962: bkod pa bde legs su gyur cig //
NK118(se)002:16963: mkhan slob chos gsum ring lugs che //
NK118(se)002:16965: 'gro rgyud mchog gsum snang ba dang //
